NK114(ye)001:1: // yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi 'grel pa bden
NK114(ye)001:2: gnyis gsal byed zla ba'i sgron me zhes bya ba'i
NK114(ye)001:4: gsum pa skyes bu chen po'i lam dngos byang chub
NK114(ye)001:5: kyi sems rnam pa gnyis bsgom pa bshad pa la
NK114(ye)001:6: gsum ste / lam gyi gzhung shing rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa ltar bshad pa /
NK114(ye)001:7: lam gyi sbas don gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa ltar bshad pa /
NK114(ye)001:8: lam gyi nye lam rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po ltar bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:9: dang po lam gyi gzhung shing rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa ltar bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK114(ye)001:10: blo sbyang ba tshad med bzhi'i le'u /
NK114(ye)001:11: dam bca' ba byang chub kyi sems yongs su bzung ba'i le'u /
NK114(ye)001:12: bslab bya la slob pa smon 'jug bslab bya'i le'u'o //
NK114(ye)001:14: theg chen lam gyi spyi sdom bshad pa /
NK114(ye)001:15: tshad med bzhi dngos bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:17: bsam pa sems bskyed skye ba'i tshul /
NK114(ye)001:18: sbyor ba theg chen gyi lam du 'gyur ba'i thabs /
NK114(ye)001:19: de gnyis zung du 'jug par rgyud la skye ba'i rim pa bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:21: de ltar skyabs su song nas theg pa chen po'i
NK114(ye)001:22: lam dngos la 'jug pa'i thog mar lam de'i khyad
NK114(ye)001:24: de la srid pa mtha' dag me'i 'obs lta bur
NK114(ye)001:25: mthong nas rang gi sdug bsngal dang nyon mongs nye
NK114(ye)001:26: bar zhi ba'i don du bslab pa gsum gyi lam
NK114(ye)001:27: la bslab pas myang 'das phyogs gcig pa tsam thob
NK114(ye)001:28: kyang bsam sbyor rgya chung bas theg pa dman pa
NK114(ye)001:29: zhes bya ste / rgyu de'i 'bras bu de ni
NK114(ye)001:30: rdzing bu ste 'khyil chu rnyog ma can lta bur
NK114(ye)001:31: nyon mongs zhi ba'i 'gog pa tsam gyi ngang du
NK114(ye)001:32: kun gzhi'i bag chags dang ma bral bar gnas pas
NK114(ye)001:33: don gnyis phun sum tshogs pa'i 'byor pa thams cad
NK114(ye)001:34: ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin 'byung ba'i rin po che
NK114(ye)001:35: lta bu'i byang chub sems kyi khams theg pa chen
NK114(ye)001:36: po'i rigs las nyams pa'i nyan rang gi skyes bu'i
NK114(ye)001:37: sems zhi ba phyogs gcig par zhugs pa de nyid
NK114(ye)001:38: mthar sangs rgyas rnams kyis bskul nas stong nyid shes
NK114(ye)001:39: pa'i shes rab dang sems can la dmigs pa'i snying
NK114(ye)001:40: rje'i blo dam pa mi gnas pa'i myang 'das su
NK114(ye)001:41: 'khrid pa'i deda dpon lta bu la sbyar ba'i mthus
NK114(ye)001:42: theg chen gyi rigs sad nas theg pa chen po'i
NK114(ye)001:43: chos zab pa dang rgya che ba rgya mtsho lta
NK114(ye)001:44: bu la bslabs te rnam pa thams cad kun mkhyen
NK114(ye)001:45: pa'i go 'phang chos kyi sku las rtag khyab lhun
NK114(ye)001:46: grub chen po'i phrin las rtsol med du 'byung ba'i
NK114(ye)001:47: rin po che'i gling du gdod 'gro dgos pas na
NK114(ye)001:48: zhes bya ste / / blo ldan rnams dang po
NK114(ye)001:49: nas gang la 'jug pa'i lam ni theg pa chen
NK114(ye)001:52: 'jig rten don bsgrub tshul la mthu med pa'i //
NK114(ye)001:53: theg pa gnyis po gtan du spang byas shing //
NK114(ye)001:54: thub rgyal theg pa snying rjes bstan pa la //
NK114(ye)001:55: gzhan phan ro gcig rang bzhin de dag 'jug /
NK114(ye)001:57: de yang mthar thug theg pa gsum du 'dod pa'i
NK114(ye)001:58: lugs ltar na theg dman gyi rigs nges dag rang
NK114(ye)001:59: 'bras las mi ldog kyang ma nges pa'i rigs can
NK114(ye)001:60: rnams dman lam sngon du song nas theg chen la
NK114(ye)001:62: dbu ma pa'i lugs la ni /
NK114(ye)001:64: zla ba sgron me'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:65: 'gro ba 'di dag ma lus sangs rgyas rgyu //
NK114(ye)001:66: 'di na snod min sems can gang yang med //
NK114(ye)001:68: gnas skabs dman pa la dgag sgras rigs chad yod par bshad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:69: theg gsum gyi rigs so sor bshad kyang mthar thug
NK114(ye)001:70: ni theg pa chen po'i lam nas 'tshang rgya bar
NK114(ye)001:71: mi 'gyur ba'i sems can ni gang yang med par
NK114(ye)001:72: 'dod la / des na kha cig dang po nas
NK114(ye)001:73: bsam pa rgya che zhing stong nya da la mos
NK114(ye)001:74: pa thob pas theg pa chen po'i lam la slob
NK114(ye)001:75: 'dod la / nus pa dang / 'ga' zhig dman pa'i lam la slob bzhin pa nas dang /
NK114(ye)001:76: gzhan dag rang 'bras thob zin nas theg pa chen po'i sems skye ba yod do //
NK114(ye)001:77: gnyis pa sbyor ba theg chen gyi lam du 'gyur ba'i thabs ni /
NK114(ye)001:78: sbyin pa la sogsa pa'i thabs kyi cha rnams shes
NK114(ye)001:79: rab dam pas ma zin pa de srid du pha
NK114(ye)001:80: rol tu phyin pa'i ming yang mi thob cing rnam
NK114(ye)001:81: pa lnga po'i ngo bo de byang chub chen po'i
NK114(ye)001:82: rgyur lung du ma bstan pas dngos po dman pa
NK114(ye)001:83: lcagsa kyi khams su yod pa lta bu dge rtsa
NK114(ye)001:84: dman zhing rnam par nyams pa de nyid la thabs
NK114(ye)001:85: kyi gtso bo byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK114(ye)001:86: shes rab kyi gtso bo chos thams cad rang bzhin
NK114(ye)001:87: med par rtogs pa'i lta ba zung du 'brel ba'i
NK114(ye)001:88: gser 'gyur gyi rtsi lta bus rgyas thebs pa'i mod
NK114(ye)001:89: la rin thang chen po gser gyi dngos po lta
NK114(ye)001:90: bu byang chub chen por rgyur bsgyur bar byed pa
NK114(ye)001:91: yin no // gsum pa de gnyis zung du 'jug
NK114(ye)001:92: par rgyud la skye ba'i rim pa bshad pa ni
NK114(ye)001:93: yin no // / mtha' gang la'ang mi gnas pa'i
NK114(ye)001:94: mya ngan las 'das pa de thob pa'i phyir lam
NK114(ye)001:95: bsgrub pa'ang de dang rjes su mthun pa zhig ste
NK114(ye)001:96: yin no // / / de yang zhi ba'i mthar
NK114(ye)001:97: ltung ba 'gog byed snying rje chen po'i sgo nas
NK114(ye)001:98: mtha' yas pa'i sems can rnams la dmigs te phyin
NK114(ye)001:99: drug gi nang du dkar chos thams cad tshang bar
NK114(ye)001:100: bsdus nas nyams su len pa'i thabs dang /
NK114(ye)001:101: srid pa'i mthar ltung ba 'gog byed chos thams cad
NK114(ye)001:102: stong pa nyid kyi ngo bor rtogs pa'i shes rab
NK114(ye)001:103: kyis 'khor gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos rnams la bden
NK114(ye)001:104: par mi blta bas dngos po 'dzin pa thams cad
NK114(ye)001:107: thabs ni bsdu ba shes pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:108: shes rab ni yongs su gcod pa shes pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:109: thabs ni sems can la blta ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:110: shes rab ni chos thams cad la mi blta ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:112: de ltar de gnyis zung du 'jug pa'i stong nyid
NK114(ye)001:113: snying rje'i snying po can gyi byang chub kyi semsa
NK114(ye)001:114: mtshan nyid pa ni sa dang po nas yod pa
NK114(ye)001:115: yin la / de ji ltar rgyud la skye ba'i rgyu'i rim pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:116: sbyor ba tshad med pa bzhi'i blo yang yang sbyong
NK114(ye)001:117: na bsam sbyor thams cad theg pa chen po'i lam
NK114(ye)001:118: du 'gyur bas na sa mkhan gyi chos dang mtshungs
NK114(ye)001:119: pas de'i tha snyad btags shing /
NK114(ye)001:120: de dag la ci'i phyir tshad med ces bya zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:122: 'di ltar sems can tshad med pa la dmigs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:125: ye shes tshad med pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:127: dang po ni khams gsum pa'i sems can mang nyung
NK114(ye)001:128: 'di tsam mo zhes dpag par mi nus pa dang
NK114(ye)001:129: / gnyis pa ni bsod nams dang ye shes rnam
NK114(ye)001:130: pa gnyis te bskyed pa'i rgyu'am ngo bo yin pa
NK114(ye)001:131: / dang / gsum pa ni sangs rgyas kyi che
NK114(ye)001:132: ba'i yon tan stobs dang mi 'jigs pa la sogs
NK114(ye)001:133: / dang / pa dang / bzhi pa ni shes
NK114(ye)001:134: bya dang shes pa tha mi dad pas de bzhin
NK114(ye)001:135: gshegs pa'i ye shes kyi dmigs pa'i yul du gyur
NK114(ye)001:136: pa ste byams pa la sogs pa chos bzhi po
NK114(ye)001:137: de dag gi ngo bor gnas pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:138: des na tshad med pa bzhi po de smon sems ma skyes pa skye ba'i sbyor ba'ang yin la /
NK114(ye)001:139: skyes zin nas smon sems kyi ngo bor gnas shing /
NK114(ye)001:141: de ltar blo sbyangs nas smon 'jug byang chub kyi
NK114(ye)001:142: sems gnyis bskyed pa dang de dag gi 'jug ldog
NK114(ye)001:143: gi bslab bya la tshul bzhin slob pa las thabs
NK114(ye)001:144: shes zung du 'jug pa'i byang chub kyi sems de
NK114(ye)001:145: tshogs sbyor du rjes mthun tsam dang /
NK114(ye)001:146: mthong lam du ji bzhin par skye ba yin no //
NK114(ye)001:147: gnyis pa tshad med bzhi dngos bshad pa la lnga ste /
NK114(ye)001:157: btang snyoms kyi dmigs rnam mo //
NK114(ye)001:158: dang po byams pa'i dmigs rnam ni /
NK114(ye)001:159: byamsa pa tshad med pa'i ngo bo gang zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:160: 'di ltar dmigs pa ni sems can gzhan mngon mtho'i
NK114(ye)001:161: bde ba tsam dang yang mi ldan pa'i ngan song
NK114(ye)001:163: mtho ris thob kyang 'byor pa yod pa'i bde ba
NK114(ye)001:164: dang mi ldan pa'i dbul po la sogs pas mtshon
NK114(ye)001:165: bde bas phongs pa rnams dang /
NK114(ye)001:166: rnam grol gyi bde ba dang mi ldan pa'i 'khor ba'i sems can thams cad kyi bar la'o //
NK114(ye)001:168: de dag mngon mtho'i bde ba nas rnam par grol
NK114(ye)001:169: ba mthar thug pa'i bde ba'i bar dang ldan par
NK114(ye)001:171: de yang bde ba dang ldan na ci ma rung
NK114(ye)001:172: snyam du smon pa tsam ni phal pa 'ga' zhig
NK114(ye)001:173: dang / nyan rang rnams la'ang yod pas /
NK114(ye)001:174: byang chub sems dpa'i byams pa ni dper na shin
NK114(ye)001:175: tu snying du sdug pa dang yid du 'ong bar
NK114(ye)001:176: blta ba'i ma yis bu de la snying nas byams
NK114(ye)001:177: shing brtse bas de nyid bde zhing skyid pa'i thabs
NK114(ye)001:178: su brtson pa na rang la dka' tshegs tsha grang
NK114(ye)001:179: bkres skom la sogs pa'i gnod pa ci byung yang
NK114(ye)001:180: bsran nus shing des tshur la gnod pa byed na'ang
NK114(ye)001:181: slar brtse bas blta ba las khong mi 'khrugs pa
NK114(ye)001:182: ji lta ba de bzhin du rtag tu sems can
NK114(ye)001:183: thams cad la phan 'dogs kyi bsam pas yid du
NK114(ye)001:184: 'ong bar bltas nas rang gi lus dang longs spyod
NK114(ye)001:185: dus gsum gyi dge ba'i rtsa ba ci yod pa
NK114(ye)001:186: thams cad kun spungs pa ste gcig tu bsdoms nas
NK114(ye)001:187: gzhan sems can de dag la gnas skabs dang mthar
NK114(ye)001:188: thug gi phan pa rgya chen po 'dogas pa dang
NK114(ye)001:189: sems can de dag gis gnod pa ji lta bu
NK114(ye)001:190: byas kyang slar yang brtse bas bltas nas bzoda par
NK114(ye)001:191: byed pa'i tshul la bslab par bya ba yin no
NK114(ye)001:192: // de yang da lta las dang po pa'i tshe
NK114(ye)001:193: na ji bzhin pa mi 'ong na'ang gzhan la phan
NK114(ye)001:194: 'dogs 'dod kyi bsam pa bzang pos blo yang yang
NK114(ye)001:195: bcos te gal te gzhan la rnam par 'tshe ba'i
NK114(ye)001:196: blo skyes na rang gis rang la khrel brdas byas
NK114(ye)001:197: te de ma thag slar yang yul de la ched
NK114(ye)001:198: du dmigs nas byams pa bsgom zhing /
NK114(ye)001:199: rgyun du lus kyis sems can la phan ci thogs dang /
NK114(ye)001:200: sprang po rnams la bza' btung gis phan 'dogs sogs
NK114(ye)001:201: longs spyod ci nus su gtong ba'i sgo nas dang
NK114(ye)001:202: / gzhan dge ba la sbyor ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:203: rang gi dge rtsa bsngo ba sogs kyis kyang sems
NK114(ye)001:204: can bde ba'i thabs 'ba' zhig lhur len pa'i thabs
NK114(ye)001:205: la ci nus su brtson par bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:206: de ltar bsgoms pa'i phan yon ni /
NK114(ye)001:207: thar pa chen po'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:208: gang zhig 'jig rten rnam dag na //
NK114(ye)001:209: bskal pa gcig gi bar dag tu //
NK114(ye)001:210: tshul khrims dag ni bsrung ba bas //
NK114(ye)001:211: skyes bu'i skad cig dga' ba tsam //
NK114(ye)001:212: de bas byams pa spyad pas mchog /
NK114(ye)001:214: lus dang ngag yid sdig spyad de //
NK114(ye)001:215: ngan song gsum du ltung nges kyang //
NK114(ye)001:220: de dag kyang ni bsrung ba 2 dang //
NK114(ye)001:224: rnam par grol bar ma gyur kyang //
NK114(ye)001:226: byams chos yon tan brgyad 'thob bo //
NK114(ye)001:228: de yang mos pas spyod pa'i dus su sems can
NK114(ye)001:229: thams cad thog ma med pa nas pha ma sogs
NK114(ye)001:230: gnyen bshes su ma gyur pa med pa'i tshul shes
NK114(ye)001:231: pa'i rgyu'i de rnams la byams sems skye ba ni
NK114(ye)001:232: sems can la dmigs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:233: ma dag sa bdun du chos thams cad rang bzhin
NK114(ye)001:234: med pa la de ltar ma rtogs pa'i mngon par
NK114(ye)001:235: zhen pa can rnams la chos kyis phan btags nas
NK114(ye)001:236: chos nyid rtogs par 'dod pa chos la dmigs pa
NK114(ye)001:237: dang / sa brgyad pa yan chad du rtog med
NK114(ye)001:238: lhun gyis grub pa'i tshul du byams pa 'byung ba
NK114(ye)001:239: ni dmigs pa med pa zhes bya ste snying rje
NK114(ye)001:241: gnyis pa snying rje'i dmigs rnam ni /
NK114(ye)001:242: snying rje tshad med pa'i ngo bo gang zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:243: dmigs pa ni mtha' yas pa'i sems can gzhan thams
NK114(ye)001:244: cad kun gyi rang bzhin sdug bsngal gsum mam brgyad
NK114(ye)001:245: kyis dam la bzhag pa las ma 'das pa la
NK114(ye)001:246: / rnam pa ni sdug bsngal de dag dang bral bar 'dod pa yin kyang /
NK114(ye)001:247: bral 'dod kyi 'dun pa tsam kho na ma yin
NK114(ye)001:248: par rang nyid kyi steng du bab pa bzhin snying
NK114(ye)001:249: gi khung rus pa'i gting nas bzod brlag med pa'i
NK114(ye)001:250: sems kyis ci mi snyam du rang gar 'jog mi
NK114(ye)001:251: phod pa dper na bu sdug gu mi gtsang ba'i
NK114(ye)001:252: dong du lhung na pha tsham tshom med par 'jug
NK114(ye)001:253: pa ltar bdag nyid kho nas sdug bsngal de thams
NK114(ye)001:254: cad dang bral ba zhig nges par bya'o snyam pa'i
NK114(ye)001:255: sems stobs drag po dang bcas pa'i sgo nas dngos
NK114(ye)001:256: brgyud gang rung du sgo gsum longs spyod dang bcas
NK114(ye)001:257: pa thams cad don de nyid kyi phyir du 'gro
NK114(ye)001:259: byams pa dang snying rje gnyis kyi khyad par yul
NK114(ye)001:260: nad pa lta bu nad las grol 'dod du 'dra
NK114(ye)001:261: yang / nad med pa'i bde ba dang mi ldan
NK114(ye)001:262: pa zhig dmigs yul du byas nas de dang ldan
NK114(ye)001:264: nad kyi sdug bsngal la dmigs nas de dang bral
NK114(ye)001:265: bar 'dod na snying rje yin te don gzhan phan
NK114(ye)001:266: gyi blor thams cad gcig kyang dmigs rnam gyis khyad
NK114(ye)001:267: par 'byed pa'o // de la dbye na nyes pa
NK114(ye)001:268: byed pa'i sems can la dmigs pa'i snying rje dang
NK114(ye)001:269: par 'byed pa'o // / sdug bsngal ba'i sems can la dmigs pa'i snying rje dang /
NK114(ye)001:270: rkyen dang mi ldan pas rnam par grol ba med
NK114(ye)001:271: pa'i sems can la dmigs pa'i snying rje gsum las
NK114(ye)001:272: / dang po ni 'gro drug gi sems can mtha'
NK114(ye)001:273: dag sdug bsngal gyi rgyu bdag tu 'dzin pa'i dbang
NK114(ye)001:274: du ma gyur pa 'ga' yang med pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:275: bdag tu 'dzin pa de'i dbang gis la las ni
NK114(ye)001:276: nyon mongs pas kun nas bslangs te sdig pa mi
NK114(ye)001:277: dge ba'i las sna tshogs pa la spyod pa mthong
NK114(ye)001:278: nas 'di thams cad kyi rgyud kyi bdag tu 'dzin
NK114(ye)001:279: pa'i rtog pa 'di drungs nas phyung ste nyon mongs
NK114(ye)001:280: pa dang sdig pa'i las thams cad rgyun chad pa
NK114(ye)001:282: gnyis pa ni sems can la la dag 'bras bu
NK114(ye)001:283: sdug bsngal dngos kyi yo lang la spyod cing ri
NK114(ye)001:284: dwags mtha' la gcur ba bzhin thar ba'i thabs dang
NK114(ye)001:285: bral ba mthonga nas sdug bsngal de thams cad thabs
NK114(ye)001:286: sna tshogs kyis nges par sel ba zhig bdag gis
NK114(ye)001:288: gsum pa ni sems can gang dag dge ba'i bshes
NK114(ye)001:289: gnyen dang ma 'phrad pas chos ma thos shing blang
NK114(ye)001:290: dor gyi gnas mi shes pas rnam grol gyi lam
NK114(ye)001:291: bsgrub pa'i skal ba med pa rnams la dmigs nas
NK114(ye)001:292: sems can de dag la bdag gis mos pa dang
NK114(ye)001:293: 'tshams par chos bstan nas rnam par grol ba'i lam
NK114(ye)001:294: la gzud par bya'o snyam du bsam par bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:295: mdor na bdag ni dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang phrad
NK114(ye)001:296: nas theg pa chen po'i lam du zhugs pa yin
NK114(ye)001:297: na sems can la mi lta bar rang don sems
NK114(ye)001:299: sems can rnams ni 'brog dgon pa 'jigs su rung bar 'khyams pa'i dmus long lta bu /
NK114(ye)001:300: blang dor gyi mig ni long /
NK114(ye)001:301: dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi long khrid dang ni bral /
NK114(ye)001:302: sbyin pa'i bza' btung ni med /
NK114(ye)001:303: tshul khrims kyi skyel mas ni bor //
NK114(ye)001:304: bzod pa'i g.yang lugs ni ral /
NK114(ye)001:306: bsam gtan gyi ngal stegs dang ni bral /
NK114(ye)001:307: shes rab kyi 'khar bas spangs pa 'ba' zhig pas
NK114(ye)001:308: las kyi dbang gis srid pa'i grong khyer drug por
NK114(ye)001:309: kha brgyud cing sdug bsngal shugs drag la yun ring
NK114(ye)001:310: bas mnar ba bzhin thar pa'i dus med pa la
NK114(ye)001:311: bsams te mig nas mchi ma slong bzhin de dag
NK114(ye)001:312: srid pa'i gnas de nas 'don pa'i thabs la rtag
NK114(ye)001:313: tu brtson pa mi 'dor ba zhig bya snyam du
NK114(ye)001:315: de lta bu'i snying rje bsgom pa 'di ni theg
NK114(ye)001:316: pa chen po'i lam thams cad kyi rtsa ba sangs
NK114(ye)001:317: rgyas kyi chos thams cad kyi rgyu ma nor ba
NK114(ye)001:318: yin te / chos yang dag par sdud pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:319: dper bgyis na srog gi dbang po mchis na dbang po gzhan rnams 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:320: de bzhin du snying rje chen po mchis na byang
NK114(ye)001:321: chub sems dpa'i chos gzhan rnams kyang 'byung bar 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:323: snying rje chen pos ni sangs rgyas kyi chos thams
NK114(ye)001:324: cad byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi lag mthil du
NK114(ye)001:327: de lta bas na 'di kho nas blo sbyangs shing
NK114(ye)001:328: 'di dang ldan na dge ba'i chos gzhan ci yang
NK114(ye)001:329: ma 'grub kyang theg pa chen po'i lam las 'dzol
NK114(ye)001:330: sa med la / 'di dang bral phan chad ni
NK114(ye)001:331: mdo sngags kyi chos mang po la snyan snyan dang
NK114(ye)001:332: zab zab kyi bshad rgyang 'then pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:333: lta ba mtho mdog dang sgom pa zab mdog gi
NK114(ye)001:334: kha skad dang rlom pa ji ltar che yang theg
NK114(ye)001:335: pa chen po'i phyogs su yang mi nye bas na
NK114(ye)001:336: gang zag theg pa chen po ma song na chos
NK114(ye)001:337: theg pa chen po yin pa tsam gyis go mi
NK114(ye)001:338: chod do // des na da lta nas kyang bdag
NK114(ye)001:339: cag gis ni dge ba'i bshes gnyen bka' drin can
NK114(ye)001:340: rnams kyi mdzad pa'i lad mo ji thon du sems
NK114(ye)001:341: can rnams la snying nas brtse bas lus ngag dang
NK114(ye)001:342: zang zing gi sgo nas pha rol gyi srog skyob
NK114(ye)001:343: chod do // pa dang / dbul phongs bsal ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:344: sdig rgyun gcod pa sogs phan pa'i bya ba la
NK114(ye)001:345: zhugs na snying rje ma nyams pa'i rtags pa yin
NK114(ye)001:346: gyi / bsam sbyor gnyis ka'i cha nas sems can la gnod pa byed bzhin /
NK114(ye)001:347: kha skad tsam du ni snying rje ba skad kyis
NK114(ye)001:348: chos bshad pa dang sems bskyed ther 'bum bsags kyang
NK114(ye)001:350: gsum pa dga' ba'i dmigs rnam ni /
NK114(ye)001:351: dga' ba tshad med pa'i ngo bo gang zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:352: dmigs pa ni sems can gzhan gang dag bde zhing skyid pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:353: 'byor zhing longs spyod dang ldan pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:354: chos dang mthun par spyod cing thos bsam dang bslab
NK114(ye)001:355: gsum gyis phyug pa la sogs pa'i zang zing dang
NK114(ye)001:356: chos kyi 'byor ba phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan
NK114(ye)001:357: pa yin la / rnam pa ni de la phrag
NK114(ye)001:358: dog dang 'gran sems med par snying nas dga' zhing
NK114(ye)001:359: spro ba'i sems kun tu 'jug cing 'di bzhin du
NK114(ye)001:360: sems can gyi khams yod do cog thams cad kun
NK114(ye)001:361: bde 'byor phun sum tshogs pa la gnas shing ma
NK114(ye)001:362: nyams na ci ma rung snyam du legs smon bsgom
NK114(ye)001:363: pa yin la / zhing / gzhan don bsgrub pa
NK114(ye)001:364: po byang chub sems dpa' rang la ltos ma dgos
NK114(ye)001:365: par sems can rang rang gi sngon bsags dge ba'i
NK114(ye)001:366: mthu yis thob pa'i phun sum tshogs pa'i dngos po
NK114(ye)001:367: de la dga' bar byed cing /
NK114(ye)001:368: phyin chad kyang de dang mi 'bral ba'i steng da dung de bas kyang tshe ring ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:370: dge ba'i bsam pa khyad par can skye ba sogs
NK114(ye)001:371: sangs rgyas kyi sa'i bar gyi yon tan dang ldan
NK114(ye)001:372: zhing ma nyams na ci ma rung de lta bu
NK114(ye)001:373: zhig bdag gis bya snyam du smon pa yin te
NK114(ye)001:375: sems can gang dag rang gi bde bas 'byor ba mthong na 'di snyam du sems te /
NK114(ye)001:376: bde ba 'di dang mi 'bral bar shog cig /
NK114(ye)001:377: lha mi'i bde ba las 'das pa thams cad mkhyen
NK114(ye)001:378: pa'i bde ba dang ldan par gyur cig snyam mo
NK114(ye)001:380: bzhi pa btang snyoms kyi dmigs rnam ni /
NK114(ye)001:381: btang snyomsa tshad med pa'i ngo bo gang zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:383: tshor ba btang snyoms dang 'du byed btang snyoms dang
NK114(ye)001:384: byams sogs bzhi'i nang tshan gyi btang snyoms gsum las
NK114(ye)001:387: pha ma nye 'brel mdza' grogs sogs byamsa shing chags pa'i yul dang /
NK114(ye)001:388: rang dang rang gi phyogs la gnod pa byed pa'i
NK114(ye)001:389: dgra dang de'i phyogs su gtogs pa sdang ba'i yul
NK114(ye)001:390: dang de las gzhan pa'i sems can bar ma'i yul
NK114(ye)001:391: rnams te / rnam pa ni de dag la chags
NK114(ye)001:392: sdang dang ci mi snyam du 'jog pa'i sems 'dral
NK114(ye)001:393: rnams te / ba ste / de yang rang phyogs
NK114(ye)001:394: dang gzhan phyogs la nye ring du blta bas blo
NK114(ye)001:395: ris su chad pa med par sems can thams cad
NK114(ye)001:396: la phan pa'i sems kyi blta ba la khyad med
NK114(ye)001:397: du mnyam pa nyid kyi ngo bor brdala zhing khyab
NK114(ye)001:398: par byas nas bsgom par bya ste 'di ltar sems
NK114(ye)001:399: can thams cad pha mar ma gyur ba med pa
NK114(ye)001:400: la nye ring chags sdang byed pa 'di re ngan
NK114(ye)001:401: rnams te / ba ste / / da lta tsam
NK114(ye)001:402: du gnod pa byed pa la dgra ru lta na
NK114(ye)001:403: gnyen 'di dag gis kyang sngar gnod pa mang po
NK114(ye)001:404: byas shing ma 'ongs pa na'ang byed par 'gyur la
NK114(ye)001:405: da lta'ang phan btags par rlom kyang brtags na dam
NK114(ye)001:406: pa'i chos kyi lam las bshol ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:407: chos min sdig pa'i las la sbyor ba sogs gnod
NK114(ye)001:408: pa chen po byed kyin yod pas dgrar blta rigs
NK114(ye)001:409: pa dang / yang da lta tsam du phan btags pa la gnyen du 'dzin na /
NK114(ye)001:410: dgra 'di dag gis kyang tshe rabs snga ma mang
NK114(ye)001:411: por phan btags shing ma 'ongs pa na'ang 'dogs par
NK114(ye)001:412: 'gyur la da lta'ang dgras gnod pa byas pas rang
NK114(ye)001:413: gi sngon gyis las ngan 'dzad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:414: skyo shas nges 'byung gi bskul mar 'gyur ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:415: bzod pa bsgoms na tshogs rdzogs pa sogs brtags na
NK114(ye)001:416: phan chen po btags pas gnyen du blta rigs pa
NK114(ye)001:417: dang / da lta phan gnod gang yang ma byas
NK114(ye)001:418: pa la bar ma'i 'du shes 'jog na'ang tshe rabs
NK114(ye)001:419: snga phyi du mar pha dang ma ru gyur nas
NK114(ye)001:420: drin chen pos ma bskyangs pa 'ga' yang med pas
NK114(ye)001:421: na yul gsum po de thams cad la pha ma
NK114(ye)001:422: bu tsha'i 'du shes nye bar bzhag ste phan 'dogsa
NK114(ye)001:423: pa'i yul du bltas nas thams cad la chos dang
NK114(ye)001:424: zang zing gi sgo nas phan pa'i thabs bsgrub pa
NK114(ye)001:425: la khyad med du mnyam par rab tu spyad par
NK114(ye)001:426: dang / bya'o // sgom tshul gyi dmigs rnam 'di
NK114(ye)001:427: ltar bshad pa'i lugs 'di ni khrid yig rnams na
NK114(ye)001:428: dang / bya'o // mang la / yang sems can
NK114(ye)001:429: thams cad thog ma med pa'i dus nas sdug bsngal
NK114(ye)001:430: 'ba' zhig la spyod pa 'di chags sdang gis lan
NK114(ye)001:431: pa yin pas sems can thams cad nye ring chags
NK114(ye)001:432: sdang dang bral bar shog cig snyam du sgom pa'i
NK114(ye)001:433: tshul ni gzhung lugs rnams las rgya cher 'byung ngo
NK114(ye)001:435: de gnyis mi 'gal te sems can thams cad chags
NK114(ye)001:436: sdang dang bral na rang yang de'i khongs su 'du
NK114(ye)001:438: rang rgyud kyi chags sdang zhi nas gzhan la'ang de
NK114(ye)001:439: ltar zhi 'dod kyi blo skye bas so //
NK114(ye)001:440: mdor na ldan 'dod bral 'dod mi 'bral 'dod zhi
NK114(ye)001:441: bar 'dod pa bzhi'i sgo nas dbye ba'i tshad med
NK114(ye)001:442: pa bzhi'i rnam pa'i sgom tshul dmigsa pa dang bcas
NK114(ye)001:443: pa thams cad la bden pa'i dmigs pa med pa'i
NK114(ye)001:444: rtsi yis sbyar bar bya ste bsgom bya'i yul sems
NK114(ye)001:445: can dang / sgom pa po rang dang /
NK114(ye)001:446: bsgom rgyu'i chos tshad med pa rnams rmi lam dang
NK114(ye)001:447: gzugs brnyan ltar snang yang rang bzhin med pa'i nges
NK114(ye)001:448: shes dang ldan pas bsgom par bya zhing /
NK114(ye)001:449: rjes la dmigs bsam brjod pa dang bral ba'i ngang la mnyam par bzhag par bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:450: de yang ye shes snang ba rgyan gyi mdor /
NK114(ye)001:451: chos thams cad kyi mtshan nyid dmigs su med pa
NK114(ye)001:452: gang yang yin pa de ni mnyam pa nyid yin
NK114(ye)001:453: no // zhes pa ltar btang snyoms bsgoms pas sems
NK114(ye)001:454: rnam par mi g.yeng bas blo las su rung ba
NK114(ye)001:455: mthar thug chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du rtogs
NK114(ye)001:456: no // par 'gyur ro // de ltar tshad med
NK114(ye)001:457: bzhi po so sor phye nas rim can du bsgom
NK114(ye)001:458: pa mngon pa'i lugs yin pas myong ba thon pa
NK114(ye)001:460: rnam pa spyi la dmigs nas rgyas 'debs pa ni
NK114(ye)001:461: sa chod che ba ltar snang yang don du gcig
NK114(ye)001:462: la'ang nges pa mi skye ba byas pa'i mdun du
NK114(ye)001:463: za 'og kha phye ba lta bu'o //
NK114(ye)001:465: 'di ltar sems yang dag par ma bskyed cing /
NK114(ye)001:466: thar pa 'dod pa'i sems kyis kyang ma zin par
NK114(ye)001:467: blo'i rnam pa bden par zhen pa dang bcas pas
NK114(ye)001:468: yul rang gi nye du dang mdza' bshes la sogs
NK114(ye)001:469: pa'i phyogs la blos 'dod cing chags pa'i sems kyis
NK114(ye)001:470: de dag gi lus sems bde zhing skyid par 'dod
NK114(ye)001:471: nas phan 'dogs pa la sogs pa'i sgo nas byams
NK114(ye)001:472: par byed cing gzhan la cang mi sems pa dang
NK114(ye)001:473: / de bzhin du yul rang gis bdag gir bzung
NK114(ye)001:474: ba'i rta khal sogs la ngo bo ser sna'i dbang
NK114(ye)001:475: gis r+ts+wa chag chu chag khur du mi 'jug pa
NK114(ye)001:476: / dang / zhon nas 'gro ba dang khal 'gel
NK114(ye)001:477: ba sogs kyis ha cang bkol mi bra bar snying
NK114(ye)001:478: rje rje byed kyang srog chags gzhan la de las
NK114(ye)001:479: / dang / ldog pa dang / yul rang dang
NK114(ye)001:480: rang gi phyogs kyi yul khams sde ris dgon gnas
NK114(ye)001:481: sogs 'byor zhing rgyas la bde zhing skyid pa la
NK114(ye)001:482: / dang / ldog pa dang / / ngo bo
NK114(ye)001:483: de nyid gzhan las lhag par shes nas blo khengs
NK114(ye)001:484: shing nga rgyal las de la spro zhing dga' ba
NK114(ye)001:485: bsgom na'ang gzhan gyi phyogs ni de las lhag pa'am
NK114(ye)001:486: de dang 'dra ba tsam du'ang mi 'dod pas phrag
NK114(ye)001:487: dog dang yang nye ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:488: yang phan gnod kyi yul gnyen dang dgra'i phyogs la /
NK114(ye)001:489: ngo bo phan 'dogs pa dang gnod pa skyel ba'i
NK114(ye)001:490: bsam pa gang yang med pa'i gti mug lung ma
NK114(ye)001:491: bstan bzang med ngan med du lus pa'i btang snyomsa
NK114(ye)001:492: dang bzhi po 'di ni thar pa mya ngan las
NK114(ye)001:493: 'das pa'i 'bras bu mngon du byed pa'i thabs shes
NK114(ye)001:494: gang dang yang mi ldan pas de'i lam ni min
NK114(ye)001:495: la / 'on kyang gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu med pa'ang ma yin no //
NK114(ye)001:496: de yang 'dod pa'i 'dod chags dang phyogs nye ba'i
NK114(ye)001:497: byams sogs kyis 'dod pa'i lha mi dang srid pa'i
NK114(ye)001:498: 'dod chags tshangs pa'i gnas pa bzhii'am de'i phyogs dang
NK114(ye)001:499: nye ba'i byams sogs kyis khams gong ma gnyis su
NK114(ye)001:502: sems gsal gcig bskyed 'bras bu gang //
NK114(ye)001:503: tshangs la sogs pa yin pa ltar //
NK114(ye)001:506: khams gnyis las skyes srid 'dod chags //
NK114(ye)001:508: de lta na'ang de dag gi dmigs pa ris su chad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:509: rnam pa mngon par zhen pa dang bcas pa nyid
NK114(ye)001:510: kyi phyir theg chen lam gyi tshad med bzhi'i gol
NK114(ye)001:511: sa yin pas rnam par spang bar bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:512: gsum pa khyad par can ni /
NK114(ye)001:513: thun mong ma yin pa theg pa chen po'i thabs
NK114(ye)001:514: shes khyad par can bshad pa'i skabs 'di na mtha'
NK114(ye)001:515: gnyis zhi ba'i mya ngan las 'das pa thob byed
NK114(ye)001:516: kyi lam dang 'brel ba yi tshad med pa bzhi'i
NK114(ye)001:517: dmigs pa'i yul ni sems can phyogs re ba ma
NK114(ye)001:518: yin par mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad yin
NK114(ye)001:519: la / blo'i rnam pa yang bde ba dang 'phrad par 'dod pa sogs yin kyang /
NK114(ye)001:520: don la rang gi sems nyid gdod ma nas spros
NK114(ye)001:521: pa thams cad dang bral zhing chos thams cad kyang
NK114(ye)001:522: de dang tshul gcig par rtogs nas dmigs yul sems
NK114(ye)001:523: can dang blo'i rnam pa ldan 'dod sogs su snang
NK114(ye)001:524: yang de la dngos por lta ba'i mtshan nyid las
NK114(ye)001:525: ldog ste rang bzhin med pa'i chos nyid kyi rtsis
NK114(ye)001:526: zin nas thabs shes zung du 'jug pa'i rnam pa'i
NK114(ye)001:527: bsgom tshul yang yang goms nas stobs su gyur pa
NK114(ye)001:528: las kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i byang chub kyi
NK114(ye)001:529: sems gnyis skye ba'i rgyur 'gro ba yin pas 'jig
NK114(ye)001:530: rten pa dang nyan rang rnams dang thun mong ma
NK114(ye)001:531: yin pa'i thabs shes gnyis ka'i phyogs nas khyad chos
NK114(ye)001:532: dang ldan pa'i tshad med pa bzhi ru 'dod pa
NK114(ye)001:534: byang chub ni nam mkha'i mtshan nyid kyi phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:535: des na rang gi sems yang dag pa ji lta
NK114(ye)001:536: ba bzhin mthong ba'i rjes su thabs kyis sems can
NK114(ye)001:537: thams cad kyi sems la dmigs pa 'byung ste /
NK114(ye)001:540: don dam byang chub kyi sems bsgom pa rin chen sgron ma las /
NK114(ye)001:541: ji ltar snang zhing grags pa'i chos //
NK114(ye)001:542: de ltar grub cing bden pa min //
NK114(ye)001:543: sna tshogs cir yang 'byung ba'i phyir //
NK114(ye)001:544: dper na mig 'phrul rnam pa bzhin //
NK114(ye)001:545: ngo bo nyid med nam mkha' 'dra //
NK114(ye)001:546: rten 'brel tsam las byung ba'i phyir //
NK114(ye)001:547: shin tu med pa'ang ma yin te //
NK114(ye)001:548: dper na rmi lam rgyu 'bras bzhin //
NK114(ye)001:549: bden pa ma grub rdzun mi ldog /
NK114(ye)001:552: 'jig rten byang chub rang sangs rgyas pa yi //
NK114(ye)001:553: dgra bcom rnams la byams pa de med na //
NK114(ye)001:554: de las gzhan la smos kyang ci dgos pa //
NK114(ye)001:555: ji ltar 'jig rten 'das pa ma yin 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:558: tshad med pa bzhi po de dag gi sgom tshul
NK114(ye)001:559: la go rim gyi nges pa can ni dkyus su
NK114(ye)001:561: de dang mtshungs par yum bar ma las kyang gsungs shing /
NK114(ye)001:562: sngags su lha'i de kho na nyid dang sbyar nas gsungs pa'ang /
NK114(ye)001:564: dang por byams pa bsgom par bya //
NK114(ye)001:565: gnyis par snying rje rnam bsgom zhing //
NK114(ye)001:566: gsum par dga' ba bsgom pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:567: kun gyi mthar ni btang snyoms so //
NK114(ye)001:569: nges pa med pa ni btang snyoms thog mar bsgom pa la sogs pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:570: slob dpon dpa' bo'i kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems sgom pa las kyang /
NK114(ye)001:571: de yang thog mar tshad med blo //
NK114(ye)001:572: btang snyoms sa gzhi legs brdal la //
NK114(ye)001:573: byams pa'i chu bos rnam bcus nas //
NK114(ye)001:574: rab tu dga' bas rnal 'byor pas //
NK114(ye)001:575: snying rjes sa bon legs par gdab //
NK114(ye)001:576: ces gsungs pas sems can thams cad la rjes su chags pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:577: khong khro ba bsal te sems snyoms pa nyid sngon
NK114(ye)001:578: du bsgrubs nas byams pa la sogs pa bsgom pa'i
NK114(ye)001:579: slad du ste / des na dmigs pa'i yul gang
NK114(ye)001:580: la tshad med pa'i blo gang skye bar sla ba
NK114(ye)001:581: de la thog mar gtad nas bsgom par bya ste
NK114(ye)001:582: slad du ste / / de yang tshad med pa 'di dag rkyen bzhi las skye ba'i phyir te /
NK114(ye)001:584: sems can gyi khams la rang bzhin du gnas pa'i rigs rgyu'i rkyen /
NK114(ye)001:585: tshad med bzhi po ston pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen bdag po'i rkyen /
NK114(ye)001:586: rang rang gi yul dmigs pa'i rkyen /
NK114(ye)001:587: de ltar bsgoms pa'i phan yon dang ma bsgoms pa'i
NK114(ye)001:588: nyes dmigs goms pa de ma thag pa'i rkyen te
NK114(ye)001:590: bde dang sdug bsngal de rgyu las //
NK114(ye)001:591: byang chub sems dpa'i snying rje ste //
NK114(ye)001:592: rgyu dang bshes gnyen rang bzhin las //
NK114(ye)001:593: blo dang ldan pa'i snying rje skye //
NK114(ye)001:595: khyad par sems dang sems byung ltar 'brel ba'i dmigs
NK114(ye)001:596: pa'i rnam pa 'di dag ni 'khor ba'i dus na
NK114(ye)001:597: bdag rkyen la sogs pa bzhis bskyed la /
NK114(ye)001:598: rgyu bdag de ma thag gsum gyis snyoms 'jug rnam pa gnyis dang /
NK114(ye)001:599: rang rang gi rgyu dang drod gsher la sogs pa'i bdag rkyen las bem po rnams skye ste /
NK114(ye)001:601: bzhi yis sems dang sems byung rnams //
NK114(ye)001:602: gsum gyis snyoms par 'jug rnam gnyis //
NK114(ye)001:603: gzhan ni gnyis po dag las skye //
NK114(ye)001:605: 'on kyang go rim la zhen pa'i gnyen por 'di
NK114(ye)001:606: ltar yid 'ong gi byams pa yang yang bsgoms pas
NK114(ye)001:607: yul de gnyen bshes lta bu'i ris can du mthong
NK114(ye)001:608: ste chags pa'i rten du gyur na nye ring dang
NK114(ye)001:609: brala ba'i btang snyoms bsgom par spos pas chags pa'i
NK114(ye)001:610: rnam pa de 'gog par 'gyur la btang snyoms bsgom
NK114(ye)001:611: pa'i blo de nyid phan 'dogs pa'i sems med par
NK114(ye)001:612: rmongs nas lung ma bstan du gyur na snying rjer
NK114(ye)001:613: spos nas bsgoms pas sems can rnams sdug bsngal gyi
NK114(ye)001:614: rgyu la spyod cing 'bras bus gzir ba'i tshul la
NK114(ye)001:615: yang yang bsam pa'i stobs kyis btang snyoms tha shal
NK114(ye)001:617: snying rje bsgoms pa na sems can gyi sdug bsngal shin tu rgya che bas sems stobs zhan te /
NK114(ye)001:618: ha cang zhum nas ris su chad par gyur na /
NK114(ye)001:619: bde zhing 'byor pa dang ldan pa'i sems can la
NK114(ye)001:620: dmigs te dga' ba bsgom par spos pas zhum zhing
NK114(ye)001:621: dman pa'i sems skye ba de nyid 'gog la /
NK114(ye)001:622: dga' ba bsgoms pasa sems ha cang rgod cing spros
NK114(ye)001:623: pa'i yul du g.yeng bar gyur na byams pa la
NK114(ye)001:624: sogsa pa matha'a dbus barjesa nas bzhi po spel mar
NK114(ye)001:629: snying rje la mnyam par 'jog go //
NK114(ye)001:631: zhes thod rgal du rtsal sbyang bar gsungs la /
NK114(ye)001:632: gzhan yang byams pa'i gegs snying rjes /
NK114(ye)001:634: dga' ba'i gegs btang snyoms kyis /
NK114(ye)001:635: btang snyoms kyi gegs byams pas 'gog pa'i lugs kyang yod do //
NK114(ye)001:636: lnga pa phan yon la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:638: khyad par gyi phan yon nas 'bras bu'o //
NK114(ye)001:640: de ltar tshad med pa bzhi po bsgom pas 'bras bu bzhi thob par 'gyur te /
NK114(ye)001:641: de la rnam par smin pa'i 'bras bu ni srid
NK114(ye)001:642: pa mngon par mtho ba'i gnas 'dod par lha dang
NK114(ye)001:643: mi'i lus rten phun sum tshogs pa thob pa dang
NK114(ye)001:644: / rten de dang des tshogs gnyis rdzogs par byas
NK114(ye)001:645: nas nges par legsa pa'i 'bras bu slob pa dang
NK114(ye)001:646: mi slob pa'i sa mngon du byed pa ste gnyis
NK114(ye)001:647: / dang / rgyu mthun la gnyis las byed pa
NK114(ye)001:648: rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu ni gang du skyes pa'i
NK114(ye)001:649: tshe rabs thams cad du sngar ji ltar bsgoms shing
NK114(ye)001:650: rgyud la 'byongs pa de dang 'dra bar tshad med
NK114(ye)001:651: pa bzhi po'i blo bsgom par 'gyur la /
NK114(ye)001:652: myong ba rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu ni rang rang gi mi mthun pa'i phyogs gnod sems dang /
NK114(ye)001:655: chags sdang ste zhi dang bral zhing /
NK114(ye)001:656: de dag med pa'i bde ba phun sum tshogs pa 'thob pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:657: dbang gi 'bras bus ni 'di ltar byams pas gnas
NK114(ye)001:658: grogs longs spyod sogs yid du 'ong ba dang 'phrad
NK114(ye)001:659: pa dang / snying rjes lus sems bde ba'i rkyen dang ldan pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:660: dga' bas sa phyogs sman shing dang me tog la
NK114(ye)001:661: sogs pas brgyan pas yid dga' ba'i rgyur 'gyur ba
NK114(ye)001:662: dang / btang snyoms kyis skye dgu mdza' zhing mi
NK114(ye)001:663: mthun pa med pa'i yul la spyod par 'gyur ro
NK114(ye)001:664: dang / // skyes bu byed pa'i 'bras bu ni
NK114(ye)001:665: tshad med pa bzhi po'i byed pa ches cher stobs
NK114(ye)001:666: su gyur nas tshad med pa'i blo rang bzhin nam
NK114(ye)001:668: so sor brtags pa las skye ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:669: yang yang goms pa las skye ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:670: rang rang gi yul mthong ba las skye ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:671: mi mthun pa'i phyogs nyams pas skye ba yi dbang
NK114(ye)001:672: gis rang don du rtogs pa'i yon tan dang bde
NK114(ye)001:673: legs kyi dngos po thams cad gong nas gong du
NK114(ye)001:675: gzhan don du tshad med pa bzhi pos blo dang
NK114(ye)001:676: mthun pa'i phan pa bsgrub pa'i bya ba 'bad med
NK114(ye)001:677: du 'byung ba ste don gnyis phun sum tshogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:678: 'byor pa'i yon tan mtha' dag 'thob par 'gyur te
NK114(ye)001:680: snying rje'i bdag nyid can gyi brtse ba ni //
NK114(ye)001:681: rang bzhin dang ni so sor brtags pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:682: de sngon goms par byas dang ldan pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:683: mi mthun phyogs nyams rnam dag thob pa bzhi //
NK114(ye)001:686: 'tshe spangs byang chub mchog gi sa bon dang //
NK114(ye)001:687: bde ba bskyed dang gdung byed 'dod pa'i rgyu //
NK114(ye)001:688: ngo bo nyid smin chos la brten pa yi //
NK114(ye)001:689: rgyal sras rnams la byang chub thag mi ring //
NK114(ye)001:690: zhes bral ba'i 'bras bu mi mthun phyogs 'tshe ba spangs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:691: bdag po'i 'bras bu snying rjes byang chub mchog gi sa bon byas nas de thob pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:692: skyes bu byed pa'i 'bras bu gzhan la bde ba
NK114(ye)001:693: bskyed pa dang de'i don du bdag la gdung ba
NK114(ye)001:695: rnam smin gyi 'bras bu snying rjes ji ltar 'dod
NK114(ye)001:696: par ram 'dod khams su skye ba'i rgyu byas nas
NK114(ye)001:698: rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu ma 'ongs pa na snying
NK114(ye)001:699: rje khyad par du 'phags pa'i ngo bo nyid sbyin
NK114(ye)001:700: pa ste 'bras bu lngar bshad do //
NK114(ye)001:701: gnyis pa khyad par gyi 'bras bu la bzhi ste /
NK114(ye)001:707: byams pa tshad med pa sems la goms shing 'byongs
NK114(ye)001:708: pas de'i rgyud brlan te 'gro ba kun la bu
NK114(ye)001:709: gcig pa'i ma ltara snying nas brtse bar 'gyur bas
NK114(ye)001:710: zhe sdang gis rgyud tha bar gyur nas sems can
NK114(ye)001:711: la rgyab kyis phyogs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:712: sems rtsub par gyur nas gnod pa'i bsam pa nam yang skye ba med cing /
NK114(ye)001:713: dper na ma la bu dga' ba de mas byams
NK114(ye)001:714: pa'i mthus yin pa ltar byams pa'i mthus sems can
NK114(ye)001:715: gzhan thams cad kun gyi yida du 'ong zhing dga'
NK114(ye)001:716: bar 'gyur ro // byamsa pa'i ngo bo yon tan
NK114(ye)001:717: thams cad sdud pa'i tshul gyis mi 'gog pa'i rnam
NK114(ye)001:718: pa la gshis gang du'ang ma grub pas stong la
NK114(ye)001:719: rang bzhin med pa'i ngang tshul las mi 'da' bar
NK114(ye)001:720: rtogs shing goms pas mthar thug mkhyen cha 'gag pa
NK114(ye)001:721: med pa me long ye shes mngon du gyur nas
NK114(ye)001:722: mtshan dang dpe byad rgya mtsho'i bdag nyid longs spyod
NK114(ye)001:724: byams pas zhe sdang gnas su dag /
NK114(ye)001:725: me long ye shes longs spyod rdzogs //
NK114(ye)001:728: de bzhin du snying rje tshad med pa'i blo goms shing rgyud la 'byongs pas /
NK114(ye)001:729: dper na snying du sdug pa'i bu chung du rim
NK114(ye)001:730: nad drag pos btab na de'i ma yang de dang
NK114(ye)001:731: rjes su mthun pa'i sems kyis sdug bsngal gyi tshor
NK114(ye)001:732: ba nyams su myong bar gyur nas bu sdug bsngal
NK114(ye)001:733: de las gdon pa'i thabs 'ba' zhig las zas kyi
NK114(ye)001:734: bya ba'ang mi dran pa de bzhin du srid par
NK114(ye)001:735: rgyu ba'i sems can gzhan thams cad kun gyi sdug
NK114(ye)001:736: bsngal ji snyed yod pa thams cad kyang bdag gi
NK114(ye)001:737: khur du 'gro ba ste bdag la bab pa bzhin
NK114(ye)001:738: mi bzod pa'i blos sdug bsngal de las gdon pa'i
NK114(ye)001:739: thabs 'ba' zhig sems pa las gzhan la rnam par
NK114(ye)001:740: 'tshe ba'i rtog pa skad cig ma tsam du skye
NK114(ye)001:742: gzhan la gnod pa sbyor ba'i rgyu mnar sems kyis
NK114(ye)001:743: de dag gi srog lus longs spyod la rgol bar
NK114(ye)001:744: 'dod pa'i chags pa zil gyiis gnon pa'am /
NK114(ye)001:745: snying rje de yang gnyen bshes ltar sems can la 'dod cing chagsa pa'i sems dang bral la /
NK114(ye)001:746: snying rje'i ngo bo rang bzhin med pas stong nyid
NK114(ye)001:747: kyi gdangs snying rje chen por shar te zung du
NK114(ye)001:748: 'brel bas 'khor ba kun rdzob pa'i chos thams cad
NK114(ye)001:749: kyi rgyu 'bras ngo bo thams cad ma 'dres par
NK114(ye)001:750: rtogs nas de dang sems can gyi rgyud so sor
NK114(ye)001:751: 'byed pa'i rnam pa yin pas mthar thug shes bya
NK114(ye)001:752: thams cad ma 'dres par 'byed pa'i so sor rtog
NK114(ye)001:753: pa'i ye shes mngon du gyur nas dkar chos kyi
NK114(ye)001:754: yon tan thams cad kyi rang bzhin chos kyi sku
NK114(ye)001:756: snying rjes 'dod chags gnas su dag /
NK114(ye)001:757: kun rtogs ye shes chos kyi sku //
NK114(ye)001:760: dga' ba tshad med rgyud la goms shing 'byongs pas
NK114(ye)001:761: gzhan gyi 'byor pa la mi dga' ba'i sems thang
NK114(ye)001:762: cig tsam yang mi skye bas phrag dog gi rtsa
NK114(ye)001:763: ba chod cing / sems can thams cad bde zhing skyid pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:764: chos kyi rang bzhin la dngos dang brgyud nas spyod
NK114(ye)001:765: pa mtha' dag la dga' ba khyad par can skyes
NK114(ye)001:766: pa'i rgyus rang gi yon tan gyi 'byor pa phun
NK114(ye)001:767: sum tshogs pa kun brtan zhing phrag dog gi zug
NK114(ye)001:768: rngu zhi ba'i bde ba rgyun mi 'achada pas bsam
NK114(ye)001:769: gtan la tsher ma med cing de las skyes pa'i
NK114(ye)001:770: dga' ba nyams su myong zhing /
NK114(ye)001:771: dga' ba'i ngo bo ni rang gzhan la mi mnyam
NK114(ye)001:772: pa med par 'byor zhing phun sum tshogs pa la
NK114(ye)001:773: dga' yang gzung 'dzin du dmigs pa'i rtsol ba med
NK114(ye)001:774: pa dang mthun par mthar thug gzhan don rtsol med
NK114(ye)001:775: du mkhyen pa'i bya ba 'grub pa'i ye shes mngon
NK114(ye)001:776: du gyur nas / gdul bya thams cad kyi don
NK114(ye)001:777: mnyam par mdzad pa'i sprul pa'i sku mchog 'thoba par
NK114(ye)001:778: du gyur nas / 'gyur te / dga' bas phrag dog gnas su dag /
NK114(ye)001:779: bya grub ye shes sprul pa'i sku //
NK114(ye)001:780: mdzad pa lhun grub dam pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:783: btang snyoms tshad med pa'i blo goms shing 'byongs pas
NK114(ye)001:784: bdag la ji ltar phan par 'dod pa de bzhin
NK114(ye)001:785: du gzhan la'ang 'dod cing dgra gnyena bar ma'i phyogs
NK114(ye)001:786: gsum kyang phan 'dogs pa'i yul du mnyam par blta
NK114(ye)001:787: bas bdag la gces par 'dzin pa'am /
NK114(ye)001:788: gzhan don byas pa la rlom sems dang bdag nyid gzengs bstod pa'i nga rgyal med cing /
NK114(ye)001:790: dngos med du zhen pa'i mtha' gnyis su lhung nas
NK114(ye)001:791: sems kyi chos nyid dbu mar mi snyoms pa'ang rang
NK114(ye)001:792: bzhin gyis stong zhing zaba pa dang spros pa thams
NK114(ye)001:793: cad nye bar zhi ba'i dbyings su btang snyoms pa'i
NK114(ye)001:794: rtogsa pa khyad par can skye zhing /
NK114(ye)001:795: btang snyoms kyi ngo bo tha dad du 'dzin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:796: gti mug gi rang bzhin rmongsa pa med cing mthar
NK114(ye)001:797: 'dzin zhi ba yin pas mthar thug chos thams cad
NK114(ye)001:798: dbyer med blang dor dang bral bar mkhyen pa chos
NK114(ye)001:800: rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'i dbyings sgrib pa thams
NK114(ye)001:801: cad dang bral ba ngo bo nyid kyi sku mngona
NK114(ye)001:803: btang snyoms btang snyoms chen po yis //
NK114(ye)001:804: nga rgyal gti mug gnas su dag /
NK114(ye)001:805: mnyam nyid chos dbyings ye shes bdag /
NK114(ye)001:806: byang chub rdo rje'i sku nyid do //
NK114(ye)001:807: zhes pa rnams pad+ma rtse mo las bshad do //
NK114(ye)001:808: de dag gi mjug bsdus te mtha' gnyis spang pa'i lam la slob par gdams pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:809: de lta bu'i theg chen thun mong ma yin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:810: lam gyi tshad med pa bzhi po yi yona tan
NK114(ye)001:811: ni / 'di ltar rgyu'i theg pa phal mo ches
NK114(ye)001:812: sku gnyis skyed byed kyi rgyu'am sa bon tshogs gnyis
NK114(ye)001:814: sngags su dag bya'i sgrib pa gnyis tshogs gnyis kyi
NK114(ye)001:815: rang bzhin thabs shes zab mos 'khrud pa de rkyen
NK114(ye)001:816: du 'dod pas don stong nyid snying rje'i snying po
NK114(ye)001:817: can bsgrub pa la don mthun cing /
NK114(ye)001:818: khyad par 'khor lo tha ma'i don khams rang bzhin
NK114(ye)001:819: gyis rnam par dag pa'i yon tan ye ldan yin
NK114(ye)001:820: pa'i phyir lam dus kyi yon tan ltar snang ba
NK114(ye)001:821: yin pas gsar byung mi 'dod la /
NK114(ye)001:822: de dang sngags kyi sde snod las 'gro ba kun
NK114(ye)001:823: kyang rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dam pa'i chos nyid
NK114(ye)001:824: du gnas pa gnyis gzhi'i ngang du gcig pas na
NK114(ye)001:825: de mngon du 'gyur byed kyi rgyu'am lam tshogs gnyis
NK114(ye)001:826: dang thabs shes ngo bo gcig cing 'bras bu sku
NK114(ye)001:827: gnyis kyang ngo bo tha mi dad pas de ltar
NK114(ye)001:828: gzhi lam 'bras bu rnams tshul mthun pa'i don rtogs
NK114(ye)001:829: nas nyams su len pa ni shin tu zab pas
NK114(ye)001:830: yon tan matha'a yasa shing mthar thug pa'i don du
NK114(ye)001:833: gang gis tshad med bzhi bsgom pa //
NK114(ye)001:834: de ni bde gshegs kun gyis dgongs //
NK114(ye)001:835: kun tu yon tan tshad med de //
NK114(ye)001:836: nam mkha'i lam las rab 'das pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:839: thub pa sh+aakya seng ge yis //
NK114(ye)001:840: ji ltar brnyes bzhin grogs po rnams //
NK114(ye)001:841: rgyal sras 'jigs pa med pa yis //
NK114(ye)001:842: 'di dag kun la yid ches gyis //
NK114(ye)001:843: yid ches gyur na sangs rgyas sam //
NK114(ye)001:844: thar par 'gyur ba the tshom med //
NK114(ye)001:846: des na ji skad bshad pa'i lam tshad med pa
NK114(ye)001:847: bzhi po de dag dang mi ldan pa ni lam
NK114(ye)001:848: ngana pa'am phyin ci log pa zhes bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:849: ci'i phyir zhe na theg pa chen po las gazhana
NK114(ye)001:850: du gyur pa kun gyi grub pa'i matha'a ni srid
NK114(ye)001:851: pa'i rgyu las mi 'da' ba'i phyir te /
NK114(ye)001:852: 'di ltar mu stegs can rnams kyi lam ni bdag
NK114(ye)001:853: tu lta ba dang bcas pas rnam pa thams cad
NK114(ye)001:854: du shes rab dang bral zhing snying rje yang med
NK114(ye)001:855: pas srid par skye ba'i rgyu yin zhing /
NK114(ye)001:856: nyan rang gi lam gyis srid par skye ba rgyun gcod kyang /
NK114(ye)001:857: snying rje chen po dang bral zhing shes rab nyi
NK114(ye)001:858: tshe ba yin pas srid pa snang ba'i rgyu'i bag
NK114(ye)001:861: tshad med pa 'di bzhi ni thar par 'gro ba'i lam ste /
NK114(ye)001:864: des nas chos thams cad la bdag gnyis kyis gdod
NK114(ye)001:865: ma nas stong ba'i stong pa nyid shes pa'i shes
NK114(ye)001:866: rab dang snying rje chen po zung du tshud par
NK114(ye)001:867: gyur pa'i lam yang dag pa dang 'agla ba gzhan
NK114(ye)001:869: thar pa sgrib gnyis kyi dri ma med pa mi
NK114(ye)001:870: gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa thob byed rgyal
NK114(ye)001:871: sras byang chub sems dpa' shes rab dang snying rje
NK114(ye)001:872: dam pa'i blo dang ldan pa rnams kyi lam thabs
NK114(ye)001:873: shes khyad par can gyis rang don yid byed kyi
NK114(ye)001:874: blo dang bden par zhen pa'i blo'i rnyog pa zhi
NK114(ye)001:875: ba'i dge ba la go yul tsam du ma lus
NK114(ye)001:876: par gomas par 'atshala lo zhes gdams so //
NK114(ye)001:877: yona tan rin po che'i mdzoda dag'a ba'i char zhes bya ba las /
NK114(ye)001:878: tshad med bzhi'i tshomsa te le'u bduna pa'i 'grel pa'o ////
NK114(ye)001:879: gnyis pa dam bca' ba byang chub sems kyi sems yongs su bzung ba'i le'u la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:883: 'di ltar srid zhi'i khams thams cad na gong na
NK114(ye)001:884: med pa'i rnyed pa mchog tu gyur pa ni bla
NK114(ye)001:885: med rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyi go 'phang gang gi
NK114(ye)001:886: dona la dmigs nas lam bsgrub pa la de thob
NK114(ye)001:887: byed kyi yona nam rgyu thams cad kun gyi mchoga
NK114(ye)001:888: gam snying po ni tshad med rnam pa bzhi yang
NK114(ye)001:889: yang goms pa'i stobs kyis thob pa'i lhag pa'i bsam
NK114(ye)001:890: pa byang chub kyi sems rin po che yin te
NK114(ye)001:891: / byams pas zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:892: byams pa byang chub sems dpa' chos gcig dang ldan na /
NK114(ye)001:893: ngan song thams cad spong zhing sdig pa'i grogs po'i
NK114(ye)001:894: lag tu mi 'gro la myur du bla na med
NK114(ye)001:895: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu 'tshang
NK114(ye)001:896: rgya ste / chos gcig po gang zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:897: 'di lta ste lhag pa'i bsam pa phun sum tshogs pa byang chub kyi sems yin te /
NK114(ye)001:899: de yang dang po smon 'jug byang chub kyi sems
NK114(ye)001:900: gnyis bskyed nas bslab bya la tshul bzhin bslab pas
NK114(ye)001:901: 'dun pa sa lta bu dang lhag pa'i bsam pa
NK114(ye)001:902: gser lta bu nas sems bskyed stobs 'phel nas lam
NK114(ye)001:903: gong nas gong du bgrod pa'i shing rta'i sgyu 'phrul
NK114(ye)001:904: gyi thabs la drangs pas rang nyid gcig pu zhi
NK114(ye)001:905: bde don du gnyer ba'i lta ba ngan pa nyams
NK114(ye)001:906: te don gnyis kyi yon tan phun sum tshogs par
NK114(ye)001:907: byed do // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK114(ye)001:908: byang chub sems kyi phan yon bshad pa /
NK114(ye)001:909: sems bskyed kyi ngo bo ngos bzung ba /
NK114(ye)001:911: byang chub kyi sems ji ltar bskyed pa'i tshul bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:913: ming don gnas 'gyur pa'i phan yon /
NK114(ye)001:915: srid pa'i mtsho las 'don pa'i phan yon no //
NK114(ye)001:917: rgyu sdig pa dang 'bras bu sdug bsngal gyi tshogs
NK114(ye)001:918: mang pos mnar ba'i 'khor ba rgyal po'i btson ra
NK114(ye)001:919: lta bur tshud nas bdag tu 'dzin pa dang sred
NK114(ye)001:920: sogs nyon mongs pas bcings pa'i gang zag tha chad
NK114(ye)001:921: pa rnams kyang byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa'i
NK114(ye)001:923: rgyal ba rnams kyi sras kyi ming gi cod pan thob cing /
NK114(ye)001:924: don gnas 'gyur te tshul de la rab tu dga'
NK114(ye)001:925: zhing dad par gyur nas 'jig rten na dkar phyogs
NK114(ye)001:926: skyong ba'i lha rnams kyis dngos su basngagasa shing mchod
NK114(ye)001:927: par byed la / rigs drug gi gtso bo lha
NK114(ye)001:928: mir bcas pa'i 'gro ba mtha' dag gis kyang mchod
NK114(ye)001:929: cing bstod la phyag 'tshal ba la sogs pas bsti
NK114(ye)001:930: stang byed pa'i 'os su 'gyur ba yin no //
NK114(ye)001:931: dpe la lar sems skyes mod la zhes snang ba ltar na'ang /
NK114(ye)001:932: sems bskyed ma thag pa la'ang skyes pa'i tha snyad thogs pas 'gal bar mi gzung ngo //
NK114(ye)001:933: gnyis pa dge 'bras 'phel che ba'i phan yon ni /
NK114(ye)001:934: rang bzhin ye nas dag kyang thog ma med pa
NK114(ye)001:935: nas bdag tu 'dzin pa'i ma rig pas bsgribs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:936: steng du srid par 'phen pa'i las kun nas slong
NK114(ye)001:937: ba'i nyon mongs rags pa mngon gyur du skyes nas
NK114(ye)001:938: sgo gsum nyes pa'i dbang du 'gyur ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:939: phra ba 'og 'gyu'i tshul du'ang las sna tshogs sogs
NK114(ye)001:940: par byed pa'i kun rtog mang pos sems rgyud khebs
NK114(ye)001:941: nas rnam par grol ba'i snang ba'i go skabs cung
NK114(ye)001:942: zad kyang med pa'i 'gro ba'i rgyud ni dper na
NK114(ye)001:943: nyi zla'i snang ba med pa'i mun nag gi dus
NK114(ye)001:944: su skar ma'i snang ba tsam yang mi mthong bar
NK114(ye)001:945: char sprin stug po 'khrigs shing khebs pa'i nam mkha'
NK114(ye)001:946: lta bu'o // de lta bu'i mun nag stug po'i
NK114(ye)001:947: gnas skabs su sprin bar nas drag cing gtum pa'i
NK114(ye)001:948: glog gi 'od 'khyug pa na phyogs rer snang ba
NK114(ye)001:949: cung zad ston kyang yun du mi gnas pa lta
NK114(ye)001:950: bu'i 'gro ba'i shes rgyud rtag tu de ltar yin
NK114(ye)001:951: pa la res 'ga' phyi rol pa'i lam gyi dkar
NK114(ye)001:953: bsam gzugs kyi sems thob pa la sogs pa'am /
NK114(ye)001:954: nang pa'i bstan pa dang 'phrad kyang rnam grol gyi
NK114(ye)001:955: 'bras bu thob byed kyi thabs kyi ma zin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:956: legs smon gyi tshul khrims sogs kyi dge ba la
NK114(ye)001:957: yun ring zhing rgyun brtan pa ma yin par skabs
NK114(ye)001:958: 'agra goms shing bsags pa'i las ni bsod nams tsam
NK114(ye)001:962: smyigs ma rnams rang rang gi 'bras bu lan gcig
NK114(ye)001:963: smin nas rtsa ba skams par 'gyur ba bzhin du
NK114(ye)001:964: 'bras bu lha dang mi'i bde ba la longs spyod
NK114(ye)001:965: nas myong stobs kyis dge ba'i rtsa ba zad cing
NK114(ye)001:967: der ma zad byang chub sems kyis ma zin na
NK114(ye)001:968: nyan rang gi lam gyi thabs shes kyis zin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:969: dge rtsa des kyang rang 'bras thob ste lhag med
NK114(ye)001:970: du 'das zin nas byams snying rje dang mngon shes
NK114(ye)001:971: rdzu 'phrul sogs kyi sgo nas gzhan don cung zad
NK114(ye)001:972: byed pa la sogs pa'i yon tan rnams kyang zad
NK114(ye)001:973: pa bzhin du med par 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:974: de bzhin du sems bskyed khyad par can gyi thabs
NK114(ye)001:975: des ma zin pa'i sbyin pa la sogs pa'i spyod
NK114(ye)001:976: phyogs dag kyang ltar snang du rgya chen po dang
NK114(ye)001:977: grangs mang po la brtson na'ang sa bcad pa'am tshogs
NK114(ye)001:978: chen po rdzogs pa med de zor ba rtul pos
NK114(ye)001:980: bskyed rim bsgom pa'ang byis pa lha khang la blta
NK114(ye)001:981: ba dang 'dra bar gnas skabs nyams dga' ba tsam
NK114(ye)001:982: las med la / rtsa rlung dang rdzogs rim bsgoms
NK114(ye)001:983: pas gnas skabs bde gsal mi rtog pa'i nyams kyi
NK114(ye)001:985: mngon shes dang rdzu 'phrul phra mo grub pa'ang mthar
NK114(ye)001:986: nyams par 'gyur bas dbyar dus su bung ba rnams
NK114(ye)001:987: me tog gi rtsi bcud myong nas gshog rtsal gyis
NK114(ye)001:988: nam mkhar lding zhing 'phur na'ang ston dus sa 'og
NK114(ye)001:990: des na rang sems dge ba'i lam la ma zhog
NK114(ye)001:991: bzhin du gzhan gyi mig sngar zang zing gi gtong
NK114(ye)001:992: phod dang / lus ngag gi spyod tshul dang lag
NK114(ye)001:993: len rgya gang che'i sgo nas 'di byas dang 'di
NK114(ye)001:994: bsgrub kyi kha skad mang po 'dod na'ang sems rgyud
NK114(ye)001:995: la yar skyed spu tsam med pas dgos pa chung
NK114(ye)001:997: sems bsrung brtul zhugs ma gtogs pa //
NK114(ye)001:998: brtul zhugs mang pos ci zhig bya //
NK114(ye)001:1000: yang rang gis gang nyams su len pa'i chos de'i
NK114(ye)001:1001: gnad rtogs pa'i thos pa tsam yang med par glen
NK114(ye)001:1002: sgom u tshugs kyis sems gcur nas sems gnas dang
NK114(ye)001:1003: nyams snang phran bu re thob pa lta sgom mthon
NK114(ye)001:1004: po'i gdings tshad rnyed do snyam du rlom kyang de
NK114(ye)001:1005: ni thar pa'i lam tsam du'ang 'gro dka' na theg
NK114(ye)001:1006: pa chen po'i lam du mi 'gyur ba ni smos
NK114(ye)001:1008: 'phags pa ting nge 'dzin mchog dam pa las /
NK114(ye)001:1009: dge slong khyod mang du thos pa spangs te bsam
NK114(ye)001:1010: gtan gyi ting nge 'dzin la 'jug go zhes ma
NK114(ye)001:1011: smra zhig / ngas bltas na khyed kyi shes rab ni /
NK114(ye)001:1012: sbrang bu'i 'dab mas nyi zla sgrib par 'dod pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:1013: dmus long gis ri rab lhun po la 'dzeg par 'dod pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:1014: gru gzings med par rgya mtsho la brgal bar 'dod pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:1015: bya 'dab ma chag pa nam mkha' la 'phur bar 'dod pa bzhin khyed kyang de dang 'dra'o //
NK114(ye)001:1017: tshul de dag la bsam nas /
NK114(ye)001:1019: sems sbyong ba yi spyod pa ni //
NK114(ye)001:1020: nges par de srid spyad par bya //
NK114(ye)001:1022: gzhan gyis mthong du yod pa'i gzugs brnyan mi che
NK114(ye)001:1023: yang bsam pa bzang po byang chub kyi sems kyis
NK114(ye)001:1024: rgyud sbyang na nam zhig sgo gsum longs spyod dang
NK114(ye)001:1025: bcas pas bya ba ci bsgrub thams cad theg pa
NK114(ye)001:1026: chen po'i lam du ngang gis 'gyur zhing gnas lugs
NK114(ye)001:1027: zab mo'i rtogs pa'ang rtsol med du 'byung bar nges
NK114(ye)001:1028: pas don 'di las zab pa ni mkhas pa stong
NK114(ye)001:1029: gi zhal bsdur kyang med nges pa yin zhes kho
NK114(ye)001:1030: bo'i bla ma rnams kyis gsungs so //
NK114(ye)001:1031: de yang sa gzhi bzang po tha bar ma gyur
NK114(ye)001:1032: zhing gshin pas brten pa'i zhing sa la sa bon
NK114(ye)001:1033: ci btab kyang dge ba ste legs pa'i lo tog
NK114(ye)001:1034: phun sum tshogs pa rgyas shing 'phel ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:1035: khyad par dpag bsam gyi shing bskal pa ma zhig
NK114(ye)001:1036: gi bar du 'bras bu thug pa med par je
NK114(ye)001:1037: 'phel du 'gro bar za ma tog bkod pa las
NK114(ye)001:1038: bshad pa ltar byang chub kyi sems kyis zin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1039: dge ba'i ljon shing ni srid pa na 'bras bu
NK114(ye)001:1040: lha dang mi'i bde ba'i longs spyod mang zhing rgya
NK114(ye)001:1041: che ba la longs spyad kyang zhi ba byang chub
NK114(ye)001:1042: chen po'i bar du 'phel bar 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:1043: gsum pa 'khor ba'i mtsho las 'don pa'i phan yon ni /
NK114(ye)001:1044: 'di ltar las dang nyon mongs pa'i me 'obs chen
NK114(ye)001:1045: pos bskor zhing 'du byed kyi chu srin gdug pa
NK114(ye)001:1046: can dang 'grogs pa'i sdug bsngal gyi chu bo gting
NK114(ye)001:1047: zab cing rgya che ba kun gyi snod du gyur
NK114(ye)001:1048: pa 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho tshul bzhin ma yin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1049: rnam par rtog pa'i rba rlabs drag pos thar ba'i
NK114(ye)001:1050: gru gzings bshig pa can shin tu 'jigs su rung
NK114(ye)001:1051: zhing skyi g.ya' ba'i gnas yin kyang /
NK114(ye)001:1052: sems can rnams kyis ni de ltar mi shes par
NK114(ye)001:1053: dga' zhing zhen pas khyim ltar rab tu bzung nas
NK114(ye)001:1054: de las thar pa'i thabs la mi brtson pa'i steng
NK114(ye)001:1055: / slar yang 'khor bar 'gyur ba'i las sna tshogs
NK114(ye)001:1056: bsags nas thar ba'i dus skabs dka' ba de las
NK114(ye)001:1057: sems can 'ga' zhig tsam ma yin par mtha' yas
NK114(ye)001:1058: pa'i sems can de thams cad gdon pa'i snying stobs
NK114(ye)001:1059: chen po' go cha bgo ba ni byang chub mchog
NK114(ye)001:1060: tu sems bskyed pa kho na yin te /
NK114(ye)001:1062: srid pa'i sdug bsngal brgya phrag gzhom 'dod cing //
NK114(ye)001:1063: sems can mi bde gsal bar 'dod pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:1064: bde mang brgya phrag spyad par 'dod pas kyang //
NK114(ye)001:1065: byang chub sems nyid rtag tu btang mi bya //
NK114(ye)001:1067: gnyis pa sems bskyed kyi ngo bo ngos bzung ba la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:1068: byang chub sems kyi ngo bo spyir bstan pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:1069: smon 'jug gi ngo bo bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:1071: 'dir gang zhig skyes bu chen pa'i lam don du
NK114(ye)001:1072: gnyer ba ni snying rje chen po'i gzhan dbang du
NK114(ye)001:1073: gyur pa yin pas de la rang gi tshe 'di'i
NK114(ye)001:1074: don dang / phyi ma mngon mtho tsam thob pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1075: phyir dge ba la brtson pa skyes bu chung ngu
NK114(ye)001:1076: don dang / dang / bdag nyid gcig pu 'khor
NK114(ye)001:1077: ba las thar ba'i don du sems nas lam la
NK114(ye)001:1078: brtson pa skyes bu 'bring gi bsam pa gnyis po
NK114(ye)001:1080: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad
NK114(ye)001:1081: thog ma med pa nas drin chen pos bskyangs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1082: pha mar ma gyur pa gcig tsam yang med la
NK114(ye)001:1083: / pha mar gyur pa'i sems can de rnams da
NK114(ye)001:1084: lta 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho brgal dka' bar bying nas
NK114(ye)001:1085: mi bzod pa'i sdug bsngal drag po'i rgyu 'bras dag
NK114(ye)001:1086: gis mnar bzhin thar ba'i thabs bsgrub mi shes pas
NK114(ye)001:1087: long ba bshes med thang dkyil du lus pa lta
NK114(ye)001:1089: 'o na snying rje ba'i sar bzhag pas kyang mi 'ong gi /
NK114(ye)001:1090: 'di thams cad skyon dang sdug bsngal kun dang bral
NK114(ye)001:1091: nas bde ba dang yon tan dam pa gong na
NK114(ye)001:1092: gzhan med pa ci 'dra ba zhig la dgod /
NK114(ye)001:1093: thabs dang nus pa ji lta bu zhig gis de
NK114(ye)001:1094: dag gi don bdag gis ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin
NK114(ye)001:1095: du bya nus pa zhig 'ong snyam du bkres pa
NK114(ye)001:1096: zasa la gdung ba dang skom pa chur gdung ba
NK114(ye)001:1097: bzhin sems can 'ba' zhig gi don du bsam pa
NK114(ye)001:1098: ni snying rje'i gzhan don la dmigs pa yin la
NK114(ye)001:1099: / yang 'di snyam du sems can rnams gang la
NK114(ye)001:1100: dgod par bya ba'i 'bras bu bla na med pa
NK114(ye)001:1101: ni rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang yin kyang
NK114(ye)001:1102: / / da lta bdag gis sems can gcig gi don yang rdzogs par bya mi nus la /
NK114(ye)001:1103: de bas 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po'am lha'i dbang
NK114(ye)001:1104: po brgya byin dang tshangs pa lta bur gyur kyang
NK114(ye)001:1105: mi nus / de bas nyan rang dgra bcom pa
NK114(ye)001:1106: gnyis kyi go 'phang la gnas kyang sems can nyung
NK114(ye)001:1107: zad tsam thar ba la 'god par nus kyi thams
NK114(ye)001:1108: cad mkhyen pa la 'god par mi nus pas /
NK114(ye)001:1109: 'gro ba mtha' yas pa'i gnas skabs dang mthar thug
NK114(ye)001:1110: gi don thams cad rdzogs par byed nus pa de
NK114(ye)001:1111: yang shes bya'i rnam pa thams cad chags thogs med
NK114(ye)001:1112: par mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang gzhan phan gyi phrin
NK114(ye)001:1113: las mnga' ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang
NK114(ye)001:1114: kho na yin pas bdag gis ci nas kyang de
NK114(ye)001:1115: nyid bsgrub par bya snyam nas don du gnyer ba
NK114(ye)001:1116: ni shes rab kyis rdzogs byang la dmigs pa yin
NK114(ye)001:1117: pas de la byang chub kyi sems zhes gragsa te
NK114(ye)001:1119: sems bskyed pa ni gzhan don phyir //
NK114(ye)001:1120: yang dag rdzogs pa'i byang chub 'dod //
NK114(ye)001:1121: ces pa ltar don gnyis sam zur gnyis dang ldan pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:1122: gang gi ched du bya ba snying rjes gzhan don la dmigs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:1123: gang ched du bya ba shes rab kyis rdzogs byang
NK114(ye)001:1124: la dmigs pa gnyis po de ma tsha nga na
NK114(ye)001:1125: / gzhan la phan 'dod tsam dang rdzogs byang thob 'dod tsam ni sems bskyed du mi 'gro ste /
NK114(ye)001:1126: mthar thug rdzogs byang thob par mi 'dod na sems
NK114(ye)001:1127: can gzhan la gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi phan
NK114(ye)001:1128: bde gzhan ji lta bu 'dod kyang byams pa dang
NK114(ye)001:1129: snying rje tsam las mi 'da' la /
NK114(ye)001:1130: rang don du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang
NK114(ye)001:1131: thob par 'dod pa tsam nyan thos kyi gzhung las
NK114(ye)001:1133: byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems gsum gyi khyad
NK114(ye)001:1134: par 'di shin tu zhib par shes dgos te theg
NK114(ye)001:1135: chen gyi lam thams cad kyi rtsa ba yin pas
NK114(ye)001:1136: kha bshad tsam la gdeng bcas pas mi 'ong ngo
NK114(ye)001:1137: // gnyis pa smon 'jug gi ngo bo bye brag tu bshad pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:1138: spyir smon 'jug gi khyad par la rgya bod kyi
NK114(ye)001:1139: mkhas pa rnams bzhed pa mi 'dra ba mang du
NK114(ye)001:1140: snang ste / so so'i skye bo'i sems bskyed smon sems dang /
NK114(ye)001:1141: 'phags lam thob nas 'jug par bzhed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:1142: cho gas ma blang ba smon pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:1143: blangs pa 'jug par bzhed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:1144: nyams len gyi bya bas ma zin pa ni smon sems dang /
NK114(ye)001:1145: zin pa 'jug par bzhed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:1146: 'bras bur dam bca' ba smon sems dang /
NK114(ye)001:1147: rgyu la dam bca' ba 'jug sems su 'dod pa
NK114(ye)001:1148: la sogs pa mang du snang yang skye 'phags kyi
NK114(ye)001:1149: sems bskyed la 'dod pa tsam ma gtogs gzhan rnams
NK114(ye)001:1150: phal cher rgyal sras zhi ba lha'i rjes su 'brangs
NK114(ye)001:1151: par 'dra yang dgongs pa len tshul mi 'dra'o //
NK114(ye)001:1152: de'ang skabs 'dir dgongs pa len tshul gang gi rjes su 'brang nas 'chad ce na /
NK114(ye)001:1153: 'di ltar smon 'jug gi sems gnyis po gzhan don du dmigs pa la 'dra yang /
NK114(ye)001:1154: ji skad du sdong po bkod pa las /
NK114(ye)001:1155: rigs kyi bu sems can gyi tshogs na gang bla
NK114(ye)001:1156: na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub
NK114(ye)001:1158: de bas kyang sems bla na med pa yang dag
NK114(ye)001:1159: par rdzogs pa'i byang chub la mngon par zhugs pa
NK114(ye)001:1160: de ni ches rnyed par daka'o //
NK114(ye)001:1161: zhes pa'i don zhi ba lhas dpe la sbyar nas bshad pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:1163: byang chub sems de mdor bsdu na //
NK114(ye)001:1164: rnam pa gnyis su shes bya ste //
NK114(ye)001:1165: byang chub smon pa'i sems dang ni //
NK114(ye)001:1166: byang chub 'jug pa nyid yin no //
NK114(ye)001:1168: bye brag ji ltar shes pa ltar //
NK114(ye)001:1169: de bzhin mkhas pas 'di gnyis kyi //
NK114(ye)001:1170: bye brag rim bzhin shes par bya //
NK114(ye)001:1171: zhes pa'i dgongs pa ni dper na yul w+aa ra n+aa s+ai lta bu zhig tu 'gro 'dod na /
NK114(ye)001:1172: rgyu 'gro ba'i bya ba la ma zhugs gong du
NK114(ye)001:1173: 'bras bu yul de la dmigs nas der 'gro bar
NK114(ye)001:1175: 'bras bu rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyi go 'phang la
NK114(ye)001:1176: dmigs nas de bsgrub par dam 'cha' ba ni smon
NK114(ye)001:1178: de ltar dam bcas nas de'i bslab bya bdag dang
NK114(ye)001:1179: gzhan sems cad thams cad bde ba 'dod pa dang
NK114(ye)001:1180: / sdug bsngal mi 'dod pa la khyad par med
NK114(ye)001:1181: par shes nas rang gzhan gnyis ka'i bde ba bsgrub
NK114(ye)001:1182: pa dang sdug bsngal bsal ba'i thabs la mnyam par
NK114(ye)001:1184: bdag gzhan gyi bde sdug barje ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:1185: bdag la 'di phyi thams cad du nyams nyes ji lta bu byung yang sla yi /
NK114(ye)001:1186: de bas sems can kho na bde ba'i thabs zhig
NK114(ye)001:1187: bya'o snyam du bdag pas gzhan gcesa par 'dzin pa
NK114(ye)001:1188: gsum du bzhag pa de'ang smon pa sems bskyed kyi
NK114(ye)001:1189: bslab pa' gnas mdor bsdus tsam bstan pa yin gyi
NK114(ye)001:1190: / spros na yul sems can blos mi btang ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:1191: mthun rkyen tshogs bsags pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:1192: sems bskyed kyi phan yon dran pa sogs mang yang
NK114(ye)001:1193: dngos shugs gang rung du gsum po der ma 'dus
NK114(ye)001:1194: pa med la / smon pa'i sems de'i ngo bo
NK114(ye)001:1195: ni byams pa la sogs pa'i tshad med pa bzhi
NK114(ye)001:1196: po la yang dag par gnas te /
NK114(ye)001:1198: byams pa de la gzhan gyi don du smon pa yang byams pa chen po dang /
NK114(ye)001:1201: btang snyoms chen po yin la /
NK114(ye)001:1203: 'o na byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems gsum
NK114(ye)001:1204: gyi khyad par shes dgos zhes pa ci yin zhe
NK114(ye)001:1205: na / spyir dam bca' dang ma 'brel yang ldan
NK114(ye)001:1206: 'dod la sogs pa tsam la byams sogs su 'jog
NK114(ye)001:1207: rung bas de dang sems bskyed gnyis mi gcig na'ang
NK114(ye)001:1208: 'dir smon sems dang ngo bo gcig par bshad pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1209: byams sogs ni don gnyis ldan pa'i sems gcig la
NK114(ye)001:1210: ldog pas dbye ba ste rdzogs byang thob 'dod kyi
NK114(ye)001:1211: na / byams pa / sgrib gnyis bral 'dod kyi snying rje /
NK114(ye)001:1212: rdzogs byang de nyid gtan bde yin pas mi 'bral ba la dga' ba /
NK114(ye)001:1213: sems can thams cad la khyad med du de ltar
NK114(ye)001:1214: 'dod pa btang snyoms te de yang dam bca' dang
NK114(ye)001:1215: 'brel ba'o // yang na bdag gzhan mnyam pa sogs
NK114(ye)001:1216: gsum po de'i ngo bo tshad med bzhi la gnas
NK114(ye)001:1217: zhes pa'i don de go sla'o //
NK114(ye)001:1218: yang 'di ltar dper na yul der 'gro 'dod pa
NK114(ye)001:1219: tsam gyis mi sleb pas dngos su 'gro ba'i bya
NK114(ye)001:1220: ba la dam bcas te dam bcas pa bzhin lam
NK114(ye)001:1222: rdzogs byang thob par 'dod pa tsam gyis mi chog
NK114(ye)001:1223: gi de'i rgyu la bslab dgos pas rgyu pha rol
NK114(ye)001:1224: tu phyin pa drug bsgrub pa la dam 'acha'a ba
NK114(ye)001:1225: dang / dam bcas pa bzhin ci nus su sgrub pa ni 'jug pa'i sems yin te /
NK114(ye)001:1226: de yang 'gro bzhin pa'i tshe na'ang 'gro 'dod mi
NK114(ye)001:1227: 'dor ba ltar lam sgrub bzhin pa'i tshe na'ang 'bras
NK114(ye)001:1228: bu la dmigs pa mi 'dor bas smon sems dang
NK114(ye)001:1229: 'brel zhing lam bsgrub pa'i bya ba sbyin sogs dngos
NK114(ye)001:1230: la bslab pa 'jug pa'i bslab bya yin kyang de'i
NK114(ye)001:1231: tshe bya ba de la sngar dam bcas pas khyab
NK114(ye)001:1232: pa'i cha de 'jug sems su bzhag pa yin nam
NK114(ye)001:1234: 'jug pa sems bskyed de yi bslab bya ni pha rol tu phyin pa drug la bslab pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:1235: 'gro 'dug la sogs pa'i spyod yul lung ma bstan
NK114(ye)001:1236: rnams kyang gzhan don du smon lam gyis yongs su
NK114(ye)001:1237: dag pa'i dge bar bsgyur ba'i tshul rnams la bsten
NK114(ye)001:1238: par bya'o // smon 'jug de gnyis kyi ngo bo yang 'phags seng gnyis kyis sems la bshad de /
NK114(ye)001:1239: 'di ltar gzhan don du rdzogs byang la dmigs pa'i gtso sems te /
NK114(ye)001:1240: de yang yid kyi rnam par shes pa la bzung gi gzhan ni ma yin te /
NK114(ye)001:1241: gzhan don dang byang chub la dmigs mi nus pa'i phyir snyam du dgongs so //
NK114(ye)001:1242: de ltar yang mdo 'grel nyi khri snang ba las /
NK114(ye)001:1243: sems bskyed pa zhes bya ba la sems ni rnam par shes pa ste rnam par rig pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:1244: rnam par shes pa gang yin zhe na yid kyi
NK114(ye)001:1245: rnam par shes pa ste dkar po'i chos thams cad
NK114(ye)001:1246: la dmigs pa ni de la srid pa'i phyir ro
NK114(ye)001:1248: thogs med sku mched sems byung du bzhed de /
NK114(ye)001:1250: byang chub sems dpa'i smon lam gyi mchog ni sems bskyed pa ste zhes pas /
NK114(ye)001:1251: smon lam ni 'dun pa gtso che bas sems byung 'dun par bzhed cing /
NK114(ye)001:1253: don gnyis ldan pa'i sems byung ba //
NK114(ye)001:1254: zhes pa'i 'grel par dbyig gnyen gyis don gnyis la dmigs pa'i sems pa ni sems bskyed pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:1255: zhes sems pa la bshad do //
NK114(ye)001:1257: sems bskyed pas ni sems byung zhar la skye bas gnyis kar bzhed do //
NK114(ye)001:1259: sems ni don gyi ngo bo rang stobs rig /
NK114(ye)001:1260: sems byung don gyi khyad par rang stobs rig /
NK114(ye)001:1261: ces pa'i don ltar 'dir yang gzhan don dang rdzogs
NK114(ye)001:1262: byang gi don gnyis po'i ngo bo tsam la gtso
NK114(ye)001:1263: sems yid kyi rnam par shes pas dmigs dus de
NK114(ye)001:1264: dag gi khyad par la de'i 'khor du yod pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1265: sems byung rnams kyis dmigs pa'i tshul gyis mtshungs pa
NK114(ye)001:1266: lngas yul gcod par byed pa las snga ma gnyis
NK114(ye)001:1267: kyis gtso sems yid shes gtso che ba la dgongs
NK114(ye)001:1268: la / sku mched gnyis kas rang rang gi bzhed
NK114(ye)001:1269: pa'i sems byung de dag gtso che ba tsam la
NK114(ye)001:1270: la / dgongs shing / kun mkhyen chen po'i bzhed
NK114(ye)001:1271: pa ni de thams cad kyi dgongs pa gcig tu
NK114(ye)001:1272: blangs nas gtso sems tsam dang sems byung tsam kho
NK114(ye)001:1273: nas ma yin par sems dang sems byung thams cad
NK114(ye)001:1274: mtshungs bar ldan pa'i sgo nas bskyed pa la dgongs
NK114(ye)001:1275: pas thams cad gnad gcig go snyam mo //
NK114(ye)001:1276: yang byang sems kyi spyod pa rgya chen po la
NK114(ye)001:1277: bslab mi nus pas smon sems kho na bskyed pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1278: tshul ni / rgyal po la gdams pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:1279: rgyal po chen po khyod ni bya ba mang la byed pa mang ba ste /
NK114(ye)001:1280: thams cad kyi thams cad rnam pa thams cad kyi
NK114(ye)001:1281: thams cad du sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa
NK114(ye)001:1282: la bslab pa nas shes rab kyi pha rol tu
NK114(ye)001:1283: phyin pa'i bar la slob mi bzod na /
NK114(ye)001:1284: 'di ltar rgyal po chen po rdzogs pa'i byang chub la 'dun pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:1294: rtag tu rgyun mi 'chad par dran par gyis shig /
NK114(ye)001:1299: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas dang /
NK114(ye)001:1300: so so'i skye bo thams cad dang /
NK114(ye)001:1301: bdag gi 'das pa dang ma 'ongs pa dang da
NK114(ye)001:1302: ltar byung ba'i dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad bsdus
NK114(ye)001:1303: te rjes su yi rang ba'i mchog gis rjes su
NK114(ye)001:1305: rjes su yi rang nas kyang sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK114(ye)001:1307: nyan thos rnams la mchod par phul cig /
NK114(ye)001:1308: phul nas kyang sems can thams cad dang thun mong du gyis shig /
NK114(ye)001:1309: de nas sems can thams cad thams cad mkhyen pa
NK114(ye)001:1310: nyid kyi go 'phang thob par bya ba'i phyir dang
NK114(ye)001:1311: / sangs rgyas kyi chos thams cad yongs su rdzogs
NK114(ye)001:1312: par bya ba'i phyir nyin gcig bzhin du dus gsum
NK114(ye)001:1313: du bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1315: rgyal po chen po khyod de ltar zhugs la rgyal po gyis shig /
NK114(ye)001:1316: rgyal po'i srid kyang mi nyams so //
NK114(ye)001:1317: byang chub kyi tshogs kyang yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:1318: zhes pa 'dis smon pa'i mtshan nyid legs par bstan
NK114(ye)001:1319: cing snyigs dus kyi sems can rnams la phan pa
NK114(ye)001:1321: gsum pa sems bskyed kyi dbye ba bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK114(ye)001:1322: gnas skabs dang grogs kyi dbye ba /
NK114(ye)001:1326: ji skad bshad pa'i sems bskyed de la gnas skabs
NK114(ye)001:1327: kyi dbye ba'i sgo nas gnyis nas drug gi bar
NK114(ye)001:1328: te / gnyis su dbye na tshogs gnyis la ltos nas sam /
NK114(ye)001:1329: phyi sems can la dmigs pa gtso che ba so so'i skye bo'i sems bskyed kun rdzob pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:1330: nang sems nyid la dmigs pa gtso che ba 'phags
NK114(ye)001:1331: rgyud kyi sems bskyed don dam pa'i rang bzhin gnyis
NK114(ye)001:1332: te / byang chub tu sems bskyed pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:1333: chos thams cad nam mkha' ltar mtshan nyid med cing
NK114(ye)001:1334: ye nas 'od gsal ba rnam par dag pa de
NK114(ye)001:1335: la ni byang chub ces bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:1336: de dang mthun pa'i sems lnga na ma skyes pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1337: sems rin po che skyes pa la ni byang chub
NK114(ye)001:1338: tu sems bskyed pa zhes bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:1339: zhes de gnyis rgyu dang 'bras bu'i rnam pa can du bstan to //
NK114(ye)001:1341: dag par byed pa tshul khrims /
NK114(ye)001:1343: grol bar byed pa shes rab ste bslab pa gsum la ltos te gsum dang /
NK114(ye)001:1344: yang na nyes spyod sdom pa /
NK114(ye)001:1346: sems can don byed de tshul khrims gsum la ltos pa'i sems bskyed gsum ste /
NK114(ye)001:1348: gang kha na ma tho ba sdom pa'i sems dang /
NK114(ye)001:1349: dge ba'i chos sdud pa'i sems dang /
NK114(ye)001:1350: sems can smin par byed pa'i sems te sems bskyed pa 'di gsum la nan tan du bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:1352: lam gyi khyad par gyis bzhi ru dbye na /
NK114(ye)001:1353: tshogs sbyor gyi lam na khams kyi sgrib pa phyogs
NK114(ye)001:1354: gcig kyang ma dag pas chos nyid mngon sum du
NK114(ye)001:1355: ma mthong par don spyi'i tshul du 'jal bas mos
NK114(ye)001:1356: pas spyod pa'i sems bskyed dang /
NK114(ye)001:1357: dang po'i sa nas bzungs bdun pa'i bar la bdag
NK114(ye)001:1358: gzhan mnyam pa nyid du rtogs shing khams kyi sgrib
NK114(ye)001:1359: pa phyogs gcig dag nas ye shes kyi mthong ba
NK114(ye)001:1360: gsal bas lhag bsam dag pa'i sems bskyed dang /
NK114(ye)001:1361: dag pa sa gsum na khams kyi sgrib pa sngar
NK114(ye)001:1362: bas kyang dag ste sa brgyad par nyon yid log
NK114(ye)001:1363: ste rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK114(ye)001:1364: dgu par yid shes dang sgo lnga log pas so
NK114(ye)001:1365: so yang dag par rig pa bzhi'i ye shes dang
NK114(ye)001:1367: bcu pa yid shes kyi byed las dag nas phrin las phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:1368: de ltar bzhi po la dbang 'byor bas rnam par smin pa'i sems bskyed dang /
NK114(ye)001:1369: sa bcu'i rgyun mthar khams kyi sgrib pa sems sems
NK114(ye)001:1370: byung gi bag chags kun gzhi dang bcas pa dag
NK114(ye)001:1371: pas sangs rgyas kyi sa na sgrib pa spangsa pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1372: semasabaskyeda te bzhi'o // de'ang sangs rgyas kyi sa na
NK114(ye)001:1373: cho ga las byung ba dang 'khor ba'i shes pa
NK114(ye)001:1374: can med kyang khams de'i yon tan ci yod pa
NK114(ye)001:1375: thams cad mngon du gyur nas thugs rje chen po'i
NK114(ye)001:1376: mdzad pa dus las mi yol ba don dam pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1377: ye shes dang ro gcig tu gyur pa de la
NK114(ye)001:1378: semasabaskyeda te bzhi'o // bya'o // de bzhin du lnga ru dbye na /
NK114(ye)001:1379: tshogs lam na las dang po pa'i sems bskyed /
NK114(ye)001:1380: sbyor lam na yongs su sbyang ba byas pa'i sems bskyed /
NK114(ye)001:1381: mthong lam na chos mthong ba'i sems bskyed /
NK114(ye)001:1382: sgom lam na rnam par grol ba'i sems bskyed /
NK114(ye)001:1383: mi slob pa'i lam na bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1384: sems bskyed de lam lnga'i rjes su 'gro ba'i sems
NK114(ye)001:1387: las dang po pa'i zhes pa nas bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i sems bskyed pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:1388: rab 'byor 'di la ma zhugs pa gzhug par bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:1389: zhugs pa yongs su sbyang bar bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:1391: 'phags pa'i lam bden pa sgom par bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:1392: sangs rgyas kyi spyan sgrib pa med pa thob par bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:1395: pha rol tu phyin pa drug la ltos nas de snyed kyi grangs te /
NK114(ye)001:1397: pha rol tu phyin pa drug dang ldan pa'i sems yangs pa /
NK114(ye)001:1398: tshad med pa nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas thams
NK114(ye)001:1399: cad dang thun mong du ma gyur pa ste zhes
NK114(ye)001:1400: so // de yang rang don du sbyin sogs sgrub
NK114(ye)001:1401: pa nyan rang la'ang yod kyang de ni byang chub
NK114(ye)001:1402: dam pa'i gtan gyi gegs su che ba'i tshul /
NK114(ye)001:1403: dmyal bar 'gro ba byang chub la //
NK114(ye)001:1404: gtan gyi gegs byed ma yin te //
NK114(ye)001:1405: nyan thos dang ni rang sangs rgyas //
NK114(ye)001:1408: yang mos spyod kyis tshogs sbyor gnyis dang /
NK114(ye)001:1409: 'phags pa slob pa'i sa bcu po so so'i sa
NK114(ye)001:1410: mtshamsa na lhag par gyur pa'i yon tan gyi sgo
NK114(ye)001:1411: nas de dang ldan pa'i sems bskyed la dbye ba
NK114(ye)001:1412: nyi shu rtsa gnyis su phye ba'i tshul ni /
NK114(ye)001:1414: de yang sa gser zla ba me //
NK114(ye)001:1415: gter dang rin chen 'byung gnas mtsho //
NK114(ye)001:1416: rdo rje ri sman bshes gnyen dang //
NK114(ye)001:1417: yid bzhin nor bu nyi ma glu //
NK114(ye)001:1418: rgyal po mdzod dang lam po che //
NK114(ye)001:1419: bzhon pa bkod ma'i chu dang ni //
NK114(ye)001:1420: sgra snyan chu bo sprin rnams kyis //
NK114(ye)001:1421: rnam pa nyi shu rtsa gnyis so //
NK114(ye)001:1422: zhes pa de dag dpe yin la /
NK114(ye)001:1423: dpe des mtshon pa'i sems bskyed kyi grogs gnyis dang /
NK114(ye)001:1424: dpe dang dpe can gnyis kyi chos mthun pa nyi
NK114(ye)001:1425: shu rtsa gnyis rnams rim bzhin sbyar nas 'chad de
NK114(ye)001:1426: / grogs byang chub don gnyer gyi 'dun pa dang mtshungs ldan du gyur ba'i sems bskyed chos can /
NK114(ye)001:1427: dpe sa lta bu yin te /
NK114(ye)001:1428: chos dkar po'i yon tan thams cad kyi rten byed pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:1429: de bzhin du gzhan la'ang sbyar te /
NK114(ye)001:1430: grogs gzhan la phan phyir phyin drug la sbyor 'dod
NK114(ye)001:1431: kyi bsam pa dang mtshungs ldan dpe gser lta bu
NK114(ye)001:1432: chos gnas skabs thams cad du 'gyur ba med pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1433: phyir / grogs bsam pa de nyid lhag par gyur
NK114(ye)001:1434: pas lhag pa'i bsam pa dang dpe zla ba tshes
NK114(ye)001:1435: pa lta bu chos dkar po'i yon tan gong nas
NK114(ye)001:1437: grogs phar phyin drug la dngos su sbyor bas sbyor
NK114(ye)001:1438: ba dang dpe me lta bu chos shing gi bye
NK114(ye)001:1439: brag gi me bzhin gong nas gong du 'gro ba'i
NK114(ye)001:1440: phyir / grogs sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa
NK114(ye)001:1441: dang dpe gter lta bu chos mi zad cing re
NK114(ye)001:1443: grogs tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang dpe rin po che'i 'byung gnas dang 'dra ste /
NK114(ye)001:1444: chos yon tan rin po che thams cad kyi 'byung khungs yin pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:1445: grogs bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa dang dpe
NK114(ye)001:1446: mtsho lta bu chos me mtshon la sogs pa'i gnod
NK114(ye)001:1448: grogs brtson 'grus kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang dpe rdo rje lta bu yin te /
