NK114(ye)001:1449: chos mi shigs shing sra ba nyid kyis gang la'ang thogs pa med pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:1450: grogs bsam gtan gyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang
NK114(ye)001:1451: dpe ri lta bu chos rnam rtog gi rlung gis
NK114(ye)001:1453: grogs shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang
NK114(ye)001:1454: dpe sman lta bu chos nyon mongs pa'i nad sel
NK114(ye)001:1455: ba'i phyir / grogs thabs la mkhas pa dang dpe
NK114(ye)001:1456: bshes gnyen lta bu chos dus thams cad du phan
NK114(ye)001:1458: grogs smon lam gyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang
NK114(ye)001:1459: dpe yid bzhin gyi nor bu chos gang ltar 'dod
NK114(ye)001:1460: pa'i don thams cad 'grub pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:1461: grogs stobs kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang dpe
NK114(ye)001:1462: nyi ma lta bu chos gdul bya'i rgyud kyi lo
NK114(ye)001:1463: tog thams cad bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:1464: grogs ye shes kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang
NK114(ye)001:1465: dpe glu dbyangs lta bu chos kun gyi yid dang
NK114(ye)001:1466: mthun par chos ston pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:1467: grogs mngon par shes pa dang dpe rgyal po lta
NK114(ye)001:1468: bu chos bya ba thams cad la rang dbang dang
NK114(ye)001:1469: bcas pa'i phyir / grogs bsod nams dang ye shes
NK114(ye)001:1470: kyi tshogs gnyis dang dpe mdzod khang lta bu chos
NK114(ye)001:1471: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs mang pa'i gnas
NK114(ye)001:1472: bcas pa'i phyir / yin pa'i phyir / grogs byang
NK114(ye)001:1473: chub kyi phyogs kyi chos dang dpe lam po che
NK114(ye)001:1474: lta bu chos dus gsum gyi 'phags pa rnams gshegs
NK114(ye)001:1475: shing rjes su gshegs pa'i lam po che lta bu
NK114(ye)001:1476: bcas pa'i phyir / yin pa'i phyir / yin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1477: phyir / grogs zhi gnas dang lhag mthong dang dpe
NK114(ye)001:1478: bzhon pa bzang po lta bu chos mtha' gnyis su
NK114(ye)001:1479: mi gol bar dbu ma'i lam du 'gro ba'i phyir
NK114(ye)001:1480: bcas pa'i phyir / yin pa'i phyir / yin pa'i phyir / / grogs gzungs dang spobs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:1481: dpe bkod ma'i chu lta bu chos chos kyi tshig
NK114(ye)001:1482: don mi zad par 'dzin cing gzhan la ston pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1483: phyir / grogs chos kyi dga' ston dang dpe sgra
NK114(ye)001:1484: snyan lta bu chos gdul bya 'dun par byed pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1486: grogs bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam dang dpe chu bo
NK114(ye)001:1487: lta bu chos rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i rgya
NK114(ye)001:1489: grogs chos kyi sku dang mtshungs par ldan pa'i sems bskyed chos can /
NK114(ye)001:1490: dpe sprin lta bu yin te /
NK114(ye)001:1491: chos dga' ldan gyi gnas na bzhugs pa la sogs pa ston pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:1493: de dag gi sa mtshams ni /
NK114(ye)001:1494: dang po gsum tshogs lam gsum /
NK114(ye)001:1495: sbyor ba me lta bu sbyor lam /
NK114(ye)001:1496: de nas pha rol tu phyin pa bcu sa bcu /
NK114(ye)001:1497: mngon shes sogs lnga dag pa sa gsum spyi la yod /
NK114(ye)001:1498: chos kyi dga' ston sogs gsum sa bcu pa kho na la yod do //
NK114(ye)001:1499: yang mi zad pa brgyad cu dang sbyar na 'dun
NK114(ye)001:1500: pa nas shes rab kyi bar sngar dang 'dra la
NK114(ye)001:1501: / de nas tshad med pa bzhi bshes gnyen lta bu yin te /
NK114(ye)001:1502: gnas skabs thams cad du phan par 'dod pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:1503: mngon par shes pa lnga yid bzhin gyi nor bu lta bu yin te /
NK114(ye)001:1504: gzhan don bsgrub pa la mthu thob pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:1505: bsdu dngos bzhi nyi ma lta bu yin te /
NK114(ye)001:1506: gdul bya'i rgyud kyi lo tog 'phel bar byed pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:1507: so so yang dag par rig pa bzhi glu dbyangs lta bu yin te /
NK114(ye)001:1508: gdul bya'i 'dul ba'i chos ston pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:1509: rton pa bzhi rgyal po lta bu yin te /
NK114(ye)001:1510: kun gyi yid ches pa'i gnas yin pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:1511: tshogs gnyis byang phyogs zhi lhag gsum 'dra la /
NK114(ye)001:1512: gzungs dang spobs dang ldan pa ni bkod ma lta bu ste /
NK114(ye)001:1513: chu 'dzin zhing mi zad par 'byin pa dang chos mthun par thos pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:1514: ma thos pa'i chos kyi tshig dang don 'dzin zhing mi zad par 'byin pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:1515: chos kyi sdom bzhi ston pa sgra snyan lta bu ste /
NK114(ye)001:1516: gdul bya'i yid dang mthun pa'i chos ston pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:1518: 'dir bshad pa kun bsdoms na brgyad cu yod pa
NK114(ye)001:1519: de dag byang chub sems dpa' rnams la zad mi
NK114(ye)001:1520: shes pa yod pas mi zad pa brgyad cu zhes
NK114(ye)001:1521: bya ste blo gros mi zad pa'i mdo las byung
NK114(ye)001:1522: ba'o // de las gzhan rnams go sla la /
NK114(ye)001:1524: drang don la mi rton nges don la rton /
NK114(ye)001:1525: kun rdzob la mi rton don dam la rton /
NK114(ye)001:1526: gang zag la mi rton chos la rton /
NK114(ye)001:1527: rnam shes la mi rton ye shes la rton pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:1528: rton ces pa ni yid ches par bya ba'i don to //
NK114(ye)001:1530: 'dus byas thams cad mi rtag pa /
NK114(ye)001:1531: zag pa dang bcas pa sdug bsngal ba /
NK114(ye)001:1532: chos thams cad stong zhing bdag med pa /
NK114(ye)001:1533: mya ngan las 'das pa zhi ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:1534: 'dir sa mtshams kyis dbye ba'i sems bskyed la bshad
NK114(ye)001:1535: tshul gnyis byung ba'i snga ma ni yum gyi mdo
NK114(ye)001:1537: phyi ma ni blo gros mi zad pa'i mdo dang sbyar ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:1538: gang ltar yang 'dun pa la sogs pa rnams ni grogs yin pas /
NK114(ye)001:1539: sems bskyed ni gzhan don du rdzogs byang don gnyer gyi sems bskyed yin la /
NK114(ye)001:1540: grogs rnams ni skabs de dang der lhag par gyur pa tsam ste /
NK114(ye)001:1541: dper na sa dang po la sbyin pa lhag par gyur pa lta bu'o //
NK114(ye)001:1542: 'di dag la dpal ye shes grags pa la sogs pas /
NK114(ye)001:1543: dang po gsum smon sems dang lhag ma bcu dgu 'jug sems su bzhed kyang /
NK114(ye)001:1544: 'dir kun mkhyen chen po'i bzhed pa ltar na de
NK114(ye)001:1545: la sogsa pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i thugs rgyud kyi
NK114(ye)001:1546: dkar chos kyi yon tan thams cad la bsam pas
NK114(ye)001:1547: smon pa'i cha dang 'jug pas lag len la khyab
NK114(ye)001:1548: par byed pa'i cha gnyis yod pas de gnyis po
NK114(ye)001:1549: re re la thams cad 'du ba yin no //
NK114(ye)001:1550: de'ang dper na 'dun pa la'ang blos byang chub la 'dun pa tsam ni smon pa'i sems yin la /
NK114(ye)001:1551: 'dun pa des drangs nas byang chub sems dpa'i spyod
NK114(ye)001:1552: pa gzhan la slob pa'i cha nas 'jug sems yin
NK114(ye)001:1553: no // gnyis pa phan yon gyi dbye ba la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:1554: smon sems kyi phan yon dang /
NK114(ye)001:1557: gang zag gang zhig rang nyid kho na lha'i bde
NK114(ye)001:1558: ba la sogs pa'i 'jig rten pa'i legs pa'i yon
NK114(ye)001:1559: tan don du gnyer nas rtag tu gcod pa med
NK114(ye)001:1560: pa'i sgo 'aphara te rgyun du sgo phye ba'i longs
NK114(ye)001:1561: spyod kyi khang pa'i nang nas slong mo ba'i gang
NK114(ye)001:1562: zag rnams kyi yid la zas gos sogs gang 'dod
NK114(ye)001:1563: pa thams cad ster ba'i sgo nas thams cad tshim
NK114(ye)001:1564: par byed pa las de dag gi sems la 'khrugs
NK114(ye)001:1565: pa cung zad kyang mi ster ba mgon med zas
NK114(ye)001:1567: sbyin pa'i don du sgo la gtan pa med par
NK114(ye)001:1568: byas pa'i phyir gtan pa med pa'i mchod sbyin byed
NK114(ye)001:1569: pa po zhes basngagasa shing bkur sti byed par 'os
NK114(ye)001:1570: pa dang / mchod sbyin de lta bu gcig gis 'dod khams kyi dbang phyug tu'ang 'gyur na /
NK114(ye)001:1571: mtha' dag pa'i sems can thams cad kyi don du
NK114(ye)001:1572: dmigs te de rnams la phan pa'i phyir rdzogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1573: byang chub kyi go 'phang thob par smon pa'i sems
NK114(ye)001:1574: rgyun chags su yod na smos ci dgos kyang thang
NK114(ye)001:1575: cig tsam skyes pas kyang gnas skabs ngan song du
NK114(ye)001:1576: 'gro ba'i rgyu sdig pa zad nas der skye ba'i
NK114(ye)001:1577: sgo gcod cing lha dang mi'i gnas rigsa su skyes
NK114(ye)001:1578: nas tshe ring zhing nad med la longs spyod dang
NK114(ye)001:1579: ldan pa la sogs pa'i bde ba la brten cing
NK114(ye)001:1580: phan pa'i bsam pa bzang po'i rgyu mthun gyi 'bras
NK114(ye)001:1581: bu'i yon tan zad mi shes pa gong du 'phel
NK114(ye)001:1582: nas nam zhig byang chub chen po thob pa'i rgyu
NK114(ye)001:1583: yang byed do // mdor bsdu na /
NK114(ye)001:1584: 'phags pa dge ba'i rtsa ba yongs su 'dzin pa las /
NK114(ye)001:1585: sh+aa ra dwa ti'i bu sems dang po bskyed pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1586: bsod nams kyi phung po ni ngan don tsam dang
NK114(ye)001:1587: cung zad tsam ma yin te /
NK114(ye)001:1590: bskal pa 'bum gyis kyang brjod par mi nus na /
NK114(ye)001:1591: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis sems bskyed pa'i bsod nams kyi tshad shes pa lta ga la 'gyur /
NK114(ye)001:1594: dmigs pa can zhig gis bskal pa gang+g+aa'i klung gi
NK114(ye)001:1595: bye ma snyed du dge ba'i rtsa ba byas pa
NK114(ye)001:1596: bas / gzhan 'ga' zhig gis nyi ma gcig gam nyi ma phyed dam /
NK114(ye)001:1597: se gol gtogs pa gcig tu byang chub tu sems bskyed pa bsod nams che'o //
NK114(ye)001:1599: gnyis pa 'jug sems kyi phan yon ni /
NK114(ye)001:1600: smon sems de las kyang khyad par 'jug pa'i sems kyi yon tan ni mtha' yas te /
NK114(ye)001:1602: byang chub smon pa'i sems las ni //
NK114(ye)001:1604: ji ltar 'jug pa'i sems bzhin du //
NK114(ye)001:1605: bsod nams rgyun chags 'byung ba min //
NK114(ye)001:1608: gzhan don du byang chub thob 'dod kyi bsam pa
NK114(ye)001:1609: tsam ma yin par de'i ched du dngos su rgyu
NK114(ye)001:1610: phyin drug la sbyor bar dam bca' bas khyab pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1611: 'jug sems de cho ga la brten nas blangs pa
NK114(ye)001:1613: phyir ldog pa med pa'i sems kyis mtha' yas pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1614: 'gro ba thams cad sangs rgyas kyi sar sgrol ba
NK114(ye)001:1615: la dam bca' bar shin tu yid brtan pa rgyud
NK114(ye)001:1617: dus de nas bzung ste bag med cing rnam par
NK114(ye)001:1618: g.yeng ba dang gnyid log pa la sogs pa'i spyod
NK114(ye)001:1619: lam lung ma bstan par gyur kyang byang chub chen
NK114(ye)001:1620: po'i rgyu bsod nams kyi shugs bar ma chad par
NK114(ye)001:1621: rgyun chags su yod par gsungs pas na dge ba
NK114(ye)001:1622: gang yang gnas skabs der sems bskyed mngon gyur bas
NK114(ye)001:1623: ma zin kyang sngar thob la ma nyams pa yod
NK114(ye)001:1624: pa'i mthus chu thigs chu bo chen po la 'dres
NK114(ye)001:1625: pa bzhin theg chen thar pa cha mthun gyi dge
NK114(ye)001:1626: ba'i rgyun nyid sems bskyed pa po de'i sems rgyud
NK114(ye)001:1629: rigs kyi bu byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa
NK114(ye)001:1630: dang ldan pa de'i lus dang ngag dang sems kyi
NK114(ye)001:1631: brtsams pa thams cad don yod pa ste rtag tu
NK114(ye)001:1632: dge ba 'ba' zhig tu ro gcig par 'gyur ro
NK114(ye)001:1634: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa'i sa las kyang 'thad pa dang bcas par bashada de /
NK114(ye)001:1636: gang nas bzung ste sems can khams //
NK114(ye)001:1637: mtha' yas rab tu sgrol ba'i phyir //
NK114(ye)001:1638: mi ldog pa yi sems kyis su //
NK114(ye)001:1639: sems te yang dag blangs gyur pa //
NK114(ye)001:1640: de nas bzung ste gnyid log gam //
NK114(ye)001:1641: bag med gyur kyang bsod nams shugs //
NK114(ye)001:1642: rgyun mi 'chad pa du ma zhig /
NK114(ye)001:1643: nam mkha' mnyam par rab tu 'byung //
NK114(ye)001:1645: legs bzang gis ni zhus pa las //
NK114(ye)001:1646: dman mos sems can don gyi phyir //
NK114(ye)001:1647: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyis gsungs //
NK114(ye)001:1649: gsum pa blo stobs kyi dbye ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:1650: spyir rgyal sras byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis lam
NK114(ye)001:1651: bsgrub pa ni snying rje chen po la sogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1652: thabs mkhas dang shes rab phun sum tshogs pa dang
NK114(ye)001:1653: ldan pa'i stobs kyis dus thung ngu la spyod pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1654: sgo re rer bslabs pas kyang thabs shes de lta
NK114(ye)001:1655: bu dang mi ldan pa rnams kyis bskal pa mang
NK114(ye)001:1656: por sgrub dgos pa'i tshogs kyang 'dums par 'gyur la
NK114(ye)001:1657: / de yang byang sems lam gyi mu tshod kyis
NK114(ye)001:1658: mthar thug gi 'bras bu'i sar myur du phyin pa
NK114(ye)001:1659: ma yin pa dang yin pa'i sgo nas dbye na
NK114(ye)001:1660: / / nges pa dang ma nges pa la 'jug
NK114(ye)001:1661: pa'i phyag rgya'i mdo las dang dpe lnga'i sgo nas
NK114(ye)001:1662: bstan pa'i tshul 'dir yang bstan te /
NK114(ye)001:1663: phyugs kyi shing rta lta bus 'gro ba'i byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK114(ye)001:1664: de bzhin du glang po che'i shing rta lta bus 'gro ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:1665: nyi ma dang zla ba lta bus 'gro ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:1666: sogs khongs nas nyan thos kyi rdzu 'phrul lta bus 'gro ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:1667: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rdzu 'phrul lta bus 'gro ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:1668: de las snga ma gnyis ni phyir ldog la /
NK114(ye)001:1669: phyi ma gsum phyir mi ldog pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:1670: dang po ni skyes bu la la zhig gis sangs
NK114(ye)001:1671: rgyas kyi zhing lnga'i rdul snyed kyi 'jig rten gyi
NK114(ye)001:1672: khams 'da' bar 'dod nas phyugs kyi shing rta la
NK114(ye)001:1673: zhon te song bas yun ring mo nas dpag tshad
NK114(ye)001:1675: phyir dpag tshad brgyar tshur rlung gis phul nas song
NK114(ye)001:1676: na des 'jig rten gyi khams de snyed 'da' mi
NK114(ye)001:1677: nus pa ltar theg chen gyi sde snod mi 'dzin
NK114(ye)001:1678: mi klog kha ton mi byed tshul bzhin yid la
NK114(ye)001:1679: mi byed par nyan thos dag la brten cing nyan
NK114(ye)001:1680: thos kyi sde snod klog pa la sogs pa ste
NK114(ye)001:1681: / de ni byang chub las phyir ldog go //
NK114(ye)001:1682: yang la la zhig 'jig rten gyi khams de snyed
NK114(ye)001:1683: 'da' bar 'dod nas glang po che'i shing rta la
NK114(ye)001:1684: gzhon te song nas lo brgyas dpag tshad nyis stong
NK114(ye)001:1685: du song nas sngar ltar phyir ded pa ltar theg
NK114(ye)001:1686: pa che chung mnyam par klog pa sogs byed pa'ang
NK114(ye)001:1687: byang chub las phyir ldog go //
NK114(ye)001:1688: yang sangs rgyas kyi zhing de snyed 'da' bar 'dod
NK114(ye)001:1689: pas nyi ma dang zla ba'i rlung gi shing rtas
NK114(ye)001:1690: song na yun ring mo nas sleb pa ltar /
NK114(ye)001:1691: nyan thos kyi theg pa tshig gcig tsam yang klog
NK114(ye)001:1692: pa sogs mi byed pa ni ring mo zhig nas
NK114(ye)001:1694: zhing de dag 'da' bar 'dod nas nyan thos kyi
NK114(ye)001:1695: rdzu 'phrul gyis 'gro na snga ma las myur yang
NK114(ye)001:1696: ha cang myur du 'da' mi nus pa ltar theg
NK114(ye)001:1697: pa chen po 'ba' zhig klog pa sogs byed cing
NK114(ye)001:1698: byang chub sems dpa' rnams la gus pa dang zhes
NK114(ye)001:1699: sa bsten cing chos tshol la /
NK114(ye)001:1700: srog gi phyir yang theg chen mi spong zhing byang
NK114(ye)001:1701: chub sems dpa' ma lobs pa rnams la mi brnyes
NK114(ye)001:1702: pa de ni snga ma las ches myur bar rdzogs
NK114(ye)001:1703: byang 'grub pa'o // yang zhing de dag 'da' bar
NK114(ye)001:1704: 'dod nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i rdzu 'phrul lta bus
NK114(ye)001:1705: 'gro na sems kyi skad cig gis phyin pa ltar
NK114(ye)001:1706: byang chub tu sems bskyed nas zab cing rgya che
NK114(ye)001:1707: ba'i chos la mos shing gzhan don 'ba' zhig sems
NK114(ye)001:1708: pas byams snying rje phyin drug rton pa bzhi sogs
NK114(ye)001:1709: la rang gnas nas gzhan yang 'god pa ni ches
NK114(ye)001:1710: myur bar rdzogs pa'i byang chub 'grub pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:1711: de yang dang po gnyis so skye mi brtan pa /
NK114(ye)001:1712: gsum pa so skye brtan pa /
NK114(ye)001:1713: bzhi pa ma dag sa bdun pa /
NK114(ye)001:1714: lnga pa dag pa sa gsum la gnas pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:1715: de ltar theg pa chen po'i sa lam bgrod pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1716: brtul zhugs te tshul myur ba dang bul ba matha'a
NK114(ye)001:1717: yas pa yod pa ltar gang zag so so'i sems
NK114(ye)001:1718: bskyed pa'i blo stobs chung 'bring chen po'i dbye bas
NK114(ye)001:1719: yang gsum ste 'og tu 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:1720: de yang blo stobs shin tu chen poo'i thabsa la mkhas pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:1721: brtson 'grus phul du byung ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:1722: shes rab zab cing rno ba'i stobs kyis myur ba'i
NK114(ye)001:1723: tshad grangs meda gsum gyi dam bca' bzhag pa'ang 'jig
NK114(ye)001:1724: par 'gyur te de tsam yang mi thogs pa yin
NK114(ye)001:1725: no zhes pa'am / yang na grangs med gsum gyis
NK114(ye)001:1726: sgrib gnyis kyis dam la bzhag pa mtha' dag 'jig
NK114(ye)001:1727: pa'i tshul gyis 'tshang rgya ba yin no //
NK114(ye)001:1729: bzhi pa sems bskyed tshul bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK114(ye)001:1737: dpe ji ltar na 'bras bu smin pa las sa bon dgos kyang /
NK114(ye)001:1738: sa bon de sa la lhung ba'am btab pa tsam
NK114(ye)001:1739: gtso mi che yi rkyen chu lud drod gsher sogs
NK114(ye)001:1740: dang 'dzoms nas de la 'bras bu smin pa gtso
NK114(ye)001:1741: che ba yin pa de bzhin du byang chub kyi
NK114(ye)001:1742: sems bcos ma ma yin pa skye ba la dang
NK114(ye)001:1743: po bcos te sems bskyed dgos kyang /
NK114(ye)001:1744: byang chub kyi sems mchog de bskyed pa tsam ni
NK114(ye)001:1745: so so'i skye bo'i rgyud la byang chub dam pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1746: sa bon bzhag pa tsam yin gyi /
NK114(ye)001:1747: lam gzhan gyis bar ma chod par mthar thug gi
NK114(ye)001:1748: 'bras bu thob pa'i nges pa med pas mi gtso
NK114(ye)001:1749: ste / sems bskyed de mi nyams shing gong du
NK114(ye)001:1750: 'phel ba la dman pa'i lam gegs su che ba'i
NK114(ye)001:1751: ste / phyir ro // de yang 'di ltar nyan
NK114(ye)001:1752: rang gi lam ni nyon mongs pa bye brag pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1753: gnyen po tsam du 'gro ba dper na sman gyi
NK114(ye)001:1754: bye brag tha dad pa res nad bye brag pa
NK114(ye)001:1756: byang chub kyi sems ni lha'i bdud rtsi dang mtshungs te /
NK114(ye)001:1757: des nad mtha' dag pa drungs nas 'byin pa ltar
NK114(ye)001:1758: sgrib pa mtha' dag gi gnyen por 'gro zhing sangs
NK114(ye)001:1759: rgyas thob par byed pa'i rgyu ma nor ba yin
NK114(ye)001:1760: pas so // des na dman lam gyis 'phrog mi
NK114(ye)001:1761: nus pa'i byang chub kyi sems bcos ma ma yin
NK114(ye)001:1762: pa skyes pa ni gtso che ba yin no //
NK114(ye)001:1763: gnyis pa sems bskyed skye ba'i rgyu dngos ni /
NK114(ye)001:1764: de la stobs rnam pa gsum las ni byang chub
NK114(ye)001:1765: kyi sems yang dag pa rgyud la skye bar 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:1766: bas na / thog mar sems kyi skad cig re
NK114(ye)001:1767: re la'ang dran pa dang shes bzhin rgyun mi 'chad
NK114(ye)001:1768: pas sems can thams cad la sems snyoms pa'i byams
NK114(ye)001:1769: pa la brten nas snying rje chen po'i blo sbyang
NK114(ye)001:1770: bas na / bar bya ste / de ltar ma
NK114(ye)001:1771: byas na dbang rtul las dang po pa rnams la
NK114(ye)001:1772: sems bskyed rnal ma mi skye la /
NK114(ye)001:1773: de ma skyes na shes rab zab mo dang yang 'brel chad par 'gyur bas so //
NK114(ye)001:1774: de ltar goms pas snying rje che bar gyur ba ni byang chub sems kyi rtsa ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:1775: byang chub kyi sems ni thams cad mkhyen pa'i rgyu yin te /
NK114(ye)001:1777: thams cad mkhyen pa'i rgyu ni byang chub kyi sems so //
NK114(ye)001:1778: rtsa ba ni snying rje chen po'i zhes so //
NK114(ye)001:1779: de bzhin du bsod nams kyi tshogs bsags pa rnams kyi rgyud la byang chub kyi sems skye yi /
NK114(ye)001:1780: bsod nams med pa la ni ma yin te /
NK114(ye)001:1781: dper na dbul po tha chad kyi khyim du rgyal
NK114(ye)001:1782: po mnga' thang can mgron du 'bod mi 'os pa
NK114(ye)001:1783: lta bu'o // des na sangs rgyas rnams kyis sngon
NK114(ye)001:1784: thugs bskyed pa'i dus su che ste 'khor los sgyur
NK114(ye)001:1785: ba'i rgyal srid phul ba nas chung ste 'ga' zhig
NK114(ye)001:1786: dbul por gyur pa na r+ts+wa'i sgron me phul nas
NK114(ye)001:1787: thugs bskyed pa sogs tshogs bsags pa sngon du btang
NK114(ye)001:1788: ba ltar rgyun du thabs sna tshogs pa'i sgo nas
NK114(ye)001:1790: sems bskyed len pa'i dus su'ang ci 'byor pa'i mchod
NK114(ye)001:1791: pa dngos su bshams pas mtshon yan lag bdun pa
NK114(ye)001:1792: la sogs pa'i tshogs bsags khyad par can ngag 'don
NK114(ye)001:1793: gyi tshig bton pa kho na tsam ma yin par
NK114(ye)001:1794: gnad du smin par bya dgos gsungs /
NK114(ye)001:1795: mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba ni sdig pa
NK114(ye)001:1796: zil gyis gnon pa'i rten gyi stobs kyang yin la
NK114(ye)001:1797: sdom pa kun gyi rten gzhi yang yin pas sngon
NK114(ye)001:1798: du 'gro dgos par ma zad skabs 'dir theg chen
NK114(ye)001:1799: thun mong ma yin pa'i skyabs 'gro sems bskyed kyi
NK114(ye)001:1800: rten nam rgyur byas nas len pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:1801: de rnams la go rim bzhin du bsam pa'i stobs dang /
NK114(ye)001:1803: rgyu yi stobs zhes su bshad pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:1804: gzhan yang mdo sde rgyan las /
NK114(ye)001:1805: grogs stobs rgyu stobs rtsa ba'i stobs //
NK114(ye)001:1806: thos stobs dge ba goms pa las //
NK114(ye)001:1807: mi brtan pa dang brtan 'byung ba //
NK114(ye)001:1808: gzhan gyis bstan pa'i sems bskyed bshad //
NK114(ye)001:1809: ces grogs dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyis bskul ba'i stobs las sems bskyed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:1810: rgyu rigs sad pa'i stobs dang /
NK114(ye)001:1811: sngon dge ba'i rtsa ba goms pa'i stobs dang /
NK114(ye)001:1812: theg chen gyi sde snod la thos pa byas pa'i stobs dang /
NK114(ye)001:1813: da lta tshogs bsags pa'i dge ba goms pa'i stobs las skye ba ste stobs lngar bshad cing /
NK114(ye)001:1814: slob dpon thogs med kyis snying rje pad dkar dang
NK114(ye)001:1815: chos bcu pa'i mdo'i rjes su 'brangs nas rkyen bzhi
NK114(ye)001:1816: dang stobs bzhi las skye bar gsungs te /
NK114(ye)001:1818: de bzhin gshegs pa'i phun sum tshogs pa mthong nas sems bskyed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:1819: de bzhin du sems bskyed kyi phan yon mthong nas dang /
NK114(ye)001:1820: dam pa'i chos 'jig pa'i nyes dmigs mthong nas dang /
NK114(ye)001:1821: sems can sdug bsngal ba mthong nas sems bskyed pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:1823: theg chen gyi rigs sad pa rgyu'i stobs dang /
NK114(ye)001:1824: skyes bu dam pa la bsten cing de las chos
NK114(ye)001:1825: la thos shing de'i don la sems pa sogs sbyor
NK114(ye)001:1826: ba'i stobs dang / rang gi dge ba goms pa'i mthu rang gi stobs dang /
NK114(ye)001:1827: gzhan gyis bskul ba'i mthus sems bskyed pa gzhan gyi stobs so //
NK114(ye)001:1828: de dag gi don nye bar bsdu na /
NK114(ye)001:1829: sangs rgyas la dmigs pa'i dad pa /
NK114(ye)001:1830: sems can la dmigs pa'i snying rje /
NK114(ye)001:1831: byang chub sems kyi phan yon bshad pa gsum ni
NK114(ye)001:1832: sems bskyed skye ba'i rgyu ma nor ba yin par
NK114(ye)001:1833: rig par bya'o // gnyis pa rten gyi gang zag ni /
NK114(ye)001:1834: sems bskyed skye ba'i rten gyi gang zag ni /
NK114(ye)001:1835: sems tsam pa'i lugs dang dbu ma pa'i lugs su grags pa gnyis su rnam pa gnyis bstan te /
NK114(ye)001:1836: dang po ltar na smon sems tsam la ma nges kyang /
NK114(ye)001:1837: 'jug sdom ma thob pa thob pa'i rten du ni /
NK114(ye)001:1839: so so thar pa rigs bdun gyi //
NK114(ye)001:1840: rtag tu sdom gzhan ldan pa la //
NK114(ye)001:1841: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa yi //
NK114(ye)001:1842: skal ba yod kyis gzhan du min //
NK114(ye)001:1844: so thar rigs brgyad las bsnyen gnas ni dus khrims tsam yin pas rten du mi rung la /
NK114(ye)001:1847: dge slong gsum po re re la pha ma gnyis rer phye ba'i drug dang /
NK114(ye)001:1848: dge slob ma'i sdom pa ste rigs bdun po gang rung gi sdom ldan nam /
NK114(ye)001:1850: dkon mchog t+aa la la'i mdor /
NK114(ye)001:1851: rgyal dang rgyal ba'i chos la dad gyur cing //
NK114(ye)001:1852: byang chub bla na med la'ang dad gyur la //
NK114(ye)001:1853: rgyal sras rnams kyi spyod la dad byed na //
NK114(ye)001:1854: blo dang ldan pa rnams kyi sems skye'o //
NK114(ye)001:1855: zhes bsam pa'ii rten gtso che ba'i tshul bshad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:1858: nam mkha'i snying po'i mdo la sogs par rten ma nges par bstan cing /
NK114(ye)001:1859: dkon mchog brtsegs pa las kyang /
NK114(ye)001:1860: de'i tshe chos kyi rnam grangs 'di bshad pa na /
NK114(ye)001:1865: lto 'phye chen po bgrang ba las 'das pa dag
NK114(ye)001:1866: gis bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1867: byang chub tu sems bskyed do zhes so //
NK114(ye)001:1868: de ltar mdo de dag gi dgongs pa'i rjes su
NK114(ye)001:1869: phyogs te lus kyi rten ma nges par bzhed pa
NK114(ye)001:1870: ni dbu ma pa'i lam srol te /
NK114(ye)001:1873: rigs kyi bu mo rten dang bsam pa phun sum
NK114(ye)001:1874: tshogs pa dang ldan pas zhes lus sems kyi sgo
NK114(ye)001:1875: nas smon sems bskyed rung ba mtha' dag 'jug sdom
NK114(ye)001:1876: gyi yang rten du rung bas bsam pa phun sum
NK114(ye)001:1877: tshogs na lus rten su rung rung la skye bas
NK114(ye)001:1878: 'jug pa'i sgo snga ma las yangs par bshad pa
NK114(ye)001:1880: dmigs bsal srog mi gcod par dam 'cha' nus pa
NK114(ye)001:1881: sogs sems bskyed de'i bslab pa dang 'gal bar mi
NK114(ye)001:1882: byed pa'i sems ldan zhig med na de la skye
NK114(ye)001:1883: mi rung ste / de 'dra'i gang zag la sdom
NK114(ye)001:1884: pa phog kyang lhung ba'i snod tsam du zad pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1885: mi rung ste / phyir ro // srol gnyis po
NK114(ye)001:1886: gang gi lugs la'ang tshogsa bsags pa ni lhag par
NK114(ye)001:1887: sems bskyed skye ba'i thabs su bzhed pas shin tu
NK114(ye)001:1888: mi rung ste / phyir ro // gal che zhing
NK114(ye)001:1889: / khyad par byang sdom len pa'i dus nus pa
NK114(ye)001:1890: yod tshad kyis dkon mchog la mchod pa bsam pa
NK114(ye)001:1892: sngon bod rnams longs spyod dar zhing rgyas pa'i tshe na'ang /
NK114(ye)001:1893: dge slong rnal 'byor spyod pa d+ai pam k+aa ra la /
NK114(ye)001:1894: mang yul dang chos 'khor chen por sems bskyed zhu dus bod kyi mchod pa la ma mnyes par /
NK114(ye)001:1896: sems bskyed mi skye gsungs nas lan gnyis kyi bar du gnas khang nas gshegs /
NK114(ye)001:1897: mthar nus pa yod tshad sprugs pas /
NK114(ye)001:1898: de la brten du rung tsam yin gsungs /
NK114(ye)001:1899: de bas na bdog pa btang ba'i tshad rang gi
NK114(ye)001:1900: longs spyod la cha gsum du bcad pa'i sum cha
NK114(ye)001:1902: sum cha gcig bla ma la phul /
NK114(ye)001:1903: sum cha gcig rang gi 'tsho ba'i rkyen du bdag gir bya bar bshad do //
NK114(ye)001:1904: gsum pa cho ga dngos bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK114(ye)001:1915: sems bskyed skye ba'i rgyu thun mong ma yin pa
NK114(ye)001:1916: ni sems can kun kyang sems kyi rang bzhin 'od
NK114(ye)001:1917: gsal zhing 'dus ma byas pa bde bar gshegs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1918: chos khams rgya mtsho lta bu smin rung gi tshul
NK114(ye)001:1919: du yod pas sa bon la myu gu bzhin de'i
NK114(ye)001:1920: snying po can yin pas cho ga'am brda can gyi
NK114(ye)001:1921: sgo nas kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems bskyed pas
NK114(ye)001:1922: / mthar thug don dam pa'i sems bskyed mtshan nyid pa bsgom stobs kyis thob pa'i tshul /
NK114(ye)001:1923: zla ba sgron me'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:1924: bde gshegs snying pos 'gro ba yongs la khyab //
NK114(ye)001:1925: sems ni rgya chen mchog tu rab bskyed de //
NK114(ye)001:1926: 'gro ba 'di dag ma lus sangs rgyas rgyu //
NK114(ye)001:1928: de yang sa bon las myu gu skye ba'i bdag rkyen chu lud la sogs pa yin pa ltar /
NK114(ye)001:1929: rigs de mngon du sad nas byang chub mchog tu
NK114(ye)001:1930: sems bskyed pa'i bdag po'i rkyen ni theg chen dge
NK114(ye)001:1931: ba'i bshes gnyen mtshan nyid dang ldan pa la rab
NK114(ye)001:1932: tu bsten pas des slob ma'i blo bcos te sdom
NK114(ye)001:1934: gnyis pa blo bcos pa dngos ni /
NK114(ye)001:1935: theg pa chen po'i rigs can gyi slob ma rnams
NK114(ye)001:1936: kyi 'dod pa'i mchog byang chub sems kyi sdom pa
NK114(ye)001:1937: ji ltar re ba bzhin cho ga'i sgo nas sbyin
NK114(ye)001:1938: nus pa'i yid bzhin noora bu lta bu'i bla ma
NK114(ye)001:1939: sdom pa dang ldan la theg pa chen po'i don
NK114(ye)001:1940: la mkhas pa'i yon tan mchog mnga' zhing /
NK114(ye)001:1941: byang chub kyi sems kyis thugs rgyud yongs su gang ba ni len pa'i yul te /
NK114(ye)001:1942: sdom pa ni nyi shu pa las /
NK114(ye)001:1943: bla ma sdom la gnas shing mkhas //
NK114(ye)001:1944: nus dang ldan las blang bar bya //
NK114(ye)001:1946: de lta bu'i bla ma des thog 1mar dge ba srid pa 'khor ba'i mtha' la skyo ba bskyed /
NK114(ye)001:1947: bar 3du dge ba zhi ba mya ngan las 'das pa'i mtha' la zhen pa dgag /
NK114(ye)001:1948: mtha' 2mar dge ba mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pa'i
NK114(ye)001:1949: stong nyid snying rje'i snying po can gyi byang chub
NK114(ye)001:1950: kyi sems la spro ba bskyed pa'i chos rnams dang
NK114(ye)001:1955: rin po che'i phung po'i mdo sogs las legs par
NK114(ye)001:1956: gsung pa'i byang chub sems kyi yon tan dpag tu
NK114(ye)001:1957: med cing mtha' yas pa brjod par bshad pas /
NK114(ye)001:1958: de dag gi don sdom du byas nas /
NK114(ye)001:1959: sems mchog bskyed pa de ni rnyed par dka' //
NK114(ye)001:1960: sangs rgyas kyi ni sa bon lta bu dang //
NK114(ye)001:1961: dkar po'i chos rnams 'phel bas zhing sa dang //
NK114(ye)001:1962: nyes pa bsreg pas bskal pa'i me lta bu //
NK114(ye)001:1963: mi dge'i chos rnams zad pas sa 'og dang //
NK114(ye)001:1964: don rnams bsgrub pa nor bu'i rgyal po ltar //
NK114(ye)001:1965: bsam kun yongs su rdzog byed bum pa bzang //
NK114(ye)001:1966: 'khor ba'i chu la rgyu 'don lcags kyu ltar //
NK114(ye)001:1967: lha dang mi yi mchod rten lta bu ste //
NK114(ye)001:1968: mdor na rdzogs sangs rgyas kyi chos yon tan //
NK114(ye)001:1969: ji snyed yod pa de yang de snyed do //
NK114(ye)001:1970: ci'i phyir byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:1971: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad 'di las so //
NK114(ye)001:1972: gser 'gyur rtsi ltar las dang nyon mongs pa //
NK114(ye)001:1973: thams cad mkhyen pa'i kha dog nyid du byed //
NK114(ye)001:1974: sgron me lta bur sgrib pa'i mun pa yang //
NK114(ye)001:1975: ye shes snang ba gsal bar byas pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:1976: nor bu'i cod pan thogs pa'i klu rgyal ltar //
NK114(ye)001:1977: snying rje can la ngan 'gro'i 'jigs pa bral //
NK114(ye)001:1978: longs spyod kun gyis dbang gi rgyal po ltar //
NK114(ye)001:1979: ji snyed dge bas rin mi chog pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:1980: gang ba'i snod du seng ge'i 'o ma ltar //
NK114(ye)001:1981: bskal brgyar bsags pa'i las nyon kun zad 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:1982: dpa' bo bsten pa'i skyes bu ji bzhin du //
NK114(ye)001:1983: spyod ngan dgra yis mi 'jigs gang lags dang //
NK114(ye)001:1984: chags kyang zil gyis gnon pa'i rdo rje ltar //
NK114(ye)001:1985: log par zhugs kyang gzhan las khyad par 'phags //
NK114(ye)001:1986: rtsal ma rdzogs kyang seng ge'i phru gu ltar //
NK114(ye)001:1987: zil gyis gnon cing bdud rnams dngas par byed //
NK114(ye)001:1988: zla ba btang nas skar ma'i gzugs la bzhin //
NK114(ye)001:1989: lam zhugs byang sems btang nas dman mi 'os //
NK114(ye)001:1990: zla ba tshes la ji bzhin nyar min ltar //
NK114(ye)001:1991: byang sems ji bzhin de bzhin gshegs la min //
NK114(ye)001:1992: rkang lag ji bzhin snying phyung ma yin pa //
NK114(ye)001:1993: de bzhin nyan thos mchog dang byang chub sems //
NK114(ye)001:1994: 'dod spyod byang chub sems dpa'i shing rta ltar //
NK114(ye)001:1995: rnam par thar pa'i sgor gnas mchog la'ang min //
NK114(ye)001:1996: thams cad mkhyen pa nyid ldan yon tan ni //
NK114(ye)001:1997: bskal pa gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye snyed du //
NK114(ye)001:1998: de bzhin gshegs pas brjod kyang mi nus te //
NK114(ye)001:1999: sems can ji snyed yod pa de snyed la //
NK114(ye)001:2000: phan pa'i sems ldan bsod nams phung po 'thob //
NK114(ye)001:2001: sems can khams ni zad pa med phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:2003: gal te de lta bu'i bshes gnyen mtshan nyid dang
NK114(ye)001:2004: ldan pa ma rnyed na rgyal ba'i rten gyi drung
NK114(ye)001:2005: du len rung bar yang srol gnyis ka mthun la
NK114(ye)001:2006: / blo'i nus stobs che ba dag gis ni sangs
NK114(ye)001:2007: rgyas byang sems rnams mdun mkhar dmigs te len pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2008: tshul 'jam dpal zhing bkod las gsungs pa ltar lam
NK114(ye)001:2010: gnyis pa tshogs bsag pa la gsum ste /
NK114(ye)001:2011: sngon 'gro sta gon du bya ba /
NK114(ye)001:2012: bsod nams kyi zhing spyan drang ba //
NK114(ye)001:2014: dang po ni gang du sems bskyed pa'i gnas sngon
NK114(ye)001:2015: gyi dam pa rnams kyi byin gyis brlabs pa'i gnas
NK114(ye)001:2016: dang / rten khyad par du 'phags pa yod pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2017: gtsug lag khang ngam min kyang sdig can gyi skye
NK114(ye)001:2018: bos dben pa'i gnas su dri bzang sna tshogs kyi
NK114(ye)001:2019: khu bas skyang nul byed pa sogs bkod pa mdzes
NK114(ye)001:2020: shing snying du sdug par ngoma pa'i sgo nas gnas
NK114(ye)001:2022: dang po byi dor legs par byas shing /
NK114(ye)001:2024: dri bzang po'i spos chu dang /
NK114(ye)001:2025: ba byung lnga la sogs pas bran zhing chag chag gdab pa dang bcas /
NK114(ye)001:2026: sgeg chos ma yin par dkon mchog la gus pa
NK114(ye)001:2027: bskyed pa'i phyir gdong la sogs pa'i yan lag lnga
NK114(ye)001:2028: bkru zhing gos gtsang ma bgos la grags 'dod dang
NK114(ye)001:2029: rlom sems kyis ma yin par dkon mchog gsum gyi
NK114(ye)001:2030: yon tan 'ba' zhig yid la sems pa yi dad
NK114(ye)001:2031: pa dang nges shes drag pos 'phan gdugs rgyal mtshan
NK114(ye)001:2033: mchod yon zhabs bsil me tog bdug spos snang gsal dri chab zhal zas rol mo /
NK114(ye)001:2035: rdzas brgyad la sogs pa'i mchod pa'i tshogs mang pos phru ma 'debs pa ste bkram pa la /
NK114(ye)001:2036: 'di ltar e ma zhing gi rab dang phul du
NK114(ye)001:2037: gyur pa dkon mchog la bsnyen bkur du yod pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2038: bsod nams 'di ni gya nom pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:2039: dge ba'i rtsa ba chud mi za ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:2040: rnyed pa legs par rnyed do snyam du snying thag pa nas dga' zhing dgod par byed do //
NK114(ye)001:2041: gnyis pa bsod nams kyi zhing spyan drangs pa la bzhi ste /
NK114(ye)001:2044: gos rgyan byug sogs dbul ba /
NK114(ye)001:2047: mchog gsum la sogs pa'i bden pa'i stobs brjod pas
NK114(ye)001:2048: sa gzhi thams cad dag pa'i zhing khams kyi bkod
NK114(ye)001:2049: pa ltar rgya che zhing rnam par dag par gyur
NK114(ye)001:2050: ba'i dbus su gnas khang de nyid stong gsum gyi
NK114(ye)001:2051: stong chen po'i zhing khams las rgya che ba'i gzhal
NK114(ye)001:2052: med khang rin po che sna tshogs las grub cing
NK114(ye)001:2053: rgyan dang bkod pa phun sum tshogs par bsam pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2054: nang du rin po che dang pad+ma nyi zla dar
NK114(ye)001:2055: zab kyi khri blta na sdug pa mang pos mdzes
NK114(ye)001:2056: par bsam la / dam tshig gi rten rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa'i gzugs brnyan dang /
NK114(ye)001:2057: theg pa chen po'i sde snod kyi glegs bam sogs
NK114(ye)001:2058: sku gsung thugs kyi rten rab gnas can ci yod
NK114(ye)001:2059: pa mtha' dag gnas khang der bos te drangs nas
NK114(ye)001:2061: dad gus rtse gcig pas zla ba sgron ma'i mdo las byung ba /
NK114(ye)001:2062: bzhengs shig bzhengs shig stobs bcu mnga' ba'i lha //
NK114(ye)001:2063: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2064: rig pa mchog las byung ba /
NK114(ye)001:2065: ma lus sems can kun gyi mgon gyur cing //
NK114(ye)001:2066: zhes pa la sogs pa'i tshig gis spos rol dang
NK114(ye)001:2067: bcas dbyings nas ye shes sems dpa' rgyal ba sras
NK114(ye)001:2068: dang bcas pa thams cad dgug cing drangs nas dam
NK114(ye)001:2069: tshig gi rten rnams la gnyis med du gzhug pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2071: rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa rnams chos kyi dbyings dang dgongs par ro gcig pas /
NK114(ye)001:2072: gang nas byon pa'ang med de rang bzhin gyi gnas
NK114(ye)001:2073: gang du bzhugs pa'ang med de yid kyis sprul pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2074: gnas de nyid du rtag par zhugs pas /
NK114(ye)001:2075: dad mos can gyis gsol ba btab cing spyan drangs pa de mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis dgongs /
NK114(ye)001:2076: brtse ba'i thugs rje rgyun mi 'chad pas gzigs /
NK114(ye)001:2077: mdzad pa'i phrin las thams cad gzhan phan 'ba' zhig
NK114(ye)001:2078: tu 'char bas chos kyi dbyings nas gzugs kyi skur
NK114(ye)001:2079: bzhengs te 'byon pa'i 'thad pa chos nyid kyi bden
NK114(ye)001:2080: pa gzigs pa rnams la mngon sum yin mod /
NK114(ye)001:2081: las dang po pa rnams la nges shes skye ba'i phyir dpe nye bar bkod de bstan na /
NK114(ye)001:2082: mas bu sdug gu stor nas yun ring por lon
NK114(ye)001:2083: pa na re zhig cig na bu de mthong bar
NK114(ye)001:2084: gyur na bya ba gzhan thams cad bshol nas der
NK114(ye)001:2085: bsnyegs te myur du rgyug pa'am /
NK114(ye)001:2086: mdza' gcugsa dus btab pa'i dam bca' dran pa las
NK114(ye)001:2087: kyang myur bar de ma thag 'byon pa ni rgyal
NK114(ye)001:2088: ba rnams kyis phyogs bcu'i gdul bya thams cad kyi
NK114(ye)001:2089: don mnyam du mdzad pa las 'ga' zhig gi don
NK114(ye)001:2090: mdzad pa'i tshe gzhan rnams lus pa lta bu mi
NK114(ye)001:2091: mnga' yang rang gis mos pa tsam gyi mod la
NK114(ye)001:2092: de nyid du 'byon pas gdul bya'i zhing khams gzhan
NK114(ye)001:2093: du gzigs pa yol ba ste de dag tu ma
NK114(ye)001:2094: byon par 'di kho na la 'byon pa'i tha snyad
NK114(ye)001:2095: btags so // de ltar yang dkon mchog brtsegs pa las /
NK114(ye)001:2096: gang zhig rgyal ba yid byed pa //
NK114(ye)001:2097: de yi mdun na de bzhugs te //
NK114(ye)001:2098: rtag par byin gyis brlab par byed //
NK114(ye)001:2099: nyes pa kun las rnam par grol //
NK114(ye)001:2101: de lta bu'i don la nges shes bskyed nas spyan
NK114(ye)001:2102: 'dren pa'i tshig 'dir bkod pa'i don yang brtse ba
NK114(ye)001:2103: dang nus pa'i yon tan ni gang zhig 'khor ba
NK114(ye)001:2104: na gnas pa'i gdul bya ma lus shing lus pa
NK114(ye)001:2105: med pa'i sems can thams cad kun gyi sdug bsngal
NK114(ye)001:2106: las skyob pa'i mgona dang phan gdags pa'i dpung nyen
NK114(ye)001:2107: mchog tu gyur kyang bdud kyi sde dpung dang bcas
NK114(ye)001:2108: pa'i tshogs ma lus pa 'joms por mdzad pa'i dgra
NK114(ye)001:2110: de yang bdud sde dpung dang bcas pa rnams sems
NK114(ye)001:2111: can thams cad kyi khongs su mi gtogs pa zhig
NK114(ye)001:2112: ma yin kyang 'dir sems can ma lus pa'i mgon
NK114(ye)001:2113: dang bdud sde'i dgrar gsungs pa ni 'gal ba'i rgyan
NK114(ye)001:2114: du byas la / don du dgra btul ba ltar
NK114(ye)001:2115: bdud sde pham par byas kyang de dag gi ba
NK114(ye)001:2116: spu'i khung bu tsam la'ang gnod pa ma byas par
NK114(ye)001:2117: ma zad phan pa mchog nye bar bsgrub par mdzad
NK114(ye)001:2118: du byas la / do // theg chen thun mong
NK114(ye)001:2119: ma yin pa'i dgongs pa ni gdul bya 'dul byed
NK114(ye)001:2120: thams cad de bzhin gshegs pa'i rnam par 'phrul pa
NK114(ye)001:2121: bsam gyis mi khyab pa ste gzhan du 'chad do
NK114(ye)001:2122: du byas la / do // // mkhyen pa'i ye
NK114(ye)001:2123: shes kyi yon tan ni ji lta ba chos rnams
NK114(ye)001:2125: ji snyed pa chos can shes bya'i dngos po mtha'
NK114(ye)001:2126: dag chags thogs med par mkhyen cing mngon gsum du
NK114(ye)001:2127: gzigs pa yi phyogs bcu'i bcom ldan 'das rgyal ba
NK114(ye)001:2128: sras dang bcas pa thams cad bdag gi sdum pa
NK114(ye)001:2129: ste gnas khang 'dir tshogs bsags pa'i zhing dang sems
NK114(ye)001:2130: bskyed pa'i dpang por mchis te gshegs su gsol zhes
NK114(ye)001:2131: pa'o // gnyis pa khrus gsol ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:2132: de ltar spyan drangs pa'i lha tshogs rnams la 'jig
NK114(ye)001:2133: rten pa'i nye bar spyad pa dang sgo bstun nas
NK114(ye)001:2135: de la dang po 'di ltar 'jig rten phal pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2136: las kyis sprul pa ste rdo shing la sogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2137: dngos po dman pa la rtsol bas bcos te byas
NK114(ye)001:2138: pa lta bu ma yin par lha tshogs rnams 'byon
NK114(ye)001:2139: pa'i shul te lam du khrus gsol ba'i gnas kyi
NK114(ye)001:2140: khang bu brtsegs pa rin po che las grub pa
NK114(ye)001:2141: dri bsung zhim pos phyogs thams cad khyab cing rgya
NK114(ye)001:2142: khyon nam mkha'i khams thams cad gang ba'i rang bzhin
NK114(ye)001:2143: cana shel dang nor bu rin po che sna tshogs
NK114(ye)001:2144: pa'i sa gzhi khod snyoms shing mig mang ris su
NK114(ye)001:2145: bris pa ltar rnam par bkra ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:2146: ka ba mdzes shing yid du 'ong ba dang bcas
NK114(ye)001:2147: par ldan zhing g.yu dmar dang mu tig la sogs
NK114(ye)001:2148: pa rin po che'i 'od chags pa'i rnam pa'i bla
NK114(ye)001:2149: bre sogs rgyan gyi rnam pa mang po dpyangs shing
NK114(ye)001:2150: mdzes par byas pa der bde bar gshegs pa sangs
NK114(ye)001:2152: de'i rigs kyi bu mchog thugs sras byang chub sems
NK114(ye)001:2153: dpa'i tshogs dang bcas pa thams cad byon nas bzhugs
NK114(ye)001:2154: pa la spos dang 'dag chal gyi chus sum gnyis
NK114(ye)001:2155: tsam gang ba'i beed+aur+ya la sogs pa'i nor bu rin
NK114(ye)001:2156: po che'i bum pa nas khrus kyi sgo nas rim
NK114(ye)001:2157: gro bgyid pa la mkhas pa'i ngang las sprul pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2158: smin legs ma ste mchod pa'i lha mo rnams kyis
NK114(ye)001:2159: bstod pa'i glu dang mdzes pa'i gar dang snyan pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2160: rola mo sna tshogs pa'i rnam par 'gyur ba dpag
NK114(ye)001:2161: tu med pas phan tshun gcig gis gcig la 'gran
NK114(ye)001:2162: pa lta bur khrus kyi bya ba la brtson te
NK114(ye)001:2163: khrus gsol bas rang gzhan sems can thams cad kyi
NK114(ye)001:2164: sdig sgrib ma lus pa dag par bsam mo //
NK114(ye)001:2165: gsum pa gos rgyan byugs pa sogs dbul ba la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:2166: sku phyi zhing gos rgyan dbul ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:2169: sku phyi ba dang na bza' dang rgyan gsol ba
NK114(ye)001:2170: sogs nye reg gi cho ga ste bya ba rnams
NK114(ye)001:2171: gus pa'i rnam 'gyur gyis byed pa la mkhas pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2172: ri dwags miga can te mchod pa'i lha mo rnams
NK114(ye)001:2173: kyis dri bzang gi phye ma dar gos sna tshogs
NK114(ye)001:2174: par thum por dril ba mang pos khrus gsol ba'i
NK114(ye)001:2175: rlan gyi cha thams cad phyis shing bsku mnye'i rdzas
NK114(ye)001:2176: sna tshogs byugs pa la sogs pa'i sri zhu byed
NK114(ye)001:2177: pa'i las kyis g.yeng pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2178: gzhan yang gos rgyan sogs dbul ba'ang 'di ltar gos
NK114(ye)001:2179: kyi bye brag mang po yon tan gzhan las 'phags
NK114(ye)001:2180: pa ste de la kha dog gi yon tan ni
NK114(ye)001:2181: dkar po kho na lta bu gcig tu mi gnas
NK114(ye)001:2182: par dbang po'i mtshon te 'ja' tshon lta bu sna
NK114(ye)001:2184: phal pa'i las kyis thags su btags pa med pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2185: yon tan ni bsod nams kyi stobs las byung ba'i
NK114(ye)001:2186: lha rdzas kyi gos rang snang dge ba'i rin chen
NK114(ye)001:2187: rin gyis nyo ba dang 'dra la /
NK114(ye)001:2188: 'bad rtsol med par gang 'dod 'byung ba'i yon tan
NK114(ye)001:2189: ni dpag bsam gyi ljon pa las byung ba'i gos
NK114(ye)001:2190: rnams btsong ba ltar mos pa'i stobs kyis bkug pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2191: pany+tsa li ste kha dog lnga pa dbyibs ni dar
NK114(ye)001:2193: gzhan yang chags bral gyi rnam pa can rnams la chos gos rnam pa gsum la sogs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2194: gos de dag kyang lcid kyis non pa'i skyon spangsa
NK114(ye)001:2195: pa sha mi sgrib pa'i srab pa reg bya 'jam
NK114(ye)001:2196: pa / ljid mi che bas yang ba ste /
NK114(ye)001:2197: de yang byang gling pa'i gos srang gcig /
NK114(ye)001:2198: rgyal chen rigs bzhi pa'i gos srang phyed yin pa
NK114(ye)001:2199: nas gzhan 'phrul pa'i gos srang gcig gi drug cu
NK114(ye)001:2200: rtsa bzhi'i cha gcig las med pa'i bar je yang
NK114(ye)001:2201: du song la / tshangs ris yan chad kyi gos
NK114(ye)001:2202: shin tu yang bas srang gis gzhal du med pa
NK114(ye)001:2203: yin pa de lta bu dang /
NK114(ye)001:2204: gos bzang po de rnams dri sna tshogs dang spos
NK114(ye)001:2205: kyi chus bgos shing byugs pa longs sprul gyi rnam
NK114(ye)001:2206: pa can so so la 'os pa'i gos kyi rnam
NK114(ye)001:2207: pa'ang cha re re la shin tu mang po dang
NK114(ye)001:2208: / rgyan gyi rnam pa'ang sangs rgyas byang sems rnams la 'os pa'i rgyan te /
NK114(ye)001:2209: de yang lha klu la sogs pa'i rgyal po rnams
NK114(ye)001:2210: kyi gtsug gi nor bu rin po che gzhan las
NK114(ye)001:2211: khyad par du 'phags pa des byang chub sems dpa'
NK114(ye)001:2212: rnams kyi zhabs kyii sor mo'i gdu bu gcig gi
NK114(ye)001:2213: rin thang gi bye ba'i char yang mi phod la
NK114(ye)001:2214: / byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi gtsug gi nor
NK114(ye)001:2215: bu mchog gis ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i ye shes
NK114(ye)001:2216: rang snang gi rgyan las zhabs kyi sor gdub gcig
NK114(ye)001:2217: gi dper yang mi bzod la bye ba brgya stong
NK114(ye)001:2218: gi char yang mi phod pas de lta bu'i rgyan
NK114(ye)001:2219: gyi rnam pa de dag gi nang nas gcig gi
NK114(ye)001:2220: cha shas tsam zhig la gser srang 'bum la sogs
NK114(ye)001:2221: pa'i ri'o zhes rin thang brjod na de la gzhan
NK114(ye)001:2222: gyis khrel ba'i gnas su 'os pa de lta bu'i
NK114(ye)001:2223: rin chen gyi rgyan phyag zhabs kyi gdu bu /
NK114(ye)001:2228: cod pan sogs rin po che'i rgyan brgyad po re
NK114(ye)001:2229: re'ang mang po dpag tu med pa yod par dmigs
NK114(ye)001:2230: nas / gang la 'bul ba'i yul ni /
NK114(ye)001:2231: 'dod pa'i yon tan mtha' dag la 'dzin zhen gyi
NK114(ye)001:2232: bag chags phra ba'ang spangs pa'i phyir thub pa'i dbang
NK114(ye)001:2233: po sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la dgos pa
NK114(ye)001:2234: med kyang / bdag gis tshe rabs sngon ma rnams
NK114(ye)001:2235: su bsod nams kyi tshogs ma bsags pas dbul zhing
NK114(ye)001:2236: bkren pa dang ldan pas bdag tu bzung ba'i longs
NK114(ye)001:2237: spyod rgya chen po med pas na bdag gi bsod
NK114(ye)001:2238: nams kyi tshogs rdzogs nas byang chub kyi sems rin
NK114(ye)001:2239: po che rgyud la skye ba'i snod du rung bar
NK114(ye)001:2240: 'gyur ba'i slad du yid kyis sprul pa'i gos rgyan
NK114(ye)001:2241: sogs 'di dag bcom ldan 'das kyis bdag gir bzhes
NK114(ye)001:2242: par mdzod cig ces sprul pa'i lha mo rnams kyis
NK114(ye)001:2243: gos dang rgyan gyi bye brag de dag de bzhin
NK114(ye)001:2244: gshegs pa rnams kyi sku la gsol ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:2245: g.yas g.yon mdun rnams su'ang mang po spungs te phul
NK114(ye)001:2246: bas rang gzhan sems can thams cad kyi bsod nams
NK114(ye)001:2248: nyes spyod kyis gdung ba las skyob pa'i ngo tsha dang khrel yod kyi gos dang /
NK114(ye)001:2249: gzungs dang ting nge 'dzin dang mtshan dang dpe byad
NK114(ye)001:2250: la sogs pa'i yon tan gyi rgyan phun sum tshogs
NK114(ye)001:2251: pa thob par gyur cig snyam du smon pa dang
NK114(ye)001:2252: / de bzhin du 'jig rten dbang phyug spyan ras
NK114(ye)001:2253: gzigs la sogs pa nye ba'i sras chen brgyad dang
NK114(ye)001:2254: / / ngan song kun 'dren la sogs pa byams pa /
NK114(ye)001:2269: bskal bzang gis byang chub sems dpa' bcu drug dang
NK114(ye)001:2270: ni gzhan yang gdul bya'i dbang gis khyim pa'i tshul
NK114(ye)001:2271: bzung ba'i byang chub sems dpa' chos 'phags dang /
NK114(ye)001:2273: li tsa b+ai dri ma med par grags pa la
NK114(ye)001:2274: sogs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la'ang gos
NK114(ye)001:2275: rgyan la sogs pa'i rnam pa de dag dbul bar
NK114(ye)001:2276: bgyi zhing sngar bzhin smon no //
NK114(ye)001:2277: gnyis pa dri'i byugs pa dbul ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:2278: 'di ltar gling bzhi ri rab nyi zla tshangs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2279: 'jig rten dang bcas pa stong ni stong dang po
NK114(ye)001:2281: de stong ni stong gnyis pa bar ma'i 'jig rten /
NK114(ye)001:2282: de stong ni stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig
NK114(ye)001:2283: rten gyii khams te de thams cad cig char du
NK114(ye)001:2284: khyab pa'i dri bzang po'i chab kyis bkang ba'i rin
NK114(ye)001:2285: po che'i snod sna tshogs thogs pa'i lha mo rnams
NK114(ye)001:2286: kyis dri'i bzhon par 'khyud pa ste rlung dang 'grogs
NK114(ye)001:2287: pa'i tsan+dana la sogs pa'i spos kyi bsung zhim po'i
NK114(ye)001:2289: bsod nams bye ba ste mang pos bskrun pa'i sku
NK114(ye)001:2290: yon chung ngu phul bas kyang tshogs chen po rdzogs
NK114(ye)001:2291: pa'i phyir bsod nams dpag tu med pa'i 'byung gnas
NK114(ye)001:2292: mtshan dang dpe byad bzang po'i brgyan pa'i byad shin
NK114(ye)001:2293: tu mdzes pa ni gser yongs su sbyangsa pa rab
NK114(ye)001:2294: tu mdzes pa'i brtan pa'nga 'phrog ste mog mog por
NK114(ye)001:2295: byed pa'i 'od dang 'od zer 'bar ba'i sku de
NK114(ye)001:2296: la byugs par bgyi bar bsam nas phul bas rang
NK114(ye)001:2297: gzhan sems can thams cad kyis rgyal ba dgyes pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2298: tshul khrims kyi dri gsung thob par smon no //
NK114(ye)001:2299: bzhi pa bzhugs su gsol ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:2300: dper na dag pa'i zhing khams kyi bkod pa ni zhing de'i sangs rgyas kyi smon lam dang /
NK114(ye)001:2301: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi bsod nams kyi stobs
NK114(ye)001:2302: kyis rang snang ba las gzhan ma yin pa de
NK114(ye)001:2303: bzhin du / 'dir yang mdo sde rgyan las /
NK114(ye)001:2304: sems can kun la brtse ba can //
NK114(ye)001:2305: phrad dang bral ba'i dgongs pa can //
NK114(ye)001:2306: mi 'bral ba yi dgongs pa can //
NK114(ye)001:2307: phan bde'i dgongs khyod la phyag 'tshal //
NK114(ye)001:2308: zhes pa ltar tshad med bzhi'i thugs dang ldan pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2309: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi ye shes kyi rang
NK114(ye)001:2310: snang dang mthun par tshad med pa bzhis blo sbyangs
NK114(ye)001:2311: pa'i gang zag tshogs bsags pa po de'i dge ba'i
NK114(ye)001:2312: yid ngor dmigs shing snang ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:2313: dmigs pa rgya che zhing nye 'khon med pa'i btang
NK114(ye)001:2314: snyomsa kyi rang bzhin shin tu rgya khyon yangs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2316: phan pa'i rlan dang ldan pa yid 'ong gi byams
NK114(ye)001:2317: pa'i rang bzhin pad+mo ge sar dang bcas pa'i 'dab
NK114(ye)001:2318: ma stong du brdal ba yi steng der 'gro ba'i
NK114(ye)001:2319: sdug bsngal gyi gdung ba zhi ba'i bsil zer can
NK114(ye)001:2320: snying rje dang rmongs pa'i mun pa sel ba'i shes
NK114(ye)001:2321: rab zung du 'jug pa'i rang bzhin nyi zla bkrag
NK114(ye)001:2322: tu 'tsher ba bstar legs pa'i gdan la /
NK114(ye)001:2323: zag pa med pa'i dga' ba chen po'i rang bzhiin
NK114(ye)001:2324: can bcom ldan 'das 'khor byang chub sems dpa' tshogs
NK114(ye)001:2325: dang bcas pa thams cad bdag gi bsod nams kyi
NK114(ye)001:2326: zhing du bskal pa rgya mtsho'i bar du bzhugs par
NK114(ye)001:2327: mdzad nas rjes su bzung du gsol zhes pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:2328: gsum pa tshogs bsags pa dngos la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:2330: don bsdus te dgos pa brjod pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:2339: rang bzhin du lus kyi rnam 'gyur las sems kyi mngon rtogs gsal ba'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:2340: sems la dad gus gang yang med bzhin grags 'dod
NK114(ye)001:2341: dang tshul 'chos sam bab bcol du goms pa lung
NK114(ye)001:2342: ma bstan gyi bya ba la 'jug pa'i tshul min
NK114(ye)001:2343: pa'i lus btud pa'i rtags kyi rnam 'gyur snying gar
NK114(ye)001:2344: thal mo sbyar bar bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:2346: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' dag /
NK114(ye)001:2347: kun tu thogs med gzigs par ldan //
NK114(ye)001:2348: de dag thams cad spyan snga na //
NK114(ye)001:2349: rtag par bdag ni gnas so zhes //
NK114(ye)001:2350: de ltar bsam nas ngo tsha dang //
NK114(ye)001:2351: gus dang 'jigs ldan de bzhin mnos //
NK114(ye)001:2355: khrel dang ngo tsha ba dang bcas pa'i sems kyi mngon rtogs ngoma pa la /
NK114(ye)001:2356: me tog gi dog pasa rab tu bzung ba ste
NK114(ye)001:2357: gang ba'i snyim pa'i snod ni pad+ma kha 'bus pa'am
NK114(ye)001:2358: ga bu chung gi brtul zhugs 'dzin pa ste dbyibs
NK114(ye)001:2359: lta bu dgos pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:2360: gnyis pa yid gus pa'i rnam 'gyur ni /
NK114(ye)001:2361: sangs rgyas byang sems rnams kyi yon tan yid la
NK114(ye)001:2362: dran nas dad pa bla lhag tu skye ba ste
NK114(ye)001:2363: / de yang 'di ltar bdud bzhi bcom zhing spangs
NK114(ye)001:2364: rtogs kyi yon tan dang ldan la srid zhi gnyis
NK114(ye)001:2365: las 'das pas na bcom ldan 'das dang /
NK114(ye)001:2366: 'das zhes pa'i sgra legs sbyar la med kyang bod skad du bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:2367: chos nyid de bzhin nyid dang rjes su mthun par gshegs pas de bzhin gshegs pa /
NK114(ye)001:2368: las nyon gyi dgra thams cad bcom zhing 'jig rten
NK114(ye)001:2369: gsum gyi mchod 'os su gyur pas na dgra bcom
NK114(ye)001:2370: pa'o // dgra bcom gyi don ar+ha te zhes pa'i sgra las mchod 'os la 'jug pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:2371: shes bya'i chos thams cad chags thogs dang bral bar
NK114(ye)001:2372: yang dag par mkhyen pas na yang dag par rdzogs
NK114(ye)001:2373: pa'i sangs rgyas / bud+d+ha khong du chud pa'i don gyis sangs rgyas zhes pa mkhyen pa'i don no //
NK114(ye)001:2374: shes rab lhag mthong gis chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs gzigs pas spyan lta bu rig pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2375: snying rjes gzhan don la gshegs pas na zhabs su ldan pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2376: de la sogs pa gzhan yang lam bde ba byang
NK114(ye)001:2377: chub sems dpa'i theg pa nas 'bras bu bde ba
NK114(ye)001:2378: sangs rgyas kyi ser gshegs pas na bde bar gshegs
NK114(ye)001:2379: pa / phung po lnga'i 'jig rten grangs med pa mkhyen pas na 'jig rten mkhyen pa /
NK114(ye)001:2380: gdul bar dka' ba'i sems can rnams kyang thabs zhi bas 'dul bas na skyes bu 'dul ba /
NK114(ye)001:2381: khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad thar ba'i lam du 'dren pas na kha lo sgyur ba /
NK114(ye)001:2382: srid zhi thams cad la mchog tu gyur pas na bla na med pa /
NK114(ye)001:2383: rigs drug gi gtso bo lha dang mi rnams la
NK114(ye)001:2384: chos ston pas na lha dang mi rnams kyi ston
NK114(ye)001:2385: pa la sogs pa sangs rgyas kyi yon tan dang
NK114(ye)001:2386: / gzhan yang dam pa'i chos dang /
NK114(ye)001:2387: 'phags pa'i dge 'dun rnams kyi yon tan mtha' dag
NK114(ye)001:2388: ste ma lus pa ni da lta sgrib pa'i mthus
NK114(ye)001:2389: gnas kyi sa thag ring por bskal ba bzhin rang
NK114(ye)001:2390: rgyud la ma thob cing gzhan rgyud la byon zin
NK114(ye)001:2391: rnams kyang 'phags sa ma thob bar du ji bzhin
NK114(ye)001:2392: pa mngon sum du mi mthong yang dad pa dang
NK114(ye)001:2393: mtshungs par ldan pa'i yid kyi skyed mos tshal du
NK114(ye)001:2394: mgron du khugs pa ltar 'ongs pa'i mod la 'jigs
NK114(ye)001:2396: skyo ba la sogs pa'i shugs kyis min par dad
NK114(ye)001:2397: pa kho na'i stobs kyis dbugs brnangs shing mig mchi
NK114(ye)001:2398: ma 'khrugs / lus kyi ba spu thams cad gcig
NK114(ye)001:2399: tu zing nas dkon mchog gsum gyi yon tan gyis
NK114(ye)001:2400: blo sna phrog ste rnam rtog gzhan skye ba'i go
NK114(ye)001:2401: skabs med par dad pa'i gdung shugs drag po rtse
NK114(ye)001:2402: gcig tu bskyed par byed pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:2403: gnyis pa yan lag bdun pa dbul ba la bdun te /
NK114(ye)001:2409: mya ngan las mi 'da' bar gsol ba 'debs pa /
NK114(ye)001:2410: dge rtsa gzhan don du bsngo ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:2411: dang po phyag 'tshal ba'i yan lag ni /
NK114(ye)001:2412: tshogs zhing de dag gi mdun sa gzhi'i ngos su
NK114(ye)001:2413: rang nyid kyi g.yas su skye ba da lta'i pha
NK114(ye)001:2415: mdun du sdang bar byed pa'i dgra gnod par byed pa'i bgegs rnams dang /
NK114(ye)001:2416: rgyab tu lan chags kyi bdag po bdag mo rnams dang /
NK114(ye)001:2417: mtha' skor du rigs drug gi sems can thams cad 'khod par bsam ste /
NK114(ye)001:2418: phyag 'tshal ba 'di ni gtso bo nga rgyal gyi
NK114(ye)001:2419: gnyen po yin pas gcom skyung zhing mig 'phang smad
NK114(ye)001:2420: de lus drang por bsrangs nas thal mo sngar bshad
NK114(ye)001:2421: pa bzhin pad+ma kha 'bus pa ltar khong stong du
NK114(ye)001:2423: thar pa chen po'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:2425: lag gnyis spyi bor thal sbyar te //
NK114(ye)001:2426: lus dpag med pa'i sprin tshogs kyis //
NK114(ye)001:2427: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas la phyag 'tshal //
NK114(ye)001:2429: de yang lus gus pa'i sgo nas phyag 'tshal //
NK114(ye)001:2430: ngag gus pa'i sgo nas phyag 'tshal gyi tshig brjod /
NK114(ye)001:2431: yid gus pa'i sgo nas mchog gsum la dad gus rtse gcig pas phyag 'tshal ba ste /
NK114(ye)001:2432: de la thal mo spyi bo mgrin pa snying ga
NK114(ye)001:2433: gsum du 'jog dus sangs rgyas chos dge 'dun gsum
NK114(ye)001:2434: dang / tshogs zhing rnams kyi sku gsung thugs kyi
NK114(ye)001:2435: yon tan la dmigs nas rang gzhan sems can thams
NK114(ye)001:2436: cad kyi sgo gsum gyi sgrib pa thams cad dag
NK114(ye)001:2437: dang / / sangs rgyas byang sems rnams kyi sku
NK114(ye)001:2438: gsung thugs kyi yon tan thams cad thob par gyur
NK114(ye)001:2440: de nas lus thams cad sa la bag yod par
NK114(ye)001:2441: brkyang ba la mar me mdzad kyi phyag ces bya
NK114(ye)001:2442: la / de ma grub na yan lag lnga ldan gyi phyag ni /
NK114(ye)001:2445: pus mo g.yas g.yon gnyis te ma lnga po sa la phab ste phyag btsal bas /
NK114(ye)001:2446: rgyud lnga'i 'gro ba rnams stongs par gyur cig /
NK114(ye)001:2447: nyer len gyi phung po lnga rgyun chad par gyur cig /
NK114(ye)001:2448: zag med kyi dbang po lnga thob par gyur cig /
NK114(ye)001:2449: stobs lnga yongs su rdzogs par gyur cig /
NK114(ye)001:2450: mig lnga rnam par dag par gyur cig snyam du smon no //
NK114(ye)001:2451: de yang rang gi lus kyang 'di nyid gcig pu
NK114(ye)001:2452: tsam ma yin par shin tu mang por sprul te
NK114(ye)001:2453: / dper na sprin dang bral ba'i ston zla shin
NK114(ye)001:2454: tu gzhon zhing 'od gsal ba de khrus la 'jug
NK114(ye)001:2455: pa dang 'dra bar gnam zla ji bzhin pa'i gzugs
NK114(ye)001:2456: brnyan 'dzin nus pa'i 'dam la sogs pa'i rnyog ma
NK114(ye)001:2457: med cing shin tu dwangs pa'i rdzing bu'i nang du
NK114(ye)001:2458: gzugs brnyan ci shar yang shin tu gsal bas na
NK114(ye)001:2459: de'i khar rma bya'i bu mo yid 'jo zhing sgeg
NK114(ye)001:2460: pa'i gzugs can dag gis zlos gar bsgyur nas rtse
NK114(ye)001:2462: rdzing bu dwangs par de dag gi gzugs brnyan shar
NK114(ye)001:2463: ba dang gzugs dngos gnyis po gang yin so sor
NK114(ye)001:2465: de lta bu'i rang gi lang tsho'i grangs dpag tu
NK114(ye)001:2466: med par sprul pa'i rnam grangs ji snyed pa ni
NK114(ye)001:2467: sa chen po'i rdul gyi rnam grangs dang so sor
NK114(ye)001:2468: mi 'byed par shin tu 'khrul pa bskyed par byed
NK114(ye)001:2469: pa de tsam du mang bar sprul te phyag gi
NK114(ye)001:2470: las kho na la sgo gsum chig dril du 'jug
NK114(ye)001:2471: pa'i bya bas brel nas las gzhan la sems khom
NK114(ye)001:2472: tsam yang med pa zhig dgos kyi /
NK114(ye)001:2473: gzhan du na lus 'khyo ro ro dgye rgu mang po byed kyang sems yeng zhor dang 'khrul zhor /
NK114(ye)001:2474: ngag gis bre mo'i long gtam sogs bshad zhor la
NK114(ye)001:2475: ni phyag 'bum ther mang po'i grangs bsogs kyang byas
NK114(ye)001:2476: la ma bsags pa'i dge ba ste /
NK114(ye)001:2477: thar pa'i sa bon tsam las snying po ci yang med gsungs /
NK114(ye)001:2478: des na phyag 'tshal ba la sogs dge ba'i las
NK114(ye)001:2479: gang bsgrub kyang sgo gsum ya ma bral ba zhig
NK114(ye)001:2481: phyag 'tshal ba'i phan yon ni 'dul ba lung las /
NK114(ye)001:2482: dge slong dag khyod kyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i dbu
NK114(ye)001:2483: skra dang sen mo'i mchod rten la dad pas phyag
NK114(ye)001:2484: 'tshal ba de'i rnam par smin pa ni ji srid
NK114(ye)001:2485: du tshangs pa mtshungs par spyod pa rnams la khong
NK114(ye)001:2486: khro ma skyes pa de srid du dbang chen gser
NK114(ye)001:2487: gyi sa gzhi la thug gi bar gyi rdul phra
NK114(ye)001:2488: rab kyi grangs dang mnyam pa'i 'khor los sgyur ba'i
NK114(ye)001:2489: rgyal po'i bde ba myong zhing lha dang mi rnams
NK114(ye)001:2490: kyi nang du phyin par 'gyur ro zhes gsungs na
NK114(ye)001:2491: / byang chub tu sems bskyed pa'i don du phyag
NK114(ye)001:2492: 'tshal ba'i bsod nams ni tshad med de mthar thug
NK114(ye)001:2493: zhi ba mchog gi go 'phang la sbyor ba'i phyir
NK114(ye)001:2494: / ro // gnyis pa mchod pa 'bul ba'i yan lag ni /
NK114(ye)001:2495: spyir byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis bdog dgu'i dngos
NK114(ye)001:2496: po thams cad gtong ba sbyin pa'i pha rol tu
NK114(ye)001:2497: phyin pa la sogs pa phyin drug gi yan lag
NK114(ye)001:2498: ni / chags bdun spong ba dang khyad chos bzhi ldan gyis yongs su rdzogs pa yin mod /
NK114(ye)001:2499: skabs 'dir las dang po pas sems bskyed pa la
NK114(ye)001:2500: sogs pa'i don du dngos su ci 'byor pa'i mchod
NK114(ye)001:2501: pa 'bul ba yang de dang rjes su mthun par
NK114(ye)001:2502: dag pa rnam pa gsum dang ldan par bya ste
NK114(ye)001:2503: / bsam pa dag pa sems bskyed skye ba'i don du /
NK114(ye)001:2504: zhing dag pa mchog gsum la dmigs te /
NK114(ye)001:2505: dngos po dag pa ni gsum ste sdig zas dang log 'tshos ma bslad /
NK114(ye)001:2506: mchod pa ni ser sna'i gnyen po yin pas ser sna dang 'jur 'gag gis ma bcing /
NK114(ye)001:2507: nga rgyal dang ngom chos su ma song ba ste rgyu bzang ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:2510: lo ma'i ser sa lta bu ma yin par rang
NK114(ye)001:2511: la ci yod rnams kyi nang nas dngos legs shing
NK114(ye)001:2512: spus gtsang ba de yin pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2513: mar me yon chab sogs ya yo 'khyag 'khyog med
NK114(ye)001:2514: par shin tu bkod legs pas sems dwangs par 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:2515: ba ste de dag tshang ba'i sgo nas mchod pa
NK114(ye)001:2516: dang / des kyang mtshon par mi nus pas dpe
NK114(ye)001:2517: zlar rung ba med pa'i mchod pa ni dag ma
NK114(ye)001:2518: dag gi 'jig rten gyi khams tshad med pa na
NK114(ye)001:2519: bdag pos ma bzung ba'i dngos po yid du 'ong
NK114(ye)001:2520: ba'i rnam pa sa gzhi dang ljon shing /
NK114(ye)001:2521: chu mtsho dang me tog /'bras bu dang sman gyi rigs /
NK114(ye)001:2524: rin po che dang dpag bsam gyi shing la sogs
NK114(ye)001:2525: pa ji snyed yod pa thams cad yid kyis bdag
NK114(ye)001:2526: gir byas nas phul na tshogs chen po rdzogs par
NK114(ye)001:2527: 'gyur te bsam pa'i khyad par gtso che bas so
NK114(ye)001:2528: // gzhan yang ting nge 'dzin gyi rnam par 'phrul
NK114(ye)001:2529: pas snang srid thams cad khyab par sprul pa 'dod
NK114(ye)001:2531: rgyal srid rin po che sna bdun /
NK114(ye)001:2532: nye ba'i rin po che bdun /
NK114(ye)001:2535: rnam par bkra ba'i me tog /'od gsal ba'i sgron me /
NK114(ye)001:2538: gzhal du med pa'i pho brang sogs mdor na blo'i
NK114(ye)001:2539: ngor 'char du rung ba thams cad mchod pa'i rdzas
NK114(ye)001:2540: su dmigs te phul ba de'i bla ste gong na
NK114(ye)001:2541: gzhan mchis pa ma yin pa'i mchod pa'i sprin rab
NK114(ye)001:2542: 'byams kyis mchod par byed pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:2543: dkon mchog t+aa la'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:2544: me tog phal cher me tog bla bre dang //
NK114(ye)001:2545: me tog bkod pa'i 'od zer rab bkye ste //
NK114(ye)001:2546: me tog sna tshogs kun tu bkram byas nas //
NK114(ye)001:2547: bdag nyid chen po rgyal ba sras bcas mchod //
NK114(ye)001:2548: lag pa'i mthil na yod pa bsam yas rnams //
NK114(ye)001:2549: rgyal ba gcig la mchod pa byed pa ltar //
NK114(ye)001:2550: rgyal ba ma lus kun la'ang de bzhin te //
NK114(ye)001:2552: zhes pa ltar 'phags pa kun tu bzang po'i ting
NK114(ye)001:2553: nge 'dzin gyi rnam par 'phrul pa bsam gyis mi
NK114(ye)001:2554: khyab pa'i mchod pa'i yon gyis phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba
NK114(ye)001:2555: rnams mchod pa de la do zlar spobs pa tsam
NK114(ye)001:2556: du 'bul ba la phrag dog bgyid pa'i tha snyad
NK114(ye)001:2557: btags so // rnam pa gcig tu na bla na med pa'i mchod pa ni 'di yin te /
NK114(ye)001:2558: nam mkha' mdzod kyi mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:2559: byang chub tu sems bskyed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2561: sems can la snying rje bsgom pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2562: chos bsgrub pa dang bzhir gsungs pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:2563: de mchod par ci'i 'grub na rgyal ba dgyes pa'i thabs de las gzhan med pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:2564: de ltar mchod pa phul ba'i phan yon ni /
NK114(ye)001:2565: byang chub kyi sems rgyud la skye ba'i snod du rung ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:2566: gnas skabs su ci bsam pa'i don legs dgu'i dngos po thams cad 'grub pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2567: mthar thug bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs nas gzugs kyi
NK114(ye)001:2568: sku 'grub pa'i rgyur 'gyur pa la sogs pa ste
NK114(ye)001:2569: / sa snying 'khor lo bcu pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:2570: khams gsum kun na bde zhing skyid pa //
NK114(ye)001:2571: de yang dkon mchog gsum las byung bas //
NK114(ye)001:2572: de bas bde zhing skyid pa 'dod na //
NK114(ye)001:2573: rtag tu dkon mchog gsum la mchod byos //
NK114(ye)001:2576: me tog gcig tsam gyis kyang mchod pa yang //
NK114(ye)001:2577: bde gshegs sku gzugs rtsig ngos bris pa la //
NK114(ye)001:2578: lus 'khrugs bzhin du sems kyis phul ba na //
NK114(ye)001:2579: de dag rim gyis sangs rgyas bye ba mthong //
NK114(ye)001:2582: sangs rgyas rnams kyi gzugs kyi sku //
NK114(ye)001:2583: bsod nams tshogs las 'khrungs pa ste //
NK114(ye)001:2585: gsum pa sdig pa bshags pa'i yan lag ni /
NK114(ye)001:2586: 'di ltar byas shing bsags pa'i sdig pa thams cad
NK114(ye)001:2587: myur du ma bshags na rdul gyis gos pa'i me
NK114(ye)001:2588: long la gzugs brnyan mi 'char ba ltar byang chub
NK114(ye)001:2589: kyi sems rgyud la skye ba'i gegs su che zhing
NK114(ye)001:2590: / 'chi ba glo bur du byung na ngan song du 'gro ba las 'os med de /
NK114(ye)001:2591: dam pa'i skyes bu rnams kyis kyang sdig ldan du
NK114(ye)001:2592: zhal gyis bzhes nas bshags pa'i tshul la brtson pa
NK114(ye)001:2593: ltar mdzad na / bdag cag rnams ni 'khor ba'i g.yang sar ltung ba /
NK114(ye)001:2594: las dang nyon mongs pas gzir ba /
NK114(ye)001:2595: nyes pa dang ltung ba brgya phrag du ma'i snod /
NK114(ye)001:2596: las dang las kyi rnam par smin pa 'ba' zhig
NK114(ye)001:2597: gi gzhan dbang can yin pas nyin mtshan rtag tu
NK114(ye)001:2598: nyes spyod mi dge ba'i dngos po 'di las thar
NK114(ye)001:2599: ba'i thabs kho na la sems par rigs so //
NK114(ye)001:2600: de la ji ltar bshags pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:2601: sbyang bya sdig pa'i sgo drug /
NK114(ye)001:2602: sbyong byed gnyen po stobs bzhis /
NK114(ye)001:2603: sbyong tshul sbyor dngos rjes gsum tshang bas bshags dgos la /
NK114(ye)001:2604: de yang sdig bshags ni gti mug gi gnyen po yin pas /
NK114(ye)001:2605: dang po sdig pa'i sgo drug po ngos zin par bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:2611: sgo gang las sdig pa byas she na /
NK114(ye)001:2612: dus ni thog ma med pa nas da lta'i bar du /
NK114(ye)001:2613: rgyu nyon mongs pas kun nas bslangs te /
NK114(ye)001:2614: sbyor bar rang gis byas pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2615: gzhan la byed du bcug pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2616: gzhan gyis byas pa la rjes su yi rang bas /
NK114(ye)001:2618: bcas pa'i kha na ma tho ba /
NK114(ye)001:2619: yul mchog gsum dang pha ma la sogs pas mtshon gang yang rung ba la /
NK114(ye)001:2620: sgo lus ngag yid gsum pos byas pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:2621: de yang spobs pa'i blo gros kyi zhus pa las /
NK114(ye)001:2623: yid ni dug gi rtsa ba yin //
NK114(ye)001:2624: nyes par smra rnams 'byung ba'i phyir //
NK114(ye)001:2625: kha ni sdig pa'i sgo nyid do //
NK114(ye)001:2627: kha ni nyes spyod thams cad 'byung ba'i sgo yin pas thog mar smos te /
NK114(ye)001:2628: ngag gi sgo nas mu cor te tshig 'chal ci
NK114(ye)001:2629: rung rung smra ba'i mi dge ba bzhi yi las
NK114(ye)001:2630: dang / yid ni lus ngag gi las thams cad dang po kun nas slong byed rgyu /
NK114(ye)001:2631: bar du bya ba la sbyor ba'i grogs /
NK114(ye)001:2632: tha ma bag chagsa 'dzin pa'i rten yin pas dngos su smos par ma zad /
NK114(ye)001:2633: lus ngag gi bdun po kun slong dge na dge bar 'gyur ba'i skabs kyang srid la /
NK114(ye)001:2634: lung ma bstan par 'gyur ba'i skabs kyang yod kyi /
NK114(ye)001:2635: yid kyi gsum po rnam pa thams cad du mi
NK114(ye)001:2636: dge ba yin pas yid 'di ni dug sdong gi
NK114(ye)001:2637: sa bon bzhin nyes pa thams cad kyi gzhi ma
NK114(ye)001:2638: yin no // de gnyis ka'i rten du gyur pa
NK114(ye)001:2639: lus kyi sgo nas kyang sdig pa'i las gang byas
NK114(ye)001:2640: yin no // pa ste / mdor na bcas pa
NK114(ye)001:2641: dang rang bzhin gyi kha na ma tho ba'i nyes
NK114(ye)001:2642: yin no // pa ste / pa thams cad /
NK114(ye)001:2643: da lta sngon gyi dge ba'i las cung zad tsam
NK114(ye)001:2644: pa'i mthus mtho ris mi'i lus rten la brten pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2645: skabs 'dir nad dang sdug bsngal sogs mi dge ba'i
NK114(ye)001:2646: rnam par smin pa 'ga' zhig nyams su myong ba
NK114(ye)001:2647: tsam ma gtogs gzhan thams cad dge 'bras des zil
NK114(ye)001:2648: gyis mnan te de la 'jigsa shing skrag nas gzhan
NK114(ye)001:2649: du bros pa'i tshul gyis sdig pa'i rang gzugsa ngan
NK114(ye)001:2650: song la sogs po'i sdug bsngal dngos su myong ba
NK114(ye)001:2651: yin no // pa ste / pa thams cad /
NK114(ye)001:2652: ma yin na'ang / gtan nas med pa min te
NK114(ye)001:2653: srid pa'i rtsa ba gnas lugs kyi don la sgrib
NK114(ye)001:2654: pa'i mun nag stug po ma rig pa dang mtshungs
NK114(ye)001:2655: par ldan pa'i nyon mongs pa can gyi yid dang
NK114(ye)001:2656: lhan cig pa'i kun gzhi'i khams la 'chab pa ste
NK114(ye)001:2657: bag nyal gyi tshul du yod pa kun bskal pa
NK114(ye)001:2658: mang por bar ma dor chud za bar mi 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:2659: zhing rkyen tshogs pa na mngon gyur du smin par
NK114(ye)001:2660: yin no // pa ste / pa thams cad /
NK114(ye)001:2661: ma yin na'ang / 'gyur te / las brgya pa
NK114(ye)001:2662: yin no // pa ste / pa thams cad /
NK114(ye)001:2663: ma yin na'ang / 'gyur te / las / lus
NK114(ye)001:2664: can dag gi las rnams ni //
NK114(ye)001:2665: bskal pa brgyar yang chud mi za //
NK114(ye)001:2666: tshogs shing dus la bab pa na //
NK114(ye)001:2669: de ltar sbyang bya sdig pa'i rang bzhin ngos zin par byas nas /
NK114(ye)001:2670: de sbyong byed kyi thabs ni gnyen po stobs bzhi'i sgo nas te /
NK114(ye)001:2671: de yang mi dge ba'i las byas pa la 'jigs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2672: ngo tsha zhing khrel ba dang bcas pas bza' btung
NK114(ye)001:2673: yang yi gar mi 'ong ba tsam gyi 'gyod pa
NK114(ye)001:2674: chen po bskyed pa ni rnam par sun 'byin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2675: stobs / nyes pa'i gnyen por sgo gsum gyi dge ba spyi dang /
NK114(ye)001:2676: bye brag tu srog bcad pa'i gnyen por srog bslu ba nas /
NK114(ye)001:2677: log lta byas pa'i gnyen por las 'bras la yid
NK114(ye)001:2678: ches bskyed pa'i mtshon nas dge ba'i phyogs la brtson
NK114(ye)001:2679: pa kun tu spyod pa'i stobs /
NK114(ye)001:2680: phyin chad srog la bab kyang sdig pa'i las mi
NK114(ye)001:2681: bsgrub snyam du snying nas dam bca' zhing sdom sems
NK114(ye)001:2682: len pa sor chud pa'i stobs /
NK114(ye)001:2683: mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba dang byang chub
NK114(ye)001:2684: tu sems bskyed pa rten gyi stobs te chos bzhi
NK114(ye)001:2685: po de dag dang ldan na nyin phyed 'bar bas
NK114(ye)001:2686: mun pa drungs nas 'byin pa bzhin sdig pa thams
NK114(ye)001:2687: cad sbyangs shing dag pa'i thabs mchog tu gyur pa
NK114(ye)001:2688: yin gyi / gzhan du na kha nas bshags pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2689: tshig mthol lo 'chags so mi 'chab bo mi sbed
NK114(ye)001:2690: do phyin chad srog la bab kyang sdom lags so
NK114(ye)001:2691: zhes brjod kyin sems la 'gyod sdom gang yang med
NK114(ye)001:2692: par yeng zhor 'khrul zhor rtse bzhin rgod bzhin chags
NK114(ye)001:2693: sdang la sogs pa'i rtog ngan sna tshogs kyi rjes
NK114(ye)001:2694: su 'brang bzhin du bshags pa yin zer nas ltung
NK114(ye)001:2695: bshags la sogs pa grangs mang po bsogs kyang gsung
NK114(ye)001:2696: rab bton pa'i phan yon kyis sdig pa cung zad
NK114(ye)001:2697: srab par 'gyur bar zad kyi yongs su dag par
NK114(ye)001:2698: 'gyur ba ni ma yin pas sdig bshags la sogs
NK114(ye)001:2699: pa dge ba'i dngos po gang yin kyang gnad du
NK114(ye)001:2700: 'gro nges byed pa gal che gsungs /
NK114(ye)001:2701: de la ji ltar sbyor ba'i tshul ni /
NK114(ye)001:2702: sbyor ba sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs
NK114(ye)001:2703: dpag tu med pa mdun gyi namakhara bsam la skyabs
NK114(ye)001:2704: su 'gro ba dang phyag 'tshal zhing mchod pa phul
NK114(ye)001:2705: ba la sogs pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK114(ye)001:2706: dngos gzhi ji skad bshad pa'i stobs bzhi tshang ba'i sgo nas phung po gsum pa'i mdo dang /
NK114(ye)001:2708: spyod 'jug sogs las byung ba'i bshags tshig rnams gang rung brjod de bshags par bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:2709: rjes su ni tshogs zhing gi lha tshogs rnams las
NK114(ye)001:2710: 'od zer dpag tu med pa 'phros nas rang gzhan
NK114(ye)001:2711: sems can thams cad la phog pas mun khung du
NK114(ye)001:2712: nyi zer phog pa bzhin sdig sgrib nyes ltung thams
NK114(ye)001:2713: cad lhag med du sangs sangs dag par bsam nas
NK114(ye)001:2715: de ltar bshags pa'i phan yon ni /
NK114(ye)001:2716: sdig pa yang 'dus byas yin pas rang rgyud dang lhan cig tu mi gnas par 'gyur te /
NK114(ye)001:2717: byams pa seng ge'i sgras zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:2718: mi shes pas ni gang byas pa'i //
NK114(ye)001:2719: sdig pa'i las ni bshags par bgyi //
NK114(ye)001:2720: mkhas pas nyes pa bshags nas ni //
NK114(ye)001:2721: las dang lhan cig mi gnas so //
NK114(ye)001:2723: de lta bu'i gnyen po yang yang goms pa'i stobs
NK114(ye)001:2724: kyis sgrib pa dag na rtogs pa yang ngang gis
NK114(ye)001:2725: skye bas sdig pa ji tsam yod kyang de las
NK114(ye)001:2726: grol zhing nyes spyod thams cad bskyed pa'i rtsa ba
NK114(ye)001:2727: bdag tu zhen pa'i mun pa'ang drungs nas 'byin par
NK114(ye)001:2728: 'gyur te / sangs rgyas mdzod kyi mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:2729: pha ma dang rang sangs rgyas bsad pa yang stong nyid bsgoms pas rnam par grol lo //
NK114(ye)001:2732: nyon mongs shes bya'i sgrib pa yi //
NK114(ye)001:2733: mun pa'i gnyen po stong pa nyid //
NK114(ye)001:2735: bzhi pa rjes su yi rang ba'i yan lag ni /
NK114(ye)001:2736: lus kyi bya ba ngag gi smra ba longs spyod
NK114(ye)001:2737: gtong ba de dag gi don du sems pa ste
NK114(ye)001:2738: / sgo gsum longs spyod dang bcas pa'i las su
NK114(ye)001:2739: bya ba'i sbyor bas ngal ba gang gis kyang bdag
NK114(ye)001:2740: nyid kyi rgyud ma 'khrugs bzhin du bsam pa bzang
NK114(ye)001:2741: po'i khyad par gcig gis gzhan sangs rgyas rnams kyi
NK114(ye)001:2742: rdzogs smin sbyangs gsum mthar phyin pa'i yon tan dang
NK114(ye)001:2743: / / byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis smon 'jug
NK114(ye)001:2744: gi sems bskyed cing phyin drug la bslab pa dang
NK114(ye)001:2745: / / / nyan rang rnams kyis bden bzhi dang rten 'brel nyams su blangs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2746: 'gro ba phal pa dag gis kyang dge bcu bsgrubs
NK114(ye)001:2747: pa sogs 'phags pa dang so so skye bo'i rnama
NK114(ye)001:2748: par dkar ba'i yon tan thams cad longs spyod phrog
NK114(ye)001:2749: pa ltar pha rol po de dang bral bar byed
NK114(ye)001:2750: pa ma yin kyang rang gis thob pa'i cha nas
NK114(ye)001:2751: tha snyad nye bar btags te yud tsam ste rtog
NK114(ye)001:2752: pa gcig 'gyu ba'i yun la 'phrog par byed pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2753: chom rkun gyi brtul zhugsa te tshul ni rjes su
NK114(ye)001:2754: yi rang ba kho nas byas te /
NK114(ye)001:2755: sngon rgya gar 'phags pa'i yul du ko sa la'i
NK114(ye)001:2756: rgyal po gsal rgyal gyis de bzhin gshegs pa 'khor
NK114(ye)001:2757: dang bcas pa la bsnyen bkur gyis mchod pa las
NK114(ye)001:2758: / dbul mo zhig gis de la rjes su yi
NK114(ye)001:2759: rang ba'i bsam pa skyes pa bsod nams mnyam po'i
NK114(ye)001:2760: nang nas che bar thob par gsungs so //
NK114(ye)001:2761: de nas rjes su yi rang ba de las gzhan
NK114(ye)001:2762: rang gis ma bsgrub bzhin de ltar thob pa'i thabs
NK114(ye)001:2764: de yang rjes su yi rang ba 'di ni phrag
NK114(ye)001:2765: dog gi gnyen po yin pas gzhan gyis byas pa'i
NK114(ye)001:2766: dge ba dang yon tan la phrag dog gi dbang
NK114(ye)001:2768: gzhan la tshul khrims 'chal ba la sogs pa'i nyes
NK114(ye)001:2769: pa byung na sems dga' bar 'gyur ba des ni
NK114(ye)001:2770: don med pa'i nyes pa chen po rang rgyud la
NK114(ye)001:2771: sog cing / dam pa rnams kyi thugs khrel la
NK114(ye)001:2772: dkar phyogs kyi lha dag gis kyang 'phya zhing smod
NK114(ye)001:2773: pa'i gnas su 'gyur bas de 'dra ba'i gang zag
NK114(ye)001:2774: sog cing / de / chos ltar bcos pa'i tshul
NK114(ye)001:2775: ji ltar bzang yang don la ngan song gi gting
NK114(ye)001:2776: rdo las mi 'da' bas rtag tu rang rgyud la
NK114(ye)001:2777: legs par brtags nas bsam ngan de 'dra ba 'dug
NK114(ye)001:2778: na rang gis rang la khrel brdas byas nas skal
NK114(ye)001:2779: chad po nga re ngan rang gis chos mi 'grub
NK114(ye)001:2780: pa'i steng du rtog ngan 'di 'dra ba skye ba
NK114(ye)001:2781: sog cing / de / ngo re tsha / dam pa rnams kyis thugs khrel du 'ong /
NK114(ye)001:2782: chos la cung zad brtson khur byas pa des kyang chos go ma chod /
NK114(ye)001:2783: chos thos tshad shes tshad thams cad phrag dog dang
NK114(ye)001:2784: nga rgyal gyi bsnon mar gyur nas thos bsam thams
NK114(ye)001:2785: cad bdud las su song ba 'di re sdug snyam
NK114(ye)001:2786: du bsam nas rang skyon rkun ma ngos bzung /
NK114(ye)001:2787: rang mtshang mal 'og gi rdo bzhin du dor te /
NK114(ye)001:2788: gzhan gyi dge ba dang yon tan gyi phyogs gang
NK114(ye)001:2789: mthong zhing thos pa thams cad la snying thag pa
NK114(ye)001:2790: nas dga' zhing mgu la rjes su yi rang bar
NK114(ye)001:2791: byed pa 'di ni chos kyi gzugs brnyan mi che
NK114(ye)001:2792: yang bya sla la chod che ba yin pas rgyud
NK114(ye)001:2793: la 'byung nges su byed pa ni gnad dam pa
NK114(ye)001:2794: yin gsungs / phan yon ni sdud pa las /
NK114(ye)001:2795: stong gsum ri rab srang la gzhal bas tshad bzung rung //
NK114(ye)001:2796: rjes su yi rang dge ba de ni de lta min //
NK114(ye)001:2798: lnga pa chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul ba'i yan lag ni /
NK114(ye)001:2799: dman pa la dgag sgras thar du med pa'am thar
NK114(ye)001:2800: dka' ba'i 'khor ba na rgyu ba'i sems can rnams
NK114(ye)001:2801: kyi nyes par spyod pa ni gnyen pos ma dul
NK114(ye)001:2802: ba rang bzhin du ma zhi zhing ma bsdams pa
NK114(ye)001:2803: sdig to mi dge ba dag g.yo sgyus phyogs bslad
NK114(ye)001:2804: pa / chos kyi phyogs su yo byad gtong ba'i
NK114(ye)001:2805: don du ni lcags kyi pha gu bzhin rnam par
NK114(ye)001:2806: pa / sra ba / las ngan gyi bag chags
NK114(ye)001:2807: goms pa ni rdo rje'i 'dag pa bzhin du mkhregsa
NK114(ye)001:2808: pa / sra ba / pa / nges 'byung gi
NK114(ye)001:2809: rlan dang bral zhing dad pa la sogs pa'i dge
NK114(ye)001:2810: ba'i lo tog gang yang skye ru mi btub pas
NK114(ye)001:2811: tha bar gyur ba dam pa'i chos ma yin pa
NK114(ye)001:2812: gzhan gang gis kyang gdul ba'i thabs kyi brtan pa
NK114(ye)001:2813: dang bral ba gang yin pa de la dgongs nas
NK114(ye)001:2814: pa / sra ba / pa / / chos kyi
NK114(ye)001:2815: 'khor lo bskor bar mdzad du gsol zhes zhu ba
NK114(ye)001:2817: de yang 'di ltar phyogs bcu'i zhing rab 'byams na
NK114(ye)001:2818: mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas chos kyi che
NK114(ye)001:2820: chos la dkon pa'i 'du shes 'jog pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2821: bskul ba po'i tshogs rdzogs pa'i phyir chos mi gsung ba'i tshul gyis bzhugs pa de thams cad la /
NK114(ye)001:2822: dad mos rtse gcig pas thal mo sbyar te /
NK114(ye)001:2823: tshangs pa bzhin du smon lam dang snying stobs dang gtong phod dang ldan par bskul ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:2824: tshe dang ldan pa rab 'byor bzhin du 'dri zhing lan ldon pa la mkhas pas bskul ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:2825: byang chub sems dpa' spyan ras gzigs dang /
NK114(ye)001:2826: gsang ba'i bdag po bzhin du zab cing rgya che ba'i gnas bskul ba la mkhas pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2827: 'phags pa blo gros mi zad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2828: li tsa b+ai dri med grags pa bzhin du bdag
NK114(ye)001:2829: nyid kyis spobs pas thabs la mkhas par bskul bar
NK114(ye)001:2830: dmigs te / 'di ni gti mug gi gnyen po
NK114(ye)001:2831: yin pas sam yang na thog med nas srid par
NK114(ye)001:2832: 'khyams byed kyi rgyu'i gtso bo 'dod chags sam sred
NK114(ye)001:2833: pa yin pas de'i gnyen por drang don dang nges
NK114(ye)001:2834: don sna tshogs pa'i rjod byed sde snod gsum dang
NK114(ye)001:2835: brjod bya bslab pa gsum gyi ngo bo chos 'khor
NK114(ye)001:2836: gyi rim pa gsum du bsdu ba'i rtsibs rnon pos
NK114(ye)001:2837: gang zag dang chos la bdag tu zhen pas drangs
NK114(ye)001:2838: pa'i nyon mongs dang shes bya'i sgrib pa bag chags
NK114(ye)001:2839: dang bcas pa gcod par byed cing mngon par mtho
NK114(ye)001:2840: ba dang nges par legs pa'i mu khyud las 'da'
NK114(ye)001:2841: ba med par 'dzin pa de bdag gzhan sems can
NK114(ye)001:2842: thams cad kyi rgyud la rang rang gi mos pa
NK114(ye)001:2843: dang 'tshams par 'pho ba'i tshul gyis bskor bar mdzad
NK114(ye)001:2845: dge ba'i bshes gnyen rnams la dngos su bskul bar bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:2846: de la spyir chos kyi 'khor lo la bzhed tshul mi 'dra ba yod de /
NK114(ye)001:2847: bye brag smra ba rnams mthong lam kho na chos 'khor du 'dod de /
NK114(ye)001:2848: sngar bcom ldan 'das kyis bden pa bzhi'i chos gsungs
NK114(ye)001:2849: pas kun shes koon+da nyi'i rgyud la mthong lam skyes
NK114(ye)001:2851: kye ma bcom ldan 'das kyis chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ro zhes sgra bsgrags pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:2853: 'khor los sgyur ba'i 'khor lo rin po che dang chos mthun pa mthong lam na yod de /
