NK114(ye)001:2859: ma rgyal ba las rgyal ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:2861: de bzhin du mthong lam gyis dmigs yul myur du gcod pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2862: dmigs rnam snga ma 'dor ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:2864: khams gong ma'i bden pa la dmigs pas mtho bar 'phar ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:2865: 'og ma'i bden pa la dmigs pas dma' bar 'bab pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2866: bar chad med lam gyis spang bya'i thob pa gcod pas ma rgyal ba las rgyal ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:2867: rnam grol lam gyis spang bya spangs pas bral thob
NK114(ye)001:2868: 'dren pas rgyal ba rnam du 'god pa dang chos
NK114(ye)001:2871: kha cig 'phags lam brgyad chos 'khor yin te /
NK114(ye)001:2872: ngag las mtha' 'tsho ba gsum tshul khrims kyi bslab pas bsdus pas brten pa'i lte ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:2873: lta ba rtog pa gnyis shes rab kyi bslab pas bsdus pas gcod pa'i rtsibs lta bu dang /
NK114(ye)001:2874: lhag ma gsum ting nge 'dzin gyi bslab pas bsdus
NK114(ye)001:2875: pas sdud pa'i mu khyud lta bu yin no zhes
NK114(ye)001:2876: bzhed / 'on kyang theg chen pa rnams ni lung
NK114(ye)001:2877: dang rtogs pa'i chos thams cad chos 'khor du bzhed
NK114(ye)001:2878: bzhed / de / de dag dam pa'i chos kyi ngo bo yin pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2879: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas nas da lta'i gang zag gi
NK114(ye)001:2880: bar rgyud gcig nas gcig tu 'khor ba'i phyir zhes
NK114(ye)001:2883: gtsug na rin po che'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:2884: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa mdzad pa la //
NK114(ye)001:2885: gang gis gsol ba 'debs pa de //
NK114(ye)001:2886: dbang gi rgyal po lta bu ste //
NK114(ye)001:2889: gzhan yang chos spangs pa'i nyes pa 'dag cing tshe
NK114(ye)001:2890: rabs thams cad du dam pa'i chos 'dzin par 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:2891: ro // drug pa mya ngan las mi 'da' bar gsol ba 'debs pa'i yan lag ni /
NK114(ye)001:2892: theg chen 'phags pa slob pa dang mi slob pa
NK114(ye)001:2893: rnams la skye shi rang mtshan pa yod par lta
NK114(ye)001:2894: ba'i log lta'i gnyen po ste /
NK114(ye)001:2895: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams mu med pa na
NK114(ye)001:2896: bzhugs pa'i rgyal ba sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams
NK114(ye)001:2897: dang / dee yi thugs sras byang chub sems dpa'
NK114(ye)001:2898: dge ba'i bshes gnyen gang zhig sku dngos kyi gdul
NK114(ye)001:2900: rtag 'dzin can rnams kyi rtag 'dzin ldog pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2901: sku gdung ring bsrel gyis gdul bya'i don 'byung ba
NK114(ye)001:2902: sogs kyi phyir mya ngan las 'da' bar bzhed pa
NK114(ye)001:2903: de dag la dmigs te thal mo sbyar nas /
NK114(ye)001:2904: sngon bdag cag gi ston pa la dge bsnyen tsun+dasa
NK114(ye)001:2905: gsol ba btab pa bzhin du gsol ba gdab par
NK114(ye)001:2906: bya ste / khyed rnams mya ngan las 'das par
NK114(ye)001:2907: gyur na rnam par grol ba'i thabs kyis spangs par
NK114(ye)001:2908: gyur pa'i 'gro ba 'di thams cad kyis chos dang
NK114(ye)001:2909: chos min gyi khyad par mi shes /
NK114(ye)001:2910: lam dang lam min gyi dbye ba mi shes pas
NK114(ye)001:2911: sdug bsngal rgyu 'bras kyi gnas skabs bsten pa las
NK114(ye)001:2912: thar pa'i dus med pa'i tshul 'di lta bu mthong
NK114(ye)001:2913: nas bskal pa rgya mtsho'i bar du mya ngan las
NK114(ye)001:2914: 'da' ba min par zhabs pad rdo rje'i gdan khri
NK114(ye)001:2915: la bzhugs par mdzad pa'i slad du lus dang longs
NK114(ye)001:2916: spyod dge ba'i dngos po kun gyi rin thang thams
NK114(ye)001:2917: cad gcig tu bsdoms te spungs nas phul ba yin
NK114(ye)001:2918: pas bzhugs par mdzad du gsol zhes zhus pas bzhugs
NK114(ye)001:2919: par zhal gyis bzhes par bsam mo //
NK114(ye)001:2921: nyon cig tshangs pa'i rgyal po khyod //
NK114(ye)001:2923: bsod nams de ni khyad par 'phags //
NK114(ye)001:2924: sangs rgyas mya ngan 'da' mi mnga' //
NK114(ye)001:2925: zhes pas gnas skabs su tshe'i bar chad thams cad
NK114(ye)001:2926: zhi nas dus ma yin par 'chi bar mi 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:2927: zhing / mthar thug 'chi med zhi ba myang 'das kyi go 'phang thob pa'i rgyur 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:2928: bdun pa bsngo ba'i yan lag ni /
NK114(ye)001:2929: 'di ltar bdag tu blta ba dang bcas pas srid
NK114(ye)001:2930: pa'i bde 'bras la dmigs pa'i dge ba ni bsod
NK114(ye)001:2931: nams cha mthun zhes bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:2932: thabs shes khyad par can gyis ma zin pas khong
NK114(ye)001:2933: khro la sogs pa'i rkyen gyis zad par 'gyur bas
NK114(ye)001:2935: gal te rkyen gyis ma zad du zin kyang de
NK114(ye)001:2936: 'dra ba'i rnam par dkar ba de'i 'bras bu yang
NK114(ye)001:2937: srid par lan gcig tsam du mngon par mtho ba
NK114(ye)001:2938: lha dang mi'i gnas thob kyang /
NK114(ye)001:2939: de nas las de myong stobs kyis zad nas srid
NK114(ye)001:2940: pa phyi mar ltung ba'i sdug bsngal dang cho nge
NK114(ye)001:2941: ste smre ngag 'don pa dang bcas pa'i rang bzhin
NK114(ye)001:2943: de bzhin du nyan rang gi sar yang bsngo bar mi bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:2944: don gnyis mthar ma phyin par phung po lhag med du zad par 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:2945: des na dge ba bsags kyang thabs la mi mkhas pas the tshom skye ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:2946: dge bar bsgyur ba'i 'dun pa med pas lung ma
NK114(ye)001:2947: bstan pa de'i gnyen por theg pa chen po'i bsngo
NK114(ye)001:2948: ba'i tshul bla na med pa la bslab par bya
NK114(ye)001:2949: ste / de yang bsngo rgyu'i dge rtsa ni phal po che las /
NK114(ye)001:2950: 'gro kun dge rtsa ji snyed yod pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:2951: byas dang byed 'gyur de bzhin byed pa dag /
NK114(ye)001:2952: ces 'gro ba gzhan thams cad kyi dge ba ji snyed yod pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:2953: rang gi dus gsum gyi dge ba thams cad do //
NK114(ye)001:2954: ched du bya ba ni sems can thams cad la
NK114(ye)001:2955: dmigs nas rdzogs pa'i byang chub 'ba' zhig gi sar
NK114(ye)001:2956: bsngo ba'o // dmigs rnam ni med snang sgyu ma lta bu'i tshul du'o //
NK114(ye)001:2957: ngo bo ni lcags khams la gser 'gyur gyi rtsis
NK114(ye)001:2958: thebs pa bzhin dge rtsa byang chub tu 'dun pas
NK114(ye)001:2959: bsgyur ba ste / 'jam dpal zhing gi yon tan bkod pa las /
NK114(ye)001:2960: chos rnams thams cad rkyen bzhin te //
NK114(ye)001:2961: 'dun pa'i rtse la rab tu gnas //
NK114(ye)001:2962: gang gis smon lam ci btab pa //
NK114(ye)001:2965: tshul 'di ni sangs rgyas rnams kyi thabs la mkhas
NK114(ye)001:2966: pa'i khyad chos las ston pa gzhan gyi lugs phyi
NK114(ye)001:2967: rol pa la ni grags pa med de /
NK114(ye)001:2969: bsod nams bya ba'i tshogs dag ni //
NK114(ye)001:2970: sems can rnams la yongs bsngo ba //
NK114(ye)001:2971: thub dbang khyed kyis gang gsungs pa //
NK114(ye)001:2972: de gzhan bstan bcos las ma bshad //
NK114(ye)001:2974: bsngo ba'i tshig kyang 'phags sa thob pa'i bden tshig
NK114(ye)001:2975: grub pa zhig gis gsungs pa'i rjes su 'brang bar
NK114(ye)001:2977: bsngo ba dang smon lam gyi khyad par ni /
NK114(ye)001:2978: rgyu dge ba sngon du song yang rung /
NK114(ye)001:2980: dge rtsa la dmigs pa can ni bsngo ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:2981: de ma yin pa 'dod rgyal du brjod pa smon lam mo //
NK114(ye)001:2982: des na bsngo ba la smon lam gyis khyab kyang /
NK114(ye)001:2983: smon lam tsam la bsngo bas ma khyab bo //
NK114(ye)001:2985: dge rtsa mi zad cing dpag tu med par byed de /
NK114(ye)001:2987: blo gros rgya mtshos zhus pa las /
NK114(ye)001:2988: ji ltar chu thigs rgya mtsho che nang lhung //
NK114(ye)001:2989: rgya mtsho ma zad bar du de mi 'dzad //
NK114(ye)001:2990: de bzhin byang chub yongs bsngosa dge ba yang //
NK114(ye)001:2991: byang chub ma thob bar du de mi 'dzad //
NK114(ye)001:2993: byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod las kyang /
NK114(ye)001:2994: sh+aa ri'i bu byang chub sems dpa'i mkhas pa ni sbyin pa nyung ngu yang mang por byed de /
NK114(ye)001:2995: ye shes kyi stobs kyis lhag par byed do //
NK114(ye)001:2996: shes rab kyi stobs kyis rgyas par byed do //
NK114(ye)001:2997: bsngo ba'i stobs kyis dpag tu med par byed do //
NK114(ye)001:2999: gsum pa lus bran du dbul ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:3000: spyir longs spyod rang la yod pas chog shes par
NK114(ye)001:3001: byed cing khyad par du rab tu byung ba rnams
NK114(ye)001:3002: ni lto 'grangs lhag skyob tsam gyis chog shes par
NK114(ye)001:3003: byed pa ni brkam chags kyi gdung ba zhi ba'i
NK114(ye)001:3004: bdud rtsi'i btung ba lta bu yin pas de dang
NK114(ye)001:3005: ldan na bdag tu bzung ba'i dngos rdzas rgya chen
NK114(ye)001:3006: po mchod rgyu med na'ang cung zad tsam gyis dmigs
NK114(ye)001:3008: bdag pos ma bzung ba dang yid sprul gyis mchod
NK114(ye)001:3009: na rang gi longs spyod kyis mchod pa dang 'dra
NK114(ye)001:3011: dgos pa'i yo byad cung zad tsam gyis ma ngomsa
NK114(ye)001:3012: par nor dang longs spyod sna tshogs pa'i gsog bskrun
NK114(ye)001:3013: la 'bad cing mang po yod bzhin du ser snas
NK114(ye)001:3014: bcings nas phul mi nus na /
NK114(ye)001:3015: skyes bu'i yid la ma bzung ba'i mchod pa'i sprin
NK114(ye)001:3016: te mang po yang gtong ba'i dngos po dang 'brel
NK114(ye)001:3017: chad pas tshig tsam dag gi pha mthar 'khyamsa te
NK114(ye)001:3018: mchod yul rnams rdzun gyis bslu ba'i nyes dmigs dang
NK114(ye)001:3019: / dmigs pa'i rnam pa gcig po la mchog tu
NK114(ye)001:3020: 'dzin pa tsam du zad pas de la skrag par
NK114(ye)001:3021: gyur nas bdag gi lus mkho zhing dgos pa gces
NK114(ye)001:3022: shing phangs pa 'di nyid mdzes shing yid du 'ong
NK114(ye)001:3023: bar dmigs te dbang thob pa'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK114(ye)001:3024: rnams kyis ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku rnams
NK114(ye)001:3025: la rang rang gi lus smon lam gus pa'i gdan
NK114(ye)001:3026: khrir phul ba bzhin du mchod yul rnams kyi stan
NK114(ye)001:3028: dus gtan du rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa rnams
NK114(ye)001:3029: kyi bran du phrin las kyi byed pa por dam
NK114(ye)001:3030: bcas nas rtag tu sgo gsum gyis dngos brgyud gang
NK114(ye)001:3031: rung du sems can la phan pa 'ba' zhig bsgrub
NK114(ye)001:3032: pa la'nga brtson par bya'o snyam du do gal bgyid
NK114(ye)001:3034: rgyal po la sogs pa'i sdig can gyi mthus non
NK114(ye)001:3035: te de'i bran du gyur nas sgo gsum ngal zhing
NK114(ye)001:3036: dub pa ni grangs mang yang /
NK114(ye)001:3037: des ni 'di phyi thams cad du sdug bsngal 'ba' zhig bsgrub pa las don ci yang med la /
NK114(ye)001:3038: gtan du bslu ba med pa'i skyabs gnas dam pa
NK114(ye)001:3039: dkon mchog gsum gyi bran du gyur pa yin no
NK114(ye)001:3040: snyam pa tsam la'ang bsod nams dpag tu med pa
NK114(ye)001:3042: rnam par rtog pa de lta bu mi tshe ril
NK114(ye)001:3043: po gcig tu'ang yid yul du 'char ma myong ba
NK114(ye)001:3045: de dag ni shin tu skal ba ngan pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:3046: des na mchog gsum gyi 'bangsa su snying thag pa
NK114(ye)001:3047: nas dam bcas pa'i gang zag de ni dkon mchog
NK114(ye)001:3048: gi thugs rje'i grib bsil la brten nas /
NK114(ye)001:3049: dper na so ka'i dus su tsha bas gdung ba
NK114(ye)001:3050: na ljon shing me tog gis brgyan pa yal ga
NK114(ye)001:3051: dang lo 'dab rgyas pa'i 'jo sgeg can gyi grib
NK114(ye)001:3052: mar bsdad pas dbugs 'byin thob pa ltar tshe 'dir
NK114(ye)001:3053: sdug bsngal las skyob cing legs dgu'i dngos po 'byur
NK114(ye)001:3054: bar ma zad 'chi ba'i tshe na'ang sangs rgyas dang
NK114(ye)001:3055: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis lam sna drangs te
NK114(ye)001:3056: dag pa'i zhing du 'khrid par mdzad cing /
NK114(ye)001:3057: gal te tshul khrims 'chal ba la sogs pa'i las
NK114(ye)001:3058: ngan la goms pa'i dbang gis rnam pa kun tu
NK114(ye)001:3059: sdang zhing 'khrugs pa'i khro gtum can gshin rje'i pho
NK114(ye)001:3060: nya'i mdun sar son na yang dkon mchog dran pa
NK114(ye)001:3061: tsam gyi mod la de dag gi khro gnyer rtsub
NK114(ye)001:3062: mo de 'jig par gyur nas gnod pa med par
NK114(ye)001:3063: sdug bsngal las thar bar 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:3064: de ni rin thang ngam don chen po zad mi shes pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:3065: gzhan yang rdo rje las rim las kyang /
NK114(ye)001:3066: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas sras bcas dang //
NK114(ye)001:3067: dbang phyug sangs rgyas da lta bdag /
NK114(ye)001:3068: ma 'ongs rang bzhin sems can la //
NK114(ye)001:3069: dgos pa gsum phyir lus dbul bya //
NK114(ye)001:3070: mchog gi yon phyir snod du 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:3071: zhes phyogs bcu'i bde gshegs sras dang bcas pa da
NK114(ye)001:3072: lta'i lam ston yod pa la ltos nas 'das pa'i
NK114(ye)001:3073: sangs rgyas su mos te lus phul bas sku gsung
NK114(ye)001:3074: thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i ye shes la dbang
NK114(ye)001:3076: dbang phyug de da ltar ba'i sangs rgyas bla ma
NK114(ye)001:3077: la lus phul bas sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dam
NK114(ye)001:3078: pa'i ye shes thob pa'i snod du rung ba'i dgos
NK114(ye)001:3079: pa dang / ma 'ongs pa na sangs rgyas su
NK114(ye)001:3080: 'gyur ba sems can gyi khams bde gshegs snying po'i
NK114(ye)001:3081: khyab byed can la lus phul bas sems can gyi
NK114(ye)001:3082: don mthar phyin pa'i dgos pa yod pas /
NK114(ye)001:3083: bde gshegs dbang phyug sems can la //
NK114(ye)001:3084: dgos pa gsum phyir lus dbul lo //
NK114(ye)001:3086: gnyis pa don bsdus te dgos pa brjod pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:3087: de ltar sems sbyangs shing tshogs bsags pa des ni
NK114(ye)001:3088: thog ma med pa nas ma rig pa gti mug
NK114(ye)001:3089: gi mthus non te de kho na nyid kyi don
NK114(ye)001:3090: la rmongs shing las dang las kyi 'bras bu yang
NK114(ye)001:3091: ma shes nas sdig pa'i las du ma goms shing
NK114(ye)001:3092: bsags pa'i sgrib pa dang ldan pa bdag gi rgyud
NK114(ye)001:3093: kyi byang chub kyi sems rin po che skye ba
NK114(ye)001:3094: la gegs su gyur pa'i dri ma'i rnam pa mtha'
NK114(ye)001:3095: dag btso blag mkhan mkhas pas tshos kyi don du
NK114(ye)001:3096: ras yug khrus kyis sbyangs pa kha dog bsgyur sla
NK114(ye)001:3097: ba'am / byi dor shin tu bsten pa'i dwangs shel
NK114(ye)001:3098: la gzugs brnyan 'char rung ba ltar bsod nams ma
NK114(ye)001:3099: yin pas rgyud rnyog pa can du byas pa de
NK114(ye)001:3100: nyid dwangs shing gtsang mar gyur te dag pa'i sems
NK114(ye)001:3101: kyi nang du rags pa brda' las byung ba'i sems
NK114(ye)001:3102: bskyed cho ga'i sgo nas blangs na ji lta ba
NK114(ye)001:3103: bzhin du thob pas bla na med pa'i sdom pa
NK114(ye)001:3104: de'i gzugs brnyan dngom pa yin no zhes pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:3105: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gsum ste /
NK114(ye)001:3106: blang yul dpang por bya ba /
NK114(ye)001:3108: sdom pa'i thob mtshams bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:3110: de la bdag cag 'khor ba'i sems can ni las
NK114(ye)001:3111: ngan pa'i gzhan dbang du gyur pa'i steng 'dod po'i
NK114(ye)001:3112: lha bdud sdig can chung ma pad+ma'i phreng ba dang
NK114(ye)001:3113: bcas pa'i spyi bo na me tog gi mda' lnga
NK114(ye)001:3115: bdud ces bya ba ni thar pa'i lam gyi chos
NK114(ye)001:3116: bsgrub pa'i bar chad du 'gyur bas chos dang 'jig
NK114(ye)001:3117: rten gyi bya bas khengs te dregs par byed pa
NK114(ye)001:3118: dang / blang dor gyi phyogs la blo rmongs par byed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3119: phyin ci log gi lta bas kun tu rmongs par byed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3120: brjed nges shing dran pa nyams pas brgyal bar byed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3121: 'jig rten chos brgyad kyi phyogs la sems te g.yeng
NK114(ye)001:3122: bar byed pa ste de'i me tog gi mda' bsnun
NK114(ye)001:3123: pas nyon mongs pa lnga gang shas che ba de
NK114(ye)001:3124: la phogs pas de rab tu 'bar bar gyur te
NK114(ye)001:3125: de'i dbang du song nas thar pa dang mngon par
NK114(ye)001:3126: mtho ba las nyams par gyur pa'i nyes pa brgya
NK114(ye)001:3127: phrag mang po'i g.yang sa yang zhing thar dka' bar
NK114(ye)001:3128: ltung ba yi rgyud la rims nad kyi rnam grangs
NK114(ye)001:3129: mi 'dra ba mang pos dus ring po nas shin
NK114(ye)001:3130: tu btab pa'i nad pa ste de lta bu'i gang
NK114(ye)001:3131: zag rnams la nad kyi rnam grangs mang po gang
NK114(ye)001:3132: dang gang gis btab ce na /
NK114(ye)001:3133: nyon mongs dug gsum dang cha mnyam pa ste bzhi
NK114(ye)001:3134: po re re la nyi khri chig stong rer phye
NK114(ye)001:3135: bas brgyad khri bzhi stong ngam /
NK114(ye)001:3136: rtsa ba'i nyon mongs pa drug dang nye ba'i nyon mongs pa nyi shur phye bas sam /
NK114(ye)001:3138: mnyam par ma bzhag pa'i sa pa 'dod pa'i khams
NK114(ye)001:3139: na sems phyi rol tu bltas te rnam par 'phro
NK114(ye)001:3140: zhing zag par byed pa 'dod pa'i zag pa dang
NK114(ye)001:3141: / mnyam bzhag gi sa pa khams gong ma gnyis
NK114(ye)001:3142: na sems kha nang du bltas te zag pa srid
NK114(ye)001:3144: de gnyis kyi gnas ma rig pa'i zag pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:3146: 'dod pa'i chu bo 'dod pa tshol ba la zhugs pa'am 'dod pa'i nyon mongs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3147: srid pa'i chu bo khams gong ma'i de dang /
NK114(ye)001:3149: ma rig pa'i chu bo ste chu bo bzhi dang /
NK114(ye)001:3150: de bzhin du de bzhi la 'dod pa'i sbyor ba sogs bzhir brjod pa sbyor ba bzhi dang /
NK114(ye)001:3151: 'dod pa nye bar len pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3152: lta ba nye bar len pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3153: tshul khrims dang brtul zhugs nye bar len pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3154: bdag tu smra ba nye bar len pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:3155: nye bar len pa bzhi dang /
NK114(ye)001:3158: gti mug gi 'ching ba ste 'ching ba gsum dang /
NK114(ye)001:3159: rjes su chags pa'i kun sbyor zhes pa khams gsum
NK114(ye)001:3160: gyi 'dod chags te des khams gsum la yid mi
NK114(ye)001:3161: 'byung bas dge ba la mi spyod cing mi dge
NK114(ye)001:3162: ba bsgrub pas phyi ma la sdug bsngal dang kun
NK114(ye)001:3163: tu sbyor bar byed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3164: de bzhin du khong khro dang /
NK114(ye)001:3166: ma rig pa'i kun sbyor dang /
NK114(ye)001:3169: the tshom gyi kun sbyor dang /
NK114(ye)001:3170: phrag dog gi kun sbyor dang /
NK114(ye)001:3171: ser sna'i kun sbyor te de dag re res kyang
NK114(ye)001:3172: mi dge ba spyod pa'i rgyu byas nas phyi mar
NK114(ye)001:3173: sdug bsngal la sbyor bas kun sbyor zhes bya ste
NK114(ye)001:3174: / de ltar kun nas sbyor ba dgu dang /
NK114(ye)001:3175: dgu po de la nang gses kyi dbye bas srid pa'i kun tu sbyor ba bco brgyad do //
NK114(ye)001:3176: de yang nga rgyal la bdun /
NK114(ye)001:3178: mchog 'dzin la gnyis su dbye bas so //
NK114(ye)001:3188: 'chab pa ste zhi gnas dang btang snyoms kyi dus
NK114(ye)001:3189: na yang yang sems la dkris par byed pa'i kun
NK114(ye)001:3196: rgod pa ste nyon mongs can la rtag tu 'byung bas nyon mongs pa'i sa mang po drug dang /
NK114(ye)001:3202: rnam 'tshe ste gang la yod pa'i rgyud kyang dri
NK114(ye)001:3203: mar byed pa'i nyon mongs pa'i dri ma drug dang
NK114(ye)001:3208: the tshom ste rim pa bzhin du /
NK114(ye)001:3209: rab tu byung bar 'dod pa'i dus dang /
NK114(ye)001:3210: legs par bskul ba bsgrub pa'i dus dang /
NK114(ye)001:3212: sems rab tu 'dzin pa'i dus dang /
NK114(ye)001:3213: btang snyoms kyi dus na dge ba'i phyogs la mi 'jug par byed pa'i sgrib pa lnga dang /
NK114(ye)001:3218: gnod sems te khams gsum pa'i tha ma 'dod pa'i
NK114(ye)001:3219: khams pa'i rgyud kho na la yod pa'i tha ma'i
NK114(ye)001:3220: cha dang mthun pa lnga dang /
NK114(ye)001:3225: nga rgyal te gong ma'i cha dang mthun pa lnga dang /
NK114(ye)001:3235: rnam 'tshe ste sa mang po ba bcu dang /
NK114(ye)001:3237: ngo tsha med pa ste mi dge ba'i sa mang
NK114(ye)001:3238: po ba gnyis te de la sogs pa'i rims nad
NK114(ye)001:3239: drag po gang yin pa de ni shin tu gnod
NK114(ye)001:3241: de dag las khro ba lta bu gcig gis kyang
NK114(ye)001:3242: 'dzam gling na gnas pa'i mi kun gyis mtshon pa'i
NK114(ye)001:3243: sems can rnams brlag par byed de /
NK114(ye)001:3245: de gcig gis kyang 'dzam gling na //
NK114(ye)001:3246: gnas pa'i mi kun brlag byed na //
NK114(ye)001:3248: nad kyi rnam grangs de dag gso ba'i thabs kyang
NK114(ye)001:3249: 'du ba'i nad la dpyad byed pa'i gso dpyad phal
NK114(ye)001:3250: pa rnams ji ltar bzang yang de'i mdun sar dbugs
NK114(ye)001:3251: mi phyin te bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi po gang yang
NK114(ye)001:3252: rung ba dag gis gzir ba'i nad tsam gso shes
NK114(ye)001:3253: kyi de'i rgyu gso mi shes pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:3254: 'o na su zhig la brten zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:3255: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams ni sman pa mchog
NK114(ye)001:3256: yin te shes bya thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyis
NK114(ye)001:3257: lus kyi zug rngu'i rgyu 'byin cing dam pa'i chos
NK114(ye)001:3258: kyi sman la bsten nas nyon mongs pa'i zug rngu
NK114(ye)001:3261: de dag gso ba'i sman gzhan ni //
NK114(ye)001:3262: phyogs rnams kun nas mi rnyed na //
NK114(ye)001:3263: de la sman pa thams cad mkhyen //
NK114(ye)001:3264: zug rngu thams cad 'byin pa yi //
NK114(ye)001:3265: bka' ltar mi byed sems pa ni //
NK114(ye)001:3266: shin tu gti mug smad pa'i gnas //
NK114(ye)001:3268: des na de la rgyu mtshan shes pa'i sgo nas
NK114(ye)001:3269: skyabs su lhag par dong zhig dang sman gyi mchog
NK114(ye)001:3270: nyon mongs brgyad khri bzhi stong po thams cad kyi
NK114(ye)001:3271: gnyen por gyur ba byang chub kyi sems rin po
NK114(ye)001:3272: che thob par 'gyur ro zhes tshogs zhing la mos
NK114(ye)001:3274: de ltar bskyed na len pa'i yul dam pa'i bla ma yod na rab /
NK114(ye)001:3275: med na rten khyad par can nam /
NK114(ye)001:3276: de yang med kyang rung ste gang ltar yang tshogs zhing gsal gdab pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:3277: yul ga shed nas spyan drangs dgos pa ma yin
NK114(ye)001:3278: kyang sngar tshogs bsags pa'i zhing gsal bzhin pa de
NK114(ye)001:3279: la slar yang nges shes drag po bskyed nas bdag
NK114(ye)001:3280: gi mos pa brtan pos gsol ba btab pa gang
NK114(ye)001:3281: gi slad du sems bskyed len pa'i gnas 'dir gshegs
NK114(ye)001:3282: nas mtha' yas pa'i sems can gyi khams thams cad
NK114(ye)001:3283: la rtag tu mas bu la brtse ba ltar dmigs
NK114(ye)001:3284: med thugs rje chen pos gzigs shing mkhyen pa'i ye
NK114(ye)001:3285: shes kyis chags thogs med par dgongs pa'i ston pa
NK114(ye)001:3286: mchog sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams ni theg pa
NK114(ye)001:3287: chen po'i lam gyis phyir mi ldog pa la gnas
NK114(ye)001:3288: pa'i skyes bu byang chub sems dpa' 'ba' zhig pa'i
NK114(ye)001:3289: tshogs kyi dbus na zla ba rgyu skar gyi tshogs
NK114(ye)001:3290: kyis bskor ba'am / ri rgyal lhun po ri phran
NK114(ye)001:3291: rnams kyi dbus na mngon par 'phags pa ltar sku
NK114(ye)001:3292: gsung thugs kyi yon tan dang gzi byin mchog tu
NK114(ye)001:3293: 'bar ba'i zhing mthong na mi mthun pa med par
NK114(ye)001:3294: lham mer mdzes shing bdag cag rnams la dgyes pa'i
NK114(ye)001:3295: kyis bskor ba'am / zhal gyis phyogs / 'dzum pa'i spyan gyis gzigs /
NK114(ye)001:3296: brtse bas thugs kyis dgongs te mngon sum bzhin du
NK114(ye)001:3297: bzhugs pa la dad gus kyi gdung shugs drag po
NK114(ye)001:3298: bskyed par bya'o // gnyis pa cho ga dngos brjod pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:3299: spyir rgya chen spyod pa'i lugs kyi cho ga rnams
NK114(ye)001:3300: su smon 'jug gi sdom pa 'bogs pa'i cho ga
NK114(ye)001:3302: zab mo lta ba'i lugs la'ang slob dpon mkhas pa
NK114(ye)001:3303: chen po krish+na pa'i spyod 'jug gi dka' 'grel las
NK114(ye)001:3304: gsungs pa ltar / bslab bya la slob mi nus
NK114(ye)001:3305: pa dang nus pa'i khyad par las smon 'jug gi
NK114(ye)001:3306: sems bskyed dang sdom pa len tshul so sor dbye
NK114(ye)001:3307: gsungs pa ltar / na / smon sems tsam len na /
NK114(ye)001:3308: ji ltar sngon gyi bde gshegs kyis //
NK114(ye)001:3309: byang chub thugs ni bskyed pa ltar //
NK114(ye)001:3310: de bzhin 'gro la phan don du //
NK114(ye)001:3311: byang chub sems ni bskyed par bgyi //
NK114(ye)001:3313: 'jug sdom dang bcas na dkyus bzhin no //
NK114(ye)001:3314: gang ltar yang skyabs 'gro bdun cu pa las /
NK114(ye)001:3315: sdom pa kun la yod mod kyis //
NK114(ye)001:3316: skyabs su ma song ba la med //
NK114(ye)001:3318: so thar la sogs pa'i sdom pa gang blang kyang skyabs 'gro gzhi rten du dgos la /
NK114(ye)001:3319: khyad par du byang sdom gyi sngon du ni theg
NK114(ye)001:3320: chen thun mong ma yin pa'i tshul gyi skyabs su
NK114(ye)001:3321: 'gro ba lan gsum gyi sgo nas skyabs 'gro byas
NK114(ye)001:3323: skabs 'dir smon 'jug stabs gcig tu len pa la /
NK114(ye)001:3325: blo bcos pa sngar bshad pa ltar bla ma nyid kyis byas la /
NK114(ye)001:3326: gal te bla ma med na rang gis blo bcos
NK114(ye)001:3327: pa'i tshul sems la nges par byas nas phyag 'tshal
NK114(ye)001:3329: pus mo g.yas pa'i lha nga sa la btsugs nas thal mo sbyar te /
NK114(ye)001:3330: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams dang /
NK114(ye)001:3331: sa bcu la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rnams dang /
NK114(ye)001:3332: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po rnams dgongs
NK114(ye)001:3333: su gsol ba gsum gyis chos kyi dbyings spros pa
NK114(ye)001:3334: thams cad dang bral ba'i ngang la mnyam par bzhag
NK114(ye)001:3335: pa las 'dzin med sgyu ma lta bu'i snying rje
NK114(ye)001:3336: chen po'i ngo bo sad par byas pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:3337: de yang chos nyid la mnyam par bzhag pa'i tshe
NK114(ye)001:3338: dgra bcom 'gog pa la zhugs pa bzhin thugs rjes
NK114(ye)001:3339: sems can la mi dgongs pa ma yin te /
NK114(ye)001:3340: skad cig kyang g.yel ba med par gdul bya'i khams
NK114(ye)001:3341: la dgongs bzhin bzhugs pa la ngang gi nges shes
NK114(ye)001:3342: pa bskyed nas de bzhin du mos pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:3343: de nas rnam par rtog pa gzhan gyis bar ma chod par 'di ltar bsam par bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:3344: ji ltar na sngon gyi rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK114(ye)001:3345: rgyas bcom ldan 'das thugs sras byang chub sems dpa'
NK114(ye)001:3346: dang bcas pa'i tshogs kyis gzhan don du byang chub
NK114(ye)001:3347: mchog tu thugs bskyed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3348: de rnams kyis lam lhag pa'i bslab pa gsum gyis
NK114(ye)001:3349: bsdus pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa drug dang bsdu
NK114(ye)001:3350: ba bzhi'i don la rim pa bzhin du bslab par
NK114(ye)001:3351: mdzad pa'i brtul zhugs la gnas pa de bzhin du
NK114(ye)001:3352: bdag gis kyang mtha' dag pa ste de thams cad
NK114(ye)001:3353: bsgrub par bya'o snyam du dam bca' yang dag par
NK114(ye)001:3354: blang ba yin no zhes spyir dam bcas nas /
NK114(ye)001:3355: bye brag tu ni thar pa la sgrib par byed
NK114(ye)001:3356: pa'i nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa'i zug rngu'i dum bu
NK114(ye)001:3357: gang zag gi bdag med pa rtogs pa'i stobs kyis
NK114(ye)001:3359: thams cad mkhyen pa la sgrib pa'i shes sgrib ni
NK114(ye)001:3360: chos kyi bdag med yongs rdzogs rtogs shing goms pa
NK114(ye)001:3361: med pas 'khor 'das blang dor du blta ba sogs
NK114(ye)001:3362: yul gyi ro la gcags nas gnyen po'i stobs kyis
NK114(ye)001:3363: drungs nas 'byin ma nus pa yi nyan rang dgra
NK114(ye)001:3364: bcom pa rnams sgrib pa'i dum bu ma bsgral bar
NK114(ye)001:3365: de las bsgral bar bya snyam pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3366: sgrib pa gnyis ka'i 'ching ba dam pos kun nas
NK114(ye)001:3367: dkris pa yi steng du lta bas ma rungs pas
NK114(ye)001:3369: phyin ci log gi grub mtha' la zhugs pa'i mu stegs byed rnams dang /
NK114(ye)001:3370: grub pa'i mtha' gang la yang ma zhugs pa'i phal
NK114(ye)001:3371: pa la sogs pa'i so so'i skye bo dman pa
NK114(ye)001:3372: rnams dang / tshogs sbyor gyi lam la gnas pa
NK114(ye)001:3373: nas sgrib gnyis ci rigs pa dang ldan pa'i theg
NK114(ye)001:3374: chen slob pa 'phags pa'i sa bcu pa'i bar la
NK114(ye)001:3375: gnas pa yi sems can sgrib pa de dag las
NK114(ye)001:3376: ma grol ba rnams bdag gis dgrola bar bya snyam
NK114(ye)001:3377: rnams dang / pa dang / shin tu sdug bsngal
NK114(ye)001:3378: drag po'i shugs kyis gzir bas bzod dka' zhing yun
NK114(ye)001:3379: rnams dang / pa dang / ring ba las /
NK114(ye)001:3380: bde ba'i dbugs 'byin thoba pa med pa'i ngan song
NK114(ye)001:3381: gsum na gnas pa'i sems can rnams dbugsa 'byin chen
NK114(ye)001:3382: rnams dang / pa dang / ring ba las /
NK114(ye)001:3383: po'i gnas / gnas skabs lam gyi rten mtho ris
NK114(ye)001:3384: dang mthar thug thar pa mchog gi go 'phang la
NK114(ye)001:3385: rnams dang / pa dang / ring ba las /
NK114(ye)001:3386: po'i gnas / sbyar ba dang / mdor na srid
NK114(ye)001:3387: pa'i rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba bcu gnyis kyi
NK114(ye)001:3388: rang bzhin bar ma chad par 'khor ba'i 'khor lo'i
NK114(ye)001:3389: rgyar las kyi dbang gis dbang med du chud de
NK114(ye)001:3390: sdug bsngal dngos su myong ba'i sems can phal ba
NK114(ye)001:3391: nas las kyi dbang gis mi 'khor yang rten 'brel
NK114(ye)001:3392: gyi bag chags gnyis snang 'khor ba'i chos su shar
NK114(ye)001:3393: ba tsam dbyings su ma ldog pa'i sa bcu'i byang
NK114(ye)001:3394: chub sems dpa'i bar sems can yod do cog thams
NK114(ye)001:3395: cad mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pa'i ye shes mya
NK114(ye)001:3396: ngan las 'das pa chen po'i grong khyer du bdag
NK114(ye)001:3397: kho nas dgod par byed do zhes kha tsam ma
NK114(ye)001:3398: yin par snying thag pa nas dam bca' bar bya'o
NK114(ye)001:3399: rnams dang / pa dang / ring ba las /
NK114(ye)001:3400: po'i gnas / sbyar ba dang / // de lta
NK114(ye)001:3401: bu'i smon 'jug gnyis po'i sdom pa ltabs gcig tu
NK114(ye)001:3402: cho gas ji ltar bzung ba'i tshul brjod pa ni
NK114(ye)001:3403: sngon byon gyi drang srong byang chub sems dpa' chen
NK114(ye)001:3404: po klu sgrub yab sras rjes 'brangs dang bcas pa
NK114(ye)001:3405: rnams kyi lugs la brten zhes dbu ma lugs kyi
NK114(ye)001:3406: sems bskyed 'bogs pa'i cho ga rgyas bsdus gang rung
NK114(ye)001:3408: gzhung gi tshig 'di dag lan gsum brjod pas kyang rung ngo //
NK114(ye)001:3409: de ltar dang po blangs nas kyang dus rtag du
NK114(ye)001:3410: nyin gyi cha la lan gsum dang mtshan mo'i cha
NK114(ye)001:3411: la gsum mam / nyin zhag phrugs gcig la lan
NK114(ye)001:3412: gsum du spyod 'jug las gsungs pa'i byang sdom len
NK114(ye)001:3413: chog sogs kyi sgo nas smon pa dang 'jug pa
NK114(ye)001:3414: byang chub kyi sems gnyis len zhing /
NK114(ye)001:3415: de yang tshig tsam bton pas kha khral gsod pa
NK114(ye)001:3416: lta bu ma yin par sems kyi rnam pa de
NK114(ye)001:3417: gnyis kyi ngo bor bskyed cing yang yang goms par
NK114(ye)001:3418: bya ba la nan tan du byas nas byang chub
NK114(ye)001:3419: kyi sems bag la nyal ba slong ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:3420: nyams pa gso zhing brjed par mi 'gyur la sems
NK114(ye)001:3421: bskyed kyi stobs kyang gong nas gong du 'phel bar
NK114(ye)001:3422: 'gyur ba'i phyir theg chen lam gyi snying po 'di
NK114(ye)001:3424: gsum pa sdom pa'i thob mtshams bshad pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:3425: cho ga la brten nas sdom pa blang ba la
NK114(ye)001:3426: sogs pa'i gnas skabs 'di dag ni kun rdzob byang
NK114(ye)001:3427: chub kyi sems don du gnyer ba'i dus yin pas
NK114(ye)001:3430: chos rnams thams cad rkyen bzhin te //
NK114(ye)001:3431: 'dun pa'i rtse la rab tu gnas //
NK114(ye)001:3433: spyir 'dus byas kyi chos thams cad rang rang gi rgyu rkyen la rag las shing /
NK114(ye)001:3434: khyad par du rang gi 'dun pa gang la bzhag
NK114(ye)001:3435: pa de'i rtse la sgo gsum gyi bya ba'i chos
NK114(ye)001:3436: de dge mi dge dang dge ba yang bsod nams
NK114(ye)001:3437: cha mthun dang / thar pa cha mthun /
NK114(ye)001:3438: thar pa cha mthun kyang theg dman dang theg chen
NK114(ye)001:3439: thar pa cha mthun rnams gang dang gang du 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:3440: ba'i rkyen chags pas na skabs 'dir yang sems gnyis
NK114(ye)001:3441: stabs gcig tu len pa'i cho ga lan gsum du
NK114(ye)001:3442: brjod pa yi dang pos smon pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3444: gsum pas smon 'jug gnyis ka ches brtan par gyur pa'i mchog nyid 'thob par gsungs pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:3445: slob dpon rgya mtsho'i sprin gyi bzhed pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:3448: de la brjod pa dang po dang /
NK114(ye)001:3450: gsum pa dag gis smon pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3452: gnyis ka ches brtan pa'i mchog nyid thob par 'gyur te /
NK114(ye)001:3453: zhes pas na brjod pa gsum ga'i dus su thob
NK114(ye)001:3454: pa'i blo'i 'dun pa gsum bzhag pas rgyud la shin
NK114(ye)001:3455: tu nges par 'gyur ba'i phyir bla na med pa'o
NK114(ye)001:3456: // 'o na brjod pa dang po'i dus su na'ang
NK114(ye)001:3457: 'jug pa'i khas blang brjod pas smon pa kho nar
NK114(ye)001:3459: 'dir ni smon 'jug ngo bo gcig tu bzhed pa'i phyir skyon med de /
NK114(ye)001:3461: kha cig gis bsod nams mngon par 'du bya ba
NK114(ye)001:3462: dang ldan pa'i sems bskyed pa ni 'jug pa byang
NK114(ye)001:3463: chub kyi sems zhes brjod la /
NK114(ye)001:3464: bsod nams mngon par 'du bya ba dang mi ldan
NK114(ye)001:3465: pa'i sems bskyed pa thams cad smon pa can no
NK114(ye)001:3466: zhes brjod pa de dag drang ba ma yin te
NK114(ye)001:3467: / 'dir ni sems sbyangs pa'i gang zag byang chub
NK114(ye)001:3468: tu smon lam btab cing bslab pa la gnas pa
NK114(ye)001:3469: de'i bslab pa mi 'jig par rjes su bsrung ba
NK114(ye)001:3470: pha rol tu phyin pa drug la spyod pa de
NK114(ye)001:3471: nyid sems bskyed pa 'phel ba dang 'jug pa'i byang
NK114(ye)001:3472: chub kyi sems so zhes blo'i pha rol tu phyin
NK114(ye)001:3474: zhes gsungs pa ltar 'jug pa'i sems blang na smon
NK114(ye)001:3475: sems kyang yod pas khyab ste smon pa'i sems med
NK114(ye)001:3476: par sbyin sogs la dam bcas pa tsam 'jug sems
NK114(ye)001:3478: de med par sbyin sogs la bslab pa 'jug pa'i bslab byar yang mi 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:3479: des na stabs gcig tu len pa'i dus de gnyis
NK114(ye)001:3480: ngo bo tha dad pa ma yin par blo rdzas
NK114(ye)001:3481: gcig dus gcig byed pa gcig pa'i bdag nyid du
NK114(ye)001:3483: byang chub sems dpa'i sa las /
NK114(ye)001:3484: smon pa dang 'jug pa 'di gnyis ni ngo bo
NK114(ye)001:3485: dbyer med pas gzhan gyi don du byed pa gcig
NK114(ye)001:3486: pa nyid dang / tha mi dad pa'i rang bzhin du shes par bya ba nyid do //
NK114(ye)001:3488: 'o na cho ga tha dad pa ltar sbyar ba'i dgos pa gang yin na /
NK114(ye)001:3489: sems bskyed par 'dod la sdom pa blang mi nus pa'i rigs can la dmigs pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:3490: mtshan nyid bsgom stobs kyis skye ba ni don dam byang chub kyi sems te /
NK114(ye)001:3491: de yang grangs med gcig la sogs par lung dam pa nod /
NK114(ye)001:3492: rjes sgrub dam pa dang ldan pas rtogs pa dam
NK114(ye)001:3493: pa stong nyid snying rje'i snying po can khong du
NK114(ye)001:3494: chud pa ste / mdo sde rgyan las /
NK114(ye)001:3495: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rab bsnyen byas /
NK114(ye)001:3496: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rab bsags //
NK114(ye)001:3497: chos la mi rtog ye shes ni //
NK114(ye)001:3498: skyes phyir de ni dam par 'dod //
NK114(ye)001:3500: gsum pa rjes kyi cho ga la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:3501: rang gi sems gzengs bstod pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:3502: gzhan dga' ba bsgom du gzhug pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:3504: bdag la sogs pa'i 'khor ba'i sems can phal pa
NK114(ye)001:3505: rnams kyis sngona chada skye ba lan grangs du ma
NK114(ye)001:3506: blangs kyang bu la gdung sems can gyi pha mas
NK114(ye)001:3507: bu la dang / mngon shes dang ldan zhing rigs
NK114(ye)001:3508: pa'i gnas mang po shes pa'i lha dang drang srong
NK114(ye)001:3509: bu la dang / rnams dang / gnyis ka dang
NK114(ye)001:3510: ldan pa'i tshangs pa la sogs par gyur pa'i tshe
NK114(ye)001:3511: na'ang sems can gzhan gyi don la lta yang ci
NK114(ye)001:3512: bu la dang / rnams dang / smos / rang
NK114(ye)001:3513: gi don nyid du mngon sum du mi skye bar
NK114(ye)001:3514: ma zad rmi lam du rmi ba'ang ma myong ba'i
NK114(ye)001:3515: rin po che thams cad kyi nang na rina chen
NK114(ye)001:3516: dbang gi rgyal po rin che ba ltar /
NK114(ye)001:3517: dge ba'i sems thams cad kya nang nas khyad par
NK114(ye)001:3518: du 'phags pa sngar rang rgyud na med pa'i gsar
NK114(ye)001:3519: pa byang chub kyi sems da lta thob cing rgyud
NK114(ye)001:3520: la skyes pa 'dis ni bdag gi mi yi srid
NK114(ye)001:3521: pa 'dir rang gzhan gnyis ka gtan du 'tshengs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:3522: don 'bras chen po rnyed posa rin thang gzhal du
NK114(ye)001:3525: rgyal bu dwa'u rgyal rigsa las nyams nas gdol ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:3526: dmangs kyi rigs su 'khyams par gyur pa gang zhig
NK114(ye)001:3527: phyis rgyal bu yin par ngo shes nas cho rigsa
NK114(ye)001:3528: kyi lhag par btsun pa rang gi pha'i rgyal srid
NK114(ye)001:3529: kyi gnas gsar du thob pa ji bzhin du sems
NK114(ye)001:3530: kyi rang bzhin chos kyi sku'i gdung ngam de bzhin
NK114(ye)001:3531: gshegs pa'i rigs su gnas kyang sngon chad ngo ma
NK114(ye)001:3532: shes pas rigs de las nyams te /
NK114(ye)001:3533: byams pa'i sems dang bral ba snying rje med pa'i
NK114(ye)001:3534: ma rabs sdig spyod can du 'khyams pa las bdag
NK114(ye)001:3535: nyid theg pa chen po'i rigs can du ngo shes
NK114(ye)001:3536: nas sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrub pa la zhugs
NK114(ye)001:3537: pa rgyal ba kun gyi thugs kyi sras su deng
NK114(ye)001:3538: gi dus gyur te theg chen chos kyi rgyal srid
NK114(ye)001:3539: la dbang bas byang chub semsa dpa' zhes pa'i ming
NK114(ye)001:3540: gi cod pan thob cing sems de ma nyams par
NK114(ye)001:3541: yod pa de srid du nan tan dang bral yang
NK114(ye)001:3542: byang chub sems dpa'i ming yang mi 'dor la nyan
NK114(ye)001:3543: thos dang rang sangs rgyas thams cad kyang zil gyis
NK114(ye)001:3547: dper na rdo rje rin po che ni chag kyang /
NK114(ye)001:3548: thams cad las khyad par du 'phags pa'i gser gyi rgyan zil gyis gnon to //
NK114(ye)001:3549: de bzhin du thams cad mkhyen pa nyid du sems
NK114(ye)001:3550: bskyed pa'i rdo rje rin po che bsam pa log
NK114(ye)001:3551: par zhugs pas chag par gyur kyang /
NK114(ye)001:3552: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas kyi yon tan gyi
NK114(ye)001:3553: gser gyi rgyan zil gyis gnon cing byang chub sems
NK114(ye)001:3555: 'khor ba'i dbul ba thams cad kyang rnam par bzlog go zhes so //
NK114(ye)001:3556: de ltar na sa bcu pa las /
NK114(ye)001:3557: sa dang po la gnas pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:3558: rigs su skyes pa yin no zhes bshad pas 'dir
NK114(ye)001:3559: sdom pa blang ba po 'phags pa'i gang zag yin
NK114(ye)001:3561: nam mkha'i snying po'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:3562: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa yang dag par len
NK114(ye)001:3563: pa ni 'phags pa ma yin pa dag la yang
NK114(ye)001:3566: mos pas spyod pa'i sa la dge ba'i rtsa ba
NK114(ye)001:3567: brtan pa gcig la byang chub kyi sems skye'o zhes
NK114(ye)001:3568: bshad pas sa dang po la gnas pa ni mtshan
NK114(ye)001:3569: nyid bsgoms stobs kyis thob pa'i rigs can yin par
NK114(ye)001:3570: bzung ste / spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:3571: chos thams cad bdag med pa'i ngo bo de kho
NK114(ye)001:3572: na mngon du byed pa'i sa mthong ba'i lam gyis
NK114(ye)001:3573: bsdus pa don dam pa'i byang chub kyi sems ngo
NK114(ye)001:3575: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs su skyes pa yin /
NK114(ye)001:3576: byang chub sems dpa'i sa dang po thob pa yin zhes so //
NK114(ye)001:3577: gnyis pa gzhan dga' ba bsgom du gzhug pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:3578: sa 'og sa steng sa bla'i srid pa gsum ka'i
NK114(ye)001:3579: bdag po gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi rgyal po dang
NK114(ye)001:3580: / tshangs pa la sogs pa dang 'jig rten gsum
NK114(ye)001:3581: po rang rang gi gnas na che ba'i lha klu
NK114(ye)001:3582: mi'i rgyal po byas te 'jig rten 'di na nga
NK114(ye)001:3583: las che ba med do snyam pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3584: che ba rlom pa de dag nyid kyis 'jig rten
NK114(ye)001:3585: rmongs pa'i dbang gis mchog tu 'dzin pa'i rgyal phran
NK114(ye)001:3586: dang blon po la sogs pa'i thob dang mnga' thang
NK114(ye)001:3587: gi bla dwags dpyangs te ming btags pa de dag
NK114(ye)001:3588: ni 'khor ba'i rang bzhin la mtho dman nges pa
NK114(ye)001:3589: med pas 'phral snang nyams dga' tsam las rtag pa
NK114(ye)001:3590: med pa de la'ang rang nyid dregs pa skye zhing
NK114(ye)001:3591: gzhan dag dga' bar byed pa'i gnas su blta na
NK114(ye)001:3592: de 'dra ba ni sngar yang lan brgya phrag du
NK114(ye)001:3593: mar byas kyang snying po med la /
NK114(ye)001:3594: theg pa chen po'i rgyal srid dang byang chub sems
NK114(ye)001:3595: dpa' zhes pa'i ming gi gnas thob ste 'gro ba
NK114(ye)001:3596: thams cad kyi mgon du zhugs pa ni de ring
NK114(ye)001:3597: tsam yin la / rgyu de las sems can gyi
NK114(ye)001:3598: khams mtha' yas pa dag kyang dbugs dbyung ba'i sems
NK114(ye)001:3599: mi 'dor zhing phan pa'i sems kho nas bde ba'i
NK114(ye)001:3600: longs spyod la mgron du bos nas tshim par byed
NK114(ye)001:3601: nus pa yin pas dga' bar bgyid pa'i 'khri shing
NK114(ye)001:3602: slong ba la lha dang yang zhes pa'i khongs nas
NK114(ye)001:3603: lha ma yin la sogs pa dag kyang phyogs shig
NK114(ye)001:3604: ces gzhan gyi sems gzengs bstod do //
NK114(ye)001:3605: de ltar nus pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK114(ye)001:3606: byang chub sems dpa' bsod nams chen po dang ldan
NK114(ye)001:3607: pa yin pas de la gnas skabs dus ma yin
NK114(ye)001:3608: pa'i 'chi ba med cing 'phags sa thob na skye
NK114(ye)001:3609: 'chi rang mtshan pa dang bral zhing /
NK114(ye)001:3610: mthar thug 'chi bdag gi bdud kyi rgyu ba rtsad
NK114(ye)001:3611: nas 'jomsa shing mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das
NK114(ye)001:3612: pa 'thob pa'i phyir bdud rtsi dang /
NK114(ye)001:3613: tshogs rnam pa gnyis kyi mdzod dang ldan pas chos
NK114(ye)001:3614: dang zang zing gi longs spyod mi zad pa'i gter
NK114(ye)001:3615: du gyur pas 'gro ba bkren pa rnams kyi dbul
NK114(ye)001:3616: ba thams cad sel ba'i yid bzhin gyi nor bu
NK114(ye)001:3617: dang / byang chub kyi sems ni sgrib pa thams
NK114(ye)001:3618: cad kyi gnyen po yin pas nyon mongs pa dang
NK114(ye)001:3619: des bskyed pa'i 'du ba'i nad thams cad rab tu
NK114(ye)001:3620: zhi bar byed pa'i sman mchog dang /
NK114(ye)001:3621: 'gro ba thams cad la rtag tu phan pa'i gnas
NK114(ye)001:3622: su gyur pas srid pa'i lam du yun ring po
NK114(ye)001:3623: nas 'khyams te sdug bsngal sna tshogs kyi dub cing
NK114(ye)001:3624: bde ba don du gnyer bar byed pa'i mgron po
NK114(ye)001:3625: sems can rnams la bde ba'i dbugs 'byin ster ba'i
NK114(ye)001:3626: ngal stegs la sogs pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:3627: bdag ni deng gi dus 'di nas bzung ste 'khor
NK114(ye)001:3628: ba ma stongs kyi bar du 'gro ba'i tshogs thams
NK114(ye)001:3629: cad kyi nye bar 'tsho ba'i gzhir gyur ba ste
NK114(ye)001:3630: / de la sogs pa'i yon tan dpag tu med
NK114(ye)001:3631: pa yod pa byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen
NK114(ye)001:3632: po byams pas gzhon nu nor bzang la dpe dang
NK114(ye)001:3633: sbyar te phan yon gyi rnam grangs nyis brgya sum
NK114(ye)001:3634: cu gsungs pa la sogs pa theg pa chen po'i
NK114(ye)001:3635: sde snod rnams las bstan pa la blta bar bya'o
NK114(ye)001:3636: / // yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba las /
NK114(ye)001:3637: byang chub kyi sems yongs su bzung ba'i tshoms te le'u brgyad pa'i 'grel pa'o ////
NK114(ye)001:3638: gsum pa bslab bya la slob pa smon 'jug bslab bya'i le'u bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:3639: bslab pa bsrung thabs bshad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3641: dang po ni 'jig rten na gnas skabs kyi bya
NK114(ye)001:3642: ba 'ga' zhig don du gnyer ba rnams kyis kyang
NK114(ye)001:3643: sngon chad bya ba de bsgrub dka' sla dang legs
NK114(ye)001:3644: nyes ci yod sogs legs par te zhib tu ma
NK114(ye)001:3645: brtags par bab bcola gyi sgo nas bdag gis bya
NK114(ye)001:3646: ba 'di bya'o zhes dam bca' byas pa na phyis
NK114(ye)001:3647: bya ba de bya dka' ba la sogs pa'i tshul
NK114(ye)001:3648: mthong na de slar gtong ba la'ang yid gnyis su
NK114(ye)001:3649: gyur te gzhan khrel ba la sogs pa'i gnas su
NK114(ye)001:3651: rgyal ba sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams dang de
NK114(ye)001:3652: yi thugs sras byang chub sems dpa'i rnams kyi thos
NK114(ye)001:3653: bsam bsgoms pa'i shes rab chen po'i mthusa bskal pa
NK114(ye)001:3654: grangs med pa mang por gdon mi za bar brtags
NK114(ye)001:3655: te yid ches shing nyams su blangs pas don gnyis
NK114(ye)001:3656: phun sum tshogs pa'i phyin ci rang nyid gang la
NK114(ye)001:3657: brten pa'i blang dor gyi gnas srid zhi'i legs tshogs
NK114(ye)001:3658: thams cad kyi rtsa ba byang chub kyi sems dang
NK114(ye)001:3659: de'i bslab bya'i gnas rnams theg pa chen po'i sde
NK114(ye)001:3660: snod du mar bstan pa dag la sems bskyed pa
NK114(ye)001:3661: po rang nyid kyis kyang yang yang brtags nas yon
NK114(ye)001:3662: tan can du shes te rgyal ba sras dang bcas
NK114(ye)001:3663: pa'i spyan sngar snying thag pa nas dam bcas pa
NK114(ye)001:3664: de bya dka' bar mthong nas slar btang na ni
NK114(ye)001:3665: bdag gis don bya ba'i yul sems can thams cad
NK114(ye)001:3666: kun bslus par byas pas phyi mar bde 'gro mtho
NK114(ye)001:3667: ris kyi gnas thob pa ma yin par mu dang
NK114(ye)001:3668: mtha' med pa'i ngan 'grora 'khyams par 'gyur te /
NK114(ye)001:3670: bla na med pa'i bde ba la //
NK114(ye)001:3671: bsam pa thag pas mgron gnyer nas //
NK114(ye)001:3672: 'gro ba thams cad bslus byas na //
NK114(ye)001:3675: rgyu mtshan de nyid kyi phyir de 'dra ba'i nyes pa chen po mi byed pa lta ci smos /
NK114(ye)001:3676: sems can gcig gi srog 'tsho ba'i bde ba'am /
NK114(ye)001:3677: longs spyod dang ldan pa la sogs pa'i bde ba tsam yang /
NK114(ye)001:3679: longs spyod 'phrog pa la sogs pa'i sgo nas bshig
NK114(ye)001:3680: na las dang des byed pa po bdag nyid bde
NK114(ye)001:3681: 'gro las nyams na ngan song du 'phen par byed
NK114(ye)001:3682: pa'i phyir dang / tha na sems can gcig la
NK114(ye)001:3683: mnar sems pa tsam mam gnod pa chung ngu tsam
NK114(ye)001:3684: zhig byed na yang bdag gi bslab pa nyams par
NK114(ye)001:3685: 'gyur bas las de tsam yang mi bgyid do //
NK114(ye)001:3686: byang sems kyi sdom pa 'di ni sor sdom lta
NK114(ye)001:3687: bu ma yin par slar gso rung bas skyon med
NK114(ye)001:3688: do snyam na / de ltar ltung ba stobs dang
NK114(ye)001:3689: ldan pa dang byang chub kyi sems stobs dang ldan
NK114(ye)001:3690: pa gnyis kar ldan zhing phan tshun 'khor bar ram
NK114(ye)001:3691: 'khor ba 'dir res mos kyis 'dre bar byed pa
NK114(ye)001:3692: gang yin pa de ni mos spyod kyi sa gong
NK114(ye)001:3693: ma dang 'phags pa'i sa dang po sogs thob pa
NK114(ye)001:3694: la yun ring por 'thogsa par 'gyur bas na shes
NK114(ye)001:3695: bzhin du blang dor gyi bslab bya rnams gtong bar
NK114(ye)001:3696: byed pa'i skyes bu ni rang nyid g.yang sar brlag
NK114(ye)001:3697: par byed pa'i smyon pa bzhin yin bslab pa'i gnas
NK114(ye)001:3698: thams cad mig 'bras las kyang gces par bzung ste
NK114(ye)001:3699: do snyam na / bsrung bar bya'o // de ltar ltung ba 'byung ba'i rgyu ni /
NK114(ye)001:3702: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyis mi 'jigs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3703: sdig pa'i grogs pos zin pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3704: byang chub chen po thag ring bar sems pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3705: bdud kyi byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3706: theg pa dman pa'i gang zag bsten pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3707: theg pa chung ngu'i gzhung la brtsams pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3708: sems can blos gtong ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:3709: byang chub sems dpa' la tshig ngan brjod cing ngan sems bskyed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3710: byang chub kyi sems dang mi mthun pa'i phyogs mi spong ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:3711: gzhan yang mi shes pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3714: nyon mongs pa mang ba'o zhes b+ham ga la'i rnal 'byor pa nyid bzhed pa las /
NK114(ye)001:3715: nyon mongs pa ni kun gyi phyi mo yin pas de nyid la 'khon du bzung ba'i tshul /
NK114(ye)001:3716: 'jig rten 'di na gang zag gang zhig gnod pa'i
NK114(ye)001:3717: rgyu mnga' thang dang longs spyod 'phrog pa'am gnas skabs
NK114(ye)001:3718: pa'i lus srog tsam la gnod par byed pa dang
NK114(ye)001:3719: de'i 'bras bu go sa dman par gyur pa dang
NK114(ye)001:3720: / longs spyod bri ba dang lus srog nyams nyes su gyur pa la sogs pa'am /
NK114(ye)001:3721: shin tu gdug rtsub che ba dug sbrul lta bu'i
NK114(ye)001:3722: sems dang ldan pa rnams ni tha na rgyu zhing
NK114(ye)001:3723: gi mu la reg pa lta bu dang /
NK114(ye)001:3724: 'bras bu chu'i ka ral ba lta bu'i chung ngu
NK114(ye)001:3725: la'ang khros pa'i dbang gis de las bdag rgyal bar
NK114(ye)001:3726: 'dod pa'i nga rgyal shin tu bdo ba rnams la
NK114(ye)001:3727: pha rol pos mda' mdung la sogs pa'i mtshon gyi
NK114(ye)001:3728: chad pa rtsub mos lus 'bigs pa dang gcod pa
NK114(ye)001:3729: dang srog gcod pa'i bar du sdug bsngal bar byas
NK114(ye)001:3730: kyang de thams cad bzod cing khyad du bsad par
NK114(ye)001:3731: byas nas rang gi bsam rgyu'i don pha rol po
NK114(ye)001:3732: 'joms pa sogs kyi bya ba de ma 'grub pa'i
NK114(ye)001:3733: bar du phyir phyogs nas 'bros par mi byed de
NK114(ye)001:3734: da lta shi ba'i dus yin no zhes rang gsod
NK114(ye)001:3735: pa la'ang mchog tu 'dzin pa las cang mi sems
NK114(ye)001:3736: na / yun ring po thog ma med pa nas
NK114(ye)001:3737: rnam pa kun tu phan mi 'dogs par ma zad
NK114(ye)001:3738: btang snyoms tsam du'ang mi gnas par bdag la sdug
NK114(ye)001:3739: bsngal sna tshogs pa'i rgyus gnod pa bsgrub pa'i dgrar
NK114(ye)001:3740: gyur pa'i nyon mongs pa 'dod chags dang zhe sdang
NK114(ye)001:3741: la sogs pa'i dpung mang po 'di dag las gcig
NK114(ye)001:3742: tsam zhig yud tsam rgyud la skyes pas kyang sems
NK114(ye)001:3743: can dmyal ba chen po mnar med du 'phangs nas
NK114(ye)001:3744: yun ring por thar du med pa'i sdug bsngal myong
NK114(ye)001:3745: dgos par 'gyur ba'i stobs chen po can gyi tshogs
NK114(ye)001:3746: 'di dang gnyen po gnyis phan tshun g.yul sprad nas
NK114(ye)001:3747: gnyen po bsten pa'i tshe na bslab pa gsum las
NK114(ye)001:3750: shes rab kyis drungs nas 'byin par byed dgos pas
NK114(ye)001:3751: so so'i skye bo las dang po pas sun 'byin
NK114(ye)001:3752: gyi gnyen po bsten te nyon mongs pa la 'khon
NK114(ye)001:3753: du bzung ba'i sgo nas gtso bo des bskyed pa'i
NK114(ye)001:3754: sgo gsum gyi kha na ma tho ba spong bar
NK114(ye)001:3755: byed pa'i thabs la brtson zhing /
NK114(ye)001:3756: de nas mgo gnon gyi gnyen po ting nge 'dzin
NK114(ye)001:3757: gyis sems las su rung bar byas nas nyon mongs
NK114(ye)001:3758: mngon 'gyur ba'i dbang du mi 'gro ba'i tshe /
NK114(ye)001:3759: drungs 'byin gyi gnyen po lhag mthong gi shes rab
NK114(ye)001:3760: bskyed nas cho ga ste nyon mongs spong ba'i gnyen
NK114(ye)001:3761: po'i phyogs la ched du brtson pa'i bya ba ma
NK114(ye)001:3762: zhig pa'am ma btang dgos la /
NK114(ye)001:3763: 'phags sa thob nas ni nyon mongs lhan skyes med
NK114(ye)001:3764: pa ma yin kyang so skye bzhin du de'i dbang
NK114(ye)001:3765: gis 'khor bar 'phen pa'i las gsog pa la sogs
NK114(ye)001:3766: pas gnod par mi 'gyur ba'i phyir de la gnyen
NK114(ye)001:3767: po che thang du bsten mi dgos so //
NK114(ye)001:3768: des na 'phags sa ma thob kyi bar du byang
NK114(ye)001:3769: sems kyi bslab pa bsrung ba'i ched du sems nyon
NK114(ye)001:3770: mongs pa'i dbang du mi 'gro ba'i phyir gnyen po
NK114(ye)001:3771: bsten pa'i brtul zhugs su zhig gis gtong ste /
NK114(ye)001:3773: bslab pa bsrung bar 'dod pa yis //
NK114(ye)001:3774: rab tu bsgrims nas sems bsrung ste //
NK114(ye)001:3775: sems 'di bsrung bar ma byas na //
NK114(ye)001:3776: bslab pa bsrung bar yongs mi nus //
NK114(ye)001:3778: de yang nyon mongs spong ba'i don du brtson pa
NK114(ye)001:3779: na phyi nang gi gnod pa dang sdug bsngal mang
NK114(ye)001:3781: nyon mongs pa'i bag chags shin tu brtan pas spang dka' ba sogs kyis sems skyo ste /
NK114(ye)001:3782: sngar bdag gis gnyen po de tsam bsten kyang spang ma nus so snyam du yid chad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3783: phyis kyang spang mi nus so snyam du sgyid lug
NK114(ye)001:3784: par mi 'gyur ba smos ci dgos te shin tu
NK114(ye)001:3787: sdug bsngal brgya phrag rgyur gyur gang gis kyang //
NK114(ye)001:3788: yid chad sgyid lug mi 'gyur smos mi dgos //
NK114(ye)001:3790: de bas na bslab pa bsrung ba'i brtul zhugs kyi
NK114(ye)001:3791: grogs su mi dbang 'phags pa la 'os pa'i rgyal
NK114(ye)001:3792: srid rin po che sna bdun gyi khyad nor bsnyen
NK114(ye)001:3793: par bya ste / slob dpon dpa' bos kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems bsgoms pa las /
NK114(ye)001:3794: dad pa'i 'khor lo rin po ches //
NK114(ye)001:3795: nyin mtshan dge ba'i lam sna drongs //
NK114(ye)001:3796: tshul khrims btsun mo rin po ches //
NK114(ye)001:3797: rab tu mdzes pa'i rgyan phreng gdags //
NK114(ye)001:3798: gtong ba'i blon po rin po ches //
NK114(ye)001:3800: thos pa'i dmag dpon rin po ches //
NK114(ye)001:3801: log rtog dgra yi g.yul ngo gzhom //
NK114(ye)001:3802: ngo tsha shes pa'i rta mchog gis //
NK114(ye)001:3803: nyon mongs bdag med sbubs su sba //
NK114(ye)001:3804: khrel yod stobs kyi glang po ches //
NK114(ye)001:3805: phyin ci log gi las rnams spang //
NK114(ye)001:3806: shes rab nor bu rin po ches //
NK114(ye)001:3807: bdag dang gzhan gyi re ba skong //
NK114(ye)001:3808: yon tan mtha' yas 'phags pa'i nor //
NK114(ye)001:3809: nor gzhan phal pa sdug bsngal rgyu //
NK114(ye)001:3811: de yang da lta 'khrul snang gi bag chags shin
NK114(ye)001:3812: tu brtan pa'i skabs 'di na nyon mongs pa'i btson
NK114(ye)001:3813: rar bdag tu 'dzin pa'i 'ching ba dam pos bsdams
NK114(ye)001:3814: pa yi rang bzhin bdag gi rgyud kyi nyon mongs
NK114(ye)001:3815: spong bar byed pa'i nus pa'i tshod kyang rig par
NK114(ye)001:3816: mi 'gyur na mtha' dag pa'i 'gro ba thams cad
NK114(ye)001:3817: nyon mongs pa bag chags dang bcas pa de las
NK114(ye)001:3818: dbugs 'byin zhing sangs rgyas kyi sar sgrol ba'i phyir
NK114(ye)001:3819: dam bcas pa de'i brtan pa mi nyams pa ga
NK114(ye)001:3820: la zhig ste de'i phyir na gzhan sems can thams
NK114(ye)001:3821: cad kyi nyon mongs bsal ba'i don du dang po
NK114(ye)001:3822: rang gi nyon mongs spong byed kyi thabs 'jug ldog
NK114(ye)001:3823: gi gnas la gzob pa lhur len pa bag yod
NK114(ye)001:3824: pa dang / bslab pa'i gnas mi brjed pa dran pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3825: sgo gsum gyi spyod lam thams cad la brtags pa
NK114(ye)001:3826: shes bzhin te 'di gsum dang ldan pa'i gang zag
NK114(ye)001:3827: gi rgyud ni sa gzhigs gshin pa dang 'dra bas
NK114(ye)001:3828: de la byang chub kyi sems kya sa bon bzhag
NK114(ye)001:3829: pa tsam ma yin par lhag pa'i bsam pa rnam
NK114(ye)001:3830: par dag pa'i myu gu bskyed sla bas na 'di
NK114(ye)001:3831: dag ni shin tu gnad gal po che yin pas
NK114(ye)001:3832: dbye 'byed sems thog nas shes par bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:3833: nyams len thams cad kyi gnad 'di gsum la 'du ba yin pas shin tu gal che'o //
NK114(ye)001:3834: de ltar sems bskyed dang bslab pa mi nyams par
NK114(ye)001:3835: bzung zhing 'di ma btang ba tsam gyis mi chog
NK114(ye)001:3836: ste mi mthun pa'i phyogs ltung ba'i dri ma sbyong
NK114(ye)001:3837: ba'i thabs bshags pa bya ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:3838: mthun phyogs sems bskyed dang bslab pa spel ba'i thabs dge ba'i bshes gnyen bsten pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3839: byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod la yang yang blta
NK114(ye)001:3840: ba dang tshogs bsags pa sogs la nan tan du
NK114(ye)001:3841: bgyid par 'tshal lo zhes gdams so //
NK114(ye)001:3842: gnyis pa bslab bya dngos bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:3843: spang ba'i bslab bya bshad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3844: bsgrub pa'i bslab bya bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:3849: de ltar sems bskyed cing sdom pa blangs nas de'i
NK114(ye)001:3850: spang sgrub kyi bslab bya rnams tshul bzhin spang blang
NK114(ye)001:3851: byed pa de la dang po gang zhig spyad na
NK114(ye)001:3852: gnas ngan du ltung bar 'gyur ba'i spang bya'i grangs
NK114(ye)001:3853: kyi rab tu dbye ba sde snod rnams las du
NK114(ye)001:3854: ma zhig gsungs pa rigs bsdu na nam snying gi
NK114(ye)001:3855: mdo las byung ba'i bco brgyad dang /
NK114(ye)001:3856: gsang chen thabs la mkhas pa'i mdo dang /
NK114(ye)001:3857: dkon mchog brtsegs pa las gsungs pa re re ste
NK114(ye)001:3858: nyi shu ni ltung mtshams legs par shes par byas
NK114(ye)001:3859: nas bsrung bar bya dgos so //
NK114(ye)001:3860: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:3864: mdo dang po las byung ba bshad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3865: phyi ma gnyis las gsungs pa bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:3867: rgyal po la 'byung nye ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:3868: blon po la 'byung nye ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:3871: nam mkha'i snying po'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:3872: rigs kyi bu rgyal po rgyal rigs spyi bo nas dbang bskur ba'i ltung ba'i rtsa ba lnga ste /
NK114(ye)001:3873: ltung ba'i rtsa ba de dag gis /
NK114(ye)001:3874: rgyal rigs spyi bo nas dbang bskur ba'i dge ba'i
NK114(ye)001:3875: rtsa ba sngon bskyed pa thams cad chud gzan te
NK114(ye)001:3876: phas pham zhing lha dang mi'i bde ba'i gnas thams
NK114(ye)001:3877: cad nas lhung nas ngan song du 'gro bar 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:3878: ro zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:3879: 'di ltar kun slong drag pos dkon mchog gsum po
NK114(ye)001:3880: thams cad dam gang rung dkor nor rang gis 'phrog
NK114(ye)001:3881: gam / gzhan la 'phroga tu 'jug pa dang la sogs pa'i khongs nas /
NK114(ye)001:3882: theg gsum gang rung gi lung rtogs kyi chos la
NK114(ye)001:3883: thar ba'i thabs min no zhes spong ngam spong du
NK114(ye)001:3884: 'jug pa dang / skra dang kha spu bregs nas
NK114(ye)001:3885: gos ngur smrig gyon pa bslab pa bzung yang rung
NK114(ye)001:3886: 'jug pa dang / / ma bzung yang rung /
NK114(ye)001:3888: tshul khrims dang ldan yang rung ste /
NK114(ye)001:3889: zhe sdang gis de'i ngur smrig 'phrog gam /
NK114(ye)001:3894: gzhan la de ltar byed du bcug pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3895: mtshams med pa lnga po las gang yang rung ba byed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:3896: las 'bras med do zhes pa'i log lta ste /
NK114(ye)001:3897: 'di lta bu'i blo skyes pa tsam nas dge rtsa
NK114(ye)001:3898: chad par 'gyur zhing bslab pa gtong yang de'i dbang
NK114(ye)001:3899: gis mi dge ba'i bya ba gzhan la sbyor ram
NK114(ye)001:3900: sbyor du bcug na nyes pa shin tu lci'o //
NK114(ye)001:3901: de dag ni rgyal po'i ltung ba lnga'o //
NK114(ye)001:3902: gnyis pa ni khyim gcig pa la sogs pa grong dang /
NK114(ye)001:3903: mi rigs bzhi gnas pas phyogs ljongs dang /
NK114(ye)001:3904: bzo sna bco brgyad yod pa'i gnas grong khyer dang /
NK114(ye)001:3905: tshong 'dus chen po yod pa'i gnas grong rdal dang /
NK114(ye)001:3906: tsam pa ka lta bu yul khams chen po ni
NK114(ye)001:3907: yul 'khor ste de dag las gang yang rung ba
NK114(ye)001:3908: zhe sdang gis me sogs kyis 'jomsa par byed pa
NK114(ye)001:3909: dang / sogsa khongs nas log lta dor ba'i rgyal
NK114(ye)001:3910: po'i ltung ba snga ma bzhi dang bcas pa ni
NK114(ye)001:3912: gsum pa ni snod ma brtags par blo ma sbyangs pa'am /
NK114(ye)001:3913: cung zad sbyangs kyang zab don la skrag pa'i rigs
NK114(ye)001:3914: can la stong nyid ston par byas pas yul de'i
NK114(ye)001:3915: byang chub kyi sems btang ste theg dman du smon
NK114(ye)001:3917: sogsa khongs nas theg chen gyi rigs can lam der
NK114(ye)001:3918: zhugs pa la shes bzhin du de las ldog ste
NK114(ye)001:3919: theg dman du sems bskyed du 'jug pa dang 2
NK114(ye)001:3920: / dman pa'i rigs can so thar la mos shing
NK114(ye)001:3921: slob pa la don du mi 'gyur bzhin theg chen
NK114(ye)001:3922: gyi basngagasa pa brjod nas so thar spangs te gnyis
NK114(ye)001:3923: ka ma yin par byed pa dang 3 /
NK114(ye)001:3924: dman pa'i lam gyis nyon mongs zad par mi spong
NK114(ye)001:3925: ngo zhes nyan thos la thar lam rnal ma med
NK114(ye)001:3927: bsam pa phrag dog gis bdag la bstod cing gzhan
NK114(ye)001:3928: la smad pa'i tshig brjod pa yul gyiis go ba
NK114(ye)001:3929: dang 5 / rnyed pa dang bkur sti don du
NK114(ye)001:3930: gnyer nas ma rtogs bzhin du zab mo'i don rtogs
NK114(ye)001:3931: so zhes mi'i chos bla ma'i rdzun gyis gzhan mgo
NK114(ye)001:3933: dbang po che'i phyogs dang bshes par byas nas chos
NK114(ye)001:3934: 'di pa'i dge sbyong chad pas gcod du bcug ste
NK114(ye)001:3935: de'i phag sug tu dkon mchog gi dkor nor byin
NK114(ye)001:3937: 'dis gsum ka byang sems yin na thams cad la ltung bar 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:3938: spong ba bsam gtan pa'i longs spyod las phri zhing
NK114(ye)001:3939: phrog nas kha ton pa'am klog pa bdag la ster
NK114(ye)001:3940: zhing chos bzhin spyod pa'i rnal 'byor 'dor du 'jug
NK114(ye)001:3941: pa'am / chos ldan gyi dge sbyong gnod pa'i khrims
NK114(ye)001:3942: ngan gyiis zhi gnas 'dor du 'jug pa ste phal
NK114(ye)001:3943: pa'i ltung ba brgyad dang bcas pa bsdoms pas ming
NK114(ye)001:3944: gis bco brgyad po rdzas su bsdu na bcu bzhi
NK114(ye)001:3945: yin te rgyal blon gyi snga ma bzhi po tha
NK114(ye)001:3947: de dag kyang rgyal po sogs la 'byung nye ba
NK114(ye)001:3948: tsam gyis de dang de'i ltung bar bzhag pa yin
NK114(ye)001:3949: gyi rang rang gi ltung bar bzhag pa de las
NK114(ye)001:3950: gzhan mi 'byung ba ma yin te /
NK114(ye)001:3951: rgyal blon dmangs gsum ga la bcu bzhi po thams
NK114(ye)001:3952: cad 'byung ba yin pas gang zag byang sems gcig
NK114(ye)001:3953: gis thams cad bsrung dgos pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:3954: gnyis pa mdo phyi ma gnyis las gsungs pa bshad pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:3955: theg pa dman par sems bskyed nas sems can blos spangs pa ni smon sems btang ba ste /
NK114(ye)001:3956: gsang chen thabs la mkhas pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:3957: rigs kyi bu byang chub sems dpa' nyan thos dang
NK114(ye)001:3958: rang sangs rgyas yid la byed pas gnas pa 'di
NK114(ye)001:3959: ni byang chub sems dpa'i rtsa ba'i ltung ba lci
NK114(ye)001:3960: ba'o zhes so // dkon mchog brtsegs pa las gsungs pa ni 'jug sems gtong ba ste /
NK114(ye)001:3961: de yang sbyin sogs bsgrub par dam bcas pa las
NK114(ye)001:3962: nyams te rang gi nus pa'i tshod tsam zhig kyang
NK114(ye)001:3963: mi sgrub po snyam pa'i blo skyes pas gtong gi
NK114(ye)001:3964: / snyom las sogs kyis dge ba la mi sbyor ba tsam gyis rtsa ba nas mi gtong ngo //
NK114(ye)001:3965: gzhan yang bslab btus las gsungs pa'i nyes byas brgyad cu ste /
NK114(ye)001:3966: de la bde sdug yal bar 'dor ba nyi shu rtsa bzhi /
NK114(ye)001:3967: sgrub pa yal bar 'dor ba bcu drug /
NK114(ye)001:3968: de dag las phye bas brgyad cu'o //
NK114(ye)001:3969: dang po ni gzhan gyi sdug bsngal dang yid mi
NK114(ye)001:3970: bde ba zhi bar nus bzhin du zhi bar mi
NK114(ye)001:3971: byed pa dang / bde ba dang yid bde ba
NK114(ye)001:3972: bskyed nus bzhin du bskyed par mi byed pa gnyis
NK114(ye)001:3973: byed pa dang / te dbye gazhi'o // de gnyis
NK114(ye)001:3974: la lus dang sems kyi rten so sor phye bas
NK114(ye)001:3975: byed pa dang / te dbye gazhi'o // bzhi /
NK114(ye)001:3976: de la da lta dang ma 'ongs pa'i dus kyis
NK114(ye)001:3977: byed pa dang / te dbye gazhi'o // bzhi /
NK114(ye)001:3978: phye bas brgyad / de'i ched du sgo gsum gyis
NK114(ye)001:3980: phan pa'i rgyu rkyen mi tshol ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:3981: gnyen po'i phyogs la mi 'bad pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:3982: de ltar rjes sgrub kyi sgo gsum po des phye bas nyi shu rtsa bzhi'o //
NK114(ye)001:3983: gnyis pa ni sdug bsngal dang yid mi bde ba
NK114(ye)001:3984: chen po'i gnyen por chung ngu mi bskyed pa gzhir
NK114(ye)001:3985: bzhag nas / de gnyis la 'di dang phyi ma'i skye bas phye bas bzhi /
NK114(ye)001:3986: rang dang gzhan gyi rgyud kyis phye bas brgyad /
NK114(ye)001:3987: yang bde ba dang yid bde ba chen po'i phyir
NK114(ye)001:3988: chung ngu nyams par mi byed pa gzhir bzhag nas
NK114(ye)001:3989: / sngar ltar skye ba dang rgyud kyis phye bas brgyad de bcu drug go //
NK114(ye)001:3990: gsum pa ni de ltar bzhi bcu po re re la'ang re zhig yal bar 'dor ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:3991: gtan du yal bar 'dor ba gnyis gnyis su phye bas brgyad cu'o //
NK114(ye)001:3993: bde sdug sgrub pa yal bar 'dor //
NK114(ye)001:3994: nyer bzhi dang ni bcu drug ste //
NK114(ye)001:3995: gzhan sdug mi bde zhi mi byed //
NK114(ye)001:3996: bde dang yid bde mi bskyed la //
NK114(ye)001:3997: lus sems dbye gzhi da 'ongs brgyad //
NK114(ye)001:3998: de'i ched mi brtson mi tshol dang //
NK114(ye)001:4000: sdug bsngal mi bde chen po yi //
NK114(ye)001:4001: gnyen por chung ngu mi bskyed dang //
NK114(ye)001:4002: bde dang yid bde chen po'i phyir //
NK114(ye)001:4003: chung ngu nyams par mi byed pa //
NK114(ye)001:4004: skye rgyud phye bas bcu drug ste //
NK114(ye)001:4005: bzhi bcu po la gnyis re'o //
NK114(ye)001:4007: de ltar ltung ba'i rnam grangs de rnams nges par byas nas spang ba bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:4008: gnyis pa phyir bcos pa'i tshul ni /
NK114(ye)001:4009: gal te ltung ba 'byung ba'i sgo bzhi la sogs
NK114(ye)001:4010: pa'i stobs kyis nyes ltung byung na yang de dang
NK114(ye)001:4011: lhan du 'grogs par mi bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:4012: mdor na rmi lam du ltung ba 'byin pa sogs
NK114(ye)001:4013: sdig pa byas pa mthong na yang sad dus kyi
NK114(ye)001:4014: bag chags ngan pa goms pa'i mthus yin pas phyi
NK114(ye)001:4015: bshol mi byed par de ma thag tu phyag 'tshal
NK114(ye)001:4017: bsngo ba ste phung po gsum pa tshang ba'i mdo
NK114(ye)001:4018: 'don pa la sogs pas bshagsa pa bya dgos pa
NK114(ye)001:4019: yin na / sad dus kyi nyes pa bsam bzhin du byas pa rnams ni smos ci dgos /
NK114(ye)001:4020: de yang bshags bya ltung ba'i lci yang gi khyad par la ltos nas phyir bcos par bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:4021: byang sems kyi bslab pa dang yon tan thams cad
NK114(ye)001:4022: kyi rten gzhi ni smon sems yin la de nyid
NK114(ye)001:4023: sems can gcig tsam snying thag pa nas 'phral yun
NK114(ye)001:4024: kun tu 'di'i don mi byed do snyam du blos
NK114(ye)001:4025: btang ba dang rdzogs byang don gnyer gyi sems btang
NK114(ye)001:4026: ba ste zur gnyis gang rung nyams pa'i sgo nas
NK114(ye)001:4027: shor ba dang / 'gal zla mi mthun pa'i phyogs
NK114(ye)001:4028: rtsa ltung gzhan gang yang rung ba byung ba dang
NK114(ye)001:4029: shor ba dang / / sdom pa rtsa ba nas
NK114(ye)001:4030: spong ba'i rkyen bslab pa phul ba gsum po dag
NK114(ye)001:4031: shor ba dang / / las / smon sems shor
NK114(ye)001:4032: na ni gyang zhig na ri mo mi gnas pa
NK114(ye)001:4033: bzhin thun tshod la ma ltos par de ma thag
NK114(ye)001:4034: byang sdom rtsa ba nas gtong bar 'gyur zhing de
NK114(ye)001:4035: bzhin du bslab pa phul ba yang /
NK114(ye)001:4036: so thar gyi sdom pa bsrung mi nus na 'bul du rung bar gnang mod /
NK114(ye)001:4037: de la'ang sdom pa phul nyams mu bzhir dpyad du yod kyang /
NK114(ye)001:4038: byang sdom ni phul bar ma gnang zhing phul na yang nyes pa shin tu lci ste /
NK114(ye)001:4039: spyir rang gzhan gyi phan bde sgrub pa'i rgyu gcig pu chud gzon par ma zad /
NK114(ye)001:4040: dus kyang byang chub snying po'i bar du dam bcas pa de btang ba'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:4042: bla na med pa'i bde ba la //
NK114(ye)001:4043: bsam pa thag pas mgron gnyer nas //
NK114(ye)001:4044: 'gro ba thams cad bslus byas nas //
NK114(ye)001:4046: zhes sngar drangs pa ltar ro //
NK114(ye)001:4047: de gnyis las gzhan pa'i 'gal zla rtsa ba'i ltung
NK114(ye)001:4048: ba rnams kyis tshul khrims rgyun 'chad par mi 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:4049: ba dang 'gyur ba'i mtshams thun tshod ma 'das pa
NK114(ye)001:4050: dang 'das pa'i bye brag gis yin te /
NK114(ye)001:4052: nye bar 'khor gyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:4053: nye bar 'khor 'di la theg pa chen po la
NK114(ye)001:4054: zhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' gal te snga dro'i
NK114(ye)001:4055: dus su ltung ba byung ba yang phyed kyi dus
NK114(ye)001:4056: na thams cad mkhyen pa'i sems dang mi 'bral bar
NK114(ye)001:4057: gnas te zhes pa nas de bzhin du kun la
NK114(ye)001:4058: sbyar te / gal te phyed kyi dus su ltung
NK114(ye)001:4059: ba byung ba yang phyi 'phred kyi dus na ltung
NK114(ye)001:4061: gal te srod la ltung ba byung na'ang nam phyed na /
NK114(ye)001:4062: nam phyed na ltung ba byung na tho rengs zhes sogs nas /
NK114(ye)001:4063: nye bar 'khor de ltar na theg pa chen po
NK114(ye)001:4064: la yang dag par zhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK114(ye)001:4065: rnams kyi bslab pa ni bcos su rung ba'o zhes
NK114(ye)001:4066: bshad pa ltar nyin mtshan so so'i cha thun gsum
NK114(ye)001:4067: gsum du bcad pa'i drug cha so so'i smad du
NK114(ye)001:4068: gnyen pos slebs na de'i tshul khrims rgyun chad par
NK114(ye)001:4069: mi 'gyur te / dper na snga dro lta bu
NK114(ye)001:4070: drug cha dang po'i thog tha bar gsum gang yang
NK114(ye)001:4071: rung bar ltung ba byung na /
NK114(ye)001:4072: de ma thag gi drug cha gnyis pa'i thun tshod
NK114(ye)001:4073: ma 'das gong ci rigs par 'gyod pa drag po
NK114(ye)001:4074: dang bcas bshags na sdom pa sor chud par 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:4075: ro // gal te 'bad du zin kyang mi shes
NK114(ye)001:4076: pa dang bag med pa la sogs pa'i dbang gis
NK114(ye)001:4077: bshags pa'i tshad de las nyams shor na gtugs pa
NK114(ye)001:4078: zhes bya ste phyir bcos kyis sor chud pa ma
NK114(ye)001:4079: yin pas 'gyod sdom dang bcas pa'i sems kyis bshags
NK114(ye)001:4080: pa sngon du 'gro bas cho ga bzhin du slar
NK114(ye)001:4081: ro // blang bar bagyi'o // bshags pa'i tshul yang
NK114(ye)001:4082: dbang dman rnams ni dngos 'dzin shugs che bas ngo
NK114(ye)001:4083: tsha dang khrel yod kyi rten theg chen gyi sdom
NK114(ye)001:4084: ldan bcu'am lnga tshogs nas gcig yan chad la nyes
NK114(ye)001:4085: ltung 'chab pa med par bshags te ldang ngo //
NK114(ye)001:4086: dbang 'bring lha'i rnal 'byor la goms pa dang mos pa brtan pa dag ni /
NK114(ye)001:4087: rang gi mdo las dge ba'i rtsa ba chad de ltung ba rnams kyi mkhar ba lta bu /
NK114(ye)001:4088: sdom pa spyod pa rnams kyi me long lta bu /
NK114(ye)001:4089: ngo tsha dang khrel yod shes pa rnams kyi gos
NK114(ye)001:4090: lta bu zhes bshad pa'i rig sngags spyi'i lha 'phags
NK114(ye)001:4091: pa nam mkha'i snying po la bshags par bya ste
NK114(ye)001:4093: nyin mtshan gyis bar ma chod par khrus dang gtsang sbra bya /
NK114(ye)001:4095: 'phags pa nam mkha'i snying po'i mtshan nas brjod cing phyag 'tshal ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:4096: 'phags pa bdag la zhal bstan te sdig pa dag
NK114(ye)001:4097: par mdzad du gsol zhes gsol ba drag tu btab
NK114(ye)001:4098: pas dngos sam rmi lam du skal ba dang 'tshams
NK114(ye)001:4099: par de nyid kyi gzugs sam mi nas bya'i bar
NK114(ye)001:4100: ci rigs pa'i gzugs kyis ltung ba las 'byin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:4102: gal te ston par ma gyur na skya rengs 'char
NK114(ye)001:4103: du nye ba na de'i mdun du gtsang sbra dang
NK114(ye)001:4104: bcas spos btul zhing kha shar phyogs su bltas te
NK114(ye)001:4105: pus mo g.yas pa'i lha nga sa la btsugs nas
NK114(ye)001:4106: / nam mkha'i snying po yid la bya zhing mos
NK114(ye)001:4107: gus chen po dang ldan pas yan lag bdun pa
NK114(ye)001:4108: / phul la / nan tan du bskul ba'i tshig
NK114(ye)001:4109: gis bos nas skye rengs skya rengs snying rje chen
NK114(ye)001:4110: po legs pa chen po khyod 'dzam bu'i gling du
NK114(ye)001:4111: shar ma thag tu bdag la thugs rjes khyab par
NK114(ye)001:4112: / phul la / mdzod cig / nam mkha'i snying
NK114(ye)001:4113: po snying rje chen po dang ldan pa la yang
NK114(ye)001:4114: bdag gi tshig gis myur du bskul te /
NK114(ye)001:4115: thabs gang gis ltung ba myur du 'chags par 'dod pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:4116: theg pa chen po'i 'phags pa la thabs dang shes
NK114(ye)001:4117: rab thob par 'gyur ba'i thabs de bdag gi rmi
NK114(ye)001:4118: lam du bstan du gsol zhes brjod nas nyal bas
NK114(ye)001:4119: skya rengs 'char ba'i tshe rmi lam du nam snying
NK114(ye)001:4120: gi gzugs skal ba bzhin ston pas ltung ba 'chags
NK114(ye)001:4121: su 'jug go // yang na rang gi yi dam
NK114(ye)001:4122: gyi lha'i mdun du thun mong ma yin pa'i yan
NK114(ye)001:4123: lag bdun pa byas la bshags pas ltung ba las
NK114(ye)001:4124: su 'jug go // ldang ngo // dbang po rab
NK114(ye)001:4125: tu gyur ba'i ltung ba ni gdod ma nas ngo
NK114(ye)001:4126: bo nyid med pa'i kun rtog gi rnam par 'char
NK114(ye)001:4127: bas chu la ri mo bris pa'am rlung la bskos
NK114(ye)001:4128: phor btab pa bzhin du des bag chags sam ltung
NK114(ye)001:4129: ba'i rgyu 'bras kyi gzugs brnyan 'jog pa med kyang
NK114(ye)001:4130: mnyam rjes res 'jog tu gyur pa dag la thar
NK114(ye)001:4131: pa chen po phyogs su rgyas pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:4133: drang por 'dug la yang dag ltos //
NK114(ye)001:4134: yang dag nyid la yang dag blta //
NK114(ye)001:4135: yang dag mthong nas rnam par grol //
NK114(ye)001:4138: 'on kyang las dang po pas ltung ba'i ngo bo
NK114(ye)001:4139: brtags nas de la stong pas rgyas 'debs pa ni
NK114(ye)001:4140: lung de'i dbyings 'jal ma shes pa yin te /
NK114(ye)001:4141: stong par bltas pas dag na rgyang 'phen pa'i gsang tshig la'ang don yod par 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:4142: mdo hril gyis dril na thog ma med pa nas
NK114(ye)001:4143: rang la gces par 'dzin pa'i blo 'di goms ches
NK114(ye)001:4144: pas sems bskyed kyang gzhan la phan 'dod kyi blo
NK114(ye)001:4145: rgyun chags su 'byung dka' bas bsam sbyor gnyis ka'i
NK114(ye)001:4146: cha nas gnod par 'gyur ba'i las bag med du
NK114(ye)001:4147: thal ba sogs kha na ma tho ba'i las sna
NK114(ye)001:4148: tshogs pas rang rgyud gos shing /
NK114(ye)001:4149: stong nyid la myong ba gting nas ma thon pa'i
NK114(ye)001:4150: rigs can thams cad ni las dang po pa yin
NK114(ye)001:4151: pas na dus dang rnam pa thams cad du nyes
NK114(ye)001:4152: pa byung res kyi dus su stobs bzhi tshang ba'i
NK114(ye)001:4153: sgo nas bshags pa la 'bad par bya zhing /
NK114(ye)001:4154: rtag tu nyin mtshan gyi cha la lan gsum gsum
NK114(ye)001:4155: du phung po gsum pa'i mdo gdon par bya zhing
NK114(ye)001:4156: sangs rgyas dang byang chub kyi sems yid la byas
NK114(ye)001:4157: na brjed nges dang shes bzhin gyis ma zin pas
NK114(ye)001:4158: phyir bcos ma grub pa dang nyes byas kyi cha
NK114(ye)001:4161: nyin dang mtshan mo lan gsum du //
NK114(ye)001:4162: phung po gsum pa gdon bya zhing //
NK114(ye)001:4163: rgyal dang byang chub sems brten nas //
NK114(ye)001:4164: ltung ba'i lhag ma des zhi bya //
NK114(ye)001:4166: spyir ltung ba de dag la yul gyi bye brag la brten nas kun dkris kyi khyad par ni /
NK114(ye)001:4167: zhe sdang gi dbang gis sems can la gnod pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:4168: gti mug gi dbang gis dam pa'i chos la gnod pa gnyis kun dkris chen po yin la /
NK114(ye)001:4169: de las gzhan pa'i chags sems dang zhe sdang la
NK114(ye)001:4170: sogs pa dag ni kun dkris chung ngu zhes bya'o
NK114(ye)001:4171: // gzhan yang byang sdom gyi rten dang len pa'i
NK114(ye)001:4172: tshul rtsa ltung dang nyes byas kyi rnam grangs kun
NK114(ye)001:4174: phyir bcos pa'i tshul sogs gdul bya la dgongs nas
NK114(ye)001:4175: mdo so so'i rjes su 'brangs pa'i srol gnyis kyi
NK114(ye)001:4176: bzhed tshul gnas skabs dgos dbang gis tha dad pa
NK114(ye)001:4177: dang / don la dgongs pa mthun pa'i tshul rnams
NK114(ye)001:4178: bshad du yod na'ang gzhung 'di gtso cher zab mo'i
NK114(ye)001:4179: lugs su bshad pas de tsam gyis mi chog pa
NK114(ye)001:4180: med la yi ge mang bas brir yang ma btub
NK114(ye)001:4181: dang / bo // gnyis pa bsgrub pa'i bslab bya bshad pa gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:4182: smon pa'i bslab bya bshad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:4190: de ltar smon pa dang 'jug pa'i rang bzhin las
NK114(ye)001:4191: sems 'da' bar mi byed pa ni sems bzung ba'o
NK114(ye)001:4192: // de'i mi mthun pa'i phyogs spang zhing ltung ba
NK114(ye)001:4193: byung ba yang de ma thag phyir bcos pa ni
NK114(ye)001:4195: de nas rnam pa thams cad du rang gzhan gyi
NK114(ye)001:4196: bde sdug barje ba la slob pa ni spel ba'i
NK114(ye)001:4199: bdag bde gzhan gyi sdug bsngal dag /
NK114(ye)001:4200: yang dag barje bar ma byas na //
NK114(ye)001:4201: sangs rgyas nyid du mi 'grub cing //
NK114(ye)001:4202: 'khor ba na yang bde ba med //
NK114(ye)001:4204: de'i phyir na 'di ltar las dang po pa'i dus
NK114(ye)001:4205: su bdag nyid phun sum tshogs par dga' ba bzhin
NK114(ye)001:4206: du gzhan dag kyang dga' la /
NK114(ye)001:4207: bdag nyid sdug bsngal mi 'dod pa bzhin du sems
NK114(ye)001:4208: can gzhan dag kyang sdug bsngal mi 'dod pa des
NK114(ye)001:4209: na bdag nyid ni bsrung zhing /
NK114(ye)001:4210: gzhan dag yal bar 'dor ba 'di bzang po ma
NK114(ye)001:4211: yin par bltas la bdag gzhan mnyam pa nyid du
NK114(ye)001:4212: bsgom par bya'o // de la goms nas sems can thams cad bdag nyid kyi khur du khyer te /
NK114(ye)001:4213: dbugs phyir 'byung ba'i gnas skabs thams cad la bdag
NK114(ye)001:4214: gi bde ba dang yon tan thams cad dbugs de
NK114(ye)001:4215: dang lhan du bdag dang bral te gzhan sems can
NK114(ye)001:4216: thams cad la yang dag par smin par bsam nas
NK114(ye)001:4217: spo ba dang / dbugs nang du rdub pa'i tshe
NK114(ye)001:4218: de dang lhan cig gzhan sems can gyi sdug bsngal
NK114(ye)001:4219: dang skyon thams cad gzhan de dag dang bral nas
NK114(ye)001:4220: bdag gi rgyud la smin pa'i khur dang du blangs
NK114(ye)001:4221: nas sems can thams cad kyi sdug bsngal bdag kho
NK114(ye)001:4222: nas bzoda par bya'o snyam pa'i go cha bgos te
NK114(ye)001:4223: spo ba dang / / de ltar gtong len gyi
NK114(ye)001:4224: dmigs pa la sgyid mi lug par thi bas brag
NK114(ye)001:4225: la tshang bca' ba ltar snying stobs kyi dpung bskyed
NK114(ye)001:4226: spo ba dang / / de / spyod 'jug las /
NK114(ye)001:4227: bdag dang gzhan du barje bya ba //
NK114(ye)001:4228: gsang ba'i dam pa spyad par bya //
NK114(ye)001:4230: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa ngo mtshar rmad du
NK114(ye)001:4231: byung ba de lta bu rang rgyud la 'du byed
NK114(ye)001:4232: pa la / dang po sems can nad pa lta
NK114(ye)001:4233: bu gcig la dmigs nas bsgom pa nas rim gyis
NK114(ye)001:4234: sems can thams cad kyi bar du bsgom zhing goms
NK114(ye)001:4235: nas dngos su rang nus dang bstun te rang gi
NK114(ye)001:4236: bde ba'i rkyen zas gos sogs gzhan la sbyin par
NK114(ye)001:4237: byed cing gzhan bkres shing grang ba sogs pa'i rkyen
NK114(ye)001:4238: rang gi thog tu len pa la bslab pa de
NK114(ye)001:4239: byang chub kyi bar du mi 'bral bar phyi phyir
NK114(ye)001:4240: te yang dang yang du smon zhing bdag gzhan gyi
NK114(ye)001:4241: don gtso bor byas pa'i skyon yon spyod 'jug la
NK114(ye)001:4242: sogs pa las gsungs pa'i tshul la bsams te blo
NK114(ye)001:4244: gnyis pa smon pa'i rgyu 'bras bshad pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:4245: smon pa'i bslab bya ni gzhan la phan 'dod kyi
NK114(ye)001:4246: bsam pa bzang po tshad med pa bzhi po dang
NK114(ye)001:4247: / bdag gzhan mnyam pa dang barje ba'i sgo nas blo legs par sbyang bar bstan pa de'ang /
NK114(ye)001:4248: sems can thams cad kyi thog ma med pa nas
NK114(ye)001:4249: pha ma byas te drin chen pos bskyangs pa'i sgo
NK114(ye)001:4250: nas phan 'dogs par byas pa de dran nas drin
NK114(ye)001:4251: du lan gzo bar 'dod pa las byams pa skye
NK114(ye)001:4252: zhing / byamsa pa las snying rje dang /
NK114(ye)001:4253: snying rje de lasa byang chub kyi sems skye ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:4254: theg pa chen po'i sde snod rnams las gsungs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:4255: don b+ham ga la'i pan+di tas rgyu 'bras man ngag
NK114(ye)001:4256: bdun ldan du bzhed pas na /
NK114(ye)001:4257: tshad ma'i lung gis yang dag par grub bo //
NK114(ye)001:4258: de la rgyu 'bras man ngag bdun ni /
NK114(ye)001:4266: de la dang po mar shes pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:4267: sems can thams cad kyis bdag gi pha ma byas pa cis shes na /
NK114(ye)001:4268: bdag 'khor ba'i gnas su skye ba grangs med pa blangs pas te /
NK114(ye)001:4269: 'phags pa yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa chen po'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:4270: sa chen po 'di ril bu sran ma tsam du byas te /
NK114(ye)001:4271: sems can gcig gis bdag gi pha ma byas pa'i
NK114(ye)001:4272: grangs bgrangs nas sa chen po 'di zad par 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:4273: gyi / sems can gcig gis pha dang ma byas
NK114(ye)001:4274: pa'i grangs ni zad par mi 'gyur ro zhes pa'i
NK114(ye)001:4276: ma yi thug mtha' rgya shug tshigs gu tsam //
NK114(ye)001:4277: ril bur dril kyang sa yis lang mi 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:4278: zhes gsungs pa des na rgyal ba bden par smra
NK114(ye)001:4279: ba'i gsung la yid gnyis za ba'i gnas med cing
NK114(ye)001:4280: / bdag nyid lan grangs dpag tu med par 'khor
NK114(ye)001:4281: ba'i gnas 'dir skye ba de tsam zhig blangs pa
NK114(ye)001:4282: de'i tshe na bardzusa te skyes pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:4283: drod gsher las skyes pa 'ga' zhig gi tshe ma
NK114(ye)001:4284: gtogs thams cad du pha ma re la brten nas
NK114(ye)001:4285: skyes pas sems can gyi khams 'di na bdag gi
NK114(ye)001:4286: ma grangs med pa ma byas pa'i sems can de
NK114(ye)001:4287: ni gcig kyang med nges snyam du snying thag pa
NK114(ye)001:4288: nas bsam te 'bu srin la sogs pa'i sems can
NK114(ye)001:4289: su mthong ba dang dran pa thams cad la 'di
NK114(ye)001:4290: ni bdag gi ma rgan yin no //
NK114(ye)001:4291: skye ba barjesa nas ngo ma shes pa tsam las
NK114(ye)001:4292: da lta'i a ma rgan mo 'di dang khyad par
NK114(ye)001:4293: spu tsam yang med do zhes yang yang bsgoms pas
NK114(ye)001:4294: thams cad da lta'i ma dang khyad med du mthong
NK114(ye)001:4295: zhing shes pa zhig byung na mar shes pa zhes
NK114(ye)001:4296: bya'o // gnyis pa drin dran pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:4297: de ltar ma ru gyur pa de'i tshe na /
NK114(ye)001:4298: dang po bdag gi rnam par shes pa bar dor
NK114(ye)001:4299: 'khyams nas lus rten tshol zhing mi rnyed pa'i sdug
