NK114(ye)001:4300: bsngal gyis gdung ba na ma'i mngal du tshud de
NK114(ye)001:4301: lto bar bzung nas ma de'i lus lci ba dang
NK114(ye)001:4302: 'gro 'dug la sogs pa'i spyod lam dka' bas mtshon
NK114(ye)001:4303: sdug bsngal gyi rnam grangs du mas mnar bzhin rang
NK114(ye)001:4304: gi kha zas kyi dwangs mas bu'i lus rim gyis
NK114(ye)001:4305: smin par byas te sdug bsngal gyi tshor ba bzod
NK114(ye)001:4306: dka' bas gdung bzhin btsas pa na /
NK114(ye)001:4307: de ma thag pa'i skyes bu mi gtsang ba'i nang gi srin bu'am sbal pa dang 'dra ba /
NK114(ye)001:4308: yan lag dang nying lag gi rtsal ma rdzogs pa /
NK114(ye)001:4309: tshor ba bde sdug tu 'char yang dbang po'i mthu nyams pa /
NK114(ye)001:4310: bzhin ngan pa grul bum gyi byad dang 'dra ba /
NK114(ye)001:4311: yid du mi 'ong bas gzhan dag gis blta ba
NK114(ye)001:4312: tsam yang mi 'dod na reg pa lta yang ci
NK114(ye)001:4313: smos pa de / ma yisa ni tsham tshom med par blangs /
NK114(ye)001:4314: pang pas ni khrus khang ltar byas nasa /
NK114(ye)001:4315: mi gtsang ba dring ba'i cha mtha' dag ni gos
NK114(ye)001:4316: la sogs par reg bya rtsub kyis dogs nas lag
NK114(ye)001:4317: pa kho nas nye reg byas te phyis /
NK114(ye)001:4318: kha zas rags pa brten mi nus pas nu zho
NK114(ye)001:4319: ro mngar zhing nus pa 'jam po kho nas bsnyen
NK114(ye)001:4320: bkur byas shing lus kyi reg bya 'jam pos g.yogs
NK114(ye)001:4321: te drod la bcar bas grang ngad rtsub mo'i gos
NK114(ye)001:4322: kyis ni mi skyo bar byas /
NK114(ye)001:4327: 'khyags kyis dogs nas mi mthun phyogs spangs /
NK114(ye)001:4328: shin tu phangs pa'i sems kyis bu chung de cung
NK114(ye)001:4329: zad na ba las bdag nyid 'chi bar 'dams pa
NK114(ye)001:4331: gom pa 'dor ba yan chad bslabs shing /
NK114(ye)001:4332: brtse ba'i sems drag pos bdag nyid sdug bsngal ba thams cad khyad du bsad de /
NK114(ye)001:4333: bu de'i don du gzhal la khong khro ba sogs sdig pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:4334: dka' tshegs tsha grang sogs sdug bsngal dang /
NK114(ye)001:4335: rang gi pha ma sogs gnyen bshes dang /
NK114(ye)001:4336: gzhan dag gis kyang ngan smras kyi gtam mi snyan
NK114(ye)001:4337: pa ngan pa ji tsam brjod pa de matha'a dag
NK114(ye)001:4338: bsran cing bzod nus pa'i ma de'i drin dang rim
NK114(ye)001:4339: gro de tsam byas pa thams cad la ci yang
NK114(ye)001:4340: mi sems par khyad du gsod par byed na de
NK114(ye)001:4341: las cho ga ste bya ba 'khrugs shing nor ba
NK114(ye)001:4343: spyod pa nyams pa gzhan 'jig rten na su zhig yod de med do //
NK114(ye)001:4344: des na sa chen po 'di ri rab dang rgya
NK114(ye)001:4345: mtsho nas lcags rira bcas bdag gi khur du song
NK114(ye)001:4346: yang khur chen po ma yin gyi /
NK114(ye)001:4347: byas pa drin du mi gzo ba'i sdug bsngal gyi
NK114(ye)001:4348: khur chen po ni shin tu bzod dka' zhing zad
NK114(ye)001:4349: pa'i mthar thug pa med pas dbyig dug dang /
NK114(ye)001:4350: gyur pa'i dug las nus pa ches cher myur ba
NK114(ye)001:4351: btsan dug bsres pa'i dug ldan gyi bza' ba khong
NK114(ye)001:4352: du chud pa'i skye bo bzhin du nyams par mi
NK114(ye)001:4355: sa rnams dang ni ri rnams dang //
NK114(ye)001:4356: rgya mtsho bdag gi khur min te //
NK114(ye)001:4357: byas pa mi gzo gang yin pa //
NK114(ye)001:4358: de ni bdag gi khur chen yin //
NK114(ye)001:4360: rgyu mtshan de dag gi phyir grangs pha mtha' yas
NK114(ye)001:4361: pa'i sems can de thams cad kun ma rul na
NK114(ye)001:4362: mang por gyur nas phan chen po btags pa de
NK114(ye)001:4363: lta bu ni gzhan sus kyang mi nus pas dam
NK114(ye)001:4364: pa mchog tu gyur pa'i drin chen po de dran
NK114(ye)001:4365: pas su mthong yang bdag gi da lta'i a ma
NK114(ye)001:4366: drin can ma bzhin du drin chen po dang ldan
NK114(ye)001:4367: pa drin lan gzhal ba shin tu dka' ba zhig
NK114(ye)001:4368: go snyam du bsam pa de 'dra ba sems can
NK114(ye)001:4369: thams cad la ma byung gi bar du blo sbyang
NK114(ye)001:4370: bar bya'o // gsum pa drin gzo ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:4371: de ltar snying thag pa nas drin dran pa de'i
NK114(ye)001:4372: tshe na 'di ltar sems can de dag thams cad
NK114(ye)001:4373: bdag la de 'dra ba'i drin chen po dang ldan
NK114(ye)001:4375: rang rang ni srid pa'i gnas 'di na sdug bsngal
NK114(ye)001:4376: rgyu 'bras kyi mnar bzhin de las thar ba'i thabs
NK114(ye)001:4377: tsam yang mi shes par shin tu nyam thag la
NK114(ye)001:4378: / bdag ni da res dal 'byor mi'i lus rten rnyed /
NK114(ye)001:4379: dge ba'i bshes gnyen mtshan nyid dang ldan pa mjal
NK114(ye)001:4380: zab dgu'i gdams pa mang po thob cing phan gnod
NK114(ye)001:4381: ngo shes shing thar lam bsgrub tu yod pa'i skabs
NK114(ye)001:4382: 'di na sems can de rnams la drin lan gang
NK114(ye)001:4383: yang ma 'jal bar rang nyid gcig pu thar bas
NK114(ye)001:4384: mi 'ong gi drin lan du phan zhig btags dgos
NK114(ye)001:4385: / phan pa de yang chung ngu tsam dang ngan
NK114(ye)001:4386: ngon tsam zhig gis mi 'ong bas thabs ji lta
NK114(ye)001:4387: bu zhig gis phan pa ji 'dra ba zhig nye
NK114(ye)001:4388: bar bsgrub par bya snyam du de kho na la
NK114(ye)001:4389: / sems par bya'o // de ltar mang du goms
NK114(ye)001:4390: pas bzhi pa yid 'ong gi byams pa skye ste
NK114(ye)001:4391: de'i tshe na sems can rang la dgra byed pa
NK114(ye)001:4392: zhig mthong na'ang mas bu sdug gu mthong ba ltar
NK114(ye)001:4393: de la khong mi khro bar ma zad snying nas
NK114(ye)001:4394: brtse zhing yid du 'ong bar 'gyur zhing 'di bde
NK114(ye)001:4395: ba dam pa dang 'phrad pa'i thabs shig bdag gis
NK114(ye)001:4396: nus na ci ma rung snyam pa'i blo lhang gis
NK114(ye)001:4397: skye ba zhig 'ong na sems can gzhan la de
NK114(ye)001:4398: 'dra ba'i blo skye ba smos kyang ci dgos te
NK114(ye)001:4399: / sems par bya'o // / klu'i rgyal po rgya mtshos zhus pa las /
NK114(ye)001:4400: byams pas brgyan na sems can thams cad la khong
NK114(ye)001:4401: khro ba med pa'i sems su 'gyur ro zhes so
NK114(ye)001:4402: // de lta bu'i byams pa de ni thams cad
NK114(ye)001:4403: mkhyen par sems bskyed pa'i rgyu grung po snying rje
NK114(ye)001:4404: chen po'i chu ba lta bu ste /
NK114(ye)001:4406: snying rje'i chu ba byams pa ste //
NK114(ye)001:4408: blo gros rgya mtshos zhus pa las /
NK114(ye)001:4409: byams pas sems can kun la yang dag lta //
NK114(ye)001:4410: 'di ni thams cad mkhyen par sems sbyong yin //
NK114(ye)001:4412: lnga pa brtse ba'i snying rje ni /
NK114(ye)001:4413: byams sems de las snying rje sogs tshad med pa'i
NK114(ye)001:4414: blo ngang gis 'byung ste de ltar byams pa'i yul
NK114(ye)001:4415: du gyur pa'i sems can de rnams kyis sdug bsngal
NK114(ye)001:4416: gyi rgyu sdig pa mi dge ba'i las sna tshogs
NK114(ye)001:4417: byed pa dang / 'bras bu sdug bsngal gsum gyis
NK114(ye)001:4418: mnar ba mthong nas shin tu mi bzod pa'i sems
NK114(ye)001:4419: kyis sdug bsngal de thams cad rang gi thog tu
NK114(ye)001:4420: bab pa tsam du gdung yang sdug bsngal rgyu 'bras
NK114(ye)001:4421: dang bcas pa de dag bsal ba'i nus pa ni
NK114(ye)001:4422: byed pa dang / bdag la med / blos btang
NK114(ye)001:4423: ste ji mi snyam du 'jog ni mi phod pas
NK114(ye)001:4424: ma lag rdum ma'i bu chus khyer ba ltar ci
NK114(ye)001:4425: byed gtol med par gyur pa zhig ste /
NK114(ye)001:4427: snying rjes brgyan na sems can yongs su mi gtong bar 'gyur ro zhes dang /
NK114(ye)001:4428: snying rje ldan pas gzhan gyi bya bar brtson //
NK114(ye)001:4430: de'i tshe na sems can 'ga' zhig bde ba'i rgyu
NK114(ye)001:4431: 'bras dang ldan na rang nyid phun sum tshogs pa
NK114(ye)001:4432: las kyang dga' ba bla lhag tu skye zhing thams
NK114(ye)001:4433: cad kun la nye ring dang chags sdang gi sems
NK114(ye)001:4434: med cing mnyam par blta bas tshad med bzhi po
NK114(ye)001:4435: gong du 'phel zhing rgyas par 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:4436: drug pa lhag bsam rnam dag ni /
NK114(ye)001:4437: de ltar tshad med bzhi'i blo goms pa de las ni 'di ltar /
NK114(ye)001:4438: 'o na snying rje ba'i sar gzhag pas mi 'ong
NK114(ye)001:4439: gis sems can 'di thams cad 'khor ba'i las snang
NK114(ye)001:4440: sdug bsngal bag chags thams cad dang bral nas gtan
NK114(ye)001:4441: gyi bde ba dam pa zhig la bdag kho nas
NK114(ye)001:4443: de'i thabs la bdag gis ngal ba brgya phrag du
NK114(ye)001:4444: ma dang du blangs te brtson pa la sems zhum
NK114(ye)001:4445: pa dang skyo ba med par bya'o snyam du bsam
NK114(ye)001:4446: nas pha rol po rnams bde dge dam pa'i rgyu
NK114(ye)001:4447: chos la sbyor ba la rtag tu dga' zhing spro
NK114(ye)001:4448: bas zhum pa'i sems mi skye zhing chos kyi mchog
NK114(ye)001:4449: gzhan phan gyi bsam pa bzang po rgyud la 'byongs
NK114(ye)001:4450: pas rjes su chags pa dang khong khro ba spangs
NK114(ye)001:4451: te sems can kun la sems mnyam par /
NK114(ye)001:4452: 'tshe ba'i blo gtan nas mi 'byung zhing de thams
NK114(ye)001:4453: cad kyi don rang nyid gcig pu'i khur du song
NK114(ye)001:4454: ba'i sems gting nas skye bar 'gyur ba zhig 'ong
NK114(ye)001:4455: ba yin te / mdo de dag las /
NK114(ye)001:4456: dga' dang ldan pas chos la pha rol sbyor //
NK114(ye)001:4457: btang snyoms ldan pas chos mchog 'tshe ba med //
NK114(ye)001:4458: 'di ni thams cad mkhyen par sems sbyong yin //
NK114(ye)001:4460: dga' bas brgyan na zhum pa med pa'i sems su 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:4461: btang snyoms kyis brgyan na rjes su chags pa dang khong khro ba spong bar 'gyur ro zhes so //
NK114(ye)001:4462: brgyan na zhes pa ni lhag pa'i bsam pa la'o //
NK114(ye)001:4463: bdun pa rang 'bras bla med ni /
NK114(ye)001:4464: de ltar byas pa shes shing drin dugzo ba la
NK114(ye)001:4465: sogs pa'i bsam pa dang ldan pa yi skyes bu
NK114(ye)001:4466: lhag pa'i bsam pa rnam par dag pa rgyud la
NK114(ye)001:4467: 'byongs pa gang yin pa de la yang bsam pa
NK114(ye)001:4468: 'di 'byung ste bdag gis sems can thams cad gang
NK114(ye)001:4469: la 'god par 'dod pa'i gtan gyi bde ba bla
NK114(ye)001:4470: na med pa de rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyi go
NK114(ye)001:4472: go 'phang gang la sems can thams cad 'god par
NK114(ye)001:4473: 'dod pa'i 'bras bu de rang gis ma thob na
NK114(ye)001:4474: gzhan de la dgod pa'i nus pa med pas bdag
NK114(ye)001:4475: gis nges par mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad
NK114(ye)001:4476: kyi don du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang
NK114(ye)001:4477: thob par bya'o snyam du snying thag pa nas dam
NK114(ye)001:4478: bca' ba'i blo rkyen gyis mi 'phrog par rgyun chags
NK114(ye)001:4479: su 'byung ba ni man ngag snga ma drug gi
NK114(ye)001:4480: 'bras bu'o // de lta bu'i gang zag de la
NK114(ye)001:4481: ni sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis
NK114(ye)001:4482: rtag tu dgongs shing byin gyis rlob par mdzad cing
NK114(ye)001:4483: 'bras bu'o // / gtsang ris kyi dpal mgon bdun cu la sogs pas nye bar bsrung ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:4484: nang gi yon tan dad sogs 'phags pa'i nor bdun
NK114(ye)001:4485: gyis kyang 'bral ba med par bsnyen par 'gyur te
NK114(ye)001:4487: byas pa shes shes byas pa gzo //
NK114(ye)001:4488: byas pa chud mi gzon pa yi //
NK114(ye)001:4489: mi la dpal mgon nye bar gnas //
NK114(ye)001:4492: yon tan ma lus byang chub sems la brten //
NK114(ye)001:4493: byang chub mchog sems snying rje'i rgyu las byung //
NK114(ye)001:4495: gsum pa dkar nag chos brgyad bshad pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:4496: byang chub smon pa'i sems ni sems can gyi khams
NK114(ye)001:4497: yin no cog yal bar mi 'dor ba'i bsam pa
NK114(ye)001:4498: bzang po'i cha shas yongs su rdzogs shing rang don
NK114(ye)001:4499: yid byed kyis ma bsgribs la 'jug pa'i gzugs brnyan
NK114(ye)001:4500: gsal bar ston pas dper na ston ka' dus kyi
NK114(ye)001:4501: zla ba nya gang ba sprin gyis ma bsgribs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:4502: gsar pa ri bong gi gzugs brnyan 'dzin pa dang
NK114(ye)001:4503: 'dra ba de gtong ba'i rkyen ni rang nyid blo
NK114(ye)001:4505: sems can mi bsrun zhing byed par ngan pas rang
NK114(ye)001:4506: gcig pu zhi bde don du gnyer bas rtsa ba
NK114(ye)001:4507: nas gtong ba ste sngar bshad zin to //
NK114(ye)001:4508: yang sems bskyed de la sgrib par byed pa sgra
NK114(ye)001:4509: gcan gyi gdong ba las kyang thu ba'i mi mthun
NK114(ye)001:4510: pa'i phyogs nag po'i chos bzhi po yin pas na
NK114(ye)001:4511: rtag tu nyes pa de mi 'byung ba'i thabs la
NK114(ye)001:4512: 'bad cing gal te byung bar gyur na'ang de ma
NK114(ye)001:4513: thag gnyen po'i stobs bskyed nas ring du spang zhig
NK114(ye)001:4515: bzhi po de gang zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:4519: sbyin gnas te yon tan dang ldan pa dag la
NK114(ye)001:4520: mchoda 'os zhes bya ste de rnams brdzun gyis mgo
NK114(ye)001:4521: bskor ba ste / de yang bla ma lta bu
NK114(ye)001:4522: la mngon gyur du gros gcig zhus nas lkog tu
NK114(ye)001:4523: de las gzhan pa'i gros sna bsdur te /
NK114(ye)001:4524: de bla mas gsan du 'ong zhes dbu g.yogs pa la sogs pas bslu ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:4525: yang gang zag gzhan bsod nams cha mthun dang theg
NK114(ye)001:4526: gsum gang rung gi lam la zhugs te thar pa
NK114(ye)001:4527: cha mthun gyi bsod nams byas shing bsags pa 'gyod
NK114(ye)001:4528: pa'i gnas ma yin la g.yo sgyu'i sems kyis de'i
NK114(ye)001:4529: bsam pa rmongs par byed pa'i gtam khyod la sdom
NK114(ye)001:4531: khyod kyis bsgrub par dka' ba'i las de bas /
NK114(ye)001:4532: gzhan sla ba zhig bsgrub na des chog mod ces zer ba'am /
NK114(ye)001:4533: khyod kyis nyams su len rgyu'i chos de rnam par
NK114(ye)001:4534: mi dag go zhes pa la sogs pa brjod de
NK114(ye)001:4535: the tshom bskyed nas 'gyod du bcug pa'am /
NK114(ye)001:4536: ma yin kyang rung ste dper na phyag skor byed
NK114(ye)001:4537: pa lta bu la khyod kyi de legs te khyim
NK114(ye)001:4538: gyi bya ba 'di dang 'di nyams par gyur to
NK114(ye)001:4539: zhes 'gyod pa'i gnas la sbyar ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:4540: yul dam pa byang chub tu sems bskyed pa'i gang
NK114(ye)001:4541: zag rnams la 'di ni ngang tshul ngan pa can
NK114(ye)001:4542: no zhes pa la sogs pas dngos su skur 'debs
NK114(ye)001:4543: bya zhing 'dis mi tshangs par spyad pa sogs mi
NK114(ye)001:4544: mthun pa 'di dang du blangs so zhes lkog tu
NK114(ye)001:4545: mi snyam pa sgrogs na nyes pa che ste /
NK114(ye)001:4546: spyir mya ngan las 'das pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:4547: gzhan gyi nyes pa mthong yang skyon mi smra ba ste /
NK114(ye)001:4548: rtag tu dge ba'i chos 'ba' zhig smra'o //
NK114(ye)001:4550: khyad par byang chub sems dpa' la skur pa 'debs pa'i nyes pa bzod par dka' ba yin te /
NK114(ye)001:4551: 'phags pa dad pa'i stobs bskyed pa la 'jug pa las /
NK114(ye)001:4552: gang la la zhig gis byang chub sems dpa' la
NK114(ye)001:4553: rkyen gang yang rung bas khyad du bsad de spyos
NK114(ye)001:4554: na de'i sdig pa'i las kyis sems can dmyal ba
NK114(ye)001:4556: lus dpag tshad lnga brgya pa la mgo lnga brgya yod de /
NK114(ye)001:4557: mgo bo re re la lce brgya brgya /
NK114(ye)001:4558: lce re re la yang lcags kyi thong gshol 'bar ba lnga brgya lnga brgyas rmo'o //
NK114(ye)001:4560: gang byang chub sems dpa' la skur ba 'debs pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:4561: sangs rgyas kyi rigs gcod par zhugs pa yin na
NK114(ye)001:4562: byang chub sems dpa' la skur pa 'debs pa des
NK114(ye)001:4563: dam pa'i chos spangs pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:4565: chos yongs su 'dzin pa gzhan ma yin te /
NK114(ye)001:4566: chos yongs su 'dzin pa de ni chos so zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:4568: lung bstan ma thob byang chub sems dpa' gang zhig gis //
NK114(ye)001:4569: lung bstan thob la sems khros rtsod pa rtsom byed na //
NK114(ye)001:4570: tha ba skyon ldan sems kyi skad cig ji snyed pa //
NK114(ye)001:4571: de snyed bskal bar gzhi nas go cha bgo dgos so //
NK114(ye)001:4572: zhes khong khro'i bsam pa ji tsam skyes pa de
NK114(ye)001:4573: srid kyi bskal bar lam gzhi nas bgrod dgos pas
NK114(ye)001:4574: rdzogs pa'i byang chub la thag shin tu ring ba
NK114(ye)001:4575: yin no // des na bcom ldan 'das kyis /
NK114(ye)001:4576: nga dang 'dra ba ma gtogs gang zag gi tshod
NK114(ye)001:4577: gang zag gis gzung bar mi bya'o zhes gsungs pas
NK114(ye)001:4578: / byang chub sems dpa' gang yin shes dka' bas kun la khong khro ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:4580: mi snyan pa brjod pa rnams gzab ste spang bar bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:4581: gzhan yang rang gi nyes pa thabs kyis mi mngon par byed pa'i g.yo dang /
NK114(ye)001:4582: yon tan med bzhin du yod par bardzu ba'i sgyu
NK114(ye)001:4583: ste de gnyis zung du 'brel bas gzhan bslu ba
NK114(ye)001:4584: dang / bre log dang srang log 'dzug pas mtshon
NK114(ye)001:4585: bslu thabs kyi spyod pa sna tshogs pas gzhan dag
NK114(ye)001:4586: mgo bo bskor bar byed pa dang bzhi'o //
NK114(ye)001:4587: de ltar nag po'i chos bzhi la bzhi tshan mang du bstan kyang /
NK114(ye)001:4589: 'od srung chos bzhi dang ldan na byang chub kyi sems brjed par 'gyur te /
NK114(ye)001:4591: bla ma dang mchod par 'os pa bslu ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:4592: gzhan 'gyod pa'i gnas ma yin pa la 'gyod pa bskyed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:4593: sems bskyed pa'i byang chub sems dpa' la sdang sems kyis skyon brjod pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:4594: sems can la g.yo dang sgyu'i spyod pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:4596: spyir 'phags yul gyi pan+di ta rnams kyis byang chub
NK114(ye)001:4597: sems dpa'i bslab pa'i dbye bsdu mdzad tshul sde snod
NK114(ye)001:4598: kyi don gtso che ba'i dbang du byas pa dang
NK114(ye)001:4599: / sems dang po bskyed pa dang spyod pa la
NK114(ye)001:4600: zhugs pa'i khyad par la dmigs nas de dang de'i
NK114(ye)001:4601: dbang du byas pa sogs rnam pa gcig tu ma
NK114(ye)001:4602: / nges shing / dkar nag chos brgyad kyi rnam dbye med pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:4603: grangs ma nges pa sogs yod kyang bod 'dir srol
NK114(ye)001:4604: 'byed gnyis kyi lugs kho na dar che ba'i rjes
NK114(ye)001:4605: su 'brang ngo // de la dkar nag gi chos brgyad po smon pa'i bslab byar mthun yang /
NK114(ye)001:4606: nag chos bzhi po skye ba 'dir gtong ba'i rgyur 'dod pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:4607: skye ba gzhan du sems bskyed mngon du mi 'gyur ba'i rgyur 'dod pa'i phyogs gnyis su gnas la /
NK114(ye)001:4608: 'on kyang smon pa'i gtong rgyu sems can blos btang
NK114(ye)001:4609: na 'jug pa'ang shugs la dengs 'gro bas gnyis ka
NK114(ye)001:4610: gtong gi / smon sems ma btang na nag chos
NK114(ye)001:4611: gcig pos de ma thag tu sems bskyed rtsad nas
NK114(ye)001:4612: gtong gi / mi gtong yang / chos bzhi po
NK114(ye)001:4613: de gang yang rung ba zhig byung nas yang yang
NK114(ye)001:4614: nyams su myong na smon sems nyams pa'i rgyu byas
NK114(ye)001:4616: phan pa'i sems dang rdzas 'gal ba'i bsam pas rgyud
NK114(ye)001:4617: bslad pa'i phyir gnam stong gi zla ba rang stobs
NK114(ye)001:4619: bco lnga'i zla ba gzhan stobs kyis bsgrib pa gnyis
NK114(ye)001:4620: bkrag tu mi mngon pa la mtshungs pa ltar gang
NK114(ye)001:4621: du byung ba'i thun de'i thog tha bar gsum gang
NK114(ye)001:4622: rung du 'gyod pa drag po dang bcas /
NK114(ye)001:4623: gnyen po bskyod de bshags pas ma sleb na thun
NK114(ye)001:4624: tshod 'das pa'i tshe de yi mod la sems bskyed
NK114(ye)001:4625: 'chor ba'i rgyu byed pa yin te /
NK114(ye)001:4626: bag chags ngan pa de'i rgyu yun ring du goms
NK114(ye)001:4627: pas gzhan la phan pa'i bsam pa bzang po de
NK114(ye)001:4629: des na phyi mar yang mngon du mi 'gyur la /
NK114(ye)001:4630: khyad par du mchod 'os bslu ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:4631: byang sems la zhe sdang bas ngan smras brjod pa'i
NK114(ye)001:4632: las kyis byang chub sems kyi rtsa ba 'chad par
NK114(ye)001:4633: bshad pa dang / g.yo sgyus gzhan bslu ba la
NK114(ye)001:4634: brten nas sems can gcig tsam gtan nas blos btang
NK114(ye)001:4635: ba'i sems byung na mdud pa grol na chun po
NK114(ye)001:4636: 'jig pa ltar snying rjes gzhan don la dmigs pa
NK114(ye)001:4637: nyams pas sems bskyed 'chor bar 'gyur ba'i phyir ro
NK114(ye)001:4638: bshad pa dang / // des na de dag gi
NK114(ye)001:4639: gnyen por ches che ba dkar po'i chos bzhi po
NK114(ye)001:4640: bshad pa dang / // ni / srog la bab
NK114(ye)001:4641: kyang brda 'phrod pa'i sems can yin no cog la
NK114(ye)001:4642: shes bzhin du rdzun mi smra ba dang po ste
NK114(ye)001:4643: bshad pa dang / // ni / / de ni
NK114(ye)001:4644: yul khyad par can rdzun gyis mgo bskor ba'i gnas
NK114(ye)001:4645: ma yin pa bslu ba'i gnyen por yang 'gyur ro
NK114(ye)001:4646: bshad pa dang / // ni / / // des gzhan gsum la'ang rigs 'gre shes par bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:4647: de bzhin du rgyal ba'i sras po byang chub sems
NK114(ye)001:4648: dpa' rnams la ston pa dang mtshungs par bltas te
NK114(ye)001:4649: gus shing don du gnas pa'i basngagasa pa brjod pa
NK114(ye)001:4650: ni gnyis pa'o // de yang byang chub sems dpa' ni rigs rus dang cho 'brang /
NK114(ye)001:4651: lus rten dang rtags sogs kyis mi shes pas /
NK114(ye)001:4652: mngon gyur du mthong ba la rim gro bskyed cing /
NK114(ye)001:4655: dud 'gro'i skye bar yang yod pas /
NK114(ye)001:4657: rtag tu kun gyi slob mar gyur //
NK114(ye)001:4658: zhes pa ltar kun la dag snang sbyong ba gnad yin no //
NK114(ye)001:4659: yang rtag tu g.yo sgyu med cing lhag pa'i bsam
NK114(ye)001:4660: pa dag pas sems can thams cad la phan pa'i
NK114(ye)001:4661: bsam sbyor don du gnyer ba gsum pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:4662: rang gis smin par nus pa'i sems can mtha' dag
NK114(ye)001:4663: blo'i thugs bskyed de sems dang po bskyed pa la
NK114(ye)001:4664: bskul ba nas / rim gyis rdzogs pa'i byang chub
NK114(ye)001:4665: kyi lam la snying thag pa nas dkri bar bya
NK114(ye)001:4666: bskul ba nas / ba dang bzhi'o // de ltar yang 'od srung gis zhus pa las /
NK114(ye)001:4667: 'od srung chos bzhi dang ldan na byang chub kyi sems brjed par mi 'gyur te /
NK114(ye)001:4669: shes bzhin du rdzun mi smra ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:4670: byang chub sems dpa' la ston pa'i 'du shes bskyed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:4671: sems can la g.yo sgyu med par lhag pa'i bsam pas gnas pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:4672: sems can thams cad theg pa chen po la yang dag par dgod pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:4674: de lta bas na nag po'i chos bzhi'i gnyen po
NK114(ye)001:4675: byed cing tshe 'dir sems bskyed brjed par mi 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:4676: zhing / tshe rabs gzhan thams cad du byang chub
NK114(ye)001:4677: kyi sems mngon du 'gyur ba'i rgyu yin par gsungs
NK114(ye)001:4678: pas nan tan gyis nyams su blang bar bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:4679: bzhii pa 'du shes bzhi bshad pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:4680: sems bskyed mi nyams shing brtan par bya ba'i sgo
NK114(ye)001:4681: nas bsrung ba'i thabs la 'du shes bzhi bsten par
NK114(ye)001:4682: bya ste / theg pa chen po'i dge ba'i bshes
NK114(ye)001:4683: gnyen ni bdag la byang chub chen po'i lam ma
NK114(ye)001:4684: nor bar ston par mdzad pas de la sangs rgyas
NK114(ye)001:4686: des bstan pa'i zab pa dang rgya che ba'i chos
NK114(ye)001:4687: ni rang gis byang chub bsgrub pa'i thabs dam pa
NK114(ye)001:4688: yin pas de la lam gyi 'du shes dang /
NK114(ye)001:4689: theg pa chen po'i lam de sgrub pa'i byang sems
NK114(ye)001:4690: gzhan rnams ni rang dang lta spyod mthun zhing byang
NK114(ye)001:4691: chub kyi bar du mi 'bral bar 'grogs shing bsten
NK114(ye)001:4692: par bya ba yin pas de dag la grogs kyi
NK114(ye)001:4693: 'du shes dang / mtha' yas pa'i sems can ma
NK114(ye)001:4694: lus pa kun ni sems bskyed pa dang bslab pa
NK114(ye)001:4695: bsgrub pa'i yul yin pas bsod nams kyi zhing du
NK114(ye)001:4696: 'du shes dang / gyur zhing / 'di rnams la
NK114(ye)001:4697: phan btags pas 'bras bu chen po 'byung ba dang
NK114(ye)001:4698: 'du shes dang / gyur zhing / / rgyal ba
NK114(ye)001:4699: dgyes pa'i thabs yang dag pa'ang sems can mgu bar
NK114(ye)001:4700: bya ba las gzhan med pa'i phyir shin tu gces
NK114(ye)001:4702: de thams cad la bu gcig pa'i 'du shes 'jog par bya dgos te /
NK114(ye)001:4703: 'di dag ni ting 'dzin rgyal po las bshad do //
NK114(ye)001:4704: de ltar bde sdug gtong len nas 'du shes bzhi'i
NK114(ye)001:4705: bar du 'di dag la tshul bzhin slob pa ni
NK114(ye)001:4706: smon pa'i bslab bya theg pa chen po'i sde snod
NK114(ye)001:4707: rnams las btus pa yang dag pa dag go //
NK114(ye)001:4708: gnyis pa 'jug pa'i bslab bya bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:4712: 'jug pa'i sdom pa blangs pa des gang la bslab par bya ba'i yul ni /
NK114(ye)001:4713: spyir theg pa chen po'i sde snod rnams las rgyal
NK114(ye)001:4714: sras byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi spyod pa rgya
NK114(ye)001:4715: mtsho lta bu zhig gsungs pa thams cad yin zhing
NK114(ye)001:4716: de dag kun kyang bsdu na pha rol tu phyin
NK114(ye)001:4718: de yang mtshan nyid pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:4720: sbyin pa mi mthun phyogs nyams dang //
NK114(ye)001:4721: rnam par mi rtog ye shes ldan //
NK114(ye)001:4722: 'dod pa thams cad yongs rdzogs byed //
NK114(ye)001:4723: sems can rnams smin byed rnam gsum //
NK114(ye)001:4724: zhes pa nas shes rab kyi bar du gsungs pa ltar /
NK114(ye)001:4725: rang rang gi mi mthun pa'i phyogs dang bral ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:4726: grogs 'khor gsum mi rtog pa'i shes rab kyis zin pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:4727: byed las gzhan gyi 'dod don rdzogs par byed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:4728: de'i sgo nas gdul bya rnams skal ba dang 'tshams
NK114(ye)001:4729: par byang chub gsum du smin par byed pa ste
NK114(ye)001:4730: / khyad chos bzhi dang ldan pa zhig yin la /
NK114(ye)001:4731: de la ci'i phyir pha rol tu phyin pa zhes bya zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:4732: pa ra mi ta zhes pa'i sgra las pa ra ma pha rol dang /
NK114(ye)001:4734: 'jig rten pa dang nyan rang gi dge ba kun
NK114(ye)001:4735: la phul du phyin pa'i pha rol tu 'gro bas
NK114(ye)001:4737: dbye na mngon rtogs rgyan las /
NK114(ye)001:4738: de dag so sor sbyin la sogs //
NK114(ye)001:4739: rnam pa drug tu bsdus pa yis //
NK114(ye)001:4740: go cha'i sgrub pa gang yin te //
NK114(ye)001:4741: drug tshan drug gis ji bzhin bshad //
NK114(ye)001:4742: ces pa ltar re re la drug drug tu phye bas sum cu rtsa drug go //
NK114(ye)001:4743: drug po 'di dag tu grangs nges pa yang /
NK114(ye)001:4744: sdud byed drug po 'dis bsdu bya byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims rnam pa gsum dang /
NK114(ye)001:4745: bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi dang /
NK114(ye)001:4746: bslab pa rnam pa gsum dang /
NK114(ye)001:4747: thabs dang shes rab bam tshogs rnam pa gnyis la
NK114(ye)001:4748: sogs pa mang po zhig bsdus pas na byang chub
NK114(ye)001:4749: sems dpa'i lam gyi sdom chen po yin pas na
NK114(ye)001:4750: de las mang mi dgos te /
NK114(ye)001:4751: de yang nyes par spyod pa thams cad ni ser
NK114(ye)001:4752: sna nas shes rab 'chal ba gti mug gi rang
NK114(ye)001:4753: bzhin can gyi bar de dag tu 'du bas de
NK114(ye)001:4754: rnams spang ba nyes spyod sdom pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:4755: dge ba'i chos thams cad kyang phyin drug gi ngo
NK114(ye)001:4756: bor 'dus pas de dag bsgrub pa dge ba chos
NK114(ye)001:4757: sdud dang / de dag gi sgo nas dngos brgyud
NK114(ye)001:4758: gang yang rung bar gzhan don byed pa sems can
NK114(ye)001:4759: don byed de tshul khrims gsum po bsdu zhing /
NK114(ye)001:4760: yang sbyin pas gdul bya 'khor du bsdus nas /
NK114(ye)001:4761: de la phyin drug gi gtam yang dag pa snyan
NK114(ye)001:4762: par brjod pas spro ba bskyed de bsgrub tshul shes
NK114(ye)001:4763: par byas nas / de dag gi don spyod du 'jug cing /
NK114(ye)001:4764: yid ches pa'i phyir rang yang don de dang mthun
NK114(ye)001:4765: par gnas pa ste bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi dang
NK114(ye)001:4768: bslab gsum dbang du mdzad nas ni //
NK114(ye)001:4769: rgyal bas pha rol phyin pa drug /
NK114(ye)001:4770: yang dag bshad de dang po gsum //
NK114(ye)001:4771: tha ma gnyis kyis rnam pa gnyis //
NK114(ye)001:4772: gcig ni gsum cha la yang gtogs //
NK114(ye)001:4774: sbyin pas longs spyod la chags pa dang bral bas tshul khrims phun sum tshogs par 'gyur la /
NK114(ye)001:4775: de las dge sbyong du byed pa'i chos bzhi dang ldan par 'gyur bas bzod pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:4776: de gsum rgyu dang ngo bo dang khyad par gyi
NK114(ye)001:4777: sgo nas lhag pa tshul khrims kyi bslab pa dang
NK114(ye)001:4778: / bsam gtan ni lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi bslab pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:4779: shes rab ni lhag pa shes rab kyi bslab pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:4780: brtson 'grus ni gsum ga'i grogs yin pa'i phyir bslab pa gsum dang /
NK114(ye)001:4781: yang drug po de dag las /
NK114(ye)001:4782: snga ma gnyis thabs bsod nams kyi tshogs dang /
NK114(ye)001:4783: phyi ma shes rab ye shes kyi tshogs dang /
NK114(ye)001:4785: sdug bsngal dang len dang gnod byed la ci mi snyam pa'i bzod pa gnyis bsod nams dang /
NK114(ye)001:4786: chos la nges sems kyi bzod pa ye shes /
NK114(ye)001:4787: dmigs pa dang bcas pa'i bsam gtan bsod nams dang /
NK114(ye)001:4788: dmigs pa med pa'i bsam gtan ye shes /
NK114(ye)001:4789: brtson 'grus gnyis ka'i grogs yin pas de gsum ni gnyis char la yang gtogs la /
NK114(ye)001:4790: shes rab kyis zin na lnga ga'ang ye shes kyi tshogs su 'gyur te /
NK114(ye)001:4792: sbyin dang tshul khrims bsod nams kyi //
NK114(ye)001:4793: tshogs yin shes rab ye shes te //
NK114(ye)001:4794: gsum ni gnyis char la yang gtogs //
NK114(ye)001:4795: lnga 'char yang ni ye shes tshogs //
NK114(ye)001:4797: yang snang bcas dang snang med gtso che ba tsam
NK114(ye)001:4798: gyis bzhag na phar phyin dang po lnga ni bsod
NK114(ye)001:4799: nams kyi tshogs te de rnams thabs la mi mkhas
NK114(ye)001:4800: pa dang / shes rab dang bral bas spyad na
NK114(ye)001:4801: 'khor ba'i lus dang longs spyod sogs phun sum tshogs
NK114(ye)001:4802: pa tsam gyi rgyu yin la /
NK114(ye)001:4803: thabs la mkhas pa dang shes rab zab mos zin
NK114(ye)001:4804: na thams cad mkhyen pa'i rgyur 'gyur bas dam pa'i
NK114(ye)001:4806: phyi ma shes rab kyi phar phyin gcig po ni
NK114(ye)001:4807: ye shes kyi tshogs kyi tshogs te de yang bdag
NK114(ye)001:4808: med pa'i rtogs pa nyi tshe ba tsam dang thabs
NK114(ye)001:4809: la mkhas pa dang bral bas ni zhi ba phyogs
NK114(ye)001:4810: gcig pa'i myang 'das tsam gyi rgyu byed la /
NK114(ye)001:4811: rtogs pa rgya che zhing thabs dang ma bral bas
NK114(ye)001:4812: tshogs chen po yin te des na shes rab kyis
NK114(ye)001:4814: thabs kyis mya ngan las 'das pa la mi gnas pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:4815: mi gnas pa'i myang 'das ni 'di gnyis kyi sgo nas bsgrub par bya dgos te /
NK114(ye)001:4816: gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:4817: ye shes kyi tshogs kyis ni nyon mongs pa thams cad spong bar 'gyur ba lags so //
NK114(ye)001:4818: bsod nams kyi tshogs kyis ni sems can thams cad nye bar 'tsho bar 'gyur ba lags so //
NK114(ye)001:4819: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK114(ye)001:4820: des na thabs dang shes rab zung 'brel gyi lam
NK114(ye)001:4821: 'di la ma bsten par mthar thug gi 'bras bu
NK114(ye)001:4822: sangs rgyas 'grub byed kyi thabs gzhan yod pa ma
NK114(ye)001:4823: yin no // 'o na phar phyin 'di dag gi
NK114(ye)001:4824: go rim 'di ltar nges pa'i rgyu mtshan ci zhe
NK114(ye)001:4825: yin no // na / snga phyii rgyu 'bras dang /
NK114(ye)001:4827: rags phra'i phyir bzhag ste mdo sde rgyan las /
NK114(ye)001:4828: snga ma la brten phyi ma skye //
NK114(ye)001:4829: dman dang mchog tu gnas phyir dang //
NK114(ye)001:4830: rags pa dang ni phra ba'i phyir //
NK114(ye)001:4831: de dag rim pas bstan pa yin //
NK114(ye)001:4833: ji ltar bsgrub pa'i tshul yang /
NK114(ye)001:4835: re ba med pa'i sbyin pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:4836: yang srid mi 'dod tshul khrims dang //
NK114(ye)001:4837: thams cad la ni bzod pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:4838: yon tan kun sdud brtson 'grus dang //
NK114(ye)001:4839: de bzhin bsam gtan gzugs med min //
NK114(ye)001:4840: shes rab thabs dang ldan pa yis //
NK114(ye)001:4841: pha rol phyin pa drug po la //
NK114(ye)001:4842: brtan pa rnams kyis yang dag spyod //
NK114(ye)001:4844: de ltar bsgrubs pa'i gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu ni /
NK114(ye)001:4846: sbyin pas longs spyod khrims kyis bde //
NK114(ye)001:4847: bzod pas gzugs mdzes brtson pas brjid //
NK114(ye)001:4848: bsam gtan gyis zhi blo yis grol //
NK114(ye)001:4851: phar phyin drug gis bsdus pa'i tshogs gnyis kyis sku gnyis 'grub ste /
NK114(ye)001:4852: sbyin pa la sogs pa'i bsod nams kyi tshogs las /
NK114(ye)001:4853: gzugs kyi sku zhing khams dang /
NK114(ye)001:4854: 'khor dang longs spyod la sogs pa phun sum tshogs pa thams cad 'byung la /
NK114(ye)001:4855: ye shes kyi tshogs kyis spros pa thams cad dang bral ba'i chos kyi sku 'grub ste /
NK114(ye)001:4857: sangs rgyas rnams kyi gzugs kyi sku //
NK114(ye)001:4858: bsod nams tshogs las 'khrungs pa ste //
NK114(ye)001:4859: chos kyi sku ni mdor bsdu na //
NK114(ye)001:4860: rgyal po ye shes tshogs las 'khrungs //
NK114(ye)001:4862: yang sbyin pa la sogs pa de dag gzhan don
NK114(ye)001:4863: du byang chub chen por bsngo bas mi zad par
NK114(ye)001:4865: mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad zil gyis gnon pa'i
NK114(ye)001:4866: stobs kyis dge ba byang chub tu nges par byed
NK114(ye)001:4867: pa'i stobs dang / 'dun pas skye ba thams cad
NK114(ye)001:4868: du sbyin sogs kyi yon tan rgyun mi 'chad par
NK114(ye)001:4869: 'byung ba'i sgo nas dge ba la rtag tu 'jug
NK114(ye)001:4870: par byed pa'i smon lam dang /
NK114(ye)001:4871: sbyin pa la sogs pa'i chos la longs spyod cing sems can smin par byed pa'i ye shes te /
NK114(ye)001:4873: mi zad pa dang rtag 'jug dang //
NK114(ye)001:4874: nges par longs spyod smin par byed //
NK114(ye)001:4876: de dag tshogs gnyis su bsdu na /
NK114(ye)001:4877: snga ma gsum bsod nams dang /
NK114(ye)001:4878: phyi ma gcig ye shes kyi tshogs so //
NK114(ye)001:4879: de ltar bzhi po de logs su bgrangs nas phar
NK114(ye)001:4880: phyin snga ma drug gi steng du bsnan pas pha
NK114(ye)001:4882: de lta bu'i phar phyin mtshan nyid pa bcu po
NK114(ye)001:4883: de 'phags pa'i sa bcu po la rim bzhin shas
NK114(ye)001:4884: che bar yod pa yin la /
NK114(ye)001:4885: byang sems las dang po pas kyang sems bskyed de
NK114(ye)001:4886: rtag tu sgo gsum gyis dge ba gang byas thams
NK114(ye)001:4887: cad thabs dang shes rab gnyis kyis zin par byas
NK114(ye)001:4888: te phar phyin de dag rjes mthun pa tshang bar
NK114(ye)001:4890: mdo sngags kyi man ngag zab mo'i sgom rim thams
NK114(ye)001:4891: cad nas kyang dang po skyabs sems nas bzung mjug
NK114(ye)001:4892: bsngo ba'i bar rnam pa dang bcas par bsten pa
NK114(ye)001:4893: thams cad thabs kyi cha dang /
NK114(ye)001:4894: de thams cad la zhen med kyis rgyas 'debs par bshad pa shes rab kyi cha ste /
NK114(ye)001:4895: de yang dge ba gzhan la bsngo ba dang man+dala dang mchod pa sogs sbyin pa /
NK114(ye)001:4896: theg pa rang sa'i 'jug sgo dang bstun pa'i blang dor ma nor bar spyod pa tshul khrims /
NK114(ye)001:4897: dge sbyor la dka' spyad sogs bzod pa bzod pa /
NK114(ye)001:4898: rang gis rang la bskul nas nyin mtshan kun tu dge sbyor gyis 'da' ba brtson 'grus /
NK114(ye)001:4899: thad ka thad ka'i dmigs pa la sems 'dzin pa bsam gtan /
NK114(ye)001:4900: de dag 'khor gsum yongs dag gi lta bas zin
NK114(ye)001:4901: pa shes rab ste rnam pa thams cad du phyin
NK114(ye)001:4902: drug gis bsdus pa'i tshogs gnyis sam thabs shes gnyis
NK114(ye)001:4903: po de ya ma bral ba la bslab pa ni
NK114(ye)001:4904: thams cad mkhyen pa'i lam bzang ma nor ba yin
NK114(ye)001:4905: gyi / de las gzhan du bdag med pa'i don
NK114(ye)001:4906: la nges pa ma rnyed par dge sbyor la brtson
NK114(ye)001:4907: pa rgya che yang de kho na la gcig tu
NK114(ye)001:4908: zhen cing 'thas pa ni srid pa'i rgyu las mi
NK114(ye)001:4909: gyi / 'da' ste / 'jam dpal rnam par 'phrul pa las /
NK114(ye)001:4910: lha'i bu gzhan yang byang chub kyi sems la mngon par zhen pa yang bdud kyi las so //
NK114(ye)001:4911: sbyin pa'i sems la mngon par zhen pa yang bdud
NK114(ye)001:4912: kyi las so zhes pa nas shes rab kyi sems
NK114(ye)001:4913: la mngon par zhen pa yang bdud kyi las so
NK114(ye)001:4914: zhes so // yang dbang po shin tu rnon po
NK114(ye)001:4915: la gsungs pa'i dgongs don phyin ci log tu bzung
NK114(ye)001:4916: nas thabs kyi cha rnams la skur pa 'debs pa
NK114(ye)001:4917: de dag la ni thar pa lta ci mngon mtho'i
NK114(ye)001:4918: rgyu tsam bsgrub pa'i skal pa'ang chad pas shin tu
NK114(ye)001:4919: zhes so // blun te / rnam par 'thag pa bsdus pa las /
NK114(ye)001:4920: de la mi blun po dag 'di skad du /
NK114(ye)001:4921: byang chub sems dpa' shes rab kyi pha rol tu
NK114(ye)001:4922: phyin pa kho na la bslab par bya'o zhes zer
NK114(ye)001:4923: zhing pha rol tu phyin pa lhag ma rnams sun
NK114(ye)001:4924: 'byin to // ma pham pa 'di ji ltar sems /
NK114(ye)001:4925: nga ka shi ka'i rgyal por gyur ba gang yin
NK114(ye)001:4926: pa des 'di ltar phug ron gyi phyir bdag gi
NK114(ye)001:4927: sha khra la byin pa de shes rab 'chal ba
NK114(ye)001:4928: yin nam / byams pas gsol ba /
NK114(ye)001:4929: bcom ldan 'das de ni ma lags so zhes pa la sogs pa ltar ro //
NK114(ye)001:4930: da lta yang gsang sngags dang rdzogs chen sogs la
NK114(ye)001:4931: kha g.yar nas dge sdig gis phan gnod med zer
NK114(ye)001:4932: te rang gi chos skal chad cing /
NK114(ye)001:4933: blun po gzhan dag mgo bskor ba shin tu mang bas gzab par bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:4934: des na sbyin sogs thabs kyi rnam pa thams cad
NK114(ye)001:4935: ma tshang na stong nyid yongs su rdzogs pa rtogs
NK114(ye)001:4937: gtsug na rin po che'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:4938: ri mo mkhan yan lag gi rnam pa gzhan dang
NK114(ye)001:4939: gzhan gang yang rung ba re 'bri shes pa drug
NK114(ye)001:4940: gis rgyal po'i gzugs bris pa'i tshe de las gcig
NK114(ye)001:4941: gzhan du song na des shes pa'i yan lag de
NK114(ye)001:4942: mi tshang bas rgyal po'i gzugs rdzogs par mi tshang
NK114(ye)001:4945: de rnams 'bri byed gang yin pa //
NK114(ye)001:4946: sbyin dang tshul khrims bzod la sogs //
NK114(ye)001:4947: rnam pa kun gyi mchog ldan pa'i //
NK114(ye)001:4948: stong pa nyid ni gzugs su brjod //
NK114(ye)001:4950: des na sangs rgyas kyi sa'i gzugs kyi sku la
NK114(ye)001:4951: sogs pa'i yon tan gyi rnam pa kun gyi mchog
NK114(ye)001:4952: dang ldan pa'i stong pa nyid chos kyi sku ni
NK114(ye)001:4953: thabs dang ldan pa'i stong nyid kyis 'grub kyi thabs
NK114(ye)001:4954: dang bral ba'i stong nyid kyis ni ma yin no
NK114(ye)001:4955: // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:4956: sgrub pa po'i blo stobs kyi dbye ba bshad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:4957: bsgrub bya pha rol tu phyin pa bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:4959: de ltar bslab par bya ba'i gnas ma nor bar
NK114(ye)001:4960: ngos bzung nas gang zag gi blo stobs kyi mthu
NK114(ye)001:4961: yis lam de sgrub par byed pa'i rgyal sras gsum
NK114(ye)001:4962: mthar thug gi 'bras bu la sbyor ba'i tshul bul
NK114(ye)001:4963: ba dang myur ba'i khyad par ni 'di ltar /
NK114(ye)001:4964: byang chub sems dpa' dbang po rtul po rnams thog
NK114(ye)001:4965: mar rang nyid 'tshang rgya ba'i don du tshogs gnyis
NK114(ye)001:4966: mthar phyin pa'i bya ba sngon du byas te /
NK114(ye)001:4967: mthar thug gi 'bras bu mngon du gyur nas rjes
NK114(ye)001:4968: la 'gro ba thams cad 'khor ba las sgrol bar
NK114(ye)001:4969: 'doda pa ni 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po rang
NK114(ye)001:4970: gis rgyal srid thob par byas nas phyis su mnga'
NK114(ye)001:4971: ris rnams bde ba la 'god pa'i thabs byed pa
NK114(ye)001:4972: bzhin te / de lta bu'i sems bskyed la 'dod
NK114(ye)001:4973: chen po'i sems bskyed ces bya ste 'phags pa byams
NK114(ye)001:4975: byang sems dbang po 'bring rnams rang dang 'gro ba
NK114(ye)001:4976: thams cad 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las snga phyi med
NK114(ye)001:4977: par stabs gcig tu sgrol ba'i thabs la brtson nas
NK114(ye)001:4978: 'bras bu sangs rgyas mnyam du thob par 'dod pa
NK114(ye)001:4979: ste gru pa rnams 'grul po dag dang lhan cig
NK114(ye)001:4980: grur zhugs nas chu'i pha rol tu mnyam du phyin
NK114(ye)001:4981: par byed pa lta bu ste de la ni ye
NK114(ye)001:4982: shes dam pa'i sems bskyed ces bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:4983: byang sems dbang po shin tu rnon po rnams byang
NK114(ye)001:4984: chub tu sems bskyed nas bslab bya la bslabs shing
NK114(ye)001:4985: nus pa rdzogs kyang 'gro ba rnams sngon la bsgral
NK114(ye)001:4986: ba'i don du 'tshang mi rgya bar byang chub sems
NK114(ye)001:4987: dpa' sa bcu pa'i ngang tshul du 'khor ba ma
NK114(ye)001:4988: stongs kyi bar gnas nas sems can gyi don mdzad
NK114(ye)001:4989: de 'khor ba na sems can gcig kyang med par
NK114(ye)001:4990: grol zin pa'i rjes la rang nyid sgrib pa thams
NK114(ye)001:4991: cad dang bral ba'i zhi ba mya ngan las 'das
NK114(ye)001:4992: pa'i go 'phang mngon du byed par 'dod pa ni
NK114(ye)001:4993: / phyugs skyong bar byed pa'i rdzi bo dag lam
NK114(ye)001:4994: 'phrad dam gcan gzan la sogs pas nyam nga ba'i
NK114(ye)001:4995: gnas mtha' dag las ba lang dang ra lug sogs
NK114(ye)001:4996: dbugs ma phyin pa de srid du bdag nyid bag
NK114(ye)001:4997: phebs par mi 'gyur ba lta bu'i dpe med pa'i
NK114(ye)001:4998: / sems bskyed de / 'jam dpal dbyangs dang spyan ras gzigs lta bu'o //
NK114(ye)001:4999: de rnams las dbang po rtul posa tshogs sbyor na bskal pa grangas med gsum /
NK114(ye)001:5000: sa bcu po re re la gsum gsum ste grangs
NK114(ye)001:5001: med sum cu rtsa gsum gyis lam mthar phyin te
NK114(ye)001:5003: dbang po 'bring pos tshogs sbyor la bzhi /
NK114(ye)001:5005: ma dag sa bdun la gcig /
NK114(ye)001:5006: dag sa gsum la gcig ste bdun gyis dang /
NK114(ye)001:5007: dbang po rnon posa ni tshogs sbyor la gcig /
NK114(ye)001:5008: ma dag sa bdun la gcig /
NK114(ye)001:5009: dag sa gsum la gcig ste gsum na grol ba
NK114(ye)001:5010: mthar thug pa bla na med pa'i byang chub tu
NK114(ye)001:5011: mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya bar 'gyur te /
NK114(ye)001:5012: tshul de dag ni mdo sde dkon mchog brtsegs pa las gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK114(ye)001:5013: de bas na blo'i nus pa ji tsam che ba
NK114(ye)001:5014: de tsam gyis grol myur ba yin pas snying stobs
NK114(ye)001:5015: kyi go cha bgo bar bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:5016: de la 'di snyam du las dang po pa rnams
NK114(ye)001:5017: bdag lta la goms shing nyon mongs pa ma spangs
NK114(ye)001:5018: bzhin yun ring po de tsam du gnas par 'dod
NK114(ye)001:5019: pa'i sems de lta bu skye daka'o zhes zhum par
NK114(ye)001:5020: mi bya ste / ci'i phyir na 'jig tshogs la
NK114(ye)001:5021: lta ba ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i gdung yin par
NK114(ye)001:5022: bshad pas de la brten nas byang chub kyi sems
NK114(ye)001:5023: mi bya ste / skye ba'i tshul / 'od srung gis zhus pas /
NK114(ye)001:5024: dper na lud bcas 'dam rdzab chu las ni //
NK114(ye)001:5025: pad+ma skye yi thang las nam yang min //
NK114(ye)001:5026: de bzhin nyon mongs lud ldan skye bo la //
NK114(ye)001:5027: rgyal sras rnams kyi rgyal ba'i chos skye'o //
NK114(ye)001:5029: thabs kyis zin pa'i bdag 'dzin dang nyon mongs pa
NK114(ye)001:5030: ni yon tan skye ba'i rgyu yin pa 'di theg
NK114(ye)001:5031: pa chen po'i khyad chos so //
NK114(ye)001:5032: sems stobs kyi khyad par 'dir bshad pa'i dgos pa'ang /
NK114(ye)001:5033: 'dul ba dang sngags kyi lam ni sngon la sdom
NK114(ye)001:5034: pa ma bzung na bslab bya mnyan du mi rung
NK114(ye)001:5035: la / byang chub sems dpa'i lam ni sngon du
NK114(ye)001:5036: bslab bya legs par shes nas dad cing sgrub nus
NK114(ye)001:5037: pa'i tshe bslab pa yang dag par blang ba byang
NK114(ye)001:5038: sa las bshad pa yin pas 'dir 'jug pa'i spyod
NK114(ye)001:5039: pa la blo stobs kyi khyad par gong nas gong
NK114(ye)001:5040: du 'phel ba'i bsgrub pa chen po dang ldan pa'i
NK114(ye)001:5042: des na da lta nas sems bskyed des bslab pa
NK114(ye)001:5043: bzung nas snying stobs drag pos le lo dang phyi
NK114(ye)001:5044: bshol med par lam la brtson pa gal che ste
NK114(ye)001:5046: mgo la sems can khur chen khyer ba yi //
NK114(ye)001:5047: sems dpa' mchog rnams dal gyis 'gro mi mdzes //
NK114(ye)001:5048: bdag gzhan sna tshogs 'ching bas rab bcings pas //
NK114(ye)001:5049: brtson pa brgya 'gyur du ni bya ba'i rigs //
NK114(ye)001:5051: de yang da lta dal ba'i rten bzang thob pa'i
NK114(ye)001:5052: dus 'dir rnyed bkur sogs 'jig rten gyi chos kyis
NK114(ye)001:5053: g.yeng na ji tsam longs spyod sogs phun sum tshogs
NK114(ye)001:5054: pa de tsam du nyon mongs pa dang sdig pa
NK114(ye)001:5055: 'phel ba'i rgyur 'gro bas sngar bsags kyi dge ba'i
NK114(ye)001:5056: 'bras bu ni shul ring gi mgron po'i lam rgyags
NK114(ye)001:5057: bzhin du spyad zin pas zad /
NK114(ye)001:5058: gsar du spel ba la ni mi brtson pas phyi
NK114(ye)001:5059: ma phan chad 'og nas 'og tu 'gro ba las
NK114(ye)001:5060: 'os med pa la skyo ba snying nas bskyed de
NK114(ye)001:5061: gzab par bya'o // gnyis pa bsgrub bya pha rol tu phyin pa bshad pa la drug ste /
NK114(ye)001:5067: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:5068: de yang byang chub sems dpa' rnams ni rang don
NK114(ye)001:5069: nyi tshe ba tsam zhig don du gnyer ba ma
NK114(ye)001:5070: yin par rang gzhan gnyis ka'i don mthar phyin par
NK114(ye)001:5071: byed dgos shing / de yang spyir byang chub sems
NK114(ye)001:5072: dpa' rnams kyis dngos brgyud gang yang rung bar gzhan
NK114(ye)001:5073: don ma gtogs rang gi don bsam par mi bya
NK114(ye)001:5074: byed dgos shing / ste / spyod 'jug las /
NK114(ye)001:5075: dngos sam yang na brgyud kyang rung //
NK114(ye)001:5076: sems can don las gzhan mi spyad //
NK114(ye)001:5078: de lta na'ang gnas skabs gtso che ba'i dbang du
NK114(ye)001:5079: byas na phar phyin snga ma gsum gzhan don dang
NK114(ye)001:5080: / phyi ma gsum gzhan gyi ched du rang nyid rnam par grol ba'i don te /
NK114(ye)001:5082: sems can don la rab brtson pa //
NK114(ye)001:5083: gtong dang mi gnod bzod pas byed //
NK114(ye)001:5084: gnas dang grol ba gzhir bcas pas //
NK114(ye)001:5085: rang don rnam pa thams cad spyod //
NK114(ye)001:5086: ces pa'i mi gnod pa ni tshul khrims /
NK114(ye)001:5089: gzhir bcas ni de gnyis brtson 'grus dang bcas pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:5090: de la dang po sbyin pa bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:5094: sbyin pa'i ngo bo bdog dgu'i dngos po thams cad
NK114(ye)001:5095: la chags pa med cing gzhan la gtong ba'i sems
NK114(ye)001:5097: bdog pa la chags pa'i gnyen po byed pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:5099: dam pa'i chos kyi sbyin pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5100: zang zing longs spyod kyi sbyin pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5101: mi 'jigsa pa skyabs kyi sbyin pa dang gsum mo //
NK114(ye)001:5102: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK114(ye)001:5104: mi 'jigs pa'i sbyin pa zhar byung dang bcas pa /
NK114(ye)001:5105: chos kyi sbyin pa bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:5110: zang zing gi sbyin pa la'ang sbyin pa po byang
NK114(ye)001:5111: chub sems dpa'i blo nus pa dang bstun par rnam
NK114(ye)001:5112: pa gsum du mdo sde las gsungs pa yin te
NK114(ye)001:5113: / blo nus stobs chung ba'i dus su gtong ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:5114: de la goms nas gtong ba chen po dang /
NK114(ye)001:5115: gtong sems goms pa phul du byung ba na shin tu gtong ba la bslab nus te /
NK114(ye)001:5116: des na gtong ba chen po'i dus su snga ma
NK114(ye)001:5117: gtong ba yang nus la phyi ma'i tshe snga ma
NK114(ye)001:5118: gnyis ka'ang nus pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:5119: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:5120: de la gtong ba zhes bya ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:5121: las dang po pas rang la bdog pa'i longs spyod
NK114(ye)001:5122: rgya che chung ci 'dra ba yin kyang de la
NK114(ye)001:5123: chags zhen spangs te gtong sems la goms par byed
NK114(ye)001:5124: cing dngos su'ang ci nus su gtong bar byed pa
NK114(ye)001:5125: ste / de yang longs spyod la chags zhen spong
NK114(ye)001:5126: nus na dngos su gtong rgyu med kyang sbyin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:5127: mchog yin te sbyin pa'i ngo bo longs spyod la
NK114(ye)001:5128: chags pa med pa'i sems yin pa'i phyir te /
NK114(ye)001:5129: sngon khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin la 'gran zla
NK114(ye)001:5130: byed pa'i khyim bdag gcig gis de'i do zlar ma
NK114(ye)001:5131: spobs nas / zang zing yod dgu spangs te rab
NK114(ye)001:5132: tu byung bas mgon med zas sbyin las lhag par
NK114(ye)001:5134: khyim pa la sogs pa'i longs spyod yod pa rnams
NK114(ye)001:5135: kyis ni thog mar kha zas dang btung ba cung
NK114(ye)001:5136: zad sbyin pa nas blo'i mthu je cher bskyed de
NK114(ye)001:5141: glang po la sogs pa'i bzhon pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5142: rgyal po lta bu zhig yin na yul khams rang la dbang ba thams cad dang /
NK114(ye)001:5143: de min pa zhig yin kyang rang la dbang ba'i
NK114(ye)001:5144: nor gyi dngos po yod dgu thams cad gzhan la
NK114(ye)001:5145: sbyin pa la gtong ba zhes bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:5146: de'i tshul yang sngon shi bi'i rgyal pos gtan pa
NK114(ye)001:5147: med pa'i mchod sbyin gyi khang bu brtsigs nas dkor
NK114(ye)001:5148: mdzod thams cad btang ba la sogs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5149: longs spyod rang la med kyang sngon dbul por gyur
NK114(ye)001:5150: ba zhig gis r+ts+wa bregs nas btsongs pa'i rin gyis
NK114(ye)001:5151: sbyin pa btang ba la sogs pa lta bu'o //
NK114(ye)001:5152: gtong ba'i yul yang dbang po dman pa 'bras bu la re ba dag gis /
NK114(ye)001:5155: 'phags pa min yang pha ma dang //
NK114(ye)001:5156: nad pa dang ni chos smra dang //
NK114(ye)001:5157: skye matha'i byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK114(ye)001:5158: yon ni gzhal du med par gsungs //
NK114(ye)001:5159: zhes pa lta bu'i yon gnas 'dam pa yin gyi /
NK114(ye)001:5160: byang sems rnams ni 'bras bu la re ba'i phyir ma yin gyi gtong sems goms pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5161: gzhan la phan gdags pa'i phyir sbyin pa gtong ba
NK114(ye)001:5162: yin pas yul la mchog dman gyi khyad par med
NK114(ye)001:5163: de / khyad par dman pa'i zhing la snying rjes gtong ba theg pa chen po'i lugs yin no //
NK114(ye)001:5164: der ma zad yul la mchog dman du bltas na
NK114(ye)001:5165: chos mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pa'i gegs kyang yin
NK114(ye)001:5166: par gsungs so // des na spyin pa'i dngos po
NK114(ye)001:5167: chung yang lan dang rnam smin la re ba med
NK114(ye)001:5168: na bsod nams rgya che zhing /
NK114(ye)001:5169: dngos po rgya che yang 'dod pa lnga'i kun slong
NK114(ye)001:5170: dang 'brel na 'bras bu ma nges par 'byin te
NK114(ye)001:5171: / sa snying 'khor lo bcu pa las /
NK114(ye)001:5172: sems can kun la phan bde'i phyir gyi //
NK114(ye)001:5173: rnam smin 'bras bu re phyir ma yin //
NK114(ye)001:5174: sbyin pa dngos po byin pa chung yang //
NK114(ye)001:5175: yang dag bsod nams zhing du de 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:5176: sbyin pa dngos po mang du byas kyang //
NK114(ye)001:5177: 'dod pa rnam lnga dag la gnas nas //
NK114(ye)001:5178: 'phags pa dag gis phyag rgyas ma btab //
NK114(ye)001:5179: ma nges pa yi tshogs la gnas 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:5181: gtong ba chen po zhes bya ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:5182: nor gyi dngos po de lta bu las kyang rab tu phangs pa'i bu dang /
NK114(ye)001:5184: khyim thab dang bcas pa thams cad gtong ba yin te /
NK114(ye)001:5185: rgyal bu thams cad sgrol bzhin no //
NK114(ye)001:5186: des na da lta yang de lta'i snying stobs dang dam bca' brtan pa la bsam ste /
NK114(ye)001:5187: bdag gis ni gnas skabs pa'i gnyen grogs rnams la
NK114(ye)001:5188: rtag tu 'grogs par 'dod pa'i blos zhen cing chags
NK114(ye)001:5189: te de dag gi phyir snying las dang chags sdang
NK114(ye)001:5191: thams cad 'bral ba'i chos can yin pas kun la zhen chags spang bar bya dgos /
NK114(ye)001:5192: nam zhig na byang chub sems dpa' chen po rnams
NK114(ye)001:5193: bzhin du dngos su gzhan la gtong nus pa de
NK114(ye)001:5194: lta bu la bslab par bya snyam du dam bca'
NK114(ye)001:5195: bar bya ste / phar phyin bsdus pa las /
NK114(ye)001:5196: thub pa rnams kyi spyod mchog dran byas shing //
NK114(ye)001:5197: de gzhol rang gi dam bcas bsam bya ste //
NK114(ye)001:5198: yongs 'dzin chags pa rnam par bsal ba'i phyir //
NK114(ye)001:5199: sems la rtog pa'i dam pa 'di dag rtogs //
NK114(ye)001:5201: de la shin tu gtong ba zhes bya ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:5202: gtong sems ma goms pa rnams kyis dngos su lta
NK114(ye)001:5203: ci de 'dra mthong zhing thos pa tsam la'ang 'jigs
NK114(ye)001:5204: pa skye bas bya dka' ba'i gnas te /
NK114(ye)001:5209: yan lag la sogs pa rang gi lus thams cad
NK114(ye)001:5210: dam bye brag gi bar ci 'dod 'dod du phangs
NK114(ye)001:5211: pa med par phan 'dod kyi lhag bsam rnam par
NK114(ye)001:5213: rgyal po zla 'od la sogs pa ltar ro //
NK114(ye)001:5214: gzhan yang bdag cag gi ston pa sa spyod nam
NK114(ye)001:5215: mkhar gyur pa'i tshe gtong ba gsum po nyams bzhes
NK114(ye)001:5216: su mdzad pa la sogs pa byang chub sems dpa'
NK114(ye)001:5217: rnams gtong sems goms pa mthar phyin pa na sbyin
NK114(ye)001:5218: par mi bya ba'i dngos po de ni gang yang
NK114(ye)001:5220: ba tsh+wa chu klung gi mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:5221: chung ma rnams dang rgyal srid dbang phyug chen po dang //
NK114(ye)001:5222: sha rnams dang ni khrag dang tshil dang lus dang mig /
NK114(ye)001:5223: pha rol dga' ba'i dbang du byas nas ngas ni btang ba yin //
NK114(ye)001:5224: gang gi sems can rnams la phan na nga la mchod mchog yin //
NK114(ye)001:5225: sems can rnams la gnod pa byas na nga la gnod pa byas //
NK114(ye)001:5227: de bas na 'di ltar bdag gi lus ni mi gtsang ba ngan skyugs kyi phung po lta bu /
NK114(ye)001:5228: srog gi 'thor rlung drag po bzhin du g.yo ba
NK114(ye)001:5229: de gnyis ka'ang las kyi phyi bzhin 'brang bas gzhan
NK114(ye)001:5230: dbang can yin te rang gis rnam pa thams cad
NK114(ye)001:5231: du sgo du ma nas bsrungs kyang me chu g.yang
NK114(ye)001:5232: sa rgyal po gcan gzan chom rkun la sogs pas
NK114(ye)001:5233: brlag par byed pas rang dbang can ma yin la
NK114(ye)001:5234: / de ltar ma gyur kyang shi ba'i tshe na ni mer bsreg gam /
NK114(ye)001:5236: gtor te bya rgod sogs la byin nam /
NK114(ye)001:5237: sa'i 'og tu bcug pa la sogs ji ltar byas
NK114(ye)001:5238: kyang mthar rdul phran tsam yang lus par mi 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:5239: na / da lta 'di ltar gces shing phangs par bltas nas shin tu bsrung ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:5240: lus 'di'i don du gzhan la gnod pa'i bsam sbyor
NK114(ye)001:5241: sna tshogs pa byed pa 'di ni sangs rgyas thugs
NK114(ye)001:5242: rje can de'i rjes su slob pa dag gi tshul
NK114(ye)001:5243: ma yin pas shin tu nongs so snyam du bsams
NK114(ye)001:5244: nas yang yang lus la chags sems spangs te bdag
NK114(ye)001:5245: gi lus 'di sems can thams cad la byin zin
NK114(ye)001:5246: pa yin pas lus 'dis sems can la dngos brgyud
NK114(ye)001:5247: gang du'ang mi gnod par bya dgos par ma zad
NK114(ye)001:5248: dngos su phan ci thogs dang brgyud nas kyang chos
NK114(ye)001:5249: kyi phyogs la brtson pa thams cad sems can gyi
NK114(ye)001:5250: don du dmigs pa ma gtogs rang don du bsgrub
NK114(ye)001:5251: par byed pa ni shin tu mi rigs so //
NK114(ye)001:5252: da lta dngos su gtong mi nus kyang mthar gyis
NK114(ye)001:5253: goms par byas te byang chub sems dpa' chen po
NK114(ye)001:5254: rnams bzhin du dngos su lus ci 'dod du sbyin
NK114(ye)001:5255: pa la'ang bslab par bya dgos snyam du bsam pa'i
NK114(ye)001:5256: sgo nas btang ba la yang yang blo ma sbyangs
NK114(ye)001:5257: na mos pa smin pa dang da gdod lus srog
NK114(ye)001:5258: ster nus pa'i skabs mi 'ong bar bslab btus las
NK114(ye)001:5259: gsungs pas da lta blo sbyong ba 'di gal che'o
NK114(ye)001:5260: // de yang byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa spyi
NK114(ye)001:5261: dang khyad par sbyin pa la bslab pa'i skabs 'di
NK114(ye)001:5262: ni thog mar gtong sems la gomsa su 'jug pa'i
NK114(ye)001:5263: las dang po pa rnams ser sna'i 'ching ba dam
NK114(ye)001:5264: pos bsdams nas kha zas tsam yang gzhan la ster
NK114(ye)001:5265: mi nus pa'i skyes bu'i ni /
NK114(ye)001:5266: sngon khyim bdag 'jur bgegs can zhig la rang gi
NK114(ye)001:5267: lag pa ni gcig gis dngos po ngan ngon cung
NK114(ye)001:5268: zad bzung nas cig shos la sbyin par bsam pa'i
NK114(ye)001:5269: sems kyis yang yang sposa te sbyin pa'i tshul la
NK114(ye)001:5270: bslab tu bcug pas mthar sbyin pa rgya chen po
NK114(ye)001:5271: gtong nus par byung ba bzhin du rang cag kyang
NK114(ye)001:5272: tshod ma la sogas pa dngos po phra mo tsam
NK114(ye)001:5273: gtong ba la goms par byas te rim gyis longs
NK114(ye)001:5274: spyod la brkam zhing chagsa pa'i sems 'jig par byed
NK114(ye)001:5275: cing gtong ba'i sems gong nas gong du stobs su
NK114(ye)001:5276: gyur te shin tu gtong ba'i bar la bslaba par
NK114(ye)001:5278: tshod ma la sogs sbyin pa la'ang //
NK114(ye)001:5279: 'dren pas thog mar sbyor bar mdzad //
NK114(ye)001:5280: de la goms nas phyi nas ni //
NK114(ye)001:5281: rim gyis rang gi sha yang gtong //
NK114(ye)001:5283: de bas na byang chub sems dpa' slob pa lam
NK114(ye)001:5284: gyi gnas skabs na sbyin pa'i bkad sa'i yang steng
NK114(ye)001:5285: la 'dzegs nas slong ba po rgyang ring po nas
NK114(ye)001:5286: mthong ba'ang mig gis bsu zhing dga' ba bsgom pa
NK114(ye)001:5287: ltar sbyin gnas la 'di ni bdag gi sbyin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:5288: pha rol tu phyin pa rdzogs par byed pa'i dge
NK114(ye)001:5289: ba'i bshes gnyen no snyam du bltas la /
NK114(ye)001:5290: dngos po 'di dang bdag ni gdon mi za bar 'bral te /
NK114(ye)001:5291: 'dis kyang bdag 'dor bdag gis kyang 'di 'dor bas
NK114(ye)001:5292: da lta btang na phyi ma'i dus 'gyod pas mi
NK114(ye)001:5293: gdung zhing chags zhen med pas yid dga' bar 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:5294: ro snyam du ci nus su byin te ser sna'i
NK114(ye)001:5295: mdud pa grol ba la 'bad par bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:5296: gnyis pa mi 'jigs pa'i sbyin pa zhar byung dang bcas pa bshad pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:5297: de la mi 'jigs pa skyabs kyi sbyin pa la bslab pa'i tshul ni /
NK114(ye)001:5298: 'di ltar sems can gzhan rgyal po'i khri mun du chud pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5300: ri dwags rngon pas bdas pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:5301: phyugs lug bsha' sar khrid pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5302: nad dang gdon gyis gtses pa sogs kun gyi lus
NK114(ye)001:5303: srog la ma rungs par gyur pa'i gnod pa mtha'
NK114(ye)001:5304: dag las skyob pa'i thabs la ci nus su brtson
NK114(ye)001:5306: bdag gis nam zhig sems can 'di thams cad gnas skabs kyi 'jigs pa thams cad dang /
NK114(ye)001:5307: mthar thug 'jigs pa'i yul chen po 'khor ba'i sdug
NK114(ye)001:5308: bsngal mtha' yas pa las bsgral te dbugs 'byin chen
NK114(ye)001:5309: po mya ngan las 'das pa'i gnas la dgod par
NK114(ye)001:5310: bya snyam du blo sbyang bar bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:5311: de ltar gtong ba gsum po las /
NK114(ye)001:5312: phyi ma gnyis mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob pa'i spyod yul te /
NK114(ye)001:5313: 'phags pa nye bar 'khor gyis zhus pa las /
NK114(ye)001:5314: mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa la gnas pa nyid kyis /
NK114(ye)001:5317: shin tu gtong ba dag kyang bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:5319: des na las dang po pa rnams kyis rang gi
NK114(ye)001:5320: nus tshod tsam zhig sbyin par bya zhing gtso bo
NK114(ye)001:5321: gzhan don du rang gi ser sna sogs nyon mongs
NK114(ye)001:5322: pa'i rtog pa 'dul ba la bslab par bya yi
NK114(ye)001:5323: / mi nus bzhin du ma brtags par ba ba
NK114(ye)001:5324: col gyi cho ga ste bya ba yi rnam par
NK114(ye)001:5325: sbyar ba'i longs spyod chen po btang nas rang nyid
NK114(ye)001:5326: dbul ba na 'gyod pa skye ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:5327: bu dang chung ma sogs dang lus dngos su btang
NK114(ye)001:5328: na phyi nas 'phangs sems skye zhing sdug bsngal mi
NK114(ye)001:5329: bzod pa dang gzhan ma mgu na nyan rang gi
NK114(ye)001:5330: sar sems bskyed pa'i nyen sogs yod pas de 'dra
NK114(ye)001:5331: ba'i sbyin pa'ang byang sems lam gyi gegs smad pa'i
NK114(ye)001:5332: gnas yin pas rang nyams dang sbyar bar bya ste
NK114(ye)001:5333: / so skye'i dus su dngos zhen dang bcas pa'i
NK114(ye)001:5334: snying rje cung zad yod kyang lhag pa'i bsam pa
NK114(ye)001:5335: de shin tu ma dag pas 'phags pa'i sa ma
NK114(ye)001:5336: thob par lus dang srog dngos su gtong ba bslab
NK114(ye)001:5337: btus nyid las bkag pa yin te /
NK114(ye)001:5339: dper na sman shing ljon pa bltar sdug pa'i //
NK114(ye)001:5340: rtsa ba la sogs spyad 'os sa bon ni //
NK114(ye)001:5341: 'byin yang dus min spyod las bsrung bar bya //
NK114(ye)001:5342: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sman shing de bzhin no //
NK114(ye)001:5344: de bzhin du bsam pa gnod sems dang phrag dog dang ngom chos sogs ma dag pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5345: sbyor ba sems can gzhan la gnod pa byas nas gtong ba sogs ma dag pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:5346: dngos po dug dang mtshon cha ster ba sogs ma dag pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5347: yul yang spyir mi 'dam mod dmigs bsal du bag med pa la chang dang /
NK114(ye)001:5349: rang dga' ba'i gnyen sogs la zhen pas gtong ba
NK114(ye)001:5350: sogs kha na ma tho bas sbyar zhing bskrun pa'i
NK114(ye)001:5351: sbyin pa de lta bu yang rang gzhan kun la
NK114(ye)001:5352: 'phral dang yun du phan par 'gyur ba'i thabs ma
NK114(ye)001:5353: yin pas byang chub sems dpas spyad par bya ba'i
NK114(ye)001:5354: gnas min par ma zad smad par bya ba'i gnas
NK114(ye)001:5355: yin te / drang srong chen po rgyas pas zhus pa las /
NK114(ye)001:5356: nor gang gi yin pa de ni sbyin bdag ma yin no //
NK114(ye)001:5357: byed du bcug pas sbyin pa ni gtong ba po yin gyi /
NK114(ye)001:5359: dug dang mtshon cha dang srog chags bsad de sbyin
NK114(ye)001:5360: pa dang bag med pa la chang sbyin pa ni
NK114(ye)001:5361: ma dag pa'o // rnam par smin pa la the tshom za ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:5362: byin nas 'gyod pas gdung pa yang ma dag pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:5363: bsod nams kyi rnam par smin pa bdag nyid kyis
NK114(ye)001:5364: spyad kyi gzhan la ma gyur cig snyam na ma
NK114(ye)001:5365: dag pa'o // na ba dang 'chi ba'i dus sangs
NK114(ye)001:5366: rgyas la dga' ba dang dad pa med par rtsa
NK114(ye)001:5367: lag gis byed du bcug nas byin na ma dag
NK114(ye)001:5368: dag pa'o // pa'o // dbul phongs bor nas phyug po la ster na ma dag pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:5369: drang srong chen po de dag gi rnam par smin
NK114(ye)001:5370: pa ni tsh+wa sgo can gyi zhing la sa bon
NK114(ye)001:5371: btab pa ltar smin pa med pa ma yin mod
NK114(ye)001:5373: drang srong chen po ma rmos ma bsal ba'i zhing
NK114(ye)001:5374: la sa bon btab nas char babs na skye srid
NK114(ye)001:5375: kyi me tog dang 'bras bur mi 'gyur ba dang
NK114(ye)001:5376: 'dra'o // zhes bka' stsal pa ltar ro //
NK114(ye)001:5377: des na sems kyi cha nas rang la bdoga pa'i
NK114(ye)001:5378: lus dang longs spyod dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad
NK114(ye)001:5379: la 'jungs pa dang ser snar blta ba'i zhen pa
NK114(ye)001:5380: btang ba ni sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:5383: bdog pa thams cad 'bras bcas te //
NK114(ye)001:5384: skye bo kun la btang sems kyis //
NK114(ye)001:5385: sbyin pa'i pha rol phyin gsungs te //
NK114(ye)001:5386: de ltas de ni sems nyid do //
NK114(ye)001:5388: des na dngos su bsam sbyor dag pas ci nus su gtong zhing /
NK114(ye)001:5389: rtag tu gtong sems goms par byed pa ni gal che'o //
NK114(ye)001:5390: blo'i nus pa de skye ba 'adi'am /
NK114(ye)001:5391: tshe rabs gzhan du mngon du 'gyur ba la dgongs nas /
NK114(ye)001:5392: bslab btus su snying nas sems can la btang ba'i
NK114(ye)001:5393: zas gos dang gnas khang la 'di ni gzhan gyis
NK114(ye)001:5394: yin te de dag la'ang phan pa'i phyir spyad par
NK114(ye)001:5395: bya'o snyam pa'i bsam pa brjed nas rang don du
NK114(ye)001:5396: sred pas longs spyod na nyon mongs pa can gyi
NK114(ye)001:5397: ltung ba dang / sred pa med kyang 'du shes
NK114(ye)001:5398: des ma zin par longs spyod na nyon mongs can
NK114(ye)001:5399: ma yin pa'i ltung ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:5400: gzhan la bsngosa pa gzhan gyi rdzas su 'du shes
NK114(ye)001:5401: kyang rang gi phyir spyod na ma byin len du
NK114(ye)001:5402: 'gyur zhing rin thang tshang na so thar gyi sdom
NK114(ye)001:5403: ldan la pham par 'gyur ba nyid du gsungs pa
NK114(ye)001:5405: bden pa gzigs pa rnams kyi tshig ni dgos pa
NK114(ye)001:5406: chen po dang ldan pa yin pas 'dul ba rang
NK114(ye)001:5407: gzhung nas bstan pa'i tshig gis klan ka brjod pa
NK114(ye)001:5408: dang / the tshom du bya bar mi rigs la /
NK114(ye)001:5409: dngos su rang gis bzung nas blos gzhan la ster
NK114(ye)001:5410: ba la dgos pa med do snyam du bsam par
NK114(ye)001:5411: yang mi bya'o // de ltar zang zing dang mi
NK114(ye)001:5412: 'jigs pa'i sbyin pa gnyis ni chos kyi sbyin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:5413: sngon du 'gro ba can yin te /
NK114(ye)001:5414: slob dpon ye shes snying pos /
NK114(ye)001:5415: de la chos kyi sbyin pa yang sems can ma bsdus pa rnams la sbyin par mi nus kyi /
NK114(ye)001:5416: sbyin pa rnam pa gsum gyi nang nas zang zing
NK114(ye)001:5417: dang mi 'jigs pa gnyis ni bsdu ba'i thabs su
NK114(ye)001:5419: chos kyi sbyin pa ni thabs des bsgrub pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:5421: gsum pa chos kyi sbyin pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:5422: de la chos kyi sbyin pa yang /
NK114(ye)001:5423: chos kyi cha rkyen snag smyug yi ge sogs sbyin pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5424: theg gsum gyi chos ston pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5425: bla na med cing bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i don
NK114(ye)001:5426: la sbyor bar byed pa ste rnam pa gsum gsungs
NK114(ye)001:5427: te / 'phags pa 'jig rten 'dzin gyis dris pa las /
NK114(ye)001:5428: de la chos kyi sbyin pa gang zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:5431: glegs bam sbyin pa ni chung ngu'o //
NK114(ye)001:5432: skal ba ji lta ba bzhin du nyan thos dang /
NK114(ye)001:5434: bla na med pa'i chos ston pa ni chen po'o //
NK114(ye)001:5435: bla na med pa'i byang chub 'dzin du 'jug cing
NK114(ye)001:5436: nam mkha' ltar bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos ston
NK114(ye)001:5437: pa ni shin tu chen po'o //
NK114(ye)001:5439: de dag las chos kyi sbyin pa dngos ni gzhan
NK114(ye)001:5440: la blo rim bzhin gdams ngag 'doms par byed pa
NK114(ye)001:5441: yin pas mos pasa spyod par rnams rang rgyud la
NK114(ye)001:5442: chos kyi tshig dang don gnyis ka'i cha nas nus
NK114(ye)001:5443: pa gsal ba med pas gzhan gyi skal ba ji
NK114(ye)001:5444: bzhin par 'doms par dka' zhes pa'am /
NK114(ye)001:5445: yang na gzhan gyi blo dang 'tshams pa'i chos ston
NK114(ye)001:5446: par sems kyis bsam te mos pas sbyod pa las
NK114(ye)001:5447: ji bzhin pa 'doms par dka' ste /
NK114(ye)001:5448: long ba gcig shos kyis cig shos la ngang pa'i
NK114(ye)001:5449: gshog pa'i sgra las gzhig ste kha dog kyang 'ur
NK114(ye)001:5450: 'ur por 'chad pa bzhin don ji lta ba bzhin
NK114(ye)001:5452: byin rlabs snod stong byo ba dang 'dra ste rang rgyud na med pas gzhan la sbyin du med /
NK114(ye)001:5453: gal te cung zad rang rgyud na yod kyang bum
NK114(ye)001:5454: pa gang byos dang 'dra ste gzhan rgyud gang tsa
NK114(ye)001:5456: gdams ngag mar me lag brgyud dang 'dra ste /
NK114(ye)001:5457: gzhan gsal tsa na rang 'grib pa'i phyir las dang
NK114(ye)001:5458: po pas chos smra ba dgongs pa bcu bstan pa
NK114(ye)001:5460: 'on kyang da lta bstan pa nub tu nye zhing
NK114(ye)001:5461: 'chad pa dang nyan pa'i gzugs brnyan tsam yang dkon
NK114(ye)001:5462: pa'i dus 'dir bstan 'gro la lhag bsam gyis zang
NK114(ye)001:5463: zing la mi blta bar bshad pa byed pa re
NK114(ye)001:5464: yod srid na phan yon kyang tshad las 'das so
NK114(ye)001:5465: // gang ltar yang gtso bo gzhan phan gyi bsam
NK114(ye)001:5466: pa yid la bcags te dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi
NK114(ye)001:5467: gdams ngag gis rang gi rgyud kyi nyon mongs pa
NK114(ye)001:5468: thams cad bsal ba'i cho ga ste thabs la dran
NK114(ye)001:5469: pa dang shes bzhin gyis 'bad pa lhur len cing
NK114(ye)001:5470: // / sems can rnams la byamsa pa dang snying
NK114(ye)001:5471: rjesa blta zhing de bzhin gshegs pa'i bka' zab mo
NK114(ye)001:5473: mthong ba tsam la'ang phan yon bsam gyis mi khyab
NK114(ye)001:5474: pa yod par yid ches shing mos pa dang bcas
NK114(ye)001:5475: pas gsung rab spyi dang khyad par theg pa chen
NK114(ye)001:5476: po'i mdo sde rnams bklagsa pa yis /
NK114(ye)001:5477: tshe rabs mang po'i sdig sgrib thams cad 'dag pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5478: gzhan phan gyi bsam pa ngang gis 'byung ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:5479: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi rnam
NK114(ye)001:5480: par 'phrul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa la thun
NK114(ye)001:5481: mong ma yin pa'i yid ches thob pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5482: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa rgya mtsho lta bu
NK114(ye)001:5483: la mos pa lhag par 'phel ba sogs yon tan
NK114(ye)001:5484: tshad las 'das pa yod pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5485: slob dpon dbyig gnyen gyis mdo sde zhal 'don mdzad
NK114(ye)001:5486: pa gdung phrag gi phug ron gyis thos pas las
NK114(ye)001:5487: srabs te tshe 'phos nas slob dpon blo gros brtan
NK114(ye)001:5488: par gyur pa bzhin gzhan la yang phan thogs che
NK114(ye)001:5489: bas thos bsam bsgom pa'i bya ba rgya chen po
NK114(ye)001:5491: 'jig rten gyi chos kyis g.yeng nas mi tshe gang
NK114(ye)001:5492: po stong zad du mi gtong bar theg pa chen
NK114(ye)001:5493: po'i mdo sde zab mo klog pa 'di lta bu'i
NK114(ye)001:5494: tshul rtag tu brtson nas chos kyi sgra des 'jig
NK114(ye)001:5495: rten gyi khams thams cad khyab ste sems can thams
NK114(ye)001:5496: cad kyi las dang nyon mongs pa thams cad dag
NK114(ye)001:5498: dkar po'i phyogs kyi lha dang klu la sogs pa
NK114(ye)001:5499: dngos su mnyan pa la 'ong ba yin pas de
NK114(ye)001:5500: dag gi rgyud kyang las dang nyon mongs pa las
NK114(ye)001:5501: grol nas rgyal ba'i bstan pa bsrung ba la lhag
NK114(ye)001:5503: mdor na rang gzhan sems can thams cad theg pa
NK114(ye)001:5504: chen po'i chos kyi snod du gyur nas bla na
NK114(ye)001:5505: med pa'i byang chub chen po'i go 'phang la gzhol
NK114(ye)001:5506: ba'i smon lam rnam par dag pa 'dun pa shugs
NK114(ye)001:5507: drag pos gdab par bya ba 'di ni shin tu
NK114(ye)001:5508: gal che'o // thub pa'i rjes 'jug ngur smrig 'dzin pa rnams //
NK114(ye)001:5509: ma nog chung nor gyi phyir du mi brel bar //
NK114(ye)001:5510: rgyal ba'i rgyal tshab gsung rab rin po che'i //
NK114(ye)001:5511: mig gi dga' ston rol la dgyes par mdzod //
NK114(ye)001:5512: ces pa ni rang dang 'dra ba'i las dang po ba rnams la gsung rab blta bar bskul ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:5513: rang gi rgyud grol nas 'du 'dzi dang rnam par
NK114(ye)001:5514: g.yeng ba la sogs pa'i yul gyi rkyen gyis mi
NK114(ye)001:5515: gnod par gyur pa na 'gro ba so so'i khams
NK114(ye)001:5516: dbang mos pa'i skal ba dang rang bzhin 'tshams par
NK114(ye)001:5517: dbang po shin tu rtul po rnams la las 'bras
NK114(ye)001:5518: kyi chos dang / 'bring rnams la bden bzhi dang rten 'brel /
NK114(ye)001:5519: rnon po rnams la phyin drug dang stong nyid /
NK114(ye)001:5520: shin tu rnon po rnams la gsang sngags phyi nang gi chos thun mong ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:5521: ches shin tu rnon po rnams la thun mong ma
NK114(ye)001:5522: yin pa rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i chos rnams
NK114(ye)001:5523: pha rol tu phyin pa drug dang ldan pa'i sgo
NK114(ye)001:5524: nas bstan pas / dper na sman pa mkhas pas
NK114(ye)001:5525: nad kyi bye brag mi 'dra ba mang po la
NK114(ye)001:5526: de dang de sel byed kyi sman btang nas nad
NK114(ye)001:5527: de dag gso ba ltar gdul bya la phan pa
NK114(ye)001:5529: gdams ngag mar me gzhi 'dzin dang 'dra bas rang
NK114(ye)001:5530: gi rtogs pa'i yon tan la yang gnod par mi
NK114(ye)001:5531: 'gyur bas de'i dus su ni gzhan don nyag gcig
NK114(ye)001:5532: gtso bor bya ba yin no //
NK114(ye)001:5533: de'ang byang sems khyim pas zang zing dang mi 'jigs pa'i sbyin pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5534: rab byung gis chos kyi sbyin pa bya bar gsungs shing /
NK114(ye)001:5535: de nyid snga ma las phan yon kyang che bar gsungs te /
NK114(ye)001:5536: byang chub sems dpa'i so so brang ba las /
NK114(ye)001:5537: sh+aa ri'i bu byang chub sems dpa' khyim pa gang
NK114(ye)001:5538: gis sangs rgyas kyi zhing gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma
NK114(ye)001:5539: snyed dag rin po che sna bdun gyis yongs su
NK114(ye)001:5540: bkang ste / de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa
NK114(ye)001:5541: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams la dbul
NK114(ye)001:5543: sh+aa ri'i bu rab tu byung bar gyur pa'i byang
NK114(ye)001:5544: chub sems dpa' gang gis tshig bzhi pa'i tshigs su
NK114(ye)001:5545: bcad pa gcig bstan na 'di ni de bas ches
NK114(ye)001:5546: bsod nams mang du bskyed de sh+aa ri'i bu de
NK114(ye)001:5547: bzhin gshegs pas ni rab tu byung bas zang zing
NK114(ye)001:5548: gi sbyin pa bya bar ma gnang ngo //
NK114(ye)001:5550: de yang yo byad btsal ba sogs kyis tshul khrims
NK114(ye)001:5551: la gnod par 'gyur ba'i rigs la dgongs kyi sngon
NK114(ye)001:5552: gyi sbyin 'bras kyi mthus rang bzhin du rnyed pa
NK114(ye)001:5553: la gtong ba bkag pa ma yin te /
NK114(ye)001:5554: mgon po klu sgrub kyis dge 'dun mang po la
NK114(ye)001:5555: 'tsho ba sbyar bas sogs sngon dang da ltar gyi
NK114(ye)001:5556: skyes bu dam pa 'ga' zhig gi mdzad pa bzhin
NK114(ye)001:5557: no // de ltar sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin
NK114(ye)001:5558: pa de thams cad kyang dam pa drug ldan du
NK114(ye)001:5559: bya bar phar phyin bsdus pa las gsungs pa'i don
NK114(ye)001:5560: no // ni / kun slong byang chub kyi sems la brten pa ni rten dam pa 1dang /
NK114(ye)001:5561: sbyin pa spyi dang bye brag gi khyad par gang
NK114(ye)001:5562: la 'jug kyang de'i bsam pa ma dor ba ni
NK114(ye)001:5564: sems can thams cad la 'phral du bde ba dang
NK114(ye)001:5565: yun du phan pa'i phyir gtong ba ni ched du
NK114(ye)001:5567: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyis zin pa ni thabs la mkhas pa dam 4pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5568: btang ba'i dge ba rdzogs byang du bsngo ba'i bsngo ba dam 5pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5569: sgrib gnyis kyi gnyen por gyur bas rnam dag dam 6pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:5570: phar phyin lhag ma rnams kyang de dag dang ldan dgos par gsungs so //
NK114(ye)001:5571: gzhan yang sbyin sogs phar phyin drug po chags bdun dang bral bar bsgrub pa'i tshul yang gsungs te /
NK114(ye)001:5572: longs spyod nas lta ba ngan pa'i bar 1dang /
NK114(ye)001:5576: rnam par smin pa la re ba 5dang /
NK114(ye)001:5577: ser sna nas shes rab 'chal ba'i bar mi mthun pa'i phyogs bag la nyal 6dang /
NK114(ye)001:5578: theg dman yid byed dang 'khor gsum du rtog pa'i rnam g.yeng rnams la ma chags pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:5580: byang chub sems dpa'i sbyin pa ni //
NK114(ye)001:5581: ma chags mi chags chags pa med //
NK114(ye)001:5582: chags pa nyid kyang ma yin te //
NK114(ye)001:5583: ma chags mi chags chags pa med //
NK114(ye)001:5584: ces pa nas shes rab kyi bar du gsungs so //
NK114(ye)001:5585: de ltar nyams su len pa'i tshe na rang la gtong phod dang /
NK114(ye)001:5586: tshul khrims sogs shes rab kyi bar yon tan cung
NK114(ye)001:5587: zad yod pa des rlom nas gzhan de lta bu
NK114(ye)001:5588: dang mi ldan pa la khyad du bsad na rang
NK114(ye)001:5589: gi sbyin sogs la sgrib par 'gyur bas spang bar
NK114(ye)001:5591: bdag la phun sum tshogs yod kyang //
NK114(ye)001:5592: gzhan la brnyas par mi bya ste //
NK114(ye)001:5593: zhun mar lta bu'i sems kyis su //
NK114(ye)001:5594: yon tan mtha' dag khong du sba //
NK114(ye)001:5596: gal te slong mo ba mang po 'ong ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:5597: gcig gis mang po slong ba sogs la sbyin ma nus na /
NK114(ye)001:5598: tshig 'jam po'i sgo nas de'i sems mi sun par
NK114(ye)001:5599: bya zhing nam zhig na bdag gis slong ba'i skye
NK114(ye)001:5600: bo thams cad kyi bsam pa yongs su rdzogs par
NK114(ye)001:5601: bya nus / de ltar nus pa zhig bya snyam du bsam par bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:5603: ji ste slong ba mngon du 'ong gyur kyang //
NK114(ye)001:5604: shin tu mthu chung sbyin par ma nus na //
NK114(ye)001:5605: ci nas slong ba dma' 'bab ma gyur par //
NK114(ye)001:5606: 'jam pa'i tshig gis de yi yid kyang bzho //
NK114(ye)001:5607: phyin chad slong ba drung du 'ong gyur na //
NK114(ye)001:5608: ci nas yid chad dma' bar mi 'gyur bar //
NK114(ye)001:5609: 'jungs pa'i skyon rnams rnam par bsal bar bya //
NK114(ye)001:5610: sred pa yongs su spang phyir nan tan bya //
NK114(ye)001:5612: gnyis pa tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:5616: tshul khrims kyi ngo bo gang zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:5617: sgo gsum gyi spang bya mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams
NK114(ye)001:5618: cad yang dag par sdom pa'i sgo nas gzhan gnod
NK114(ye)001:5619: gzhi bcas la spong sems goms shing brtan pa ste
NK114(ye)001:5620: / de la dbye na nyes spyod sdom pa'i tshul khrims dang /
NK114(ye)001:5621: dge ba chos sdud kyi tshul khrims dang /
NK114(ye)001:5622: sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims te rnam pa
NK114(ye)001:5623: gsum du theg pa chen po'i sde snod rnams las
NK114(ye)001:5625: de gsum gyi khyad par ni /
NK114(ye)001:5626: kun slong dang bcas pa'i dbang du byas nas sgo
NK114(ye)001:5627: gsum gyi mi dge ba'i las lam bcu spong ba
NK114(ye)001:5628: dang / rang gi ngo bo'i dbang du byas nas
NK114(ye)001:5629: lus ngag gi mi dge ba bdun spong ba'i sdom
NK114(ye)001:5631: de la nyon mongs pa dang du mi len pa'i phyir dang /
NK114(ye)001:5632: sdig pa mi 'byung ba'i phyir sems la yid gcags
NK114(ye)001:5633: pa'i me zhi bas bsil ba nyid kyi phyir ram
NK114(ye)001:5634: / bde ba'i rgyu yin pa nyid kyis dam pa
NK114(ye)001:5635: dag gis bsten par bya ba nyid yin pa'i phyir
NK114(ye)001:5637: de yang spong ba bdun gyi mtshan nyid can no //
NK114(ye)001:5638: chos gos gsum po la ma chags pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5640: yang dag pa'i lta ba ni de dag kun nas slong bar byed pa yin te /
NK114(ye)001:5641: de'i phyir kun nas slong bar byed pa dang bcas
NK114(ye)001:5642: pa'i tshul khrims kyi dbang du byas nas las kyi
NK114(ye)001:5643: lam bcu ni rnam par bshad do //
NK114(ye)001:5645: de yang rten so thar gyi sdom ldan zhig yin
NK114(ye)001:5646: na rigs bdun gang rung gi skabs kyi spang bya
NK114(ye)001:5647: dang bcas la / min na rang sa'i rtsa ba
NK114(ye)001:5648: dang yan lag gi spang bya rnams yang dag par
NK114(ye)001:5649: sdom par byed pa ni nyes spyod sdom pa'i tshul
NK114(ye)001:5650: dang bcas la / khrims yin la / nyes spyod
NK114(ye)001:5651: bsdams nas dge ba nyi tshe ba tsam la 'jug
NK114(ye)001:5652: pa ma yin par sgo gsum gyi dge ba'i las
NK114(ye)001:5653: lam thams cad khyad chos bzhis lhag pa'i pha rol
NK114(ye)001:5654: tu phyin pa drug dang ldan par bsgrub pa ni
NK114(ye)001:5655: dge ba chos sdud kyi tshul khrims te /
NK114(ye)001:5656: 'di mthun phyogs dge ba'i chos thams cad rang rgyud
NK114(ye)001:5657: la sdud pa'i tshul la bshad kyang phar phyin rang
NK114(ye)001:5658: rang gi mi mthun phyogs bsdams nas byang sems kyis
NK114(ye)001:5659: bsgrub bya thun mong ma yin pa la bslab pas
NK114(ye)001:5660: tshul khrims kyi ngo bo tshang ba'i cha nas der
NK114(ye)001:5661: gzhag go // de yang rang don tsam ma yin
NK114(ye)001:5662: par dngos brgyud gang yang rung bar gzhan sems can
NK114(ye)001:5663: rnams la phan pa lhur len pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:5664: dngos su ni bsdu ba bzhi'i sgo nas phan gdags la /
NK114(ye)001:5665: brgyud nas ni rang gi rgyud sbyong ba la sogs
NK114(ye)001:5666: pa'ang gzhan don la dmigs pa can te de ni
NK114(ye)001:5667: sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims yin zhing /
NK114(ye)001:5668: de yang rang don yid la byed pa'i blo ni
NK114(ye)001:5669: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi spang bya'i gtso bo
NK114(ye)001:5670: yin pas mi mthun pa'i phyogs de sdom pa'i cha
NK114(ye)001:5671: nas tshul khrims su bzhag pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:5672: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK114(ye)001:5673: nyes spyod sdom pa'i tshul khrims /
NK114(ye)001:5674: dge ba chos sdud kyi tshul khrims /
NK114(ye)001:5675: sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims so //
NK114(ye)001:5677: nyes spyod sdom pa dngos bshad pa /
NK114(ye)001:5678: sdom pa gsum ldan gyi mtha' dpyad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:5680: theg pa gong 'og gi sdom pa'i khyad par bshad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5681: theg chen nyes spyod sdom pa dngos bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:5683: de la spyir theg pa dman mchog gi sgor zhugs
NK114(ye)001:5684: pa'i gang zag rnams kyis nyes spyod sdom zhing dge
NK114(ye)001:5685: ba la gzhol ba tsam du 'dra na'ang /
NK114(ye)001:5686: nang gsesa theg dman gyi so so thar ba'i tshul
NK114(ye)001:5687: khrims las byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims la khyad
NK114(ye)001:5688: chos gnyis te / khyad gzhi dang bcas na khyad par bzhi yi sgo nas 'phags pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:5689: 'di ltar so so thar pa ni rang rgyud kyi
NK114(ye)001:5690: nyes spyod sdom pas gzhan gnod gzhi bcas las ldog
NK114(ye)001:5691: pa tsam gyi sdom pa'i tshul khrims la brten no
NK114(ye)001:5692: // byang chub sems dpa' ni gzhan la mi 'tshe
NK114(ye)001:5693: ba de yi steng du phan 'dogs pa bsnon pa
NK114(ye)001:5696: sems can don byed gsum ga dang ldan pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:5697: so so thar pa ni rigs bdun po gang yin
NK114(ye)001:5698: kyang ltung ba'i mtshams rnam par bzhag pa'i tshul lus
NK114(ye)001:5700: ngag gi mi dge ba bzhi ste spangsa pa bdun
NK114(ye)001:5701: po ru bsdus nas de dag las ci rigs sam
NK114(ye)001:5702: thams cad sdom par byed pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:5703: 'di ltar dge slong gi khrims nyis brgya lnga bcu
NK114(ye)001:5704: rtsa gsum po thams cad la kun slong ba'i bsam
NK114(ye)001:5705: pa dang gzhi gang la der 'du shes pa sogs
NK114(ye)001:5706: mi dgos pa ma yin kyang /
