NK114(ye)001:5707: lus ngag tu ma thon na ltung ba'i dngos gzhir
NK114(ye)001:5708: mi 'gyur bas lus ngag gi las tsam gtso la
NK114(ye)001:5709: / byang sems kyi skabs su bshad pa'i ltung ba
NK114(ye)001:5710: rnams ni lus ngag tu thon dgos pa rnams kyang
NK114(ye)001:5711: / / gzhan la phan 'dod ma yin par rang don du dmigs pa sogs sems gtso che zhing /
NK114(ye)001:5712: rgyal po'i rtsa ltung lnga pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5713: smon sems gtong ba lta bu lus ngag tu ma
NK114(ye)001:5714: thon kyang ltung bar 'gyur ba yod pas kun slong
NK114(ye)001:5715: dang bcas pa'i spang ba bcu ka gtso bor byed
NK114(ye)001:5716: pa ste / phar phyin bsdus pa las /
NK114(ye)001:5717: mtho ris thar pa'i bde lam gyur pa ste //
NK114(ye)001:5718: las lam bcu po 'di las nyams mi bya //
NK114(ye)001:5719: 'di la gnas pas 'gro la phan bsam pa'i //
NK114(ye)001:5720: bsam pa'i khyad par 'bras bu yod par 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:5721: ngag lus yid rnams yang dag bsdam bya ba //
NK114(ye)001:5722: mdor bsdus tshul khrims yin zhes rgyal bas gsungs //
NK114(ye)001:5724: des na khyad gzhi gnyis po de byang sems kyi rgyud la yod pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:5725: byang sems ma yin pa'i rab byung gi rgyud las
NK114(ye)001:5726: khyad par 'phags pas khyad chos bzhir don gyis 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:5727: ro // de lta na'ang gnang bkag shes nas bslab pa'i tshul ni /
NK114(ye)001:5728: so byang gi khyad par 'di ltar gang spang pa
NK114(ye)001:5729: la bslab par bya ba'i gnas srog gcod pa la
NK114(ye)001:5730: sogs pa ni so thar gyi skabs su rten gyi
NK114(ye)001:5731: gang zag rang don kho na bsgrub pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5732: dngos po la mngon par zhen pa can yin pa
NK114(ye)001:5733: la dgongs nas gzhan gyi don du 'gyur yang byed
NK114(ye)001:5734: par ma gnang bas ji ltar bcas pa de las
NK114(ye)001:5735: mi 'bral la / byang chub sems dpa' ni gzhan don gyi bsam pa rgya che zhing /
NK114(ye)001:5736: dngos po la mngon zhen chung bas de la dgongs nas gzhan gyi don du 'gyur na /
NK114(ye)001:5737: lus dang ngag gnyis kyi mi dge ba rnam pa bdun ga yang gnang bar bshad de /
NK114(ye)001:5738: de yang gzhan don du dngos su 'gyur ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:5739: 'gyur bar ngang gis shes pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5740: rang gi dge ba'i tshogs de las gya nom pa la mi sgrib pa'i steng /
NK114(ye)001:5741: sems kyi 'phen pa'i stobs kyis 'phel bar 'gyur ba
NK114(ye)001:5742: yi gnas skabs gsum po de brtags nas tshang na
NK114(ye)001:5743: mi dge ba'i rnam pa ltar snang ba de dang
NK114(ye)001:5744: de byed par gnang ba'i skabs yod de /
NK114(ye)001:5745: dge ba bcu'i las kyi lam bstan pa las /
NK114(ye)001:5746: gang dag bdag gi don la blta ba cung zad tsam yang med la /
NK114(ye)001:5747: byed pa gzhan gyi don 'ba' zhig 'dod cing thams
NK114(ye)001:5748: cad du snying rje dang ldan pa dag la ni
NK114(ye)001:5749: / yid kyi nyes par spyod pa gsum ma gtogs pa'am /
NK114(ye)001:5750: log par lta ba nyid ma gtogs pa dag la lar rjes su gnang ba snang ste /
NK114(ye)001:5751: de la byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa gtan la phab pa'i gtsug lag dag la blta'o //
NK114(ye)001:5753: lus ngag gi las bdun po byang sems ji lta bu la gnang na /
NK114(ye)001:5754: 'di ltar ded dpon snying rje chen po zhes bya
NK114(ye)001:5755: ba tshong pa lnga brgya dang 'grogs nas 'gro ba'i
NK114(ye)001:5756: skabs / mi nag mdung thung can zhes bya bas
NK114(ye)001:5757: tshong pa de dag gi srog 'phrog par ded dpon
NK114(ye)001:5758: des shes nas sdig to can las kyi rnam smin
NK114(ye)001:5760: tshong pa rnams srog gi 'jigs pa las grol ba'i
NK114(ye)001:5761: phyir rang nyid ngan song du ltung yang bzod snyam
NK114(ye)001:5762: pa'i sems stobs chen po bskyed nas mi nag mdunga
NK114(ye)001:5763: thung can bsad pas bskal pa brgyad khri'i tshogs rdzogs
NK114(ye)001:5764: par bshad pa lta bu dang /
NK114(ye)001:5765: 'byor yang ser snas mi sbyin pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5766: bkres pas srog la thug pa gnyis ka'i don du
NK114(ye)001:5767: sems bskyed nas phyug po las brkus te dbul po
NK114(ye)001:5768: la ster ba lta bu dang /
NK114(ye)001:5769: bram ze'i khye'u skar ma la dga' ba zhes bya
NK114(ye)001:5770: bas lo bzhi khri nyis stong nags khrod du tshangs
NK114(ye)001:5771: par spyad pa'i mthar grong khyer du bsod snyoms la
NK114(ye)001:5772: byon pa na / tshong dpon gyi bu mo de
NK114(ye)001:5773: la chags te 'dod pas gdung nas skabs de nyid
NK114(ye)001:5774: du 'chi bar brtsam pa las bzlog pa'i slad du
NK114(ye)001:5775: bdag dmyal bar skye yang sla snyam pa'i snying rje'i
NK114(ye)001:5776: sems kyis tshangs spyod gtang bas bskal pa bzhi khri'i
NK114(ye)001:5777: tshogs rdzogs par bshad pa lta bu dang /
NK114(ye)001:5778: de dge ba la rim gyis sbyor ba'i phyir de
NK114(ye)001:5779: la spyod pa lta bu 'dod log dang de dag
NK114(ye)001:5780: dper mtshon nas ngag gi las bzhi yang /
NK114(ye)001:5781: gsod nges pa'i sems can kyi srog skyob pa'i phyir rdzun smra ba lta bu dang /
NK114(ye)001:5782: sdig pa'i grogs kyis yongs su bslad cing ngan 'gror
NK114(ye)001:5783: 'khrid pa las ldog phyir de gnyis phra mas dbye
NK114(ye)001:5785: mya ngan gyis non pa yengs la bor ba'i phyir ram /
NK114(ye)001:5786: chos la 'jug pa'i dgos pa mthong nas sgrung dang bzhad gad smra ba lta bu'i ngag 'khyal dang /
NK114(ye)001:5787: sdig pa'i bya ba la 'jug pa de las bzlog phyir tshig rtsub mos spyo ba lta bu ste /
NK114(ye)001:5788: byang chub sems dpa' rang 'dod kyi 'khris med cing
NK114(ye)001:5789: gzhan phan don gnyer gyi bsam pa dang ldan pa
NK114(ye)001:5790: rnams kyis ni rnam pa'i gzugs brnyan nyes pa mi
NK114(ye)001:5791: dge ba ltar snang ba ci byed na'ang don la
NK114(ye)001:5792: dge ba yin pa'i phyir de 'dra ba'i byang sems
NK114(ye)001:5795: bsam pa byang chub sems dpa' yi //
NK114(ye)001:5796: dge ba'am yang na mi dge ba //
NK114(ye)001:5797: thams cad dge ba nyid 'gyur te //
NK114(ye)001:5798: gang phyir sems de gtso phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:5801: snying rje ldan zhing byams phyir dang //
NK114(ye)001:5802: sems dge ba la nyes pa med //
NK114(ye)001:5805: dge slong rang gi pha rgan la //
NK114(ye)001:5806: myur 'dong zhes ni bskul gyur nas //
NK114(ye)001:5807: phul bas de ni shi gyur kyang //
NK114(ye)001:5808: mtshams med spyor ba ma yin no //
NK114(ye)001:5810: de lta bas na rgyu las dge sdig dang 'bras
NK114(ye)001:5811: bu bde sdug dag nus pa mthu can du bsam
NK114(ye)001:5812: pa'i bye brag gis byas pa'i phyir na yid kyi
NK114(ye)001:5813: mi dge ba gsum po ni kun slong rang bzhin
NK114(ye)001:5814: gyi mi dge bar skye bas de la gnang ba'i
NK114(ye)001:5815: skabsa yod pa ma yin no //
NK114(ye)001:5816: 'o na dge ba bcu'i las kyi lam bstan pa las /
NK114(ye)001:5817: log par lta ba nyid ma gtogs pa zhes yid
NK114(ye)001:5818: kyi las snga ma gnyis gnang bar bstan pa ji
NK114(ye)001:5819: zhe na / de ni kun slong legs par brtags
NK114(ye)001:5820: na tshogs bsags pa'i skal bas dman pa'i gang zag
NK114(ye)001:5821: gi nor la de'i don du mchod sbyin gyi phyir
NK114(ye)001:5822: brnabs sems pa lta bu dang /
NK114(ye)001:5823: bstan 'gro la gnod pa'i gang zag gi kha rje
NK114(ye)001:5824: dbang thang la sogs nyams par 'dod pa'i gnod sems
NK114(ye)001:5825: lta bu las lam gnyis po'i mtshan nyid mi tshang
NK114(ye)001:5826: bas gnang ba'i skabs yin par bsdu bar byas kyi
NK114(ye)001:5827: / yid kyi las mtshan nyid pa gnyis po de ni gnang bar bstan pa gang na'ang med do //
NK114(ye)001:5828: des na theg dman du bkag pa dag theg pa
NK114(ye)001:5829: chen por gnang ba rnams ni sems can gyi blo
NK114(ye)001:5830: rim dang nus pa la dgongs pa yin pas drang
NK114(ye)001:5831: nges sna tshogs pa'i sgo nas bstan pa'i gsung rab
NK114(ye)001:5832: rnams brjod don tha dad pa ltar snang yang don
NK114(ye)001:5835: gnang ba dang ni bkag pa la //
NK114(ye)001:5836: khyod bka' la lar gcig tu nges //
NK114(ye)001:5837: la lar nges pa ma lags la //
NK114(ye)001:5838: phan tshun 'gal ba ma mchis so //
NK114(ye)001:5840: des na spyir btang rten gyi gang zag theg dman
NK114(ye)001:5841: pa la bkag pa de theg chen pa la gnang
NK114(ye)001:5843: theg pa chen po ba rgyal sras kyi sdom pa
NK114(ye)001:5844: la gnas pa las dang po pa rnams kyis kyang
NK114(ye)001:5845: gnang bkag gi gnas gang la'ang rang rang gi blo'i
NK114(ye)001:5846: mthu dang nyams la dpags nas dgag sgrub rigs pa
NK114(ye)001:5847: dang mi rigs pa ma brtags par rang gis nus
NK114(ye)001:5848: shing gzhan don du 'gyur nges pa lta bu brtsam
NK114(ye)001:5849: par bya ba'i gnas mthong yang rang don zhi bde
NK114(ye)001:5850: tsam gnyer nas de nyid bzlog pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5851: bzlog par bya ba'i gnas nyes pa can du mthong
NK114(ye)001:5852: yang bslab pa'i gnas 'og ma bya dka' ba la
NK114(ye)001:5853: 'jigs nas de bsrung ba spangs te gong ma bab
NK114(ye)001:5855: 'jug ldog gnyis ka'i cha la btang snyoms su 'jog
NK114(ye)001:5856: pa ste mdor na dngos brgyud gang yang rung bar
NK114(ye)001:5857: gzhan gyi phyir phan par mi sems pa dang rang
NK114(ye)001:5858: rgyud kha na ma tho bas gos pa spang ba'i
NK114(ye)001:5859: thabs mi bsgrub pa ganga dang gang yin pa de
NK114(ye)001:5860: rnam pa ji lta bu yin kyang ltung ba'i rgyu
NK114(ye)001:5861: ru thams cad gcig par gsungsa pa yin te /
NK114(ye)001:5862: 'di ltar ltung ba dang de'i gzugs brnyan /
NK114(ye)001:5863: ltung med dang de'i gzugs brnyan du 'chad pa'i mu bzhi po tshul khrims gsum du sbyar na /
NK114(ye)001:5864: sdom pa'i tshul khrims la zhe sdang gis srog gcod pa ltung ba /
NK114(ye)001:5865: phan sems kyis gsod pa ltung ba'i gzugs brnyan /
NK114(ye)001:5866: snying rjes mi gsod pa ltung med /
NK114(ye)001:5867: gzhan la phan kyang mi gsod pa ltung med kyi gzugs brnyan no //
NK114(ye)001:5869: ser snas mi ster ba ltung ba //
NK114(ye)001:5870: phan sems kyis mi ster ba ltung ba'i gzugs brnyan /
NK114(ye)001:5871: bsam pa dag pas ster ba ltung med /
NK114(ye)001:5872: gzhan la gnod phyir ster ba ltung med kyi gzugs brnyan no //
NK114(ye)001:5874: nad pa'i rim gro ma byas pa ltung ba /
NK114(ye)001:5875: don chen bsgrub pa'i slad du de las ldog pa ltung ba'i gzugs brnyan /
NK114(ye)001:5876: brtse bas nad g.yog byed pa ltung med /
NK114(ye)001:5877: de la rim gro ba yod bzhin du rang gi
NK114(ye)001:5878: dge ba'i las don chen po dor nas nad g.yog
NK114(ye)001:5879: byed pa ltung med kyi gzugs brnyan no //
NK114(ye)001:5880: de ltar gnang bkag gi tshul de rnams thog mar
NK114(ye)001:5881: shes par byas nas shes pa tsam du ma lus
NK114(ye)001:5882: par dran shes bag yod kyis dngos su lag len
NK114(ye)001:5883: la thebs pa zhig byung na don che ba yin
NK114(ye)001:5884: no // gnyis pa theg chen nyes spyod sdom pa dngos bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:5888: so so'i skye bo 'ching ba kun ldan gsar du
NK114(ye)001:5889: sems bskyed nas bslab pa la slob pa'i dang po'i
NK114(ye)001:5890: las can gyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams ni rang
NK114(ye)001:5891: gi nyon mongs pa 'dul ba'i dus yin pas /
NK114(ye)001:5892: 'dod pa'i nyes dmigs shes shing thar pa'i phan yon
NK114(ye)001:5893: la brod pa bskyed de nyon mongs pas bskyed pa'i
NK114(ye)001:5894: nyes spyod kyis rang rgyud gos par mi 'gyur ba'i
NK114(ye)001:5895: thabs la blo yang yang sbyong ba'i tshul ni ras
NK114(ye)001:5896: yug khrus kyis sbyang ba'am snam bu tshos su btsos
NK114(ye)001:5897: pa bzhin 'dod pa la mngon par zhen pa la
NK114(ye)001:5898: sogs pa'i skyon gyis je dag dang /
NK114(ye)001:5899: nges 'byung dang dad pa la sogs pa'i rnam par
NK114(ye)001:5900: sems 'gyur te yon tan gyi tshogs gong nas gonga
NK114(ye)001:5901: du 'phel ba la bslab cing spyod pa ni gtso
NK114(ye)001:5902: che ste / de yang chos pa rab la zhag skyed /
NK114(ye)001:5904: tha ma la'ang lo skyed thon pa zhig dgos par
NK114(ye)001:5905: bshad pas rtag tu rang rgyud la brtags dpyad byas
NK114(ye)001:5906: te chos kyis sems la phan thogs sam ma thogs
NK114(ye)001:5907: pa lta zhing rang rgyud 'dul ba la bslab par
NK114(ye)001:5908: bya dgos so // de bas na byang chub sems
NK114(ye)001:5909: dpa'i sdom pa rnam pa gsum las thog mar nyes
NK114(ye)001:5910: spyod sdom pa'i tshul khrims kyis rang rgyud ma dag
NK114(ye)001:5911: par dge ba'i chos sdud pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:5912: sems gyi don byed pa ste tshul khrisama gzhan gnyis
NK114(ye)001:5913: po rang gi nus tshod tsam zhig las gtso bor
NK114(ye)001:5914: gnyer te dper na rnyed pa mang po rtsol bas
NK114(ye)001:5915: bsgrubs nas re dogs dang mngon rlom bskyed pa'i rten
NK114(ye)001:5916: bzhengs dang mchod sbyin rgya cher byed pa dang 'tshogs
NK114(ye)001:5917: pa mang po bsdus nas rnam g.yeng dang bag med
NK114(ye)001:5918: bskyed pa'i chos bshad byed pa lta bus mtshon nyes
NK114(ye)001:5919: pa dang 'dres pa'i dge sbyor dang /
NK114(ye)001:5920: rang don stor ba'i gzhan don byed pa de 'dra
NK114(ye)001:5921: ba la rang cag phal cher gyis mchog tu rlom
NK114(ye)001:5922: na'ang dge ba'o chos sgra ji bzhin pa stobs su
NK114(ye)001:5923: 'gyur ba dang / gzhan don ji bzhin pa 'ong
NK114(ye)001:5924: dka' bar ma zad rang gi byang chub sgrub pa'i
NK114(ye)001:5925: lam bslab pa gsum la bar chad mang por 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:5926: 'gyur ba dang / ba'i phyir / b+ham ga la'i pan+di tas /
NK114(ye)001:5927: tshogs kyi lam pa la ni sdom pa'i tshul khrims gtso bo yin no //
NK114(ye)001:5928: sbyor ba'i lam pa la ni dge ba'i chos sdud pa'i tshul khrims gtso bo yin no //
NK114(ye)001:5929: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lam pa la ni sems
NK114(ye)001:5930: can don byed kyi tshul khrims gtso bo yin no
NK114(ye)001:5931: // gang zag gcig gi rgyud la brtsis na tshogs
NK114(ye)001:5932: lam chung ngu'i dus su gang zag dang po'i bslab
NK114(ye)001:5934: tshogs lam 'bring gi dus su gang zag 'bring po'i bslab pa la brtson par bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:5935: tshogs lam chen po'i dus su gang zag gsum pa'i bslab pa la brtson par bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:5937: rgyu mtshan des na las dang po pas smon 'jug
NK114(ye)001:5938: gi mi mthun pa'i phyogs rang sa'i rtsa ba dang
NK114(ye)001:5939: yan lag gi nyes ltung rnams phras nas bsrung ba
NK114(ye)001:5940: dang / der ma zad so so thar pa'i sdom
NK114(ye)001:5941: pa ni nyan thos kyi yin pas nyam chung ngo
NK114(ye)001:5942: snyam du mi blta bar rigs bdun gang rung gi
NK114(ye)001:5943: sdom pa yang dag par blangs te bsrung zhing /
NK114(ye)001:5944: de dag las kyang rab tu byung ba'i sdom pa
NK114(ye)001:5945: dang ldan pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i ni khyim pa
NK114(ye)001:5946: byang chub sems dpa' las khyad par can du mdo
NK114(ye)001:5949: rab tu byung ba'i phyogs dag ni //
NK114(ye)001:5950: yon tan tshad med rnams dang ldan //
NK114(ye)001:5951: de ltas sdom brtson khyim pa yi //
NK114(ye)001:5952: byang sems rnams las mchog tu bshad //
NK114(ye)001:5954: de bzhin du cho 'phrul chen po bstan pa'i mdo las kyang /
NK114(ye)001:5955: smad par bya ba'i khyim la brten pa de //
NK114(ye)001:5956: bla med byang chub dam pa gzhar mi thob //
NK114(ye)001:5958: khyim gyis skrag ste khyim nas mngon byung ba //
NK114(ye)001:5959: de dag byang chub mchog 'di rnyed mi dka' //
NK114(ye)001:5960: zhes gsungs pas 'phags pa'i sa ma thob kyi bar
NK114(ye)001:5961: du byang chub chen po'i lam gyi rten du rab
NK114(ye)001:5962: tu byung ba basngagasa pas las dang po pas rab
NK114(ye)001:5963: byung gi sdom khrims blangs nas tshul bzhin bsrung ba'i
NK114(ye)001:5964: sgo nas nyes spyod sdom pa la gtso bor bslab
NK114(ye)001:5965: par bya ste / tha na rtags kyi khyad par
NK114(ye)001:5966: las kyang bsrung sems kyi gnyen po che ba dang
NK114(ye)001:5967: rten der gyur pa tsam nas lha dang mi rnams
NK114(ye)001:5968: kyi mchod gnas su shes sla bas 'tsho bas mi
NK114(ye)001:5969: par bya ste / ngal ba dang / sdig pa'i grogs kyis dma' dbab par dka' ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:5970: sems la 'gyod pa dang rnam par g.yeng ba med
NK114(ye)001:5971: pas ting nge 'dzin gyi rgyu'i gtso bo dang ldan
NK114(ye)001:5972: pa dang / thog ma nyid du grol ba dang
NK114(ye)001:5973: mi ldan yang tshul khrims dang ldan pa'i rgyus dkor
NK114(ye)001:5974: dang dad zas 'ju sla bas nyes dmigs dang mi
NK114(ye)001:5975: 'grogs pa la sogs pa'i yon tan mang po dang
NK114(ye)001:5977: 'on kyang byang chub sems dpa' rang sa'i thun mong
NK114(ye)001:5978: ma yin pa'i sdom pa tsam la so thar mtshan
NK114(ye)001:5979: nyid pa'i sgra bshad pa yang med de /
NK114(ye)001:5980: so so thar pa ni rgyu la 'bras bu'i ming du chags te /
NK114(ye)001:5981: legs pa'i lam bstan pa las /
NK114(ye)001:5982: lam 'di ni so so thar par 'gro bas na so so thar pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:5983: dper na grong khyer du 'gro ba'i lam la grong khyer gyi lam zhes bya ba dang 'dra'o //
NK114(ye)001:5984: zhes gsungs pa ltar rang nyid las dang nyon mongs
NK114(ye)001:5985: pa'i rgyus 'khor bar 'khor ba las thar pa'i thabs
NK114(ye)001:5986: su nyes spyod sdom pa la bshad pas so //
NK114(ye)001:5987: des na byang chub sems dpa'i sdom ldan gyi rgyud
NK114(ye)001:5988: so thar gyi sdom pas bsdams pa la byang chub
NK114(ye)001:5989: sems dpa'i so so thar pa zhes btags pa tsam
NK114(ye)001:5991: rgyu mtshan de lta bas na cho ga'i sgo nas
NK114(ye)001:5992: sor sdom len gso la sogs pa'i tshul theg chen
NK114(ye)001:5993: gyi sde snod rnams las gsal bar bstan pa med
NK114(ye)001:5994: de / so so thar pa chos bzhi bstan pa
NK114(ye)001:5995: zhes bya ba'i mdo sde tshan gcig pa zhig bod
NK114(ye)001:5997: 'dul ba gleng gzhis 'chad pa ltar lus ngag gi
NK114(ye)001:5998: nyes par spyad pa'i sdom pa'i rab dbye dang cho
NK114(ye)001:5999: ga'i khyad par zur du ma bstan to //
NK114(ye)001:6000: des na byang sems kyi sdom pa so thar gyi
NK114(ye)001:6001: rten du mi rung ba'i lha klu gnod sbyin gyi
NK114(ye)001:6002: rigs la'ang skye rung bar bshad de /
NK114(ye)001:6003: de'i rgyu mtshan kyang tshogs gnyis kyi sbyangs pa sngon
NK114(ye)001:6004: song zhing theg pa chen po'i chos nam mkha' ltar
NK114(ye)001:6005: rgya che zhing zab pa'i don nyams 'og tu chud
NK114(ye)001:6006: nus pa'i sems stobs chen po can ni lus rten
NK114(ye)001:6007: khyim pa dang rab byung gang yin yang bsam pa'i
NK114(ye)001:6008: rten gtso che ste o rgyan gyi rgyal po in+d+ra
NK114(ye)001:6009: b+h+au ti 'dod pa'i yon tan thams cad ma spang
NK114(ye)001:6010: bzhin du dbang bskur nod pa tsam gyis mod la
NK114(ye)001:6011: sdom pa gsum char ngo bo gcig pa'i tshul gyis
NK114(ye)001:6012: thob par gyur pa bzhin no //
NK114(ye)001:6013: gnyis pa bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:6017: byang chub sems dpa' gang zhig nyan thos dang thun
NK114(ye)001:6018: mong pa'i so thar gyi sdom pa blangs nas de
NK114(ye)001:6019: dang bcas pa srung ba la /
NK114(ye)001:6020: spyir sor sdom thob byed kyi cho ga ni gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:6021: tshegs chung ngus rdzogs pa sngon gyi cho ga ni
NK114(ye)001:6022: sangs rgyas dang rang sangs rgyas gnyis rang byung gi
NK114(ye)001:6023: dge slong dang / ston pa rdzogs sangs rgyas nas
NK114(ye)001:6024: yun ring por ma lon pa'i dus su gdul bya
NK114(ye)001:6027: dbang po rnams smin pa shas che zhing /
NK114(ye)001:6028: las dang nyon mongs pa dang rnam par smin pa'i sgrib pa gsum shas chung bas /
NK114(ye)001:6029: lnga sde bzang po ye shes khong chud kyis dang /
NK114(ye)001:6030: sh+aa ri'i bu sogs tshur shog gis dang /
NK114(ye)001:6031: 'od srung chen po ston par khas blangs pas dang /
NK114(ye)001:6032: skye dgu'i bdag mo lci chos brgyad khas blangs pas dang /
NK114(ye)001:6033: legs byin dris pa'i lan la dgyes pas dang /
NK114(ye)001:6034: bzang sde'i tshogs drug cu skyabs gsum 'dzin par khas blangs pas dang /
NK114(ye)001:6035: chos sbyin ma phrin gyis te thabs sla ba mang po dang /
NK114(ye)001:6036: mkhan slob med par dge 'dun gyis gsol bzhi'i las
NK114(ye)001:6037: kyis rab byung bsnyen rdzogs cig char du bsgrub pa
NK114(ye)001:6038: rnams te de dag las gsol bzhis bsgrub pa ni
NK114(ye)001:6040: tshegs dang bcas pa da lta'i cho ga'i sgo nas rdzogs par byed pa la /
NK114(ye)001:6041: dus phyis kyi gang zag rnams smin gsum shas chung zhing sgrib gsum shas che bas /
NK114(ye)001:6042: 'gal rkyen nges pa lnga dang bral zhing sdom pa
NK114(ye)001:6043: skye ba dang gnas pa dang khyad par du 'gro
NK114(ye)001:6044: ba dang / mdzes pa'i bar chad rnams med cing
NK114(ye)001:6045: mthun rkyen phun sum tshogs pa lnga dang ldan pa'i
NK114(ye)001:6046: bsgrub bya de sgrub byed brtan mkhas kyi yon tan
NK114(ye)001:6047: gnyis dang ldan pa'i mkhan po dang bcas pa'i dge
NK114(ye)001:6048: 'dun yul dbus matha'i khyad par gyis bcu tshogs sam
NK114(ye)001:6049: lnga'i tshogs pas bslab tshigs gsum po rim gyis sbyin
NK114(ye)001:6050: pa'i sgo nas rdzogs par byed par byed pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:6051: thob bya sdom pa'i bye brag ni byang chub sems
NK114(ye)001:6052: dpa'i khyim pa'i phyogs la brten pa rnams kyis ni
NK114(ye)001:6053: dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa'i dbye ba 'og tu 'chad
NK114(ye)001:6054: 'gyur lta bu'i gang yang rung ba dang ni /
NK114(ye)001:6055: yang na bsnyen gnas kyi sdom pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:6056: de yang spyir dus khrims yin pas gong ma'i rten
NK114(ye)001:6057: du mi rung bar bshad kyang 'di'i bsrung bya brgyad
NK114(ye)001:6058: po ji srid 'tsho'i bar du bsrung ba'i go ma'i
NK114(ye)001:6059: dge bsnyen du grags pa de'am /
NK114(ye)001:6060: yang na nyin gcig tu srog gcod pa spangs te
NK114(ye)001:6061: sems bskyed par bshad pa lta bus mtshon nya stong
NK114(ye)001:6062: tshes brgyad sogs su yan lag brgyad pa'i khrims bsrung
NK114(ye)001:6064: dus dang dus su len par byed na theg chen
NK114(ye)001:6065: gso sbyong du yang 'gyur bas de ltar gtan khrims
NK114(ye)001:6066: dang dus khrims gnyis po de las gang yang rung
NK114(ye)001:6067: ba zhig blangs nas de'i steng du smon 'jug byang
NK114(ye)001:6068: chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas de gnyis kyi thun
NK114(ye)001:6069: mong ma yin pa'i spang sgrub kyi bslab bya dang
NK114(ye)001:6070: bcas pa rtag tu bsrung bar byed pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:6071: rab tu byung ba'i phyogs la brten pa rnams kyis ni dge slong gi sdom pa'am /
NK114(ye)001:6072: dge tshul gyi sdom pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:6073: dge slob ma yi sdom pa gang yang rung ba
NK114(ye)001:6074: zhig blangs te tshul bzhin bsrung ba dang ldan pa'i
NK114(ye)001:6075: steng du smon pa dang 'jug pa'i bslab pa thun
NK114(ye)001:6076: min gnyis dang bcas bsrung ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:6077: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa rang sa'i tshul khrimsa te /
NK114(ye)001:6078: de dag gi rgyud kyi sor sdom de theg chen nyes spyod sdom pa'i tshul khrims yin no //
NK114(ye)001:6081: dge slong gi sdom pa gsum po la brten skyes
NK114(ye)001:6082: pa dang bud med kyi bye brag gis pha ma
NK114(ye)001:6083: gnyis rer phye bas drug dang /
NK114(ye)001:6084: de'i steng du dge slob ma'i dang bsnyen gnas kyi
NK114(ye)001:6085: sdom pa gnyis bsnan pas so thar rigs brgyad dang
NK114(ye)001:6086: / bsdu na snga ma gsum po'i pha ma'i sdom rdzas la tha dad med pas bzhi yin te /
NK114(ye)001:6088: so sor thar zhes bya rnam brgyad //
NK114(ye)001:6089: rdzas su rnam pa bzhi yin te //
NK114(ye)001:6090: mtshan las ming ni 'pho ba'i phyir //
NK114(ye)001:6091: tha dad de dag 'gal ba med //
NK114(ye)001:6093: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:6094: khyim pa'i bslab bya bshad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:6095: rab byung gi bslab bya bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:6097: dge bsnyen gyi bslab bya bshad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:6098: bsnyen gnas kyi bslab bya bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:6100: khyim pa'i sdom pa la dbye na /
NK114(ye)001:6102: tshangs par spyod pa'i dge bsnyen rnam pa gnyis yin
NK114(ye)001:6103: te sna gcig sogs ni snga ma'i bsrung bya'i nang
NK114(ye)001:6104: du 'du zhing / bsnyen gnas ni phyi ma'i phyogs su gtogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:6105: 'di la nang gses kyi dbye ba lnga po la bsam nas lnga yin te /
NK114(ye)001:6106: zhes 'bru bcos byas par snang bas de ltar yang
NK114(ye)001:6107: 'gal ba med mod yi ge phal che ba na
NK114(ye)001:6108: gnyis zhes yod pas de bzhin du 'grel lo //
NK114(ye)001:6109: de la dang po yongs rdzogs dge bsnyen gyi bsrung bya las srog gcod pa'am /
NK114(ye)001:6112: rdzun du smra ba rnams las gang yang rung ba
NK114(ye)001:6113: gcig spong ba la sna gcig bsrung ba zhes bya
NK114(ye)001:6114: ste srog gcod pa lta bu kho na spang ba'o
NK114(ye)001:6115: // 'di dag kyang yul gyi yan lag tu mi yin pa dgos te /
NK114(ye)001:6116: 'gro ba'i gtso bo mi yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:6117: de yi steng ma byin len pa lta bu gcig
NK114(ye)001:6118: spong ba bsnan te gnyis po bsrung ba la ni
NK114(ye)001:6119: phyogs gcig ldan pa'am sna 'ga' bsrung ba zhes bya'o
NK114(ye)001:6120: // de yi steng du rdzun smra ba spang ba
NK114(ye)001:6121: lta bu bsnan te gsum bsrung ba la phal cher
NK114(ye)001:6123: de steng 'dod log spang ba bsnan te rtsa ba
NK114(ye)001:6124: phyed dang bzhi chang dang bcas pa spangs na yongs
NK114(ye)001:6125: rdzogs bsrung ba'i dge bsnyen dag tu 'dod pa yin
NK114(ye)001:6126: no // de la chang yan lag tu bzhag pa
NK114(ye)001:6127: ni de ma spang na bslab pa gzhan rnam par
NK114(ye)001:6128: dag par mi 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:6129: rtsa ba bzhi la phyed pa'i sgra zhugs pa ni
NK114(ye)001:6130: 'dod log tsam las mi tshangs spyod ma spang bas
NK114(ye)001:6131: so // de yang khyim pas bsrung sla ba la dgongs te /
NK114(ye)001:6133: log g.yem shin tu smad phyir dang //
NK114(ye)001:6134: sla phyir mi byed thob phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:6136: mi tshangs spyod dang bcas rtsa ba bzhi chang dang
NK114(ye)001:6137: lnga ga spang ba la ni tshangs par spyod pa'i
NK114(ye)001:6138: dge bsnyen no zhes yongs su grags pa yin no
NK114(ye)001:6139: // de la 'dul bar yongs rdzogs dge bsnyen las
NK114(ye)001:6140: gzhan pa'i 'bogs chog ma bstan pas sdom pa zhu
NK114(ye)001:6141: // ba'i dus / bdag dge bsnyen du bzung du gsol //
NK114(ye)001:6143: bslab pa brjod pa'i dus dge bsnyen gang dang gang gi mtshams 'byed pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:6144: de'ang sdom pa ni brjod pa gsum gyi tha ma la skye na /
NK114(ye)001:6146: de'i phyi nas brjod pas ma nges pa'i sdom par 'gro snyam pa mi bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:6147: mdo sde ba de ltar 'dod srid kyis /
NK114(ye)001:6148: lung rnam bzhi las bdag che ge mo'i dge bsnyen
NK114(ye)001:6149: du bzung du gsol zhes bya ba mi 'byung bas
NK114(ye)001:6150: so // spyir brjod pa dgongs ma gnyis la don ma mchis par /
NK114(ye)001:6151: phyi mas bzung du gsol zhes bya ba de rang nus pa chen nas skye ba ma yin gyi /
NK114(ye)001:6152: brjod pa gsum gyi tha ma la gsum ga'i thob
NK114(ye)001:6153: mtshams brjod pa yin pas skyes snyam pa mdzod ces
NK114(ye)001:6154: bya ba de 'dun pa la brten nas man ngag
NK114(ye)001:6156: gnyis pa bsnyen gnas kyi bslab bya bshad pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:6157: khyim na gnas pa rnams dus thams cad du tshangs
NK114(ye)001:6158: par spyad dka' ba nyid kyis nyin zhag gcig pa'i
NK114(ye)001:6159: tshangs spyod pa sbyar ba'i ched du bstan pa ste
NK114(ye)001:6160: / de yang rab tu byung ba'i bslab pa'i gnas rags pa bcur dril nas bstan pa las /
NK114(ye)001:6161: gser dngul len pa ni khyim pa la mi dgag
NK114(ye)001:6162: ste bu smad ces te chung ma dang bu dang
NK114(ye)001:6163: bu mo sogs ma smad rnams gso dgos pa la
NK114(ye)001:6164: dgongs te de'i phyir gnang ba yin zhing /
NK114(ye)001:6165: de bzhin du gar sogs dang /
NK114(ye)001:6166: phreng sogs dge tshul la re rer bgrang yang khyim
NK114(ye)001:6167: pa la de gnyis po mtshang chung bas gcig tu
NK114(ye)001:6168: bgrang ngo zhes sa sde las bshad pa yin la
NK114(ye)001:6169: / don du gser dngul len pa las gzhan dgu po thams cad bsnyen gnas pas spang dgos kyang /
NK114(ye)001:6170: tha snyad tsam du yan lag brgyad pa'i khrims zhes grags pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:6171: 'di nyin zhag phrugs gcig tu spang bar khas blangs
NK114(ye)001:6172: nas bsrung ba ni rang gi sdom pa'i mtshan nyid
NK114(ye)001:6174: nam bsrung ba'i nyin par blang gis dang po blangs nas phyis blang mi dgos pa ni med do //
NK114(ye)001:6175: zhes bshad pas khyim pa rnams kyis nya stong brgyad gsum dang /
NK114(ye)001:6176: dus chen bzhi gtso bor gyur ba'i dus la blang zhing bsrung ba'i phyir dus khrims dang /
NK114(ye)001:6177: 'di dge bsnyen rnams kyis blang na gso sbyong du 'gro ba yin no //
NK114(ye)001:6178: mdo sde pa rnams kyis dus khrims 'di dud 'gro'i rten la'ang skye bar 'dod cing /
NK114(ye)001:6179: blang yul kyang dge bsnyen gso sbyong la gnas pa yan chad do //
NK114(ye)001:6180: de lta bu'i yan lag brgyad pa'i khrims gang zhig

NK114(ye)001:6237: bya ba'i dngos po ni thams cad nyes byas kyi

NK114(ye)001:6789: chen gyi lam las ni dngos po'i chos thams cad

NK114(ye)001:6796: thob na sdom pa yang skye rung bar bshad pa
NK114(ye)001:6797: bar bzhed do // dang / khyad par du kha
NK114(ye)001:6798: ba can pa rnams ni theg pa chen po kho
NK114(ye)001:6799: na'i gdul bya yin par gsungs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:6800: snyigs ma'i dus 'dir ni bstan pa shin tu nyams
NK114(ye)001:6801: dma' bas ngur smrig gi rtags tsam 'chang ba dang
NK114(ye)001:6802: / bsrung 'dod kyi 'du shes tsam yod pa dang /

NK114(ye)001:6804: shin tu dkon pa dgongs nas da lta'i bshes gnyen
NK114(ye)001:6805: dam pa thabs mkhas kyi mdzad pa can rnams kyis
NK114(ye)001:6806: sor sdom nyams pa rnams la yang gsang 'dod yod
NK114(ye)001:6807: med kyi dri rtog ye mi mdzad par sdom pa
NK114(ye)001:6808: sbyin pa'i bka' gnang thob pa yang rgyu mtshan de
NK114(ye)001:6809: ltar yin no snyam du sems so //
NK114(ye)001:6810: gzhan yang dge slong gi lhag ma la sogs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:6811: dge tshul sogs kyi bshags bya rnams lci yang la
NK114(ye)001:6812: ltos pa'i bshags tshul ji ltar bshad pa gzhan las
NK114(ye)001:6813: shes par bya zhing thams cad la stobs bzhi tshang
NK114(ye)001:6814: ba ni gnad gal po che'o //
NK114(ye)001:6815: de ltar na ltung ba mi 'byung ba dang byung
NK114(ye)001:6816: yang phyir bcos pa'i thabs kyis ltung ba dang mi
NK114(ye)001:6817: 'grogs pa dang / tshul khrims kyis mi rlom zhing
NK114(ye)001:6818: nga rgyal med pa sogs ni bslab pa la mkhas
NK114(ye)001:6819: par bya ba la rag las pas na lus ngag
NK114(ye)001:6820: gi sbyor ba las byung ba'i ltung ba'i mtshams phra
NK114(ye)001:6821: mo yan chad nges par bya ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:6822: gal te lus ngag gi tshul tsam gyis nyes pa ma 'byin na'ang 'dod pa la g.yengs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:6823: tshul khrims dang brtul zhugs la mchog tu 'dzin pa
NK114(ye)001:6824: yod na rgyud rnam par dag par mi 'gyur bas
NK114(ye)001:6825: na sgo gsum gyi spang blang gi gnas thams cad
NK114(ye)001:6826: la mkhas par bya dgos te /
NK114(ye)001:6827: de skad du legs pa'i lam bstan pa las kyang /
NK114(ye)001:6828: yang dag pa dang ma dag pa'i dbye bas rnam pa gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:6829: sred pa dang lta ba ngan dang nga rgyal dang
NK114(ye)001:6830: yang dag pa ma yin pa'i rtog pa dang ma
NK114(ye)001:6831: 'dres pa dang yongs su tshang ba ni dag pa'i
NK114(ye)001:6832: tshul khrims so // de las ldog pa ni ma dag pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:6833: dag pa la'ang rnam pa gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:6834: gang 'da' ba med par rnam par byang ba de
NK114(ye)001:6835: ni ltung ba med pa'i rnam par dag pa'i tshul
NK114(ye)001:6836: khrims so // gang ltung ba slar bcos pa rnam
NK114(ye)001:6837: par dag pa de ni ldang ba'i rnam par dag
NK114(ye)001:6839: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK114(ye)001:6840: gzhan du na bsrung mtshams zhib mor phye ste shes pa lta ci /
NK114(ye)001:6841: ltung ba sde lnga la sogs pa bsrung bya'i rnam
NK114(ye)001:6842: grangs brtsi ba tsam yang mi shes bzhin du bdag
NK114(ye)001:6845: tshul ldan no snyam du bslab pa bsrung bar rlom
NK114(ye)001:6846: pa de ni mtshar zhes gzhan gyis khrel ba'i gnas
NK114(ye)001:6847: yin te chu med pa la khron par rlom pa
NK114(ye)001:6848: bzhin no // de ltar yang 'dul ba lung las /
NK114(ye)001:6849: gang zhig rab tu byung yang yon tan snod ma gyur //
NK114(ye)001:6850: skra dang kha spu bregs kyang dge sbyong tshul ma zhugs //
NK114(ye)001:6851: rab byung de ni rab byung ma yin khyim pa'ang min //
NK114(ye)001:6852: chu med khron pa ri mo'i mar me bzhin //
NK114(ye)001:6854: rgyu mtshan des na ltung ba dang ltung min sogs
NK114(ye)001:6855: kyi mtshams dang phyir bcos tshul dang byin gyis brlabs
NK114(ye)001:6856: pa'i tshul sogs legs par shes pa zhig yin na
NK114(ye)001:6857: de tsam gyis kyang ltung ba mi 'byung ba dang
NK114(ye)001:6858: / gal te bag med pa la sogs pa'i dbang
NK114(ye)001:6859: gis nyes pa 'ga' zhig byung na yang nyams pa
NK114(ye)001:6860: de slar gso ba dang ltung ba sbyong ba'i thabs
NK114(ye)001:6861: kyis sor chud sla ba yin pa'i phyir na ltung
NK114(ye)001:6862: ba 'byung ba'i sgo ltung ba yin min gyi dbye
NK114(ye)001:6864: bslab pa la mi gus pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:6866: nyon mongs pa mang zhing shugs drag pa ste bzhi'i
NK114(ye)001:6867: dang po'ang mi shes pa yin no zhes 'phags pa
NK114(ye)001:6868: thogs med kyis bzhed pa yin te gang ma shes
NK114(ye)001:6869: pa de la gus shing bag bya ba la sogs
NK114(ye)001:6870: pas 'bad du med pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:6871: de dag ni gang bkag pa de mi byed pa yin pas ldog pa'i tshul khrims zhes bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:6872: gnyis pa bsgrub pa'i bslab bya bshad pa la /
NK114(ye)001:6873: bsgrub pa'i bslab bya dngos dang /
NK114(ye)001:6874: zhar byung rung mthun brtsi tshul lo //
NK114(ye)001:6876: gnyen po rnam par byang ba'i phyogs rgyud la bskyed
NK114(ye)001:6877: par byed pa'i thabs kyi cha yan lag dang bcas
NK114(ye)001:6878: pa dang du blang ba'i tshul gyis bsgrub par byed
NK114(ye)001:6879: pas na bsgrub pa'i bslab bya zhes bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:6880: de la yang tshul khrims kyi snying po dag par
NK114(ye)001:6881: byed pa'i thabs gso sbyong dang dbyar gnas dang dgag
NK114(ye)001:6882: dbye ste / gzhi gsum gyi cho ga gtso bor
NK114(ye)001:6883: bstan nas de dang bcas pa bslab pa gsum gyi
NK114(ye)001:6884: rten gzhir gyur pa'i gzhi bcu bdun gyi bslab bya
NK114(ye)001:6885: dbye ste / rnams gsungs te / lung gzhi las /
NK114(ye)001:6889: koo sh+aam 9 b+ai dang las 10kyi gzhi //
NK114(ye)001:6894: zhes gsungs pa de rnams de bzhin gshegs pas rjes
NK114(ye)001:6895: su gnang bas de dag la bslab pa ni 'jug
NK114(ye)001:6896: pa'i tshul khrims zhes bya bas bslab bya thams cad
NK114(ye)001:6897: 'jug ldog gi tshul khrims gnyis pa der 'dus so
NK114(ye)001:6898: // gzhi bcu bdun po de rnams cung zad bkral te bshad na /
NK114(ye)001:6899: dang po sdom pa ma thob pa thob byed kyi gzhi gcig /
NK114(ye)001:6900: bar du thob pa mi nyams pa bsrung byed kyi gzhi brgyad /
NK114(ye)001:6901: tha ma nyams na phyir bcos kyi gzhi bdun /
NK114(ye)001:6902: de thams cad la khyab pa'i gzhi gcig go //
NK114(ye)001:6903: de la dang po thob byed kyi gzhi ni /
NK114(ye)001:6904: rab byung gi bslab pa rnams ston pa la rten
NK114(ye)001:6905: gyi gang zag gzhi grub dgos pa'i phyir rab byung
NK114(ye)001:6907: de yang sngar bshad pa ltar tshur shog la sogs pa'i thabs sla ba mang po dang /
NK114(ye)001:6908: dge 'dun gyis gsol bzhi'i las kyis rab byung bsnyen
NK114(ye)001:6909: rdzogs cig char bsgrub pa ste tshegs med par rdzogs
NK114(ye)001:6910: pa sngon gyi cho ga dang /
NK114(ye)001:6911: mkhan slob dang bcas pa'i dge 'dun gyis sbyor dngos
NK114(ye)001:6912: rjes gsum gyi spros pa dang bcas pa'i cho ga
NK114(ye)001:6913: la brten nas bslab tshigs gsum rim gyis sbyin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:6914: sgo nas tshegs dang bcas bsgrub pa da ltar gyi
NK114(ye)001:6915: cho ga ste gnyis kyis so //
NK114(ye)001:6916: gnyis pa bsrung byed kyi gzhi la /
NK114(ye)001:6917: bslab pa yongs sbyong gi gzhi gsum //
NK114(ye)001:6918: bde bar gnas pa'i rkyen gyi gzhi lnga ste brgyad do //
NK114(ye)001:6919: dang po yongs sbyong gi gzhi gsum ni gnyen po dge ba'i phyogs gso zhing /
NK114(ye)001:6920: spang bya nyes pa'i phyogs sbyong bar byed pas gso sbyong dang /
NK114(ye)001:6921: dbyar zla gsum la sogs par gnas gcig tu gnas pas dbyar gnas dang /
NK114(ye)001:6922: dbyar zla gsum du dgag pa byas pa'i bslab bya rnams dbye bas dgag dabye'o //
NK114(ye)001:6923: dang po gso sbyong la'ang spang bya la ltos te sngar bsags kyi sgrib pa sbyong ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:6924: blang bya la ltos te lhag pa'i sems dang shes rab dag byed zhi gnas kyi gso sbyong dang /
NK114(ye)001:6925: de bzhin du spang bya phyis 'byung gi rgyun tshe 'di'i zag pa sdom pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:6926: blang bya lhag pa'i tshul khrims dag byed mthun pa'i gso sbyong gnyis yod pa las /
NK114(ye)001:6927: dang po zhi gnas kyi gso sbyong la 'dod pa'i
NK114(ye)001:6928: sems rags pa zhi byed 'dod chags kyi gnyen po
NK114(ye)001:6929: mi sdug pa / zhe sdang gi gnyen po byams pa /
NK114(ye)001:6930: gti mug gi gnyen po rten 'brel /
NK114(ye)001:6931: rnam rtog gi gnyen po dbugs 'byin 'jug dran pa'i sgom tshul rnams dang /
NK114(ye)001:6932: khams gong ma'i sems bsam gtan bzhi dang /
NK114(ye)001:6933: gzugs med bzhi'i snyoms 'jug bsgom pa rnams zhi gnas dang /
NK114(ye)001:6934: thar pa'i lam byang chub phyogs so bdun gyis bsdus pa'i lhag mthong bsgom pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:6935: gnyis pa mthun pa'i gso sbyong la'ang dus nges pa dang ma nges pa gnyis las /
NK114(ye)001:6936: dang po la bcu bzhi pa dang bco lnga pa gnyis las /
NK114(ye)001:6940: de nas zla ba re dor ba'i mar ngo rnams so //
NK114(ye)001:6942: rgyal dang dbo dang sa ga dang //
NK114(ye)001:6943: chu stod khrums smad smin drug bcas //
NK114(ye)001:6944: 'di rnams kyi ni nag po'i phyogs //
NK114(ye)001:6945: zla phyed gso sbyong bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:6946: zhes lo gcig gi nang du mar ngo drug po
NK114(ye)001:6947: de zhag mi thub dor ba'i bcu bzhi pa dang
NK114(ye)001:6948: / de las gzhan mar ngo drug dang /
NK114(ye)001:6949: yar ngo bcu gnyis te bco brgyad ni bco lnga pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:6950: gnyis pa dus ma nges pa la bkra shis pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:6952: mkhon pa bsdum pa'i gso sbyong ngo //
NK114(ye)001:6953: ji ltar byed pa'i tshul yang grub pa la sogs
NK114(ye)001:6954: pa'i gnas su sbyor ba gan+di brdungs nas dge 'dun
NK114(ye)001:6955: bsdus te rgyud chags gsum pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:6956: dus bzang gi mdo 'don pa sogs dang /
NK114(ye)001:6957: dngos gzhi gsol ba'i las kyis thugs bstun nas /
NK114(ye)001:6958: so sor thar pa'i mdo 'don pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:6959: rjes mkhyen par gsol nas bsngo ba bya ba la sogs pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:6960: gnyis pa dbyar gnas la phan yon dang dbyar gnas dngos gnyis las /
NK114(ye)001:6967: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la dbyar snga ma dang phyi ma gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:6969: gro zhun zla ba'i tshes gcig nas //
NK114(ye)001:6970: snga ma'i dbyar de gtso bo yin //
NK114(ye)001:6971: de nyid khrums kyi zla ba yi //
NK114(ye)001:6972: tshes gcig nas ni phyi mar grags //
NK114(ye)001:6974: ji ltar gnas pa'i tshul la /
NK114(ye)001:6976: dam tshig bsrung ba gnyis las /
NK114(ye)001:6977: dang po la sbyor dngos gnyis /
NK114(ye)001:6978: sbyor ba la gtsug lag khang brgyan pa sogs ring sbyor dang /
NK114(ye)001:6979: gnas mal stob pa sogs nye sbyor ro //
NK114(ye)001:6980: dngos gzhi ni sngags lan gsum brjod pas khas blang ngo //
NK114(ye)001:6981: dam tshig bsrung ba ni dbyar gnas kyi nang khrims dang mi 'gal bar bya ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:6982: gsum pa dgag dbye la dus nges pa dang ma nges pa gnyis las dang po ni /
NK114(ye)001:6983: dbyar khas blangs nas zla ba gsum rdzogs pa'i dus su byed pa yin la /
NK114(ye)001:6984: gnyis pa ni rkyen dbang gis de'i sngon du byed pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:6985: ji ltar bya ba'i tshul la sbyor dngos gnyis las /
NK114(ye)001:6986: dang po la ring sbyor spyod yul du go bar bya ba sogs dang /
NK114(ye)001:6987: nye sbyor bzod par gsol nas thugs bstun pa'i bar ro //
NK114(ye)001:6988: dngos gzhi ni r+ts+wa brims nas sngags lan gsum brjod
NK114(ye)001:6989: de ltung ba'i dgag dbye byas nas rdzas kyi dgag
NK114(ye)001:6990: dbye bya ba'o // gnyis pa bde bar gnas pa rkyen gyi gzhi la /
NK114(ye)001:6991: bkres skom la sogs pa'i nad la phan pa'i bza'
NK114(ye)001:6992: btung gi bye brag rnams bsten du rung mi rung
NK114(ye)001:6993: dang ji ltar bsten pa'i tshul rnams ston pa sman
NK114(ye)001:6994: gyi gzhi dang / gos kyi bye brag la mtshan ma gdab pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:6995: kha dog bsgyur ba'i tshul sogs ston pa gos kyi gzhi dang /
NK114(ye)001:6996: gnas khang dang mal stan sogs kyi bye brag ston pa gnas mal gyi gzhi dang gsum mo //
NK114(ye)001:6997: dang po sman gyi gzhi la sman dngos dang /
NK114(ye)001:6999: dang po ni log 'tsho dang bral zhing mtha' gnyis
NK114(ye)001:7000: spang ba'i sgo nas bsgrub pa'i dri ro reg bya'i
NK114(ye)001:7006: gnyis pa rung khang ni mtshams nang yin yang zas
NK114(ye)001:7007: bco ba dang zhag lon par bzhag rung ba la
NK114(ye)001:7008: sogs pas rung ba'i khang pa zhes bya ste 'di
NK114(ye)001:7011: ba lang gi lhas lta bu gsum mo //
NK114(ye)001:7012: gnyis pa gos kyi gzhi la /
NK114(ye)001:7013: 'tsho ba'i yo byad dang 'brel ba'i gos /
NK114(ye)001:7014: bag yangs dang 'brel ba'i sra brkyang /
NK114(ye)001:7015: dmigs bsal dang 'brel ba'i ko lpags te gsum gyi
NK114(ye)001:7016: dbye bas bde bar gnas pa rkyen gyi gzhi lngar
NK114(ye)001:7018: de la dang po 'tsho ba'i yo byad dang 'brel
NK114(ye)001:7019: ba'i gos ni log 'tshos ma bsgrubs shing mtha' gnyis
NK114(ye)001:7021: dbye na rang ming gis byin gyis brlab rung gi
NK114(ye)001:7022: rigs su gnas pa'i 'tsho ba'i yo byad bcu gsum
NK114(ye)001:7023: po tshad dang ldan par dngos su grub pa dang
NK114(ye)001:7024: / rgyu'i byin rlabs 'bral spangs khegs pa'i sngags rten
NK114(ye)001:7025: chos gos gsum gang rung gi rgyur rung ba ste
NK114(ye)001:7027: gzhan ming nyid kyis brlabs pa'am yid gtad de bcang
NK114(ye)001:7028: rung gi rigs gnas snam sbyar gnyis pa lta bu
NK114(ye)001:7029: la sogs pa lhag po'i yo byad dang /
NK114(ye)001:7030: rang gzhan gnyis ka'i ming gis brlabs rung 'tsho ba'i
NK114(ye)001:7031: yo byad gang rung gi dbyibs su ma grub pa'i
NK114(ye)001:7032: gos khru gang yan chad kyi dar ras snam bu
NK114(ye)001:7033: sogs nor gyi 'du shes skye ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:7034: stod 'bogs dang 'gags ring sogs gos kyi 'du shes
NK114(ye)001:7035: skye ba mkho ba'i yo byad dang rnam pa gsum
NK114(ye)001:7036: mo // gnyis pa bag yangs dang 'brel ba sra brkyang ni /
NK114(ye)001:7037: dbyar khas blangs pa'i gnas der dgag dbye'i phyi de
NK114(ye)001:7038: nyin nas spyir btang la zla ba lnga'i yun du
NK114(ye)001:7039: dbyar snga ma khas blangs shing ma ral ba'i dge
NK114(ye)001:7040: slong rnams kyis dbyar rnyed kyi rgyu las byung zhing
NK114(ye)001:7041: dge 'dun la dbang ba'i chos gos sum phrugs gcig
NK114(ye)001:7042: yan chad cho ga sbyor dngos rjes gsum gyis bting
NK114(ye)001:7048: gos slong ba'i nyes pa rnams khegs shing /
NK114(ye)001:7049: rnyed pa thun mong du dbang ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:7050: rung ba ma byas pa'i gos 'chang du rung ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:7051: snam sbyar med par ljongs rgyur rung ba rnams so //
NK114(ye)001:7052: sra brkyang bting ba'i tshul bod du ma dar bas
NK114(ye)001:7053: sa khongs 'dzin byed du mdo tsam las dbyung ba'i
NK114(ye)001:7054: tshul ni yi ge mang bas ma smos so //
NK114(ye)001:7055: gsum pa dmigs bsal dang 'brel ba ko lpags kyi gzhi ni /
NK114(ye)001:7056: spyir yul dbus su gnas mal skyob pa'i phyir ko lpags kyi lhwam tsam dar /
NK114(ye)001:7057: gtsug lag khang las gzhan pa'i khyim du stan gzhan
NK114(ye)001:7058: med na ko lpags la 'dug pa tsam gnang gi
NK114(ye)001:7060: mtha' 'khob tu ni grang ba skyob pa'i phyir gnang
NK114(ye)001:7061: bas lhwam dang mal stan gnyis ka brten du rung
NK114(ye)001:7062: zhing / mchil lhwam khra bo dang rgyan can grang
NK114(ye)001:7063: dang stag seng rta bong sogs kyi ko ba bcang
NK114(ye)001:7064: zhing / mi rung la / bye brag yul a
NK114(ye)001:7065: smra pa r+aan+tara ni ko lpags kyi gos ci dgar
NK114(ye)001:7066: bsten pa bsgrub pa'i bslab byar gsungs so //
NK114(ye)001:7067: spyir chu la chab rom chags pa'i yul du zhwa
NK114(ye)001:7068: dang lhwam yu ba can gnyis ka gnang bar bshad
NK114(ye)001:7069: do // gsum pa gnas mal gyi gzhi la /
NK114(ye)001:7071: ngos gcig gi dbus su dri gtsang khang dang /
NK114(ye)001:7073: sgor gnod sbyin lag na rdo rje /
NK114(ye)001:7074: sgo khang du 'khor ba'i 'khor lo cha lnga pa sogs 'dri bar gsungs so //
NK114(ye)001:7075: der mal stan sogs la longs spyod pa'i tshul ni /
NK114(ye)001:7077: mi slob pa ni bdag por spyod //
NK114(ye)001:7078: slob pa byin pa spyod pa ste //
NK114(ye)001:7079: bsam gtan klog dang ldan pa ni //
NK114(ye)001:7080: rjes gnang spyod pas nyes pa med //
NK114(ye)001:7081: lhag ma le los bcom pa yi //
NK114(ye)001:7082: bdag nyid rnams ni bu lon spyod //
NK114(ye)001:7083: khrims 'chal rnams la nam du yang //
NK114(ye)001:7084: gtsug lag khang sogs nyer spyod bkag /
NK114(ye)001:7086: zhar byung phyag bya ba dang mi bya ba'i tshul ni /
NK114(ye)001:7088: rab byung gis dge slong la /
NK114(ye)001:7089: thams cad kyis sangs rgyas la'o zhes pa la sogs pa'i tshul gyis shes par bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:7090: gsum pa nyams na phyir bcos kyi gzhi bdun po bsdu na gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:7093: dang po la bzhi yod de /
NK114(ye)001:7094: dmar ser can gyi dge slong mang po la bcas pas dmar ser can phyir bcos kyi gzhi /
NK114(ye)001:7095: zla ba phyed la sogs par spo ba sbyin pas spo ba spyod pas gzhan na gnas pa'i gzhi /
NK114(ye)001:7096: gang zag re re la ltung ba bcas pa dang
NK114(ye)001:7097: ma bcabs pa dang ldang ba'i dus yin min sogs
NK114(ye)001:7098: mdor bsdus te ston pas gang zag dus dang dus
NK114(ye)001:7099: ma yin pa bsdus pa'i gzhi /
NK114(ye)001:7100: nyes pa du ma la brten te gso dgag bzhag
NK114(ye)001:7101: par bya bas gdams ngag gso dgag bzhag pa'i gazhi'o
NK114(ye)001:7102: // dang po dmar ser can la mi spro ba nan tur dang /
NK114(ye)001:7103: spro ba mthol bshags kyis phyir bcos gnyis las /
NK114(ye)001:7105: 'thab krol byed pa la gsol bzhi'i las kyis khyad
NK114(ye)001:7106: spyod spang ba'i chad las bkal kyang ma btang na
NK114(ye)001:7107: gnas nas dbyung ngo zhes bsdigs 1pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:7108: lhag ltung byung ba spo ba sogs bgyis kyang yang
NK114(ye)001:7109: yang byung na gzhan la gnas chos shig ces gnyen
NK114(ye)001:7110: po chung ba'i sgo nas dmad pa 2dang /
NK114(ye)001:7111: khyim sun 'byin pa gnas de nas ma dad pa bzlog pa'i phyir bskrad pa 3dang /
NK114(ye)001:7112: khyim pa la brnyas thabs byed pa dge 'dun gyis
NK114(ye)001:7113: mdza' gcugs kyi dngos pos sbyangs nas phyir 'gyed pa
NK114(ye)001:7115: gnas dbyung 'di la bdun yod de /
NK114(ye)001:7116: ltung ba yod kyang med do zhes smra na de
NK114(ye)001:7117: gnas nas dbyung ste de la ma mthong ba gnas
NK114(ye)001:7119: de bzhin du lhag ma sogs lhung ba byung ba
NK114(ye)001:7120: kun la grags kyang phyir mi 'chos pa dang 2
NK114(ye)001:7121: / chang btung ba la nyes pa med do zhes pa sogs sdig ltar can dang 3 /
NK114(ye)001:7122: 'thab krol byed pa la 'bad pas ma log pa dang 4 /
NK114(ye)001:7123: 'phral lus ngag btsun pa ltar byed kyang 'thab krol
NK114(ye)001:7124: gyi rgyud ma du bzung nas nye bar bsgrub pa
NK114(ye)001:7125: dang 5 / dge slong ma dang 'phyar g.yengs dang rtsa hral gyis 'dres shing gnas pa dang 6 /
NK114(ye)001:7126: chos rnam par gtan la dbab pas rtsod pa zhi
NK114(ye)001:7127: ba'i thabs byas kyang zhi bar ma gyur pa 7rnams
NK114(ye)001:7129: gnyis pa spro ba mthol bshags kyis phyir bcos pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:7130: ltung ba byung ba'i gang zag de la 'gyod sdom
NK114(ye)001:7131: gyi sems yod cing phyir bcos par spro na pham
NK114(ye)001:7132: pa 'chab med nas nyes byas kyi bar lci yang
NK114(ye)001:7133: la ltos te tshul bzhin du bshags su 'jug par
NK114(ye)001:7134: bya ba'o // gnyis pa spo ba spyod pas gzhan na gnas pa'i gzhi la /
NK114(ye)001:7137: de gnyis kyi kun spyod dang /
NK114(ye)001:7139: dang po ni gang zag khyad par can min pas
NK114(ye)001:7140: lhag ma'i ltung ba ji tsam bcabs pa'i zhag grangs
NK114(ye)001:7141: dang mnyam par spo bar bya ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:7142: spo ba byed bzhin par rigs 'dra'i lhag ma gnyis
NK114(ye)001:7143: pa byung nas bcabs na gzhi nas spo ba dang
NK114(ye)001:7144: / gsum pa byung na gzhi nas bslangs te spo ba bya zhing /
NK114(ye)001:7145: bzhi pa byung na dmad pa nan tur bya ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:7146: gnyis pa mgu ba ni lhag ltung dngos gzhi dag pa'i ched de /
NK114(ye)001:7147: dge slong gis zhag drug dang /
NK114(ye)001:7148: dge slong mas zla ba phyed dang /
NK114(ye)001:7149: lci chos las 'das pa'i phyir bcos kyang yin no //
NK114(ye)001:7150: de yang dang po mgu ba byed bzhin pa na
NK114(ye)001:7151: lhag ltung byung na gzhi nas mgu ba sogs gong
NK114(ye)001:7152: dang 'dra'o // gsum pa de gnyis kyi kun spyod ni /
NK114(ye)001:7153: bdag gir byed 1dang mnyam par spyod2 //
NK114(ye)001:7154: bla ma'i gnas 3dang chad pa'i las4 //
NK114(ye)001:7155: rten 5pa'i khyad par rnams spang ngo //
NK114(ye)001:7158: thams cad dus 5su ji ltar bsgrub //
NK114(ye)001:7159: ces pa'i khyad spyod lnga spangs shing /
NK114(ye)001:7160: dman spyod lnga dang du blang bar bya ba bslab byin dang 'dra ba las /
NK114(ye)001:7161: gzhan med na gso sbyong gi mdo 'don du rung bar gsungs /
NK114(ye)001:7164: ma la bzhi bcu'i tshogs kyis spyor ba sngon du
NK114(ye)001:7165: song nas gsol bzhi'i las kyis bkur gnas su byed
NK114(ye)001:7166: do // gsum pa gang zag gi gzhi la /
NK114(ye)001:7167: rang rgyud dang 'brel ba'i lhag ltung ngo shes sam
NK114(ye)001:7168: yid gnyis za ba mthol yul yod bzhin mtshan mtha'
NK114(ye)001:7170: ltung ba'i nyes pa byas sam ma byas dang /
NK114(ye)001:7172: bsam bzhin du byas ma byas mi shes pa dang 2 /
NK114(ye)001:7173: spo mgu spyod 'phro la khyim pa la sogs par
NK114(ye)001:7174: babs te dge slong du phyir 'ong ba na spo
NK114(ye)001:7175: mgu spyod pa de'i 'phro'i gnas skabs la babs pa
NK114(ye)001:7176: dang 3 / bcabs pa'i dus dang ltung ba'i tshad mi nges pas tshad med pa dang 4 /
NK114(ye)001:7178: gzhi nas yongs su gnas pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:7180: gzhi gnas yongs su mgu ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:7181: dbyung ba ste las kyi sde tshan lnga dang 5 /
NK114(ye)001:7182: dus dang ltung ba'i tshad ma nges pa nyung ba
NK114(ye)001:7183: nyid du mi 'gyur bar dag pa'i mtha' can zla
NK114(ye)001:7184: ba bzhi la sogs par mang po gang bcos pa
NK114(ye)001:7185: dang 6drug go // bzhi pa gdams ngag gso dgag bzhag pa'i gzhi la /
NK114(ye)001:7187: gzhi med chos ma yin pa /
NK114(ye)001:7188: de gang las byung ba'i dge 'dun no //
NK114(ye)001:7189: gnyis pa rtsod pa phyir bcos la /
NK114(ye)001:7190: dge 'dun gyi rtsod pa phal cher zhi bar bya bas rtsod pa'i gzhi dang /
NK114(ye)001:7191: yangs pa can pa dang koo sh+aam b+ai ba rnams
NK114(ye)001:7192: ma mthun par las so sor byas pa na de
NK114(ye)001:7193: la bcas pas las phye ba'i gzhi dang /
NK114(ye)001:7194: dge 'dun rnams lta ba dang ston pa tha dad
NK114(ye)001:7195: du gyur te cha gnyis su dbye ba bsdu ma
NK114(ye)001:7196: pas dge 'dun dbyen gyi gzhi dang gsum yod pa
NK114(ye)001:7197: las / dang po rtsod pa'i gzhi la /
NK114(ye)001:7201: 'dus byas rtag mi rtag lta bu rtsod pa 'gyed phyir 1dang /
NK114(ye)001:7202: gdams ngag gso dgag bzhag pa la 'jog pa po
NK114(ye)001:7203: dang bzhag bya rtsod pa lta bu mi gdams phyir
NK114(ye)001:7204: dang 2 / rtsod pa gsum gyi dbang gis gso
NK114(ye)001:7205: sbyong sogs kyi las la mthun pa mi sbyin pas
NK114(ye)001:7206: rtsod par gyur ba bya phyir dang 3 /
NK114(ye)001:7207: ltung ba gleng ba na khas mi len pa gleng
NK114(ye)001:7208: bya gleng byed rtsod pa lta bu ltung phyir rtsod
NK114(ye)001:7212: shes rab dang snying rje khyad par can rgyud la
NK114(ye)001:7213: skyes pa lta bu yin na rang gi ngang gis
NK114(ye)001:7214: zhi bar 'gyur ba yin pas mi dgos la /
NK114(ye)001:7215: de lta ma yin pa dag la ni /
NK114(ye)001:7217: de bzhin gang mang 4ngo bo nyid5 //
NK114(ye)001:7218: r+ts+wa rnams bkram pa 6lta bu dang //
NK114(ye)001:7222: rgol 1dang gzu 2dang dge 'dun bzhi pa dang 3 //
NK114(ye)001:7223: gsal ba 4dang ni gsal ba'i gsal ba 5dang //
NK114(ye)001:7225: gnas brtan mthu dang ldan pas mngon gsum mo //
NK114(ye)001:7226: zhes pa'i mngon sum brgyad dang /
NK114(ye)001:7227: dge 'dun gyis tshul shing brims te gang mang gi
NK114(ye)001:7228: phyogs la dag pa sbyin pa gang mang ste gnyis
NK114(ye)001:7229: 'jug / mi gdams phyir la ltung ba gleng rgyu yod pa la mngon sum dang /
NK114(ye)001:7233: phyir bcos zin gleng ba gsum la ni 'di la
NK114(ye)001:7234: nyes pa med do zhes dran pas 'dul ba sbyin
NK114(ye)001:7235: pa dang / smyos pas byas pa gleng ba la
NK114(ye)001:7236: ma smyos pa'i dus su ma byas pas ltung ba
NK114(ye)001:7237: med do zhes ma smyos pas 'dul ba sbyin no
NK114(ye)001:7238: pa dang / // ltung phyir la nyes par rang
NK114(ye)001:7239: gi ngo bo nyid mi shes pa la ngo bo
NK114(ye)001:7241: gleng bya gleng byed gnyis las ma 'phros na khas blangs kyis zhi ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:7242: gang zag nyi tshe ba dang 'brel ba mngon sum gyis dang /
NK114(ye)001:7243: dge 'dun mtha' dag dang 'brel ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:7244: r+ts+wa bkram pa ltar phan tshun 'dud de thams cad blo rtse mthun pas zhi bar byed do //
NK114(ye)001:7246: las la mthun pa sbyin pas dngos su zhi bar byed cing /
NK114(ye)001:7247: brgyud nas zhi byed bdun po thams cad 'jug ste
NK114(ye)001:7248: rtsod pa snga ma gsum la brten nas las la
NK114(ye)001:7249: mthun pa mi sbyin pa 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:7250: gnyis pa koo sh+aam b+ai las bye ba'i gzhi ni /
NK114(ye)001:7251: mtshams nang gcig tu chos ma yin par smra ba'i
NK114(ye)001:7252: dge slong bzhir longs bas chos smra ba'i dge 'dun
NK114(ye)001:7253: las logs su gso sbyong sogs las byas pa zin
NK114(ye)001:7254: pa na las kyi dbyen du 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:7257: dge 'dun bye ba'i dgag bya yod pa'i ltung ba gleng ba /
NK114(ye)001:7258: nan tur bsgo gyur grangs su 'jug pa sogs spang ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:7260: nang gi gnyen po dge sbyong gi chos bzhi las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:7261: phyi'i gnyen po las phye ba'i rtsod pa byung na /
NK114(ye)001:7262: dge 'dun la bzod par gsol nas /
NK114(ye)001:7263: dge 'dun gyis gsol bzhi'i las kyis bzod pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:7265: mthun pa'i gso sbyong byin nas de'i rjes su phan tshun mnyam du mthun pa'i gso sbyong bya ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:7266: gsum pa dbyen gyi gzhi la /
NK114(ye)001:7267: dge 'dun lhag mar gyur pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:7268: mtshams med du gyur ba gnyis las dang po ni /
NK114(ye)001:7269: ston pa dang mchog zung gcig 'das pa'i 'og tu
NK114(ye)001:7270: las dang po ma yin pa'i dge slong gis bslab
NK114(ye)001:7271: tshigs lnga lta bu la slob pa'i ched du tshul
NK114(ye)001:7272: shing brims pa'i las byas pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:7273: de'i tshe bzlog bsgo'i mthar ma btang na brims pa po la dbyen gyi lhag ma dang /
NK114(ye)001:7274: len pa po la de'i rjes phyogs kyi lhag mar 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:7275: mtshams med du gyur ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:7276: 'byed pa po dge slong lta spyod tshul ldan gyis /
NK114(ye)001:7277: gnas ston pa'i mdun las gzhan du /
NK114(ye)001:7279: mthar thug sangs rgyas las gzhan pa'i ston pa lhas sbyin dang /
NK114(ye)001:7280: dam chos gzhan pa lhas sbyin brtul zhugs lnga sha za mi rung ba /
NK114(ye)001:7282: dras shing drubs pa'i gos mi bgo ba /
NK114(ye)001:7283: lan tsh+wa zar mi rung ba /
NK114(ye)001:7284: dgon par gnas mi rung ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:7286: la lam du bzod cing tshul shing blangs pa ni dbye ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:7288: mchog zung gcig gis 'dums par mdzad par bshad pa de yin no //
NK114(ye)001:7290: dge 'dun phye nas ma 'dums kyi bar du ston
NK114(ye)001:7291: pa gcig gi zhing khams su lam lnga gang yang
NK114(ye)001:7292: mi skye'o // bzhi pa de thams cad la khyab pa las kyi gzhi la /
NK114(ye)001:7293: sems can du mi gtogs pa la bya ba ni mtshams che chung bcad pa sogs brgyad /
NK114(ye)001:7294: sems can du gtogs pa la'ang khyim pa dang rab byung gnyis las dang po la bya ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:7295: khyim gyi bslab sbyin lhung bzed kha sbub /
NK114(ye)001:7297: mu stegs gnas pa sbyin pa rnams so //
NK114(ye)001:7299: bsnyen par rdzogs pa la bya ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:7300: snga logs kyi sdom pa gnyis sbyin pa /
NK114(ye)001:7302: dbyar mtshams kyi phyi rol du 'gro ba'i gnang ba sbyin pa /
NK114(ye)001:7303: dge tshul bsnyil ba ste sbyin chad gnyis /
NK114(ye)001:7304: bsnyen par rdzogs pa la bya ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:7309: grangs su 'jug pa bzhi rnams so //
NK114(ye)001:7310: de thams cad la chos dang chos ma yin pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:7312: mi mthun pa'i bya ba ste snga ma gnyis bsgrub bya dang /
NK114(ye)001:7313: phyi ma gnyis spang bar bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:7314: de ltar 'jug ldog gi bslab bya rnams la blang
NK114(ye)001:7315: dor byed pa'i tshul khrims yang dag pas ni ting
NK114(ye)001:7317: de'i yan lag gi gtso bo ni sbyangs pa'i yon
NK114(ye)001:7318: tan yin pas de yang dag par blang bar bya
NK114(ye)001:7321: phyag dar khrod pa nyid dang 2 /
NK114(ye)001:7325: zas phyis mi len pa 6nyid dang /
NK114(ye)001:7331: bla gab med pa 12nyid dang bcu gnyis po yin no //
NK114(ye)001:7332: gnyis pa zhar byung rung mthun brtsi tshul ni /
NK114(ye)001:7333: bslab pa la gces spras kyis blang dor du brtson pa'i skabs 'di na /
NK114(ye)001:7335: lhag ma bcu gsum ste bcu bdun dang /
NK114(ye)001:7336: de las gzhan dud 'gro gsod pa la sogs pa
NK114(ye)001:7337: rang bzhin gyi kha na ma tho ba dang bcas
NK114(ye)001:7338: pa gnyis ka yin pa rnams la byin gyis brlabs
NK114(ye)001:7339: nas spyad du rung bar gnang ba'i skabs so thar
NK114(ye)001:7340: rang gzhung na bshad pa med la /
NK114(ye)001:7341: de ma gtogs pa'i bcas rkyang gi rigs brten du
NK114(ye)001:7342: mi rung bar gsungs pa la la dag ci nas
NK114(ye)001:7343: kyang bsrung ma nus par longs spyod dgos pa byung
NK114(ye)001:7344: na sems bskyed de byin gyis rlobsa pa'i tshul na
NK114(ye)001:7345: / 'di ltar dus ma yin par phyi dro'i kha zas dang /
NK114(ye)001:7346: byin len ma byas pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:7347: yang yang za ba la spyod dgos par gyur na spyir rang bzhin dang /
NK114(ye)001:7350: spong ba zhes pa'i tshul khrims rnam pa bzhi las
NK114(ye)001:7351: byang gi sgra mi snyan pa'i mi rnams ni rang
NK114(ye)001:7352: bzhin gyi tshul khrims can yin pas rang nyid gling
NK114(ye)001:7353: de nyid du yod par mos nas longs spyod du
NK114(ye)001:7357: tshong pa mang po dag cig gis sangs rgyas dang /
NK114(ye)001:7358: dge slong gi dge 'dun la sogs pa bshos la spyan drangs so //
NK114(ye)001:7359: de dag gis bshos sbyar te bro sar bskyal nas
NK114(ye)001:7360: ma drangs kyi bar du tshong khang du me shor
NK114(ye)001:7361: te / de dag me gsod du song ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:7362: gdugs tshod yol la thug nas dge slong dag gis
NK114(ye)001:7363: ji ltar gyur ba bcom ldan 'das la gsol ba
NK114(ye)001:7364: dang / bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK114(ye)001:7365: de'i sems kyis yongs su btang bas na /
NK114(ye)001:7366: dge slong dag de la the tshom ma byed par bza' bar bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:7367: zos nas byang gi sgra mi snyan gyi dus su byin gyis rlobs shig /
NK114(ye)001:7370: byin lan ma bstabs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:7371: rung bar ma byas pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:7372: dus ma yin par za ba la sogs pa rung
NK114(ye)001:7373: bar bya ba dag las rtsom 'dod na byang gi
NK114(ye)001:7374: sgra mi snyan dag na grags pa yid la byed
NK114(ye)001:7375: pa bya'o // zhes gsungs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:7376: de bzhin du nad la phan pa'i ched du dus
NK114(ye)001:7377: ma yin par zla ba phyed ma song bar khrus
NK114(ye)001:7378: byed dgos par gyur ba la bdag ni nad pa
NK114(ye)001:7379: yin pas na ba'i nyes pa de dang de la
NK114(ye)001:7380: phan pa'i phyir gnang ba yin snyam pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:7381: gos lhag po gcig gam gnyis la sogs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:7382: kha dog gis rung ba ma yin pa'i bgo ba dkar po la sogs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:7383: ko ba'i lhwam dang stan la sogs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:7384: lug lpagsa la sogs par longs spyod dgos pa na /
NK114(ye)001:7385: de la sems bskyed tshul ni da lta gos stan
NK114(ye)001:7386: 'di rnams nam 'dod 'dod du mi rnyed pas phongs
NK114(ye)001:7388: gal te ma rnyed bzhin du longs ma spyad na
NK114(ye)001:7389: grang bas nyam thag par gyur te dge sbyor dang
NK114(ye)001:7390: srog gi yang bar chad du 'gyur bas de dag
NK114(ye)001:7391: bsrung ba'i slad du gnang ba yin no snyam du
NK114(ye)001:7392: bsam pa dang / rin po che la reg pa
NK114(ye)001:7393: dang bdag gir bya dgos na dkon mchog gsum la
NK114(ye)001:7394: mchod pa'i phyir yin snyam pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:7395: sems can rnams gso ba dang de la phan pa
NK114(ye)001:7396: bsgrub pa'i slad du gan nga ba yin par bsgom
NK114(ye)001:7398: de dag las gzhan dngos su gnang ba yang med
NK114(ye)001:7399: pa bkag pa yang med pa rnams la spang blang
NK114(ye)001:7400: ji ltar bya ba ni gnang bkag gang gi rjes
NK114(ye)001:7401: su mthun brtsi ba yin te /
NK114(ye)001:7403: dge slong dag ngas khyed la 'dul ba rgya cher ni bstan na /
NK114(ye)001:7404: mdor bsdus te ma yin no //
NK114(ye)001:7405: 'on kyang mdor bsdus pa yang nyon cig /
NK114(ye)001:7406: dge slong dag ngas khyed la gang zhig thog ma
NK114(ye)001:7407: nyid nas gnang ba yang med bkag pa yang med
NK114(ye)001:7408: pa de / gal te rung ba dang nye zhing
NK114(ye)001:7409: ma rung ba bzlog par byed pa yin na ni
NK114(ye)001:7410: rung ba yin par bzung bar bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:7411: gal te mi rung ba dang nye ba yin zhing
NK114(ye)001:7412: rung ba bzlog par byed pa yin na ni mi
NK114(ye)001:7413: rung ba yin pas kun tu spyad par mi bya'o
NK114(ye)001:7415: mdor bsdu na ston pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK114(ye)001:7416: 'og tu nyan thos sde pa bco brgyad du gyes
NK114(ye)001:7417: pa rtsa ba'i sde pa gnyis sam bzhi yin te
NK114(ye)001:7418: / gnyis ni dang po'i gyes gzhi gnas brtan pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:7420: bzhi ni de'i steng du gzhi thams cad yod par smra ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:7421: mang pos bkur ba gnyis bsnan pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:7422: de yang rgyal rigs sgra gcan 'dzin gyi brgyud pa thams cad yod par smra ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:7423: bram ze 'od srung chen po'i brgyud pa phal chen sde pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:7424: smyig mkhan k+aa t+y+aa na'i brgyud pa gnas brtan pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:7425: 'dreg mkhan nye bar 'khor gyi brgyud pa mang pos
NK114(ye)001:7426: bkur ba ste bzhi las bod 'dir dar che ba
NK114(ye)001:7427: thams cad yod par smra ba yin zhing /
NK114(ye)001:7428: de dag gi bslab pa'i rnam pa 'ga' zhig la
NK114(ye)001:7429: mi mthun pa cung zad yod na'ang rgyal po kri
NK114(ye)001:7430: ki'i rmi ltas dang mthun par bkar bsdus pa'i phyir
NK114(ye)001:7431: na sde pa bzhi ka'i bslaba pa thams cad rab
NK114(ye)001:7432: byung sde lnga'i spyod pa dang 'brel zhing de la
NK114(ye)001:7433: ston pa sangs rgyas kyis gnang bkag gi mtshams ji
NK114(ye)001:7434: ltar bstan pa'ii bcas pas ma khyab pa mi srid
NK114(ye)001:7435: pas na rang gang gi sde par gtogs pa de'i
NK114(ye)001:7436: bslab pa'i rnam pa la tshul bzhin du gnas na
NK114(ye)001:7437: bslab pa kun la dbang thob par byed pa yin
NK114(ye)001:7438: pas nan tan du bsrung ba gal che'o //
NK114(ye)001:7439: ma bsrung ba'i nyes dmigs ni /
NK114(ye)001:7441: dam chos thos par mi 'gyur la //
NK114(ye)001:7442: thos pa myur du brjed par 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:7443: sa lam rtogs pa'ang yongs mi skye //
NK114(ye)001:7445: pham lhag sogs ltung ba sde lnga pos rim par
NK114(ye)001:7446: tsha ba nas yang sos kyi bar skye bar 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:7447: ba'i tshul mdo sde nas gsungs so //
NK114(ye)001:7449: 'jigs skyob dang legs smon gyi tshul khrims tsam gyis
NK114(ye)001:7450: 'khor ba las thar bar mi 'gyur yang gnas skabs
NK114(ye)001:7451: su gang gi don du bsrung ba'i don de thob
NK114(ye)001:7455: rab basngagasa nor ni phun tshogs shing //
NK114(ye)001:7456: lha yi khang bzang dam par skye //
NK114(ye)001:7458: khyad par nges 'byung gi bsam pas zin pa'i so
NK114(ye)001:7459: thar gyi tshul khrims mtshan nyid pa bsrung ba'i phan
NK114(ye)001:7461: dge slong la rab tu gces pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:7462: shin tu legs par tshul khrims gang //
NK114(ye)001:7463: bsdams pa'i mi de mdzes pa'i gzugs //
NK114(ye)001:7464: 'dul ba la ni nye bar gnas //
NK114(ye)001:7465: tshul khrims bslab par rang yid ches //
NK114(ye)001:7466: mi de nyi ma gcig la yang //
NK114(ye)001:7467: bsod nams phung po dpag tu med //
NK114(ye)001:7471: lha rdzas dga' rgyu mi yi longs spyod dang //
NK114(ye)001:7472: bde mchog ro mchog lha yi phun sum tshogs //
NK114(ye)001:7473: tshul khrims rgyus byung ci zhig ngo mtshar che //
NK114(ye)001:7474: sangs rgyas chos rnams de las byung la ltos //
NK114(ye)001:7476: de yang dang po nas mtha' gnyis las nges par
NK114(ye)001:7477: 'byung ba'i bsam pa byang chub sems kyis zin pa
NK114(ye)001:7478: zhig yin na theg chen so thar du 'gyur bas
NK114(ye)001:7479: byang chub chen po'i dngos rgyu yin pa smos mi
NK114(ye)001:7480: dgos kyang / theg dman gyi bsam pas bsrung na
NK114(ye)001:7481: yang mthar sangs rgyas thob pa'i brgyud 'gyur te mthar
NK114(ye)001:7482: thug theg pa gcig tu grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:7483: bye brag tu ni bstan pa yar ldan gyi dus
NK114(ye)001:7484: su bslab gzhi yongs su rdzogs pa bsrungs pa las
NK114(ye)001:7485: / da lta bstan pa 'grib la nye ba'i dus
NK114(ye)001:7486: 'dir nyin zhag gcig gi bar du bslab gzhi sna
NK114(ye)001:7487: gcig bsrung ba phan yon che ste /
NK114(ye)001:7489: bskal pa bye ba gang+g+aa'i bye snyed du //
NK114(ye)001:7490: dang ba'i sems kyis zas dang skom rnams dang //
NK114(ye)001:7491: gdugs dang ba dan mar me'i phreng ba yis //
NK114(ye)001:7492: sangs rgyas bye ba phrag khrig rim gro byas //
NK114(ye)001:7493: gang zhig dam chos rab tu 'jig pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:7494: bde gshegs bstan pa 'gag par 'gyur ba'i tshe //
NK114(ye)001:7495: nyin zhag tu ni bslab pa gcig spyod pa //
NK114(ye)001:7496: bsod nams 'di ni de bas khyad par 'phags //
NK114(ye)001:7498: gnyis pa sdom pa gsum ldan du bsrung tshul gyi mtha' dpyad pa la gsum ste /
NK114(ye)001:7499: rang bzhed rgyas par bzhag pa /
NK114(ye)001:7500: bzhed srol gzhan gyi gnad bsdu tshul /
NK114(ye)001:7501: gang zag gi rgyud tshod dang sbyar nas nyams su len tshul gyis mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:7503: mya ngan zhes bya ba sdug bsngal te 'bras bu
NK114(ye)001:7504: 'khor ba'i rang bzhin rgyu las nyon dang bcas pa
NK114(ye)001:7505: yin la / de las 'da' ba ni sdug kun
NK114(ye)001:7506: gyi rgyun 'gog pa'i zhi ba dam pa'i go 'phang
NK114(ye)001:7507: yin la / ste / nyan rang gi byang chub
NK114(ye)001:7508: yin zhing der bsngo ba ni de'i ched du blangs
NK114(ye)001:7509: pa yin pas bsam pa de lta bus 'dul ba'i
NK114(ye)001:7510: las chog la brten nas so thar rigs bdun gang
NK114(ye)001:7511: rung gi sdom pa blangs te nyon mongs pa dang
NK114(ye)001:7512: mi dge ba'i phyogs spong sems kyis sdom pa ni
NK114(ye)001:7513: mngon mtho tsam don du gnyer nas bsrung ba las
NK114(ye)001:7514: lhag pa'i so thar gyi tshul khrims mtshan nyid pa
NK114(ye)001:7515: yin la / ste / yin zhing / de'i steng
NK114(ye)001:7516: du rang don du thar pa nyi tshe ba tsam
NK114(ye)001:7517: don du gnyer ba'i blo de na 'phar nas mtha'
NK114(ye)001:7518: yas pa'i sems can gzhan la phan pa rgya chen
NK114(ye)001:7519: po bsgrub pa'i phyir rdzogs pa'i byang chub thob par
NK114(ye)001:7520: 'dod pas srol gnyis gang rung gi cho ga la
NK114(ye)001:7521: brten nas smon 'jug gi sdom pa blangs te dge
NK114(ye)001:7522: ba'i chos mtha' dag rgyun chags par sdud pas sems
NK114(ye)001:7523: can la phan 'dogs pa ni byang sdom yin la
NK114(ye)001:7524: yin la / ste / yin zhing / / da
NK114(ye)001:7525: dung de'i steng du thabs zab mos gzhan la phan
NK114(ye)001:7526: pa rlabs po che myur du bsgrub par 'dod pa'i
NK114(ye)001:7527: kun slong gi rgyud sde chen po'i dgongs pa ma
NK114(ye)001:7528: nor ba'i sngags kyi cho ga las dbang bskur nod
NK114(ye)001:7529: de bskyed rdzogs zab mo'i don la mos pa brtan
NK114(ye)001:7530: por gyur ba yan chad kyi rig pa 'dzin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:7531: sdom pa rnal ma zhig thob na sngags sdom mtshan
NK114(ye)001:7532: yin la / ste / yin zhing / / nyid
NK114(ye)001:7533: pa ste / de ltar sdom pa gsum po de
NK114(ye)001:7534: gang zag gcig gi rgyud la rdzogs pa'i tshe na
NK114(ye)001:7535: spang blang gi bslab bya yang rang rang gi skabs
NK114(ye)001:7536: nas ji skad bshad pa bzhin bsrung dgos pas shin
NK114(ye)001:7537: yin la / ste / yin zhing / / nyid
NK114(ye)001:7538: pa ste / tu mang la / bsrungs pa'i phan
NK114(ye)001:7539: yon yang theg pa dman mchog dang /
NK114(ye)001:7540: mchog gi yang mdo sngags gnyis kar ji skad bshad
NK114(ye)001:7541: pa'i lam dang 'bras bu'i yon tan mtha' dag 'thob
NK114(ye)001:7542: par 'gyur ba'i phyir shin tu mang ngo //
NK114(ye)001:7543: gsum pa de bar du ji ltar gnas pa yin zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:7544: ngo bo gnas gyur pa'i tshul gyis gcig tu gyur pas rdzas tha dad pa med la /
NK114(ye)001:7545: ldog pa thob la ma nyams pa'i tshul du yod
NK114(ye)001:7546: pas ma 'dres par tha dad du gang zag gcig
NK114(ye)001:7547: gi rgyud la rang rang gi gtong rgyu ma byung
NK114(ye)001:7548: gi bar du gnas pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:7549: de ltar ldog pa tha dad par yod pa'i gnad
NK114(ye)001:7550: kyis so sor ma 'dres par bsrung dgos shing gal
NK114(ye)001:7551: te so thar du mi gsod pa lta bu pham
NK114(ye)001:7552: par bshad pa'i spang bya de /
NK114(ye)001:7553: byang sems la rjes su gnang bar gsungs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:7554: sngags bla med kyi skabs su rdo rje'i rigs kyi
NK114(ye)001:7555: dam tshig tu dang du blang bar bshad pa lta
NK114(ye)001:7556: bu nang 'gal ba can du byung ba rnams la
NK114(ye)001:7558: gzhan phan gyi bsam pa khyad par can 'byongs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:7559: bskyed rdzogs kyi gdeng dang ldan pa dag la dgongs
NK114(ye)001:7560: nas gong ma byang sems dang sngags kyi lugs gtso
NK114(ye)001:7561: bor bton dgos pa'i tshul sngon chad byon pa'i mkhas
NK114(ye)001:7562: pa dang grub pa rnams kyi lugs la grags pa
NK114(ye)001:7563: yin la / de'i gnad kyang 'di yin te 'og
NK114(ye)001:7564: ma so so thar pa'i skabs kyi bslab pa'i rnam
NK114(ye)001:7565: pa dang 'gal ba srog gcod pa la sogs pa
NK114(ye)001:7567: so thar skabs srog la mi 'tshe ba la sogs
NK114(ye)001:7568: pa tsam gyis pha rol po la gnod pa spong
NK114(ye)001:7569: zhing phan 'dogs pa'i dgos pa bsgrub la byang chub
NK114(ye)001:7570: sems dpas sdig can gang dag bsad par byas na
NK114(ye)001:7571: de'i las ngan rgyun chad nas sdug yun thung bar
NK114(ye)001:7572: gyur te gnod pa spong ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:7574: thar pa'i sa bon 'jog pa sogs phan 'dogs rgya
NK114(ye)001:7575: chen po bsgrub pa yin pa'i phyir gnyis po dgos
NK114(ye)001:7576: pa mthun par ma zad gong ma dgos don lhag
NK114(ye)001:7577: par che la rgyu mtshan des na byed pa po
NK114(ye)001:7578: byang sems de la nyes pa mi 'byung bar ma
NK114(ye)001:7579: zad tshogs kyang rdzogs par 'gyur te dge sdig thams
NK114(ye)001:7580: cad gzugs brnyan tsam la ma ltos par bsam pa'i
NK114(ye)001:7581: bye brag gis 'jog dgos pa'i phyir na byang sems
NK114(ye)001:7582: de gzhan la gnod pa'i bsam pa las log pa'i
NK114(ye)001:7583: steng snying rje chen po'i dbang gis byas pa yin
NK114(ye)001:7584: pa'i phyir ro // de ltar yang spyod 'jug las /
NK114(ye)001:7585: thugs rje mnga' ba ring gzigs pas //
NK114(ye)001:7586: bkag pa rnams kyang de la gnang //
NK114(ye)001:7588: de'i phyir ston pa thabs la mkhas pas khams dang
NK114(ye)001:7589: mos pa sna tshogs pa'i 'gro ba 'dul ba'i dbang
NK114(ye)001:7590: gis gsungs pa'i bslab pa'i gzhi gang zhig don gyi
NK114(ye)001:7591: ngos nas 'gal ba 'du ba zhig yin na rjes
NK114(ye)001:7592: su gnang bar mi srid de /
NK114(ye)001:7593: las dang po pa rang don yid byed kyi bsam
NK114(ye)001:7594: pa yang ma log cing 'dod yon dang nyon mongs
NK114(ye)001:7595: rang rgyud par 'chor ba'i gnas skabs na gsang sngags
NK114(ye)001:7596: la kha g.yar nas sbyor sgrol la sogs pa byeed
NK114(ye)001:7597: na 'ching bar 'gyur bas de 'dra ba la gnang
NK114(ye)001:7598: ba med pa lta bu yin la /
NK114(ye)001:7599: gang zag mchog rnams la lus ngag gi mi dge
NK114(ye)001:7600: ba ltar snang ba'i spyod pa rnams la spyad par
NK114(ye)001:7601: gnang ba yin na rnam pa tsam las don la
NK114(ye)001:7602: 'gal bar mi srid de bshad ma thag pa ltar
NK114(ye)001:7603: ro // des na shes bya thams cad mngon sum
NK114(ye)001:7604: du gzigs pa'i mkhyen pa mnga' ba de bzhin gshegs
NK114(ye)001:7605: pas drang nges kyi chos sna tshogs pa bstan pa
NK114(ye)001:7606: thams cad kyi dgongs gnad de bzhin nyid gcig tu
NK114(ye)001:7607: 'bab cing gzhol ba'i chos can yin pa ni rtogs
NK114(ye)001:7608: par bya ba'i gnas chen po ste /
NK114(ye)001:7610: koon+di nya ngas ni gzugs kyi de bzhin nyid 'ba' zhig gsungs na /
NK114(ye)001:7611: la las ni gzugs stong zhes bya bar thos /
NK114(ye)001:7612: la las ni gzugs mi stong zhes bya bar thos /
NK114(ye)001:7613: la las ni gzugs bde zhes bya bar thos /
NK114(ye)001:7614: la las ni gzugs sdug bsngal zhes bya bar thos zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pas so //
NK114(ye)001:7615: khyad par du gsang sngags kyi lta sgom rmad du
NK114(ye)001:7616: byung ba dang 'brel ba'i spyod pa ni 'di ltar
NK114(ye)001:7617: yin te / bslab pa phyogs gcig gi dpes mtshon na /
NK114(ye)001:7618: gang zhig ltung na nyan thos pa la ltung byed du 'gyur ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:7619: byang chub sems dpar de dang phyogs mthun pa'i nyes
NK114(ye)001:7620: byas su 'gyur ba'i myos byed chang gi dngos po
NK114(ye)001:7621: de sngags kyis dam tshig gi rdzas su med du
NK114(ye)001:7624: ma h+aa m+aam sa bdud rtsir bcas //
NK114(ye)001:7625: med du mi rung dngos grub rdzas //
NK114(ye)001:7627: 'dod pa'i yon tan thams cad do //
NK114(ye)001:7629: khyad par sha chang med mi rung //
NK114(ye)001:7631: de la longs spyod par byed pa'i gang zag gi rim pa yang /
NK114(ye)001:7632: sngags sdom dang ldan phyin chad /
NK114(ye)001:7633: rab byung las dang po ba zhig yin kyang tshogs
NK114(ye)001:7634: 'khor la sogs pa'i dus su ha cang dngos por
NK114(ye)001:7635: zhen pa'i dbang gis theg pa 'og ma'i dge sbyor
NK114(ye)001:7636: la 'thas te chang la sogs pa'i dam rdzas rnams
NK114(ye)001:7637: khyad gsod kyis spong na rtsa ltung bcu gsum pa'i
NK114(ye)001:7638: rgyur 'gyur pas na gong ma'i sgom spyod la mos
NK114(ye)001:7639: pa lam byed kyis cung zad re bsten dgos par
NK114(ye)001:7640: gsungs shing / 'on kyang bslab pa 'og ma khyad
NK114(ye)001:7641: gsod kyi bsam pas yin na rtsa ltung gnyis par
NK114(ye)001:7642: gsungs shing / yang 'gyur la / sgra ji bzhin
NK114(ye)001:7643: par dus thams cad du spang blang med par spyod
NK114(ye)001:7644: pa'i skyes bu'i rang bzhin ni bskyed rdzogs kyi thabs
NK114(ye)001:7645: kyis rtog tshogs thams cad lhar shar bas mtshan ma'i
NK114(ye)001:7646: rtog pa zil gyis gnon nus pa zhig yin gsungs
NK114(ye)001:7647: gsungs shing / yang 'gyur la / te / de
NK114(ye)001:7648: yang spyir tshogs lam na mos pa'i lha sku zhes
NK114(ye)001:7649: bya ba rnam rtog gi gzugs brnyan lhar snang ba'i
NK114(ye)001:7650: bskyed rim tsam zhig rdzogs rim gyi ye shes rjes
NK114(ye)001:7651: mthun pa dang zung du 'brel ba yod la /
NK114(ye)001:7652: sbyor lam du ni rlung sems kyi lha sku zhes
NK114(ye)001:7653: rnam rtog gis ched du bskyed pa ma yiin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:7654: mtshan bcas kyi rdzogs rim goms pa'i stobs las sgyu
NK114(ye)001:7655: ma lta bu'i lha skur ldang ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:7656: mthong lam du ni 'od gsal gyi lha sku zhes
NK114(ye)001:7657: pa mtshan ma med pa'i rdzogs rim gyi ngo bo
NK114(ye)001:7658: don gyi ye shes mngon du gyur te ye shes
NK114(ye)001:7659: de'i rang gdangs 'gag med du lha'i skur shar ba
NK114(ye)001:7660: ste de yan chad sgom lam gyi gnas skabs kun
NK114(ye)001:7661: tu slob pa'i zung 'jug gi lha sku zhes bya
NK114(ye)001:7662: la / sangs rgyas pa'i tshe ni chos gzugs kyi
NK114(ye)001:7663: sku zung du 'jug pa la mi slob pa'i zung
NK114(ye)001:7665: des na sngags lam pas sbyor mthong sgom gsum du smos ci dgos kyang /
NK114(ye)001:7666: tshogs lam du gnas pa bskyed rim pas kyang dam
NK114(ye)001:7667: rdzas khyad par can chang la sogs pa cis mi
NK114(ye)001:7668: spyod de / sngags nang pa'i dag mnyam gyi lta
NK114(ye)001:7669: ba khyad par can gyis zin pa'i sgom pa thams
NK114(ye)001:7670: cad kyi grogs su gzung 'dzin la dor ba'i spyod
NK114(ye)001:7671: pa 'gro dgos pa'i phyir na bskyed pa'i thabs kyis
NK114(ye)001:7672: phung khams sogs lha dang gzhal yas khang du gsal
NK114(ye)001:7673: ba'i ngang nas sngags dang phyag rgya ting nge 'dzin
NK114(ye)001:7674: gyis chang la sogs pa'i dam rdzas bdud rtsir byin
NK114(ye)001:7675: gyis brlabs nas spyod pa'i tshe na gzhi chang dang
NK114(ye)001:7676: bsam pa chags sred gnyis ka rang mtshan mi 'dzin
NK114(ye)001:7677: par gzhan dag pa lha dang bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin
NK114(ye)001:7678: du 'du shes gnas 'gyur ba yin zhing /
NK114(ye)001:7679: der ma zad sngags bla med kyi lugs la bskyed
NK114(ye)001:7680: rdzogs gnyis kyi zlas phye ba'i bskyed rim bsgom pa'i
NK114(ye)001:7681: gnas skabs su'ang dgongs pa mi 'gyur ba'i gzer chos
NK114(ye)001:7682: nyid kyi lta ba dang zung 'jug tu yod pas
NK114(ye)001:7683: sbyor ba bag med pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:7684: mthar thug myos pa la sogs pa'i nyes pa thams
NK114(ye)001:7685: cad lhag mthong rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes
NK114(ye)001:7686: chen pos zil gyis non pas nyes pas mi gos
NK114(ye)001:7687: shing theg pa 'og mas spang byar bltas te ma
NK114(ye)001:7688: brten pa las lam yang myur ba ni thabs shes
NK114(ye)001:7689: gnyis po khyad du 'phags pas yin te /
NK114(ye)001:7691: gsang sngags tshul chen shin tu rmad byung ni //
NK114(ye)001:7692: lam gyi nang nas nye lam chen po ste //
NK114(ye)001:7693: thabs kyi nang nas ma nor dam pa nyid //
NK114(ye)001:7694: shes rab nang nas shes rab khyad par can //
NK114(ye)001:7696: de 'dra ba'i rnal 'byor pa de la ni rang
NK114(ye)001:7697: don du spang blang la dngos por zhen nas bdag
NK114(ye)001:7698: dge slong yin no snyam pa'ang yod pa ma yin
NK114(ye)001:7699: la / gzhan gyi don du sbyin sogs kyi spyod
NK114(ye)001:7700: pa la tha snyad du mtshan mar bltas te bdag
NK114(ye)001:7701: byang chub sems dapa'o snyam pa'i dngos por zhen pa'ang
NK114(ye)001:7703: de ni nyon mongs dang 'dod yon lam du byed
NK114(ye)001:7704: pa'i thabs dang bral nas chags sred spong bar byed
NK114(ye)001:7705: pa'i nyan thos lta bu dang /
NK114(ye)001:7706: nyon mongs pa'i mthus non te 'khor bar 'phen byed
NK114(ye)001:7707: kyi las gsog pa'i so skye phal pa lta bu
NK114(ye)001:7708: yang min par bskyed rdzogs zab mo'i rnal 'byor gyis
NK114(ye)001:7709: gang snang ba'i phyi nang gi chos mtha' dag lha
NK114(ye)001:7711: spyad par bya ba'i dam rdzas chang la sogs pa'ang
NK114(ye)001:7712: bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin du 'du shes gnas 'gyur ba
NK114(ye)001:7713: yin pas / de lta bu'i gang zag de la
NK114(ye)001:7714: gnang ba yin te nyes pas mi gos par ma
NK114(ye)001:7715: zad so so thar pa'i lam gyi sdom khrims la
NK114(ye)001:7716: yin pas / gnas pa dang / dag mnyam ma
NK114(ye)001:7717: rtogs par gzhan don la brtson pa'i byang chub sems
NK114(ye)001:7718: yin pas / gnas pa dang / dpa' yis /
NK114(ye)001:7719: dge slong dang ni dge 'dun rnams la zas gos
NK114(ye)001:7720: sogs byin na phan yon rgya che yang /
NK114(ye)001:7721: de las kyang rnal 'byor pa rang gis dam rdzas
NK114(ye)001:7722: bsten na dkon mchog gsum ka dang yi dam gyi
NK114(ye)001:7723: lha la dngos su phul ba yin te /
NK114(ye)001:7726: bden don bden pa'i rang bzhin de nyid gzigs //
NK114(ye)001:7727: rnal 'byor pa de dkon mchog gsum dngos nyid //
NK114(ye)001:7730: srid gsum 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK114(ye)001:7731: phung po khams dang skye mched dang //
NK114(ye)001:7732: brjod med brjod kyis mi lang ba //
NK114(ye)001:7734: mngon rdzogs rgyal por de nyid nges //
NK114(ye)001:7735: gnyis med lhun grub dkyil 'khor na //
NK114(ye)001:7736: thams cad bdag nyid rtag par bzhugs //
NK114(ye)001:7737: zhes pa'i don rtogs shing thabs ldan du spyad pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:7738: des ni rdo rje phung po'i grong khyer nyams brtas
NK114(ye)001:7739: shing rtsa rlung thig le'i kha stobs su gyur pas
NK114(ye)001:7740: bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs pa sogs lam gyi yon
NK114(ye)001:7741: tan thams cad kyang yar ldan du 'gyur ba yin
NK114(ye)001:7742: pas nyon mongs dang 'dod yon lam du byed pa'i
NK114(ye)001:7743: bslab pa'i cha shas gzhan phra rags thams cad la'ang
NK114(ye)001:7744: de yis rigs 'gre sbyar nas shes par bya dgos
NK114(ye)001:7745: te rang dgar spyad na rgyud 'ching zhing thabs ldan
NK114(ye)001:7746: du spyad na don che ba'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:7747: des na nang 'gal ba rnams gong ma gtso bor ston pa'i tshul de ltar yin mod /
NK114(ye)001:7748: 'on kyang sdom pa gsum ka thob pa'i gang zag
NK114(ye)001:7749: las dang po pa rnams kyis kyang gsum ka'i bslab
NK114(ye)001:7750: pa ci nus su bsrung dgos pa de'i phyir rang
