NK114(ye)001:9171: de bas bzod la nan tan du //
NK114(ye)001:9172: sna tshogs tshul gyis bsgom par bya //
NK114(ye)001:9174: khyad par du 'dis bdag la 'di lta bu'i gnod
NK114(ye)001:9175: pa byas so zhes gnod pa'i yul du bzung zhing
NK114(ye)001:9176: brtags pas ni bzod pa mi 'grub pas rang sems
NK114(ye)001:9178: 'di ltar bdag la mi rigs shing mi 'os par
NK114(ye)001:9179: snang ba thams cad la skyon du bltas nas de
NK114(ye)001:9180: thams cad bzlog pa'i thabs la 'bad na ni de
NK114(ye)001:9181: 'dra ba'i gnod pa'i yul ni dpag tu med de
NK114(ye)001:9182: / dper na nags tsher ma can du phyin nas
NK114(ye)001:9183: rang la mi gnod pa'i phyir shing thams cad kyi
NK114(ye)001:9184: tsher ma med par byed 'dod na 'dzad du med
NK114(ye)001:9185: / pas na / de bas der ma phyin na mi gnod pa bzhin /
NK114(ye)001:9186: gnod pa'i yul de thams cad gdul gyis mi lang
NK114(ye)001:9187: ste 'ga' zhing btul 'ga' zhig la mthun par byas
NK114(ye)001:9188: kyang rang gi kun rtog gis bskyed pa'i gnod yul
NK114(ye)001:9189: mang po slar yang kun nas 'phel bar 'gyur ba
NK114(ye)001:9190: can yin pas zad du med de /
NK114(ye)001:9192: bze re can la gnod mang zhing //
NK114(ye)001:9194: de bas na phan tshun mi 'dod pa'i bsam pas 'khon pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:9195: de'i dbang gis khro bo'i kun rtog bzod dka' bas
NK114(ye)001:9196: rang gzhan kun gyi rgyud ma rungs par 'gyur ba
NK114(ye)001:9197: thams cad kyi byed pa po ni thog mar yul
NK114(ye)001:9198: la mi 'dod pa'i rnam par bzung nas nye bar
NK114(ye)001:9199: len pa'i sems yid mi bde ba 'byung ba de
NK114(ye)001:9200: yin pas de nyid gcig pu shed ma rgyas gong
NK114(ye)001:9201: du phag sna gtun brdung dang /
NK114(ye)001:9202: rkong bu dro phyis zhes pa'i dpe ltar btul bar
NK114(ye)001:9203: byas na bzod pa'i dka' thub ces mi theg pa'i
NK114(ye)001:9204: khur chen po de yang bdag la mdza' bar 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:9205: ba'i phyir gang la yang khro mi dgos pa zhig
NK114(ye)001:9206: 'ong bas na / da lta nas ha cang gnod
NK114(ye)001:9207: pa chen po la bzod ma nus na'ang chung ngu
NK114(ye)001:9208: nas goms par byas na mthar gyis thams cad la
NK114(ye)001:9210: de skad du yang spyod 'jug las /
NK114(ye)001:9211: sems can mi bsrun nam mkha' bzhin //
NK114(ye)001:9212: de dag gzhom gyis yong mi lang //
NK114(ye)001:9213: khro ba'i sems 'di gcig bcom na //
NK114(ye)001:9214: dgra de thams cad chom dang 'dra //
NK114(ye)001:9216: de ltas bdag gi dgra bo de'i //
NK114(ye)001:9217: zas ni rnam par gzhom par bya //
NK114(ye)001:9219: 'o na gnod pa'i rkyen thams cad rang gi kun
NK114(ye)001:9220: rtog gi nye bar len pa la brten nas 'byung
NK114(ye)001:9221: ba'i tshul ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:9222: 'di ltar pha rol pos rang la skyon mtshang nas
NK114(ye)001:9223: brjod pa lta bu'i tshig ngan zhig smras pa na
NK114(ye)001:9224: / yul de'i smras pa'i tshig de dang /
NK114(ye)001:9225: rang gi rna ba'i dbang po dang shes pa gnyis
NK114(ye)001:9226: te gsum po phrad cing reg pa'i tshe tshor ba
NK114(ye)001:9227: shin tu rtsub pa'i rang bzhin du tshig gi rnam
NK114(ye)001:9229: dper na madsa skyes bu'i gnad la bsnun pa ltar /
NK114(ye)001:9230: snying tshal par 'gas pa tsam du sdug bsngal nas mi bzod pa drag po skye na'ang /
NK114(ye)001:9231: brtag na tshig de ni brag ca bzhin yin pas
NK114(ye)001:9232: snying la zug pa ltar snang ba de la dngos
NK114(ye)001:9233: su zug 'gro rgyu zhig cang mchi'am ste ci yang
NK114(ye)001:9234: med do // 'o na ci zhe na tshig de
NK114(ye)001:9235: nyid rang la gnod pa'i ngo bor dang du blang
NK114(ye)001:9236: ba'i nyer len sgra don 'dres 'dzin gyi rtog pas
NK114(ye)001:9237: yang yang myang bas phan tshun gnod bya dang gnod
NK114(ye)001:9238: byed rten dang brten par gyur nas khong 'khrugs bzhin
NK114(ye)001:9239: du des bskyed pa'i sdug bsngal gyis mnar bar 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:9240: bas na de 'dra ba'i rtog dpyod kyi rjes su
NK114(ye)001:9241: mi 'brang bar ci snang yang ci thos kyang btang
NK114(ye)001:9242: snyoms su bzhag nas bag yangs su gnas par bya
NK114(ye)001:9244: ci la bab kyang bdag gis ni //
NK114(ye)001:9245: dga' ba'i yid ni dkrugs mi bya //
NK114(ye)001:9247: 'on kyang rtog dpyod kyi sgo nas gnyen po brten
NK114(ye)001:9248: pa dag gis ni 'di ltar srid pa'i gnas 'di
NK114(ye)001:9249: na rang la gnod pa'i rgyu gzhan gyis byas pa
NK114(ye)001:9250: ltar snang ba'i brdung brdeg dang longs spyod phrog pa
NK114(ye)001:9251: dang / ngan smras brjod pa sogs dang /
NK114(ye)001:9252: de dag gis bskyed pa'i 'bras bu lus dang sems
NK114(ye)001:9253: sdug bsngal ba'i rnam grangs zad pa med par mtha'
NK114(ye)001:9254: yas pa rnams su snang ba ji snyed pa thams
NK114(ye)001:9255: cad / bdag nyid las byung ba yin pa ni
NK114(ye)001:9256: dper na skyes bu ca co'i sgra bsgrags pa dang
NK114(ye)001:9257: brag ca 'byung ba bzhin yin te /
NK114(ye)001:9258: spyir bdag nyid ma byung ste gtan nas med na
NK114(ye)001:9259: pha rol pos gnod pa bya ba'i yul med la
NK114(ye)001:9260: / khyad par du tshe snga ma'am da lta'i gnas
NK114(ye)001:9261: skabs su sngon la rang gis rang la gnod pa'i
NK114(ye)001:9262: rgyu ma bsgrubs na des gnod pa'i 'bras bu 'byin
NK114(ye)001:9264: rang gisa sngon byas pa'i rkyen gyis gnod byed de'i
NK114(ye)001:9265: rgyud bskul ba lta bu'i sgo nas bos te gnod
NK114(ye)001:9266: pa sna tshogs pa 'di 'byung ba yin no zhes
NK114(ye)001:9267: de lta bu'i tshul la sems shing ltos la le
NK114(ye)001:9268: lan thams cad rang la gda' bar gyis shig ces
NK114(ye)001:9270: bdag gis sngon chad sems can la //
NK114(ye)001:9272: de bas sems can 'tshe byed pa //
NK114(ye)001:9275: gnod byed phan pa'i rkyen du brtag pa yang /
NK114(ye)001:9276: spyir theg pa che chung gi yon tan thams cad bzod pa'i gzhi las byung ba'i tshul /
NK114(ye)001:9278: bdag kyang nges par snga ma'i sdig /
NK114(ye)001:9279: bsdug bsngal rnam smin 'di myong snyam //
NK114(ye)001:9280: bden bzhi dran dang yang dag spong //
NK114(ye)001:9281: dbang stobs byang chub yan lag lam //
NK114(ye)001:9282: thams cad bzod pas gzhi byed pas //
NK114(ye)001:9283: mkhas pa su zhig bzod mi bsgom //
NK114(ye)001:9285: bzod pa de ni gnod byed kyi rkyen las 'grub
NK114(ye)001:9286: pas brtag na gnod pa chen po byas pa ma
NK114(ye)001:9287: yin par phan chen po btags pa yin te /
NK114(ye)001:9288: 'di ltar dper na rang gzhan thams cad la phan
NK114(ye)001:9289: pa'i rkyen yo byad thams cad zad med du bsgrub
NK114(ye)001:9290: 'dod pas gzings la brten nas rgya mtsho'i pha rol
NK114(ye)001:9291: tu song na nor bu rin po che thob nas
NK114(ye)001:9292: ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin 'ong ba de ltar /
NK114(ye)001:9293: gnod pa byed pa'i dgra gang la brten nas theg
NK114(ye)001:9294: chen gyi rgya mtshor bgrod pa'i bzod pa'i gru gzings
NK114(ye)001:9295: dang / de la brten nas byang chub sems kyi
NK114(ye)001:9296: nor bu rin po che rang gzhan thams cad 'phral
NK114(ye)001:9297: dang yun gyi bde ba dam pa'i rgyu 'thob par
NK114(ye)001:9298: dang / 'gyur gyi / de las gzhan du khong
NK114(ye)001:9299: khro ba ma sdang zhing ci yang bzod mi nus
NK114(ye)001:9300: bzhin byang chub sems dpa' yin par rlom pa ni
NK114(ye)001:9301: me la bsil ba'i reg bya bzhin du 'gal bas
NK114(ye)001:9302: na legs par rang rgyud la brtag dpyad btang nas
NK114(ye)001:9303: theg chen gyi lam la zhugs nas byang chub sems
NK114(ye)001:9304: dpa'i ming zhig 'dzin par 'dod na bzod pa 'di
NK114(ye)001:9305: la thog mar nan tan du bya dgos gsungs /
NK114(ye)001:9306: lar 'jig rten pa rnams kyis 'di skad du /
NK114(ye)001:9307: dge slong ngam bla ma bzang po zhig yin te thugs khro che zhes zer yang /
NK114(ye)001:9308: skyon gcig la khong khro las thu ba med na /
NK114(ye)001:9309: de yod tshe dge slong ngam bla ma ji ltar bzang gsungs /
NK114(ye)001:9310: de bas na don chen po bzod pa'i rgyur gyur
NK114(ye)001:9311: pa de 'dra ba'i gnod pa byed pa'i dgra de
NK114(ye)001:9312: la khong mi khro bar ma zad bsod nams kyi
NK114(ye)001:9313: zhing du bsam nas dam pa'i chos ltar mchod par
NK114(ye)001:9315: de lta bas na b+ham ga la'i pan+di ta rtag
NK114(ye)001:9316: tu khro ba ldon pa'i a tsa ra dang 'grogs
NK114(ye)001:9317: nas 'di kho bo'i bzod pa'i rten lags so zhes
NK114(ye)001:9318: gsungs pa ltar gnod byed che chung thams cad phan
NK114(ye)001:9319: pa'i rkyen du brtags nas blo sbyong ba'i tshul 'di
NK114(ye)001:9320: ni theg chen lam gyi gnad che shos zhig yin
NK114(ye)001:9321: pas yang yang zlos par byas so //
NK114(ye)001:9322: de yang legs smon sngon du song ba'i skal ba
NK114(ye)001:9323: bzang po dang ldan pa rnams la ni gnod pa
NK114(ye)001:9324: dang sdug bsngal ci byung yang snying rje la sogs
NK114(ye)001:9327: gzhan yang sdug bsngal yon tan ni //
NK114(ye)001:9328: skyo bas dregs pa sel bar byed //
NK114(ye)001:9329: 'khor ba pa la snying rje skye //
NK114(ye)001:9330: sdig la 'dzin zhing dge la dga' //
NK114(ye)001:9332: yang chos la nges sems kyi bzod pa'i rkyen du 'gro ba'i thabs su brtag pa'i tshul ni /
NK114(ye)001:9333: 'di ltar don dam dpyod byed kyi rigs pas grub
NK114(ye)001:9334: ma grub kyi rang bzhin la shin tu brtags shing
NK114(ye)001:9335: dpyad na rang la gnod par 'gyur ba'i dngos po'i
NK114(ye)001:9336: ngo bo de gnod byed yul gyi steng na 'dug
NK114(ye)001:9337: gam / des byas pa'i las kyi steng na 'dug gam /
NK114(ye)001:9338: gnod bya rang gi steng na 'dug ces brtags na
NK114(ye)001:9339: gzhan gang na'ang mi 'dug ste sngar bshad pa bzhin
NK114(ye)001:9340: rkyen sna tshogs pa na rang gi nye bar len
NK114(ye)001:9341: pa'i sems kyis blo bur du bzos pa yin la
NK114(ye)001:9342: / sems de yang brtags na mtshan nyid rgyun chags
NK114(ye)001:9343: su 'dzin pa'i nus pa med de dper na chu
NK114(ye)001:9344: yi ri mo ni mod la byung kyang mod la
NK114(ye)001:9345: med par 'gyur ba bzhin 'du byed kyis bsdus pa
NK114(ye)001:9346: / / rnam par rtog pa dang bcas pa'i khro
NK114(ye)001:9347: gnyer rtsub mo rgyud dkrugs par byed pa'i ma rungs
NK114(ye)001:9348: pa de rang tshugs ma thub par zhig pa'i mod
NK114(ye)001:9349: la nam mkhar sprin dengs pa ltar khro ba'i sems
NK114(ye)001:9350: byung lhag ma ma lus pa zhi bar 'gyur te
NK114(ye)001:9352: ji ltar nam mkha' cung zad sprin med la //
NK114(ye)001:9353: glo bur du ni sprin gyi dkyil 'khor dag /
NK114(ye)001:9354: byung nas zhig ste sprin gyi dkyil 'khor med //
NK114(ye)001:9355: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par gyis //
NK114(ye)001:9357: de'i tshe sems kyi rang bzhin nam mkha' rnam par
NK114(ye)001:9358: dag pa bzhin du rnam par rtog pa thams cad
NK114(ye)001:9359: dang bral ba'i ye stong chen por gnas pa la
NK114(ye)001:9360: thob shor ram blang dor gang yang med pa de'i
NK114(ye)001:9361: ngang bskyangs te rkyen gyi dbang du ma song bar
NK114(ye)001:9362: bya ba 'di yang zab mo dbu ma'i lam gyis
NK114(ye)001:9363: nyon mongs chos nyid du sbyangs zhes pa de yin
NK114(ye)001:9364: la / chos la nges sems kyi bzod pa yang de la zer ro //
NK114(ye)001:9366: sa'i snying po 'khor lo bcu pa las /
NK114(ye)001:9367: 'du byed thams cad rab tu zhi zhing //
NK114(ye)001:9368: rtog pa thams cad yongs su spangs te //
NK114(ye)001:9369: sems ni nam mkha' 'dra bar mnyam pa //
NK114(ye)001:9370: bzod pa 'di la thams cad gtod 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:9373: mos pas spyod pa ba ni sgra'i rjes su 'gro ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:9374: ma dag sa bdun la ni rjes su mthun pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:9375: sa brgyad pa la sogs par ni mi skye ba'i chos bzod pa'o zhes spyod 'grel las bshad do //
NK114(ye)001:9376: des na sangs rgyas chos kyi sku'i dngos rgyu /
NK114(ye)001:9377: rgyal sras byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi lam po
NK114(ye)001:9378: che shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i don
NK114(ye)001:9379: zab mo 'di la blo kha tsam phyogs su yod
NK114(ye)001:9380: pa 'di yang shin tu skal ba bzang ba yin
NK114(ye)001:9381: par shes par byas nas ci nus su go yul
NK114(ye)001:9382: tsam du ma lus par nyams su len pa la
NK114(ye)001:9383: 'bad par bya'o // gsum pa skabs kyi mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:9384: de ltar bzod par byas na yid bde ba las
NK114(ye)001:9385: mi nyams shing dge ba'i phyogs thams cad brtan la
NK114(ye)001:9386: gzhan kun gyis byams shing yid du 'ong ba la
NK114(ye)001:9387: sogs pa dang / tshe rabs thams cad du yang
NK114(ye)001:9388: log par mi ltung zhing gzugs bzang ba la sogs
NK114(ye)001:9389: pa mngon mtho'i dpal gyis 'byor zhing mthar nges par
NK114(ye)001:9390: legs pa'i go 'phang la sbyor bar byed pa'i phan
NK114(ye)001:9391: yon chen po dang ldan pa yin la /
NK114(ye)001:9392: gal te bzod par ma nus na de las bzlog
NK114(ye)001:9393: pa'i nyes dmigs dpag tu med cing khyad par theg
NK114(ye)001:9394: chen gyi lam la bar du gcod par 'gyur ba'i
NK114(ye)001:9395: skyon de las thu ba med de gang gi phyir
NK114(ye)001:9396: zhe na / 'di ltar bzod pa'i dka' thub gsum las /
NK114(ye)001:9397: dang po dka' ba dang du len pa'i bzod pa
NK114(ye)001:9398: yang spyir dam pa'i chos nyams su len pa de
NK114(ye)001:9399: gnad du ma song na bar chad mang po mi
NK114(ye)001:9400: 'byung yang / gnad du song ba'i thar lam rnal
NK114(ye)001:9401: ma zhig bsgrub na gnas 'pho khar bu lon ldang
NK114(ye)001:9402: 'byung yang / ba ltar / phyi dgra bgegs /
NK114(ye)001:9404: gsang ba nyon mongs pa rnams slong nas gnod pa
NK114(ye)001:9405: dang sdug bsngal mang po bstud mar 'byung bar gsungs
NK114(ye)001:9406: la / khyad par da lta snyigs ma'i dus 'dir
NK114(ye)001:9407: ni bde ba'i rkyen nyung zhing sdug bsngal gyi rkyen
NK114(ye)001:9408: shin tu mang bas rkyen de'i dbang gis sems sran
NK114(ye)001:9409: ma tshugs par dge ba'i phyogs la brtson pa lhod
NK114(ye)001:9410: na mar me rlung gseb tu bzhag pa bzhin rkyen
NK114(ye)001:9411: chung ngus kyang gnod par 'gyur zhing /
NK114(ye)001:9412: rkyen ngan dang sdug bsngal ci byung yang khyad du
NK114(ye)001:9413: bsad de sems stobs bskyed na nags chen la me
NK114(ye)001:9414: 'bar na rlung chen grogs su 'gro ba bzhin mi
NK114(ye)001:9415: gnod par ma zad lam gyi grogs su 'gyur bas
NK114(ye)001:9416: na sdug bsngal thams cad dang du blang bar bya'o
NK114(ye)001:9417: // phyogs gnyis pa gnod byed la ci mi snyam pa'i bzod pa med na /
NK114(ye)001:9418: gzhan dge ba'i rtsa ba rgya chen po ci yod kyang mi skyob ste /
NK114(ye)001:9419: zla ba sgron ma'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:9420: phan tshun gnod pa'i sems su gang byed pa //
NK114(ye)001:9421: de la tshul khrims thos pas skyob mi byed //
NK114(ye)001:9422: bsam gtan dang ni dgon gnas mi skyob ste //
NK114(ye)001:9423: sbyin dang sangs rgyas mchod pa'ang skyob mi byed //
NK114(ye)001:9425: phyogs gsum pa chos nyid la nges par sems pa'i bzod pa med na /
NK114(ye)001:9426: snga ma gnyis yod kyang 'jig rten pa'i lam tsam
NK114(ye)001:9427: las 'phags mi nus pas de rnams nyams shing med
NK114(ye)001:9428: na sbyin pa la sogs pa'i pha rol tu phyin
NK114(ye)001:9429: pa gzhan lnga po dang rjes su mthun pa tsam
NK114(ye)001:9430: grub pa'i las dang po pa'i skabs 'dir longs spyod
NK114(ye)001:9431: gtong ba dang / tshul khrims bsrung ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:9432: dge ba'i phyogs la brtson pa lhur len pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:9433: sems rtse gcig pa'i bsam gtan la mnyam par 'jog pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:9434: thos pa dang bsam pa'i shes rab bskyed pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:9435: de lta bu'i dge ba'i phyogs ji tsam bzang yang
NK114(ye)001:9436: dper na phyi mtha' thams cad dgra rkun dang gcan
NK114(ye)001:9437: gzan du ma yis bskor ba'i bshul lam la dpung
NK114(ye)001:9438: gnyen med par zhugs te song na rang 'dod pa'i
NK114(ye)001:9439: sar phyin dka' ba de bzhin du sbyin sogs de
NK114(ye)001:9440: dag la brten nas lam dang 'bras bu'i yon tan
NK114(ye)001:9442: ji ltar 'dod pa'i don de thob pa'i gnas su
NK114(ye)001:9443: phyin pa ni shin tu dka' bas rang gis rang
NK114(ye)001:9444: la bskul ma gdab nas blo'i stobs bskyed de bsgom
NK114(ye)001:9445: par bya'o // spyir phar phyin mtshan nyid pa ni
NK114(ye)001:9446: sa thob pa rnams la yod pas de rnams la
NK114(ye)001:9447: bzod pa med pa'i skyon gyis gzhan nyams par 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:9450: khyad par las dang po pa rnams la gdams pa yin pa'i tshul 'di khong du chud par bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:9451: bzhi pa brtson 'grus kyi pha rol du phyin pa bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:9455: brtson 'grus kyi ngo bo dge ba la mngon par spro ba'i sems rtse gcig pa yin pas /
NK114(ye)001:9456: dus skad cig tsam yang rang gis don du gnyer bya thos bsam dang /
NK114(ye)001:9457: bslab gsum gyi nyams len gyi don de las gzhan
NK114(ye)001:9458: du yol ba med pa'i spro ba shugs drag po
NK114(ye)001:9459: dang bcas pa'i gus sbyor dang spro ba rgyun mi
NK114(ye)001:9460: 'chad pa'i rtag sbyor gyi brtson 'grus kyi rang dbang
NK114(ye)001:9461: nyid du bsgrub bya dge ba'i chos ji snyed pa
NK114(ye)001:9462: mtha' dag dper na skyed mos tshal du /
NK114(ye)001:9463: 'brog dgon par sgo nga la gab pas yid gdung
NK114(ye)001:9464: ba'i ngang pa khyo shug bu'i nus pa rdzogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:9465: tshe tsham tshom dang phyi bshol med par 'gro ba
NK114(ye)001:9466: ji lta ba bzhin du le lo rnam pa gsum
NK114(ye)001:9467: po'i g.yang sa la dge ba'i phyogs bskyud pa ste
NK114(ye)001:9468: brjed nas lus pa med par ched du bya ba
NK114(ye)001:9469: la 'jug pa rgyun mi 'chad pa nyid du bya'o
NK114(ye)001:9470: // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:9471: brtson 'grus kyi mi mthun pa'i phyogs bshad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:9473: dang po ni 'di ltar bdag cag gis theg pa
NK114(ye)001:9474: che chung gi sde snod mang po zhig mnyan te
NK114(ye)001:9475: bsgrub par khas blangs kyang don la gtugs tsa na
NK114(ye)001:9476: / thos bsam dang nyams len thams cad kyi bya
NK114(ye)001:9477: ba rgyang du bor nas 'jig rten phal pa'i bya
NK114(ye)001:9478: ba ngan pa de da dung 'phro ma chod par
NK114(ye)001:9479: khyim chung spangs nas khyim chen bzung ste /
NK114(ye)001:9480: tshong dang g.yo sgyu'i mgo skor /
NK114(ye)001:9481: rta phyugs sems can gyi 'tsho skyong /
NK114(ye)001:9483: gnas khang dang mkhar las kyi bya bzhag /
NK114(ye)001:9484: bza' btung dang longs spyod kyi zhen chags la sogs
NK114(ye)001:9485: pa'i dbang gis skye bo mang po'i 'du long dang
NK114(ye)001:9486: / 'dzi ba ni 'dzings pa ste gnyen la chags pas 'brel /
NK114(ye)001:9488: longs spyod la gsog bsrung spel ba'i las kyis 'brel
NK114(ye)001:9489: te de dag gi gseb nas mi thar ba dper
NK114(ye)001:9490: na srin bu'i kha chu'i thag pas rang nyid dkris
NK114(ye)001:9491: te de ru 'khums nas 'chi ba bzhin lha chos
NK114(ye)001:9492: bsgrub 'dod tsam zhig yod kyang brel ngo de'i ngang
NK114(ye)001:9493: du mi tshe zad nas 'chi khar brang lag 'thab
NK114(ye)001:9494: nas chos med du 'chi ba de lta bu dang
NK114(ye)001:9495: / dka' ba'i gnas cung zad mthong bas bdag gis
NK114(ye)001:9496: 'di lta bu bsgrub mi nus so snyam du sgyid
NK114(ye)001:9497: lug pa'i le lo'i mthus non te /
NK114(ye)001:9498: dge ba'i bya ba de la dang por sbyor bas
NK114(ye)001:9499: nus pa'ang btang ste phyi bshol du lus pa dang
NK114(ye)001:9500: / yang 'jig rten pa'i bya ba la brtson pa'i
NK114(ye)001:9501: dus su ni dka' tshegs dang tsha grang la sogs
NK114(ye)001:9502: pa'i gnod pa ci byung yang sran tshugs par byas
NK114(ye)001:9503: nas 'bad rtsol ri bo tsam byed dgos pa la
NK114(ye)001:9504: yang sems mi zhum pa'i snying stobs chen po yod
NK114(ye)001:9505: pa de chos kyi phyogs la bskor dus ni bdag
NK114(ye)001:9506: gis bdag nyid brnyas nas ngas mi shes /
NK114(ye)001:9507: ngas mi nus snyam nas bong chad gyen la ded
NK114(ye)001:9508: pa bzhin sems zhum pa'i brtul zhugs dang du blangs
NK114(ye)001:9509: pa des ni rang gi chos skal rang gis bcad
NK114(ye)001:9510: pa yin te / dper na rin po che'i gling
NK114(ye)001:9511: du mi mang po phyin tsa na thob chen po
NK114(ye)001:9512: pa yin te / 'tshengs / chung thob chung ngus 'tshengs par gyur na'ang /
NK114(ye)001:9513: mi gcig pu zhig ci yang ma lon par lag stong du phyir log pa bzhin /
NK114(ye)001:9514: lung dang rtogs pa'i dam chos ci dgar rang rgyud
NK114(ye)001:9515: la len du yod pa'i gnas 'dir skyes pa don
NK114(ye)001:9516: med du gyur nas snang ba nas mun pa'i gnas
NK114(ye)001:9517: su 'gro dgos pa'i stong log mkhan de lta bur
NK114(ye)001:9520: zhum bcas rtsol ba dor ba la //
NK114(ye)001:9521: phongs las thar pa yod dam ci //
NK114(ye)001:9523: des na de 'dra ba'i gang zag de rnams ni
NK114(ye)001:9524: le lo gsum gyi nyes pa'i mtsho ru bying nas
NK114(ye)001:9525: thar ba'i skam sar thon pa'i dus med de /
NK114(ye)001:9526: dper na lcags gzer zhig pa'i gzings la zhon na chu'i ngogs su mi phyin pa bzhin no //
NK114(ye)001:9527: gnyis pa brtson 'grus dngos bshad pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:9528: lam gang bsgrub kyang dang po nas lus ngag gi
NK114(ye)001:9529: bya ba la zhugs pa tsam gyis mi 'ong ste
NK114(ye)001:9530: snying stobs chen pos dam bca' ba gal che bas
NK114(ye)001:9531: / 'di ltar theg pa chen po'i lam la zhugs
NK114(ye)001:9532: nas rang gzhan gyi don bsgrub par 'dod pa dag
NK114(ye)001:9533: / gis / de'i gegs su gyur pa'i bdud bzhi'i
NK114(ye)001:9534: dpung thams cad 'joms par byed pa la dpa' bo
NK114(ye)001:9536: go cha sra ba bgos na pha rol gyi mtshon
NK114(ye)001:9537: gyis mi phigs pa bzhin blo stobs kyi go cha
NK114(ye)001:9539: thar pa la bar du gcod pa'i bdud nyon mongs
NK114(ye)001:9540: pa'i rtog pa brgyad khri bzhi stong po'i nang nas
NK114(ye)001:9541: 'dod chags lta bu gcig spang ba'i phyir yang bskal
NK114(ye)001:9542: pa rgya mtsho'i bar du ngal ba brgya phrag gi
NK114(ye)001:9543: sgo nas brtson dgos kyang dam bca' mi 'dor ba
NK114(ye)001:9544: dang / ting 'dzin la bar du gcod pa'i lha bdud la mtshon na /
NK114(ye)001:9545: bdag lam gyi dka' thub la gnas pa'i tshe 'khor los sgyur rgyal gyi mnga' thang dang snyan grags /
NK114(ye)001:9546: 'khor dang 'byor pa lta bu yod kyang bdag gis
NK114(ye)001:9547: dge ba'i phyogs la brtson pa'i yid skad cig tsam
NK114(ye)001:9548: yang mi lhod cing 'gyur bar mi bya snyam du
NK114(ye)001:9549: dam bcas na / tshe la bar du gcod pa'i 'chi bdud dang /
NK114(ye)001:9550: lhag med la bar du gcod pa'i phung bdud 'joms
NK114(ye)001:9551: pa'i go cha shugs la 'ong bas de ltar dam
NK114(ye)001:9552: bca' ba dang / yang gzhan don du 'di ltar
NK114(ye)001:9553: bskal pa chen po grangs med pa'i grangs bye ba
NK114(ye)001:9554: snyed kyis gzhal ba'i bar du sems can gcig gi
NK114(ye)001:9555: sdug bsngal ba'i phyir du sems can dmyal ba chen
NK114(ye)001:9556: po kho nar gnas nas rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu
NK114(ye)001:9557: 'gro bar 'gyur na'ang de'i brtson 'grus kyi mtha' mi
NK114(ye)001:9558: gtong na de las gzhan du smos ci dgos snyam
NK114(ye)001:9559: bca' ba dang / pa dang / mdor na theg
NK114(ye)001:9560: pa chen po'i sde snod rnams nas ji skad bstan
NK114(ye)001:9561: pa'i zab pa dang rgya che ba'i chos ji snyed
NK114(ye)001:9562: yod pa de thams cad kyi brjod don ma lus
NK114(ye)001:9563: pa thams cad bdag gi khong du chud par byas
NK114(ye)001:9564: nas nyams su blang bar bya snyam du dam bca'
NK114(ye)001:9565: bca' ba dang / pa dang / bar bya ste / phar phyin bsdus pa las /
NK114(ye)001:9566: 'khor tshe rang gi sdug bsngal sems btang zhing //
NK114(ye)001:9567: go cha brtan pa dpag yas de bskyed na //
NK114(ye)001:9568: brtul zhugs dpa' bo snying rje'i ngang can la //
NK114(ye)001:9569: yang dag blangs pa dang po yin par brjod //
NK114(ye)001:9571: de ltar dam bca' ba'i snying stobs kyi go cha
NK114(ye)001:9572: de dang ma bral ba'i sgo nas mthar thug gi
NK114(ye)001:9573: ched du bya ba sangs rgyas kyi sa'i spangs rtogs
NK114(ye)001:9574: phrin las gsum yongs su rdzogs par byed pa'i thabs
NK114(ye)001:9575: sdom sdud gzhan phan gyi tshul khrims gsum gyis bsdus
NK114(ye)001:9576: pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa bcu yis 'phags pa'i
NK114(ye)001:9577: sa bcu'i ngo bo mthar phyin par byed pa la
NK114(ye)001:9578: slob lam bzhi po'i 'gros kyis bsgrod dgos pas na
NK114(ye)001:9579: / las dang po pas nyes spyod sdom pa /
NK114(ye)001:9580: de nas mos spyod pas dge ba chos sdud /
NK114(ye)001:9581: 'phags sa thob nas sems can don byed kyi tshul
NK114(ye)001:9582: khrims la gtso che bar bslab pa'i tshul ji skad
NK114(ye)001:9583: bshad pa bzhin / da lta las dang po pa'i
NK114(ye)001:9584: gnas skabs nas kyang dngos su sdom pa'i tshul khrims
NK114(ye)001:9585: dang gzhan gnyis la'ang ci nus su sbyor ba'i sgo
NK114(ye)001:9586: nas rim gyis lam lnga'i yon tan mtha' dag mthar
NK114(ye)001:9587: phyin par byed pa'i brtson 'grus rtsom pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:9588: gtso bo gzhan don du lam bsgrub par dam bcas
NK114(ye)001:9589: nas dngos su brtson pa'i bsam sbyor gnyis po de
NK114(ye)001:9590: slar je zhan du song nas mi 'gong ba dang
NK114(ye)001:9591: / ded dpon slong ldan gyis sems can gyi dbul
NK114(ye)001:9592: ba sel ba'i don du rin po che'i gling nas
NK114(ye)001:9593: nor bu blangs pa rgya tsho'i gting du lhung ba
NK114(ye)001:9594: las rgya tsho'i chu snyims pas dor te bskam par
NK114(ye)001:9595: 'dod pa lta bu thog mar dam bcas pa de
NK114(ye)001:9596: rkyen gang gis kyang bar ma dor mi ldog pa
NK114(ye)001:9597: zhig dgos par gsungs la da lta rang re snyigs
NK114(ye)001:9598: ma'i skye bo rnams kyis ni spyir dge ba'i phyogs
NK114(ye)001:9600: cung zad yod kyang blo stobs dman pas yun thung ngu tsam dang /
NK114(ye)001:9601: dge rtsa phra ba re tsam las dam 'cha' mi nus pas zhan pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:9602: gal te glo bur du nges 'byung la sogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:9603: dge ba'i kun slong re skyes nas sdom pa zhu
NK114(ye)001:9604: ba dang / dge sdig la blang dor gyi khas
NK114(ye)001:9605: len dang dam bca' tsam byas kyang dam bca' lhod
NK114(ye)001:9606: ba dang / pa'i dbang dang / khrel dang ngo
NK114(ye)001:9607: tsha chung ba'i stobs kyi rkyen phra ba tsam gyis
NK114(ye)001:9608: kyang 'jig rten pha rol phar zhog /
NK114(ye)001:9609: da lta gzhan gyis khrel zhing mi kha dang gtam
NK114(ye)001:9610: ngan 'byung ba'i tshul la'ang cang mi sems par sdom
NK114(ye)001:9612: khas len dang dam bca' nyams par 'gyur ba'i tshul
NK114(ye)001:9613: 'di la bsam nas nyi ma re re bzhin dam
NK114(ye)001:9614: bca' yang len byas nas blang dor gyi gnas la
NK114(ye)001:9615: 'bad par ma byas na sdug bsngal dang nyon mongs
NK114(ye)001:9616: pa 'di zad pa'i mthar nam zhig phyin te /
NK114(ye)001:9618: nyin mtshan phyed par ma 'bad na //
NK114(ye)001:9619: bdag gi sdug bsngal nam mthar phyin //
NK114(ye)001:9621: de ltar bsam sbyor gnyis kyi sgo nas lam bsgrub
NK114(ye)001:9622: pa la zhugs pa na lam gyi yon tan ci
NK114(ye)001:9623: byung yang de tsam gyis 'ong ngo snyam du chog
NK114(ye)001:9624: shes pa ni med pa zhig dgos te /
NK114(ye)001:9625: skyon ci tsam ma spangs yon tan ci tsam rgyud
NK114(ye)001:9626: la skyes kyang da dung skyon kun zad yon tan
NK114(ye)001:9627: kun ldan sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang ma thob par
NK114(ye)001:9628: du skyon spang du yod cing /
NK114(ye)001:9629: yon tan gong ma bsgrub tu yod pas brtson pa mi 'dor par bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:9630: lar da lta rab byung gi gzugs brnyan 'dzin pa
NK114(ye)001:9631: rnams kyis ston pa'i rjes 'jug tu khas 'che na'ang
NK114(ye)001:9632: chog shes byed dgos par gsungs pa'i 'jig rten pa'i
NK114(ye)001:9633: nor dang longs spyod la ni ci tsam yod na'ang
NK114(ye)001:9634: chog shes pa med par dug zhig rnyed kyang gsog
NK114(ye)001:9636: chog shes mi rung bar gsungs pa'i chos ni gzhung
NK114(ye)001:9637: gcig tsam la bslab gnyer byas na de tsam gyis
NK114(ye)001:9639: bsrung sdom sna re bsrung na de tsam gyis chog
NK114(ye)001:9640: snyam pa 'di tsho ni blang dor go nor ba
NK114(ye)001:9641: yin pas de'i tshul shes dgos gsungs /
NK114(ye)001:9642: des na gong du ji skad bshad pa yi brtson
NK114(ye)001:9643: 'grus bslab gsum gyi grogs su bsten pa can gyi
NK114(ye)001:9644: lam sgrub pa po dag gis ni rlung gis shing
NK114(ye)001:9645: bal la dbang bsgyur ba bzhin yid la ji ltar
NK114(ye)001:9646: smon pa'ii gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi rang gzhan
NK114(ye)001:9647: gyi don kun 'grub pa ni gdon mi za'o //
NK114(ye)001:9648: khyad par du tshe la long med du bsam pa
NK114(ye)001:9649: ni brtson 'grus kyi yan lag le lo'i gnyen po
NK114(ye)001:9650: yin pas 'di ltar bsam par bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:9651: bdag gi tshe 'di la ni nyin mo'i snang ba
NK114(ye)001:9652: bzhin gnyen dang mdza' bshes nor dang longs spyod sogs
NK114(ye)001:9654: tshe 'dzad pa'i tshul ni nya ma nub kyii ri
NK114(ye)001:9655: la phyogs nas mgyogs par 'gro ba bzhin skad cig
NK114(ye)001:9656: skad cig gis zad cing mthar thug par gyur te
NK114(ye)001:9657: myur ba myura bar grib so tshur tshur 'ong nas
NK114(ye)001:9658: mun rub pa bzhin 'chi ba'i mun nag gis gtugs
NK114(ye)001:9660: tshe ni nyi ma bzhin du phar phar 'gro //
NK114(ye)001:9661: 'chi bdag grib so bzhin du tshur tshur 'ong //
NK114(ye)001:9663: de'i tshe na mi 'di shi ba'i rjes su longs
NK114(ye)001:9664: spyod 'di dag gis 'di ltar bya'o zhes gnyen grogs
NK114(ye)001:9666: yo byad kyi bgo bsha' sogs byed pa'i tshul yad
NK114(ye)001:9667: yud du mthong ba'i 'khor ba'i spyod pa 'jig rten
NK114(ye)001:9668: pa'i bya bzhag mtshan mo'i rgyu skar las kyang rnama
NK114(ye)001:9669: grangs mang ba zhig yod pa yin na'ang /
NK114(ye)001:9670: rang la dbang zhing rjes su 'brang ba ni gcig kyang med cing /
NK114(ye)001:9671: rang byas kyi dge ba zhig med na shul mi
NK114(ye)001:9672: rnams kyis longs spyod mchod sbyin sogs byas kyang de
NK114(ye)001:9673: kho na yis bar do'i 'jigs skrag la sogs pa
NK114(ye)001:9676: gshin rje'i pho nyas zin pa la //
NK114(ye)001:9677: gnyen gyis ci phan bshes ci phan //
NK114(ye)001:9678: de tshe bsod nams gcig skyabs na //
NK114(ye)001:9679: de yang bdag gis ma bsten to //
NK114(ye)001:9681: tshul de lta bu la bsam nas brtson 'grus rtsom pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:9683: mago'am gos la glo bur me shor na //
NK114(ye)001:9684: de dag bzlog slad bgyi ba btang nas ni //
NK114(ye)001:9685: yang srid med par bgyi slad 'bad 'tshal te //
NK114(ye)001:9686: de bas ches mchog dgos pa gzhan ma mchis //
NK114(ye)001:9687: zhes brtson 'grus la bskul ba'i gtam myur ba'i mthar thug pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:9688: de bas na le lo dang ma 'dres pa'i brtson 'grus rtsom dgos pa'i tshul ni /
NK114(ye)001:9690: nyon mongs kun gyi gzhi gcig ni //
NK114(ye)001:9691: le lo yin te gang la yod //
NK114(ye)001:9692: gang la le lo gcig yod pa //
NK114(ye)001:9693: de la chos kun med pa yin //
NK114(ye)001:9695: le lo'i skyon dang bcas nas /
NK114(ye)001:9696: chu mig chung ngu 'dam gyi rnyog pa can dag
NK114(ye)001:9697: ni char 'babs pa la sogs pa'i tshe na rgyun
NK114(ye)001:9699: dus gzhan du rgyun chad pa'am phyogs gcig tu 'khyil ba bzhin /
NK114(ye)001:9700: res 'ga' brtson yang le lo'i dbang gis rgyun chad
NK114(ye)001:9701: nas theg gsum gyi lam gang yang mi 'grub pa'am
NK114(ye)001:9702: / khyad par theg pa chen po'i lam gyi mi
NK114(ye)001:9703: mthun pa'i phyogs rang don tsam la zhen nas lam
NK114(ye)001:9704: bsgrub kyang zhi ba phyogs gcig pa'i mthar lhung nas
NK114(ye)001:9705: 'gog pa'i dbyings su bag chags phra ba dang bcas
NK114(ye)001:9706: pa'i sems kyi rgyun 'khyil ba las rnam mkhyen gyi
NK114(ye)001:9708: skyon de dag gis dwangs pa'i brtson 'grus kyi grogs
NK114(ye)001:9709: dang bcas nas lam gyi bgrod pa'i tshul dal 'bab
NK114(ye)001:9710: ste chu chen po'i rgyun kha 'bab kyi chu bo
NK114(ye)001:9711: chen po bzhi lta bu ni chu phran phyogs su
NK114(ye)001:9712: lhung nas skams par gyur ba'am 'khyil bar ston pa
NK114(ye)001:9713: de lta bu ma yin par rgya mtsho chen por
NK114(ye)001:9714: ngang gis 'bab pa bzhin rnam pa thams cad kun
NK114(ye)001:9715: mkhyen ba'i ye shes kyi rgya mtsho chen por phyin
NK114(ye)001:9716: pa de srid du rtag par thang lhod med pa'i
NK114(ye)001:9717: gus sbyor dang rtag sbyor gyi brtson 'grus kyis 'bras
NK114(ye)001:9718: bu'i sar g.yo zhing myur ba'i sgo nas bgrod pa'i
NK114(ye)001:9719: brtul zhugs nyams par mi bgyid do //
NK114(ye)001:9722: mgo la sems can khur chen khyer ba yi //
NK114(ye)001:9723: byang chub sems dpa' dal gyis 'gro mi mdzes //
NK114(ye)001:9724: bdag gzhan sna tshogs 'ching bas rab bcings pas //
NK114(ye)001:9725: brtson pa brgya 'gyur du ni bya ba'i rigs //
NK114(ye)001:9727: lnga pa bsam gtan gyi pha rol tu phyin pa bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:9728: bsam gtan 'grub pa'i rgyu tshogs bshad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:9731: nags tshal gyi gnas la basngagasa pa /
NK114(ye)001:9732: longs spyod la chags pa spang ba /
NK114(ye)001:9733: grogs ngan la chags pa spang ba /
NK114(ye)001:9734: yul la chags pa spang ba /
NK114(ye)001:9735: dben pa'i yon tan dran pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:9736: dang po nags tshal gyi gnas la basngagasa pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:9737: gang du gzhi thams cad r+ts+wa ljang dang ldum bu'i
NK114(ye)001:9738: rigs sna tshogs kyis bkab pa la rma bya'i mgrin
NK114(ye)001:9739: pa lta bu'i kha dog shin tu legs pa'i nags
NK114(ye)001:9740: tshal shing ljon pa'i rigs du ma'i yal ga phyogs
NK114(ye)001:9741: phyogs su gyes pa la lo 'dab dang me tog
NK114(ye)001:9742: dang 'bras bu sna tshogs pas mdzes par spud pa
NK114(ye)001:9743: / sa gzhi'i ngos na yang me tog gi rigs
NK114(ye)001:9744: kha dog du ma dgod pa dang 'dra bar 'dab
NK114(ye)001:9745: ma kun tu rgyas shing ze'u 'bru ngom pa la
NK114(ye)001:9746: bung ba rnams glu len zhing 'phur lding g.yo bzhin
NK114(ye)001:9747: 'khor ba la sogs pas nyams dga' bar 'khrigs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:9748: gnas su rlung sil bu'i rkyen gyis dri bzang po'i
NK114(ye)001:9749: ngad phyogs kun tu ldang ba'i sman gyi ljongs der
NK114(ye)001:9750: / ni / phu chu bsil ba'i sgra ha cang
NK114(ye)001:9751: rtsub mo ma yin pa 'bab stegs bzang po nas
NK114(ye)001:9756: matshe'u sogs ne'u seng gi mu khyud can la ngang
NK114(ye)001:9757: pa dang ngur pa sogs chu bya'i rigs spu mdangs
NK114(ye)001:9758: legs shing skad snyan 'byin la spyod lam shin tu
NK114(ye)001:9759: zhi ba mang pos brten par byas shing ri bo'i
NK114(ye)001:9760: ngos rnams su blta na sdug pa'i brag ri ngos
NK114(ye)001:9761: 'jam zhing kha dog snum pa'i dkyil dag na rang
NK114(ye)001:9763: steng 'og dang phyogs rnams su brag them dang ri
NK114(ye)001:9764: mo rnam par bkra zhing kha dog phyed pa'i dbyibs
NK114(ye)001:9765: pha gu dang / rta babs kyi rnam pa can gyis mdzes pa'i spo na bya dang /
NK114(ye)001:9766: ngos dang gsham rnams su ri dwags gzhon nu 'grogs na bde ba /
NK114(ye)001:9767: gnod pa'i bsam ma mchis pa mang po rtse zhing rgyug pas mdzes pa yod cing /
NK114(ye)001:9768: gzhan yang ri rnams kyi spyi bo zla ba'i lwa
NK114(ye)001:9769: thod kyis mdzes par byas pa'i mgul na spang ljang
NK114(ye)001:9770: bzang po dar zab gcal du bkram pa lta bu'i
NK114(ye)001:9771: rked chings char sprin gyis 'khrigs shing /
NK114(ye)001:9772: gel ba ma yin pa'i rang bzhin snying la dga'
NK114(ye)001:9773: ba bskyed pa'i nags tshal lha'i bu mo'i gzugs bas
NK114(ye)001:9774: kyang lhag par mdzes pa'i rked chings ni shing bal
NK114(ye)001:9775: gzhon nu'i lu gu rgyud du sbrel bas d+r+wa ba
NK114(ye)001:9776: dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa'i rnam par byas pa dang
NK114(ye)001:9777: yal ga'i lcug phran ldem por mu tig gi lan
NK114(ye)001:9778: tshar dpyangs pa lta bu'i lo ma dang me tog
NK114(ye)001:9779: phang phung rlung 'jam pos g.yo zhing dal bar bskyed
NK114(ye)001:9780: pa'i rtse na 'dab chags rnams kyi rje bo gnyen
NK114(ye)001:9781: zhing lcug pa'i lang tsho la bye ru'i 'dren byed
NK114(ye)001:9783: 'tshe ba la dogs pasa skrag pa mina pa'i khu
NK114(ye)001:9784: byug gi tshogs rnams kyis 'khor ba'i rang bzhin g.yo
NK114(ye)001:9785: ba 'jig pa 'pho 'gyur can snying po med la
NK114(ye)001:9787: yid brtan du mi rung ba'i mtshan nyid can la
NK114(ye)001:9788: mngon par skyo ba'i gtam gyi spring yig gsar pa
NK114(ye)001:9789: 'grem pas bsam gtan pa rnams la brtson 'grus kyi
NK114(ye)001:9790: bskul ma byed pa yod de /
NK114(ye)001:9792: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor rgyas pas nye bar brgyan byas shing //
NK114(ye)001:9793: rked chings char chen sprin gyis 'khrigs pa 'khyud gyur pa //
NK114(ye)001:9794: ri rtse nags kyi mthongs der chags pa med par ni //
NK114(ye)001:9795: rlung ltar g.yo ba'i rang bzhin tshe gtugs skal ba che //
NK114(ye)001:9798: bung ba rgyags lding glu len cing //
NK114(ye)001:9799: ljon shing yal ga gar byed la //
NK114(ye)001:9800: bya rnams snyan pa'i skad kyang 'byin //
NK114(ye)001:9801: bsil yab ngad 'jam phyogs na g.yo //
NK114(ye)001:9802: phu chu ltung rgyun sgra yang sgrog /
NK114(ye)001:9803: mdzes pa'i ri dwags rgyug cing bskor //
NK114(ye)001:9804: me tog tshogs ni dgod pa 'dra //
NK114(ye)001:9805: tsan+dana spos sogs dri ngad ldan //
NK114(ye)001:9806: dgon pa'i yon tan 'di lta bu'i //
NK114(ye)001:9807: rang gzhan dag la phan 'dogs shing //
NK114(ye)001:9808: lan la cung zad mi re ste //
NK114(ye)001:9809: grogs mang rnal 'byor ci phyir skyo //
NK114(ye)001:9810: 'jig rten phal pa de ltar min //
NK114(ye)001:9812: gnyis pa longs spyod la chags pa spang ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:9813: de lta bu'i chos dang mthun pa'i dga' ba'i longs
NK114(ye)001:9814: spyod mang pos brgyan pa'i dben gnas de ru myur
NK114(ye)001:9815: bar gshegs shig ces bskul te /
NK114(ye)001:9816: su zhig na bsam gtan bsgom par 'doda pa rnams so //
NK114(ye)001:9817: rgyu mtshan ni 'jig rten pa'i phun sum tshogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:9818: dbus nas bsam gtan grub pa su yang med pas
NK114(ye)001:9819: bdag cag gi ston pa byang chub kyi spyod pa
NK114(ye)001:9820: la bskal pa grangs med pa gsum du bsten goms
NK114(ye)001:9821: mdzad pa de yang 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po'i
NK114(ye)001:9822: rgyal srid spangs nas dben pa la gshegs dgos na
NK114(ye)001:9824: de yang 'di ltar 'jig rten gyi 'byor pa ni khyim la gnas pa rnams la yod pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:9825: de'i rang bzhin ni nor dang zas gos la sogs
NK114(ye)001:9826: pa'i longs spyod gang ji snyed pa thams cad snying
NK114(ye)001:9827: po med cing nyes pa'i char rgyun 'dzin pa /
NK114(ye)001:9828: mi brtan zhing yud tsam gyis yod med byed pa
NK114(ye)001:9829: nam mkha' la glo bur du byung ba'i sprin gyi
NK114(ye)001:9830: bla re lta bu'i nang shed na /
NK114(ye)001:9831: skyes bu rnams kyi tshe brtan zhing srog 'tsho ba'i
NK114(ye)001:9832: rkyen du phan par rlom nas rol zhing spyod na
NK114(ye)001:9833: yang longs spyod g.yo ba de bas kyang tshe srog
NK114(ye)001:9835: shin tu mi brtan pa'i sprin gyi dngos po las
NK114(ye)001:9836: kyang ches 'gyur sla zhing yud tsam pa'i snang ba
NK114(ye)001:9837: las med pa'i glog gi 'gyur ba lta bu ni
NK114(ye)001:9838: skad cig skad cig gis g.yo zhing 'dar nas zad
NK114(ye)001:9839: par 'gyur ba las yun du sdod pa'i long khom
NK114(ye)001:9840: med la / de ltar yud tsam gnas pa'i skabs
NK114(ye)001:9841: der yang 'gyur ba'i sdug bsngal dang sdug bsngal gyi
NK114(ye)001:9842: med la / sdug bsngal dang / khyab pa 'du
NK114(ye)001:9843: byed kyi sdug bsngal gsum gyi chom rkun lta bu
NK114(ye)001:9844: rtag tu dkyu zhing 'gro bas mnar bar byed cing
NK114(ye)001:9845: med la / sdug bsngal dang / / khyad par
NK114(ye)001:9846: du 'di phyi thams cad phung krol te nyes pa
NK114(ye)001:9847: du ma bskyed par byed pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:9848: dper na rba rlabs drag tu 'phyur zhing rgyun myur
NK114(ye)001:9849: du 'bab pa'i chu klung 'ur sgra sgrogs pa'i ca
NK114(ye)001:9850: co can de'i rgyun gzhan du bzlog tu med par
NK114(ye)001:9851: rgya mtsho chen por ngang gis 'bab pa bzhin /
NK114(ye)001:9852: skye bo rnams kyang skyes nas cung zad nar son
NK114(ye)001:9853: te nus pa yod tsam nas bzung ste longs spyod
NK114(ye)001:9854: gsog pa dang / bsrung ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:9855: spel ba gsum gyi bya bas rtag tu brel zhing
NK114(ye)001:9856: ngal dub dang tsha grang la sogs pa'i sdug bsngal
NK114(ye)001:9857: shugs drag pos gdung ba'i ngang la 'doda pas gdung
NK114(ye)001:9858: zhing chog mi shes la re dogs la sogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:9859: rnam rtog ngan pas rgyud 'khrugs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:9860: de yang cung zad 'byor na ni khengs shing pha
NK114(ye)001:9861: rol khyad du gsod pa las longs spyod la snying
NK114(ye)001:9862: po len pa'i mchod sbyin ni mi nus pa'i steng
NK114(ye)001:9863: dgos rgyu yang lhag par cher ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:9864: de las bri yis dogs nas 'jungs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:9865: rang nyid kyi kha zas rgyab gos bzang po tsam
NK114(ye)001:9866: la yang ser sna byed pa de lta bu'i las
NK114(ye)001:9867: ngan gyi shugs bzlog tu med pa des bdas bzhin
NK114(ye)001:9868: tshe yi mthar gtugs nas rgyu des ngan 'gro'i chu
NK114(ye)001:9869: gter gting zab la thar dka' bar bying nas mu
NK114(ye)001:9870: dang mtha' med par 'khyams par 'gyur te /
NK114(ye)001:9872: bsag dang bsrung dang brlag pas gdung ba yi //
NK114(ye)001:9873: nor ni phung khrol mtha' yas shes par bya //
NK114(ye)001:9874: nor la chags pas g.yeng bar gyur pa rnams //
NK114(ye)001:9875: srid pa'i sdug bsngal las grol skabs med do //
NK114(ye)001:9877: des na nor rdzas ni sdug bsngal gyi gyur nges te //
NK114(ye)001:9878: dang po nas longs spyod bsgrub pa'i byed pa mi
NK114(ye)001:9879: dge ba'i kun slong ngan pas bskyed pa can te
NK114(ye)001:9880: / rgyud mi drang ba'i bsam pa gya gyu ba g.yo dang /
NK114(ye)001:9881: gzhan bslu ba'i bsam pa sgyu ste de gnyis 'brel
NK114(ye)001:9882: ba'i rang bzhin dbyar dus kyi char sprin brnagsa pa
NK114(ye)001:9883: na lam sogs mi mthong ba lta bu'i sgo nas
NK114(ye)001:9884: gzhan mgo rmongs par byas te /
NK114(ye)001:9887: tshul 'chos la sogs pa'i thabs kyis ster du 'jug pa'am /
NK114(ye)001:9888: khyad par du tshong byed pa rnams kyis ni /
NK114(ye)001:9894: nyin mtshan kho mor yug tu de kho na la sems /
NK114(ye)001:9897: gnyis kyis gsum sogs e 'thon blta ba'i zhe khrel
NK114(ye)001:9898: dang g.yo sgyu'i bskor mgo 'ba' zhig gis dus 'das
NK114(ye)001:9899: nas 'chi khar yang 'khrul 'ong ba la sogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:9901: spyir dal 'byor chud zos su 'gyur ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:9902: khyad par du yang ston pa'i rjes 'jug rnams kyi
NK114(ye)001:9903: rgyud chud zos su byed pa'i nyes pa zhig la
NK114(ye)001:9904: tshong 'di bas thu ba med gsungs /
NK114(ye)001:9905: de lta bu'i mi dge ba'i bsam sbyor gyis bsgrub
NK114(ye)001:9906: pa'i rin thang can gyi nor longs spyod kyi dngos
NK114(ye)001:9907: po ni ji tsam zhig 'byor zhing yod bzhin de
NK114(ye)001:9908: nyid gzhan gyis brlag dogs pa la sogs pas skrag
NK114(ye)001:9909: pa dang bsrung ba'i 'bad rtsol yang ches mang bas
NK114(ye)001:9910: sdug bsngal / de la brten pa'i nyes pa yang de tsam che bas /
NK114(ye)001:9911: 'di phyi kun tu sdug bsngal dpag tu med pa'i rgyu yin te /
NK114(ye)001:9913: klu mchog rnams la mgo bo ji snyed pa //
NK114(ye)001:9914: de las byung ba'i sdug bsngal de snyed do //
NK114(ye)001:9917: zang zing phyir na rtsod 'gyur te //
NK114(ye)001:9918: zang zing med la rtsod pa med //
NK114(ye)001:9919: zang zing yongs su spang ba las //
NK114(ye)001:9921: zhes chu skyar gyis nya kha nas bor na rtsod
NK114(ye)001:9922: pa zhi ba bzhin longs spyod med pa la rtsod
NK114(ye)001:9923: pa med pas bde bar 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:9924: de bas na lto 'grangs pa lhag pa skyob nus
NK114(ye)001:9925: pa tsam gyi longs spyod nyi tshe ba las med
NK114(ye)001:9926: pa'i yo byad bsnyungs pa rnams ni dgra rkun gyi
NK114(ye)001:9930: tha ma brlag par gyur na'ang 'gyod pa med /
NK114(ye)001:9931: de la brten nas nyes pa mi sogs shing /
NK114(ye)001:9932: zhen chags mi skye bas bsam gtan 'grub sla ba'i
NK114(ye)001:9933: sogs de las ldog pa'i yon tan mtha' yas la
NK114(ye)001:9934: / des na chog shes thob pa ni 'byor pa thams cad pa'i rtse mora 'gro ba yin te /
NK114(ye)001:9935: 'byor ldan rnams ni longs spyod kyi bde ba la
NK114(ye)001:9936: spyad pa de bas 'byor pas bskyed pa'i sdug bsngal
NK114(ye)001:9937: che ba dang 'dod pas gdung la /
NK114(ye)001:9938: chog shes dang ldan pa rnams ni de las ldog pas so //
NK114(ye)001:9939: de skad du bshes spring las /
NK114(ye)001:9940: nor rnams kun gyi nang na chog shes pa //
NK114(ye)001:9941: rab mchog lags par lha mi'i ston pas gsungs //
NK114(ye)001:9942: kun tu chog shes mdzod cig chog mkhyen na //
NK114(ye)001:9943: nor mi bdog kyang yang dag 'byor pa lags //
NK114(ye)001:9945: gsum pa grogs ngan la chags pa spang ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:9946: spyir 'phags pa rnams la ltos na so skye thams cad la byis pa zhes bya zhing /
NK114(ye)001:9947: de bzhin du mkhas pa la ltos na blun po rnams dang /
NK114(ye)001:9948: rgan po la ltos na gzhon nu rnams la byis
NK114(ye)001:9949: pa zhes brjod pa las 'dir so so skye bo'i
NK114(ye)001:9950: nang nas phal pa blun po rnams kyi rang bzhin
NK114(ye)001:9951: ni byis pa ste bus pa ma rabs zhig ste
NK114(ye)001:9952: / 'di ltar byis pa de rnams kyi rgyud ni
NK114(ye)001:9953: bsam sbyor phyin ci log gi nyes pa'i sprin gyis
NK114(ye)001:9954: rtag tu gang zhing 'khrigsa pa'i dbang gis bdag nyid
NK114(ye)001:9955: kyi skyon yang yon tan du bsgoms nas de la
NK114(ye)001:9957: gzhan gyi yon tan yang skyon du bzung nas de la mi snyan pa sna tshogs sgrog pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:9958: nyon mongs pa'i dug gis khong gang zhing dug sbrul
NK114(ye)001:9959: gdug pa can gyi lce bzhin bsam sbyor rtsub mo'i
NK114(ye)001:9960: nyams bag la rtag tu bsten nas sdig pa mi
NK114(ye)001:9962: 'jig rten pa'i dpal dang 'byor pa gnyen grogs dang
NK114(ye)001:9963: nor rdzas sogs g.yo zhing mi brtan pa snying po
NK114(ye)001:9964: med cing 'jig sla ba sdug bsngal du ma'i gzhir
NK114(ye)001:9965: gyur ba gang la'nga rtag brtan snying po can bde
NK114(ye)001:9966: ba'i rgyu yin par sems nas dge ba zhi ba'i
NK114(ye)001:9967: lam la brtson pa dor nas de kho na la
NK114(ye)001:9969: de dag la ni dge ba'i bshes gnyen sogs kyis
NK114(ye)001:9970: phan pa bsgrub pa'i bya ba ci byas pa la
NK114(ye)001:9971: yang 'dis bdag la 'di lta bu'i phan btags so
NK114(ye)001:9972: snyam du bsam nas drin lan mi gzo bar ma
NK114(ye)001:9973: zad phan lan du gnod pa byed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:9974: de dag ni mos pa sna tshogs pa can yin pas mgu ba'i dus mi 'ong zhing /
NK114(ye)001:9975: chos dang mthun pa'i ngag bkod dang 'di phyir phan
NK114(ye)001:9976: pa'i bsam sbyor bzang po byed pa rnams la mgu
NK114(ye)001:9977: ba'i rnam 'gyur gyi gzugs brnyan phyin ci log tu
NK114(ye)001:9978: 'khyog nas khro zhing mi dga' ba'i rnam 'gyur mang
NK114(ye)001:9979: po ston te / slob dpon sh+aan+ta de bas /
NK114(ye)001:9980: dga' ba'i gnas la khro byed pas //
NK114(ye)001:9981: so so skye bo mgu bar dka' //
NK114(ye)001:9983: phan par smras na khro bar byed //
NK114(ye)001:9984: bdag kyang phan las bzlog par byed //
NK114(ye)001:9986: gzhan mthun pa'am btang snyoms su gnas pa la'ang mi dga' bas mkhon du 'chos pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:9987: mkhon gyi zug rngu me lce chung du lta bu
NK114(ye)001:9988: cung zad yod pa'ang phra ma byed pa'i ngag sbyor
NK114(ye)001:9989: rlung chen po lta bu dag gis bskyod de 'thab
NK114(ye)001:9990: mo sbar bar byed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:9991: rang bzhin mi brtan pa spre'u bzhin du spyod pa
NK114(ye)001:9992: thams cad chos dang 'gal bas gnod pa'i rgyu mi
NK114(ye)001:9993: dge ba sna tshogs pa ster ba /
NK114(ye)001:9994: chu srin gyi kha gdangs pa'i nang srog chags mang
NK114(ye)001:9995: po rgya mtsho'i chu dang bcas rdub ste lto bar
NK114(ye)001:9996: chud pa bzhin du sdig pa'i las bsgrub pa'i sems
NK114(ye)001:9997: kyi lto ba ni shin tu yangs te nyi ma
NK114(ye)001:9998: re re bzhin sems can mang po'i srog la 'tshe
NK114(ye)001:9999: ba sogs sgo gsum ga'i 'bad pa chig dril du
NK114(ye)001:10000: mi dge ba'i phyogs la brtson kyang nyes pa tsam
NK114(ye)001:10001: du yang mi sems par da dung ngoms su med
NK114(ye)001:10002: pa / dug rlangs 'thul ba'i sbrul gdug pa bzhin
NK114(ye)001:10003: du su zhig dang phrad pa yin kyang nyes pa'i
NK114(ye)001:10004: dug gis de'i thar ba'i srog la rgol zhing rgyud
NK114(ye)001:10006: rtag tu rgyu 'bras khyad du gsod pa'i log lta dang /
NK114(ye)001:10007: khong khro la sogs pa'i dbang gis me chen po
NK114(ye)001:10008: bzhin du rang dang gzhan gyi rgyud kyi dge ba'i
NK114(ye)001:10009: ljon shing thams cad yud tsam la bsreg par 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:10010: ba'i tha chad kyi byis pa sdig pa'i grogs po
NK114(ye)001:10011: dge ba'i bar chad du gyur pa de rnams las
NK114(ye)001:10012: thag ring du bsring ste dam pa'i bsti gnas dben
NK114(ye)001:10013: khrod nyams dga' bar bgrod par bya dgos pa'i tshul
NK114(ye)001:10014: la gdams pa'o // bzhi pa yul la chags pa spang ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:10015: 'di ltar 'dod pa'i yul gzugs la sogs pa drug
NK114(ye)001:10016: po la rtag tu dbang po drug g.yo zhing zhen
NK114(ye)001:10017: pa dang bcas pas bag med par spyod pa ni
NK114(ye)001:10018: / rno zhing myur ba'i dug la spyad pa bas kyang thu ba yin pa'i tshul 'di lta ste /
NK114(ye)001:10019: dug zos pas ni nad kyis gzir zhing srog 'gag pa tsam gyi gnod pa 'byung la /
NK114(ye)001:10020: 'dod yul la zhen pas spyad pa'i rnam par smin
NK114(ye)001:10021: pas ni shin tu drag cing rtsub pa'i tshor ba
NK114(ye)001:10022: bzod dka' ba ngan song gi sdug bsngal yun ring
NK114(ye)001:10023: bor myong dgos pa'i phyir dang /
NK114(ye)001:10025: zas zhim po zos pa sogs longs spyad pa'i mod
NK114(ye)001:10026: la 'bral bde nyams dga' dga' ltar snang ba ni
NK114(ye)001:10027: / dug zos pa'i tshe bda' ba'i ro mngar ba
NK114(ye)001:10028: sogs bro zhing myong ba lta bu dang 'dra na
NK114(ye)001:10029: yang dug nad ni yun thung zhing sman dang sngags
NK114(ye)001:10030: kyis gso ru yod kyi yul la spyad pa'i nyes
NK114(ye)001:10031: pas tshe rabs gcig tsam zhig min par skye ba
NK114(ye)001:10032: mang po'i dus thams cad du sdug bsngal gyis gdung
NK114(ye)001:10033: bar 'gyur ba'i nyes pa de ni dug drag po
NK114(ye)001:10034: 'joms pa'i nus pa dang ldan pa'i gsang sngags mchog
NK114(ye)001:10035: / dang / bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad thams cad
NK114(ye)001:10036: sel nus pa'i sman gyis kyang gso bar mi rung
NK114(ye)001:10037: bas rtag tu dbang po yul la g.yo ba'i 'jug
NK114(ye)001:10038: pa dran shes kyis bsrungs nas nyes pa'i g.yul las
NK114(ye)001:10039: rgyal bar byed pa de ni dpa' bo mchog yin
NK114(ye)001:10041: gang dag dbang po drug yul rnams la ni //
NK114(ye)001:10042: rtag tu mi brtan g.yo dang gang dag gcig /
NK114(ye)001:10043: g.yul ngor dgra tshogs rgyal ba de dag las //
NK114(ye)001:10044: mkhas rnams dang po dpa' rab lags par 'tshal //
NK114(ye)001:10046: de bas na so so skye bo gang zhig yul
NK114(ye)001:10047: la brten nas 'dod pa'i dug gis myos pa'i sems
NK114(ye)001:10048: kyi glang po che lhag mthong gi stobs kyis ma
NK114(ye)001:10049: dul bar du / bslu bar byed pa'i yul gyi
NK114(ye)001:10050: nyes dmigs de mngon du mi mthong bas yon tan
NK114(ye)001:10052: bslu thabs kyi rnam 'gyur sna tshogs su snang bas
NK114(ye)001:10053: 'phrul ba lta bus ni byis pa'i skye bo rmongs
NK114(ye)001:10054: pa rnams bslus nas thar pa'i lam la bar du
NK114(ye)001:10055: gcod pa'i mthu ni 'dod pa'i yul las che ba
NK114(ye)001:10057: gzugs kyi phung po'i 'du byed zhing ste shi ba'i dus khyogs la bzhag nas mi bzhis bteg pa'am /
NK114(ye)001:10058: rta khal la sogs pas khur nas dur khrod sogs su ma bskyal ba de srid du /
NK114(ye)001:10059: 'du 'dzi dang rnam rtog gis g.yeng ba ngang gis
NK114(ye)001:10060: zhi ba'i nags kyi mthongs sogs dben pa'i gnas phun
NK114(ye)001:10061: sum tshogs pa dag la bsnyen par mdzoda cig ces
NK114(ye)001:10062: gdams pa ste / dben pa'i gtam las /
NK114(ye)001:10063: ji srid skyes bu bzhi yis lus //
NK114(ye)001:10064: khyogs la bteg par ma gyur bar //
NK114(ye)001:10065: de srid dgon par rab phyogs te //
NK114(ye)001:10066: zhi ba'i ting 'dzin bsgrub par bya //
NK114(ye)001:10068: lnga pa dben pa'i yon tan dran pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:10069: 'di la bas mtha' ni rgyang grags phyed dam grong
NK114(ye)001:10070: zad pa'i mur thug pa dang 'brog dgon pa ni
NK114(ye)001:10071: ma 'tha' grong las rgyang grags yan chad 'phags pa'i
NK114(ye)001:10072: gnas yin te / de ni 'khor ba la skyo ba rnams kyi yid du 'ong zhing /
NK114(ye)001:10074: de la brten nas dge ba'i blo thams cad rtsol med du 'byung ste /
NK114(ye)001:10075: sems skyo ba'i gnas la dad pa 'khor //
NK114(ye)001:10077: skyo shas la brten nas dad pa 'byung zhing de
NK114(ye)001:10078: la brten nas zhi lhag sogs kyi rtogs pa khyad
NK114(ye)001:10079: par can rgyud la skye ba yin pa'i phyir ro
NK114(ye)001:10080: // yon tan de dag gi mi mthun pa'i phyogs nyo tshong byed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10081: zhing las la sogs pa'i 'jig rten pa'i so nama dang /
NK114(ye)001:10082: bsam sbyor ngan pa can sdig pa'i grogs la sogs pa rnams kyis spangs te med pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10083: dpya 'bebs pa ste 'u lag tu 'ded pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10085: bran g.yog la sogs pa lta bu gzhan gyi nus
NK114(ye)001:10086: pa la brten nas 'tsho dgos pa zho shas 'tsho
NK114(ye)001:10087: ba la sogs pa'i brel bas mi gdung zhing de
NK114(ye)001:10088: na 'khod pa'i bya rnams ni skad snyan par sgrog
NK114(ye)001:10089: pa dang / ri dwags rnams ni bag phebs par rtse ba las /
NK114(ye)001:10090: chags sdang gi gtam dang mi snyan pa sgrog pa
NK114(ye)001:10091: la sogs pa'i mi mthun pa gang yang med la
NK114(ye)001:10098: lo ma la sogs pa'i 'phags pa dgyes shing chos
NK114(ye)001:10099: dang mthun pa'i nyer spyod rgya che la rtsol sgrub
NK114(ye)001:10101: rang byung gi brag ri'i phug pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10102: lo ma'i spyil bu'i khang bzang bsrung sla zhing chags
NK114(ye)001:10103: zhen mi skye la spyod lam bzhi shong bas yangsa
NK114(ye)001:10104: pa dang / ljon pa'i shing gi yal ga phyogs
NK114(ye)001:10105: su gyes pa khyon yangs la nyams dga' ba'i grib
NK114(ye)001:10106: bsil tsha gdung bcil ba la mkhas pa la sogs
NK114(ye)001:10107: pa'i gnas grogs longs spyod rgyun du 'grogs shing bsten
NK114(ye)001:10108: na 'di phyi thams cad du bde ba'i rkyen du
NK114(ye)001:10109: gyur pa de dag dang nam zhig na sngon gyi
NK114(ye)001:10110: dam pa gong ma rnams bzhin du bdag gcig pur
NK114(ye)001:10111: ni lhan cig gnas par 'gyur ba zhig byung na
NK114(ye)001:10112: ci ma rung snyam du bsam ste smon dgos pa'i
NK114(ye)001:10113: pa dang / tshul / slob spring las /
NK114(ye)001:10114: rtsa ba 'bras bu shun pa lo ma phun sum tshogs pa'i ljon shing ldan //
NK114(ye)001:10115: nags tshal ltos med ri bo'i chu rgyun bsil 'bab chags pa med pa'i gnas //
NK114(ye)001:10116: chu klung yangs pa'i mtha' ru 'bras bu me tog lhung bas brgyan pa yi //
NK114(ye)001:10117: nyams dga' bas mthar ci zhig med de dmyal dong khyim gyis bslus te sdod //
NK114(ye)001:10119: der yang gcig pur gnas dgos pa'i tshul ni /
NK114(ye)001:10121: mang po dag ni rtsod par 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:10122: gnyis po dag ni gtam bcas 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:10123: gzhon nu ma yi gdu bu bzhin //
NK114(ye)001:10124: gcig pu zhi bar gnas par bya //
NK114(ye)001:10126: dper na bud med gzhon nu ma zhig tsan+dana brdar
NK114(ye)001:10127: ba na gdu bu mang po 'khril ba te ma
NK114(ye)001:10128: bde na rim gyis phyung ste gnyis shig bzhag pa
NK114(ye)001:10129: na de yang 'thab nas ma bde ste gcig bzhag
NK114(ye)001:10130: pas bde bar gyur ba bzhin no //
NK114(ye)001:10131: de la nags khrod la sogs pa'i dben pa'i yon
NK114(ye)001:10132: tan gyi khyad par gzhan yang 'dus byas kyi rang
NK114(ye)001:10133: bzhin snying po med cing so sor 'gyes pa'i chos
NK114(ye)001:10134: can la rtag par 'dzin pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10135: dga' bar byed pa'i blo gros ngan pa can yang de ru bsdad na /
NK114(ye)001:10136: phyi nam zla dus bzhi'i 'gyur ldog shin tu g.yo
NK114(ye)001:10137: zhing snga phyir 'gyur ba ni dper na mgron po
NK114(ye)001:10138: snga ma snga ma song ba'i rjes la de min
NK114(ye)001:10139: pa'i phyi ma phyi ma gsar dang gsar du slebs
NK114(ye)001:10140: te bardze ba lta bu yis /
NK114(ye)001:10141: shing rnams kyang dbyar ni sngo zhing lcug pa /
NK114(ye)001:10142: ston ni brjid cing snum pa /
NK114(ye)001:10144: dpyid ni skams shing 'thor ba'i rnam pa mi 'dra
NK114(ye)001:10145: ba'i 'pho 'gyur gyi mngon rtogs gsar pa gsar par
NK114(ye)001:10146: ngom pas nges 'byung dang skyo shas bcos min du
NK114(ye)001:10147: 'phel zhing brtson 'grus kyi bskul mar 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:10148: de lta bu'i dben pa la brten na der yod
NK114(ye)001:10149: pa'i nags tshal rnams rang nyid nyon mongs pa'i rkyen
NK114(ye)001:10150: ma yin pa'i tshul rgyal ba'i bka' la gtan tshigsa
NK114(ye)001:10151: su byas te / dben gnas de ru goms pa
NK114(ye)001:10152: bdun du phyogs te song ba tsam pa'i bsod nams
NK114(ye)001:10153: ni tshad med zhes sgrog pa dang 'dra ba la
NK114(ye)001:10154: ltos zhes rab btags kyi rgyan du sbyar nas basngagasa
NK114(ye)001:10155: su byas te / pa ste / 'phags pa ting 'dzin rgyal po las /
NK114(ye)001:10156: gang la la zhig gis sangs rgyas thams cad la bskal pa'i bar du me tog dang /
NK114(ye)001:10158: zhal zas dang bde bar sbyar ba'i yo byad thams cad kyis bskal bar mchod pa bas /
NK114(ye)001:10159: rab tu skyo ba'i sems kyis dgon par phyogs te gom pa bdun tsam bor na /
NK114(ye)001:10160: 'di de bas ches bsod nams kyi phung po dpag tu med de /
NK114(ye)001:10161: lus dang srog la blta ba rab spongs la //
NK114(ye)001:10162: stong pa zhi ba mchog tu bsgom par gyis //
NK114(ye)001:10163: brtson zhing rab tu brtson pa'i yid kyis kyang //
NK114(ye)001:10164: ri dwags bzhin du dgon par gnas par gyis //
NK114(ye)001:10166: gnyis pa bsam gtan dngos bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK114(ye)001:10169: lam gyi yon tan bskyed pa'i bsam gtan bstan pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10171: dben pa'i gnas gang du phyin pa der ni le
NK114(ye)001:10172: lo'i dbang gis sos dal du bsdad pas mi 'ong
NK114(ye)001:10173: bas zhi lhag gi don la mnyam par 'jog dgos
NK114(ye)001:10174: shing / de yang rang gis bsgoms shing nyams su
NK114(ye)001:10175: len rgyu'i chos de la thog mar thos bsam gyis
NK114(ye)001:10176: sgro 'dogs bcad nas nges pa gting nas rnyed pa
NK114(ye)001:10177: shing / zhig dang / khyad par du theg pa
NK114(ye)001:10178: dman mchog gang yin kyang lam gyi mngon rtogs thams
NK114(ye)001:10179: cad bslab pa gsum gyi ngo bor nyams su len
NK114(ye)001:10180: pa la ni khyad par med cing de rnams kyi
NK114(ye)001:10181: go rim yang 'gyod pa med pa'i tshul khrims rnam
NK114(ye)001:10183: dmigs pa la rtse gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin 'byung zhing /
NK114(ye)001:10184: sems las su rung ba'i ting nge 'dzin la brten
NK114(ye)001:10185: nas lhag mthong gi ye shes yang dag pa skye
NK114(ye)001:10187: dge slong dag tshul khrims goms par byas pas ting nge 'dzin yun ring du gnas par 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:10188: ting nge 'dzin goms par byas nas shes rab yun ring du gnas par 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:10189: shes rab goms par byas na 'di lta ste /
NK114(ye)001:10192: gti mug las sems yang dag pa kho nar rnam par grol bar 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:10194: des na tshul khrims dang ldan pa'i gang zag des
NK114(ye)001:10195: bsam gtan las mnyam par 'jog pa na shin tu
NK114(ye)001:10196: zhes skad cig tsam du yang mi yeng bar dmigs
NK114(ye)001:10197: rnam mi brjed pa'i dran pas sems rtse gcig tu
NK114(ye)001:10198: 'dzin pa'i thabs la brten par bya dgos te /
NK114(ye)001:10200: ci nas ting 'dzin brtson pa ni //
NK114(ye)001:10201: skad cig gcig kyang mi 'chor bar //
NK114(ye)001:10202: bdag gi yid 'di gar spyod ces //
NK114(ye)001:10203: de ltar yid la so sor brtag /
NK114(ye)001:10205: de ltar yang yang bsgoms pas sems dge ba'i dmigs
NK114(ye)001:10206: pa la rtse gcig tu gnas pa ni ting nge
NK114(ye)001:10209: ting nge 'dzin rang gi ngo bo ni sems rtse gcig tu gnas pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10211: de lta bu'i bsam gtan gyi gnas 'di ni bslab
NK114(ye)001:10212: pa gsum gyi nang nas lhag pa sems kyi bslab
NK114(ye)001:10213: pa'i mtshan nyid gtso bor 'dzin pa'i bdag nyid de
NK114(ye)001:10214: / de'i ngo bo la ldog pas phye na tshul
NK114(ye)001:10215: khrims dang shes rab ste bslab pa gsum char dang
NK114(ye)001:10216: / / phyin drug kyang tshang ba'i tshul bshad zin pa ltar ro //
NK114(ye)001:10217: de ltar nges par byas nas sems can thams cad
NK114(ye)001:10218: byang chub snying po la 'god 'dod kyi lhag pa'i
NK114(ye)001:10219: bsam pa mngon du byas la /
NK114(ye)001:10220: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams
NK114(ye)001:10221: cad la phyag bya zhing ci nus pa'i mchod pa
NK114(ye)001:10222: dang / bshags pa sogs yan lag bdun pa byas la /
NK114(ye)001:10223: de nas rten 'brel lus la bsgrigs nas 'dug tshul
NK114(ye)001:10224: legs na rtsa dang rlung drang ba'i gnad kyi rten
NK114(ye)001:10225: cing 'brel 'byung las rtogs pa sems la 'char bar
NK114(ye)001:10226: 'gyur bas lus kyi cho ga ste 'dug tshul gyi
NK114(ye)001:10227: bya ba ni / stan bde ba la rnam par
NK114(ye)001:10228: snang mdzad kyi chos bdun gyis 'dug par bya ste
NK114(ye)001:10229: bya ba ni / / de'i tshul ni rkang pa skyil krung ngam /
NK114(ye)001:10231: mig ha cang mi phye ha cang mi zum bar sna'i rtse mor gtad2 /
NK114(ye)001:10232: lus dgye rgu'i phyogs gnyis su ma lhung ba drang por bsrang 3 /
NK114(ye)001:10233: phrag pa mtho dman med pa nyid du mnyam par bzhag4 /
NK114(ye)001:10234: mgrin pa cung zad bkug nas sna dang lte ba drang por bstun5 /
NK114(ye)001:10235: lce yang so'i drung du bzhag6 /
NK114(ye)001:10236: dbugs 'byin 'jug rang babs su dal bar 7bya ba rnams te /
NK114(ye)001:10237: de ni sems kyi srog shing can zhes srog shing
NK114(ye)001:10238: brtan pa btsugs pa bzhin sems gzhan du mi 'phro
NK114(ye)001:10239: ba'i thabs so // lus gnad de dang ldan pa'i sgo nas sems kyi gnad ni /
NK114(ye)001:10240: dmigs pa'i yul gang la sems 'dzin pa de gcig
NK114(ye)001:10241: pu las mi dge ba dang lung ma bstan pa
NK114(ye)001:10242: smos ci dgos / dge ba'i dmigs pa gnyis pa
NK114(ye)001:10243: la'ang gtad pa ma yin par dmigs yul de kho
NK114(ye)001:10244: na la sems cha mnyam par bzhag pa la brtson
NK114(ye)001:10245: smos ci dgos / dgos te / de yang 'di ltar gzugs can nam /
NK114(ye)001:10246: gzugs can ma yin pa'i dmigs pa gang yang rung
NK114(ye)001:10247: ba'i don la sems rtse gcig tu 'dzin pa dang
NK114(ye)001:10248: / skabs dang skabs su dpyad pa'i stobs kyis yid
NK114(ye)001:10249: ni dge ba'i don la rnam par bcing zhing dpyad
NK114(ye)001:10251: thog mar las dang po pas zhi ga nas gtso
NK114(ye)001:10252: bor bsgrub pa na de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku mtshan
NK114(ye)001:10253: dang dpe byad kyis brgyan pa la sems rtse gcig
NK114(ye)001:10255: 'phags pa ting nge 'dzin rgyal po las /
NK114(ye)001:10256: gser gyi kha dog lta bu'i sku lus kyi //
NK114(ye)001:10257: 'jig rten mgon po kun nas mdzes pa ste //
NK114(ye)001:10258: dmigs pa de la gang gis sems 'jog pa //
NK114(ye)001:10259: byang chub sems dpa' de mnyam bzhag ces bya //
NK114(ye)001:10261: de ltar sku gzugs la sems yun ring du bzung
NK114(ye)001:10262: nas de kho na la lhan gyis gnas pa'i tshe
NK114(ye)001:10263: na / lhag mthong bsgrub pa'i phyir dang po dpyad
NK114(ye)001:10264: par bya ste 'di ltar sems yul du snang ba'i
NK114(ye)001:10265: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gzugs mtshan dpes brgyan pa
NK114(ye)001:10266: 'di la yang sems las gzhan du grub pa rdul
NK114(ye)001:10267: tsam yang med de sems nyid der snang ba tsam
NK114(ye)001:10268: du zad la sems de yang ngo bo 'di zhes
NK114(ye)001:10269: gang du'ang dmigs su med de /
NK114(ye)001:10270: gang mi dmigs pa de ni dus gsum gyi dngos
NK114(ye)001:10271: po thams cad dang bral ba'i bsam gyis mi khyab
NK114(ye)001:10272: pa'i chos nyid do zhes nges par byas nas mthar
NK114(ye)001:10273: cir yang mi rtog pa'i ngang la mnyam par bzhag
NK114(ye)001:10274: par bya ste / dkon mchog brtsegs pa las /
NK114(ye)001:10275: 'od srung sems ni yongs su btsal na mi rnyed do //
NK114(ye)001:10276: gang ma rnyed pa de ni mi dmigs so //
NK114(ye)001:10277: gang mi dmigs pa de 'das pa'ang ma yin /
NK114(ye)001:10279: da ltar byung ba'ang ma yin no zhes so //
NK114(ye)001:10280: de ltar yun bsrings te bsgom pas mthar rnam par
NK114(ye)001:10281: rtog pa'i 'dzin stangs kyis spros pa'i snang ba thams
NK114(ye)001:10282: cad chos nyid stong pa'i rang bzhin gcig tu nuba
NK114(ye)001:10283: cing / de yang snang cha 'gag pa'i phyang chad
NK114(ye)001:10284: pa ma yin bar snang yul gzugs la sogs pa
NK114(ye)001:10285: ma 'gags kyang dngos po med pas phra ba /
NK114(ye)001:10286: mtshan nyid ma grub pas bltar dka' ba'i phyir der
NK114(ye)001:10287: 'dzin gyi 'du shes bcos ma ni gang yang med
NK114(ye)001:10288: pa yin te / gshis kyi gnas lugs la sems rab tu zhugs pa'i phyir te /
NK114(ye)001:10290: ting nge 'dzin ni snyoms pa'i sa //
NK114(ye)001:10291: zhi ba phra ste blta dka' ba //
NK114(ye)001:10292: 'du shes thams cad bcom pas na //
NK114(ye)001:10293: de phyir ting nge 'dzin zhes bya //
NK114(ye)001:10295: de lta bu'i ngang la dran pa'i thag pas btags
NK114(ye)001:10296: nas rgyun du bying rgod la sogs pa'i skyon gyis
NK114(ye)001:10297: mi 'phrog pa'i shes pa yul la mi rtog par
NK114(ye)001:10298: rtse gcig tu gnas pa'i cha mnyam bzhag gam zhi
NK114(ye)001:10299: gnas yin la / de dang ngo bo gcig pa'i
NK114(ye)001:10300: ye shes rang bzhin yongs su shes pa'am nang sems
NK114(ye)001:10301: nyid tsam la'ang ma zhen pa'i cha ni rjes thob
NK114(ye)001:10304: zhi gnas ni sems rtse gcig pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10305: lhag mthong ni yang dag par so sor rtog pa'o zhes so //
NK114(ye)001:10306: gnyis pa bsam gtan gyi dbye ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:10307: bsam gtan de la nang gses kyis dbye ba byas na /
NK114(ye)001:10308: byis pa so so skye bo lam la ma zhugs pa rnams nye bar spyod pa'i bsam gtan dang /
NK114(ye)001:10309: don rab tu rnam par 'byed pa mthong lam gyi
NK114(ye)001:10310: rgyur gyur pa'i lam zhugs 'jig rten pa'i rgyud kyi
NK114(ye)001:10311: bsam gtan dang / 'phags pa'i lam la zhugs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:10312: rgyud kyi de bzhin gshegs dge'i bsam gtan te rnam
NK114(ye)001:10313: bsam gtan dang / pa gsum dang / yang rtog
NK114(ye)001:10314: pa dang dpyod pa dang dga' ba dang bde ba
NK114(ye)001:10315: rnams yod med kyi mu bzhi'i dbye bas bsam gtan
NK114(ye)001:10316: dang po la sogs pa bzhi dang /
NK114(ye)001:10317: de bzhin du nam mkha' mtha' yas la sogs pa
NK114(ye)001:10318: gzugs med pa'i ting nge 'dzin bzhi ste rnam pa'i
NK114(ye)001:10319: grangs snyoms 'jug brgyad rnams yod pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:10320: de la theg pa gsum po gang yang rung ba'i
NK114(ye)001:10321: lam la ma zhugs pa'i byis pa phal pa rnams
NK114(ye)001:10322: kyis nyon mongs mngon gyur dang /
NK114(ye)001:10323: des bskyed pa'i sdug bsngal rags pa tsam la skyon
NK114(ye)001:10324: du bltas te bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin las skyes
NK114(ye)001:10325: pa'i dga' bde sogs dang de'i 'bras bu khams gong
NK114(ye)001:10326: ma'i tshor ba la nye bar spyod pa'i phyir de'i
NK114(ye)001:10328: bsam gtan bzhi dang gzugs med pa'i snyoms 'jug bzhi
NK114(ye)001:10329: ste brgyad po gang yin yang de dag la byis
NK114(ye)001:10330: pa nyer spyod kyi bsam gtan zhes bya bar brjod
NK114(ye)001:10331: pa yin no // 'di dag gi don cung zad phral te bshad na bsam gtan bzhi dang /
NK114(ye)001:10333: dang po bsam gtan la nyer bsdogs dang /
NK114(ye)001:10335: dang po nyer bsdogs la sgom tshul mang yang 'jig
NK114(ye)001:10336: rten pa'i lam rkyang pa la zhi rags kyi rnam
NK114(ye)001:10337: pa can du bsgom pa shas che bas de ltar
NK114(ye)001:10338: na / dang po 'dod pa'i sems ni rags pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10340: mtshan mar dman par bltas nas /
NK114(ye)001:10342: de bas lhag par yang zhi ba dang bde ba
NK114(ye)001:10343: dang gya nom pa'o snyam nas thos bsam 'dres ma'i
NK114(ye)001:10344: tshul gyis yang dang yang du yid la byas pas
NK114(ye)001:10345: nam zhig thos bsam las 'das nas sgom byung du
NK114(ye)001:10346: song ste 'dod pa'i nyon mongs che 'bring drug spangs
NK114(ye)001:10347: pa'i bar ni bsam gtan gyi nyer bsdogs so //
NK114(ye)001:10348: de nas 'dod pa'i nyon mongs pa chung ngu gsum
NK114(ye)001:10349: spangs pa'i tshe na bsam gtan dngos gzhi'i sems thob
NK114(ye)001:10350: pa'o // bsam gtan dang po la yan lag lnga ste /
NK114(ye)001:10356: rtog dpyod gnyis ni mdzod las /
NK114(ye)001:10357: rtog dang dpyod pa rtsing zhib nyid //
NK114(ye)001:10358: ces pa ltar sems ting nge 'dzin skyon med du gnas mi gnas rags par rtog pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10360: sems ting nge 'dzin la gnas pas yid shes bde bas khyab pa dga' ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:10361: de'i stobs kyis lus la shin sbyang gi bde ba skyes pa bde ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:10362: sems rtse gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa ting nge 'dzin no //
NK114(ye)001:10363: bsam gtan gnyis pa la yan lag bzhi ste /
NK114(ye)001:10368: dran pa dang shes bzhin dang btang snyoms kyi ngo
NK114(ye)001:10369: bo yin yang 'dir dga' ba'i g.yo ba dang ma
NK114(ye)001:10370: bral ba'i phyir rab dang gi sgras bstan no //
NK114(ye)001:10371: lhag ma gsum ni sngar bzhin no //
NK114(ye)001:10372: bsam gtan gsum pa la yan lag lnga ste /
NK114(ye)001:10378: bde ba ni sngar dang 'dra la /
NK114(ye)001:10379: btang snyoms ni sems bying rgod med par gnas pa'i tshe rang babs su 'jog pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10380: dran pa ting nge 'dzin mi brjed pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10381: shes bzhin ni bying rgod la sogs byung ma byung rtog pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10382: ting nge 'dzin ni sngar ltar ro //
NK114(ye)001:10383: bsam gtan bzhi pa la yan lag bzhi ste /
NK114(ye)001:10388: dran pa dang ting nge 'dzin ni sngar dang 'dra la /
NK114(ye)001:10389: tshor ba btang snyoms ni lung ma bstan dang /
NK114(ye)001:10390: 'du byed btang snyoms kyang sngar dang 'dra'o //
NK114(ye)001:10391: de yang rtog dpyod la sogs yan lag lnga dang
NK114(ye)001:10392: ldan pa ni bsam gtan dang po'i dngos gzhi tsam
NK114(ye)001:10394: de las rtog pa med la dpyod pa dang bcas pa ni dngos gzhi khyad par can no //
NK114(ye)001:10395: rtog dpyod gnyis ka spangs pa ni bsam gtan gnyis pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10396: rtog dpyod dga' ba gsum spangs pa ni bsam gtan gsum pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10397: de gsum bde ba dang bzhi spangs pa ni gsam gtan bzhi pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10398: bsam gtan dngos gzhi ma thob kyang bsam gtan dang
NK114(ye)001:10399: po'i nyer bsdogs yang dag pa des kyang lhag mthong
NK114(ye)001:10400: gi rten byed pas na nyer bsdogs mi lcogs med
NK114(ye)001:10401: ces bya la / nyer bsdogs de dang dang po'i dngos gzhi la tsam khyad gnyis /
NK114(ye)001:10402: lhag ma gsum dang drug la bsam gtan sa drug zhes bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:10403: gnyis pa gzugs med rnams ni yan lag gi dbye ba med pas dmigs rnams kyi 'byed de /
NK114(ye)001:10404: bsam gtan bzhi pa thob pa des gru bzhi zlum po la sogs dbyibs kyi 'du shes dang /
NK114(ye)001:10405: dkar ser dmar ljang la sogs kha dog gi 'du shes dang /
NK114(ye)001:10406: ri dang khang khyim la sogs thog reg gi 'du shes gsum ga bkag nas /
NK114(ye)001:10407: chos thams cad nam mkha' ltar bsgoms pas gzugs kyi
NK114(ye)001:10408: 'du shes thams cad las 'das nas nam mkha' lta
NK114(ye)001:10409: bu'i ngang du gnas pa ni nam mkha' mtha' yas
NK114(ye)001:10410: / nam mkha' tsam du'ang 'dzin pa spangs nas nam
NK114(ye)001:10411: mkha'o snyam byed rnam shes tsam gyi ngang du gnas
NK114(ye)001:10412: pa ni rnam shes mtha' yas /
NK114(ye)001:10413: rnam shes tsam du 'dzin pa yang spangs nas ci
NK114(ye)001:10414: yang med do snyam du gnas pa ni ci yang
NK114(ye)001:10415: med pa / ci yang med do snyam du 'dzin
NK114(ye)001:10416: pa yang spangs nas ci yang med do snyam mkhan
NK114(ye)001:10417: gyi 'du shes la brtags nas 'du shes kyi 'gyu
NK114(ye)001:10418: ba rags pa thams cad bkag nas 'du shes phra
NK114(ye)001:10419: mo tsam la gnas pa ni 'du shes med 'du
NK114(ye)001:10420: shes med min gyi skye mched do //
NK114(ye)001:10421: 'di la yod min med min yang zer ro //
NK114(ye)001:10422: yang theg gsum gang rung gi lam la zhugs pa'i gang zag gis tshogs kyi lam dang /
NK114(ye)001:10423: sbyor ba'i lam du lhag mthong dang 'brel bar bsgoms
NK114(ye)001:10424: pa'i ting nge 'dzina gyis thar pa ste mthong lam
NK114(ye)001:10425: mngon du byed pas don rab 'byed pa'i gsam gtan
NK114(ye)001:10426: zhes bya bar grags te de yang mthong lam gyi
NK114(ye)001:10427: ye shes kyiis bdag med pa'i don rab tu ste
NK114(ye)001:10428: mngon sum du mthong zhing rnam par 'byed pas na
NK114(ye)001:10429: de skad ces bya la 'dir rgyu la 'bras bu'i
NK114(ye)001:10430: ming gis btags pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:10431: byang chub sems dpa'i lam gyis 'phags pa'i ye shes
NK114(ye)001:10432: dang po thob pa'i sa rab tu dga' ba yan
NK114(ye)001:10433: chad nas theg chen 'phags pa'i ting nge 'dzin slob
NK114(ye)001:10434: pa sa bcu la gnas pa dang mi slob pa
NK114(ye)001:10435: sangs rgyas kyi rgyud kyis bsdus pa zhi lhag zung
NK114(ye)001:10437: de dag gi rang bzhin zag pa med pa'i ye
NK114(ye)001:10438: shes yin pas phyi ma ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:10439: ye shes kyi ngo bo zhi gnas dang lhag mthong
NK114(ye)001:10440: zung 'jug tu mthar phyin pas zag pa bag chags
NK114(ye)001:10441: dang bcas pa bral zhing dge ba dam pa'i pha
NK114(ye)001:10442: rol tu son pa'i bsam gtan yin la snga ma
NK114(ye)001:10443: yang de dang rjes su mthun cing de'i rgyu yin
NK114(ye)001:10445: spyir zag pa yod med la rnam pa mang yang
NK114(ye)001:10446: 'dir bdag lta'i gnyen po byed mi nus pa dang
NK114(ye)001:10448: de yang tshogs sbyor gyi lam du bdag med don
NK114(ye)001:10449: spyi'i tshul du bsgom pa'i zhi lhag zung 'jug des
NK114(ye)001:10450: kyang bdag lta nyams smad par byed kyang sa bon
NK114(ye)001:10451: drung nas 'byin pa'i tshul gyis spong ba min pas
NK114(ye)001:10453: 'phags pa slob pa'i zhi lhag gis bdag lta drungs 'byin gyi tshul du spangs shing /
NK114(ye)001:10454: mi slob pa'i sar bdag lta'i bag nyal phra mo
NK114(ye)001:10455: yang zad pas zag med ces brjod pa yin no
NK114(ye)001:10456: // de ltar byis pa nyer spyod nas de bzhin
NK114(ye)001:10457: gshegs dge'i bar gyi bsam gtan de dag kun kyang
NK114(ye)001:10458: ngo bo ni phyi rol gyi yul la mi g.yeng
NK114(ye)001:10459: bar nang du sems rtse gcig par 'dzin pa yin
NK114(ye)001:10460: // la / de 'grub pa dang mthar phyin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:10461: rgyun ni dmigs rnam mi brjed pa'i dran pa rgyun
NK114(ye)001:10462: chags pa dang spro ba'i brtson 'grus kyi rkyen la
NK114(ye)001:10464: de yang byis pa rnams kyis ni bdag tu mngon
NK114(ye)001:10465: par zhen pa dang bcas pas dmigs pa la rtse
NK114(ye)001:10466: gcig pa'i bsam gtan de dran pa dang brtson pa'i
NK114(ye)001:10467: rgyus bsgrub la / lam zhugs rnams kyis de bdag
NK114(ye)001:10468: med rtogs pa'i shes rab kyi rtsi yis sbyar te
NK114(ye)001:10469: rgyus bsgrub la / bsgrub cing / sangs rgyas kyi sa na dmigs rnam mam /
NK114(ye)001:10471: gnyis snang phra ba'i bag chags mtha' dag pa 'gags
NK114(ye)001:10472: nas yul can gyi ye shes yul chos dbyings spros
NK114(ye)001:10473: pa dang bral bar ro gcig tu gyur te rtag
NK114(ye)001:10474: tu dgongs pa de las mi g.yo bas nang du
NK114(ye)001:10476: dran brtson sogs su btags pa tsam las ched du rtsol ba med do //
NK114(ye)001:10477: de la las dang po pa rnams kyis thog mar
NK114(ye)001:10478: lhag mthong gi rten du sems las rung du bsgrub
NK114(ye)001:10479: pa na rtag tu dran shes kyis dge ba'i dmigs
NK114(ye)001:10480: pa la rtse gcig tu bzhag nas bsgom pa'i tshe
NK114(ye)001:10481: dran pa'i rgyun nyams nas phyi rol du rnama para
NK114(ye)001:10482: g.yengas par gyur na de ma thag shes bzhin gyis
NK114(ye)001:10483: zin par byas te brtson 'grus kyis slar yang dmigs
NK114(ye)001:10484: pa de la bslan nas bsgoms te de lta bu'i
NK114(ye)001:10485: rgyun yun ring du goms par byed pa yin par
NK114(ye)001:10486: gsungs so // de yang yum mdo las 'jog thabs dgu bstan pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK114(ye)001:10493: rnam par zhi bar byed do //
NK114(ye)001:10497: de la dang po ni dmigs pa la sems 'jog pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10498: gnyis pa ni dmigs pa de nyid la rgyun du 'jog pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10499: gsum pa ni rnam par g.yeng ba shes nas de spong ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:10500: bzhi pa ni rnam par g.yeng ba spangs nas phyi
NK114(ye)001:10501: phyir brtun te dmigs pa de nyid la 'jog pa'o
NK114(ye)001:10502: // lnga pa ni dga' ba bskyed pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10503: drug pa ni rnam par g.yeng ba'i nyes pa mthong
NK114(ye)001:10504: nas mi dga' ba rab tu zhi bar byed pa'o
NK114(ye)001:10505: // bdun pa ni rmugs pa dang gnyid la sogs pa sel ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:10506: brgyad pa ni mngon par 'du byed pas 'jug par byed pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10507: dgu pa ni sems mnyam par gyur pa na btang
NK114(ye)001:10508: snyoms su byed pa'o zhes bya ba'i tha tshig tu
NK114(ye)001:10509: mgon po byams pas bstan to //
NK114(ye)001:10510: de ltar bsgom pa'i tshe mi mthun pa'i phyogs rnam
NK114(ye)001:10511: par g.yeng ba'i rgyu shin tu mang po zhig gsungs
NK114(ye)001:10512: shing / dran pa nyer bzhag las kyang /
NK114(ye)001:10513: rigs kyi bu bcu po 'di dag gis byang chub
NK114(ye)001:10514: sems dpa' rnams kyi bsam gtan dang kha ton gyi
NK114(ye)001:10515: bar du gcod par byed do //
NK114(ye)001:10516: bcu gang zhe na 'di lta ste /
NK114(ye)001:10520: gaza'i tshogs dang rgyu skar sems pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10521: zas rnyed pa bdag gir byed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10522: sha za mo ltar nor bsgyur bar sems pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10523: rgyal po la brten pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10524: mkhas pa la mi 'dri ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:10525: bde ba la mgron du 'bod pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10526: 'dre zhing gnas pa ste bcu po 'di dag go zhes so //
NK114(ye)001:10527: de bas na de dag spangs nas sems kyi rgyun
NK114(ye)001:10528: rnam par mi g.yeng ba 'ba' zhig la gnas pas
NK114(ye)001:10529: thun mong gi bsam gtan bsgrub par byas na de'i
NK114(ye)001:10530: byed las ni lus dang sems la shin tu sbyangs
NK114(ye)001:10532: rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs 'grub pa'i rten byed la /
NK114(ye)001:10533: bsam gtan de grub pa'i tshe 'bras bu ni sngon gyi gnas rjes su dran pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10534: gzhan gyi sems shes pa sogs mngona shes dang /
NK114(ye)001:10535: gzhan yang zad pa dang zil gnon la sogs pa
NK114(ye)001:10536: nyan thos dang thun mong gi yon tan rnams thob
NK114(ye)001:10537: pa yin no // 'jig rten pa'i bsam gzugs de dag rim gyis bsgom pa'i tshe /
NK114(ye)001:10538: bsam gtan dang po'i nyer bsdogs yid byed drug gi
NK114(ye)001:10539: tshe rags par rtog cing zhib par dpyod pa gnyis
NK114(ye)001:10542: khams gong 'og gi mtshan nyid zhi rags kyis thos
NK114(ye)001:10543: bsam 'dres mar yid la byed pa ni mtshan nyid
NK114(ye)001:10544: rab tu rig pa yid la byed pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10545: thos bsam las 'das nas zhi lhag tu son pa ni mos pa yid la byed pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10546: 'dod nyon chen po gsum spong ba'i lam skye ba ni bden pa yid la byed pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10547: de las skyes pa'i dga' bde chung ngu'i reg pa
NK114(ye)001:10548: ni dga' ba dud pa yid la byed pa ste
NK114(ye)001:10549: 'dod nyon 'bring gsum spong ba'i gnas skabs so //
NK114(ye)001:10550: nyon mongs phra ba yod med dpyad nas chung ngu
NK114(ye)001:10551: gsum spong ba ni dpyod pa yid la byed pa
NK114(ye)001:10552: dang sbyor ba'i mtha' yid la byed pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10553: dang po'i dngos gzhi la rtog pa med la dpyod pa tsam dang /
NK114(ye)001:10554: lhag ma bsam gtan gnyis pa gsum pa bzhi pa
NK114(ye)001:10555: gsum por rtog dpyod gnyis ka med pa yin la
NK114(ye)001:10556: / bsam gtan dang pos gnyis pa'i nyer bsdogs byed
NK114(ye)001:10557: pa sogs rim gyis snga ma snga mas phyi ma
NK114(ye)001:10558: phyi ma'i nyer bsdogs byed cing /
NK114(ye)001:10559: de bzhin du bsam gtan bzhi bas nam mkha' mtha'
NK114(ye)001:10560: yas skye mched kyi snyoms 'jug gi nyer bsdogs byed
NK114(ye)001:10561: pa sogs gzugs med phyi ma gsum po la'ang rig
NK114(ye)001:10562: par bya zhing / srid rtse la brten nas 'phags
NK114(ye)001:10563: pa rnams kyis 'gog pa'i snyoms 'jug kyang bsgrub par
NK114(ye)001:10564: par bya zhing / byed do // des na snyoms
NK114(ye)001:10565: 'jug dgu po de la 'phags pa gsum ga'i mthong
NK114(ye)001:10566: sgom gyi lam gyi rten gzhi zhes su grags pa
NK114(ye)001:10567: yin la 'on kyang 'gog snyoms ni theg dman 'phags
NK114(ye)001:10568: pa phyir mi 'ong yan chad kyis mthong chos bder
NK114(ye)001:10570: theg chen 'phags pas ting nge 'dzin la rtsal sbyang
NK114(ye)001:10571: ba'i phyir 'jug pa tsam las de la brten nas
NK114(ye)001:10572: mthong sgom gyi lam thob dgos pa'i don min la
NK114(ye)001:10573: / yang bsam gzugs brgyad ka mthong sgom gyi lam
NK114(ye)001:10574: mngon du byed pa'i rten du dgos pas kyang ma
NK114(ye)001:10575: / khyab ste / theg dman lam gyi 'bras bu
NK114(ye)001:10576: thod rgal ba'i phyir 'ong 'bras gnas kyi sngon du
NK114(ye)001:10577: bsam gtan dang po'i dngos gzhi ma thob pas khyab
NK114(ye)001:10578: / khyab ste / pa'i phyir dang / theg chen
NK114(ye)001:10579: 'phags lam gyi rten du'ang bsam gtan bzhi pa gtso
NK114(ye)001:10580: che bar bstan pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:10581: gsum pa lam gyi yon tan bskyed pa'i bsam gtan bshad pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:10582: de la spyir theg pa gsum po'i lam dang 'bras
