NK114(ye)001:10583: bu'i yon tan ji snyed cig yod pa de thams
NK114(ye)001:10584: cad bskyed par byed pa'i rgyu ni zhi lhag gnyis
NK114(ye)001:10585: yin te ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo thams cad zhi
NK114(ye)001:10586: lhag zung du 'brel bas bsdus pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:10587: de'ang zhi gnas brtan par ma gyur pa'i lhag mthong
NK114(ye)001:10588: ni rlung dang 'grogs pa'i mar me bzhin mi gsal
NK114(ye)001:10589: zhing yun ring du mi gnas pas sgrib pa 'joms
NK114(ye)001:10590: mi nus la / lhag mthong dang bral ba'i zhi
NK114(ye)001:10591: gnas kyi sgrib pa'i sa bon gcod mi nus pas
NK114(ye)001:10592: ji ltar bzang yang srid pa'i rgyu las mi 'da'
NK114(ye)001:10593: bas na theg pa dman mchog gi lam kun gyi
NK114(ye)001:10594: thun mong du zhi lhag zung du 'brel dgos pa'i
NK114(ye)001:10595: mi nus la / tshul ni / zhi gnas kyi
NK114(ye)001:10596: stobs kyis rnam par rtog pa'i rlung gi sems mi
NK114(ye)001:10598: lhag mthong gi stobs kyis rmongs pa'i sgrib pa dang
NK114(ye)001:10599: 'jig tshogs la lta ba sogs drung nas 'byin par
NK114(ye)001:10600: byed do // de yang nyan thos ni ting nge 'dzin shas che la shes rab shas chung ngo //
NK114(ye)001:10601: byang chub sems dpa' rnams ni de las ldog cing /
NK114(ye)001:10602: de bzhin gshegs pa ni gnyis ka mnyam ste /
NK114(ye)001:10603: mya ngan las 'das pa chen po'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:10604: nyan thos rnams kyis ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs
NK114(ye)001:10605: mi mthong ste ting nge 'dzin shas che ba'i phyir
NK114(ye)001:10606: dang shes rab chung ba'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:10607: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis ni mthong mod kyi
NK114(ye)001:10608: mi gsal te shes rab shas che ba'i phyir dang
NK114(ye)001:10609: / ting nge 'dzin chung ba'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:10610: de bzhin gshegs pas ni thams cad gzigs te zhi
NK114(ye)001:10611: gnas dang lhag mthong mtshungs par ldan pa'i phyir ro
NK114(ye)001:10613: khyad par du theg pa chen po'i lam dang 'bras
NK114(ye)001:10614: bu'i yon tan kun gyi rgyur gyur pa'i bsam gtan
NK114(ye)001:10615: ni / bsam gzugs dang tshad med la sogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:10616: rnam pa dang bcas pa'i sgom thams cad la dang
NK114(ye)001:10617: po sbyor ba sems bskyed pa ni sems can la
NK114(ye)001:10619: de'i ngang nas bsgom bya sgom byed la mtshan ma'i
NK114(ye)001:10620: zhen pa dang ni bral ba'i ye shes dam pas
NK114(ye)001:10621: zin pa'i sgo nas yang yang goms par byas pas
NK114(ye)001:10622: dmigs rnam de rgyun chags su rnam g.yeng gis mi
NK114(ye)001:10623: 'phrog par gyur pa na gang yang yid la mi
NK114(ye)001:10624: byed pa'i ngang ci gnas su mnyam par bzhag ste
NK114(ye)001:10625: mthar sgyu ma lta bu'i dran 'dun gyis bsngo bar
NK114(ye)001:10626: bya'o // de yang gang bsgom par bya ba'i dmigs
NK114(ye)001:10627: pa de la sems rtse gcig pa'i cha ni zhi
NK114(ye)001:10628: bya'o // gnas dang / de la ma zhen pa'i
NK114(ye)001:10629: cha ni lhag mthong ste zhi lhag zung 'jug go
NK114(ye)001:10630: bya'o // gnas dang / // yang rnam pa thams
NK114(ye)001:10631: cad pa dang bral ba'i stong pa nyid la mnyam
NK114(ye)001:10633: sngon du sems can thams cad la snying rje chen
NK114(ye)001:10634: po'i lta bas blta ba'i dmigs pa la sems nye
NK114(ye)001:10635: bar 'jog pa ni byang chub sems dpa'i thabs khyad
NK114(ye)001:10637: dngos gzhi'i dus su rnam pa dang bcas pa'i snying
NK114(ye)001:10638: rje la sogs pa dang spros bral gyi ngang la
NK114(ye)001:10639: sems rab tu zhugs pa gnyis zung du tshud pa
NK114(ye)001:10640: ni so skye'i gnas skabs na lta ci /
NK114(ye)001:10641: ma dag sa bdun du'ang 'byung dka' bar gsungs pas
NK114(ye)001:10642: rab tu zhi ba'i sems mtha' gnyis la mi gnas
NK114(ye)001:10643: shing yul dang yul can gyi sproos pa nye bar
NK114(ye)001:10644: zhi ba'i ngang du snyoms par 'jug pa de shes
NK114(ye)001:10645: rab rnam par dag pa nyid yin pas de'i tshe'ang
NK114(ye)001:10647: spros pa dang bral lo zhes pa la sogs pa
NK114(ye)001:10648: lta bu'i rtog dpyod zhig med na so sor rtog
NK114(ye)001:10649: pa'i shes rab dang bral bas de 'dra ba'i lhag
NK114(ye)001:10650: mthong gi cha de 'dor mi rung snyam du rnam
NK114(ye)001:10651: shes kyi spyod yul tsam kho na la rtag tu
NK114(ye)001:10652: blo rtse gtad par mi bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:10654: yod dang med ces bya ba gnyis ka mtha' //
NK114(ye)001:10655: gtsang dang mi gtsang 'di yang mtha' yin te //
NK114(ye)001:10656: de phyir gnyis ka'i mtha' ni rnam spangs nas //
NK114(ye)001:10657: mkhas pa dbus la'ang gnas pa yod mi byed //
NK114(ye)001:10659: de ltar mnyam par bzhag pa de'i tshe na dmigs
NK114(ye)001:10660: med kyi ngang la rtse gcig tu gnas pa ni
NK114(ye)001:10661: zhi gnas dang / rang bzhin yongs shes kyi shes rab ni lhag mthong ste zung 'jug go //
NK114(ye)001:10662: de las langs pa na sngar bzhin bsngo ba bya
NK114(ye)001:10663: ba ni thabs shes khyad par can dang ldan pa'i
NK114(ye)001:10664: theg chen lam gyi nyams len yin te /
NK114(ye)001:10665: lha'i bu rab rtsal gyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:10666: gang tshe sems ni chags med pa //
NK114(ye)001:10667: bla med byang chub sems yin te //
NK114(ye)001:10668: sems kyi rang bzhin mngon sum pa //
NK114(ye)001:10669: de ni shes rab mtshan nyid do //
NK114(ye)001:10670: sems rnams bskyed pa thams cad ni //
NK114(ye)001:10671: byang chub tu ni yongs bsngo zhing //
NK114(ye)001:10672: byang chub sems ni rab brtas pa //
NK114(ye)001:10673: de ni thabs kyi mtshan nyid do //
NK114(ye)001:10675: 'phags pa blo gros mi zad pas bstan pa las /
NK114(ye)001:10676: de la byang chub sems dpa'i thabs ni gang /
NK114(ye)001:10677: shes rab mngon par bsgrub pa ni gang zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:10678: gang gi phyir mnyam par bzhag pa na sems can
NK114(ye)001:10679: la blta bas na snying rje chen po'i dmigs pa
NK114(ye)001:10680: la sems nye bar 'jog pa de ni de'i thabs
NK114(ye)001:10681: so // gang gi phyir zhi ba dang rab tu
NK114(ye)001:10682: zhi bar snyoms par 'jug pa de ni de'i shes
NK114(ye)001:10684: de ltar zhi lhag zung 'jug gi lam de la
NK114(ye)001:10685: goms pa stobs su gyur pa las rang dang ngo
NK114(ye)001:10686: bo gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo mang po
NK114(ye)001:10688: 'di ltar kun rdzob kyi chos thams cad med bzhin
NK114(ye)001:10689: snang ba sgyu ma lta bu'i mnyam bzhag nyams 'og
NK114(ye)001:10690: tu chud cing dbang thob pa las rjes thob sgyu
NK114(ye)001:10691: ma mkhan bzhin du sprul pa'i bya ba ci 'dod
NK114(ye)001:10692: du byed pa la dbang 'byor pas sgyu ma lta
NK114(ye)001:10694: dpa' bo g.yul du 'jug pa na dpung tshogs yan lag bzhi dang /
NK114(ye)001:10695: 'khor los sgyur rgyal 'gro ba na rin chen sna bdun yang 'gro zhing dpa' ba brtul phod pa /
NK114(ye)001:10696: pha rol rnam par gnon pa bzhin zag pa med
NK114(ye)001:10697: pa'i ting nge 'dzin gang dang ldan par 'gro ba
NK114(ye)001:10698: na byang chub phyogs kyi chos thams cad kyang rjes
NK114(ye)001:10699: su 'brangs nas mdzad pa rlabs po che ston cing
NK114(ye)001:10700: lhag med kyi myang 'das su lhung gis dogs pa
NK114(ye)001:10701: med pas dpa' bar 'gro ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang
NK114(ye)001:10702: / rdo rje rin po ches dngos po thams cad
NK114(ye)001:10703: 'joms pa bzhin ting nge 'dzin gang gis phra rgyas
NK114(ye)001:10704: thams cad 'joms pas rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge
NK114(ye)001:10705: 'dzin te de la sogs pa ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK114(ye)001:10706: rnam grangs tshad med cing dpag tu med pa thams
NK114(ye)001:10708: de yang ma dag sa bdun na dang po dang /
NK114(ye)001:10709: dag sa gsum na gnyis pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10710: sa bcu'i rgyun mtha' na gsum pa yod la /
NK114(ye)001:10711: sbyor ba'i lam du de dag la bslab tshul yod
NK114(ye)001:10712: kyang dang po gnyis mos pas spyod pa tsam dang
NK114(ye)001:10713: / phyi ma ni sgrib pa bshig pa'i cha nas brjod do //
NK114(ye)001:10714: de ltar ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo de rnams thob
NK114(ye)001:10715: pa'i stobs kyis theg pa chen po'i thun mong ma
NK114(ye)001:10716: yin pa'i sa dang lam gyi yon tan ji snyed
NK114(ye)001:10717: pa'i rnam pa thams cad 'grub par byed cing /
NK114(ye)001:10718: de dag gis sgrib pa spong ba'i tshul yang /
NK114(ye)001:10719: mnyam rjes la dbye ba phye tshul gnyis las /
NK114(ye)001:10720: mnyam rjes ngo bo gcig pa'i dbang du byas na sems rtse gcig tu mnyam par bzhag pa'i tshe /
NK114(ye)001:10721: sems dang sems byung gi 'gyu ba rags pa thams
NK114(ye)001:10722: cad nub nas sems rtog med du gnas pa ni
NK114(ye)001:10724: de'i tshe dbang shes ma 'gags pa la yul snang
NK114(ye)001:10725: thams cad snang la 'dzin pa med par gsal ba'i
NK114(ye)001:10726: cha ni rjes thob yin pas blo rdzas gcig pa'i
NK114(ye)001:10727: mnyam bzhag dang rjes thob de yis gzung 'dzin gyi
NK114(ye)001:10728: rtog pa rim gyis spong bar byed la /
NK114(ye)001:10730: gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa zhes pa'i don la /
NK114(ye)001:10732: snang yul blo la shar ba'i tshe snang tsam gyis mi 'ching mod /
NK114(ye)001:10733: der zhen pa'i blo skyes pa na yul gyi rang
NK114(ye)001:10734: bzhin na med bzhin blo ngor bden par snang ba
NK114(ye)001:10736: der 'dzin pa skyes pa ni 'dzin pa yin la /
NK114(ye)001:10737: gnyis pa'i don yul gzugs sogs la de dang der 'dzin pa gzung rtog dang /
NK114(ye)001:10738: yul can tshogs brgyad kyi rtog pa la de dang der 'dzin pa 'dzin rtog zhes bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:10739: yid bzhin rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK114(ye)001:10740: 'di ltar yul las gzung ba'i rnam rtog dang //
NK114(ye)001:10741: don las 'dzin pa'i rnam rtog rnam gnyis skye //
NK114(ye)001:10742: de lus nyon mongs gzeb dang rten byed de //
NK114(ye)001:10743: mi mkhas bden par zhen pas rtag tu 'khor //
NK114(ye)001:10745: de yang gnas don lus gsum las don ni tshogs brgyad du bzhed pas de skad ces bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:10746: des na gzung 'dzin spong ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:10747: gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa spong ba don gcig ste
NK114(ye)001:10748: gzung 'dzin rtog pa spang na gzung 'dzin kyang spang
NK114(ye)001:10749: ba yin pa'i phyir ro snyam ste blo gsal dag
NK114(ye)001:10750: gis dpyod cig / yang mnyam rjes tha dad pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:10751: sems rtse gcig tu mnyam par bzhag pa'i tshe na mnyam bzhag yin la /
NK114(ye)001:10752: de las langs nas za nyal la sogs pa'i spyod
NK114(ye)001:10753: lam gyi tshe sgyu ma lta bu'i dran rdzi dang
NK114(ye)001:10754: ma bral ba ni rjes thob bo //
NK114(ye)001:10755: gzhan yang sngar bshad pa'i zhi lhag gi ting 'dzin
NK114(ye)001:10756: rnam med spros bral gyi ngo bo kho na bsgom
NK114(ye)001:10758: rnam bcas snying rje sogs bsgom pa la rjes thob tu bshad pa'ang yod do //
NK114(ye)001:10759: de dag gi tshe yang sbyin pa btang bas ser sna dang /
NK114(ye)001:10760: byams pa bsgoms pas zhe sdang dang //
NK114(ye)001:10761: zhen med kyi lta bas zin pas gzung 'dzin gyi
NK114(ye)001:10762: rtog pa spong ba'i gnyen po byed pas mtshon sgrib
NK114(ye)001:10763: pa gnyis ka'i gnyen po 'gro ba yin no //
NK114(ye)001:10764: rjes thob 'gro 'dug la sogs pa'i dus su tshogs
NK114(ye)001:10765: drug gi shes pa phyi rol la yeng nas rgya
NK114(ye)001:10766: yan du song ba la rgya yana pa zhes bya
NK114(ye)001:10767: ste / sems dran shes dang bral nas 'khrul 'byams
NK114(ye)001:10768: su song ba ste gzung 'dzin la sogs pa'i zhen
NK114(ye)001:10770: des na de lta bu ni sa bdun pa tshun
NK114(ye)001:10771: chad kun na yod pa yin zhes 'phags pa de
NK114(ye)001:10772: rnams la'ang skabs res 'gar de 'dra ba yod pa
NK114(ye)001:10773: yin la / dag sa thob nas med de mgon po byams pas /
NK114(ye)001:10774: bya ba bsgrub la rtag tu blo //
NK114(ye)001:10775: me bzhin du ni 'bar ba dang //
NK114(ye)001:10776: zhi ba'i bsam gtan snyoms 'jug la'ang //
NK114(ye)001:10777: rtag tu snyoms par 'jug pa yin //
NK114(ye)001:10779: 'on kyang mnyam rjes kyi khyad par tsam ni sangs rgyas ma thob bar du yod de /
NK114(ye)001:10780: mnyam par bzhag bzhin du spyod lam mdzad pa sangs rgyas kho na'i khyad chos yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:10781: drug pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:10782: shes rab gsum gyi rang bzhin spyir bstan pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10783: thos bsam sgom pa'i shes rab bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10784: dang po ni bslab pa gsum gyi nang tshan lhag
NK114(ye)001:10785: pa shes rab kyi bslab pa'i ngo bo dang dbye
NK114(ye)001:10786: ba la sogs pa'i don nges par 'byed cing gsal
NK114(ye)001:10788: ngo bo chos can dang chos nyid kyi don phyin
NK114(ye)001:10789: ci ma log par rnam par 'byed pa'i blo dam
NK114(ye)001:10791: de la dbye na sgom byung gi shes rab kho
NK114(ye)001:10792: na'i dbang du byas te ting nge 'dzin gyi sbyor
NK114(ye)001:10793: ba nyer bsdogs la goms pa las byung ba ste
NK114(ye)001:10794: de'i ngo bor skyes pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10795: yongs su sbyang ba byas pas sems las su rung
NK114(ye)001:10796: zhing sgrib pa'i rnyog pa dwangs ba'i bsam gtan dngos
NK114(ye)001:10797: gzhi'i ngo bor skyes pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10798: de ltar mnyam par bzhag pa'i dus su bsam gtan
NK114(ye)001:10799: gyi ngo bor shes rab mi rtog pa'i ye shes
NK114(ye)001:10800: skyes pa de'i rjes thob la /
NK114(ye)001:10801: de'i stobs las phung sogs kyi chos rnams sgyu ma
NK114(ye)001:10802: dang rmi lam la sogs pa bzhin du shes pa'i
NK114(ye)001:10803: shes rab ngang gis byung ba'i dbye bas rnam pa
NK114(ye)001:10805: yang gzhal bya bden pa gnyis kyi don gtso bo
NK114(ye)001:10806: gsung rab dgongs 'grel dang bcas pa'i tshig gi rjes
NK114(ye)001:10807: su gzhol te sgro 'dogs gcod par byed pa thos
NK114(ye)001:10809: de nas nang du sems pa na 'ol spyi tsam
NK114(ye)001:10810: du ma lus par gnad don bsdu zhing bye brag
NK114(ye)001:10811: 'byed pa'i bsam shes kyis brtags shing dpyad nas rang
NK114(ye)001:10812: rgyud la sbyar ba bsam pa'i shes rab dang /
NK114(ye)001:10813: bsam byung gis nges par byas pa'i don de la
NK114(ye)001:10814: rtse gcig tu mnyam par bzhag nas yang yang rang
NK114(ye)001:10815: rgyud la 'dris shing goms par byed pa bsgom pa
NK114(ye)001:10816: las byung ba'i shes rab ste /
NK114(ye)001:10817: de gsum la rim gyis bslab pas lhag mthonga rnam
NK114(ye)001:10818: par mi rtog pa'i ye shes yang dag par 'grub
NK114(ye)001:10820: thar ba la bar du gcod pa'i nyon mongs pa'i tshogs dang /
NK114(ye)001:10821: thams cad mkhyen pa la bar du gcod pa'i shes
NK114(ye)001:10822: bya'i sgrib pa thams cad rim gyis nyams smad de
NK114(ye)001:10823: drungs nas 'byin pa'i tshul gyis 'jomsa par byed cing
NK114(ye)001:10824: / chos nyid zab mo'i gnas lugs dang /
NK114(ye)001:10825: chos can 'khrul ngo la snang ba mtha' dag pa'i don ma nor bar shes pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10826: de ltar shes pas rgyu 'bras bslu ba med pa la nges pa rnyed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10827: chos dang chos ma yin pa'i bye brag phyed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10828: 'dod pa'i yon tan gyis bslur mi tshugs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10829: ston pa dang bstan pa'i yon tan la snying nas nges shes skye ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:10830: yon tan thams cad dge ba'i bshes gnyen la rag las par shes par dang /
NK114(ye)001:10831: bden gnyis dang drang nges sogs kyi don dang mdo
NK114(ye)001:10832: sngags kyi nyams len thams cad mi 'gal bar shes
NK114(ye)001:10833: shing nyams su len pa la blo mthu che ba
NK114(ye)001:10834: la sogs pa'o // 'bras bu ni de ltar shes
NK114(ye)001:10835: pas srid pa'i grong khyer sdig pa dang nyon mongs
NK114(ye)001:10836: pa shin tu brgal dka' ba 'di las ring por
NK114(ye)001:10837: mi thogs par brgal nas mya ngan te sdug bsngal
NK114(ye)001:10839: gtan bde 'gyur ba med pa'i sa la gtan srid
NK114(ye)001:10840: zin nas srid pa ji srid du 'gro ba'i don
NK114(ye)001:10841: 'bad pa med par 'byung ba yin te /
NK114(ye)001:10843: rmongs pas sdug bsngal can don du //
NK114(ye)001:10844: chags dang 'jigs mtha' las grol ba //
NK114(ye)001:10848: des na sbyin pa la sogs pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa rnam pa drug po'ang rgyu 'bras dang /
NK114(ye)001:10849: dman mchog dang rags phra'i dbang gis snga ma snga
NK114(ye)001:10850: ma las phyi ma phyi ma gong nas gong du
NK114(ye)001:10851: khyad zhugs pa'i tshul mdo sde'i rgyan gyi lung sngar
NK114(ye)001:10852: drangs pa ltar yin pas snga ma lnga ga'i 'bras
NK114(ye)001:10853: bu shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa yin
NK114(ye)001:10854: zhing / yang sbyin pa la ser sna med pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10855: tshul khrims kyis mi rlom pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10856: bzod pa bsgom pa la mi zhum pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10857: brtson 'grus la phyi bshol med pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10858: bsam gtan la mi zhen pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:10859: de thams cad byang chub chen po'i rgyur 'gro ba
NK114(ye)001:10860: yang shes rab kyis byed pas de thams cad kyi
NK114(ye)001:10861: yon tan shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa
NK114(ye)001:10864: pha rol phyin lnga byang chub yon tan ji snyed pa //
NK114(ye)001:10865: de dag kun kyang shes rab pha rol phyin la brten //
NK114(ye)001:10867: shes rab med pa'i nyes dmigs ni de las ldog pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10868: gnyis pa thos bsam sgom pa'i shes rab bye brag tu bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK114(ye)001:10871: bsgom pa'i shes rab bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10872: dang po thos pa'i shes rab bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:10873: thos pa gtso che ba'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK114(ye)001:10874: thos pa'i shes rab dngos bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:10876: de ltar phar phyin gzhan rnams las mchog tu 'phags
NK114(ye)001:10877: pa'i shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa rgyud
NK114(ye)001:10878: la bsten pa'i tshul de'ang lam la zhugs pa'i skabs
NK114(ye)001:10879: 'di na so so skye bo'i sar ni gang zag
NK114(ye)001:10880: thams cad la skyes thob kyi shes rab dang po
NK114(ye)001:10882: gal te 'ga' zhig la sngon goms pa brtan pas
NK114(ye)001:10883: skye ba 'di la thos bsam rgya chen po ma
NK114(ye)001:10884: byas kyang rang stobs kyi rig pa rno bas ye
NK114(ye)001:10885: sbyang mi dgos par shes pa lta bur snang ba
NK114(ye)001:10886: yod kyang / ji srid so so yang dag par
NK114(ye)001:10887: rig pa bzhi dang ldan pa sa dgu pa'i yon
NK114(ye)001:10888: tan rgyud la ma skyes pa de srid du dge
NK114(ye)001:10889: ba'i bshes gnyen las bslab dgos pa yin te gzhon
NK114(ye)001:10890: nu nor bzang la sogs pa'i rnam thar bzhin no
NK114(ye)001:10891: yod kyang / // de'i phyir na thog mar thos
NK114(ye)001:10892: pa las byung ba'i shes rab kyis 'khor ba dang
NK114(ye)001:10893: mya ngan las 'das pa'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK114(ye)001:10894: de'i rgyu la spang blang byed pa'i tshul dang /
NK114(ye)001:10895: de yang theg pa dman mchog dang /
NK114(ye)001:10896: mdo sngags kyi lam gyi khyad par dang /
NK114(ye)001:10897: nyams len gyi gnad thams cad bka' dang bstan bcos dag las shes par byas nas /
NK114(ye)001:10898: bslab gsum gyi nyams len thams cad rang rgyud la sgrub par byed dgos la /
NK114(ye)001:10899: de tsam mi nus pa dag gis kyang rang gi
NK114(ye)001:10900: blo nyams dang dpag pa'i nyams su len rgyu'i chos
NK114(ye)001:10901: de la thos pa re byed dgos par gsungs shing
NK114(ye)001:10902: / gal te de lta bu'i shes rab tsam yang
NK114(ye)001:10903: ma bsten na yun ring du bsam pa dang bsgom
NK114(ye)001:10904: pa dag 'bad pa drag pos byas kyang de'i yon
NK114(ye)001:10905: tan gang yang mi skye ba'am /
NK114(ye)001:10906: gnas min par 'khyams pa ste rnam grol gyi lam
NK114(ye)001:10907: las ring du gyur te srid pa'i rgyu las mi
NK114(ye)001:10908: 'da' zhing / der ma zad thos pa med pa'i
NK114(ye)001:10909: gang zag gis tshul khrims la sogs pa'i dge sbyor
NK114(ye)001:10910: ci byas kyang phal cher lung ma bstan tsam las
NK114(ye)001:10911: dge ba'i las su 'gyur bar yang dka' zhing /
NK114(ye)001:10912: gal te dge ba tsam du 'gyur srid na'ang dang po'i kun slong dngos gzhi'i sgrub tshul /
NK114(ye)001:10913: rjes su bsngo ba'i tshul gang yang ma shes na
NK114(ye)001:10914: thar lam rnal mar 'gyur dka' bas skyon che ba
NK114(ye)001:10915: yin te / ting 'dzin rgyal po las /
NK114(ye)001:10916: gal te tshul khrims grags pas de rgyags shing //
NK114(ye)001:10917: mang du thos la brtson par mi byed na //
NK114(ye)001:10918: tshul khrims 'bras bu ma lus zad nas ni //
NK114(ye)001:10919: phyir yang sdug bsngal rab tu myong bar 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:10921: gal te thos pa rgya mi che yang nyams len
NK114(ye)001:10922: gyi gnad khyad par can zin pa rnams kyis ni
NK114(ye)001:10923: de kho na bsgom po'i stobs kyis bsgom byung gi
NK114(ye)001:10924: shes rab nang nas rdol te ji lta ba dang
NK114(ye)001:10925: ji snyed pa'i don la ma rmongs pa'i shes rab
NK114(ye)001:10926: shugs kyis 'byung bar 'gyur ba yin la /
NK114(ye)001:10927: yang thos pa rgya che yang nyams len gyi gnad ma zin par tshig tsam la 'chel ba'am /
NK114(ye)001:10928: rang rgyud la ma sbyar na thos pa'i bag chags
NK114(ye)001:10929: tsam las rgyud la ci yang mi phan pas thos
NK114(ye)001:10930: pa gtan nas mi dgos pa'ang ma yin la thos
NK114(ye)001:10931: pa tsam gyis chog pa'ang ma yin te mdo sde'i
NK114(ye)001:10932: rgyan las / de ltas rnal 'byor can gyis bsgom pa gang yin de ni don med min //
NK114(ye)001:10933: de ltar bde bar bshegs kyis bstan pa gang yin de yang don med min //
NK114(ye)001:10934: gal te thos pa tsam gyis don mthong 'gyur na bsgom pa don med 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:10935: gal te ma thos par yang sgom 'jug 'gyur na bstan pa don med 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:10937: des na thos pa'i don bsam zhing de'i don tshul
NK114(ye)001:10938: bzhin bsgom pa las lam dang 'bras bu'i yon tan
NK114(ye)001:10939: thams cad 'byung bas na thos pa'i shes rab ni
NK114(ye)001:10940: de kun gyi rgyu ru gsungs pa yin te /
NK114(ye)001:10942: thos nyung dmus long bsgom pa'i tshul mi shes //
NK114(ye)001:10943: de med de kos ci zhig bsam par bya //
NK114(ye)001:10944: de bas thos la brtson bya de rgyu la //
NK114(ye)001:10945: bsam bzhin bsgom pas shes rab yangs pa 'byung //
NK114(ye)001:10948: shes rab mchog yin de'i gzhi ni //
NK114(ye)001:10949: thos pa de phyir thos pa mchog /
NK114(ye)001:10952: bzod bya thos pa btsal bar bya //
NK114(ye)001:10953: de nas nags su gnas par bya //
NK114(ye)001:10954: mnyam par bzhag la brtson bya zhing //
NK114(ye)001:10956: gnyis pa thos pa dngos bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:10957: 'jal byed rin chen lde'u mig gi rnam bzhag dang /
NK114(ye)001:10958: gzhal bya dam chos mdzod kyi rnam bzhag go //
NK114(ye)001:10962: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:10963: de la spyir theg pa chen po pa rnams kyis
NK114(ye)001:10964: thos pas gzhal bar bya ba'i gnas chen po lnga
NK114(ye)001:10965: la 'jal byed kyi shes rab kyis ma rmongs par
NK114(ye)001:10966: byas te rang gzhan gnyis ka'i don bsgrub pa yin
NK114(ye)001:10968: rig pa'i gnas lnga dag la brtson par ma byas na //
NK114(ye)001:10969: 'phags mchog gis kyang thams cad mkhyen nyid mi 'gyur te //
NK114(ye)001:10970: de lta bas na gzhan dag tshar bcad rjes bzung dang //
NK114(ye)001:10971: bdag nyid kun shes bya phyir de la de brtson byed //
NK114(ye)001:10973: bstan pa la ma dad pa rnams tshar bcad pa'i phyir sgra tshad gnyis /
NK114(ye)001:10974: dad pa rnams rjes su bzung ba'i phyir bzo gso gnyis /
NK114(ye)001:10975: bdag nyid kyis kun shes par bya ba'i phyir nang
NK114(ye)001:10976: rig pa 'tshol bar byed pa ni dgos pa bye
NK114(ye)001:10978: de thams cad kyang gzhan don du byang chub thob pa'i phyir 'tshol ba la khyad par med do //
NK114(ye)001:10979: de dag las 'dir phyi ma'i dbang du byas te /
NK114(ye)001:10980: gzhal bya'i chos bden pa gnyis kyi don ston pa'i gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis la /
NK114(ye)001:10981: 'jal byed thos pa'i shes rab kyis /
NK114(ye)001:10982: gzhal tshul drang don nges don gnyis dang dgongs pa
NK114(ye)001:10983: bzhi dang ldem dgongs rnam pa bzhir gzhal ba yin
NK114(ye)001:10984: no // de yang rgyal ba'i bstan pa la tshul
NK114(ye)001:10985: bzhin du 'jug par byed pa la rton pa bzhi
NK114(ye)001:10986: dang ldan par bya dgos te /
NK114(ye)001:10987: chos shes pa ni dge ba'i bshes gnyen la rag
NK114(ye)001:10988: las pas de bsten dgos kyang gang zag de bsten
NK114(ye)001:10989: pa tsam gyis rang la mi phan pas de kho
NK114(ye)001:10990: na la yid mi rton par de'i bstan pa'i chos
NK114(ye)001:10991: de la brtags nas yid rton par byed dgos shing
NK114(ye)001:10992: / chos de'i tshig ji ltar yang don rnam par
NK114(ye)001:10993: dag na de nyams su len dgos pa'i phyir tshig
NK114(ye)001:10994: shes pa tsam gyis mi chog pas de tsam la
NK114(ye)001:10995: mi rton par don rnam par dag pa de rang
NK114(ye)001:10996: rgyud la sbyar nas yid rton par byed dgos la
NK114(ye)001:10997: / / don de yang gdul bya dkri tshul gyis drang don dgongs pa can dang /
NK114(ye)001:10998: nges don dgongs pa can ma yin pa gnyis yod pa las /
NK114(ye)001:10999: drang don gyi gsung rnams gnas skabs kyi lam tsam
NK114(ye)001:11000: du bzung nas nyams su len na'ang de tsam la
NK114(ye)001:11001: mthar thug gi don du yid mi rton par nges
NK114(ye)001:11002: pa'i don la rton par byed cing /
NK114(ye)001:11003: nges don mthar thug pa don dam pa'i bden pa
NK114(ye)001:11004: ni blos gzhal dgos na'ang rnam par shes pas gzhal
NK114(ye)001:11005: zhing yul du byas pa thams cad ji ltar bzang
NK114(ye)001:11006: yang kun rdzob las mi 'da' bas de tsam la
NK114(ye)001:11007: yid mi rton par rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye
NK114(ye)001:11008: shes kyis mngon sum du mthong ba la rton par
NK114(ye)001:11010: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:11011: drang nges kyi khyad par dang /
NK114(ye)001:11012: dgongs ldem gyi khyad par bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:11013: dang po drang nges kyi khyad par bshad pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:11014: 'di ltar 'khor 'das lam gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK114(ye)001:11015: rnams thams cad kun gyi ngo bo'am gshis kyi gnas
NK114(ye)001:11016: tshul chos nyid de bzhin nyid dbyings rang bzhin gyis
NK114(ye)001:11017: rnam par dag pa sems nyid 'od gsal ba'i dgongs
NK114(ye)001:11018: pa ni rang bzhin gyis dag cing 'pho 'gyur med
NK114(ye)001:11019: pa skye 'gag gnas gsum las 'das pas rnam par
NK114(ye)001:11020: thar pa'i sgo stong pa nya da dang /
NK114(ye)001:11022: smon pa med pa gsum gyi rang bzhin du ye nas gnas pa ni nges pa'i don yin la /
NK114(ye)001:11023: de ston pa'i gsung rab rnams ni nges don gyi sde snod dang /
NK114(ye)001:11024: de'i dgongs pa 'grel pa ni nges don gyi dgongs pa 'grel ba'i bstan bcos so //
NK114(ye)001:11025: chos can kun rdzob kyi rang bzhin 'khrul ngor snang
NK114(ye)001:11026: tshod tsam 'di la brten nas lam la rim gyis
NK114(ye)001:11027: 'jug pa'i phyir gshis la ma grub bzhin rigs pas
NK114(ye)001:11028: gzhal nasa sgro btags te gzhi phung khams skye mched
NK114(ye)001:11029: sogs dang lam theg pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i rnam
NK114(ye)001:11031: 'bras bu'i rnam par bzhag pa myang 'das gsum gyi
NK114(ye)001:11032: rang bzhin du bstan pa thams cad ni drang ba'i
NK114(ye)001:11034: de ston pa'i gsung rab rnams ni drang don gyi sde snod dang /
NK114(ye)001:11035: de'i dgongs pa 'grel ba ni drang don gyi dgongs pa 'grel ba'i bstan bcos so //
NK114(ye)001:11036: 'o na phung po la sogs pa 'khrul snang gis
NK114(ye)001:11037: bsdus pa'i chos rnams kyi rnam bzhag bstan pa drang
NK114(ye)001:11039: theg pa dang 'bras bu'i rnam par bzhag pa rnams drang don du ji ltar bshad ce na /
NK114(ye)001:11040: theg pa zhes pa'ang 'gro ba'i blo ngor snang ba tsam las don la ma grub ste /
NK114(ye)001:11042: ji srid sems ni 'jug pa'i bar //
NK114(ye)001:11043: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK114(ye)001:11044: sems ni nam zhig gyur pa na //
NK114(ye)001:11045: theg pa med cing 'gro ba'ang med //
NK114(ye)001:11048: nga mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas mya ngan
NK114(ye)001:11049: las 'das pa de srid du chos gang yang bstan
NK114(ye)001:11050: pa med kyang de bzhin nyid las 'gro ba'i mos
NK114(ye)001:11051: pa ji lta ba bzhin du so sor snang ba
NK114(ye)001:11052: 'di yang sangs rgyas kyi gsung gi gsang ba bsam
NK114(ye)001:11055: 'bras bu sku gsum la sogs pa ji snyed cig
NK114(ye)001:11056: bstan pa de thams cad chos nyid bsam gyis mi
NK114(ye)001:11057: khyab pa'i ngo bor lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin
NK114(ye)001:11058: la tha snyad btags pa tsam las sgra gzugs la
NK114(ye)001:11059: sogs pa mtshan ma can du grub pa gang yang
NK114(ye)001:11060: med de / rdo rje gcod pa las /
NK114(ye)001:11061: gang dag nga la gzugs su mthong //
NK114(ye)001:11062: gang dag nga la sgrar shes pa //
NK114(ye)001:11063: log pa'i lam du zhugs pa ste //
NK114(ye)001:11064: skye bo des ni nga mi mthong //
NK114(ye)001:11065: sangs rgyas rnams ni chos nyid lta //
NK114(ye)001:11066: 'dren pa rnams ni chos kyi sku //
NK114(ye)001:11067: chos nyid shes bya ma yin te //
NK114(ye)001:11068: de ni shes par nus ma yin //
NK114(ye)001:11070: de'i phyir drang nges kyi mdo sde'i bstan don gsal bar ston pa /
NK114(ye)001:11071: 'phags pa blo gros mi zad pas bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:11072: nges pa'i don gyi mdo sde ni gang /
NK114(ye)001:11073: drang ba'i don gyi mdo sde ni gang zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:11074: mdo sde gang dag lam la 'jug pa'i phyir bstan pa de dag ni drang ba'i don zhes bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:11075: mdo sde gang dag 'bras bur 'jug pa'i phyir bstan pa de dag ni nges pa'i don zhes bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:11076: mdo sde gang dag bdag dang sems can dang sogs nas /
NK114(ye)001:11077: bdag po med pa la bdag po dang bcas par
NK114(ye)001:11078: bstan pa de dag ni drang ba'i don zhes bya'o
NK114(ye)001:11079: // mdo sde gang dag stong pa nyid dang sogs nas /
NK114(ye)001:11080: bdag po med pa dang rnam par thar pa'i sgo'i
NK114(ye)001:11081: bar du med par bstan pa ni nges pa'i don
NK114(ye)001:11083: des na bka' dang po drang don du bzhed pa la kun mthun kyang /
NK114(ye)001:11084: 'ga' zhig bar pa kho na nges don du bzhed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11085: 'ga' zhig bar ba drang nges phyed ma dang /
NK114(ye)001:11086: tha ma nges don du bzhed pa de rnams don
NK114(ye)001:11087: la dgongs pa'i gnad gcig ste bar tha gnyis kar
NK114(ye)001:11088: rang bzhin gshis kyi bzhugs tshul bstan pa rnams nges
NK114(ye)001:11090: de rtogs byed kyi thabs su tha snyad pa'i rnam
NK114(ye)001:11091: bzhag bstan pa'i cha rnams drang don du 'jog dgos
NK114(ye)001:11092: pa'i phyir mdo de dag gi brjod bya'i don gtso
NK114(ye)001:11093: che chung tsam la dgongs nas gdul bya dkri tshul
NK114(ye)001:11094: gyi dbang gis de ltar bzhed pa yin no snyam
NK114(ye)001:11095: mo // de ltar drang don dang nges don gyi
NK114(ye)001:11096: mdo sde de gnyis po'i brjod bya'i don ji ltar
NK114(ye)001:11097: yin shes pas drang don dang nges don gang la
NK114(ye)001:11098: yid rton pa dang mi rton pa'i tshul sngar bshad
NK114(ye)001:11099: pa ltar shes pa de ni gsung rab kyi sde
NK114(ye)001:11100: snod thams cad brjod bya sna tshogs pa dang ldan
NK114(ye)001:11101: pa'i mdzod khang lta bur gyur pa de so sor
NK114(ye)001:11102: 'byed cing blta bar bya ba'i lde'u mig dang po
NK114(ye)001:11104: gnyis pa dgongs ldem dgongs kyi khyad par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:11105: dgos pa brjod nas mdor bstan pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11106: so so'i ngo bo rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:11108: gong du ji skad bshad pa'i drang don dang nges
NK114(ye)001:11109: don de dag gi rang bzhin tha dad par gsal
NK114(ye)001:11110: bar byas nas drang don dgongs pa can gyi gsung
NK114(ye)001:11111: 'di lta bu'o zhes ston pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11112: drang don gyi mdo'i dgongs gzhi dang dgos pa brtags
NK114(ye)001:11113: nas mthar nges don gyi dgongs pa ji lta ba
NK114(ye)001:11114: bzhin rtogs par bya ba'i phyir dgongs pa bzhi dang
NK114(ye)001:11115: ldem dgongs bzhi ste gnyis bshad pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:11116: gnyis pa so so'i ngo bo rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK114(ye)001:11117: dgongs pa bzhi bshad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11118: ldem dgongs bzhi bshad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11119: de gnyis kyi khyad par bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:11120: dang po dgongs pa bzhi bshad pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:11124: de ltar gnyis las dang po dgongs pa bzhi ni /
NK114(ye)001:11125: rang rang gi dgongs gzhi'i don de la cung zad sgro btags nas bshad du yang yod la /
NK114(ye)001:11126: gdul bya'i yul gyi gang zag rnams re zhig tshig
NK114(ye)001:11127: tsam gyis dgongs gzhi'i don rtogs pa la kha drang
NK114(ye)001:11128: ba gcig pu'i slad du bsten pa ldem dgongs lta
NK114(ye)001:11130: de las gzhan pa'i dgosa ched dang bcas nas dgongs
NK114(ye)001:11131: pa rnam pa bzhir ston pa ste des na 'di
NK114(ye)001:11132: dag dgongs gzhi gtso che bas na dgos ched grub
NK114(ye)001:11133: kyang dgongs gzhi da dung mi rtogs so //
NK114(ye)001:11134: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:11136: mnyam pa nyid dang don gzhan dang //
NK114(ye)001:11137: de bzhin du ni dus gzhan dang //
NK114(ye)001:11138: gang zag gi ni bsam pa la //
NK114(ye)001:11139: dgongs pa rnam par bzhir shes bya //
NK114(ye)001:11141: dang po ni spyir chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs la bzang ngan dang tha dad med pas /
NK114(ye)001:11142: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyang chos sku'i klong du mnyam zhing gcig pa nyid la dgongs nas /
NK114(ye)001:11143: nga nyid de'i tshe na yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:11144: sangs rgyas rnam par gzigs su gyur to zhes gsungs
NK114(ye)001:11146: de yang tshur rol mthong ba can gyi blo ngor 'khor 'das dang /
NK114(ye)001:11148: blang dor gyi mtshan nyid thams cad shin tu 'gal bar snang bas /
NK114(ye)001:11149: sangs rgyas de dag dus snga phyi dang gzugs sku
NK114(ye)001:11150: tha dad par snang bas 'gal ba lta bu yin
NK114(ye)001:11151: na'ang gcig tu bstan pas sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa
NK114(ye)001:11153: sku bongs chung ba sogs su blta ba'i brnyas pa ldog pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:11155: don gzhan ngo bo nyid med pa kun brtags la
NK114(ye)001:11156: sogs pa gsum po la dgongs nas gzugs nas rnam
NK114(ye)001:11157: mkhyen gyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad la dpyad na
NK114(ye)001:11158: gang yang ma grub par bstan pas dpyad pa la
NK114(ye)001:11159: sogs pa la brten nas bden zhen ldog pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:11160: mtshan nyid gsum po ngo bo nyid med pa'i don
NK114(ye)001:11161: kun mkhyen 'jigs gling rang nyid kyis dgongs 'grel gyi
NK114(ye)001:11163: nges don gyi mdo'i chings chen po yang dag pa nyid yin par rig pa bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:11165: yongs grags la sems tsam pa rnams kyis 'di gsum
NK114(ye)001:11166: ngo bo med tshul de tsam las chos thams cad
NK114(ye)001:11167: ngo bo nyid med pa ma yin pas yum mdo'i
NK114(ye)001:11168: dngos bstan drang don du 'dod pa de la bshad
NK114(ye)001:11169: nas dbu ma'i 'dod par ma bzhag go //
NK114(ye)001:11171: dus gzhan ma 'ongs pa zhig la 'tshang rgya ba'i
NK114(ye)001:11172: rgyu'am sa bon tsam zhig thebs pa la dgongs nas
NK114(ye)001:11173: gzungs sngags 'ga' zhig lan gcig brjod pa tsam mam
NK114(ye)001:11174: / de bzhin gshegs pa dri med zla 'od kyi
NK114(ye)001:11175: mtshan bzung ba tsam gyis 'bad pa med par 'tshang
NK114(ye)001:11176: rgya bar bstan pa lta bu'i le lo can dge
NK114(ye)001:11179: gang zag la la dag sbyin pa la mngon par rlom pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11180: yang 'ga' zhing tshul khrims la mchog tu 'dzin pa
NK114(ye)001:11181: sogs dge ba'i bya ba gang la mchog tu 'dzin
NK114(ye)001:11182: na dge ba de nyid bdud las ma yin kyang
NK114(ye)001:11183: mchog tu 'dzin pa ni thar ba'i gegs yin pa
NK114(ye)001:11184: la dgongs nas / sbyin pa ni bdud kyi las
NK114(ye)001:11185: so zhes smad nas tshul khrims sogs la basngagasa pa'am
NK114(ye)001:11186: la dgongs nas / / tshul khrims ni bdud kyi
NK114(ye)001:11187: las so zhes smad nas sbyin pa sogs gzhan la
NK114(ye)001:11188: bstod pa lta bu gang dang gang la mchog tu
NK114(ye)001:11189: 'dzin pa de dang de'i mchog 'dzin la smad nas
NK114(ye)001:11190: mngon rlom zhi bar byed pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:11191: rlom sems dang mtshan 'dzin ni mi mthun pa'i phyogs chen po yin te /
NK114(ye)001:11192: 'jam dpal rnam par 'phrul ba'i le'u las /
NK114(ye)001:11193: lha'i bu ji tsam du las la 'jug pa de tsam du bdud kyi las so //
NK114(ye)001:11194: ji tsam du smon pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11196: ji tsam du mchog tu 'dzin pa de tsam du
NK114(ye)001:11197: bdud kyi las so zhes pa la sogs pa dang
NK114(ye)001:11198: / sbyin pa'i sems la mngon par zhen pa yang bdud kyi las so zhes pa nas /
NK114(ye)001:11199: shes rab kyi sems la mngon par zhen pa yang
NK114(ye)001:11200: bdud kyi las so zhes gsungs pas rtag tu dge
NK114(ye)001:11201: sbyor ci byed kyang sgyu ma rmi lam lta bu'i
NK114(ye)001:11202: dran 'dun gyis ma zhen par bya ba gal che'o
NK114(ye)001:11203: // gnyis pa ldem dgongs bzhi bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:11207: ldem por dgongs pa zhes pa ni don ji bzhin
NK114(ye)001:11208: min pa'i ngag gis don de nyid bstan pa ste
NK114(ye)001:11209: / de'i tshul ni gdul bya blo dman pa gang
NK114(ye)001:11210: zhig la bden gnyis dbyer med dang sangs rgyas byang
NK114(ye)001:11211: sems kyi thun min gyi yon tan ji lta ba
NK114(ye)001:11212: bzhin gsal por brjod pa'i tshig gis dang po nas
NK114(ye)001:11213: bstan na de dag gi blo la mi chud par
NK114(ye)001:11214: yid gnyis kyi gnas thoba ste don de la 'jug
NK114(ye)001:11215: mi nus pa'i rigs rnams la /
NK114(ye)001:11216: re zhig de nyid kyi blo chud cing dga' bar
NK114(ye)001:11217: 'gyur ba'i ming dang cha ldan cung zad yod pa'i
NK114(ye)001:11218: rgyu mtshan gyis de las rnam par kyogs nas yang
NK114(ye)001:11219: dag pa'i don dgongs gzhi de bsgrub pa'i lam la
NK114(ye)001:11220: gzud pa'i phyir / tshig ni nyan pa po de'i
NK114(ye)001:11221: blo dang mthun pa ste 'tshams pa zhig yin yang
NK114(ye)001:11222: don mi mthun par bshad pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:11223: de la dbye na mdo sde'i rgyan las /
NK114(ye)001:11224: zhugs pa ldem por dgongs pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:11225: mtshan nyid ldem por dgongs pa gzhan //
NK114(ye)001:11226: gnyen po ldem por dgongs pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:11227: bsgyur ba ldem por dgongs pa ste //
NK114(ye)001:11228: zhes pa ltar zhugs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11231: bsgyur ba ldem por dgongs pa ste bzhi yod do //
NK114(ye)001:11232: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la de ltar rnam pa bzhi las /
NK114(ye)001:11233: dang po zhugs pa ldem por dgongs pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:11234: gang zhig rigs dang mos pa sogs dman pa nyan
NK114(ye)001:11235: thos dag la chos kyi bdag med yongs rdzogs ston
NK114(ye)001:11236: pa'i gzhung yum mdo lta bu'i don dang po nas
NK114(ye)001:11237: bstan na / des de rten 'byung gi don du
NK114(ye)001:11238: mi go bar tha snyad kyis stong pa'i chad lta
NK114(ye)001:11239: lta bur go nas brjod bya'i don dang rjod byed
NK114(ye)001:11240: kyi tshig gnyis ka la skrag nas theg chen gyi
NK114(ye)001:11241: lam dang bka' gnyis ka spong ba de rnams la
NK114(ye)001:11242: bstan na / mdo las / rab 'byor gzugs ni mtshan ma'o //
NK114(ye)001:11245: gzugsa la sogs pa'i chos rnams yod do zhes smos
NK114(ye)001:11246: pas nyan pa po skrag pa mi skye bar don
NK114(ye)001:11247: la grub par go nas lam la rim gyis 'jug
NK114(ye)001:11248: pa ni dgos ched yin la /
NK114(ye)001:11249: dgongs gzhi ni 'khrul ngor snang tshod rmi lam lta bur dgongs pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:11250: de yang stong nyid la skrag pa'i tshul pan+di ta
NK114(ye)001:11251: d+ai pam k+aa ra'i mdun du 'phags yul gyi dge
NK114(ye)001:11252: slong sbyangs pa'i yon tan bcu gnyis la gnas pa
NK114(ye)001:11253: gnyis byung / jo bos gang zag gi bdag med gsungs pa'i tshe khong gnyis dad /
NK114(ye)001:11254: chos kyi bdag med gsungs pa'i tshe de skad mi gsung ba zhu 'jigs 'jigs zer ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:11255: shes rab snying po thos pa'i tshe rna ba dgab /
NK114(ye)001:11256: jo bo thugs chad nas byams snying rje byang chub
NK114(ye)001:11257: kyi sems kyis 'phangs nas tshogs khyad par can la
NK114(ye)001:11258: ma 'bad na bsrung sdom dag pa gcig pus gar
NK114(ye)001:11259: yang mi phyin gsungs pa lta bu'o //
NK114(ye)001:11260: gnyis pa mtshan nyid la ldem por dgongs pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:11261: chos rnams kyi gnas lugs ngo bo nyid med par
NK114(ye)001:11262: bstan pa de gtan med lta bu ma yin par
NK114(ye)001:11263: rnam par thar pa'i sgo gsum gyi rang bzhin du
NK114(ye)001:11264: gnas pa'i don de shes pa'i don du rim pa
NK114(ye)001:11265: bzhin / byis pas bden par sgro btags pa'i kun brtags dang /
NK114(ye)001:11266: rten 'brel gyi ngo bor snang tsam pa'i gzhan dbang dang /
NK114(ye)001:11267: rang bzhin spros pa dang bral ba'i yongs grub rnam pa gsum po dag las /
NK114(ye)001:11268: dang por ngo bo nyid med pa'i tshul ni kun
NK114(ye)001:11269: brtags la mtshan nyid kyi ngo bo nyid med de
NK114(ye)001:11270: byis pa'i log shes kyi yul de don du nges
NK114(ye)001:11272: dper na thag khra la sbrul du 'khrul pa bzhin dang /
NK114(ye)001:11273: gnyis par ngo bo nyid med pa'i tshul ni gzhan dbang la skye ba ngo bo nyid med de /
NK114(ye)001:11274: skye ba ltar snang yang dpyad na mu bzhi las
NK114(ye)001:11275: skye ba ma grub pa'i phyir dper na sgyu ma'i
NK114(ye)001:11277: gsum par ngo bo nyid med pa'i tshul ni yongs
NK114(ye)001:11278: grub la don dam pa'i ngo bo nyid med de
NK114(ye)001:11279: don dam pa yin zhing bdag nyid la ma dag
NK114(ye)001:11280: pa la sogs pa spros pa'i ngo bo nyid med
NK114(ye)001:11281: pa'i phyir / dper nam mkha'i ngo bo la sprin gyis mi gos pa bzhin yin pas /
NK114(ye)001:11282: don de rnams la dgongs nas gzugs nas rnam mkhyen
NK114(ye)001:11283: gyi bar gyi chos rnams ngo bo nyid med pa
NK114(ye)001:11284: ma skyes pa zhes pa la sogs pa'i brjod pa
NK114(ye)001:11285: zab pa gting dpag dka' ba dag tu ston par
NK114(ye)001:11287: ma skyes dgras 'jam dpal la bdag gi 'gyod pa bsal du gsol zhus pas /
NK114(ye)001:11289: rgyal po khyod kyi 'gyod pa ni sangs rgyas bcom
NK114(ye)001:11290: ldan 'das gang g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed kyis
NK114(ye)001:11291: kyang bsal bar mi spyod do //
NK114(ye)001:11292: de nas rgyal po ma skyes dgra skyabs ma rnyed
NK114(ye)001:11293: nas shing bcad pa ltar sa chen po la 'gyel
NK114(ye)001:11294: to // de nas gnas brtan 'od srung chen pos
NK114(ye)001:11295: rgyal po ma skyes dgra la 'di skad ces smras
NK114(ye)001:11296: to // so // rgyal po chen po 'jal dpal
NK114(ye)001:11297: gzhon nur gyur pa ni ldem po'i ngag tu ston
NK114(ye)001:11298: pa la mkhas kyis ma 'jigs ma skrag par don
NK114(ye)001:11299: de ci la dgongs te gsungs dras shig ces pa
NK114(ye)001:11300: to // so // lta bu'o // mtshan nyid ldem dgongs 'di yongs grags la /
NK114(ye)001:11302: gzhan dbang rang skye ba'i dang /
NK114(ye)001:11303: yongs grub gzhan dbang las logs su med pa'i phyir ngo bo med pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:11304: de gsum la dgongs nas ngo bo nyid med par
NK114(ye)001:11305: ston pa drang don no zhes sems tsam pa kho
NK114(ye)001:11307: 'di'i bshad tshul dang mi gcig go //
NK114(ye)001:11308: gsum pa gnyen po ldem dgos ni /
NK114(ye)001:11310: sangs rgyas chos la brnyas pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:11311: le lo cung zad chog 'dzin dang //
NK114(ye)001:11312: nga rgyal 'dod chags spyod pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:11313: 'gyod dang ma nges ldog pa ni //
NK114(ye)001:11314: sems can rnams kyi sgrib pa ste //
NK114(ye)001:11315: de yi gnyen por theg mchog gsungs //
NK114(ye)001:11316: zhes pa ltar nyes pa brgyad 'dul ba'i phyir bstan pa lta bu ste /
NK114(ye)001:11317: dang po sangs rgyas la brnyas pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:11318: blo dman pa gzhan gyis 'di snyam du bskal pa
NK114(ye)001:11319: bzang po'i mdo sde nas sangs rgyas stong rtsa ston
NK114(ye)001:11320: pa'i tshe de dag gi nang nas sh+aakya thub pa
NK114(ye)001:11321: ni sku bongs chung zhing 'od kyang 'dom gang ba
NK114(ye)001:11323: sku tshe yang thung bas gzhan las dman no snyam
NK114(ye)001:11324: du log par rtog na de ldog pa'i ched du
NK114(ye)001:11325: / rnam snang gangs chen mtsho'i sku gsung thugs yon
NK114(ye)001:11326: tan phrin las mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i
NK114(ye)001:11327: tshul la basngagasa nas sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sprul
NK114(ye)001:11328: gzhi bdag nyid yin par zhal gyis bzhes pa lta
NK114(ye)001:11329: / bu ste / de ltar bstan pas nyan pa
NK114(ye)001:11330: pos gzugs sku'i rang bzhin gcig tu mnyam par go
NK114(ye)001:11332: 'chad pa po'i sku tshe dang rigs dang sku bongs kyi tshad kyis mnyam pa min yang /
NK114(ye)001:11333: sangs rgyas thams cad gzugs sku gdul bya'i ngor snang tsam dang /
NK114(ye)001:11334: chos sku skye ba med par mnyam pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11335: tshogs gnyis kyi bya ba yongs su rdzogs par dang /
NK114(ye)001:11336: gdul bya'i yul la'ang phrin las rtsol med du 'jug pa la mnyam pa lta bur dgongs so //
NK114(ye)001:11337: des mtshon nas gnyis pa lung gi chos la brnyas
NK114(ye)001:11338: pa'i gnyen por gang g+aa'i klung gi bye ma dang
NK114(ye)001:11339: mnyam pa'i sangs rgyas la bsnyen bkur byas na /
NK114(ye)001:11340: gzod theg chen gyi rtogs pa skye'o zhes gsungs pa lta bu'o //
NK114(ye)001:11341: de'i don bshad sbyar du lung las don gzhan theg
NK114(ye)001:11342: chen gyi rtogs pa'i chos la dgongs nas gsungs par
NK114(ye)001:11343: bshad do // gsum pa le lo'i sgrib pa'i gnyen por ni /
NK114(ye)001:11344: dus gzhan la dgongs par bshad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11345: bzhi pa cung zad tsam gyis chog par 'dzin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:11346: gnyen por gang zag gi bsam pa la dgongs par
NK114(ye)001:11347: bshad pa dang / lnga pa nga rgyal la spyod
NK114(ye)001:11348: pa'i gnyen por sangs rgyas la la'i phun sum tshogs
NK114(ye)001:11349: pa basngagasa pa lta bu dang /
NK114(ye)001:11350: drug pa 'dod chags la spyod pa'i gnyen por sangs
NK114(ye)001:11351: rgyas kyi zhing gi 'byor pa basngagasa pa lta bu
NK114(ye)001:11352: dang / bdun pa 'gyod pa'i gnyen por gang dag
NK114(ye)001:11353: sangs rgyas byang sems la gnod pa byed pa de
NK114(ye)001:11354: dag mtho ris su 'agro'o zhes pa lta bu dang
NK114(ye)001:11355: dang / / brgyad pa ma nges pa ldog pa'i
NK114(ye)001:11356: sgrib pa'i gnyen por nyan thos rnams lung bstan pa
NK114(ye)001:11357: dang / / dang / theg pa gcig tu bshad pa lta bu'o //
NK114(ye)001:11358: dbu ma pas theg gcig ston pa'i mdo sde nges don du bzhed pas /
NK114(ye)001:11360: bzhi pa bsgyur ba ldem dgongs ni /
NK114(ye)001:11361: dge sbyong goo ta ma ni nan tan gyis ma
NK114(ye)001:11362: bskul yang chos 'chad do zhes zer ba'i 'phya ba
NK114(ye)001:11363: bsal ba dang / lo drug tu dka' ba spyad
NK114(ye)001:11364: pa kho nas khyad par thob na thob bya'i chos
NK114(ye)001:11365: de yang gting dpag sla'o snyam pa bsal ba'i phyir
NK114(ye)001:11366: bsal ba dang / / zab zhi spros bral sogs
NK114(ye)001:11367: gsungs nas chos mi gsung bar bzhugs pa'i tshul bstan
NK114(ye)001:11369: khyad par du brjod bya zab mo gzhan du 'dren
NK114(ye)001:11370: pa ste 'di ltar bsad par bya ba ma yin
NK114(ye)001:11371: pa'i pha dang ma gsod par bstan pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11372: de bzhin du bcom bya min pa'i rgyal po dang
NK114(ye)001:11373: ni bram ze dang dge sbyong ste gtsang sbra can
NK114(ye)001:11374: gnyis dang / yul 'khor skor dang bcas pa rnams
NK114(ye)001:11375: bcom na de ltar byed pa po de dag pa
NK114(ye)001:11376: nyid du 'gyur bar gsungs pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:11377: ched du brjod pa'i tshoms las /
NK114(ye)001:11378: pha dang ma ni bsad bya zhing //
NK114(ye)001:11379: rgyal po gtsang sbra can gnyis dang //
NK114(ye)001:11380: yul 'khor skor bcas rab bcom na //
NK114(ye)001:11381: mi de dag pa nyid du 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:11383: de dag gi dgongs gzhi ni 'khor bar 'du byed
NK114(ye)001:11384: pas sred pa dang len pa ni pha dang ma'o
NK114(ye)001:11385: // bag chags sna tshogs pa'i rten nam gzhir gyur bas kun gzhi ni rgyal po'o //
NK114(ye)001:11386: sogs khongs nas bram ze ni 'jigs tshogs la lta ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:11387: dge sbyong ni tshul khrims dang brtul zhugs mchog 'dzin
NK114(ye)001:11388: te yang dag pa'i lta spyod kyis ma gos pas
NK114(ye)001:11390: nang gi skye mched gzung 'dzin dang bcas pa'i rnam
NK114(ye)001:11391: shes tshogs brgyad ni yul 'khor gyi skor dang bcas
NK114(ye)001:11392: pa ste / bsad pa dang bcom pa'i don yang
NK114(ye)001:11393: dag pa'i lta spyod kyis sred len rgyun bcad nas
NK114(ye)001:11394: tshogs brgyad bag chags dang bcas pa dag par byas
NK114(ye)001:11395: na 'tshang rgya ba la dgongs nas de ltar btags
NK114(ye)001:11396: pa ste / pa yin pas / dgongs gzhi de
NK114(ye)001:11397: lta bu yin pa ma shes par sgra ji bzhin
NK114(ye)001:11398: par bltas te pha ma gsod pa la sogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:11399: don rnal mar bzung na shin tu nor ba chen
NK114(ye)001:11402: snying po med la snying por shes //
NK114(ye)001:11403: phyin ci log la legs par gnas //
NK114(ye)001:11404: nyon mongs pas ni rab nyon mongs //
NK114(ye)001:11405: byang chub dam pa thob par 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:11407: de yang sa ra zhes pa'i sgra gcig las du
NK114(ye)001:11408: ma 'phro ba lta bu la 'jug pas snying po'am
NK114(ye)001:11409: rnam par 'phro ba rnam g.yeng gnyis ka la bshad
NK114(ye)001:11410: du yod pas / snying po ni sems kyi rnam
NK114(ye)001:11411: g.yeng dang de med pa ni snying po med pa'o
NK114(ye)001:11412: du yod pas / // phyin ci log ni gtsang bde rtag bdag las log pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:11413: nyon mongs pa ni yun ring por dka' spyad kyis
NK114(ye)001:11414: ngal ba la dgongs nas de ltar gsungs pa'i don
NK114(ye)001:11415: rnam g.yeng spangs nas phyiin ci log gi rtog pa
NK114(ye)001:11416: bzhi'i gnyen po yun ring du brten nas byang chub
NK114(ye)001:11417: thob pa la go dgos pa la sogs pa lta
NK114(ye)001:11421: nyan thos dang ni ngo bo nyid //
NK114(ye)001:11422: de bzhin nyes pa 'dul ba dang //
NK114(ye)001:11423: brjod pa zab pa nyid la ni //
NK114(ye)001:11424: ldem por dgongs pa rnam pa bzhi //
NK114(ye)001:11426: gsum pa de gnyis kyi khyad par ni /
NK114(ye)001:11427: mdor bsdu na dgongs pa bzhi dang ldema por dgongs
NK114(ye)001:11428: pa bzhi ste de gnyis po'i rang bzhin ci rigs
NK114(ye)001:11429: par ngo bo gcig la bye brag tha dad pa
NK114(ye)001:11430: yang yod de de'i khyad par ni /
NK114(ye)001:11431: dgongs pa ni sgras zin tshod de tshig de'i dgongs pa min par logs su bshad nas /
NK114(ye)001:11432: 'di la bsams te gsungs so zhes smra ba pos
NK114(ye)001:11433: yid la rnam par bzhag pa'i bsam pa tsam ston
NK114(ye)001:11434: pa'i cha nas bzhag pa yin gyi pha rol gzung
NK114(ye)001:11435: ba la ltos pa min zhes de'i cha nas bzhag
NK114(ye)001:11436: pa min no // ldem por dgongs pa ni thad
NK114(ye)001:11437: kar mi ston par 'khyog po'i ngag gis bstan pa'i
NK114(ye)001:11438: dgos pa 'adi'o zhes pha rol gzung ba la ltos
NK114(ye)001:11439: pa ste dgos pa ston pa'i cha nas bzhag go
NK114(ye)001:11440: pa min no // // 'di la lo ts+aa ba
NK114(ye)001:11441: blo ldan shes rab kyis ni smra ba po'i bsam
NK114(ye)001:11442: pa'i don las don zhen smra ba po'i tshig las
NK114(ye)001:11443: nyan pa pos go bar byed pa ni dgongs pa
NK114(ye)001:11444: pa min no // // yin la / smra ba
NK114(ye)001:11445: po'i bsam pa'i don de nyid nyan pa pos go
NK114(ye)001:11446: bar byed pa ni ldem dgongs so zhes bzhed cing
NK114(ye)001:11447: pa min no // // yin la / / theg bsdus kyi 'grel pa bshad sbyar las /
NK114(ye)001:11448: dgongs pa ni yid la rnam par bzhag pa tsam yin gyi /
NK114(ye)001:11449: pha rol gzung ba la ltos pa ni khas mi len to //
NK114(ye)001:11450: ldem por dgongs pa ni pha rol gzung ba la ltos pa'o zhes gsungs so //
NK114(ye)001:11451: de gnyis ka'ang 'gal ba med de /
NK114(ye)001:11452: de'ang 'ga' zhig la ltos nas de'i cha ldan du bshad pa ni pha rol gzung ba'am /
NK114(ye)001:11453: gzung ba la ma ltos kyang dgongs pa yin la
NK114(ye)001:11454: de nyid gzhan gyis dris pa la sogs pa'i tshe
NK114(ye)001:11455: don mtha' dag ma rdzogs pas da dung dgongs gzhi
NK114(ye)001:11456: la lus pa'i phyir dgongs pa zhes bya la /
NK114(ye)001:11457: gzhan la phan gdags pa'i phyir rgyu mtshan cung zad
NK114(ye)001:11458: la brten nas kho'i snang ba dang mthun par ston
NK114(ye)001:11459: pa ni ldem dgongs zhes bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:11461: pha rol pos kyang de go nas zhugs pas da
NK114(ye)001:11462: gzod don gzhan rdzogs par go ba'i rten byed cing
NK114(ye)001:11463: brdzun du'ang ma gyur tsam du gnas pa'i phyir ro
NK114(ye)001:11464: // des na de ltar sgra dang /
NK114(ye)001:11467: dgos ched kyi gnas skabs du ma yod pa de
NK114(ye)001:11468: rnams tshul bzhin du rnam par 'byed shes pa'i shes
NK114(ye)001:11469: rab ni gsung rab mdo rgyud rnams la blta ba'i
NK114(ye)001:11470: lde mig gnyis pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:11471: gnyis pa gzhal bya dam chos mdzod kyi rnam bzhag bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:11472: bden gnyis kyi rang bzhin spyir bshad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11473: grub matha'i 'dod gzhung bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:11478: de lta bu'i shes rab dri ma med pa des
NK114(ye)001:11479: gang la gzhal bar bya ba'i yul gyi ngos nasa
NK114(ye)001:11480: rgyal ba thabs mkhas la thugs rje chen po dang
NK114(ye)001:11481: ldan pa des gdul bya'i khams dbang mos pa bsam
NK114(ye)001:11482: pa'i bye brag dang 'tshams pa'i chos kyi rnam grangs
NK114(ye)001:11483: ji snyed cig bstan pa de thams cad yin la
NK114(ye)001:11484: de dag kyang srid par 'ching byed kyi rtsa ba
NK114(ye)001:11485: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug ste /
NK114(ye)001:11486: dug gsum gyi gnyen por brjod bya mngon rtogs bslab
NK114(ye)001:11487: pa gsum gyi don ston par byed pa'i rjod byed
NK114(ye)001:11488: lung gi chos 'dul ba mdo sde mngon pa ste
NK114(ye)001:11490: dug gsum cha mnyam pa'i gnyen por bslab pa gsum
NK114(ye)001:11491: gyi rang bzhin cha mnyam la rgya che zhing zab
NK114(ye)001:11492: par ston pa rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde snod dang
NK114(ye)001:11493: bzhir gnas la / de re re la nyi khri
NK114(ye)001:11494: chig stong rer phye ba'i chos kyi sgo brgyad khri
NK114(ye)001:11495: bzhi stong gsungs pa mtha' dag pa'i brjod bya'i don
NK114(ye)001:11496: gyi dbye ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig yod
NK114(ye)001:11497: na'ang bsdu na rnam pa gnyis su 'du ba yin
NK114(ye)001:11498: bzhir gnas la / no // gnyis po de gang zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:11499: snang lugs kun rdzob kyi bden pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11500: gnas lugs don dam pa'i bden pa dag ste /
NK114(ye)001:11502: sangs rgyas rnams kyis chos bstan pa //
NK114(ye)001:11503: bden pa gnyis la yang dag brten //
NK114(ye)001:11504: 'jig rten kun rdzob bden pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:11505: dasama pa'i don gyi bden pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:11507: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bdun te /
NK114(ye)001:11516: bden pa gnyis ka'i spyi'am thun mong ba'i ngo bo
NK114(ye)001:11517: 'adi'o zhes ngos bzung byed rgyu mtshan nyid pa zhig
NK114(ye)001:11518: med de chos thams cad bden pa dang bden pa
NK114(ye)001:11519: ma yin pa'i tha snyad las 'das shing /
NK114(ye)001:11520: mtshan nyid dang bral ba'i dbyings su tshul gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:11521: de lta na'ang 'jig rten pa'i blo don bden pa
NK114(ye)001:11522: ma yin pa log tsam gyi bden pa tsam zhig
NK114(ye)001:11524: rigs pa drug cu pa'i 'grel pa las /
NK114(ye)001:11525: bden pa gnyis su 'jig rten pa'i blo la ltos nas 'jog go //
NK114(ye)001:11527: de'ang 'jig rten 'khor ba'i chos sems dang sems las
NK114(ye)001:11528: byung ba yul gyi rnam pa snang ba dang bcas
NK114(ye)001:11529: pa thams cad kun rdzob kyi bden pa'i ngo bo
NK114(ye)001:11531: blo ni kun rdzob yin par brjod //
NK114(ye)001:11534: sems nyid kyis ni sems can 'jig rten dang //
NK114(ye)001:11535: snod kyi 'jig rten shin tu sna tshogs 'god //
NK114(ye)001:11537: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i ye shes so so rang
NK114(ye)001:11538: gi rig pa chos kyi dbyings dang ro gcig pa
NK114(ye)001:11539: ni don dam bden pa'i ngo bo ste /
NK114(ye)001:11540: sgra gcan 'dzin gyis yum la bstod pa las /
NK114(ye)001:11541: smra bsam brjod med shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK114(ye)001:11542: ma skyes mi 'gag nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK114(ye)001:11543: so so rang rig ye shes spyod yul ba //
NK114(ye)001:11544: dus gsum rgyal ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK114(ye)001:11546: des na chos can dang chos nyid 'du 'bral med pas gnyis ka'ang rang bzhin med de /
NK114(ye)001:11548: bden pa gnyis char du yang rang bzhin med de'i phyir //
NK114(ye)001:11549: 'di dag rtag pa ma yin chad pa'ang min //
NK114(ye)001:11551: gnyis pa mtshan nyid la gnyis las /
NK114(ye)001:11552: kun rdzob bden pa'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK114(ye)001:11553: blo'i yul las ma 'das pa'i chos dpyad mi bzod pa sgrib pa'i rnam par skyes pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:11554: blo zhes pa ni sems sems byung la zer gyis /
NK114(ye)001:11555: so so rang rig pa'i ye shes la mi bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:11556: de ltar yang de nyid las /
NK114(ye)001:11557: gti mug rang bzhin sgrib phyir kun rdzob ste //
NK114(ye)001:11558: des gang bcos ma bden par snang de ni //
NK114(ye)001:11559: kun rdzob bden zhes thub pa des gsungs te //
NK114(ye)001:11560: bcos mar gyur pa'i dngos ni kun rdzob tu'o //
NK114(ye)001:11562: don dam bden pa'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK114(ye)001:11563: chos dang chos nyid dag mnyam spros pa las 'das
NK114(ye)001:11564: pa'i ngo bo blo dang mtshan mas dben pa ste
NK114(ye)001:11566: gzhan las shes min zhi ba dang //
NK114(ye)001:11567: spros pa rnams kyis ma spros pa //
NK114(ye)001:11568: rnam rtog med don tha dad med //
NK114(ye)001:11569: de ni de yi mtshan nyid do //
NK114(ye)001:11572: sgyu mar snang la rang bzhin med pas kun rdzob dang /
NK114(ye)001:11573: re zhig 'khrul ngor rang rang gi mtshan nyid mi
NK114(ye)001:11574: bslu bar snang bas bden pa zhes pa'i tha snyad
NK114(ye)001:11575: btags pa dang / yang gnyer bya'i don mchog gam dam pa yin pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11576: lam dang 'bras bu'i chos su mi bslu bas bden pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:11578: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ni rtogs par bya zhing bsgom par bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:11579: yongs su bsgom pa las ni bla na med pa'i chos thob par bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:11580: de'i phyir byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi don dam
NK114(ye)001:11581: pa ni shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'o
NK114(ye)001:11585: sgrub phyogs gnyis su nges pas phung po gsum pa khegs te /
NK114(ye)001:11586: spros pa las ma grol ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:11587: grol ba gnyis su nges pas bden pa gnyis su
NK114(ye)001:11588: rnam par bzhag pa ste de yang lam bsgrub pa'i
NK114(ye)001:11589: gnas skabs kyi snang cha kun rdzob pa thams cad
NK114(ye)001:11590: kyang mthar dbyings su dag dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:11591: yang rnam pa gcig tu na yul rnams snang tshul
NK114(ye)001:11592: dang gnas tshul gnyis su nges te blo la gnyis
NK114(ye)001:11593: su snang zhing btags pa thams cad kun rdzob dang
NK114(ye)001:11594: / blo las 'das pa'i ye shes kyis snang mi
NK114(ye)001:11595: snang gi tha snyad dang bral ba'i gnas tshul mthong
NK114(ye)001:11596: ba don dam pa yin la /
NK114(ye)001:11597: yul de yang yul can la ltos nas 'jog pa
NK114(ye)001:11598: na 'khrul pa dang ma 'khrul pa gnyis las mi
NK114(ye)001:11599: 'da' bas kyang gnyis su nges te /
NK114(ye)001:11601: dngos kun yang dag brdzun par mthong ba yis //
NK114(ye)001:11602: dngos rnyed ngo bo gnyis ni 'dzin par 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:11603: yang dag mthong yul gang de don dam ste //
NK114(ye)001:11604: mthong ba brdzun pa kun rdzob bden par gsungs //
NK114(ye)001:11606: des na chos thams cad gtan la dbab par byed
NK114(ye)001:11607: pa la shes bya bden pa gnyis po der 'du
NK114(ye)001:11608: bas de las gzhan phung po gsum pa zhig ma
NK114(ye)001:11610: de skad du yang yab sras mjal ba'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:11611: 'jig rten mkhyen pas gzhan las ma gsan par //
NK114(ye)001:11612: bden pa 'di gnyis nyid kyis ston par mdzad //
NK114(ye)001:11613: gang zhig kun rdzob bden dang don dam ste //
NK114(ye)001:11614: bden pa gsum pa gang yang ma ma chis so //
NK114(ye)001:11616: 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi la sogs pa bshad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11617: sngags su lhag pa'i kun rdzob dang /
NK114(ye)001:11619: dbyer med sogs bshad pa ni gnyis po 'di las gzhan min no //
NK114(ye)001:11620: lnga pa nges par byed pa'i tshad ma ni /
NK114(ye)001:11621: chos dbyings don dam pa'i bden pa ni spros pa las grol ba yin te /
NK114(ye)001:11622: dmigs bcas kyi blo'i spyod yul ma yin zhing rnam
NK114(ye)001:11623: par mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyis dmigs pa med
NK114(ye)001:11624: pa'i tshul gyis rtogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:11625: chos can kun rdzob pa rnams spros pa dang bcas par snang ba yin te /
NK114(ye)001:11626: dmigs bcas kyi blo'i spyod yul yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:11628: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin gcig du ma dang
NK114(ye)001:11629: bral bas rang gi ngo bo'i dbye ba med de
NK114(ye)001:11630: / dgongs pa nges par 'grel ba'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:11631: 'du byed khams dang don dam mtshan nyid ni //
NK114(ye)001:11632: gcig dang tha dad bral ba'i mtshan nyid de //
NK114(ye)001:11633: gcig dang tha dad nyid du gang rtog pa //
NK114(ye)001:11634: de dag tshul min lta la zhugs pa yin //
NK114(ye)001:11636: des na gnas tshul la gcig dang tha dad gang
NK114(ye)001:11637: du rtog kyang skyon bzhi bzhi dag gis gnod par
NK114(ye)001:11638: gsungs te / de la dang po ni dgongs pa nges 'grel las /
NK114(ye)001:11639: kun rdzob mngon sum tshad mas rtogs pa na /
NK114(ye)001:11640: de dang ldog pa tha dad med pas don dam
NK114(ye)001:11641: pa'i bden pa'ang rtogs pa'i phyir 'khor ba'i sems can
NK114(ye)001:11642: dang po nas mya ngan las 'das pa thob par
NK114(ye)001:11644: tha dad mi ldan pa'i don dam pa'i bden pa
NK114(ye)001:11645: dang ldog pa tha dad med pas kun rdzob gzugs
NK114(ye)001:11646: la sogs pa'ang tha dad kyis stong par 'gyur ba
NK114(ye)001:11647: dang 2 / gang dmigs pa'i yul du byas pas
NK114(ye)001:11648: nyon mongs pa 'phel bar 'gyur ba'i kun rdzob kyi
NK114(ye)001:11649: bden pa dang ldog pa tha dad pa med pas
NK114(ye)001:11650: don dam pa'i bden pa dmigs pa'i yul du byas
NK114(ye)001:11651: pa las nyon mongs pa rgyas par 'gyur ba dang
NK114(ye)001:11652: dang 2 / 3 / tshad mas gzod rtogs par
NK114(ye)001:11653: byar med pa'i kun rdzob kyi bden pa dang ldog
NK114(ye)001:11654: pa tha dad med pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:11655: don dam pa'i bden pa'ang da gzod gtan la dbab tu med par 'gyur ro4 //
NK114(ye)001:11657: gnyis pa yang de nyid las /
NK114(ye)001:11658: don dam pa'i bden pa mngon du rtogs na'ang kun
NK114(ye)001:11659: rdzob de bas logs su dmigs pa'i phyir mya ngan
NK114(ye)001:11660: las 'das pa mi thob par 'gyur ba dang 1
NK114(ye)001:11661: / kun rdzob dang dngos po tha dad pa'i don
NK114(ye)001:11662: dam pa'i bden pa de kun rdzob kyi bden pa'i
NK114(ye)001:11663: chos nyid ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK114(ye)001:11664: bum pa snam bu'i chos nyid ma yin pa 2bzhin no //
NK114(ye)001:11665: bden pa gnyis dngos po tha dad pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:11666: kun rdzob kyi bdag rab tu ma grub pa tsam
NK114(ye)001:11667: don dam pa'i bden pa ma yin par 'gyur te
NK114(ye)001:11668: / bum pa rab tu ma grub pa tsam snam bu ma yin pa 3 bzhin no //
NK114(ye)001:11669: don dam pa'i bden pa mngon sum du rtogs pas mya ngan las 'das pa thob pa'i dus na'ang /
NK114(ye)001:11670: kun rdzob de bas logs su dmigs pas kun nas
NK114(ye)001:11671: nyon mongs par 'gyur bas skyes bu gcig gi rgyud
NK114(ye)001:11672: la kun nas nyon mongs dang rnam byang dus gcig
NK114(ye)001:11675: 'o na bden pa gnyis su ji ltar dbye zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:11676: gshis la ma grub bzhin 'jig rten pa'i blo ngor
NK114(ye)001:11677: ltos te brda shes pa'i yan lag tu sgro 'dogs
NK114(ye)001:11678: pa'i tshul gyis gsungs pa yin te /
NK114(ye)001:11680: yi ge med pa'i chos rnams las /
NK114(ye)001:11681: nyan pa gang dang ston pa gang //
NK114(ye)001:11682: 'gyur ba med la sgro btags nas //
NK114(ye)001:11683: nyan cing ston par byed pa'ang yin //
NK114(ye)001:11684: zhes pa ltar bden pa gnyis su spyir dbye na
NK114(ye)001:11685: skye 'gag kun byang dgag sgrub sogs mtshan nya da
NK114(ye)001:11686: mi 'dra ba du ma blo la snang zhing tha
NK114(ye)001:11687: snyad pa'i blo ngo der gnod pa med pa'i cha
NK114(ye)001:11688: ji snyed pa ni kun rdzob kyi bden pa yin
NK114(ye)001:11689: la / kun rdzob de nyid kyi rang bzhin snang
NK114(ye)001:11690: mi snang skye mi skye bdag yod med la sogs
NK114(ye)001:11691: pa'i spros pa'i d+r+wa ba ma lus pas dben pa
NK114(ye)001:11692: la don dam pa zhes btags kyi spros bral zhes
NK114(ye)001:11693: pa'i chos shig gud na med de /
NK114(ye)001:11695: ji ltar snang ba 'di kho na //
NK114(ye)001:11696: kun rdzob gzhan ni cig shos yin //
NK114(ye)001:11698: bye brag tu bden pa gnyis po rang rang gi
NK114(ye)001:11699: nang gses kyis dbye na de lta bu'i blo snang
NK114(ye)001:11700: gi chos kun rdzob pa de la'ang 'khrul ma 'khrul
NK114(ye)001:11701: gnyis las / byis pa rnams kyi 'khrul ngor snang
NK114(ye)001:11702: ba de la tha snyad 'jig rten pas bden rdzun
NK114(ye)001:11703: gnyis su byed pa ltar snang lugs rnam pa gnyis
NK114(ye)001:11704: gnyis las / su phye ste / dus de'i 'khrul shes kyi ngo bo me chu sogs dang /
NK114(ye)001:11705: zla gcig la sogs par snang ba ni snang ba
NK114(ye)001:11706: ji snyed pa de snyed kyi rang rang gis mes
NK114(ye)001:11707: btso bsregs dang chus brlan sdud dang /
NK114(ye)001:11708: zla bas mun pa sel ba la sogs pa snang
NK114(ye)001:11709: tshod de nyid dang mthun par don byed pa rnams
NK114(ye)001:11710: rang rang gi shes pa dang bcas pas bsdus pa
NK114(ye)001:11711: la yang dag pa'i kun rdzob nyid du bshad de
NK114(ye)001:11713: rgyu las skyes pa btags pas dben pa nyid kyi phyir de skad ces brjod do //
NK114(ye)001:11714: yang 'khrul ngor snang na'ang smig rgyu la chur dang /
NK114(ye)001:11715: thag khra la sbrul du dang /
NK114(ye)001:11716: zla ba la gnyis su snang ba lta bus ni brlan pa'i bya ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:11718: mun pa sel ba'i don mi byed pa la sogs
NK114(ye)001:11719: pa de dag gi shes pa dang bcas pa la
NK114(ye)001:11720: ni log pa'i kun rdzob ces bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:11721: mthun par mi snang zhing tha snyad tsam du'ang rgyu
NK114(ye)001:11722: las ma skyes pa'i med snang yin pa'i phyir te
NK114(ye)001:11723: / de yang 'khrul rkyen 'dzom pas snang ba yin
NK114(ye)001:11724: pa'i phyir rgyu med min kyang sa myug bzhin du
NK114(ye)001:11725: rang skyed byed kyi rgyu bem po'i chos su grub
NK114(ye)001:11726: pa tha snyad du'ang med pa'i phyir de skad ces
NK114(ye)001:11727: / bya'o // de'ang dbu ma rang rgyud pa'i lugs
NK114(ye)001:11728: la ni de gnyis ka'ang don dam dpyod byed kyi
NK114(ye)001:11730: bag chags 'khrul pa las skyes par mnyam /
NK114(ye)001:11731: dbang po so so snang bar mnyam pas mtshungs shing bden par ma grub na'ang /
NK114(ye)001:11732: tha snyad tsam du rang gi mtshan nyid kyi grub
NK114(ye)001:11733: ma grub yod pas yang log gi kun rdzob gnyis
NK114(ye)001:11734: su grags so // de ltar yang bden gnyis las /
NK114(ye)001:11735: snang du 'dra yang don byed dag /
NK114(ye)001:11736: nus pa'i phyir dang mi nus phyir //
NK114(ye)001:11737: yang dag yang dag ma yin pa'i //
NK114(ye)001:11738: kun rdzob kyi ni dbye ba byas //
NK114(ye)001:11740: thal 'gyur bas ni mtshan nyid kyis grub pa dang
NK114(ye)001:11741: bden par grub pa don gcig pas tha snyad du'ang
NK114(ye)001:11742: ma grub par 'dra yang 'jig rten pas de gnyis
NK114(ye)001:11743: bden rdzun du byed pa dang bstun nas phye ba
NK114(ye)001:11746: skyon ldan dbang can rnams kyi shes pa ni //
NK114(ye)001:11747: dbang po legs gyur shes ltos log par 'dod //
NK114(ye)001:11748: gnod pa med pa'i dbang po drug rnams kyis //
NK114(ye)001:11749: bzung ba gang zhig 'jig rten gyis rtogs te //
NK114(ye)001:11750: 'jig rten nyid las bden yin lhag ma ni //
NK114(ye)001:11751: 'jig rten nyid las log par rnam par bzhag /
NK114(ye)001:11752: ces tshig rkang snga ma gnyis shes pa'i dbang du byas nas dang /
NK114(ye)001:11753: phyi ma bzhi yul gyi dbang du byas nas gsungs so //
NK114(ye)001:11754: yang rnam pa gcig tu na snga ma gnyis char bden zhen dang /
NK114(ye)001:11755: bcas pa'i sems rtog dang snang ba yin pas log pa'i kun rdzob dang /
NK114(ye)001:11756: 'phags pa'i ye shes thob nas bden zhen med pa'i
NK114(ye)001:11757: 'char sgo dang snang ba thams cad ni yang dag
NK114(ye)001:11758: pa'i kun rdzoob yin te ma 'khrul pa'i blo snang
NK114(ye)001:11759: yin pa'i phyir / de ltar yang bsod nams thams cad bsdus pa'i ting nge 'dzin las /
NK114(ye)001:11760: byang chub sems dpa' gang spyad pa thams cad la spyod la /
NK114(ye)001:11761: spyod pa thams cad kyis kyang mi gos pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11762: sems can thams cad yongs su smin par bya ba'i
NK114(ye)001:11763: phyir spyod pa thams cad kyang 'grub par snang ba'i
NK114(ye)001:11764: byang chub sems dpa' de ni byang chub sems dpa'i
NK114(ye)001:11765: spyad pa spyod pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:11767: khye'u bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin gyi mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:11768: thams cad shes kyang rnam shes yod min zhing //
NK114(ye)001:11769: thams cad bsgom yang rnam bsgom yod min la //
NK114(ye)001:11770: thams cad rtogs kyang rtogs pa yod min zhing //
NK114(ye)001:11771: thams cad brjod kyang gang la'ang mi gnas la //
NK114(ye)001:11772: zab chos chos kyi 'du shes yod min zhing //
NK114(ye)001:11773: sems can 'gro la yang sems can 'du shes med //
NK114(ye)001:11774: zhi dben zhi ba'i 'du shes yod min zhing //
NK114(ye)001:11775: byang chub rtogs kyang byang chub 'du shes med //
NK114(ye)001:11777: de lta bu'i ma 'khrul ba'i kun rdzob de la'ang gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:11778: 'bras bu thob byed kyi lam la ma 'khrul ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:11780: dang po ni 'phags pa slob pa'i rgyud kyi rnam
NK114(ye)001:11781: pa dang bcas pa'i ting nge 'dzin thams cad dang
NK114(ye)001:11782: / rjes thob snang ba dang bcas pa'i skabs kyi tshogs bsags pa'i sgo thams cad do //
NK114(ye)001:11783: phyi ma ni sangs rgyas kyi gzugs sku ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang bcas pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:11784: 'o na sngar 'jug pa'i phung don ltar 'khrul ma
NK114(ye)001:11785: 'khrul gyi yul can gnyis kyi yul du nges pas
NK114(ye)001:11786: bden pa gnyis kyi grangs nges bshad pa dang 'gal
NK114(ye)001:11787: te ma 'khrul pa'i kun rdzob yod pa'i phyir zhe
NK114(ye)001:11788: na / sngar ni 'phags pa slob pa rnams kyi
NK114(ye)001:11789: rjes thob kyi snang ba gnyis snang dang bcas pas
NK114(ye)001:11790: gshis don la sgrib pa'i cha yod pas 'khrul pa'i
NK114(ye)001:11792: 'dir ni 'gyur zhing gong du bgrod pas mi rtag
NK114(ye)001:11793: kyang gshis kyi sar bsgrod pas dang bden zhen med
NK114(ye)001:11794: pas ma 'khrul ba zhes brjod cing /
NK114(ye)001:11795: sangs rgyas kyi sa'i sku dang ye shes sogs ni snang ba'i cha tsam gyis brjod par zad kyi /
NK114(ye)001:11796: kun rdzob mtshan nyid pa ni ma yin te /
NK114(ye)001:11797: don dam nyag gcig gi dgongs pa mthar phyin pa'i gnas skabs yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:11801: sngags kyi skabs su lhag pa'i kun rdzob la sogs
NK114(ye)001:11802: pa'i tha snyad tsam ni gdags su mi rung ba
NK114(ye)001:11803: ma yin pas de skad ces bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:11804: don dam pa'i bden pa ni gshis kyi bzhugs tshul
NK114(ye)001:11805: lam gnas tshul yin pas ngo bo la dbyer med
NK114(ye)001:11806: kyang brdar btags nas dbye na /
NK114(ye)001:11807: blos dpyad de skye ba la sogs pa bkag nas
NK114(ye)001:11808: skye med dang spros bral sogs su bsgoms kyang rnam
NK114(ye)001:11809: shes kyi spyod yul las ma 'das pas ngo bo
NK114(ye)001:11810: kun rdzob kyis bsdus kyang don dam pa rtogs byed
NK114(ye)001:11811: kyi thabs dngos yin pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11812: de dang rjes su mthun pa'i phyir rnam grangs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:11813: don dam mam mthun pa'i don dam zhes bya ste
NK114(ye)001:11815: skye la sogs pa ma grub phyir //
NK114(ye)001:11816: skye ba med la sogs mi 'grub //
NK114(ye)001:11818: skye la sogs pa bkag pa yang //
NK114(ye)001:11819: yang dag pa dang mthun nyid bzhed //
NK114(ye)001:11820: skye med spros kun zhi ba la //
NK114(ye)001:11821: don dam zhes pa'i brdar mdzad do //
NK114(ye)001:11823: des na rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don dam ni
NK114(ye)001:11824: skye ba dang skye med la sogs pa'i spros pa
NK114(ye)001:11825: thams cad dbyings su zhi nas gshis thog tu phyin
NK114(ye)001:11826: pa ste sa thob 'phags pa'i mnyam bzhag dang /
NK114(ye)001:11827: sangs rgyas kyi sa'i shes dang shes bya ro gcig tu gyur pa'i ye shes te /
NK114(ye)001:11828: de'i ngo bo ni 'khor ba dang ni mya ngan
NK114(ye)001:11829: las 'das pa'i chos thams cad gzod ma nas ngo
NK114(ye)001:11830: bo nyid med pas gnyis su med cing gdod nas
NK114(ye)001:11831: spros pa thams cad dang bral bas snyam byed kyi
NK114(ye)001:11833: sgra tshig gis brjod pa las 'das pas na rtogs pa'i blo yis don dam pa yin pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11834: ma rtogs pa'i blo yis ma yin par ma bzhag
NK114(ye)001:11835: ste rtogs kyang rung ma rtogs kyang rung chos rnams
NK114(ye)001:11836: kyi chos nyid ni rang bzhin gyis de ltar gnas
NK114(ye)001:11838: de ltar yang ma pham mgon pos /
NK114(ye)001:11839: ji ltar sngar bzhin phyis de bzhin //
NK114(ye)001:11840: 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid do //
NK114(ye)001:11843: thams cad dngos po med cing yi ge med //
NK114(ye)001:11844: stong pa zhi ba bzod nas dri ma med //
NK114(ye)001:11845: de ltar chos rnams gang gis shes pa ni //
NK114(ye)001:11846: gzhon nu de ni sangs rgyas zhes kyang brjod //
NK114(ye)001:11848: de ltar bden pa gnyis su dbye ba'ang gdul bya 'dul ba'i thabs la mkhas pas gsungs kyi /
NK114(ye)001:11849: dngos po'i cha nas ma he'i rwa ltar tha dad pa med pa'i tshul ni 'di ltar /
NK114(ye)001:11850: bden pa gnyis po ye nas ro gcig tu 'dres
NK114(ye)001:11851: shing dbyer med pa'i snang stong zung 'jug ni dper
NK114(ye)001:11852: na / rdzing bu dwangs par zhugs pa ste shar
NK114(ye)001:11853: ba'i zla ba'i skye mched dam gzugs brnyan la mtshon
NK114(ye)001:11854: na gzugs snang ba'i cha dang /
NK114(ye)001:11855: zla bar bden pa med pa'i cha dang gnyis su
NK114(ye)001:11856: phye ru yod kyang de gnyis rdzing bu'i chu der
NK114(ye)001:11857: med par ngo bo gcig pa bzhin du /
NK114(ye)001:11858: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i chos 'di dag gtan
NK114(ye)001:11859: med ri rwa lta bu ma yin par snang tsam
NK114(ye)001:11860: pa ba'i cha nas kun rdzob kyi bdena pa dang
NK114(ye)001:11861: / snang dus nyid nas rang bzhin gang yang ma
NK114(ye)001:11862: grub pa'i cha nas don dam pa'i bden pa'o zhes
NK114(ye)001:11863: gnyis su phye yang gnyis ka rang bzhin med par
NK114(ye)001:11866: bden pa gnyis su'ang rang bzhin med de'i phyir //
NK114(ye)001:11867: de dag rtags pa ma yin chad ma yin //
NK114(ye)001:11869: de ltar bden pa gnyis po'i ngo bo dang mtshan
NK114(ye)001:11870: nyid sogs so sor shes par byas nas mthar dbyer
NK114(ye)001:11871: med du bsgrub pa de yang snang stong ngam yod
NK114(ye)001:11872: med gnyis zung du sbyor ba lta bu ma yin
NK114(ye)001:11873: par rang bzhin ngang gis dbyer med cing tshur rol
NK114(ye)001:11874: rtog pa'i blo'i yul las 'das pa'i gnas lugs zab
NK114(ye)001:11875: mo'i don la som nyi spang bar bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:11877: kun rdzob dang ni don dam dag /
NK114(ye)001:11878: so so'i char ni shes gyur te //
NK114(ye)001:11879: gang du yang dag 'dres gyur pa //
NK114(ye)001:11880: zung du 'jug par de bshad do //
NK114(ye)001:11882: bden gnyis dbyer med la tha snyad du dbye ba
NK114(ye)001:11883: byed pa'i tshul 'di la kun mkhyen chen pos sems
NK114(ye)001:11884: nyid ngal gso'i 'grel pa sogs su rang bzhin gcig
NK114(ye)001:11885: la ldog pa tha dad pa yin te /
NK114(ye)001:11887: kun rdzob stong pa nyid du bshad //
NK114(ye)001:11888: stong nyid kho na kun rdzob ste //
NK114(ye)001:11889: byas pa dang ni mi rtag bzhin //
NK114(ye)001:11890: med na mi 'byung nges phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:11891: zhes pa la sogs pa'i khungs drangs nas /
NK114(ye)001:11892: gcig pa bkag pa tsam gyi tha dad ma yin te /
NK114(ye)001:11893: rang bzhin so so ba med phyir dang /
NK114(ye)001:11894: gzhi gcig la dbye dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:11896: kho bo'i bla ma bka' drin can gyis sher phyin spyi don du ni /
NK114(ye)001:11897: gcig pa bkag pa'i tha dad tsam du 'dod de dngos po dang dngos med bzhin no //
NK114(ye)001:11899: ngo bo gcig la ldog pa tha dad pa'o zhes zer ba yang mi 'thad cing /
NK114(ye)001:11900: sems 'grel gyi lung de yang de'i khungs ma yin te /
NK114(ye)001:11901: des bden pa gcig med par cig shos med pa'i dper /
NK114(ye)001:11902: byas mi rtag blang bas 'di yang de nyid dang
NK114(ye)001:11903: gzhan du med pa'i rigs pa'o zhes gsungs pa ni
NK114(ye)001:11904: re zhig rang rgyud pa'i gzhung dang bstun par snang
NK114(ye)001:11905: yang / de dag gi dgongs pa la brtags na gnad gcig par sems te /
NK114(ye)001:11906: snga mas ni chos rnams kyi gnas tshul gzhi lam
NK114(ye)001:11907: 'bras bu'i bar thams cad snang stong zung 'jug gi
NK114(ye)001:11908: ngo bor tshul gcig pa la dgongs la /
NK114(ye)001:11910: gti mug rang bzhin sgrib phyir zhes pa la sogs pa'i dgongs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11911: yid bzhin rin po che'i mdzod du nges pa don
NK114(ye)001:11912: gyi bden pa dbyer med chen po la dkri ba'i
NK114(ye)001:11913: thabs su brdar btags pa'i bden gnyis 'khor ba'i chos
NK114(ye)001:11915: myang 'das kyi chos rnams don dam par byas te
NK114(ye)001:11916: de gnyis dbyer med du bshad kyang don la dbyer
NK114(ye)001:11917: med rgyu'i 'khor ba'i chos rnams gtan nas med par
NK114(ye)001:11918: gsungs pa bzhin / snang tshul 'khor ba'i chos tsam
NK114(ye)001:11919: la kun rdzob tu dgongs pa yin mam snyam du
NK114(ye)001:11920: gsungs pa bzhin / bsam mo // 'on kyang zab
NK114(ye)001:11921: mo'i gnas 'di lta bu ni ji bzhin rtogs pa
NK114(ye)001:11922: gsungs pa bzhin / bsam mo // lta ci /
NK114(ye)001:11923: phyogs tsam yang gting dpogs par shin tu dka' bas
NK114(ye)001:11924: blo gsal gsar bu pa rnams la dpyad gzhi tsam
NK114(ye)001:11925: du bris pa yin pas phyogs gcig pa'i shes rab
NK114(ye)001:11926: kyis mdo sngags la sogs pa'i gzhung lugs kyi bshad
NK114(ye)001:11927: tshul mi 'dra ba rnams 'gal 'du can du mi
NK114(ye)001:11928: lta bar thams cad dgongs mthun du bzung nas nyams
NK114(ye)001:11929: len gyi gnad 'gag gcig la blo rtse gtad pher
NK114(ye)001:11930: ba zhig byung na thos bsam byas pa don dang
NK114(ye)001:11931: ldan pa yin pas zhib tu dpyad par mdzod cig
NK114(ye)001:11932: gsungs pa bzhin / bsam mo // lta ci /
NK114(ye)001:11933: / bden gnyis dbyer med rtog yul las 'das pa
NK114(ye)001:11934: de lta na'ang re zhig mos spyod pa'i lam la
NK114(ye)001:11939: reg bya ste 'dod pa'i yul lnga po sgo lnga'i
NK114(ye)001:11940: shes pa'i ngo la tshon ris kyi kha dog ma
NK114(ye)001:11941: 'dresa pa lta bus so sor snang ba na /
NK114(ye)001:11942: gzugs la sogs pa'i yul lnga po snang tsam pa des mi 'ching mod /
NK114(ye)001:11943: de dag la gzung 'dzin du skyes nas 'dod pa'i
NK114(ye)001:11944: longs spyod du nye bar len pa'i cha bzung ba
NK114(ye)001:11945: ni / de dang de la 'di ni gzugs so
NK114(ye)001:11946: zhes pa la sogs pa'i der 'dzin gyi sgo nas
NK114(ye)001:11947: mi 'dod pa la dgag pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11948: 'dod pa la bsgrub pa'i blo sems dang rtog pa
NK114(ye)001:11949: sems byung gi 'khrul snang bar ma chad pa la
NK114(ye)001:11951: de dag gzhig pa'i phyir snang ba de thams cad
NK114(ye)001:11952: rang bzhin ma grub cing spros pa'i mtha' brgyad dang
NK114(ye)001:11953: bral ba'i tshul sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad nyid du brtag
NK114(ye)001:11954: par bya ste / skye ba med pa rmi lam lta bu /
NK114(ye)001:11955: 'gag pa med pa sgyu ma lta bu /
NK114(ye)001:11956: rtag pa med pa smig rgyu lta bu /
NK114(ye)001:11957: chad pa med pa chu zla lta bu /
NK114(ye)001:11958: 'ong ba med pa mig yor lta bu /
NK114(ye)001:11959: 'gro ba med pa brag cha lta bu /
NK114(ye)001:11960: tha dad pa ma yin pa dri za'i grong khyer lta bu /
NK114(ye)001:11961: don gcig ma yin pa sprul pa lta bu'o snyam
NK114(ye)001:11962: du yang yang bsam zhing dpyad nas snang stong dbyer
NK114(ye)001:11963: med kyi don la nges shes bskyed de /
NK114(ye)001:11964: de nas de'i don la rtse gcig tu mnyam par 'jog par bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:11965: de ltar goms shing rtogs pa rnams ni srid pa'i
NK114(ye)001:11966: grong khyer nas thar ba'i lam sna zin pa zhes
NK114(ye)001:11968: 'on kyang de tsam gyis chog shes par mi byed de /
NK114(ye)001:11969: nyan thos lta bu rang don nyi tshe ba tsam
NK114(ye)001:11970: zhig bsgrub pa ma yin par byang chub sems dpa'
NK114(ye)001:11971: rang gzhan gyi don rgya chen po bsgrub dgos pas
NK114(ye)001:11972: byang chub sems kyis zin pa'i sgo nas sbyin sogs
NK114(ye)001:11973: bsod nams kyi tshogs la'ang che thang du 'bad par
NK114(ye)001:11974: byed cing der ma zad bden pa gnyis su dbye
NK114(ye)001:11975: ba dang / dbyer med du bsgrub pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:11976: mtha' brgyad sgyu ma'i dpe yis rang bzhin med par
NK114(ye)001:11977: shes shing bsgom pa de yang mthar thug pa'am chos
NK114(ye)001:11978: rnams kyi gnas lugs ma yin te /
NK114(ye)001:11979: ci'i phyir zhe na blo yisa 'di lta bu'o zhes
NK114(ye)001:11980: rnam par dpyad bzod pa ste yul du byar rung
NK114(ye)001:11981: ba zhig yod na de ni don dam pa ma
NK114(ye)001:11982: yin te / don dam pa ni rnam par mi
NK114(ye)001:11983: rtog pa'i ye shes kyis yul dang yul can gnyis
