NK114(ye)001:11984: su med pa'i tshul gyis rtogs par bya ba yin
NK114(ye)001:11985: yin te / la / yul dang yul can du
NK114(ye)001:11986: skye ba'i blo thams cad ni gnyis med kyi don
NK114(ye)001:11987: la sgrib pa'i kun rdzob yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK114(ye)001:11988: gzhan yang blo'i yul du byas pa'i rnam pa rnams yang na ni gcig gi ngo bor rtog la /
NK114(ye)001:11989: yang na ni du ma'i ngo bor rtog pa las
NK114(ye)001:11990: ma 'das pas gcig du ma dang bral ba'o snyam
NK114(ye)001:11991: du bsam na yang gcig du ma dang bral rgyu'i
NK114(ye)001:11992: chos shig gi rnam par 'char ba las 'os med
NK114(ye)001:11993: pas / gcig dang du ma dang yod med la
NK114(ye)001:11994: sogs pa'i spros pa dang rnam par 'gal ba'i spros
NK114(ye)001:11995: pas / bral dang / chos nyid dang /
NK114(ye)001:11996: ye shes la sogs pa'i mtshan nyid rnams ni blo
NK114(ye)001:11997: yi yul na nam du yang gnas ma myong ste
NK114(ye)001:11998: / rnam par mi rtog par 'jug pa'i gzungs las /
NK114(ye)001:11999: dam chos 'di la rgyal ba'i sras //
NK114(ye)001:12000: rnam par mi rtog bsam gyur na //
NK114(ye)001:12001: rnam rtog bgrod dka' rnams 'das te //
NK114(ye)001:12002: rim gyis mi rtog thob par 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:12005: don dam blo yi spyod yul min //
NK114(ye)001:12007: bdun pa bden gnyis gtan la dbab pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:12008: tha snyad pa'i bden pa la brten nas don dam pa'i bden pa gtan la dbab ste /
NK114(ye)001:12009: de kho na nyid la sgrib pa'i gti mug 'khrul pa'i cha thams cad bsal ba'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:12010: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba tsam du bsod nams
NK114(ye)001:12011: kyi tshogs bsags pa mi 'dor yang 'khor gsum du
NK114(ye)001:12012: zhen pa'i yul rang bzhin med pa'i chos nyid kyi
NK114(ye)001:12013: don shes pa'i shes rab kyis zin pas tshogs gnyis
NK114(ye)001:12014: zung 'jug tu song nas yang dag pa'i gnas lugs
NK114(ye)001:12015: ji lta ba bzhin mngon du 'gyur zhing mthar phyin
NK114(ye)001:12016: par byed pa'i dgos pa yod de /
NK114(ye)001:12018: tha snyad bden pa thabs su gyur pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:12019: don dam bden pa thabs byung gyur pa ste //
NK114(ye)001:12020: de gnyis rnam dbye gang gis mi shes pa //
NK114(ye)001:12021: de ni rnam rtog log pas lam ngan zhugs //
NK114(ye)001:12024: bden gnyis rnam dbye shes pa dag /
NK114(ye)001:12025: thub pa'i bka' la mi rmongs te //
NK114(ye)001:12026: de dag ma lus tshogs bsags nas //
NK114(ye)001:12030: yang dag kun rdzob rnams kyi skas //
NK114(ye)001:12031: med par don dam khang chen gyi //
NK114(ye)001:12032: steng du 'dzegs par bya ba ni //
NK114(ye)001:12033: mkhas la rung ba ma yin no //
NK114(ye)001:12035: gnyis pa grub matha'i 'dod gzhung bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:12039: spyir bden gnyis kyi rang bzhin de ltar yin pa la /
NK114(ye)001:12040: re zhig grub pa'i mtha' smra ba po so so
NK114(ye)001:12041: yis rgyal ba'i bka'i dgongs pa len tshul tha dad
NK114(ye)001:12042: pa'i dbang gis rang rang gis gzhi lam 'bras bu'i
NK114(ye)001:12043: don rnam par bzhag pa'i tshul ni 'di ltar yin
NK114(ye)001:12044: te zhes pa'o // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK114(ye)001:12048: dbu ma pa rnams bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:12049: dang po bye brag smra ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:12050: bden par zhen pas phyi don 'dod cing rang rig
NK114(ye)001:12051: tha snyad du'ang khas mi len pa'i theg dman gyi
NK114(ye)001:12052: grub mtha' smra ba'i gang zag de ni bye brag
NK114(ye)001:12054: de la gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las /
NK114(ye)001:12055: gzhi'i chos bden pa gnyis su gtan la dbab tshul ni /
NK114(ye)001:12056: 'dus byas kyi chos rnams phung po lnga dang /
NK114(ye)001:12058: bem po gnyis su bsdus te /
NK114(ye)001:12059: tshogs drug gi shes pa'i rgyun chu bo'i rgyun 'bab
NK114(ye)001:12060: pa bzhin skad cig snga phyi bar ma chad par
NK114(ye)001:12061: 'byung ba 'di la byis pa rnams kyis ji ltar
NK114(ye)001:12062: bzung ba lta mi bden te /
NK114(ye)001:12063: dpyad na dus gsum gyi shes pa du mar 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:12064: bas dge ba'am mi dge ba'i rtog pa 'di lta
NK114(ye)001:12065: bu'o snyam pa'i rang 'dzin gyi blo 'dor du rung
NK114(ye)001:12066: bas kun rdzob tsam du yod pa yin la /
NK114(ye)001:12067: don dam par shes pa'i rang bzhin ci yang ma
NK114(ye)001:12068: grub na rags pa'i rgyun kun rdzob pa de snang
NK114(ye)001:12069: du'ang mi rung bas blo yis ji ltar dpyad kyang
NK114(ye)001:12070: dus gsum du bgo ru med pa'i shes pa dus
NK114(ye)001:12071: kyi cha med pa rang 'dzin gyi blo 'dor mi
NK114(ye)001:12072: rung ba zhig rgyun rtsom pa'i gzhir yod pa dang
NK114(ye)001:12073: / bem po'i dngos po rags par snang ba bum
NK114(ye)001:12074: pa la sogs pa'ang rdul phran dang cha shas du
NK114(ye)001:12075: ma bsags pa'i rang bzhin la byis pa phal pa
NK114(ye)001:12076: rnams kyis bum pa'o zhes dngos po gcig tu bzung
NK114(ye)001:12077: ba ltar mi bden te gnyen pos bcom zhing gzhig
NK114(ye)001:12078: par byas na bum 'dzin de ldog par 'gyur la
NK114(ye)001:12079: / / de bzhin du gzhig pas da dung cha
NK114(ye)001:12080: shas su phye ru yod pa de srid du rang
NK114(ye)001:12081: 'dzin gyi blo 'dor rung bas kun rdzob tsam yin
NK114(ye)001:12082: / / la / 'on kyang ci yang ma grub
NK114(ye)001:12083: pa zhig yin na rags snang 'di yang yod mi
NK114(ye)001:12084: rung bas de dag rtsom pa'i gzhi don dam par
NK114(ye)001:12085: ni gnyen po tho ba la sogs pas bcom zhing
NK114(ye)001:12086: gzhig par byas kyang cha shas phye ru med pa
NK114(ye)001:12087: yi rdul phran phyogs kyi cha med zhig yod do
NK114(ye)001:12088: zhes 'dod pa ni nyan thos sde pa bye brag
NK114(ye)001:12091: gang la bcom dang blo yis gzhan //
NK114(ye)001:12092: bsal na de blo mi 'jug pa //
NK114(ye)001:12093: bum chu bzhin du kun rdzob tu //
NK114(ye)001:12094: yod de don dam yod gzhan no //
NK114(ye)001:12096: de yang 'dus ma byas kyi chos rnams kyang don dam du bsdu la /
NK114(ye)001:12097: kun rdzob bden pa dang btags yod don gcig cing /
NK114(ye)001:12098: don dam bden pa dang rdzas yod don gcig par 'dod do //
NK114(ye)001:12099: spyir grub pa'i mtha' 'dis ni phyi rol pa rnams
NK114(ye)001:12100: 'dod pa'i gang zag gi bdag legs par bkag ste
NK114(ye)001:12101: / de'i steng du cha med gnyis la bdag tu
NK114(ye)001:12102: gdags pa'i gzhi med pa la gang zag gi bdag
NK114(ye)001:12103: ril po bden grub tu 'dzin pa'i blo lhan skyes
NK114(ye)001:12104: kyang log shes yin par shes nas bdag med du
NK114(ye)001:12105: / khas blangs shing / de'i lta ba go ba
NK114(ye)001:12106: las mdo sde pa'i lta ba legs par go ba'i
NK114(ye)001:12108: gzhan du nam mkha' rtag dngos gnyis ka yin pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:12110: mtshungs pa lnga ldan gyi rgyu 'bras sogs rdzas grub tu khas len zhing /
NK114(ye)001:12111: dus gsum yang rdzas grub dang dngos por 'dod pas
NK114(ye)001:12112: nam yang med par mi 'gyur ba sogs shin tu
NK114(ye)001:12114: kha che bye brag tu smra ba rnams la mdo
NK114(ye)001:12115: sde ba dang mthun par las 'bras kyi 'brel ba'i
NK114(ye)001:12116: rten du las kyi rgyun khas len pa'i khyad par
NK114(ye)001:12117: yod do // gnyis pa lam gyi rnam bzhag ni
NK114(ye)001:12118: bden bzhi'i rnam pa mi rtag sogs bcu drug po
NK114(ye)001:12119: la dmigs nas bsgoms pa'i tshul la lam lnga'i rnam
NK114(ye)001:12120: bzhag tsam byed kyang sa bcu la sogs pa'i rnam
NK114(ye)001:12122: lam de dag gi spang bya nyon mongs can dang /
NK114(ye)001:12123: de las ldog pa'i mi shes pa gnyis las snga
NK114(ye)001:12124: ma spangs pa las dman pa'i dgra bcom pa'i go
NK114(ye)001:12125: 'phang dang / phyi ma spangs pa las sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob par 'dod cing /
NK114(ye)001:12126: bcu drug pa lam rjes shes bsgom lam dang /
NK114(ye)001:12127: mthong lam skad cig bco lnga po dag kyang rim can du skye bar 'dod pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:12128: gsum pa 'bras bu'i rnam bzhag ni /
NK114(ye)001:12129: bshad ma thag pa'i dman pa'i dgra bcom la'ang nyams pa'i chos can sogs 'dod cing /
NK114(ye)001:12130: bskal pa grangs med gsum gyi tshogs mi rtag pa sogs bcu drug gi lam dang /
NK114(ye)001:12131: 'brel bar nyams su blangs pas mi shes pa gnyis ka spangs te sangs rgyas thob par 'dod la /
NK114(ye)001:12132: de'ang bdag cag gi ston pa la mtshon na /
NK114(ye)001:12133: dang po thugs bskyed pa nas bzung srod la bdud
NK114(ye)001:12134: btul ba'i bar thar pa cha mthun tsam la gnas
NK114(ye)001:12135: pa'i so so skye bo dang /
NK114(ye)001:12136: gang gi mtshan thog gcig po de nyid la sbyor lam gyi gnas skabs drod la sogs pa bzhi /
NK114(ye)001:12137: mthong lam gyi gnas skabs skad cig bco lnga rnams
NK114(ye)001:12138: stan thog de nyid du rdzogs par mdzad nas tho
NK114(ye)001:12139: rangs bsgom lam rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin
NK114(ye)001:12140: gyis nyon mongs pa can ma yin pa'i mi shes
NK114(ye)001:12141: pa drungs nas phyung ste sangs rgyas pa 'dod do
NK114(ye)001:12142: // de ltar sangs rgyas pa de yang thugs rgyud
NK114(ye)001:12143: kyi zad pa dang mi skye ba shes pa'i ye
NK114(ye)001:12145: phyi'i gzugs phung de nyid ni sdug bsngal bden pa
NK114(ye)001:12146: yin pas sangs rgyas su mi 'dod de lhas sbyin
NK114(ye)001:12147: gyis sgyogs 'phangs pa'i tshe zhabs bsnad pa sogs tshul
NK114(ye)001:12148: bstan ma yin par bzung nas drang don thad drang
NK114(ye)001:12149: du khas len / 'on kyang thugs rgyud la dpags
NK114(ye)001:12150: nas sangs rgyas phyin chad kyi mdzad pa rnams sangs
NK114(ye)001:12152: sku lus la dpags nas lhag bcas kyi dgra bcom pa zhes 'dod cing /
NK114(ye)001:12153: mya ngan las 'das nas lhag med kyi dbyings su
NK114(ye)001:12154: zhugs pa yin pas bem rig gi 'jug pa rgyun
NK114(ye)001:12155: chad par 'dod pas zhing khams gzhan du gzugs sku'i
NK114(ye)001:12157: longs spyod rdzogs sku la sogs pa'i rnam bzhag kyang mi 'dod la /
NK114(ye)001:12158: lhag bcas lhag med gnyis las logs su gyur pa'i
NK114(ye)001:12159: mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'ang khas mi
NK114(ye)001:12160: len zhing / de bzhin du skyes bu zung bzhi
NK114(ye)001:12161: dang gang zag ya brgyad kyi rnam bzhag tsam 'dod
NK114(ye)001:12162: len zhing / kyang / de dag gang zag yin pas dge 'dun dkon mchog tu mi 'dod la /
NK114(ye)001:12163: de dag gi rgyud kyi slob pa dang mi slob
NK114(ye)001:12164: pa'i chos rnams la dge 'dun dkon mchog tu 'dod
NK114(ye)001:12165: pa'o // gnyis pa mdo sde pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:12166: bden zhen gyi ngos nas phyi don dang rang rig
NK114(ye)001:12167: gnyis ka khas len pa'i theg dman gyi grub mtha'
NK114(ye)001:12168: brjod pa la zhugs pa'i gang zag de mdo sde
NK114(ye)001:12170: dbye ba'i sgo nas lung dang rigs pa'i rjes 'brang gnyis las /
NK114(ye)001:12171: dang po ni bye smra rnams bkar 'dod pa'i mngon
NK114(ye)001:12172: pa sde bdun po sh+aa ri'i bu la sogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:12173: dgra bcom bdun gyi bstan bcos su 'dod nas grub
NK114(ye)001:12174: mtha' de las smra ba yin la /
NK114(ye)001:12175: phyi ma ni bstan bcos la tshad mar mi 'dzin
NK114(ye)001:12176: cing mdo sde la brten nas grub mtha' smra bas
NK114(ye)001:12177: chos kyi ming gang zag la chags te de skad
NK114(ye)001:12178: ces bya zhing chos rnams dpe dang 'brel bar ston
NK114(ye)001:12179: pas na dpe ston pa zhes kyang grags so //
NK114(ye)001:12180: 'di la gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las /
NK114(ye)001:12181: dang po gzhi'i chos rnams bden pa gnyis gtan la dbab pa'i tshul ni /
NK114(ye)001:12182: chu skyor ba'i don byed pa'i bum pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:12183: gdung ma 'degs pa'i don byed pa'i nus pa yod
NK114(ye)001:12184: pa ka ba dngos lta bu gang yin pa de
NK114(ye)001:12185: 'di ba'i grub matha'i skabs 'dir ni don dam par
NK114(ye)001:12186: yod pa min te rdzas su yod pa'i rdul phran
NK114(ye)001:12187: du ma 'dus pa las ma 'das pa'i phyir ro
NK114(ye)001:12188: // des na cha med gnyis 'dod pa tsam bye smra ba dang mtshungs kyang /
NK114(ye)001:12189: dus gsum rdzas grub dang nam mkha' rtag dngos sogs mi 'dod do //
NK114(ye)001:12190: de las gzhan yid rtog pa'i snang yul la shar
NK114(ye)001:12191: ba'i chu skyor ba la sogs pa'i don byed mi
NK114(ye)001:12192: nus pa'i ka bum sogs lta bu ni don rang
NK114(ye)001:12193: mtshan gyi gnas lugs mthong ba la sgrib pa'i phyir
NK114(ye)001:12194: kun rdzob yin la de yang 'khrul ba'i blo ngor
NK114(ye)001:12195: snang ba tsam du yod pa las grub pa med
NK114(ye)001:12196: do // de dag la rim pa bzhin don rang mtshan dang spyi'i mtshan nyid kyis bshad de /
NK114(ye)001:12197: mngon sum pa'i snang yul la rang mtshan gyis khyab cing /
NK114(ye)001:12198: de yang rang gi mtshan nya da 'dzin pas rang mtshan dang /
NK114(ye)001:12199: gzhi grub pas dngos po dang /
NK114(ye)001:12200: skye 'gag byed pas mi rtag pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:12201: rang rgyu sa bon sogs las skyes pas 'dus byas dang /
NK114(ye)001:12202: rang gi ngo bos mi stong pas don dam bden pa ste de rnams don gcig par 'dod cing /
NK114(ye)001:12203: rtog pa'i snang yul la spyi mtshan gyis khyab la /
NK114(ye)001:12204: de yang don gyi rnam par shar ba tsam las
NK114(ye)001:12205: don rang gi mtshan nyid mi 'dzin pas spyi mtshan
NK114(ye)001:12206: dang / rtsom gzhi med pas dngos med dang /
NK114(ye)001:12207: rang don skye 'gag byed rgyu med pas rtag pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:12208: des na rang rgyu sa bon sogs las skyes pa min pas 'dus ma byas dang /
NK114(ye)001:12209: rang gi ngo bo ma grub pas kun rdzob bden
NK114(ye)001:12210: pa ste de rnams kyang bden gcig khar 'dod pa'o
NK114(ye)001:12212: don byed nus pa gang yin pa //
NK114(ye)001:12213: de 'dir don dam yod pa yin //
NK114(ye)001:12214: gzhan ni kun rdzob yod pa ste //
NK114(ye)001:12215: de dag rang spyi'i mtshan nyid bshad //
NK114(ye)001:12217: des na mdo sde pa'i lugs kyi tha snyad rnam
NK114(ye)001:12218: par bzhag pa'i tshul rnams tshad ma nas ji skad
NK114(ye)001:12219: bshad pa dang mtshungs pas sam /
NK114(ye)001:12220: bye mdo gnyis ka'i bden gnyis gtan la dbab tshul
NK114(ye)001:12221: gyi ngo bo rang rang gi rtog ge'i blo yis
NK114(ye)001:12222: bzhag pa tsam las dngos po'i gnas tshul ji bzhin
NK114(ye)001:12223: pa min par mtshungs pas phyogs mthuna pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:12224: 'on kyang de gnyis kas de ltar brtags shing dpyad
NK114(ye)001:12225: pas phung sogs kyi chos rnams cha med gnyis tsam
NK114(ye)001:12226: su shes pas chos su bden par zhen pa phra
NK114(ye)001:12227: ba ma khegs kyang gang zag rang rkya ba'i rdzas
NK114(ye)001:12228: su grub pa'i bdag med par nges pa rnyed nas
NK114(ye)001:12230: thog ma nas dman par bltas te dgag pa gtso
NK114(ye)001:12231: bor mi byed par tshul 'di dag la brten nas
NK114(ye)001:12232: kyang thog med nas goms pa'i dngos 'dzin rags pa
NK114(ye)001:12233: ldog pa'i thabs su 'gro ba la 'bad na gzhung
NK114(ye)001:12234: lugs thams cad gdams par 'gro bas gal che bar
NK114(ye)001:12235: gsungs / gnyis pa lam gyi rnam bzhag ni /
NK114(ye)001:12236: bden bzhi'i rnam pa mi rtag sogs yin kyang gang
NK114(ye)001:12237: zag gi bdag med rtogs pa'i shes rab rkyang pa
NK114(ye)001:12238: thabs snying rje chen po sogs dang ma 'brel bar
NK114(ye)001:12239: nyams su len pa ni theg dman rang lam yin
NK114(ye)001:12240: la / shes rab de dang sems can la'ang phan
NK114(ye)001:12241: par 'dod pa'i bsam pa phun sum tshogs pa zung
NK114(ye)001:12242: du sbrel ba ni theg chen gyi nyams su len
NK114(ye)001:12243: la / tshul dang / dman mchog gi lam bgrod tshul snga ma dang phyogs mtshungs pa las /
NK114(ye)001:12244: lam gyi spang bya sgrib pa la yang /
NK114(ye)001:12246: nyon mongs pa can gyi mi shes pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:12247: nyon mongs pa can ma yin pa'i mi shes pa sogs kyi tha snyad tsam las /
NK114(ye)001:12249: shes sgrib sogs kyi tha snyad khas mi len to //
NK114(ye)001:12250: gsum pa 'bras bu'i rnam bzhag ni /
NK114(ye)001:12251: mi rtag sogs bcu drug po rkyang pa tsam bsgoms
NK114(ye)001:12252: pas nyon mongs pa can gyi mi shes pa spangs
NK114(ye)001:12253: te dgra bcom pa'i go 'phang mngon du byed pa
NK114(ye)001:12254: ni dman pa'i byang chub dang /
NK114(ye)001:12255: de bzhin du myang 'das gnyis kyis mtshon pa'i 'gog bden rnams chos dkon mchog dang /
NK114(ye)001:12256: lam bden dge 'dun dkon mchog tu 'dod la /
NK114(ye)001:12257: thabs snying rje chen po la sogs theg chen gyi
NK114(ye)001:12258: lam dang rjes su 'brel bar nyams su blangs pas
NK114(ye)001:12259: mi shes pa gnyis ka'i sa bon drungs nas phyung
NK114(ye)001:12260: ste / spangs pa khyad par gsum ldan dang /
NK114(ye)001:12261: rtogs pa khyad par gsum ldan gyis rang don mthar
NK114(ye)001:12262: phyin nas gzhan don mthar thug gdul bya la bden
NK114(ye)001:12263: pa bzhi'i chos 'khor bskor te smin grol la 'god
NK114(ye)001:12264: pa ni bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi 'bras
NK114(ye)001:12265: bur 'dod do // spyir nyan thos la dbye ba bzhir gsungs te /
NK114(ye)001:12267: nyan thos rnam bzhi sprul pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:12268: rdzogs pa'i byang chub 'gyur ba dang //
NK114(ye)001:12271: dang po ni mchog zung dang /
NK114(ye)001:12274: myang 'das las ni lhas byin dang /
NK114(ye)001:12275: drug sde yang der bsdus so //
NK114(ye)001:12277: rang lam gyis sbyor lam bzod pa thob nas theg
NK114(ye)001:12278: chen du zhugs te sangs rgyas su 'gyur ba la
NK114(ye)001:12279: gsungs shing / yang rigs ma nges pa dag rang
NK114(ye)001:12280: lam gyis 'bras bu bzhi po gang rung thob nas
NK114(ye)001:12281: gzod rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu 'gyur bar yang bshad
NK114(ye)001:12282: gsungs shing / do // gsum pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:12283: rigs nges pa rnams rang lam nas lhag med du song ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:12284: 'di yang mthar thug theg gcig tu bzhed pa klu
NK114(ye)001:12285: sgrub kyi dgongs pa ltar na zhing dag par pad+ma'i
NK114(ye)001:12286: sbubs su skyes pa la sangs rgyas kyis bskul nas
NK114(ye)001:12287: theg chen la 'jug dgos par gsungs so //
NK114(ye)001:12289: 'ga' zhig dman pa'i rigs can dag gis bshad ma
NK114(ye)001:12290: thag pa'i bye mdo'i grub mtha' bzung nas lta ba
NK114(ye)001:12291: de la brten nas rang 'bras dgra bcom thob pa
NK114(ye)001:12294: slob dpon klu sgrub zhabs kyi lam las ni //
NK114(ye)001:12295: phyi rol gyur la zhi ba'i thabs med do //
NK114(ye)001:12296: zhes pas dbu ma'i lta ba ma rtogs par mi
NK114(ye)001:12297: thob par bzhed pas de la grub mtha' 'dzin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:12298: nyan thos zer ro zhes gsungs shing /
NK114(ye)001:12299: rang lugs la bsam pa theg chen pas nyan thos kyi grub mtha' 'dzin pa la gsungs so //
NK114(ye)001:12300: gsum pa sems tsam pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:12301: phyi don mi 'dod cing rang rig bden grub tu
NK114(ye)001:12302: khas len pa'i theg chen gyi grub mtha' smra ba'i
NK114(ye)001:12303: gang zag de sems tsam pa'i mtshan nyid yin la
NK114(ye)001:12304: / dbye na so so skye bo'i rgyud kyi dbang
NK114(ye)001:12305: po'i mngon sum la snang ba'i gzugs sogs rags par
NK114(ye)001:12306: snang ba 'di dag snang ba ltar phyi don du
NK114(ye)001:12307: ma grub kyang sems su bden par 'dod pa rnam
NK114(ye)001:12308: / bden pa dang / de 'dra'i rnam pa de
NK114(ye)001:12309: phyi don du'ang ma grub nang sems su yang ma
NK114(ye)001:12310: grub par med snang du 'dod pa rnam rdzun pa
NK114(ye)001:12311: / bden pa dang / gnyis so // ting nge
NK114(ye)001:12312: 'dzin gyi cha nas nyams len gtan la 'bebs pas
NK114(ye)001:12313: rnal 'byor spyod pa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:12314: de ltar yang ye shes snying po kun las btus pa las /
NK114(ye)001:12315: cha shas can zhes byar med cing //
NK114(ye)001:12316: phra rab rdul rnams med pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:12317: so sor snang la dmigs med la //
NK114(ye)001:12318: nyams su myong ba rmi lam 'dra //
NK114(ye)001:12319: gzung dang 'dzin pa las grol ba'i //
NK114(ye)001:12320: rnam shes dam pa'i don du yod //
NK114(ye)001:12321: blo mtsho'i pha rol phyin pa yi //
NK114(ye)001:12322: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i gzhung lugs bsgrags //
NK114(ye)001:12324: 'di la gzhi lam 'bras bu'i rnam par bzhag pa gsum las /
NK114(ye)001:12325: dang po gzhi gtan la dbab tshul ni /
NK114(ye)001:12326: shes bya thams cad kun brtags gzhan dbang yongs grub gsum du bsdus nas shes par bya ba ste /
NK114(ye)001:12327: de yang bag chags kyi dbang gis gzung ba dang
NK114(ye)001:12328: 'dzin pa gnyis su med bzhin snang ba'i yul gzugs
NK114(ye)001:12330: yul can de dag 'dzin pa'i sems sogs blos bkod
NK114(ye)001:12331: cing sgro btags pa'i cha thams cad kun brtags yin
NK114(ye)001:12332: la / gnyis su snang tsam dang de'i gzhi ni
NK114(ye)001:12333: sems sems byung yin te de ni gzhan dbang ngo
NK114(ye)001:12334: la / // gzhan dbang de la kun brtags med
NK114(ye)001:12335: pa'i cha gang yin pa de ni yongs grub bo
NK114(ye)001:12336: la / // // de yang dper na rde'u dang
NK114(ye)001:12337: shing bu la sngags btab pas rta glang du snang
NK114(ye)001:12338: dus rde shing lta bu ni gzhan dbang /
NK114(ye)001:12339: de la rta glang du snang zhing der 'dzin pa dang btags pa lta bu ni kun brtags /
NK114(ye)001:12340: de ltar snang dus nyid nas rde shing tsam las
NK114(ye)001:12341: rta glang gis stong pa lta bu ni yongs grub
NK114(ye)001:12342: bo // de dag bden pa gnyis su bsdu na /
NK114(ye)001:12343: kun brtags ni gzung 'dzin gnyis su med bzhin snang
NK114(ye)001:12344: ba la der bden par sgro btags pa yin pas
NK114(ye)001:12345: kun rdzob kyi bden pa nyid de /
NK114(ye)001:12346: gang kun brtags lasa gzhan snang gzhi gzhan dbang gi
NK114(ye)001:12347: ngo bo gzung 'dzin gnyis med kyi shes pa rang
NK114(ye)001:12348: rig dang / de'i steng na kun brtags kyi stong
NK114(ye)001:12349: pa'i yongs grub gnyis ni don dam pa'i bden pa
NK114(ye)001:12350: ru 'dod pa ste snga ma ni chos can don
NK114(ye)001:12351: rig dang / dam dang / phyi ma ni chos nyid don dam mo //
NK114(ye)001:12352: yang na gzhan dbang kun rdzob kyi phyogs su bsdu ste chos can gyis bsdus pa yin pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:12353: gzung 'dzin gnyis su snang tsam la bden par sgro ma btags pa'i cha yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:12354: des na bden pa sgro ma btags na gnyis su
NK114(ye)001:12355: snang tsam ni sems sems byung rang rig gi ngo
NK114(ye)001:12356: bor snang ba'i gnas tshul 'phags pa'i rjes thob kyi
NK114(ye)001:12357: snang ba bzhin yin pas gzhan dbang gi gnas tshul
NK114(ye)001:12359: so skye'i dus su kun brtags kyis bslad nas ji bzhin par mthong ba ma yin par gsungs shing /
NK114(ye)001:12360: gsum po de la nang gses kyis dbye na kun brtags la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:12361: don la mi srid bzhin blos btags pa chos dang
NK114(ye)001:12362: gang zag gi bdag lta bu mtshan nyid chad pa
NK114(ye)001:12363: dang / med bzhin blo la snang ba gzugs brnyan
NK114(ye)001:12364: dang don spyi dang ming gis btags pa thams cad
NK114(ye)001:12365: rnam grangs pa'i kun brtags so //
NK114(ye)001:12367: 'jig rten pa'i sems sems byung yul dang bcas pa ma dag gzhan dbang dang /
NK114(ye)001:12368: 'phags pa'i rjes thob kyi sems sems byung yul dang bcas pa dag pa gzhan dbang ngo //
NK114(ye)001:12370: de bzhin nyid 'gyur med yongs grub dang /
NK114(ye)001:12371: de rtogs pa'i ye shes phyin ci ma log pa'i yongs grub bo //
NK114(ye)001:12372: sems tsam pa 'di yi grub pa'i mtha' 'dzin pa rnams kyis yul can gyi rnam bzhag ni /
NK114(ye)001:12373: tshogs brgyad khas len pa dag gis kun gzhi ni
NK114(ye)001:12374: gsal tsam snod bcud rgya chen po la dmigs pa
NK114(ye)001:12375: can ngo bo ma bsgribs lung ma bstan no //
NK114(ye)001:12376: nyon yid ni kun gzhi la dmigs nas bdag tu
NK114(ye)001:12377: 'dzin pa ste ngo bo sgribs lung ma bstan no
NK114(ye)001:12378: // 'jug shes drug po spyi dang mthun kyang tshur
NK114(ye)001:12379: mthong gi rgyud kyi rang rig dang rnal 'byor mngon
NK114(ye)001:12380: sum gnyis las gzhan 'khrul ba'i cha can du 'dod
NK114(ye)001:12381: // la / 'on kyang mngon sum ni rtog bral gyis khyab pa can yin no //
NK114(ye)001:12382: skye tshul yang tshogs bdun 'khor bcas rang gi rgyun
NK114(ye)001:12383: las mi skye ste rigs 'du phyi ma 'grub pa'i
NK114(ye)001:12384: bag chags kun gzhi la bgos te bum pa'i grib
NK114(ye)001:12385: ma ltar kun gzhi'i skad cig re re las skye
NK114(ye)001:12386: bar 'dod do // kun gzhi khas mi len pa
NK114(ye)001:12387: ltar na yid shes rtog med rgyun ldan du 'jug
NK114(ye)001:12388: pa la bag chags bzhag pa las gnas don lus
NK114(ye)001:12390: tshul 'di lta bus kyang rang rgyud kyi phyi don
NK114(ye)001:12391: gyi zhen pa 'gog par 'gyur bas rang gi zhen
NK114(ye)001:12392: pa'i gnyen por 'gro ba ni gdams ngag go //
NK114(ye)001:12393: gnyis pa lam gyi rnam bzhag ni /
NK114(ye)001:12394: dman lam la bden bzhi'i rnam pa mi rtag sogs
NK114(ye)001:12395: bcu drug la dmigs nas bskal pa brgya la sogs
NK114(ye)001:12396: pa'i bsod nams kyi tshogs dang 'brel bar spyod pa'i
NK114(ye)001:12397: yun gyi goms pa ngang bsrings pa'i khyad par gyis
NK114(ye)001:12398: rang rgyal dgra bcom pa'i go 'phang dang /
NK114(ye)001:12399: tshogs de tsam dang ma 'brel ba'i gang zag gi
NK114(ye)001:12400: bdag med rkyang pa tsam gyis nyan thos kyi byang
NK114(ye)001:12401: chub tsam las mi thob bo //
NK114(ye)001:12402: de bas na rang rgyal la sde snod logs pa med do //
NK114(ye)001:12403: theg chen gyi lam ni gang zag rang rkya thub
NK114(ye)001:12404: pa'i rdzas yod kyis stong pa'i gang zag gi bdag
NK114(ye)001:12405: med dang / gzung 'dzin rdzas gzhan gyis stong pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:12406: kun brtags rang gi mtshan nya da kyis grub pas
NK114(ye)001:12407: stong pa'i chos kyi bdag med gsum la dmigs nas
NK114(ye)001:12408: sems skad cig ma'i phreng ba tsam la btags pa'i
NK114(ye)001:12409: sems can kun gyi don du grangs med gsum la
NK114(ye)001:12410: sogs pa'i tshogs dang 'brel bar lam lnga dang sa
NK114(ye)001:12411: bcu rim gyis bsgrod de gang zag gi bdag 'dzin
NK114(ye)001:12412: nyon sgrib dang / chos kyi bdag 'dzin shes sgrib
NK114(ye)001:12413: zad par spangs te bla na med pa'i byang chub
NK114(ye)001:12415: gsum pa 'bras bu'i rnam bzhag ni /
NK114(ye)001:12416: lhag bcas lhag med mi gnas pa'i myang 'das gsum dang /
NK114(ye)001:12417: gnas 'gyur ba'i ye shes sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi rnam bzhag dang /
NK114(ye)001:12418: chos sku la ngo bo nyid dang ye shes chos sku gnyis /
NK114(ye)001:12419: phrin las lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:12420: rgyun mi 'chad pa'i rnam bzhag rnams kyang 'dod pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:12421: bzhi pa dbu ma pa'i grub mtha' bshad pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:12422: gzung 'dzin gnyis ka don dam par ma grub par
NK114(ye)001:12423: rtogs nas phyi don rang rig gnyis ka bden grub
NK114(ye)001:12424: tu mi 'dod pa'i theg chen gyi grub mtha' 'dzin
NK114(ye)001:12425: pa'i gang zag de dbu ma pa'i mtshan nyid /
NK114(ye)001:12426: dbye na tshul gsum rang ngos nas grub pa'i rtags
NK114(ye)001:12427: yang dag la brten nas bden dngos 'gog par byed
NK114(ye)001:12429: thal 'gyur tsam gyis phyir rgol gyi rgyud la bsgrub
NK114(ye)001:12430: bya rtogs pa'i rjes dpag skye bar 'dod pa thal
NK114(ye)001:12432: de la dang po ni tshogs drug gi blo gnod
NK114(ye)001:12433: med kyi yul la gzugs la sogs pa'i chos ji
NK114(ye)001:12434: ltar snang ba 'di thams cad tha snyad kun rdzob
NK114(ye)001:12435: tu rang gi mtshan nyid kyis grub ste /
NK114(ye)001:12436: tha snyad dpyod byed kyi ngor grub pa'i phyir zhes bzhed de /
NK114(ye)001:12437: des na bden grub sogs med kyang rang ngos nas grub pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:12438: rang bzhin gyis grub pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:12439: rang gi mtshan nyid kyis grub pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:12440: rdzas su grub pa rnams ni don gcig cing de
NK114(ye)001:12441: don dam dpyod byed kyi rtags kyis dgag byar mi
NK114(ye)001:12442: 'dod do // des na dbu ma'i gzhung las rang
NK114(ye)001:12443: bzhin ma grub par gsungs pa 'ga' zhig snang ba
NK114(ye)001:12444: la don dam gyi khyad par sbyar dgos zhes bzhed
NK114(ye)001:12446: de yang rgyu rkyen gyi rten 'brel tsam las snang
NK114(ye)001:12447: ba'i sgyu ma lta bu'i mtshan nyid du grub pa
NK114(ye)001:12448: de la las 'bras la sogs pa'i chos rnams ma
NK114(ye)001:12449: 'dres par rnam par 'jog tu yod na'ang /
NK114(ye)001:12450: don dam dpyod byed kyi rig shes kyis yul rang
NK114(ye)001:12451: gi grub tshul la dpyad na gang du'ang grub pa
NK114(ye)001:12452: med pa nam mkha' ltar rnam par dag pa ste
NK114(ye)001:12453: / des na bden par grub pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:12454: don dam par grub pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:12455: yang dag par grub pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:12456: de kho na nyid du grub pa rnams don gcig
NK114(ye)001:12457: pas don dam la dpyod byed kyi rtags kyis dgag
NK114(ye)001:12459: dgag bya bdag 'dzin gnyis po'ang dmigs yul gyi sgo
NK114(ye)001:12460: nas mi 'byed par 'dzin stabs kyi sgo nas 'byed
NK114(ye)001:12461: de gang zag la dmigs nas rang rkya thub pa'i
NK114(ye)001:12462: rdzas yod du 'dzin pa gang zag gi bdag 'dzin
NK114(ye)001:12463: dang / gang zag sogs la dmigs nas bden grub
NK114(ye)001:12464: tu 'dzin pa chos kyi bdag 'dzin du 'doda pa
NK114(ye)001:12465: dang / yin no // de dag ni dbu ma rang rgyud pa spyi yi 'dod lugs so //
NK114(ye)001:12466: bye brag gi dbye ba rang rgyud 'og ma dang /
NK114(ye)001:12468: dang po 'og ma la'ang sgyu mar rigs grub pa
NK114(ye)001:12469: zhes bya ba slob dpon rgya mtsho'i sprin la sogs
NK114(ye)001:12470: pa ni chos thams cad ngo bo ma grub pa
NK114(ye)001:12471: sgyu ma'i rang bzhin du bden pa gnyis char gnas
NK114(ye)001:12472: te kun rdzob kyi snang ba mi bden pa sgyu
NK114(ye)001:12474: don dam stong yang rten 'brel du snang ba ma
NK114(ye)001:12475: 'gags pas tshogs gnyis sgyu ma lta bu bsags pas
NK114(ye)001:12476: 'bras bu byang chub sgyu ma lta bu thob nas
NK114(ye)001:12477: sgyu ma'i rang bzhin la rtag tu mnyam par bzhag
NK114(ye)001:12478: bzhin sgyu ma'i phrin las kyis sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK114(ye)001:12479: sems can gyi don byed do //
NK114(ye)001:12480: des na rgyu rkyen rten 'brel gyi dbang las snang ba thams cad sgyu ma lta bu ste /
NK114(ye)001:12481: 'khrul snang sgyu ma dang 'khrul pa bral ba'i ye
NK114(ye)001:12482: shes kyi snang yul du spros pa zhi yang gsal
NK114(ye)001:12483: ba ma 'gags pa'i snang ba sgyu ma lta bu
NK114(ye)001:12484: ste / mdor na gzhi lam 'bras bu thams cad sgyu ma ltar 'dod pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:12485: yang snang stong tha dad pa zhes bya ba slob dpon dpal sbas la sogs pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:12486: don dam par cir yang ma grub pa'i phyir sgyu ma zhes dmigs su med la /
NK114(ye)001:12487: kun rdzob tha snyad tsam du bum sogs stong nyid ma yin te /
NK114(ye)001:12488: don byed par snang zhing bden pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:12489: don dam par ni dpyad na ci yang mi rnyed pa'i phyir stong pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:12490: des na don dam pa dpyad bzod dang /
NK114(ye)001:12491: kun rdzob dpyad mi bzod pa gnyis chos can dang chos nyid ces gzhi gcig la mi 'du ste /
NK114(ye)001:12492: kun rdzob mi rtag pa ltar don dam yang der thal ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:12493: don dam skye 'gag med pa ltar kun rdzob kyang
NK114(ye)001:12494: der thal bar 'gyur bas snang ba kun rdzob chos
NK114(ye)001:12495: can dang / stong pa don dam chos nyid gnyis
NK114(ye)001:12496: phan tshun ltos pas grub pa tsam mo zhes 'dod
NK114(ye)001:12497: can dang / / kun rdzob la yang log gnyis su phye ba gong ma dang 'dra'o //
NK114(ye)001:12498: gnyis pa rang rgyud gong ma slob dpon ye shes snying po dang /
NK114(ye)001:12500: ka ma la sh+ai la la sogs pas ni /
NK114(ye)001:12501: don dam sgyu ma dang stong pa kho nar rigs
NK114(ye)001:12502: pas dpyad bzod pa med pas gnas lugs mthar thug
NK114(ye)001:12503: gi don la rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don dam
NK114(ye)001:12504: spros pa kun las 'das pa yin na'ang /
NK114(ye)001:12505: gnas skabs su kun rdzob tha snyad kyi dngos po
NK114(ye)001:12506: rang rang gi mtshan nyid 'dzin cing mi bslu bar
NK114(ye)001:12507: gnas 'di la / rigs pas dpyad na grub pa
NK114(ye)001:12508: cung zad med pa'i stong pa'am don dam rnam grangs
NK114(ye)001:12509: pa gnyis mgo mnyam par bsgrub pas na khas len
NK114(ye)001:12510: gnas 'di la / dang bcas shing / rang lugs sgrub pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:12511: gzhan phyogs dgag pa thams cad gtan tshigs rang rgyud pa'i sgo nas byed de /
NK114(ye)001:12512: dper na dngos po rtag par 'dod pa na /
NK114(ye)001:12517: zhes pas bkag pa'i rjes su /
NK114(ye)001:12521: byas pa yin pa'i phyir te /
NK114(ye)001:12522: rgyu rkyen las skyes pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:12523: zhes pa lta bu yin la /
NK114(ye)001:12525: kun rdzob la yang log byed tshul ni sngar bden gnyis spyir bstan pa'i skabs su bshad zin la /
NK114(ye)001:12526: de yang 'khrul pa'i kun rdzob rnams dag pa'i sa
NK114(ye)001:12527: ma thob kyi bar du mi ldog ste 'phags pa
NK114(ye)001:12528: rnams kyi rjes thob kyi snang ba la dag pa
NK114(ye)001:12530: de ltar bden gnyis 'gal med du shes pas tshogs gnyis bsags te sku gnyis thob par 'dod do //
NK114(ye)001:12531: yang phyi don bzhed mi bzhed kyis tha snyad btags
NK114(ye)001:12532: na legs ldan 'abyedakyisa rtsa shes 'grel pa shes rab
NK114(ye)001:12534: de'i rjes 'brangs ye shes snying pos dbu ma bden gnyis rang 'grel bcas mdzad /
NK114(ye)001:12535: yab sras 'di gnyis kyis phyi don tha snyad du
NK114(ye)001:12536: bzhed cing rang rig mi bzhed pa sogs kyi cha
NK114(ye)001:12537: nas mdo sde spyod pa'i dbu mar rang rgyud pa
NK114(ye)001:12538: zhes bya la / zhi ba 'tshos dbu ma rgyan dang /
NK114(ye)001:12539: de'i slob ma ka sh+ai'i dbu ma snang ba mdzad
NK114(ye)001:12540: de yab sras 'di gnyis tha snyad du phyi don
NK114(ye)001:12542: rang rig bzhed pas rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu ma rang rgyud pa zhes grags pa yin zhing /
NK114(ye)001:12543: zhi 'tsho'i sngon nas byon pa'i 'phags pa grol sde
NK114(ye)001:12544: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu ma rang rgyud pa yin
NK114(ye)001:12545: yang srol 'byed du mi 'jog ste de 'dra gzhan
NK114(ye)001:12547: de ltar rang rgyud pa de dag gis bden gnyis
NK114(ye)001:12548: gtan la dbab tshul 'di la brten nas don dam
NK114(ye)001:12549: par ma grub bzhin rten 'byung gi snang ba 'gog
NK114(ye)001:12550: med du 'char rung ba 'di la nges shes rnyed
NK114(ye)001:12551: na rab tu mi gnas pa'i dbu ma chen po
NK114(ye)001:12552: la 'jug pa'i go skabs yod par 'gyur gyi /
NK114(ye)001:12553: de ltar ma yin par thog med nas goms pa'i
NK114(ye)001:12554: bden zhen a 'thas kyi rtog pa 'di la rma
NK114(ye)001:12555: ma byas par thog ma nas mtho rnyab byas te
NK114(ye)001:12556: 'og ma khyad du gsod par byas na grub mtha'
NK114(ye)001:12557: smod pa dang / chos spang ba'i nyes pa 'go
NK114(ye)001:12558: ba tsam las gong ma'i dgongs don rtogs dka' bas
NK114(ye)001:12559: man ngag yod dgu'i rno so thams cad sems kyi
NK114(ye)001:12560: tha ba 'di la 'bebs par byas na gzhung lugs
NK114(ye)001:12561: thams cad gdams par shar 'ong gsungs /
NK114(ye)001:12562: rang rgyud pa de dag gis kyang dbu ma'i gzhung
NK114(ye)001:12563: nas ji skad bshad pa'i gtan tshigs chen po rnams
NK114(ye)001:12564: kyis rtag chad kyi mtha' sel bar byed pa tsam
NK114(ye)001:12565: la ni thal 'gyur ba dang mi 'dra ba med
NK114(ye)001:12566: pas gtan tshigs rnams 'og tu ston no //
NK114(ye)001:12567: gnyis pa dbu ma thal 'gyur pa'i grub mtha' bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK114(ye)001:12568: gzhi dbu ma bden gnyis zung 'jug /
NK114(ye)001:12569: lam dbu ma tshogs gnyis zung 'jug /'bras bu dbu ma sku gnyis zung 'jug go //
NK114(ye)001:12571: gzhi gtan la dbab tshul dngos bshad pa /
NK114(ye)001:12572: de gzhan las 'phags pa'i rgyu mtshan bstan pa /
NK114(ye)001:12573: de ltar gtan la dbab pa'i sgom don ngos bzung ba /
NK114(ye)001:12574: khas len mi len gyi rnam bzhag bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:12576: shes bya bden gnyis kyi rang bzhin gtan la dbab pa /
NK114(ye)001:12577: dgag bya bdag gnyis kyi ngo bo ngos bzung ba /
NK114(ye)001:12578: 'gog byed gtan tshigs kyis ji ltar dpyad pa'i tshul bstan pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:12579: dang po shes bya bden gnyis kyi rang bzhin gtan la dbab pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:12580: 'di ltar snang zhing srid pa'i chos so cog thams
NK114(ye)001:12581: cad rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba sgyu ma dang
NK114(ye)001:12582: rmi lam lta bu'i tshul du snang ba tsam 'di
NK114(ye)001:12583: nyid grub ma grub sogs su ma dpyad par don
NK114(ye)001:12584: dam pa'i bden pa la ni 'jug pa'i thabs su
NK114(ye)001:12585: kun rdzob bo zhes brjod par bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:12587: de'i phyir kun rdzob kyi bden pa gang yin pa
NK114(ye)001:12588: de ni don dam pa'i bden pa la 'jug par
NK114(ye)001:12589: bya ba'i thabs yin pa'i phyir bdag dang gzhan las
NK114(ye)001:12590: skye ba ma dpyad par 'jig rten pa'i lugs kyis
NK114(ye)001:12591: khas len par byed pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:12594: bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jig rten nga dang lhan cig rtsod kyi /
NK114(ye)001:12595: nga ni 'jig rten dang lhan cig mi rtsod de /
NK114(ye)001:12596: gang 'jig rten na yod par 'dod pa de ni nga yang yod par bzhed do //
NK114(ye)001:12597: gang 'jig rten na med par 'dod pa de ngas kyang med par bzhed de /
NK114(ye)001:12599: de yang 'jig rten pa'i lugs zhes bya ba gzhan
NK114(ye)001:12600: ngo tsam du ston pa kho na ma yin te
NK114(ye)001:12601: brten nas 'byung ba'i snang ba gang zhig rang gzhan
NK114(ye)001:12602: thams cad la bslu med du snang ba de ji
NK114(ye)001:12603: ltar snang tsam pa de bzhin du yod med du
NK114(ye)001:12604: ma dpyad par khas len pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:12605: chos can de dang tha mi dad pa'i chos nyid
NK114(ye)001:12606: ni snang ba de yi rang gi rang bzhin yod
NK114(ye)001:12607: med sogs gang du'ang ma grub pa'i stong pa nyid
NK114(ye)001:12608: du gdod ma nas gnas pa la don dam pa'o
NK114(ye)001:12609: zhes bya bar tha snyad kyi sgo nas btags pa
NK114(ye)001:12610: tsam gyi don la de gnyis snang ba dang stong
NK114(ye)001:12611: pa gang gi yang phyogs su ma lhung bar chos
NK114(ye)001:12612: rnams rang gi ngo bo gzhi dang rtsa ba med
NK114(ye)001:12613: pas spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba yin
NK114(ye)001:12614: gyis / gzhan du na tha snyad du yod pa
NK114(ye)001:12615: ma bkag par de'i steng gi bden grub yan gang
NK114(ye)001:12616: bas stong pa'i snang stong gnyis pos yod med kyi
NK114(ye)001:12617: spros pa 'gog pa'i spros bral ni 'di dang ming
NK114(ye)001:12618: tsam du 'dra yang don mi gcig ste /
NK114(ye)001:12619: bden med dang bden med kyis khyad par du byas
NK114(ye)001:12620: pa'i snang ba gnyis yod rgyu dang med rgyu tha
NK114(ye)001:12621: dad du song ba de 'dra'i bden med shes kyang
NK114(ye)001:12622: des chags sogs cung zad kyang ldog mi nus te
NK114(ye)001:12623: stong nyid de 'dra ji ltar goms kyang tha snyad
NK114(ye)001:12624: kyi chos de dag la der 'dzin pa'i 'du shes
NK114(ye)001:12626: de ma zhig na de la chags sdang sogs kyang ji ltar 'jig ste /
NK114(ye)001:12628: rang rgyud 'og ma snang stong tha dad pa'i lugs dgag pa'i skabs su /
NK114(ye)001:12629: snang ba ma yin pa'i stong pa bden pa gnyis char mi srid pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:12630: rtogs byar mi rung ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:12631: tha dad du gyur na spang gnyen mi 'thad de /
NK114(ye)001:12632: dgra la zhe sdang skyes pa la nam mkha' stong par shes pas mi phan pa ltar /
NK114(ye)001:12633: gzhi rdzun snang la zhen nas logs su stong par
NK114(ye)001:12634: shes pas ci yang mi phan par gsungs pa dang
NK114(ye)001:12636: su dag bud med 'du shes gnas //
NK114(ye)001:12638: 'du shes dag ni rnam bshig na //
NK114(ye)001:12641: gal te 'du shes med na byams sogs ji ltar
NK114(ye)001:12642: bsgom ste de dag bden grub kyi 'du shes la
NK114(ye)001:12643: sbyar dgos kyi yul de dang de'i 'du shes med
NK114(ye)001:12644: dgos pa ma yin no zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:12645: bud med dang dgra la sogs pa yul gang dang
NK114(ye)001:12646: gang la de dang der 'dzin pa ni gzung 'dzin
NK114(ye)001:12647: gyi rtog pa nyon mongs skyed byed kyi rgyu yin
NK114(ye)001:12648: pas de ma spang na de las gzhan yul de'i
NK114(ye)001:12649: steng na bden grub ces pa'i dgag rgyu zhig med
NK114(ye)001:12650: de / cang skya rol pa'i rdo rje'i gsung mgur las /
NK114(ye)001:12651: da lta rang re yi blo gsal 'ga' zhig /
NK114(ye)001:12652: snang ba ling ling de rang sar bzhag nas //
NK114(ye)001:12653: dgag rgyu rwa can zhig tshol bar 'dug kyang //
NK114(ye)001:12654: a ma rgan mo de bros dogs 'dug go //
NK114(ye)001:12656: des na las dang po pa la go bde ba'i
NK114(ye)001:12657: phyir bden grub kyis stong pa'i tha snyad kyi chos
NK114(ye)001:12658: shig yod pa ltar gsungs kyang gnas tshul de 'dra
NK114(ye)001:12659: ba'i gnas mi rnyed de byams sogs bsgom pa yang
NK114(ye)001:12660: dper na 'ga' zhig gi rmi lam na 'jigs skrag
NK114(ye)001:12661: gi yul dgra dang gcan gzan sogs kyis ded nas
NK114(ye)001:12662: sdug bsngal zhing de dag med pa'i bde ba don
NK114(ye)001:12663: du gnyer ba la mngon shes can gzhan zhig gis
NK114(ye)001:12664: de na dgra yang med la des ded pa yang
NK114(ye)001:12665: med pa shes kyang de 'jigs skrag de dang bral
NK114(ye)001:12666: nas dbugs dbyung ba'i phyir de sad pa'i thabs la
NK114(ye)001:12667: sems pa bzhin yang dag par na chos gang yang
NK114(ye)001:12668: dmigs su med kyang tha snyad du dmigs pa gnyis
NK114(ye)001:12670: rgyu mtshan de lta bas na gzugs la sogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:12671: chos 'di dag mig la sogs pa'i tshogs drug gi
NK114(ye)001:12672: yul la skye 'gag dang 'gro 'ong la sogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:12673: rnam par snang dus nyid nas gzugs brnyan dang smig
NK114(ye)001:12674: rgyu bzhin skye ba dang 'gag pa dang 'gro ba
NK114(ye)001:12675: dang 'ong ba la sogs pa chos de rang rang
NK114(ye)001:12676: gi ngo bo na med de skye sogs su snang
NK114(ye)001:12677: ba'i chos tsam pa'i ngo bo yang grub ma myong
NK114(ye)001:12678: ba'i phyir / brten nas byung ba'i snang ba thams
NK114(ye)001:12679: cad ye nas ma skyes pa'i rang bzhin du rtogs
NK114(ye)001:12684: gzugs las kyang stong pa nyid gzhan ma yin /
NK114(ye)001:12685: stong pa nyid las kyang gzugs gzhan ma yin no //
NK114(ye)001:12686: zhes gsungs pa'i stong nyid bzhi sbyor gyi dgongs pa
NK114(ye)001:12687: ltar snang stong mnyam pa nyid du shes pas na
NK114(ye)001:12688: / sems tsam pas gzhan dbang gi shes pa rang
NK114(ye)001:12689: gsal gyi ngo bo mi stong par 'dod pa dang
NK114(ye)001:12690: / / rang rgyud pas gzugs sogs rgyu rkyen gyi
NK114(ye)001:12691: gzhan dbang can gyi dngos po 'di dag tha snyad
NK114(ye)001:12692: du grub par 'dod pa lta bu'i sgo nas ni
NK114(ye)001:12693: kun rdzob kyi chos rnams kyang thal 'gyur ba de
NK114(ye)001:12694: yi grub pa'i mtha' ru khas ma blangs na don
NK114(ye)001:12695: dam par ni smos ci dgos te /
NK114(ye)001:12697: gal te ngas dam bcas 'ga' yod //
NK114(ye)001:12698: de tshe nga la skyon de yod //
NK114(ye)001:12699: nga la dam bca' med pas na //
NK114(ye)001:12700: nga ni skyon med kho na yin //
NK114(ye)001:12703: yod dang med dang yod med ces //
NK114(ye)001:12704: gang la phyogs ni yod min pa //
NK114(ye)001:12705: de la yun ni ring por yang //
NK114(ye)001:12706: klan ka brjod par nus ma yin //
NK114(ye)001:12709: ji ltar khyod kyi gzhan dbang dngos 'dod ltar //
NK114(ye)001:12710: kun rdzob kyang ni bdag gis khas ma blangs //
NK114(ye)001:12711: 'bras phyir 'di dag med kyang yod do zhes //
NK114(ye)001:12712: 'jig rten ngor byas bdag ni smra bar byed //
NK114(ye)001:12714: de ltar rgyal bas nges don gyi mdo sde nas
NK114(ye)001:12715: ji skad gsungs pa'i dgongs don phyin ci ma log
NK114(ye)001:12716: par ji lta ba bzhin bkral ba'i tshul de ni
NK114(ye)001:12717: thal 'gyur kyi thog ma'i shing rta'i srol 'byed chen
NK114(ye)001:12718: po / lung gis zin pa'i skyes bu dam pa
NK114(ye)001:12719: dpal ldan klu yi dbang pos dgongs 'grel gzhan la
NK114(ye)001:12720: ma ltos par rang stobs kyis bkral te dbu ma
NK114(ye)001:12721: rigs pa'i tshogs rnams mdzad nas da lta'i bar du
NK114(ye)001:12725: lho phyogs be ta'i yul du ni //
NK114(ye)001:12726: dge slong dpal ldan cher grags pa //
NK114(ye)001:12727: de ming klu zhes 'bod pa ste //
NK114(ye)001:12728: yod dang med pa'i phyogs 'jig pa //
NK114(ye)001:12729: nga yi bstan pa 'jig rten du //
NK114(ye)001:12730: bla med theg chen rab bshad nas //
NK114(ye)001:12731: rab tu dga' ba'i sa bsgrubs te //
NK114(ye)001:12735: de bzhin gshegs pa nga 'das nas //
NK114(ye)001:12736: lo ni bzhi brgya lon pa na //
NK114(ye)001:12738: bstan pa la ni dad cing phan //
NK114(ye)001:12739: rab tu dga' ba'i sa 'thob pa //
NK114(ye)001:12740: lo ni drug brgya dag tu 'tsho //
NK114(ye)001:12741: rig pa rma bya chen mo ni //
NK114(ye)001:12742: bdag nyid chen po des kyang 'grub //
NK114(ye)001:12743: bstan bcos sna tshogs don dang ni //
NK114(ye)001:12744: dngos po med pa'i don de rig /
NK114(ye)001:12745: gang tshe lus de bor ba na //
NK114(ye)001:12746: bde ba can du skye bar 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:12747: de ni mthar gyis sangs rgyas nyid //
NK114(ye)001:12748: nges pa kho nar yang dag 'thob //
NK114(ye)001:12750: yang gser 'od dam pa nas bshad pa ston pa
NK114(ye)001:12751: zhal bzhugs dus kyi li ts+aa byi gzhon nu 'jig
NK114(ye)001:12752: rten thams cad kyis mthong na dga' ba zhes bya
NK114(ye)001:12753: ba de nyid lung bstan pa yin te /
NK114(ye)001:12755: gzhon nu'i 'di nga mya ngan las 'das nas lo
NK114(ye)001:12756: bzhi brgya lon pa na klu zhes bya ba'i dge
NK114(ye)001:12757: slong du gyur nas nga'i bstan pa rgyas par byed
NK114(ye)001:12758: de mthar rab tu dwangs pa'i 'od ces bya ba'i
NK114(ye)001:12759: zhing du ye shes 'byung gnas 'od ces bya ba'i
NK114(ye)001:12760: rgyal bar 'gyur ro zhes mdo'i tshig sna cung zad
NK114(ye)001:12761: bsdud do // de'i gzhung rigs pa'i tshogs drug gi don 'grel ba po'ang 'phags pa lha dang /
NK114(ye)001:12764: zla ba grags pa la sogs pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:12765: de dag gi nang nas mi 'phrogs pa'i mkhyen rab
NK114(ye)001:12766: dang thugs rje ldan pa zla ba grags pas ni
NK114(ye)001:12767: slob dpon gyi dgongs pa phyin ci ma log par
NK114(ye)001:12768: thugs su chud nas dbu ma rtsa ba'i don 'grel
NK114(ye)001:12770: tshig 'grel tshig gsal mdzad de rgyal ba'i dgongs pa
NK114(ye)001:12771: mthar thug pa'i don ji bzhin par bkral ba'i thal
NK114(ye)001:12772: 'gyur ba'i grub pa'i matha'i nyi ma 'dzam bu'i gling
NK114(ye)001:12773: du shar bar mdzad pas lta ba ngan pa'i mun
NK114(ye)001:12774: pa mtha' dag bsal bar byas pa'i khyad chos dang
NK114(ye)001:12776: gnyis pa dgag bya bdag gnyis kyi ngo bo ngos bzung ba la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:12777: bdag dang bdag 'dzin sogs kyi khyad par dpyad nas spang bya ngos bzung ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:12778: khyad par gyi chos gzhan bstan pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:12779: dang po ni 'dir bdag zhes bya ba'i dgag bya
NK114(ye)001:12780: rang mtshan pa zhig med kyang thag khra la sbrul
NK114(ye)001:12781: ltar bdag 'dzin gyi zhen yul sun ma phyung na
NK114(ye)001:12782: bdag 'dzin spong mi nus pas de bshad pa ni
NK114(ye)001:12783: / spyir gang zag dang chos zhes pa'i gang zag
NK114(ye)001:12784: ni rang gi gdags gzhi'i phung po la brten nas
NK114(ye)001:12785: btags pa'i gang zag lhas byin lta bu yin la
NK114(ye)001:12786: / / chos zhes pa ni chos dang gang zag
NK114(ye)001:12787: gnyis su phye ba'i chos gang zag gi gdags gzhir
NK114(ye)001:12788: gyur pa lhas byin gyi mig lta bus mtshon gang
NK114(ye)001:12789: zag gi rgyud kyi phung po dang de las gzhan
NK114(ye)001:12792: gang zag rang bzhin gyis grub pa gang zag gi bdag dang /
NK114(ye)001:12793: chos rang bzhin gyis grub pa chos kyi bdag ste /
NK114(ye)001:12794: dper na thag khra la sbrul du 'khrul dus thag
NK114(ye)001:12795: khra'i steng gi sbrul lta bu bdag 'dzin gnyis kyi
NK114(ye)001:12796: zhen yul te / de gnyis ni ri rwa ltar tha snyad du yang med do //
NK114(ye)001:12798: gang zag rang bzhin gyis grub par 'dzin pa gang zag gi bdag 'dzin dang /
NK114(ye)001:12799: chos rang bzhin gyis grub par 'dzin pa chos kyi bdag 'dzin yin zhing /
NK114(ye)001:12800: bdag 'dzin gnyis kyi dmigs yul ni gang zag dang
NK114(ye)001:12801: chos gnyis yin te dper na sbrul du 'khrul pa'i
NK114(ye)001:12804: gang zag rang bzhin gyis ma grub pa gang zag gi bdag med dang /
NK114(ye)001:12805: chos rang bzhin gyis ma grub pa chos kyi bdag med do //
NK114(ye)001:12806: de ltar rtogs pa ni bdag med gnyis rtogs pa'i shes rab bo //
NK114(ye)001:12807: 'di dag ni tha snyad du yod par brjod do //
NK114(ye)001:12808: des na spang bya sgrib pa gnyis ka'i rtsa ba
NK114(ye)001:12809: ni bdag 'dzin gnyis yin la de gnyis kyi zhen
NK114(ye)001:12810: yul ni bdag gnyis por 'du bas de ni dgag
NK114(ye)001:12812: gtan nas med pa la yod par bzung ba'i 'khrul
NK114(ye)001:12813: rtog gi zhen yul de med par dpyad pa'i sgo
NK114(ye)001:12814: nas sun phyung ste bdag med gnyis kyi don la
NK114(ye)001:12815: nges shes bskyed de bdag 'dzin gnyis dang dngos su
NK114(ye)001:12816: 'gal ba'i nges shes mar me lta bu'i rgyun yang
NK114(ye)001:12817: yang bskyangs te tshul bzhin ma yin par rtog pa'i
NK114(ye)001:12818: mun pa rang rgyud la thog med nas zhugs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:12819: gnyen por 'gro ba'i thabs la 'bad par bya zhing
NK114(ye)001:12820: nges shes nyams par gyur na slar yang dpyad pas
NK114(ye)001:12821: drangs te rgyun mthud par bya la /
NK114(ye)001:12822: nges shes de nyid rtag tu brtan par gyur pa'i
NK114(ye)001:12823: tshe na ni dpyad pa dor nas de'i ngang bskyang
NK114(ye)001:12824: bar gsungs shing / de yang las dang po pa'i
NK114(ye)001:12825: dus su bdag med pa'i 'dzin stangs dang bcas pas
NK114(ye)001:12826: bsgom zhing des drangs nas nges shes mchog tu 'drongs
NK114(ye)001:12827: pa'i tshe na med 'dzin mi dgos shing /
NK114(ye)001:12828: mthar ni sgro 'dogs thams cad dang bral ba'i spros bral stong pa chen po bsgom par bshad do //
NK114(ye)001:12829: gnyis pa khyad par gyi chos gzhan bstan pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:12831: de yang rang gi mtshan nyid dang /
NK114(ye)001:12833: rang rig khas mi len pa'i khyad par /
NK114(ye)001:12834: bden 'dzin nyon sgrib tu 'dod pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:12835: bdag med gnyis la phra rags mi 'byed pa'i khyad par /
NK114(ye)001:12837: nyan rang 'phags pas chos kyi bdag med rtogs pas khyab par khas len pa'i khyad par /
NK114(ye)001:12838: so skye'i shes pa 'khrul shes dang /
NK114(ye)001:12839: dpyad shes tshad mar 'dod pa'i khyad par /
NK114(ye)001:12840: yid mngon dang rtog pa'i gzhi mthun 'dod cing /
NK114(ye)001:12841: phra ba'i mi rtag pa mngon sum du rtogs pa'i so skye yod pa'i khyad par /
NK114(ye)001:12842: dus gsum dngos por 'dod cing rags pa'i mi rtag
NK114(ye)001:12843: sogs bcu drug rtogs pa tsam gyis theg pa gsum
NK114(ye)001:12844: gang rung gi sbyor lam tsam du yang bgrod par
NK114(ye)001:12845: mi nus par thal 'gyur 'phen pa'i khyad par yod
NK114(ye)001:12846: pa'o // zhes 'dug pa 'di dag gi don cung zad 'grol bar byed pa la /
NK114(ye)001:12847: spyir rang nyid thos rgya dman zhing shes rab rtul ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:12848: khyad par thal 'gyur ba'i gzhung rnams la rgyus chung ba'i phyir ji bzhin pa mi shes mod /
NK114(ye)001:12849: 'on kyang dpyad gzhi tsam du bri bar byed na
NK114(ye)001:12850: khyad par 'di dag dngos smra ba thams cad dang
NK114(ye)001:12851: / rang rgyud pa las kyang khyad par gyi chos su gsungs pa ltar snang bas de ltar na /
NK114(ye)001:12852: thal rang gi shing rta chen po rnams mthar thug gi don la dgongs pa dbyer med na'ang /
NK114(ye)001:12853: gnas skabs chos thams cad bden med du gtan la
NK114(ye)001:12854: dbab tshul gyis gnyis su gyes te thal 'gyur ba
NK114(ye)001:12855: rnams kyis khas len kun bral rnam grangs min pa'i
NK114(ye)001:12856: don dam 'ba' zhig gtan la 'bebs shing /
NK114(ye)001:12857: tha snyad kyi khas len thams cad ma brtags 'jig
NK114(ye)001:12858: rten pa dang thun mong du mdzad kyi dpyad nas
NK114(ye)001:12859: smra ba rang rgyud pa sogs kyi bzhed pa ltar
NK114(ye)001:12860: mi mdzad la / rang rgyud pas ni khas len
NK114(ye)001:12861: dang bcas pa rnam grangs pa'i don dam rtsal du
NK114(ye)001:12862: bton nas 'chad tshul gyi dbang gis rang rgyud kyi
NK114(ye)001:12863: gtan tshigs la gtso bor mdzad cing dpyad nas tha
NK114(ye)001:12864: snyad tshad grub bzhed pa la sogs yin par gsungs
NK114(ye)001:12865: mi mdzad la / pas / thog mar rang gi mtshan nyid dang /
NK114(ye)001:12866: rang rgyud khas mi len pa'i don /
NK114(ye)001:12867: rang rgyud pas tha snyad du skye ba zhes pa
NK114(ye)001:12868: rang gi ngo bo nyid dam rang gi mtshan nyid
NK114(ye)001:12869: kyis grub pa de ni don dam dpyod pas dpyad
NK114(ye)001:12870: kyang ma bkag par khas len pas de 'dra ba'i
NK114(ye)001:12871: dngos po de la tha snyad du rang gi skad
NK114(ye)001:12872: cig ma'i rgyud kyang yod par 'dod pa la /
NK114(ye)001:12874: bden pa gnyis char ma skyes par gsungs te /
NK114(ye)001:12876: de nyid skabs su rigs pa gang zhig gis //
NK114(ye)001:12877: bdag dang gzhan las skye ba rigs min pa //
NK114(ye)001:12878: rigs des tha snyad du yang rigs min pas //
NK114(ye)001:12879: khyod kyi skye ba gang gis yin par 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:12881: de'i phyir rang gi mtshan nyid kyi skye ba ni
NK114(ye)001:12882: bden pa gnyis char du yang yod pa ma yin
NK114(ye)001:12884: rang rig khas mi len zhes pa don dam du rang rig mi 'dod pa lta ci smos kyang /
NK114(ye)001:12885: tha snyad du dngos po rang mtshan du grub par
NK114(ye)001:12886: yang 'dod cing rang rig kyang 'dod na rig bya
NK114(ye)001:12887: rig byed du yod dgos pas de 'dra ba'ang khas
NK114(ye)001:12888: mi len to // 'on kyang dbu ma'i gzhung rigs
NK114(ye)001:12889: tshogs sogs na rang rig gi zhal bzhes dngos su
NK114(ye)001:12890: med pa tsam zhig gis tha snyad du med nges
NK114(ye)001:12892: dper na thal 'gyur ba'i lugs la gnyug ma'i sems dang /
NK114(ye)001:12893: bde chen ye shes sogs kyi tha snyad sbyar don
NK114(ye)001:12894: med pas ma gsungs kyang de dag tha snyad du
NK114(ye)001:12895: med pa ma yin pa bzhin no //
NK114(ye)001:12896: de dang mi 'dra ste rang rig ni ched du bkag pas tha snyad du med do snyam na /
NK114(ye)001:12897: ched du bkag pa thams cad tha snyad du gtan
NK114(ye)001:12898: nas med dgos na gzhan rigs sogs tha snyad thams
NK114(ye)001:12900: tha snyad kyi rnam bzhag rnams ni 'jig rten pa'i
NK114(ye)001:12901: rjes su 'brang ba'i phyi rgyun chad par mi 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:12902: ro zhe na / de tsam du rang rig kyang brjod rung ste /
NK114(ye)001:12903: 'jig rten pa rnams kyis rang blo rang la lkog tu ma gyur bar 'dod pas so //
NK114(ye)001:12904: des na tha snyad du med nges yin na tha
NK114(ye)001:12905: snyad pa'i rig shes kyis dngos su gnod pa rtag
NK114(ye)001:12906: pa'i sgra dang / byed po dbang phyug dang gtso
NK114(ye)001:12907: bo la sogs pa lta bu yin dgos pa la
NK114(ye)001:12908: 'di la ni de 'dra ba'i tha snyad tshad mas
NK114(ye)001:12909: dngos su gnod pa med do //
NK114(ye)001:12910: 'jig rten pa'i tha snyad kyi dbang du'ang rang rig
NK114(ye)001:12911: pa'i rgyu can gyi dran pa mi srid pa zhes
NK114(ye)001:12913: rang rig pa ni grub la rags mod kyi //
NK114(ye)001:12914: de lta'ang dran pas dran pa rig min te //
NK114(ye)001:12915: gzhan phyir ma shes rgyud la skyes pa bzhin //
NK114(ye)001:12916: zhes gsungs pa ltar snga phyi'i shes pa rang mtshan
NK114(ye)001:12917: gyis grub pa'i so so ba la sngar rang gis
NK114(ye)001:12918: rang myong du chug kyang da lta dran mi srid
NK114(ye)001:12920: gal te 'di snyam du rang rig tha snyad du
NK114(ye)001:12921: yod na bya byed las gsum rang ngos nas grub
NK114(ye)001:12922: par thal te / dper na rig bya sngon po /
NK114(ye)001:12923: rig byed sngo 'dzin gyis rig pa'i bya ba dang bcas nas rig pa bzhin dgos so zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:12924: de yang tha snyad btags pa tsam las don la ma grub ste /
NK114(ye)001:12925: sngon po dang sngo 'dzin gnyis phrad ma phrad dang /
NK114(ye)001:12926: snga phyi sogs brtags na gang ltar yang ma grub pas so //
NK114(ye)001:12927: 'on kyang tha snyad du rig bya rig byed sogs kyi tha snyad nye bar gdags rung ba bzhin /
NK114(ye)001:12928: bde sdug myong ba lta bu la'ang brtags na bya
NK114(ye)001:12929: byed sogs mi grub kyang tha snyad tsam du myong
NK114(ye)001:12930: bya bde sdug sogs myong byed shes pas gsal bar
NK114(ye)001:12931: nyams su myong ngo zhes pa tsam gyi tha snyad
NK114(ye)001:12932: sbyar ba la ni gnod pa gang yang med par
NK114(ye)001:12933: ma zad ches shin tu 'thad pa dang bcas pa
NK114(ye)001:12935: gang phyir gang gis yul myong gyur de las //
NK114(ye)001:12936: dran pa 'di gzhan nga la yod min pa //
NK114(ye)001:12937: de phyir nga yis mthong snyam dran 'gyur te //
NK114(ye)001:12938: 'di yang 'jig rten tha snyad tshul lugs yin //
NK114(ye)001:12940: gang nyams su myong ba'i myong bde dran pa'i shes
NK114(ye)001:12941: pas myong ba ma yin pa ma yin pas dran
NK114(ye)001:12942: pa yul dang ldan par 'byung la /
NK114(ye)001:12943: nyams su myong ba'i shes pas yongs su gcod pa
NK114(ye)001:12944: gang yin pa de dran pas yongs su ma bcad
NK114(ye)001:12945: pa ma yin pas zhes rang 'grel las gsungs so
NK114(ye)001:12946: // chos kyi grags pa'i zhal nas kyang //
NK114(ye)001:12947: blo yis nyams myong bya gzhan med //
NK114(ye)001:12948: de yis myong ba'ang gzhan yod min //
NK114(ye)001:12949: gzung dang 'dzin pa gnyis med phyir //
NK114(ye)001:12950: de ni de ltar rang nyid gsal //
NK114(ye)001:12953: rnam shes bem po'i rang bzhin las //
NK114(ye)001:12954: ldog pa rab tu skye ba ste //
NK114(ye)001:12955: bem min rang bzhin gang yin pa //
NK114(ye)001:12956: de 'di bdag nyid shes pa yin //
NK114(ye)001:12957: gcig pa cha med rang bzhin la //
NK114(ye)001:12958: gsum gyi rang bzhin mi 'thad phyir //
NK114(ye)001:12959: de yis rang gis rig pa na //
NK114(ye)001:12960: bya dang byed pa'i dngos por min //
NK114(ye)001:12961: zhes gzung 'dzin tha mi dad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:12962: bya byed kyi rdzas tha dad med pa'i rang gsal tsam la bshad pas 'gal bar mi sems so //
NK114(ye)001:12963: yang gal te spyod 'jug shes rab le'ura /
NK114(ye)001:12964: rang rig med kyang rnam shes dran pa'i dper //
NK114(ye)001:12965: gzhan myong ba dang 'brel ba las //
NK114(ye)001:12966: dran 'gyur byi ba'i dug bzhin no //
NK114(ye)001:12968: sngar dug ma myong yang phyis dran pa bkod pas
NK114(ye)001:12969: tha snyad du med pa'i don ma yin nam snyam
NK114(ye)001:12970: na / dpe bkod tshul la de ltar snang yang /
NK114(ye)001:12971: gzhan myong ba dang 'brel zhes pas /
NK114(ye)001:12972: gzhan yul sngon po lta bu myong ba na sngo
NK114(ye)001:12973: 'dzin gyi shes pa rang la skyes pa rang gis
NK114(ye)001:12974: myong ba'i stobs kyis phyis de gnyis mnyam du dran
NK114(ye)001:12975: rigs kyi / sngar sngo 'dzin rang la yod pa
NK114(ye)001:12976: rang gis gtan ma myong na phyis yul de mthong
NK114(ye)001:12977: yang de'i shes pa dran mi srid de sngar gang
NK114(ye)001:12978: zag gzhan gyis mthong ba'i yul bzhin no //
NK114(ye)001:12979: des na rang rig rdzas su med kyang tha snyad
NK114(ye)001:12980: du yul dang yul can 'brel ba dang bcas pa'i
NK114(ye)001:12981: stobs kyis dran pa tsam yin la /
NK114(ye)001:12982: dper na myong dran gnyis tha snyad du'ang ma grub ces pa'i don to //
NK114(ye)001:12983: ral gri'i dpe sogs kyang rnam pa thams cad du
NK114(ye)001:12984: mtshungs mi dgos te bum sogs skye ba med pa'i
NK114(ye)001:12985: dper mo gsham gyi bu sogs bkod pa bzhin no
NK114(ye)001:12986: // bden 'dzin nyon sgrib tu 'dod ces pa'i don /
NK114(ye)001:12987: spyir chos dang gang zag gnyis ka la bden par
NK114(ye)001:12988: grub pa can du 'dzin pa'i ma rig pa las
NK114(ye)001:12989: chags sogs nyon mongs 'byung zhing nyon mongs pa de
NK114(ye)001:12990: dag gti mug gi ngo bor gnas pa yin pas
NK114(ye)001:12993: lus la lus dbang ji bzhin du //
NK114(ye)001:12994: gti mug kun la gnas gyur te //
NK114(ye)001:12995: de phyir nyon mongs thams cad kyang //
NK114(ye)001:12996: gti mug bcom pas bcom par 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:12998: 'dir dngos po rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba rnams
NK114(ye)001:12999: ni rang bzhin gyis rnam par dben pa nyid kyi
NK114(ye)001:13001: gti mug ni de rnams la ji ltar bden par rtogs pa las rmongs pa nyid kyi phyir /
NK114(ye)001:13002: dngos po bden pa'i rang gi ngo bor lhag par sgro 'dogs par rab tu 'jug go //
NK114(ye)001:13003: 'dod chags la sogs pa dag kyang gti mug gis
NK114(ye)001:13004: kun tu brtags pa'i dngos po'i rang bzhin kho na
NK114(ye)001:13006: mi sdug pa la sogs pa'i khyad par sgro 'dogs par 'jug pa nyid kyi phyir /
NK114(ye)001:13007: gti mug las tha mi dad par 'jug par 'gyur zhing /
NK114(ye)001:13008: gti mug la brten par yang 'gyur te gti mug gtso bo nyid kyi phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:13010: des na rang rgyud pas gang zag rang rkya thub
NK114(ye)001:13011: pa'i rdzas yod du 'dzin pa gang zag gi bdag
NK114(ye)001:13012: 'dzin yin la / des drangs pa'i chags sogs nyon sgrib dang /
NK114(ye)001:13013: phung sogs la bden par 'dzin pa shes sgrib tu 'dod pa dang mi 'dra ba'i khyad par ro //
NK114(ye)001:13014: 'o na shes sgrib gang la ngos 'dzin zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:13016: 'khor gsum rnam par rtog pa gang //
NK114(ye)001:13017: de ni shes bya'i sgrib par 'dod //
NK114(ye)001:13018: ces pa ltar ser sna la sogs pa'i nyon mongs
NK114(ye)001:13019: pa'i rtsa ba dang ngo bor gyur ba'i bden 'dzin
NK114(ye)001:13020: las gzhan pa'i 'khor gsum mam blang dor la zhen
NK114(ye)001:13021: pa'i rnam par rtog pa tsam zhig la bya ste
NK114(ye)001:13022: / sher phyin du gzung rtog dang 'dzin rtog gi
NK114(ye)001:13023: rnam grangs du ma bshad pa yang 'di dang don
NK114(ye)001:13024: / gcig la / de'i rags pa ni mthong spang dang /
NK114(ye)001:13025: phra ba ni sgom spang ngo //
NK114(ye)001:13030: byang chub sems dpa' nyon mongs pa can gyi ma rig pa'i gzigs pa spangs pa /
NK114(ye)001:13031: 'du byed gzugs brnyan la sogs pa'i yod pa nyid
NK114(ye)001:13032: dang 'dra bar gzigs pa rnams la ni bcos ma'i
NK114(ye)001:13033: rang bzhin yin gyi bden par ni ma yin te
NK114(ye)001:13034: bden par mngon par rlom pa med pa'i phyir ro
NK114(ye)001:13035: // byis pa rnams la ni slu bar byed pa yin la /
NK114(ye)001:13036: de las gzhan pa rnams la ni sgyu ma la
NK114(ye)001:13037: sogs pa ltar rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba nyid
NK114(ye)001:13038: kyis kun rdzob tsam du 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:13039: de yang shes bya'i sgrib pa'i mtshan nyid can ma
NK114(ye)001:13040: rig pa tsam kun tu spyod pa'i phyir snang ba
NK114(ye)001:13041: dang bcas pa'i spyod yul can gyi 'phags pa rnams
NK114(ye)001:13042: la snang gi / snang ba med pa'i spyod yul can mnga' ba rnams la ni ma yin no //
NK114(ye)001:13044: ye shes snang ba rgyan gyi mdor /
NK114(ye)001:13045: dag byed gnyen po la zhen pa shes sgrib tu gsungs pa'ang 'di dang tshul mthun no //
NK114(ye)001:13046: bdag med gnyis la phra rags mi 'byed ces pa'i don /
NK114(ye)001:13047: spyir bdag med phra rags kyi 'jog tshul la /
NK114(ye)001:13048: gang zag rtag gcig rang dbang can du grub pas
NK114(ye)001:13049: stong pa gang zag gi bdag med rags pa dang
NK114(ye)001:13050: / gang zag rang rkya thub pa'i rdzas yod kyis
NK114(ye)001:13051: stong pa gang zag gi bdag med phra mor 'jog
NK114(ye)001:13052: pa tsam la rang rgyud pa man chad kyi rang
NK114(ye)001:13053: / sde rnams 'dra / 'on kyang gnas ma bu
NK114(ye)001:13054: pa sogs kyis de 'dra'i gang zag gi bdag med
NK114(ye)001:13056: bye mdo gnyis kyis chos kyi bdag med khas mi len pas bdag med phra mo dang /
NK114(ye)001:13057: gang zag gi bdag med phra mo don gcig tu 'dod /
NK114(ye)001:13058: sems tsam pas rdul phran cha med bsags pa'i phyi
NK114(ye)001:13059: rol don gyis stong pa chos kyi bdag med rags
NK114(ye)001:13060: pa dang / gzugs dang gzugs 'dzin tshad ma rdzas
NK114(ye)001:13061: gzhan gyis stong pa lta bu chos kyi bdag med
NK114(ye)001:13062: pa dang / phra mor 'dod / rnal 'byor spyod
NK114(ye)001:13063: pa'i dbu ma rang rgyud pas gzung 'dzin rdzas gzhan
NK114(ye)001:13064: gyis stong pa lta bu chos kyi bdag med rags
NK114(ye)001:13065: pa dang / phra mor 'dod / pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:13066: chos rnams bden grub kyis stong pa chos kyi bdag
NK114(ye)001:13068: mdo sde spyod pa'i dbu ma rang rgyud pas phyi don bzhed pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:13069: gzugs dang gzugs 'dzin tshad ma rdzas gzhan gyis stong pa sogs mi 'jog cing /
NK114(ye)001:13070: chos kyi bdag med rags pa 'jog tshul sems tsam pa dang 'dra la /
NK114(ye)001:13071: chos kyi bdag med phra mo 'jog tshul rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu ma dang 'dra'o //
NK114(ye)001:13072: de rnams la gang zag gi bdag med phra mo
NK114(ye)001:13073: stong nyid du 'dod mi 'dod kyi khyad par yod
NK114(ye)001:13075: gang zag rang rkya thub pa'i rdzas yod kyis stong pa gang zag gi bdag med rags pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:13076: gang zag rang bzhin gyis grub pas stong pa gang zag gi bdag med phra mo dang /
NK114(ye)001:13077: rdul phran cha med bsags pa'i rags pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:13078: de 'dzin pa'i tshad ma rdzas gzhan gyis stong pa chos kyi bdag med rags pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:13079: gang zag gi gdags gzhi sogs phung po rang gi
NK114(ye)001:13080: mtshan nyid kyis grub pas stong pa chos kyi bdag
NK114(ye)001:13081: med phra mor 'jog pa yin pas /
NK114(ye)001:13082: bdag 'dzin gnyis ka'ang dmigs yul gyi sgo nas 'byed kyi /
NK114(ye)001:13083: 'dzin stangs kyi sgo nas min te /
NK114(ye)001:13084: gang zag la dmigs nas rang bzhin gyis grub par 'dzin pa gang zag gi dang /
NK114(ye)001:13085: gang zag gzhan la bden grub tu 'dzin pa gang
NK114(ye)001:13086: zag gi bdag 'dzin yin kyang 'jig lta lhan skyes
NK114(ye)001:13087: min zhes rje rin po che gsungs /
NK114(ye)001:13088: chos la dmigs nas rang bzhin gyis grub par 'dzin pa chos kyi bdag 'dzin du bzhed do //
NK114(ye)001:13089: de'i phyir bdag med gnyis kyang stong gzhi'i sgo nas 'byed kyi dgag bya'i sgo nas mi 'byed de /
NK114(ye)001:13090: gang zag rang bzhin gyis grub pas stong pa gang zag gi dang /
NK114(ye)001:13091: chos rang bzhin gyis grub pas stong pa chos kyi
NK114(ye)001:13092: bdag med du 'jog pa'i phyir stong gzhi'i khyad tsam
NK114(ye)001:13093: las dgag bya la phra rags med pas bdag med
NK114(ye)001:13094: gnyis la phra rags mi 'byed pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:13095: 'gog bden don dam pa zhes pa'i don 'du byed
NK114(ye)001:13096: thams cad gdod ma nas zhi zhing rang bzhin spros
NK114(ye)001:13097: pa dang bral ba'i 'gog pa'i bden pa ni chos
NK114(ye)001:13098: kyi dbyings dang / don dam pa'i bden pa yang yin te /
NK114(ye)001:13100: chos kyi dbyings la ma gtogs pa'i //
NK114(ye)001:13101: chos 'ga' yod pa ma yin no //
NK114(ye)001:13103: byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod las /
NK114(ye)001:13104: gzhan yang bden pa ni gcig pu gnyis ma yin pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:13108: don dam par skye ba med pas bdag dang gzhan las skyes ba dgag pa la rag mod /
NK114(ye)001:13109: gzugs dang tshor ba la sogs pa gang dag mngon
NK114(ye)001:13110: sum dang rjes su dpag pa dag gis dmigs pa
NK114(ye)001:13111: de dag gi rang bzhin ni gdon mi za bar
NK114(ye)001:13113: ci ste de ltar mi 'dod na ni bden pa gnyis zhes ci ste brjod de /
NK114(ye)001:13114: bden pa gcig kho nar 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:13115: ci'i phyir na gzhan las skye ba med pa nyid do //
NK114(ye)001:13118: don dam bar na bden pa gnyis yod pa ma yin te /
NK114(ye)001:13119: dge slong dag bden pa dam pa 'di ni gcig ste /
NK114(ye)001:13120: 'di lta ste mi bslu ba'i chos mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:13121: 'du byed thams cad ni brdzun pa bslu ba'i chos can no zhes 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:13123: 'di ni 'og ma rnams kyis bden gnyis tha dad du 'dzin pa las khyad par du gyur pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:13124: nyan rang 'phags pa chos kyi bdag med rtogs pas
NK114(ye)001:13125: khyab par khas len pa'i khyad par zhes pa'i don
NK114(ye)001:13126: ni / rang rgyud pa man chad kyis gang zag
NK114(ye)001:13127: gi bdag med tsam las ma rtogs par 'dod la
NK114(ye)001:13128: ni / / de'i rgyu mtshan yang gang zag rang
NK114(ye)001:13129: rkya thub pa'i rdzas yod kyi bdag med par rtogs
NK114(ye)001:13130: na gang zag gi bdag med phra ba rtogs pa
NK114(ye)001:13131: yin pas de tsam rtogs pa la phung por bden
NK114(ye)001:13132: bar 'dzin pa ldog mi dgos par bdag 'dzin des
NK114(ye)001:13133: drangs pa'i nyon mongs pa thams cad zad pa'i dgra
NK114(ye)001:13134: bcom pa thob pa yod par 'dod la /
NK114(ye)001:13135: thal 'gyur ba'i lugs la de gang zag gi bdag
NK114(ye)001:13136: med rags pa tsam las phra ba yin par mi
NK114(ye)001:13137: bzhed pas na gang zag ngo bo nyid kyis grub
NK114(ye)001:13138: pas stong pa gang zag gi bdag med phra ba
NK114(ye)001:13139: rtogs pa la / ji skad du nyan thos la bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:13140: gzugs ni dbu ba rdos pa 'dra //
NK114(ye)001:13141: tshor ba chu yi chu bur bzhin //
NK114(ye)001:13142: 'du shes smig rgyu lta bu ste //
NK114(ye)001:13143: 'du byed rnams ni chu shing bzhin //
NK114(ye)001:13144: rnam shes sgyu ma lta bu zhes //
NK114(ye)001:13145: nyi ma'i gnyen gyis bka' stsal to //
NK114(ye)001:13148: ji srid phung por 'dzin yod pa //
NK114(ye)001:13149: de srid de la ngar 'dzin yod //
NK114(ye)001:13150: ngar 'dzin yod na yang las te //
NK114(ye)001:13151: de las kyang ni skye bar 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:13153: phung po rags pa la ril po gcig 'dzin gyi
NK114(ye)001:13154: blo yod pa de srid du ngar 'dzin rgyun mi
NK114(ye)001:13155: 'chad pas / de 'dra ba'i 'dzin pa nges par ldog dgos shing /
NK114(ye)001:13156: des na 'du byed thams cad mi rtag pa du
NK114(ye)001:13157: ma sil bu'i rnam par mngon sum du mthong ba'i
NK114(ye)001:13158: dgra bcom pa rnams la rang rgyud kyi phung por
NK114(ye)001:13159: snang ba yang char dang 'bab chu bzhin du du
NK114(ye)001:13160: ma tshogs pa skad cig kyang mi rtag par g.yo
NK114(ye)001:13161: zhing 'gyur ba 'gul ba rdeg pa'i rnam pa can
NK114(ye)001:13162: du gzigs par gsungs pas de ltar gzigs pa'i tshe
NK114(ye)001:13163: gang zag tu gdags pa'i gzhi'i phung po yang ril
NK114(ye)001:13164: po gcig pu dang rtag pa ni du ma tshogs
NK114(ye)001:13165: pa dang skad cig ma'i rgyun la brten nas btags
NK114(ye)001:13166: pa tsam las ngo bos ma grub pa'i stong pa'i
NK114(ye)001:13167: rang bzhin khong du chud cing de'i stobs kyis nga
NK114(ye)001:13168: zhes gcig tu 'dzin pa'ang nor ba'i blo yin par
NK114(ye)001:13169: shes te / tshogs pa dang rgyun de tsam la
NK114(ye)001:13170: brten nas btags tsam las rang gi rang bzhin gyis
NK114(ye)001:13171: grub pa med pa'i tshul shes pas stong nyid rtogs
NK114(ye)001:13172: zhes pa'i tha snyad kyang btags la /
NK114(ye)001:13173: gang zag ni chos tsam gyi bye brag yin pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:13174: phung po'i chos kyi rags pa rang bzhin med par
NK114(ye)001:13175: rtogs pa'i phyir chos kyi bdag med kyang rtogs par
NK114(ye)001:13177: de ltar rtogs pa'i dgra bcom de'i phung po lnga
NK114(ye)001:13178: ga skad cig gis skye zhing 'gag la sil bu
NK114(ye)001:13179: pa 'dus pa snying po med pa dbu ba rdos
NK114(ye)001:13180: pa la sogs pa'i tshul du dngos su rtogs par
NK114(ye)001:13182: nyan thos pa de dag kyang dbang po'i rno rtul gyi khyad kyis rtogs pa bzang ngan yod de /
NK114(ye)001:13183: rtul pos phung po skad cig ma'i rang bzhin du
NK114(ye)001:13184: mthong bas nga dang nga yi ba'i 'dzin pa ldog
NK114(ye)001:13185: pa tsam las rang rgyud kyi phung po thams cad
NK114(ye)001:13186: gzhi med par shes pa'i stong nyid ma rtogs la
NK114(ye)001:13187: / rnon pos rten 'brel tsam du shes kyang rmi
NK114(ye)001:13188: lam gyi bde sdug tsam la'ang skrag nas zhi bar
NK114(ye)001:13189: mos pa yin par kun mkhyen gyis gsungs so //
NK114(ye)001:13190: de lta na'ang theg chen pa ltar phyi nang gi
NK114(ye)001:13191: chos thams cad gzhi rtsa dang bral ba'i nam mkha'
NK114(ye)001:13192: lta bu'i stong nyid kyi don rtogs pa ni med
NK114(ye)001:13193: de / dri ma med pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:13194: stong pa nyid la mos pa'i nyon mongs can nyid bla'i /
NK114(ye)001:13195: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas dmigs pa dang bcas
NK114(ye)001:13196: pa'i nyon mongs pa med pa ni de lta ma
NK114(ye)001:13197: yin no // de dag gi 'dus ma byas mngon
NK114(ye)001:13198: sum du byas nas dmigs pa dang bcas pa ji
NK114(ye)001:13199: yin no // ltar lags / bka' stsal pa /
NK114(ye)001:13200: de'i 'dus ma byas ni rgya mtsho las skra'i rtse mos blang ba ltar shin tu chung ngo //
NK114(ye)001:13202: tshangs pa khyad par sems kyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:13204: nyan thos sgra'i rjes su 'brang bar rang gi rgyud
NK114(ye)001:13205: snang ba nyi tshe ba'i ye shes kyis rnam par
NK114(ye)001:13206: grol ba'i shes rab de'i bdag shes rab can gyi
NK114(ye)001:13209: 'od srung gis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:13210: de dag gis rtogs pa'i stong nyid ni yungs 'bru
NK114(ye)001:13211: srin gyis zos pa'i nang gi nam mkha' ltar chung
NK114(ye)001:13214: bdag med 'di ni 'gro ba rnams dgrol phyir //
NK114(ye)001:13215: chos dang gang zag dbye bas rnam gnyis gsungs //
NK114(ye)001:13216: zhes pa'i thad kyi 'jug par rang 'grel las /
NK114(ye)001:13217: de la gang zag gis bdag med ni /
NK114(ye)001:13219: nyan thos rnams rnam pa rang grol ba'i phyir bstan la /
NK114(ye)001:13220: byang chub sems dpa' rnams rnam pa thams cad mkhyen
NK114(ye)001:13221: pa nyid thob pa'i rnam dgrol gyi phyir gnyis ka
NK114(ye)001:13222: bstan to // nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas rnams
NK114(ye)001:13223: kyis kyang rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba rkyen nyid
NK114(ye)001:13225: de lta na yang de dag la chos kyi bdag med yongs su rdzogs pa bsgom pa med do //
NK114(ye)001:13226: khams gsum na spyod pa'i nyon mongs pa spong ba'i thabs tsam zhig ni yod do //
NK114(ye)001:13227: de dag la gang zag gi bdag med pa ma
NK114(ye)001:13228: lus par bsgom pa ni yod par rnam par bzhag
NK114(ye)001:13230: spros dang bcas par stong pa nyid //
NK114(ye)001:13231: bcu drug bshad nas mdor bsdus te //
NK114(ye)001:13232: slar yang bzhir bshad de dag ni //
NK114(ye)001:13233: theg chen du yang bzhed pa yin //
NK114(ye)001:13235: 'o na dbu ma thal 'gyur ba'i lugs la'ang nyan
NK114(ye)001:13236: rang rnams kyis phung po skad cig mar mthong ba
NK114(ye)001:13237: de tsam las chos kyi bdag med rtogs pa'i tshul
NK114(ye)001:13239: legs ldan 'byed kyis de ltar bshad pa zla bas sun byung ba dang 'gal lo //
NK114(ye)001:13240: de yang 'di ltar tshig gsal las /
NK114(ye)001:13241: slob dpon legs ldan 'byed ni nyan thos dang rang
NK114(ye)001:13242: sangs rgyas rnams la ji skad bshad pa'i stong pa
NK114(ye)001:13243: nyid rtogs pa yod par khong du ma chud nas
NK114(ye)001:13244: / ji skad du 'phags pa nyan thos 'du byed
NK114(ye)001:13245: kyi tshogs gzhan dang gzhan skye ba'i skad cig ma
NK114(ye)001:13246: re re la 'jig pa'i ngang can bdag dang bdag
NK114(ye)001:13247: gi ba med pa la nges par lta ba la
NK114(ye)001:13248: / yang / bdag ces bya ba'i dngos po med
NK114(ye)001:13249: pa'i phyir skye ba dang 'jig pa 'di dag ni
NK114(ye)001:13250: chos tsam du zad do zhes bya bar lta ba
NK114(ye)001:13251: / yang / skye ste / 'di ltar bdag ni
NK114(ye)001:13252: ngar 'dzin pa'i yul yin pas de med na de
NK114(ye)001:13254: de med pa kho na'i phyir 'ga' la yang nang
NK114(ye)001:13255: dang phyi rol gyi dngos po med pas nga yir
NK114(ye)001:13257: tha snyad kyi brdar byas pa ma gtogs par /
NK114(ye)001:13258: nga la ni ngar 'dzin pa med cing /
NK114(ye)001:13259: nga yir 'dzin pa med do zhes bya bar rang
NK114(ye)001:13260: gi ngo bo nges pa skye bar mi 'gyur na
NK114(ye)001:13261: / byang chub sems dpa' chen po 'du byed skye
NK114(ye)001:13262: ba med par lta ba rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK114(ye)001:13263: shes rab kyi spyod yul la gnas pa rnams la
NK114(ye)001:13264: lta smos kyang ci dgos pas de'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:13265: nga dang nga yir 'dzin pa med gang /
NK114(ye)001:13266: de yang yod pa ma yin te //
NK114(ye)001:13269: slob dpon 'di ji ltar rnam pa de lta bu'i
NK114(ye)001:13270: yul la slob dpon gyi lugs kyi rjes su 'jug
NK114(ye)001:13271: pa ma yin pa de ltar ni /
NK114(ye)001:13273: ring du song bar blo yang lhag par 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:13274: zhes bya ba der bstan zin pas yang de sun dbyung ba la 'bad par mi bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:13275: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:13277: slob dpon legs ldan 'byed ni nyan rang gis phung
NK114(ye)001:13278: po skad cig mar rtogs pas gang zag ril po
NK114(ye)001:13279: gcig 'dzin gyi blo ldog par 'gyur ba yin kyang
NK114(ye)001:13280: / skye 'jig can gyi phung po la chos tsam
NK114(ye)001:13281: du lta ba ni da dung mi ldog pas de
NK114(ye)001:13282: bdag med par mi rtogs par bshad la /
NK114(ye)001:13283: lugs 'dir ni de ltar phung po skad cig mar
NK114(ye)001:13284: rtogs pas phung po zhes gcig pur zhen pa'i yul
NK114(ye)001:13285: de yang skad cig ma'i rgyun la brten nas btags
NK114(ye)001:13286: par zad kyi rang gi ngo bos ma grub par
NK114(ye)001:13287: shes pas gang zag tu gdags pa'i gzhi brten nas
NK114(ye)001:13288: rtag pa'i stong pa nyid du rtogs pa na phung
NK114(ye)001:13289: po rang la ril po gcig 'dzin gyi blo las
NK114(ye)001:13290: ldog pas chos kyi bdag med rtogs so //
NK114(ye)001:13291: zhes bzhed pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:13292: 'di la mkhas mchog 'ga' zhig thal 'gyur ba'i lugs
NK114(ye)001:13293: la gdags gzhi btags chos zhes pa mi 'thad de
NK114(ye)001:13294: / gang zag tu gdags pa'i rgyu zhes bshad pa'i phyir zhes gsungs kyang brjod tshul tsam mo //
NK114(ye)001:13295: nyan rang gnyis kyi rtogs pa'i khyad par ni /
NK114(ye)001:13296: nyan thos kyis chos kyi bdag med rtogs pa'i gzhi
NK114(ye)001:13297: de rang rgyud kyis bsdus pa'i phung po tsam zhig
NK114(ye)001:13298: yin la / rang sangs rgyas kyis 'dzin pa rang
NK114(ye)001:13299: bzhin med par ma rtogs kyang gzung yul phyi nang
NK114(ye)001:13300: gis bsdus pa thams cad sems kyi bag chags kyi
NK114(ye)001:13301: dbang gis snang ba las don la mi g.yor ltar
NK114(ye)001:13302: ma grub par rtogs pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:13304: gzung don rtog pa spong phyir dang //
NK114(ye)001:13305: 'dzin pa mi spong phyir dang ni //
NK114(ye)001:13306: zhes pa la sogs pa ltar ro //
NK114(ye)001:13307: 'on kyang byang chub sems dpa'i rnams kyi rtogs pa'i khyad par ni sngar bshad pa ltar la /
NK114(ye)001:13311: rdzogs pa gsum gyis nyan thos dang /
NK114(ye)001:13312: rang sangs rgyas rnams las 'phags par gsungs so //
NK114(ye)001:13313: so skye'i shes pa 'khrul shes dang dpyad shes tshad mar 'dod pa'i khyad par /
NK114(ye)001:13314: zhes pa'i don rang rgyud pa sogs kyis mngon sum
NK114(ye)001:13315: rnams so skye'i dus su'ang rang mtshan la tshad mar
NK114(ye)001:13316: 'dod kyang / 'di bas rang mtshan mi bzhed pas /
NK114(ye)001:13317: so skye'i blo thams cad chos nyid las gol ba'i
NK114(ye)001:13318: gzung 'dzin can yin pas 'khrul shes yin pa ni
NK114(ye)001:13319: spyir btang la / bye brag tu de kho na
NK114(ye)001:13320: nyid la dpyod pa'i gcig du bral la sogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:13321: gtan tshigs rnams la brten pa'i dpyad shes rjes dpag
NK114(ye)001:13322: gis chos nyid don spyi'i tshul du gzhal bas don
NK114(ye)001:13323: mi bslu bar rtogs pas tshad ma'o //
NK114(ye)001:13324: yid mngon du rtog pa'i gzhi mthun pa'i ces pa /
NK114(ye)001:13325: spyir tshad ma ltar na mngon sum thams cad la
NK114(ye)001:13326: sgra don 'dres 'dzin gyi rtog pa med pas khyab
NK114(ye)001:13327: par bzhed kyang / 'dir tha snyad 'jig rten par grags pa'i rjes su rnam par bzhag pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:13328: 'jig rten pa rnams kyis mngon sum du mthong ngo //
NK114(ye)001:13330: nyams su myong ngo zhes pa la sogs pa la'ang
NK114(ye)001:13331: mngon sum gyi tha snyad gdags par gsungs pas sgra
NK114(ye)001:13332: don 'dres 'dzin dang bcas pa'i yid kyis dngos su
NK114(ye)001:13333: shes pa lta bu la de gnyis kyi gzhi mthun
NK114(ye)001:13334: yin par rnam par bzhag pa yin nam snyam mo
NK114(ye)001:13335: // phra ba'i mi rtag pa mngon sum rtogs pa'i so skye yod ces pa yang /
NK114(ye)001:13336: sngar bshad pa ltar phung po mi rtag par rtogs
NK114(ye)001:13337: pa las gang zag gi bdag med rtogs par 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:13338: bas bdag med mngon sum du rtogs pa ni 'das
NK114(ye)001:13339: lam kho na la yod kyang /
NK114(ye)001:13340: de'i gzhir gyur pa'i mi rtag pa mngon sum rtogs
NK114(ye)001:13341: pa tsam zhig ni so skye'i dus nas yod dgos
NK114(ye)001:13342: pa'i don yin par sems so //
NK114(ye)001:13343: dus gsum dngos por 'dod ces pa'i dus gsum ni skye 'jig gnas gsum ste /
NK114(ye)001:13344: skye zhing gnas pa zhes pa'i dngos po zhig don
NK114(ye)001:13345: dam par med kyang tha snyad tsam du rang rgyud
NK114(ye)001:13346: pa sogs kyis rang mtshan par 'dod kyang 'jig pa
NK114(ye)001:13347: ni dngos med du 'dod de de'i rgyu mtshan tha
NK114(ye)001:13348: snyad du de gnyis gzhi grub ma grub yod par
NK114(ye)001:13349: rtog nas de ltar rnam bzhag byed la 'dir ni
NK114(ye)001:13351: gang zhig 'jig pa rgyu med nyid du khas blangs
NK114(ye)001:13352: nas 'dus byas rnams skad cig ma nyid du smra
NK114(ye)001:13353: ba de'i ltar na nam mkha'i me tog ltar rgyu
NK114(ye)001:13354: med pas 'jig pa med pa'i phyir dngos po rnams
NK114(ye)001:13356: 'jig pa dang bral ba rnams 'dus byas nyid du'ang 'grub par ga la 'gyur /
NK114(ye)001:13357: de'i phyir des thams cad mi 'grigs pa nyid du 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:13358: skye ba'i rkyen gyis rga shi zhes bya ba dang /
