NK114(ye)001:13359: 'dus byas kyi mtshan nyid rnams kyang 'du byed kyi phung po'i nang du 'du bar gsungs pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:13360: bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jig pa rgyu dang bcas pa
NK114(ye)001:13361: nyid du gsal bar bstan pa ma yin nam zhes
NK114(ye)001:13362: pa la sogs pa ltar dngos po zhes pa'i tha
NK114(ye)001:13363: snyad tsam gdags pa la rang mtshan par grub mi
NK114(ye)001:13364: dgos pa'i gnad kyis de gsum mtshungs par dngos por
NK114(ye)001:13366: de lta na'ang las dang las kyi 'bras bu ni
NK114(ye)001:13367: rten 'brel bslu ba med pa'i dbang gis 'byung ba
NK114(ye)001:13368: tsam las de 'dra ba'i dngos po dang rgyun gyis
NK114(ye)001:13369: bsgrub dgos par ni mi blta'o //
NK114(ye)001:13370: rags pa'i mi rtag pa la sogs bcu drug rtogs
NK114(ye)001:13371: pa tsam gyis theg gsum gang rung gi sbyor lam
NK114(ye)001:13372: tsam du yang bgrod par mi nus zhes pa'i don
NK114(ye)001:13373: / theg gsum gang rung gi sbyor lam thob pa
NK114(ye)001:13374: la lhan skyes kyi bdag med par don spyi'i tshul
NK114(ye)001:13375: du rtogs dgos pas rags pa'i bcu drug gi gtso
NK114(ye)001:13376: bo rtag bdag med par rtogs kyang de mi nus
NK114(ye)001:13377: / pas so // gsum pa 'gog byed gtan tshigs kyis ji ltar dpyad pa'i tshul bstan pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:13378: gtan tshigs chen po bzhi'am lngas chos thams cad rang
NK114(ye)001:13379: bzhin med par gtan la 'bebs par byed pa ste
NK114(ye)001:13381: gzhal tshul spyir bstan pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:13382: gtan tshigs bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:13384: de yang rang rgyud pa ltar kun rdzob tu bden pa bkag nas rdzun par bsgrub pa'am /
NK114(ye)001:13385: don dam la spros pa bkag nas spros bral bsgrub pa ltar ma yin te /
NK114(ye)001:13386: gang du zhen pa de dngos su bkag kyang shugs
NK114(ye)001:13387: la gang yang mi bsgrub pas pha rol gyi log
NK114(ye)001:13389: des na dngos zhen dgag pa la zhen yul sun
NK114(ye)001:13390: phyung dgos pas sngar bshad pa ltar dgag bya bdag
NK114(ye)001:13391: gnyis kyi ngo bo nges par byas te dpyad dgos
NK114(ye)001:13392: kyi gzhan du na 'ben ma mthong bar mda' 'phangs
NK114(ye)001:13393: pa ltar rang rgyud kyi dngos zhen 'gog mi nus
NK114(ye)001:13394: so // da lta rang cag rnams kyis dbu ma'i
NK114(ye)001:13395: gtan tshigs kyis de kho na nyid kyi don tshol
NK114(ye)001:13396: ba na pha rol po'i log rtog ces pa'i tshig
NK114(ye)001:13397: tsam gyis kha phyir bltas su shor te gzhan zhig
NK114(ye)001:13398: gi 'dod pa kho na dang po nas dgag pa
NK114(ye)001:13399: lta bur ma song bar thog ma med pa nas
NK114(ye)001:13400: ma dpyad bzhin du de kho na nyid las phyin
NK114(ye)001:13401: ci log tu gol ba'i lhan skyes kyi rtog pa
NK114(ye)001:13402: so // dang / dpyad pa'i sgo nas sgro btags
NK114(ye)001:13403: pa phyi nang gi grub mtha' 'dzin pa rnams kyi
NK114(ye)001:13404: zhen rtog thams cad rang rgyud la mi gnas pa'i
NK114(ye)001:13405: tshul du drungs nas phyung ste phyi nas bsgom pa'i
NK114(ye)001:13406: tshe na gang la'ang ma zhen pas gang yang mi
NK114(ye)001:13407: bsgom par bzhag kyang blun bsgom thom yor du bzhag
NK114(ye)001:13408: pa tsam ma yin par rang bzhin med rtogs kyi
NK114(ye)001:13409: nges shes kyis drangs pa'i lhag mthong khyad par ba
NK114(ye)001:13410: dang ldan pa'i zhi lhag zung 'jug gi don la
NK114(ye)001:13411: mnyam par 'jog shes shing the tshom med pa ni
NK114(ye)001:13412: dpyad pa gnad du song ba'i lag rjes yin gsungs
NK114(ye)001:13413: so // dang / / de yang spyir deng sang
NK114(ye)001:13414: gi dbu ma'i grub mtha' 'dzin pa'i skyes bu dam
NK114(ye)001:13415: pa rnams kyis 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das
NK114(ye)001:13416: pa'i chos thams cad kyi snang tshul 'di nyid rtog
NK114(ye)001:13417: pas btags tsam las rang gi ngo bos ma grub
NK114(ye)001:13418: so // dang / / pa dang / stong pa'i
NK114(ye)001:13419: rang bzhin rten 'byung du shar bas stong dang rten
NK114(ye)001:13420: 'byung zung 'jug yin no zhes bzhed pa tsam du
NK114(ye)001:13421: so // dang / / pa dang / kun mthun
NK114(ye)001:13422: na'ang / rang lugs la ni rtog btags zhes pa
NK114(ye)001:13423: de yang bden par sgro btags pa la mi bden
NK114(ye)001:13424: pa'i dngos po zhig yod par mi blta ste /
NK114(ye)001:13425: skye ba med pa'i sems kyi rtsal snang stong gzugs 'ba' zhig tu bzhed la /
NK114(ye)001:13426: stong dang rten 'byung dbyer med ces pa'ang stong pa
NK114(ye)001:13427: dang dbyer med rgyu'i snang ba zhig tshad mas grub
NK114(ye)001:13428: par mi blta bar snang ba thams cad gzhi med
NK114(ye)001:13429: rtsa ba dang bral bas grub tshul gang yang med
NK114(ye)001:13430: kyang rten 'byung gi snang ba thams cad 'gog med
NK114(ye)001:13431: du 'char ba 'di tsam du go ba yin no
NK114(ye)001:13432: // des na dgag bya rang bzhin gyis grub pa'i
NK114(ye)001:13433: bdag gnyis ngos 'dzin rgyu de'ang de gnyis bkag pa'i
NK114(ye)001:13434: shul na dgag gzhi gang zag dang chos zhes bya
NK114(ye)001:13435: ba zhig gang yang med de /
NK114(ye)001:13436: gang zag dang chos rang rang la rang rang gis
NK114(ye)001:13437: stong gi de dag gi steng na bden pa'am rang
NK114(ye)001:13438: bzhin gyis grub pas stong zhing /
NK114(ye)001:13439: stong gzhi rang rang gi ngo bos tha snyad du mi stong pa lta bu ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:13440: gzugs ni gzugs kyis stong ngo zhes pa la sogs pa lta bu ste /
NK114(ye)001:13441: des na chos gang yang rang bzhin med pa'i phyir dgag bya rang mtshan pa med kyang /
NK114(ye)001:13442: med pa la yod par sgro btags pa nyid 'dir bkag pa tsam du zad de /
NK114(ye)001:13444: dgag bya ci yang med pas na //
NK114(ye)001:13445: nga ni ci yang mi 'gog go //
NK114(ye)001:13446: de phyir 'gog par byed do zhes //
NK114(ye)001:13447: skur pa de ni khyod kyis btab //
NK114(ye)001:13449: 'o na sngar bdag gnyis bden grub kyis khyad par du byas nas /
NK114(ye)001:13450: gang zag dang chos tsam tha snyad du yod par bshad pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:13451: de ni 'khrul ngor bag chags ma zad pa'i ring
NK114(ye)001:13452: la tha snyad pa'i snang ba rgyun mi 'chad par
NK114(ye)001:13453: 'gog med du 'char ba tsam la bya yi /
NK114(ye)001:13454: rang gi ngo bo zhig yod par bshad pa ni ma yin no //
NK114(ye)001:13455: gnyis pa gtan tshigs bye brag tu bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK114(ye)001:13456: rgyu la dpyod pa rdo rje ga zegs ma /
NK114(ye)001:13457: 'bras bu la dpyod pa yod med skye 'gog /
NK114(ye)001:13458: gnyis ka la dpyod pa mu bzhi skye 'gog /
NK114(ye)001:13459: ngo bo la dpyod pa rten 'brel chen mo dang /
NK114(ye)001:13462: 'di ltar snang bzhin pa thams cad chos can /
NK114(ye)001:13464: bdag dang gzhan dang gnyis ka dang rgyu med las skye ba mi srid pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:13465: de yang 'di ltar rang las skye zhe bya ba mi 'thad de /
NK114(ye)001:13466: bdag las skye ba chos can /
NK114(ye)001:13467: yod dus skye'am med dus skye bar 'dod grang /
NK114(ye)001:13468: dang po ltar na mi 'thad de /
NK114(ye)001:13469: bskyed bya skyed byed tha dad du med pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:13470: yod bzhin skye bas na nam yang mi skye bar mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:13471: skye ba thug pa med par 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:13472: phyi ma ltar na mi 'thad de /
NK114(ye)001:13473: skyed byed rang med na rang gi tha snyad mi thogs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:13474: rgyu med pa las skye ba dang mtshungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:13475: gzhan las skye zhes pa'ang mi 'thad de /
NK114(ye)001:13476: 'di ltar gzhan las skye ba chos can /
NK114(ye)001:13478: bskyed bya rang ma grub na skyed byed gzhan mi 'grub pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:13479: thams cad las thams cad skye bar thal ba'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:13480: gnyis ka las skye zhes pa'ang mi 'thad de /
NK114(ye)001:13481: gzhi gcig la rang yang yin la gzhan yang yin pa ma grub pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:13482: so so'i skye ba bkag pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:13483: rgyu med las skye ba'ang mi 'thad de /
NK114(ye)001:13484: rgyu las 'bras bu 'byung ba mngon sum pa dang 'gal ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:13485: nam mkha' las pad mo skye ba sogs ha cang thal ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:13486: rtsom pa thams cad don med pa nyid du 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:13487: de ltar yang rtsa ba shes rab las /
NK114(ye)001:13488: bdag las ma yin gzhan las min //
NK114(ye)001:13489: gnyis las ma yin rgyu med min //
NK114(ye)001:13490: dngos po gang dag gang na yang //
NK114(ye)001:13491: skye ba nam yang yod ma yin //
NK114(ye)001:13493: gnyis pa 'bras bu la dpyod pa yod med skye 'gog ni /
NK114(ye)001:13494: 'di ltar 'bras bu sna tshogs su snang ba chos can /
NK114(ye)001:13496: 'bras bu'i dngos po yod pa dang med pa gnyis ka skye bas stong pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:13497: de yang 'di ltar 'bras bu yod pa la skye ba med de /
NK114(ye)001:13499: med pa la skye ba med de gzhi ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:13502: med dam yod pa'i don la yang //
NK114(ye)001:13503: rkyen ni rung ba ma yin te //
NK114(ye)001:13504: med na gang gi rkyen du 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:13505: yod na rkyen gyis ci zhig bya //
NK114(ye)001:13507: gsum pa rgyu 'bras gnyis ka la dpyod pa mu bzhi'i skye 'gog ni /
NK114(ye)001:13508: rgyus 'bras bu bskyed par snang ba chos can /
NK114(ye)001:13510: 'di ltar rgyu gcig pu zhig gis 'bras bu gcig pu dang /
NK114(ye)001:13511: rgyu du mas 'bras bu du ma dang /
NK114(ye)001:13512: rgyu gcig gis 'bras bu du ma dang /
NK114(ye)001:13513: rgyu du mas 'bras bu gcig mi bskyed pa'i phyir te /
NK114(ye)001:13514: rgyu 'bras gnyis char gcig du ma dang bral ba'i
NK114(ye)001:13515: phyir skye bar btags pa ni nam mkha' la dngos
NK114(ye)001:13517: de skad du bden gnyis 'jug pa las /
NK114(ye)001:13518: du mas dngos po gcig mi byed //
NK114(ye)001:13519: du mas du ma byed ma yin //
NK114(ye)001:13520: gcig gis du ma'i dngos mi byed //
NK114(ye)001:13521: gcig gis gcig nyid byed pa'ang min //
NK114(ye)001:13523: bzhi pa chos rang gi ngo bo la dpyod pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:13524: dang po ma yin dgag gtan tshigs su bkod pa rten 'brel chen mo ni /
NK114(ye)001:13526: dngos por ma grub par thal /
NK114(ye)001:13527: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba de yang skye 'gag
NK114(ye)001:13528: la sogs pa'i mtha' brgyad dang bral ba yin pas
NK114(ye)001:13529: bden pa'i rang bzhin gyis stong pa'i phyir /
NK114(ye)001:13530: dper na chu zla bzhin no //
NK114(ye)001:13533: gang zhig rkyen las skyes pa de ma skyes //
NK114(ye)001:13534: de la skye ba'i rang bzhin yod ma yin //
NK114(ye)001:13538: chos 'ga' yod pa ma yin no //
NK114(ye)001:13539: de phyir stong nyid ma gtogs pa'i //
NK114(ye)001:13540: chos 'ga' yod pa ma yin no //
NK114(ye)001:13542: gnyis pa med dgag gtan tshigs su bkod pa gcig du bral ni /
NK114(ye)001:13543: phyi nang gi snang ba thams cad chos can /
NK114(ye)001:13545: gcig du ma dang bral bas khyab pa gang zhig
NK114(ye)001:13546: bden pa'i dngos pos stong pas khyab pa'i phyir te
NK114(ye)001:13548: ji ltar skad cig mtha' yod ltar //
NK114(ye)001:13549: thog ma dbus kyang brtag par gyis //
NK114(ye)001:13550: skad cig gsum gyi bdag nyid phyir //
NK114(ye)001:13551: 'jig rten skad cig la mi gnas //
NK114(ye)001:13553: de lta bu'i gtan tshigs rnams kyis dpyod pa'i dus ni gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:13554: phan tshun grub mtha' rnam par rtsod pa'i dus dang /
NK114(ye)001:13555: lam shes rab kyis grol bar byed pa'i tshe na'o //
NK114(ye)001:13556: de yang grub mtha' rtsod dus /
NK114(ye)001:13557: rang phyogs las khas len med pas dam bca' sgrub pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:13558: skyon spong ba mi dgos la /
NK114(ye)001:13559: dngos por smra ba de nyid kyi gzhung nang 'gal
NK114(ye)001:13560: ba bsgrigs te dngos zhen thams cad sun phyung dgos
NK114(ye)001:13561: so // lam shes rab kyis grol bar byed pa'i dus na'ang /
NK114(ye)001:13562: phyi sna tshogs su snang ba'i yul /
NK114(ye)001:13563: nang rtog pa dang mi rtog pa'i sems /
NK114(ye)001:13564: ting nge 'dzin dang sgom pa la sogs pa'i nyams myong /
NK114(ye)001:13566: 'gro 'dug la sogs pa'i gnas skabs thams cad du bdag gzhan dang /
NK114(ye)001:13571: chos dang chos min la sogs pa la de dang
NK114(ye)001:13572: der 'dzin pa'i khas len dang snyam byed gang byung
NK114(ye)001:13573: yang dpyad par re res kyang rdul du bshig ste
NK114(ye)001:13574: gang la'ang mtshan zhen dang gtad so med par spros
NK114(ye)001:13575: bral nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang du so thub par
NK114(ye)001:13576: bya'o // des na gang zag gi bdag med shing
NK114(ye)001:13577: rta rnam bdun gyi rigs pas gtan la 'bebs par
NK114(ye)001:13578: bya'o // gsungs kyang / gtan tshigs 'di dag gis
NK114(ye)001:13579: kyang bdag med gnyis ka gtan la phebs par 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:13580: bya'o // gsungs kyang / ro // gnyis pa de gzhan las 'phags pa'i rgyu mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:13581: dbu ma thal 'gyur pa'i grub pa'i mtha' 'dir ni
NK114(ye)001:13582: dngos zhen dang bcas pa'i khas len gang yang med
NK114(ye)001:13583: pas skyon med cing rnam par dag pa'i phyir grub
NK114(ye)001:13584: mtha' smra ba 'og ma gsum po'i rang rang gi
NK114(ye)001:13585: blo yis chos rnams kyi mtshan nyid la btags shing
NK114(ye)001:13586: shes rab kyi yul bdag med dang /
NK114(ye)001:13589: mtha' bral sogs su dpyad nas spros pa phyogs re
NK114(ye)001:13590: tsam bcad kyang da dung dngos zhen gyi rnam pa
NK114(ye)001:13591: dang bcas pa yin par ma zad /
NK114(ye)001:13592: rang rgyud pas tha snyad du grub par khas len
NK114(ye)001:13593: pa la sogs pa thams cad la'ang brtsad cing brtags
NK114(ye)001:13594: pas mthar 'dzin gyi zhen pa re re nas thal
NK114(ye)001:13596: rang la ni rgol ba'i gnod pa gang yang mi
NK114(ye)001:13597: 'jug pas grub pa'i mtha' thams cad kyi nang nas
NK114(ye)001:13598: gong ma'am rtse mo yin pa nora bar mi 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:13599: ro // de ltar rigs pa bzhi po gshis thog
NK114(ye)001:13600: tu gtan la phebs pa la dbu ma'i lta bar
NK114(ye)001:13601: ro // 'dod kyi / gtan la 'bebs yul gyi
NK114(ye)001:13602: stong nyid mtha' bral dbu ma'i lta bar 'dod na
NK114(ye)001:13603: ro // 'dod kyi / ni / mtha' bzhi po
NK114(ye)001:13604: de ga mthar 'dzin gyi lta bar 'gyur pas mtha'
NK114(ye)001:13605: dang mthar 'dzin gyi khyad par ma phyed pa yin
NK114(ye)001:13606: pas mtha' dang bral ba'o zhes pa tsam du'ang mi
NK114(ye)001:13609: yod min med min yod med min //
NK114(ye)001:13610: gnyis ka'i bdag nyid kyang min pa //
NK114(ye)001:13611: mtha' bzhi las grol dbu ma pa //
NK114(ye)001:13612: mkhas pa rnams kyi de kho na //
NK114(ye)001:13614: gsum pa de ltar gtan la dbab pa'i sgom don ngos bzung ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:13615: de la spyir 'phags pa'i yul na phyi nang gi
NK114(ye)001:13616: grub pa'i mtha' 'dzin pa la nang gses kyi dbye
NK114(ye)001:13618: bod 'dir yang rang rang gi 'dod zhen gyisa sbyar
NK114(ye)001:13619: ba'i grub pa'i mtha' 'dra min sna tshogs byung zhing
NK114(ye)001:13620: / dbu ma dang gsang sngags kyi lam srol 'dzin
NK114(ye)001:13621: pa poo rnams kyis kyang dgongs pa len tshul dang
NK114(ye)001:13622: bshad srol tha dad du song ba shin tu mang
NK114(ye)001:13623: / na yang / de dag thams cad ni rang
NK114(ye)001:13624: rang gi ngor ltos te rang gi blos bzhag pa'i
NK114(ye)001:13625: tshul de mthar thug gi don du grub par 'dod
NK114(ye)001:13626: / na yang / kyi / zhib tu dpyad na
NK114(ye)001:13627: phyin ci log pa dang ltar snang yang dag pa
NK114(ye)001:13629: 'ga' zhig ni thabs la mkhas pas gdul bya'i dbang gis de ltar bzhag pa'ang yod la /
NK114(ye)001:13630: phal cher rang rang gi blo'i nus pa dang rjes
NK114(ye)001:13631: su mthun pa'i rgyal ba'i phrin las kyis sems can
NK114(ye)001:13632: la phan pa can sha stag yin pas kun la
NK114(ye)001:13633: gus pa bskyed dgos te don ci yang med bzhin
NK114(ye)001:13634: du phyi rol pa'i grub mtha' la smad na yang
NK114(ye)001:13635: sngags kyi rtsa ltung du gsungs pas chags sdang dang
NK114(ye)001:13636: phyogs zhen gyi ngan rtog gis ma sbag par rang
NK114(ye)001:13637: gis yang dag pa'i don nyams su len shes pa
NK114(ye)001:13638: dang / gzhan la'ang rang rang dang rjes su mthun
NK114(ye)001:13639: pa'i lam ston shes pa'i phyir grub pa'i mtha' yi
NK114(ye)001:13640: rnam bzhag ji snyed pa thams cad kyi mtshan nyid
NK114(ye)001:13641: thos pa'i shes rab kyis rang gi nyams 'og tu
NK114(ye)001:13642: chud de shes par bya dgos shing /
NK114(ye)001:13643: de yang bdag med pa'i don bsgom pa dang gzhan
NK114(ye)001:13644: la ston pa la'ang thog mar de'i mi mthun pa'i
NK114(ye)001:13645: phyogs bdag smra ba rnams kyi 'dod pa'i tshul shes
NK114(ye)001:13646: nas spang bar bya ba ste /
NK114(ye)001:13648: de nyid 'tshol ba'i thog mar ni //
NK114(ye)001:13649: thams cad yod ces brjod par bya //
NK114(ye)001:13650: don dam rtogs shing chags med la //
NK114(ye)001:13651: de nas rnam par dben don nyid //
NK114(ye)001:13653: de dag las blang bar bya ba rang sde'i grub
NK114(ye)001:13654: pa'i mtha' bzhi po kun 'chos skyob kyi yon tan
NK114(ye)001:13655: gnyis dang ldan pa yin mod kyang /
NK114(ye)001:13656: 'chos skyob mthar thug pa'i yon tan dang ldan zhing
NK114(ye)001:13657: nges don gyi mdo sde'i dgongs don phyin ci ma
NK114(ye)001:13658: log par ston pa'i grub pa'i mtha' dngos thal 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:13659: ba dang / dngos don de dang cha 'dra ba'am mthun par ston pa rang rgyud dang /
NK114(ye)001:13660: shes pa tsam dang don shes gnyis ka'i ngo bos
NK114(ye)001:13661: mi stong bar ston pas mtha' bral dbu ma'i lam
NK114(ye)001:13662: dngos min pa sems tsam pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:13663: nyan thos sde pa gnyis yin la /
NK114(ye)001:13664: de kun gyis yang dag pa'i don gtan la phebs pa'i legs pa'i cha dang /
NK114(ye)001:13665: dngos por zhen pa'i cha'i mtshan nyid thams cad ma
NK114(ye)001:13666: 'dres par so sor legs par phyed pas tshig tsam
NK114(ye)001:13667: la ma ltos par nang du nges pa yang dag
NK114(ye)001:13668: pa rnyed pa ni bsam pa'i shes rab yin kyang
NK114(ye)001:13669: / de 'dra ba'i bsam byung gi ngo bo ni
NK114(ye)001:13670: thos pa dri ma med pa'i shes rab la brten
NK114(ye)001:13671: / nas 'byung zhing / de yisa rnyed pa'i don
NK114(ye)001:13672: rang rgyud la bkal te 'dres shing goms par byas
NK114(ye)001:13673: na chos rab tu rnam par 'byed pa'i shes rab
NK114(ye)001:13674: yang dag pa des nang du nyon mongs dang dngos
NK114(ye)001:13675: po la mngon par zhen pa'i rtog pa thams cad
NK114(ye)001:13676: bcil ba ste sems rgyud la mi gnas par byed
NK114(ye)001:13677: / nas 'byung zhing / cing / mngon par zhen
NK114(ye)001:13678: pa dang nyon mongs pa med pa la ni phyi
NK114(ye)001:13680: rgol ba ngan pa gang la'ang 'jigs pa med pa'i
NK114(ye)001:13681: spobs pa rgya chen po thob pas de rnams kyis
NK114(ye)001:13682: glags mi rnyed pas bardzi mi nus so //
NK114(ye)001:13684: sred med kyi bus zhus pa las /
NK114(ye)001:13685: rigs kyi bu thos pa dang ldan na shes rab 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:13686: shes rab dang ldan na nyon mongs pa rab tu zhi bar 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:13687: nyon mongs pa med pa la bdud kyis glags mi rnyed do zhes so //
NK114(ye)001:13688: 'o na de dag gi nang nas 'dir mthar thug
NK114(ye)001:13689: pa'i nyams len du gang bzung zhe na 'phags pa
NK114(ye)001:13690: shes rab kyi mig dri ma med pa dang ldan
NK114(ye)001:13691: pa thal 'gyur gyi shing rta'i srol 'byed chen po
NK114(ye)001:13692: rnams kyis ji ltar bstan pa'i don chos rnams kyi
NK114(ye)001:13693: gshis kyi bzhugs tshul chos kyi dbyings rang bzhin gyis
NK114(ye)001:13694: spros pa dang bral ba la ngag gis smra ba
NK114(ye)001:13696: tshig gis brjod du med pa byang sems 'phags pa'i
NK114(ye)001:13697: mnyam bzhag dang sangs rgyas kyi ye shes ji lta
NK114(ye)001:13698: ba'i rang bzhin sems dang sems las byung ba'i 'jug
NK114(ye)001:13699: pa thams cad zhi ba'i don dam pa'i bden pa
NK114(ye)001:13700: de ni rtogs bya mthar thug pa'i don yin la
NK114(ye)001:13701: / de lta na'ang rtsal snang 'gags pa med pa
NK114(ye)001:13702: rten 'brel gyi snang cha 'di la blo ste sems
NK114(ye)001:13703: sems byung gi rtog pa yi cha nas smra bsam
NK114(ye)001:13705: btags pa ji lta bar snang ba'i cha 'gog med
NK114(ye)001:13706: du 'char ba rnams kun rdzob kyi bden pa'i char
NK114(ye)001:13707: bzhag nas mnyam bzhag tu rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK114(ye)001:13708: ye shes nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang la 'jog cing
NK114(ye)001:13709: / rjes thob tu sgyu ma lta bu'i dran 'dun
NK114(ye)001:13710: gyis bsod nams kyi tshogs mi 'gog par bsgrub na
NK114(ye)001:13711: yang bden gnyis so so'i phyogs su ltung ba ma
NK114(ye)001:13712: yin par rjes thob snang ba dang bcas pa'i gnas
NK114(ye)001:13713: skabs su'ang rang bzhin gshis kyi bzhugs tshul las g.yo
NK114(ye)001:13714: / mi srid la / mnyam bzhag spros pa dang
NK114(ye)001:13715: bral ba'i ngang la gnas pa'i tshe na'ang chad stong
NK114(ye)001:13716: ci yang med par 'gyur mi srid pas dus nam
NK114(ye)001:13717: du yang gnyis po zung du 'jug cing 'du 'bral
NK114(ye)001:13718: med pa'i don de ni chos kyi dbyings kyi rang
NK114(ye)001:13719: bzhin yin pas de'i ngo bo rtogs bya yul dang
NK114(ye)001:13720: rtogs byed shes pa la sogs pa blos btags pa'i
NK114(ye)001:13721: gnyis chos thams cad las 'das pa yin pas gang
NK114(ye)001:13722: zag sus kyang shes bya shes byed kyi tshul gyis
NK114(ye)001:13724: dmigs rnam can gyi lta bas bltar med cing /
NK114(ye)001:13725: rtsol ba dang bcas pa'i lam bsgrubs pas sngar med
NK114(ye)001:13726: gsar du thob pa dang mthar phyin rgyu yang rdul
NK114(ye)001:13727: tsam med la / lam ma bsgrubs par rang gar
NK114(ye)001:13728: tha mal du bsdad kyang ma thob par shor ba
NK114(ye)001:13729: tsam med la / yang med de / chos nyid
NK114(ye)001:13730: rnal ma'i ngos na de gnyis ka bzang ngan med
NK114(ye)001:13731: par mnyam pa nyid kyi phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:13732: 'o na 'bras bu thob ces pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:13733: lta ba rtogs zhes pa la sogs pa ci la brjod ce na /
NK114(ye)001:13734: rtogs thob rang mtshan pa zhig yod nas de skad brjod pa min te /
NK114(ye)001:13735: chos nyid stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin ni dngos
NK114(ye)001:13736: mtshan dang gnyis chos thams cad yod ma myong ba
NK114(ye)001:13737: ngang gis spros pa'i zug rngu thams cad dang bral
NK114(ye)001:13738: bar gnas pa la de dang nges par rjes su
NK114(ye)001:13739: mthun pa'i blo mthar 'dzin gyi dri ma thams cad
NK114(ye)001:13740: zad cing yul dang yul can ro gcig pa'i tshul
NK114(ye)001:13741: du skyes pa ste lan tsh+wa chur zhu ba ltar
NK114(ye)001:13742: chos nyid dang tha dad med par gyur pa la
NK114(ye)001:13744: 'bras bu thob pa la sogs pa'i bla dwags te ming gi tha snyad btags pa yin te /
NK114(ye)001:13746: de phyir thar pa nor tsam zad pa yin //
NK114(ye)001:13749: stong pa nyid dang rjes su mthun pa'i blo skyes
NK114(ye)001:13750: pa la ni stong pa nyid rtogs so zhes brjod
NK114(ye)001:13751: kyi / stong pa nyid rtogs pa ni ma yin no //
NK114(ye)001:13753: bzhi pa khas len mi len gyi rnam bzhag bye brag tu bshad pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:13754: 'di ltar dbu ma thal 'gyur ba la don dam
NK114(ye)001:13755: du khas len mi len gyi dpyad ra med pas
NK114(ye)001:13756: na re zhig kun rdzob tha snyad tsam du skabs
NK114(ye)001:13757: kyi dbye bas khas len pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:13758: mi len pa gnyis su go bar bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:13759: de'ang rtsod pa dang don dam yul du byed pa'i
NK114(ye)001:13760: tshe snang ba gang yang rang bzhin med pas gang
NK114(ye)001:13761: yang khas blang bar bya ba ma yin no //
NK114(ye)001:13762: lam rjes thob pa tha snyad yul du byed dus
NK114(ye)001:13763: gsung rab las bshad pa ltar rnam dbye dang bcas
NK114(ye)001:13764: pa rmi lam sgyu ma'i grub mtha' tsam du shes
NK114(ye)001:13765: nas rang gis kyang dpyad de bsam zhing /
NK114(ye)001:13766: gzhan la'ang bstan pas blang dor gyi dmigs phyed nas
NK114(ye)001:13767: lam dbu ma tshogs gnyis la zhugs te 'bras bu
NK114(ye)001:13768: sku gnyis 'grub pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK114(ye)001:13769: des na dbu ma'i gzhung rnams las khas mi len pa'i tshul yang gsungs te /
NK114(ye)001:13770: gal te ngas dam bcas 'ga' yod //
NK114(ye)001:13771: ces pa la sogs pa sngar drangs pa ltar ro //
NK114(ye)001:13772: khas len pa'i tshul yang gsungs te /
NK114(ye)001:13774: chu 'dod pas snod ltar thog mar kun rdzob kyi
NK114(ye)001:13775: bden pa ni gdon mi za bar khas blang bar
NK114(ye)001:13778: phyogs 'di ni mkhas pa dag gis skyon med cing yon tan dang ldan pa'o snyam du bsam te /
NK114(ye)001:13779: gdon mi za bar khas blang bar bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:13781: grub mtha' bzhi po de yang don bsdu na /
NK114(ye)001:13782: phyi don 'dod rang rig mi 'dod pa bye brag smra ba /
NK114(ye)001:13783: phyi don rang rig gnyis ka 'dod pa mdo sde pa /
NK114(ye)001:13784: phyi don mi 'dod rang rig 'dod pas sems tsam pa /
NK114(ye)001:13785: phyi don rang rig gnyis ka mi 'dod pa dbu ma pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:13786: phyi don 'dod mi 'dod ni phyi rol gyi don
NK114(ye)001:13787: du snang ba'i gzugs sgra la sogs pa'i dngos po
NK114(ye)001:13788: don dam par yod med yin la /
NK114(ye)001:13789: rang rig 'dod mi 'dod ni tha snyad du shes
NK114(ye)001:13790: pas rang rig par 'dod pa dang mi rig par
NK114(ye)001:13792: de dag ni spyir btang tsam yin la /
NK114(ye)001:13793: dmigs bsal du zhib cha cung zad dgos pa rnams
NK114(ye)001:13794: ni rang rang gi skabs su phyogs tsam bshad pa
NK114(ye)001:13795: yin no // sa bcad gnyis pa lam dbu ma tshogs gnyis zung 'jug dang /
NK114(ye)001:13796: gsum pa 'bras bu dbu ma sku gnyis zung 'jug
NK114(ye)001:13797: ste de gnyis ni bsam sgom gyi skabs su 'chad
NK114(ye)001:13798: par 'gyur ba dang don gcig pas logs su bshad
NK114(ye)001:13799: mi dgos so // gnyis pa bsam pa'i shes rab bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:13803: gzhi lam 'bras bus bsdus pa'i chos gang zhig rang
NK114(ye)001:13804: bzhin gyis ma grub la byed pa pos ma byas
NK114(ye)001:13805: par rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i rang bzhin du
NK114(ye)001:13807: gsung rab kyi chos rnams ma lus kun gyi brjod byar gnas pas mdzod du gyur ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:13808: gang zhig gnas de lta bu thos pas gtan la phebs pa'i rjes su /
NK114(ye)001:13809: gnad don gcig tu bsdus te bsam pa'i shes rab
NK114(ye)001:13810: kyis mthar 'dzin dang phyogs zhen gyi dri mas ma
NK114(ye)001:13811: bslad par yang dag par 'jug pa na gsung rab
NK114(ye)001:13812: kyi brjod don zab mo'i sgo 'phar 'byed pa'i lde
NK114(ye)001:13815: 'phags pa yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa chen po las /
NK114(ye)001:13816: rigs kyi bu dge ba'i chos ni ma bsam par na gzhan gyis thob pa med do //
NK114(ye)001:13817: de ci'i phyir zhe na gang gis bskal pa grangs
NK114(ye)001:13818: med tshad med mtha' yas pa'i bar du chos mnyan
NK114(ye)001:13819: kyang gal te ma bsam na bla na med par
NK114(ye)001:13820: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub thob par mi
NK114(ye)001:13822: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK114(ye)001:13827: 'di ltar snang ba ni bslu zhing rdzun pa /
NK114(ye)001:13828: srid pa ni g.yo zhing 'du byed pa /
NK114(ye)001:13829: 'khor ba ni kun 'byung rang rgyud ldan /
NK114(ye)001:13830: mya ngan las 'das pa'ang rang bzhin pa'i chos nyid la ming gis gdags pa nyid de /
NK114(ye)001:13831: 'di ltar chos can dang chos nyid du snang ba'i
NK114(ye)001:13832: chos rnams thams cad kun dang po gang nas kyang
NK114(ye)001:13833: ni ma 'ongsa pas ma skyes pa bya ste 'das
NK114(ye)001:13835: tha mar gang du'nga ma song bas mi 'byung ba ste ma 'ongs pa ma yin zhing /
NK114(ye)001:13836: bar du gang na'ang mi gansa pas rang bzhin ma
NK114(ye)001:13837: mchis pas da lta ba ma yin pa ste de
NK114(ye)001:13838: ltar chos thams cad gdod ma nas dus gsum mnyam
NK114(ye)001:13839: pa nyid kyi rang bzhin du gnas pa ni gshis
NK114(ye)001:13840: la gansa pa'i rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba yin
NK114(ye)001:13841: te / yab sras mjal ba las /
NK114(ye)001:13842: chos 'di dag thams cad ni dus gsum du mnyam pa nyid kyis mnyam pa dag ste /
NK114(ye)001:13843: zhes pa la sogs pa ltar ro //
NK114(ye)001:13844: yang 'di ltar chos can sna tshogs su snang ba
NK114(ye)001:13845: nyid kyang skye 'gag la sogs pa ltar snang yang
NK114(ye)001:13846: / snang dus de nyid nas rang gi ngo bo
NK114(ye)001:13847: nyid du gyur ba'i 'khrul gzhi rdul tsam yang med
NK114(ye)001:13848: de rang gi rang bzhin stong bzhin du snang ba
NK114(ye)001:13849: ma 'gags par shar bas yod med la sogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:13850: spros pa'i mtha' gang la'ang mi gnas pa'i don la
NK114(ye)001:13851: shes rab kyis nges pa gting nas rnyed nas chos
NK114(ye)001:13852: can mthun snang du grub pa med pa'i stong nyid
NK114(ye)001:13853: la brten nas gdags pa tsam du shes pa'i lam
NK114(ye)001:13854: de ni mtha' bral dbu ma'i lam gyi rang bzhin
NK114(ye)001:13855: nyid du bstan pa yin te /
NK114(ye)001:13858: de ni stong pa nyid du bshad //
NK114(ye)001:13859: de ni brten nas gdags pa ste //
NK114(ye)001:13860: de nyid dbu ma'i lam yin no //
NK114(ye)001:13862: de yang gshis rnal ma'i ngo bo la dag pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:13863: ma dag pa gnyis ka med kyang sems rtog glo
NK114(ye)001:13864: bur ba langs pa'i bag chags kyi dbang gis don
NK114(ye)001:13865: la med pa yin kyang med bzhin du phyi nang
NK114(ye)001:13866: gi snang ba sna tshogs pa 'di snang zhing /
NK114(ye)001:13867: snang ba de la 'di ni yul lo //
NK114(ye)001:13868: 'di ni yul can no zhes pa la sogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:13869: tshul gyis gzung 'dzin rnam par kun tu sgrog btags
NK114(ye)001:13870: te blang dor dang dgag sgrub tu zhen pas nye
NK114(ye)001:13871: bar len pa'i sgo nas 'khrul snang dang 'khrul rtog
NK114(ye)001:13872: lu gu rgyud du bar ma chad par 'khor ba
NK114(ye)001:13873: yin la / yang gshis kyi yin lugs tshol bar
NK114(ye)001:13874: 'dod pa'i phyi nang gi grub mtha' smra ba po
NK114(ye)001:13875: dag gis tshul de la rtog cing yang yang dpyad
NK114(ye)001:13876: pas mtha' bral gyi don ji bzhin pa khong du
NK114(ye)001:13877: ma chud pa rnams kyi blos bzhag pa'i sgro skur
NK114(ye)001:13878: gyi mtha' bzhi byung ba yin te /
NK114(ye)001:13879: gang zhe na rang sde rnams kyis phyi don dang
NK114(ye)001:13880: rang rig la sogs pa yod par lta ba dang
NK114(ye)001:13881: / dngos po rags pa dang gzung 'dzin la sogs
NK114(ye)001:13882: pa med par bkag pa'i med dgag stong rkyang tsam
NK114(ye)001:13884: phyi rol pa dag gtso bdag la sogs pa brtag par 'dod pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:13885: da lta'i snang ba 'di tsam glo bur du byung
NK114(ye)001:13886: ba las snga phyi'i rgyun chad par bltas te las
NK114(ye)001:13887: 'bras la sogs pa med par lta ba ste de
NK114(ye)001:13888: bzhi po'i nang du chos nyid las gol ba'i mthar
NK114(ye)001:13889: 'dzin thams cad 'du ba yin pas gang la'ang ma
NK114(ye)001:13891: der ma zad dngos zhen dang mthar 'dzin gcod pa tsam las /
NK114(ye)001:13892: mtha' dang bral ba'i dbus zhes bya ba zhig blos
NK114(ye)001:13893: bzos te 'di ni zung 'jug dbu ma'i lam mo
NK114(ye)001:13894: zhes mchog 'dzin dang bcas pas de la gnas par
NK114(ye)001:13895: byed pa'nga chos nyid kyi don la mkhas pa min
NK114(ye)001:13896: te / gshis don la dbus zhes bya ba'ang ma grub pa'i phyir gol ba'i blo yin no //
NK114(ye)001:13899: rtog can dag gis yod dang med ces btags //
NK114(ye)001:13900: de ltar dpyod pas sdug bsngal zhi mi 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:13901: yod dang med ces bya ba gnyis ka mtha' //
NK114(ye)001:13902: gtsang dang mi gtsang 'di yang mtha' yin te //
NK114(ye)001:13903: mkhas pa dbus la'ang gnas par yongs mi 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:13905: de lta bu'i gnas lugs ma rtogs na gzhi tha
NK114(ye)001:13906: dad pa'i rtag chad sel ba tsam ni 'jig rten
NK114(ye)001:13907: pa'i lta ba la'ang yod pas yang dag pa ma
NK114(ye)001:13908: yin te / phyir mi ldog pa 'khor lo'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:13909: yod ces bya ba mtha' gcig ste //
NK114(ye)001:13910: med ces bya ba gnyis pa yin //
NK114(ye)001:13911: de ni bdag dang bdag med mtshungs //
NK114(ye)001:13912: rtag pa dang ni chad pa mtshungs //
NK114(ye)001:13913: zhes nyes pa bsal ba'i tshul bka' stsal pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:13914: de ltar chos nyid kyi don la yod med sogs
NK114(ye)001:13915: gang yang ma grub kyang dngos zhen can dag gis
NK114(ye)001:13916: ni / ji ltar dar gyi srin bu zhes pa
NK114(ye)001:13917: sdom srin gyis rang gi kha chu'i thags rgya bran
NK114(ye)001:13918: te des rkang lag bcings nas mi thar ba bzhin
NK114(ye)001:13919: ni / du / rang rang gis 'dod pa'i grub
NK114(ye)001:13920: mtha' sgra rtog gis bzhag pa de yis rang nyid
NK114(ye)001:13921: bcings te yang dag pa'i don las ring bar 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:13922: ni / du / ba yin te / lang ka'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:13923: dngos por shes pa'i sgra 'dzin pa //
NK114(ye)001:13924: ji ltar dar gyi srin bu bzhin //
NK114(ye)001:13925: byis pa mtshams sbyor mi mkhas pa //
NK114(ye)001:13926: rang gi grub mtha' dman pas 'ching //
NK114(ye)001:13928: des na 'di ltar bag chags mthu brtas pa'i skabs
NK114(ye)001:13929: 'di na blo yis sgro btags shing snang tsam pa'i
NK114(ye)001:13930: chos 'di dag thams cad kyi rang bzhin /
NK114(ye)001:13931: skye med gnas lugs yin pas 'gag med gshis la grub ste /
NK114(ye)001:13932: skye 'gag sogs su snang yang blos btags pa ltar dang po skye ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:13935: phyi nang dang phan tshun du 'gro 'ong zhes bya ba yod pa min zhing /
NK114(ye)001:13936: bdag gzhan dang don shes sogs don gcig ma yin la tha dad pa'ang mina zhing /
NK114(ye)001:13937: 'pho 'gyur med pa'i rtag pa ma yin zhing /
NK114(ye)001:13938: dang po yod nas mthar chad pa'ang min pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:13939: de ltar med pa drug dang ma yin pa gnyis
NK114(ye)001:13940: te spros pa'i mtha' brgya po dag nye bar zhi
NK114(ye)001:13942: mgon po klu'i dbang po'i zhal nas /
NK114(ye)001:13944: 'gag pa med pa skye med pa //
NK114(ye)001:13945: chad pa med pa rtag med pa //
NK114(ye)001:13947: tha dad don min don gcig min //
NK114(ye)001:13948: spros pa nyer zhi zhi bstan pa //
NK114(ye)001:13950: des na de lta bu'i gshis thog nyid du blo
NK114(ye)001:13951: phebs shing ji bzhin pa'i gnas lugs shes pa ni
NK114(ye)001:13952: bsam pa las byung ba'i shes rab kyi ngo bo
NK114(ye)001:13955: 'di ltar lang kar gshegs pa la sogs pa zab
NK114(ye)001:13956: mo'i mdo sde dag las kun gzhi'i rnam par shes
NK114(ye)001:13957: pa dgongs pa can gyis gsungs pa des /
NK114(ye)001:13958: thog mar mu stegs can gyi lugs bsal ba'i don chen po 'dren par 'gyur ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:13959: phyi nas gsung rab zab mo'i don rig pa rnams
NK114(ye)001:13960: kyis kun gzhi'i rnam shes yod par 'dzin pa spong
NK114(ye)001:13961: ba nyid de / des na tshogs drug las gzhan
NK114(ye)001:13962: pa'i kun gzhi zhes bya ba zhig tha snyad du'ang
NK114(ye)001:13963: rdzas su grub pa med kyang /
NK114(ye)001:13964: shes pa rtog med yengs thabs kyi dus snang yul 'dzin pa la kun gzhir btags pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:13965: gsal snang la der 'dzin mi 'jug pa de'i rnam shes /
NK114(ye)001:13966: de sgo lnga'i yul la dgag sgrub gzung 'dzin du
NK114(ye)001:13967: rten cing 'brel bas rnam shes bdun du btags pa'i
NK114(ye)001:13968: 'khrul ngor spyir sa dang chu dang me dang rlung
NK114(ye)001:13969: ste 'byung ba bzhi po nam mkha' go 'byed pa
NK114(ye)001:13970: tsam du yod pa la snang zhing /
NK114(ye)001:13971: bye brag tu ri dang nags tshal dang /
NK114(ye)001:13976: sa myug sogs 'dus byas kyi dngos po thams cad
NK114(ye)001:13977: rang rang gi rgyu las thams cad skyes te 'di
NK114(ye)001:13982: me tog /'bras bu ste drug po la rgyu dang 'brel ba drug ces bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:13983: ljon pa lta bu la de drug po dngos dang /
NK114(ye)001:13984: gzhan bum snam sogs la'ang de dang cha 'dra ba brtsi ru yod pa yin la /
NK114(ye)001:13985: 'byung ba lnga dus kyi 'gyur ba ste drug po la rkyen dang 'brel ba drug ces bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:13986: de ltar bcu gnyis kyi rang bzhin du phyi don
NK114(ye)001:13987: gyi bag chags ma zad pa de srid du rgyun
NK114(ye)001:13988: mi 'chad par 'khor ba ni phyi'i rten cing 'brel
NK114(ye)001:13990: yang ma rig pa yod pa las 'khor bar 'phen
NK114(ye)001:13991: byed kyi las 'du byed de de bzhin du rnam
NK114(ye)001:13992: shes sogs snga ma snga ma las phyi ma phyi
NK114(ye)001:13993: ma gcig la gcig brten gyi tshul gyis rga shi'i
NK114(ye)001:13994: bar du bar ma chad du 'brel ste /
NK114(ye)001:13995: thog ma med pa nas 'khor ba ni nang gi
NK114(ye)001:13996: sems dang lus kyi bag chags ma zad kyi bar
NK114(ye)001:13997: du 'byung ba nang gi rten cing 'brel bar 'byung
NK114(ye)001:13998: ba yin no // 'di dag gi don theg chen
NK114(ye)001:13999: gtso bor gyur pa'i spyi'i lugs ni sngar bshad zin
NK114(ye)001:14000: ba yin no // la / 'dir nyan thos kyi
NK114(ye)001:14001: sde snod kyi dbang du byas nas cung zad bshad
NK114(ye)001:14002: ba yin no // la / na / ma rig
NK114(ye)001:14003: pa ni skye ba 'di 'grub pa'i tshe snga ma'i
NK114(ye)001:14004: nyon mongs pa spyod dus kyi phung po lnga'o //
NK114(ye)001:14005: 'du byed ni tshe 'di 'grub pa'i sngon rol gyi las gsog dus kyi phung po lnga'o //
NK114(ye)001:14006: rnam shes ni ma'i mngal du nying mtshams sbyor ba'i gnas skabs kyi phung po lnga'o //
NK114(ye)001:14007: ming gzugs ni mer nur la sogs pa'i gnas skabs
NK114(ye)001:14008: lnga nyams su myong nas dbang po'i sgo ma dod
NK114(ye)001:14009: kyi bar gyi phung po lnga'o //
NK114(ye)001:14010: skye mched drug ni dbang po'i sgo dod nas yul
NK114(ye)001:14011: la longs spyod mi nus pa'i bar tshun chad kyi
NK114(ye)001:14012: phung po lnga'o // reg pa ni dbang po yul
NK114(ye)001:14013: la sad pa ste bde sdug gi yul 'dzin pa
NK114(ye)001:14014: nas bzung bde sdug gi bye brag dngos mi shes
NK114(ye)001:14015: pa'i bar gyi phung po lnga ste 'di dus thung
NK114(ye)001:14016: phung po lnga'o // ngo // tshor ba ni mngal
NK114(ye)001:14017: du bde sdug rags pa myong ba nas bzung 'khrig
NK114(ye)001:14018: pa spyod mi nus pa'i bar gyi phung po lnga'o
NK114(ye)001:14019: phung po lnga'o // ngo // // sred pa ni
NK114(ye)001:14020: 'khrig pa spyod nus pa nas bzung nor rdzas sam
NK114(ye)001:14021: phung po lnga'o // ngo // // / bud med dam /
NK114(ye)001:14022: skyes pa btsal ba'i 'dun pa med pa tshun chad kyi phung po lnga ste /
NK114(ye)001:14024: len pa ni srid yul tshol zhing ma rnyed pa'i bar gyi phung po lnga'o //
NK114(ye)001:14025: srid pa ni yul de rnyed nas spyad pas tshe
NK114(ye)001:14026: phyi ma 'grub pa'i las gsogs pa ste 'chi kha
NK114(ye)001:14027: tshun chad kyi phung po lnga'o //
NK114(ye)001:14028: skye ba ni las de'i nus pas tshe phyi ma mngal du zhugs ma thag pa'i phung po lnga'o //
NK114(ye)001:14029: rga shi ni mngal der zhugs nas phyi ma'i ming
NK114(ye)001:14030: gzugs dang skye mched dang reg pa dang tshor ba
NK114(ye)001:14031: ste bzhi po rdzogs pa'i bar gyi phung po lnga
NK114(ye)001:14032: ste 'di ni 'gag par phyogs pa yin pas der
NK114(ye)001:14033: bzhag go // de'i sred pa nas rten cing 'brel gzhan gyi mgo 'dzug pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:14034: de dag gi tshul mdzod las /
NK114(ye)001:14035: sngon dang phyi mthar gnyis gnyis dang //
NK114(ye)001:14036: bar du brgyad yongs rdzogs ldan pa //
NK114(ye)001:14037: ma rig nyon mongs sngon gnas skabs //
NK114(ye)001:14038: 'du byed dag ni sngon las kyi'o //
NK114(ye)001:14039: rnam shes mtshams sbyor phung po yin //
NK114(ye)001:14040: ming dang gzugs ni de phan chad //
NK114(ye)001:14041: skye mched drug dod tshun chad do //
NK114(ye)001:14042: de ni gsum 'dus tshun chad do //
NK114(ye)001:14043: reg pa bde sdug la sogs kyi //
NK114(ye)001:14044: rgyu shes nus pa tshud chad do //
NK114(ye)001:14045: tshor 'khrig tshun chad sred pa ni //
NK114(ye)001:14046: longs spyod 'khrig pa'i chags can gyi'o //
NK114(ye)001:14047: nye bar len pa longs spyod rnams //
NK114(ye)001:14048: thob par bya phyir yongs rgyug pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:14050: las byed de ni srid pa yin //
NK114(ye)001:14051: nying mtshams sbyor ba skye ba yin //
NK114(ye)001:14052: tshor ba'i bar na rga shi'o //
NK114(ye)001:14053: sngon dang phyi ma bar dag la //
NK114(ye)001:14054: rmongs pa rnam par bzlog phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:14056: de dag mngon 'gyur ba tshang bar 'dod khams pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14057: mngal skyes tshe yongs su rdzogs pa zhig la yod
NK114(ye)001:14058: par bshad do // gsum pa myang 'das kyi rten
NK114(ye)001:14059: 'brel ni de la spyir theg pa chen po'i lugs
NK114(ye)001:14060: kyi mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las
NK114(ye)001:14061: 'das pa chos sku'i rang bzhin ni sngar bshad pa
NK114(ye)001:14062: ltar don dam pa'i bden pa 'dus ma byas pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14063: ngo bor gnas pa yin te /
NK114(ye)001:14065: dngos dang dngos med 'dus byas te //
NK114(ye)001:14068: des na de lta bu'i chos sku'i ye shes de
NK114(ye)001:14069: nyid rgyu dang rkyen gyis gsar du 'dus byas pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14070: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba ma yin kyang lam
NK114(ye)001:14071: bsgrub pa'i rgyu rkyen la brten nas dri ma glo
NK114(ye)001:14072: bur ba dag las myang 'das mngon du 'gyur ba
NK114(ye)001:14073: dang / 'dus ma byas pa'i ye shes de'i rang
NK114(ye)001:14074: rtsal 'gags pa med par 'char ba la rten cing
NK114(ye)001:14075: 'brel bar 'byung ba zhes brjod du rung bas de'i
NK114(ye)001:14076: dang / tshul ni / slob lam bzhi'i gnas skabs
NK114(ye)001:14077: dang 'bras bu mi slob pa'i gnas skabs gnyis su
NK114(ye)001:14079: de yang slob pa'i lam gyi dus su ni 'khor
NK114(ye)001:14080: ba'i rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba ma rig pa
NK114(ye)001:14081: nas rga shi'i bar sngar bshad zin pa ltar lugs
NK114(ye)001:14082: su 'jug pa bcu gnyis kyi rtsa ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:14083: bden pa'i de kho na nyid kyi don la rmongs
NK114(ye)001:14084: pa'i ma rig pa chen po yin par ni tshogs
NK114(ye)001:14085: lam du gtso bo thos bsam gyis shes par byas
NK114(ye)001:14086: nas de'i gnyen po bdag med pa'i don rig pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14087: ye shes ji lta ba bzhin gtan la phab ste
NK114(ye)001:14088: / sbyor lam du dad sogs lnga'i sgo nas don
NK114(ye)001:14089: spyi'i tshul du bsgoms te ma rig pa nyams smad
NK114(ye)001:14090: / par byas nas / mthong lam du rig pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14091: ye shes de'i rang bzhin ji lta ba bzhin mngon
NK114(ye)001:14092: sum du mthong ste ma rig pa'i sgo nas srid
NK114(ye)001:14093: par dbang med du 'phen par byed pa'i zag bcas
NK114(ye)001:14094: kyi las gsog par mi 'gyur zhing /
NK114(ye)001:14095: skye shi sogs so skye tha mal pa bzhin rang mtshan pa yod pa min kyang /
NK114(ye)001:14096: da dung ma rig bag chags kyi sa sogs yod
NK114(ye)001:14097: pas zag med kyi las la brten nas skye 'chi
NK114(ye)001:14098: sogs su ston par byed pa yin la /
NK114(ye)001:14099: sgom lam sa dgu por mngon sum du rtogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14100: ye shes de'i rgyun goms shing gong du 'phel ba'i
NK114(ye)001:14101: stobs kyis / ma rig pa'i bag chags rim gyis
NK114(ye)001:14102: ldog pas 'du byed la sogs pa'i yan lag lhag
NK114(ye)001:14103: ma gzhan rnams kyi bag chags kyang lugs ldog tu
NK114(ye)001:14104: 'gag nas rgyun matha'i rdor ting gis srid pa'i rtsa
NK114(ye)001:14105: ba ma rig pa'i bag chags shin tu phra ba
NK114(ye)001:14106: gnyis snang dang bcas pa spangs pas rgyun chad de
NK114(ye)001:14107: 'bras bu chos sku'i ye shes mngon du gyur te
NK114(ye)001:14108: 'gags med thugs rje'i rol pa cir yang 'char bar
NK114(ye)001:14109: 'gyur ba ni 'bras bu'i rten 'brel yin no //
NK114(ye)001:14110: de dag ni theg pa chen po'i lam bgrod tshul gyi rten 'brel te /
NK114(ye)001:14111: theg dman gyi lam 'bras la sbyar tshul yang des mtshon nas shes par bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:14112: de ltar gzhi lam 'bras bu'i chos thams cad rten
NK114(ye)001:14113: cing 'brel 'byung gi tshul du snang tsam las ngo
NK114(ye)001:14114: bos ma grub pa'i mtshan nyid ma nor bar mthong
NK114(ye)001:14116: sdug bsngal bden pa'i rang bzhin snod bcud thams cad
NK114(ye)001:14117: kun 'byung gi bag chags smin pa'i rten 'brel tsam
NK114(ye)001:14118: las snang ba yin par shes shing /
NK114(ye)001:14119: de'i rgyu kun 'byung las nyon gyi rtsa ba ma
NK114(ye)001:14120: rig pa spong ba'i rten 'brel gyis 'gog pa mya
NK114(ye)001:14121: ngan las 'das pa dam pa mngon du gyur bar
NK114(ye)001:14122: shes nas ma rig pa'i dngos gnyen lam bden bdag
NK114(ye)001:14123: med rtogs pa'i shes rab mchog gi don bsgom pas
NK114(ye)001:14124: mngon du mthong zhing goms pa mthar phyin par 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:14125: bas na / rnam grol gyi lam theg pa gsum
NK114(ye)001:14126: gyi brjod don thams cad rten 'brel zab mo'i don
NK114(ye)001:14127: shes pa 'di la rag las pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:14128: gsum pa bsgom pa'i shes rab bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:14132: gong du ji skad bshad pa de ltar 'khor 'das
NK114(ye)001:14133: lam gsum gyi snang ba ji snyed de thams cad
NK114(ye)001:14134: gdod ma nas skye ba med pa'i rang bzhin du
NK114(ye)001:14135: bsam pa las byung ba'i shes rab rnam par dag
NK114(ye)001:14136: pas gtan la phab pa de'i tshe gnas lugs kyi
NK114(ye)001:14137: rang bzhin nam ngo bo ma nor bar shes pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14138: chos nyid de'i ngang la gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pas
NK114(ye)001:14139: ma bslad par 'jog pa la ni bsgom pa'i shes
NK114(ye)001:14140: rab ces su thun mong ma yin pa'i mdo dang
NK114(ye)001:14142: tshad ma'i skyes bu rnams la grags pa yin te /
NK114(ye)001:14143: ye shes snang ba rgyan gyi mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:14144: kun tu rtog pas ma brtags pa //
NK114(ye)001:14145: rab tu mi gnas pa yi yid //
NK114(ye)001:14146: dran pa med cing yid byed med //
NK114(ye)001:14150: dmigs pa med cing mtshan ma med //
NK114(ye)001:14151: rnam rtog med cing spros pa med //
NK114(ye)001:14152: skye med de ni de bzhin nyid //
NK114(ye)001:14155: brjod par bya ba ldog pa ste //
NK114(ye)001:14156: sems kyi spyod yul ldog pas so //
NK114(ye)001:14157: ma skyes pa dang ma 'gag pa //
NK114(ye)001:14158: chos nyid mya ngan 'das dang mtshungs //
NK114(ye)001:14161: gang tshe skye med de nyid yin zhing blo yang skye ba dang bral ba /
NK114(ye)001:14162: de tshe de rnams la brten nas las de yis de nyid rtogs pa lta bu ste //
NK114(ye)001:14163: ji ltar sems ni gang gi rnam pa can du gyur ba de yis yul //
NK114(ye)001:14164: de yongs shes pa de bzhin tha snyad nye bar brten nas rig pa yin //
NK114(ye)001:14167: dus gsum gyi stong pa'i chos lugs la //
NK114(ye)001:14168: phar bltar med yul gyis bslus par 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:14169: tshur bltar med rang gis bslus par 'gyur //
NK114(ye)001:14170: nga gnyis med shes pa bltar med pa //
NK114(ye)001:14172: 'o na bsgom pa'i tshe ci yang bsam du med na thos bsam byas pas ci zhig bya ste /
NK114(ye)001:14173: ci yang mi shes pa rnams kyang rang gar bsdad pas chog par 'dug go zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:14174: de ni ma yin te chos nyid spros pa dang
NK114(ye)001:14175: bral ba'i don la thos bsam gyis nges pa gting
NK114(ye)001:14176: nas ma rnyed na lhag mthong gi ye shes khyad
NK114(ye)001:14178: lhag mthong gi rgyur tshul khrims dag cing thos bsam sngon du 'gro ba ni gal che ste /
NK114(ye)001:14180: bcom ldan 'das zhi gnas dang lhag mthong rgyu gang las byung ba lags /
NK114(ye)001:14181: byams pa tshul khrims rnam par dag pa'i rgyu las byung ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:14182: thos pa dang bsam pa las byung ba'i lta ba
NK114(ye)001:14183: rnam par dag pa'i rgyu las byung ba yin no
NK114(ye)001:14185: 'phags pa'i gtam 'dod pa bzhin ma thos pa ni lhag mthong gi gegs yin no //
NK114(ye)001:14188: de ltar bsam pa'i shes rab kyi yang dag pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14189: don bye brag phyed par byas la de mngon sum
NK114(ye)001:14190: du bya ba'i phyir bsgom pa'i shes rab bskyed do
NK114(ye)001:14191: // thos pa la sogs pa tsam gyis ni don mngon sum du mi 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:14193: de ltar thos bsam gyi lta bas dpyad pa kun
NK114(ye)001:14194: rdzogs nas bsgom pa'i tshe na 'dzin stangs dang bral
NK114(ye)001:14195: dgos par bzhed pa tsam du gsar snying gi dbu
NK114(ye)001:14197: rang lugs la yod 'dzin nam bden pa'i 'dzin stangs
NK114(ye)001:14198: med pa tsam kho na ma yin par spros pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14199: matha'i zhen rtog thams cad dang bral ba zhig dgos
NK114(ye)001:14201: tshul 'di la dam pa 'ga' zhig gis dgongs 'grel
NK114(ye)001:14202: las gsungs pa ltar ji snyed pa dang ji lta
NK114(ye)001:14203: ba'i dmigs pa rtog dpyod kyis dpyad pa'i tshul dang
NK114(ye)001:14206: sher phyin man ngag sogs nas byung ba'i lhag mthong
NK114(ye)001:14207: gi don btsal ba'i tshul du ma'i sgo nas so
NK114(ye)001:14208: sor rtog pa'i shes rab bskyed dgos par gsungs pa
NK114(ye)001:14209: ni / so so'i skye bo las dang po pa
NK114(ye)001:14210: rnams la nges par gal che bar snang ste lta
NK114(ye)001:14211: ba'i dpyad pa ma rdzogs kyi bar dang /
NK114(ye)001:14212: sgom pa'i tshe na'ang bdag med pa'i don la nges
NK114(ye)001:14213: shes je gsal du 'gro ba dang bogs 'don pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14214: phyir skabs dang skabs su dpyad pas nges shes drangs
NK114(ye)001:14215: par bya'o // 'on kyang rnam par thams cad du
NK114(ye)001:14216: bsgom pa dngos gzhi'i gnas skabs su de 'dra'i dpyad
NK114(ye)001:14218: bdag med pa'i don la nges shes dang bcas pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14219: 'dzin stangs shig med na lhag mthong gi ngo bo
NK114(ye)001:14220: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes med do zhe na
NK114(ye)001:14221: ni / de ltar na 'phags pa'i mnyam bzhag dang /
NK114(ye)001:14222: sangs rgyas kyi sa na'ang de 'dra'i dpyad rig de
NK114(ye)001:14223: yod par 'dod dgos te de med na lhag mthong
NK114(ye)001:14224: gi ye shes med par 'dod pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:14225: de mi dgos te 'phags pa rnams kyis chos nyid
NK114(ye)001:14226: mngon sum du mthong ba'i phyir lhag mthong yod la
NK114(ye)001:14227: / so so'i skye bo ni de dang mi 'dra ba'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK114(ye)001:14228: rnam pa thams cad du 'dra dgos pa ma yin kyang /
NK114(ye)001:14229: chos nyid mngon sum du gzigs shing de la mnyam
NK114(ye)001:14230: par bzhag pa'i ye shes de dang rjes su mthun
NK114(ye)001:14231: pa zhig med na spros pa'i rtog pa dang bcas
NK114(ye)001:14232: pa'i rgyu yis spros pa med pa'i ye shes 'grub
NK114(ye)001:14233: pa ni gnas ma yin no //
NK114(ye)001:14234: 'di la 'ga' zhig gis de ltar na sa bon
NK114(ye)001:14235: skya bo las myu gu sngon po yang 'byung mi
NK114(ye)001:14236: rigs te rgyu 'bras 'dra ba kho na dgos pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14237: phyir gsungs kyang / dpe des ni shin tu 'thad pa kho nar 'gyur bar rigs te /
NK114(ye)001:14238: sa bon skya bo lta bu so so'i skye bo'i
NK114(ye)001:14239: blo yin kyang sa bon de 'bras yin na de
NK114(ye)001:14240: dang 'dra ba'i 'bras kyi myu gu skye ba bzhin
NK114(ye)001:14241: / da lta 'dzin med du bsgom na de dang
NK114(ye)001:14242: 'dra ba'i 'phags pa'i ye shes skye ba gnas yin
NK114(ye)001:14243: / gyi / sa bon de bra bo yin na
NK114(ye)001:14244: de la 'bras kyi myu gu smin pa gnas ma
NK114(ye)001:14246: da lta 'dzin rtog dang bcas pa'i sgom pa de
NK114(ye)001:14247: las 'phags pa'i mi rtog pa'i ye shes skye ba
NK114(ye)001:14248: ni gnas ma yin no snyam mo //
NK114(ye)001:14249: de bzhin du byang sems 'phags pa rnams kyis snying
NK114(ye)001:14250: rje chen po'i sgo nas khyad chos bzhi dang ldan
NK114(ye)001:14251: pa'i sbyin sogs kyi spyod pa rlabs po ches gzhan
NK114(ye)001:14252: don byed pa dang mnyam pa so skye la med
NK114(ye)001:14253: kyang de dang rjes su mthun pa'i sbyor ba sems
NK114(ye)001:14254: bskyed dang / rjes bsngo ba'i thabs kyis zin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14255: sbyin sogs la da lta nas slob dgos pa ni
NK114(ye)001:14256: su'i lugs la yang 'dod pa yin na de dag
NK114(ye)001:14257: kyang rgyu 'bras rigs mthun pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:14258: yang byang sems 'phags pa rnams kyis mnyam bzhag spros
NK114(ye)001:14259: pa dang bral ba'i ye shes dang rjes su mthun
NK114(ye)001:14261: rjes thob byang chen gyi spyod pa bslab pas gzugs
NK114(ye)001:14262: sku phrin las dang bcas pa 'grub pa yang tshul
NK114(ye)001:14264: gzhan yang 'di skad du gsungs te bdag gnyis su
NK114(ye)001:14265: mtshan mar bzung ba la de ltar med pa'i nges
NK114(ye)001:14266: shes kyis 'khrul ba'i rdzun phug rdib pa zhig dgos
NK114(ye)001:14267: kyi nges pa ci yang ma rnyed par bdag gnyis
NK114(ye)001:14268: su sems mi 'phro bar 'jog pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:14269: dper na mtshan mo rgyus med pa'i brag phug tu
NK114(ye)001:14270: srin po yod dam med snyam du 'jigs pa na
NK114(ye)001:14271: / sgron ma btegs nas rtsar bcad de 'jigs pa
NK114(ye)001:14272: mi sel bar srin po la rtog pa 'phror ma
NK114(ye)001:14273: bcug par sems bzung ba dang 'dra ba yin no
NK114(ye)001:14275: de la 'di snyam du sems te nges pa ci
NK114(ye)001:14276: yang ma rnyed par sems bzung ba tsam ni de
NK114(ye)001:14277: lta yin pa thugs mad kyang /
NK114(ye)001:14278: rnam pa thams cad du sems 'phro ba med pa la snyad gdags par mdzad pa yin na ni /
NK114(ye)001:14279: brag phug tu sgron ma btegs nas srin po med
NK114(ye)001:14280: par shes zin kyang 'di na srin po med med
NK114(ye)001:14281: snyam du yang yang yid la ma byas na 'jigs
NK114(ye)001:14282: pa de med par mi 'gyur zer ba dang 'dra
NK114(ye)001:14283: bas na stong nyid la nges pa rnyed nyid zin
NK114(ye)001:14284: kyang stong 'dzin 'dor mi rung ba yin par ni
NK114(ye)001:14285: mi sems so // ci'i phyir na bden med dang
NK114(ye)001:14286: stong nyid dang bdag med sogs kyi don gnas lugs
NK114(ye)001:14287: ma yin par mi brjod kyang /
NK114(ye)001:14288: spros pa mtha' dag ma khegs pa'i bden med dang
NK114(ye)001:14289: stong nyid sogs su 'dzin pa de yum nas bshad
NK114(ye)001:14290: pa'i stong nyid mthar thug ma yin te /
NK114(ye)001:14292: rgyal ba kun gyis stong pa nyid //
NK114(ye)001:14293: lta kun nges par 'byin par gsungs //
NK114(ye)001:14294: gang dag stong pa nyid lta ba //
NK114(ye)001:14295: de dag bsgrub tu med par gsungs //
NK114(ye)001:14296: zhes pa la sogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:14297: des na dngos po med pa'i 'du shes can la /
NK114(ye)001:14298: mthun pa'i bzod pa tsam yang med pa gsungs te /
NK114(ye)001:14300: dngos po med pa'i 'du shes can la mthun pa'i bzod pa'ang med do zhes so //
NK114(ye)001:14302: 'di ltar ci yang mi bsam mo zhes smra na
NK114(ye)001:14303: yang dag par so sor rtog pa'i mtshan nyid kyi
NK114(ye)001:14305: yang dag pa'i shes rab kyi rtsa ba ni yang
NK114(ye)001:14306: dag par so sor rtog pa yin pas de spang
NK114(ye)001:14307: na rtsa ba bcad pa'i phyir 'jig rten las 'das
NK114(ye)001:14308: pa'i shes rab spang bar 'gyur ro zhes pa la
NK114(ye)001:14309: sogs pa gsungs pa ni thos bsam sogs kyis chos
NK114(ye)001:14310: rang bzhin med par nges pa ma rnyed bzhin tsom
NK114(ye)001:14311: 'jog mun thom du 'dug pa dag la dgongs nas
NK114(ye)001:14312: gsungs kyi / lhag mthong gi ye shes khyad par
NK114(ye)001:14313: ba spros bral 'dzin med kyi ngang la 'jog pa
NK114(ye)001:14314: la gsungs pa ga la yin te /
NK114(ye)001:14315: slob dpon zla ba'i dbu ma shes rab la 'jug pa las /
NK114(ye)001:14316: de yi don ni bsgom bya ste //
NK114(ye)001:14317: rtog med blo ni rang zhir bzhag /
NK114(ye)001:14318: ngos bzung med cing yengs pa med //
NK114(ye)001:14319: mtshan ma med cing gsal bar bsgom //
NK114(ye)001:14321: yang so so skye bo'i stong nyid bsgom pa de mngon gyur yin nam lkog gyur yin /
NK114(ye)001:14322: dang po ltar na de 'phags pa yin par thal zhing /
NK114(ye)001:14323: phyi ma ltar na lkog gyur gyi don rtog bral gyis 'dzin pa bzhad gad kyi gnas so //
NK114(ye)001:14324: mdor na stong nyid sgom pa'i so skye de'i yul
NK114(ye)001:14325: bdag med la blo kha ma phyogs na sgom zhes
NK114(ye)001:14326: pa 'gal la / phyogs na mngon lkog gang rung
NK114(ye)001:14327: yin dgos na so skye la lkog gyur las med
NK114(ye)001:14328: pas sbyor lam chos mchog man chad du don spyi'i
NK114(ye)001:14329: tshul du rtogs pa yin pa 'dod bzhin du rtog
NK114(ye)001:14330: bral du sgom zhes pa shin tu 'gal lo zhes
NK114(ye)001:14331: pa 'gal la / gsungs na yang / thos bsam
NK114(ye)001:14332: gyis dpyad pa'i tshe ni rtog bcas kyi yul du
NK114(ye)001:14333: bdag med pa'i don byas nas don spyi'i tshul du
NK114(ye)001:14334: rtogs pa yin par ni mi 'gal ba smos mi
NK114(ye)001:14335: pa 'gal la / gsungs na yang / dgos la
NK114(ye)001:14336: / bdag med pa'i ngang la mnyam par 'jog pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14337: tshe na ni de 'dra ba'i 'gal 'du bsgrigs mi
NK114(ye)001:14339: stong nyid dam bdag med pa zhes pa'i mtshan mar
NK114(ye)001:14340: grub pa can zhig yod na ni de ltar gsungs
NK114(ye)001:14341: rigs kyi chos nyid kyi ngo bo dngos dngos med
NK114(ye)001:14342: sogs kyi mtshan ma gang du'ang ma grub na blos
NK114(ye)001:14343: kyang ci yang mi 'dzin pa de gnas tshul dang
NK114(ye)001:14344: mthun pa yin pas rtog bral du 'jog pa yin
NK114(ye)001:14345: na'ang / da dung mnyam bzhag gi tshe na yang
NK114(ye)001:14346: rtog bral gyi ngo bo de sems kyi sgrib g.yogs
NK114(ye)001:14347: dang bral ba'i 'dus ma byas pa'i ye shes su
NK114(ye)001:14348: ma son pas don spyi'i tshul du bsgom pa yin
NK114(ye)001:14349: par 'dod kyi stong nyid zhes pa'i mtshan ma zhig
NK114(ye)001:14350: yid yul du byas nas rtog pa dang bcas pas
NK114(ye)001:14351: bsgom pa la mi 'dod pas 'gal ba med do
NK114(ye)001:14352: na'ang / // yang dge mi dge'i rtog pa thams
NK114(ye)001:14353: cad 'khor bar 'ching byed yin pas rtog bral gyi
NK114(ye)001:14354: ngo bo skyong ba kho na dgos zer ba hwa
NK114(ye)001:14355: shang gi lta ba dngos yin pas theg chen chos
NK114(ye)001:14356: kyi rtsa ba gcod pa'o gsungs pa la brtags na
NK114(ye)001:14357: na'ang / // / spyir rtog pa bzang ngan gang
NK114(ye)001:14358: yin kyang der 'dzin gyi zhen pa yod na 'ching
NK114(ye)001:14359: byed yin pa la khyad par med de /
NK114(ye)001:14360: gser sgrog dang thag sgrog gnyis ka 'ching byed yin pa la 'dra ba bzhin no //
NK114(ye)001:14361: 'on kyang theg chen gyi lam du rtog pa thams
NK114(ye)001:14362: cad la mtshan ma can gyi chos su zhen nas
NK114(ye)001:14363: dgag dgos par ni mi 'dod de /
NK114(ye)001:14364: dge ba'i rtog pa mi spang bar ma zad mi
NK114(ye)001:14365: dge ba'i rtog par btags pa'i nyon mongs pa rnams
NK114(ye)001:14366: kyang zhen med kyi rtsis zin par byas te chos
NK114(ye)001:14367: nyid du sbyong ba'i thabs kyis lam gyi grogs sam
NK114(ye)001:14368: ngo bor bsgyur bar byed pas rnam bcas kyi ting
NK114(ye)001:14369: nge 'dzin byams pa la sogs pa bsgom pa dang
NK114(ye)001:14370: / sbyin sogs rjes thob kyi spyod pa'i sgo thams
NK114(ye)001:14371: cad kyang ji lta ba bzhin bsgrub dgos par 'dod
NK114(ye)001:14372: / do // de lta na'ang dag pa'i sa ma
NK114(ye)001:14373: thob kyi bar ma dag sa bdun gyi gnas skabs
NK114(ye)001:14374: na'ang mnyam rjes kyi nyams len so sor yod par
NK114(ye)001:14375: bshad na so skye'i gnas skabs su smos ci dgos
NK114(ye)001:14376: / do // pas / stong nyid gtso bor sgom
NK114(ye)001:14377: pa'i dus su rtog pa'i 'dzin stangs med par 'jog
NK114(ye)001:14378: / do // pas / cing / rnam bcas byams sogs sgom pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:14379: sbyin pa gtong ba la sogs pa'i dus su sgyu
NK114(ye)001:14380: ma lta bu'i dran 'dun gyis gang la yang ma
NK114(ye)001:14381: zhen par byas te rtog bcas su bsgrub pa yin
NK114(ye)001:14382: par gsungs so // des na zab mo'i don gzigs
NK114(ye)001:14383: pa'i skyes bu dam pa dag gis kyang spros bral
NK114(ye)001:14384: du 'jog pa lung dang rigs pas bkag nas med
NK114(ye)001:14385: par gsungs so // dgag dang / stong 'dzin kho
NK114(ye)001:14386: na rtsal du bton nas bsgrub par mdzad 'dug pa
NK114(ye)001:14387: 'di tsho bka' dang dgongs 'grel dang man ngag zab
NK114(ye)001:14388: mo'i gnad ci yang mi shes pa'i blun sgom mun
NK114(ye)001:14389: rdo 'phen pa dag la dgongs nas yin gyi dam
NK114(ye)001:14390: pa de rnams rang rang gi thugs kyi brnag bya
NK114(ye)001:14391: mthar thug pa ni ga la yin te /
NK114(ye)001:14392: thos bsam gyi dpyad pa la ye ma sbyangs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14393: dad gus can gyi slob ma mang pos sngags spyi
NK114(ye)001:14394: dang phyag rdzogs kyi lam gyis grol ba thob pa
NK114(ye)001:14395: mngon sum pa de rnams la bsnyon du ci zhig
NK114(ye)001:14396: yod de med pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:14397: des na rang lugs 'dzin pa dag gis rtsol med
NK114(ye)001:14398: kyi lam bsgom pa'i gnas skabs su'ang da dung rtog
NK114(ye)001:14399: pa yod dgos sam mi dgos snyam du the tshom
NK114(ye)001:14400: pa dang / gzhan 'ga' zhig gis kyang ji skad
NK114(ye)001:14401: bshad pa 'di dag ni chos phyiin ci log pa
NK114(ye)001:14402: zhig go snyam du log par lta bar snang bas
NK114(ye)001:14403: de dag la cung zad phan pa srid dam snyam
NK114(ye)001:14404: pa dang / nas / rang rgyud na lhag mthong
NK114(ye)001:14405: lta ci sems las su rung ba'i zhi gnas kyi
NK114(ye)001:14406: nyams len tsam yang med kyang med bzhin dam pa
NK114(ye)001:14407: rnams kyi zhal rgyun yang yang thos pa rna bar
NK114(ye)001:14408: bzhag pa 'di la rang gis bed ma chod phyin
NK114(ye)001:14409: 'chi kha'i kha chems su skabs skabs su bris pa
NK114(ye)001:14410: 'di tsam las thos pa la don dgos med pas
NK114(ye)001:14411: de skad smras pa yin na'ang /
NK114(ye)001:14412: ma rtogs pa dang log par rtog pa sogs kyis
NK114(ye)001:14413: brjod nyes pa'i skyon du thal ba yod na bzod
NK114(ye)001:14414: par gsol lo // de ltar dogs pa bsal nas /
NK114(ye)001:14415: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK114(ye)001:14416: bsgom pa'i shes rab dngos bshad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:14419: phyin drug gi don bsdu ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:14420: dang po bsgom pa'i shes rab dngos bshad pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:14425: mtha' dang dbus med pa de bzhin du sems kyi
NK114(ye)001:14426: rang bzhin ye nas rnam par dag pa'i chos kyi
NK114(ye)001:14427: dbyings su mnyam par bzhag pa na bsgom pa'i don
NK114(ye)001:14428: chos nyid dang yul can gyi ye shes gnyis ro
NK114(ye)001:14429: gcig tu gyur pa las tha dad du yod pa
NK114(ye)001:14430: ma yin te / 'di la sher phyin du nyams
NK114(ye)001:14431: len sbyor ba bzhi bsgom pa'i gnas skabs su dkar
NK114(ye)001:14432: chos mkhyen gsum gyi rnam pa brgya don gsum po
NK114(ye)001:14433: zhen med kyi tshul du bsgom pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:14434: skye med du 'jog pa'i gnas skabs na /
NK114(ye)001:14435: mi gnas pa'i sbyor ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:14436: mi sbyor ba'i sbyor ba zhes yul dang yul can
NK114(ye)001:14437: gnyis ka la zhen spyod 'gog pa'i don du gsungs
NK114(ye)001:14438: shing / gzhan du gnas pa dang rnal 'byor 'gog pa zhes kyang bshad la /
NK114(ye)001:14439: yang bsgom bya dang sgom byed med ces kyang bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:14440: yang gang yang yid la mi byed pa yum gyi don du bshad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:14441: yul gang du'ang ma grub pas blos cir yang mi 'dzin zhes pa dag kyang 'di'i don yin te /
NK114(ye)001:14443: bsgom par lta ba med rnams kyi //
NK114(ye)001:14444: bsgom pa dam par 'dod pa ste //
NK114(ye)001:14446: chos nyid dang ro gcig tu gyur pa'i sems kyi
NK114(ye)001:14447: gshis lugs de la dngos po'i mtshan ma med pas
NK114(ye)001:14448: gzugs sogsa phung po lnga dang /
NK114(ye)001:14449: 'dus ma byas yin pas rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad po kun kyang yod pa ma yin te /
NK114(ye)001:14451: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa bsgom pa 'di ni nam mkha' bsgom pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:14452: nam mkha' la ni gzugs ma mchis /
NK114(ye)001:14456: rnam par shes pa ma mchis zhes pa nas /
NK114(ye)001:14458: zhes pa'i bar gyis gsungs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:14460: gzugs rnams mi mthong tshor ba dag kyang mi mthong zhing //
NK114(ye)001:14461: 'du shes mthong ba med la sems pa mi mthong zhing //
NK114(ye)001:14462: gang la rnam par shes dang sems yid mthong med pa //
NK114(ye)001:14463: 'di ni chos mthong yin zhes de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs //
NK114(ye)001:14465: de yang mtha' bzhi'i skye ba 'gog pa'i dam bca'
NK114(ye)001:14466: ston pa nyid dbu ma thal 'gyur ba'i bzhed pa
NK114(ye)001:14467: yin kyang / med cesa yod mtha' blo yi bkag
NK114(ye)001:14468: nas med pa zhig glo bur du bsgom par byar
NK114(ye)001:14469: med de med pa gshis la mi gnas pa'i phyir
NK114(ye)001:14470: na gshis kyi gnas tshul shes pa'i shes rab nyid
NK114(ye)001:14471: dang lhag par yang 'gal ba yin te /
NK114(ye)001:14472: sems kyi rang bzhin rnam par thar ba'i sgo gsum
NK114(ye)001:14473: du gnas pa 'di ni cang med phyang chad pa
NK114(ye)001:14474: nyid ma yin par de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi
NK114(ye)001:14475: sku dang ye shes kun gyi 'byung gnas yin pas
NK114(ye)001:14478: 'di la bsal bya ci yang med //
NK114(ye)001:14479: bzhag par bya ba cung zad med //
NK114(ye)001:14480: ces gzhi yi gshis lugs gtan la phab nas //
NK114(ye)001:14481: yang dag nyid la yang dag blta //
NK114(ye)001:14482: yang dag mthong na rnam par grol //
NK114(ye)001:14483: zhes so sor rtog pa'i shes rab so so skye
NK114(ye)001:14484: bo'i blo'i yul las 'das pa mngon du byas pa
NK114(ye)001:14485: la dbu ma'i lta bar bzhag pa yin no //
NK114(ye)001:14486: des na gnas lugs ji bzhin pa mngon sum du
NK114(ye)001:14487: mthong ba ni 'phags pa kho na yid mod so
NK114(ye)001:14488: so skye bo'i dus na'ang chos rnams kyi rang bzhin
NK114(ye)001:14489: chos nyid du rnam par dag zin pa'i yang dag
NK114(ye)001:14490: pa'i don nyid la bcos ma'i blo yis ma bslad
NK114(ye)001:14491: par yang dag par blta bar byed pa ni dmus
NK114(ye)001:14492: long ltar rkyen ma tshogs pa'am /
NK114(ye)001:14493: gnyid kyis log pa lta bu'am /
NK114(ye)001:14494: 'du shes med pa'i snyoms 'jug ltar ma yin te
NK114(ye)001:14495: lhag mthong gi ye shes dang lhan cig pa yin
NK114(ye)001:14496: no // de ltar yang yum bar ma las /
NK114(ye)001:14497: gang gis ci yang ma gzigs pa'i don de gzigs pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:14499: don dam pa mthong ba gang zhe na gang chos thams cad mthong ba med pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:14501: blta zhes bya ba de'ang tha snyad kun rdzob tsam du brda' sprod pa'i ming ste /
NK114(ye)001:14502: rang bzhin ma bcos pa'i ngang de las gzhan du
NK114(ye)001:14503: ma yeng zhing mi bsgom pa'i tshul gyis ma g.yos
NK114(ye)001:14504: na / gnas lugs ji bzhin pa bsgom pa yin pa'i phyir gzhan las mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:14505: de ltar mnyam par bzhag pa'i ye shes de yi
NK114(ye)001:14506: mdun te yul na blo zhes pa gtso sems dang
NK114(ye)001:14507: ni yid byed sogs sems byung gis bsdus pa'i rtogs
NK114(ye)001:14508: tshogs yul dang bcas pa'i gzung 'dzin gyi rnam pa
NK114(ye)001:14509: thams cad gnas pa min pa ni dbu ma'i lam
NK114(ye)001:14510: so sor rtog pa'i shes rab yang dag pa yin
NK114(ye)001:14511: te / 'od srung gis zhus pa las /
NK114(ye)001:14512: dbus gang yin pa de ni dpyad du med pa /
NK114(ye)001:14516: rnam par rig pa med pa /
NK114(ye)001:14518: 'od srung 'di ni dbu ma'i lam chos rnams la so sor rtog pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:14520: gnas 'di la de bzhin gshegs pa nyid las tshad
NK114(ye)001:14521: mar gyur pa gzhan med pas dogs pa cung zad
NK114(ye)001:14522: kyang nye bar bsten par mi bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:14523: la la dag sngar bshad pa ltar so sor rtog
NK114(ye)001:14524: pa'i shes rab dpyad shes rnon po la ngos bzung
NK114(ye)001:14525: nas de las ye shes 'byung ba'i khungs su /
NK114(ye)001:14526: yang dag par so sor rtog pa nyid las yang
NK114(ye)001:14527: dag pa ji lta ba bzhin du shes pa'i me
NK114(ye)001:14528: byung nas gtsubs shing gtsubs pa'i me bzhin du rtog
NK114(ye)001:14531: de'i don ni blo dang yid byed kyi rkyen me'i
NK114(ye)001:14532: sa bon ngar lcags las byung ba lta bu la
NK114(ye)001:14533: ma ltos par gtsubs shing rang nyid las byung ba'i
NK114(ye)001:14534: mes bud shing rang nyid bsreg pa dper mdzad nas
NK114(ye)001:14535: blo dang snyam byed la ma ltos pa'i yang dag
NK114(ye)001:14536: pa'i shes rab kyi snang ba rnam par mi rtog
NK114(ye)001:14537: pa'i ye shes me lta bu des /
NK114(ye)001:14538: blo rtog gi bud shing bsregs nas rang gi rang
NK114(ye)001:14539: bzhin ji lta ba bzhin shes par byed pa nyid
NK114(ye)001:14540: la brjod de / dpal mar me mdzad kyis dbu ma'i man ngag bkral ba las /
NK114(ye)001:14541: cir yang mi 'dzin pa ni gzung ba dang 'dzin pa'i rtog pa dang bral bas so //
NK114(ye)001:14542: dran pa dang yid la byed pa thams cad spangs
NK114(ye)001:14543: pa ni 'das pa dang ma 'ongs pa la dmigs
NK114(ye)001:14546: des na shes bya shes byed kyis btags pa'i grub
NK114(ye)001:14547: matha'i spros pa dang bral ba'i cha nas shing rta
NK114(ye)001:14548: chen po gnyis ka rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye
NK114(ye)001:14549: shes kyang bzhed pa ma yin pa'i tshul /
NK114(ye)001:14551: slob dpon 'phags pa thogs med ni yang dag par
NK114(ye)001:14552: na gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyang mi bzhed
NK114(ye)001:14553: la / rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyi rjes la thob pa yang mi bzhed de /
NK114(ye)001:14554: sa gsum pa'i dbang phyug brnyes pas chos thams cad
NK114(ye)001:14555: skye ba med par thugs su chud pa'i phyir ro
NK114(ye)001:14556: // zhes pas de'i gzhung lugs dbu mar gdon mi za'o gsungs /
NK114(ye)001:14557: slob dpon klu'i dbang po'i zhal nas kyang /
NK114(ye)001:14558: mnyam par bzhag dang ma bzhag pa //
NK114(ye)001:14559: gang la 'di dag thams cad med //
NK114(ye)001:14560: dngos dang dngos med rnam spangs pa //
NK114(ye)001:14561: zung 'jug yin par ston pas gsungs //
NK114(ye)001:14563: 'on kyang sangs rgyas la sku dang ye shes yon
NK114(ye)001:14564: tan phrin las med par 'gyur ro snyam nas chad
NK114(ye)001:14566: rang byung gi ye shes chen po chos kyi dbyings
NK114(ye)001:14567: rang bzhin gyis 'dus ma byas pa las gdul bya'i
NK114(ye)001:14568: ngo la sku dang mdzad pa thams cad 'gog med
NK114(ye)001:14570: de ltar phyogs gcig pa'i shes rab tsam ma yin
NK114(ye)001:14571: par mthar 'dzin gyi spros pa kun dang bral ba'i
NK114(ye)001:14572: shes rab de 'dra bar blo 'byor zhing chos thams
NK114(ye)001:14573: cad sgro skur dang bral bar yongs su shes na
NK114(ye)001:14574: / sems bskyed dang sbyin sogs kyi thabs kyisa rnam par grol bar 'gyur te /
NK114(ye)001:14575: shes rab kyi stobs kyi 'khor bar mi ltung la /
NK114(ye)001:14576: thabs kyis stobs kyis mya ngan las 'das par ltung bas na /
NK114(ye)001:14577: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsang ba'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:14579: dper na me ni rgyu las 'bar te /
NK114(ye)001:14580: rgyu med na zhi bar 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:14581: de bzhin du dmigs pa las sems 'bar gyi dmigs pa med na sems zhi bar 'gyur ro //
NK114(ye)001:14582: de la thabs la mkhas pa'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK114(ye)001:14583: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa yongs su
NK114(ye)001:14584: dag pas dmigs pa nye bar zhi bar yang shes
NK114(ye)001:14585: la / dge ba'i rtsa ba la dmigs pa yang zhi bar mi byed /
NK114(ye)001:14586: nyon mongs pa la dmigs pa yang 'byung bar mi byed la /
NK114(ye)001:14587: pha rol tu phyin pa'i dmigs pa 'jog par byed /
NK114(ye)001:14588: stong pa nyid du dmigs pa la yang so sor rtog la /
NK114(ye)001:14589: sems can thams cad snying rje chen pos dmigs pa yang blta'o //
NK114(ye)001:14591: de lta bu'i shes rab de med par dngos zhen
NK114(ye)001:14592: dang bcas pa'i sgo nas sbyin pa la sogs pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14593: thabs kyi cha la 'bad rtsol chen pos yun ring
NK114(ye)001:14594: po ji tsam la brtson kyang de nyid kyis ni
NK114(ye)001:14595: mu stegs can gyi lam bzhin du srid pa'i gnas
NK114(ye)001:14596: su rang rgyud bcings pa' rgyu nyid du 'gyur ba
NK114(ye)001:14597: las grol ba'i skabs med la /
NK114(ye)001:14598: gal te thabs snying rje chen po sogs dang bral
NK114(ye)001:14599: ba'i shes rab kyis kyang nyan thos rnams bzhin du
NK114(ye)001:14600: myang 'das phyogs gcig pa la gol bar 'gyur bas
NK114(ye)001:14601: na / shin tu mnyam par bzhag pa'i gnas skabs
NK114(ye)001:14602: na thabs la brten pa mi 'byung du zin kyang
NK114(ye)001:14603: na / / sbyor ba'am rjes la thob pa'i tshe
NK114(ye)001:14604: na sems bskyed dang bsngo ba sogs thabs kyi cha
NK114(ye)001:14605: la zhen pa med pa'i shes rab kyis zin pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14606: zung 'brel la bslab par bya dgos so //
NK114(ye)001:14607: de ltar na thabs shes kyi lam nyams su len tshul dang /
NK114(ye)001:14608: bka' 'khor lo gsum gyi dgongs don dang /
NK114(ye)001:14609: shing rta chen po gnyis kyi lugs thams cad 'gal
NK114(ye)001:14610: med du shes dgos tshul rnams rje bla ma bka'
NK114(ye)001:14611: drin can gyi sher phyin sgom pa'i man ngag las
NK114(ye)001:14612: dper na sman pa mkhas pas sems can gyi nad
NK114(ye)001:14613: zhi bar byed pa'i phyir rin po che dngul chu'i
NK114(ye)001:14617: btso ba'i sgo nas dngul chu nyid dag par byas te /
NK114(ye)001:14618: dug dang bral bar gyur nas sman sna tshogs dang
NK114(ye)001:14619: sbyar te sems can rnams kyi nad mi 'dra ba
NK114(ye)001:14620: kun kyang sel bar byed do //
NK114(ye)001:14621: dpe de bzhin du byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis
NK114(ye)001:14622: kyang srid zhi'i rgud pa ma lus pa sel ba'i
NK114(ye)001:14623: rgyu gcig pu rin chen byang chub kyi sems rgyud
NK114(ye)001:14625: de yang so skye'i sar rang 'dod kyi dug dang
NK114(ye)001:14626: bcas pa nyid kyi phyir zab mo stong pa nyid
NK114(ye)001:14628: mthong lam du chos nyid mngon du byas pas chos
NK114(ye)001:14629: mnyam pa nyid khong du chud de rang 'dod kyi
NK114(ye)001:14630: dri ma kun dang bral nas dag par gyur ba
NK114(ye)001:14631: na rgyal sras kyi spyod pa rgya mtsho kun kyang
NK114(ye)001:14632: 'khor gsum rnam par mi rtog pa'i tshul dang sbyar
NK114(ye)001:14633: te rang don yal bar 'dor ba'i brtson 'grus rmad
NK114(ye)001:14634: du byung ba'i sgo nas sems can rnams kyi nyon
NK114(ye)001:14635: mongs pa dang shes bya'i sgrib pa'i nad ma lus
NK114(ye)001:14636: pa gso bar byed pa yin la /
NK114(ye)001:14637: gzungs kyi dbang phyug rgyal pos zhus pa'i mdo lung
NK114(ye)001:14638: nor bu sbyong ba'i dpe gsungs pa yang lam gyi
NK114(ye)001:14639: go rim 'di nyid kho na bstan pa yin te
NK114(ye)001:14640: / de las snga ma gnyis ni go bar sla la /
NK114(ye)001:14641: phyi ma'i skabs kyi phyir mi ldog pa 'khor lo'i
NK114(ye)001:14642: gtam ni thabs snying rje chen po dang shes rab
NK114(ye)001:14643: stong pa nyid zung du 'jug pa'i lam yin par
NK114(ye)001:14644: mdo btus 'grel pa sogs las bshad cing /
NK114(ye)001:14645: 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa ni sbyin sogs rgyal
NK114(ye)001:14646: sras kyi spyod pa rnams yin te 'khor gsum mi
NK114(ye)001:14647: dmigs pa'i tshul gyis nyams su len pa'i phyir ro
NK114(ye)001:14648: // de'ang 'phags mchog klu sgrub zhabs kyis mdo btus
NK114(ye)001:14649: su lung 'di drangs nas mthar thug theg pa gcig
NK114(ye)001:14651: dang po mi rtag pa dang sdug bsngal sogs kyis
NK114(ye)001:14652: 'khor ba la skyo ba bskyed nas gzod zab pa
NK114(ye)001:14653: dang rgya che ba'i theg chen la 'jug par gsungs
NK114(ye)001:14654: pas nyan rang gi lam theg chen gyi rkang stegs
NK114(ye)001:14656: rgyal sras thogs med zhabs ni rgyud bla'i 'grel par
NK114(ye)001:14657: lung 'di nyid drangs nas byang chub sems dpa'i rgyud
NK114(ye)001:14658: 'di ltar rim pa bzhin sbyong bar gsungs pas na
NK114(ye)001:14659: sbyang bya snying po'i khams rnam par dag pa yod
NK114(ye)001:14660: par grub bo zhes de bzhin gshegs pa'i khams sgrub
NK114(ye)001:14662: de gnyis gang ltar yang 'dra ste skabs dang por mi rtag sdug bsngal sogs kyis blo sbyang /
NK114(ye)001:14663: skabs gnyis par rnam thar sgo gsum gyi gtam la
NK114(ye)001:14664: brten nas zab mo lta ba'i chos nyid mngon sum
NK114(ye)001:14665: du byas / skabs gsum par phyir mi ldog pa 'khor lo'i gtam dang /
NK114(ye)001:14666: 'khor gsum rnam par dag pa'i gtam la brten nas
NK114(ye)001:14667: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa rlabs po che la
NK114(ye)001:14668: slob pa'i lam gyi go rim 'di kho na ltar
NK114(ye)001:14669: shing rta'i srol 'byed gnyis ka bzhed pas na 'dzam
NK114(ye)001:14670: gling rgyan mchog gnyis kyi gzhung dri ma med pa
NK114(ye)001:14671: rnams kyang 'gal ba med par zung du bsdebs te
NK114(ye)001:14672: gang zag gcig gi nyams len du hril gyis dril
NK114(ye)001:14673: shes na mkhas pa zhes bya yi /
NK114(ye)001:14674: phyogs 'dzin pa'i chags sdang gis rtsod pa la bsgrims
NK114(ye)001:14675: pas ni chos spong gi las tshabs po che sogs
NK114(ye)001:14676: par 'gyur gyi thos pas rgyud grol bar mi 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:14678: gnyis pa lam bgrod tshul bstan pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:14679: gong du ji skad bshad pa'i stong nyid spros pa
NK114(ye)001:14680: dang bral ba'i don de da lta so skye'i gnas
NK114(ye)001:14681: skabs su gtso bor bsgom dgos te /
NK114(ye)001:14682: chos rje bla ma'i gsung las /
NK114(ye)001:14683: kha cig nam mkha' ltar spros bral blo las 'das
NK114(ye)001:14684: pa'i stong nyid zab mo ston pa rnams 'phags pa
NK114(ye)001:14685: sogs gang zag mchog gi chos yin zhing /
NK114(ye)001:14686: 'khor lo tha ma'i mdo dang de'i dgongs 'grel rnams
NK114(ye)001:14687: lta bu spyod phyogs ston pa rnams las dang po
NK114(ye)001:14688: pa'i chos yin zhes smra ba rnams ni rgyal ba
NK114(ye)001:14689: sras bcas kyi ring lugs las go logs su smra
NK114(ye)001:14690: bar zad de / dper na bu ram mur bzhin
NK114(ye)001:14691: pa'i gang zag la bu ram gyi ro 'chad kyang
NK114(ye)001:14693: mdang sum btsas pa'i byis pa la g.yos su byas
NK114(ye)001:14694: pa'i zas sna mang pos ston mo bshams kyang ci
NK114(ye)001:14696: dpe de bzhin du zab mo mngon du byas pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14697: 'phags pa la zab don 'chad kyang ci zhig dgos
NK114(ye)001:14698: la / mthong lam chos nyid ma mthong zhing sgom
NK114(ye)001:14699: lam ting 'dzin ma goms pa'i gang zag gis bsam
NK114(ye)001:14700: gyis mi khyab pa'i rnam par thar ba thob pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14701: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa rlabs po che lta
NK114(ye)001:14702: la / ci / theg chen lam gyi phyin drug mtshan nyid pa tsam yang slob mi nus te /
NK114(ye)001:14703: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pas /
NK114(ye)001:14704: lam gang du rang rgyud kyi gzung 'dzin gyi 'ching
NK114(ye)001:14705: ba gcod cing thabs kyi cha rnams la dngos por
NK114(ye)001:14706: zhen pa dag par bya ba'i phyir gtso bo mnyam
NK114(ye)001:14707: bzhag tu stong nyid sgom pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:14708: rjes thob tu snying rje'i sgo nas tshogs bsags pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14709: sgo rnam pa gnyis dang por rgyud la brten nas
NK114(ye)001:14710: rim gyis goms par byed pa tshogs lam chung 'bring
NK114(ye)001:14712: lam 'di'i rgyu ni sngon du tshogs bsags pa dang thos bsam la sogs pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:14713: 'bras bu ni sbyor ba'i lam mo //
NK114(ye)001:14714: rten la lus rten ni theg chen sems bskyed skye
NK114(ye)001:14715: ba'i rten te klu dang gzugs khams kyi lha la'ang
NK114(ye)001:14716: skye bar bshad pas 'dod khams pa dang mi kho
NK114(ye)001:14718: sems rten ni 'di la sgom byung mtshan nyid pa
NK114(ye)001:14719: yod par kun btus las bshad pa ltar na bsam
NK114(ye)001:14721: mtshan nyid ni bral ba'i khyad par la phan 'dogs
NK114(ye)001:14722: byed gang rnam byang dbang po'i ngo bor ma gyur
NK114(ye)001:14723: pa'i gnas skabs kyi lam bla med byang chub tu
NK114(ye)001:14724: bgrod pa'i go skabs phye shul lo //
NK114(ye)001:14725: 'di dag gi dus su yang thos bsam gtso che ba tsam las /
NK114(ye)001:14726: rnam bcas dang rnam med kyi ting 'dzin gnyis ka
NK114(ye)001:14727: mi bsgom pa ni min te byang phyogs so bdun
NK114(ye)001:14728: las dran nye sogs sde tshan gsum sgom par bshad
NK114(ye)001:14729: cing / lhag ma rnams kyang lam phyi ma rnams su bsgom pa'i tshul ni sngar bshad zin to //
NK114(ye)001:14730: de nas rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes mthong lam la myur du sbyor ba'i lam 'byung ste /
NK114(ye)001:14734: chos mchog bzhi yod pa'i chos mchog man chad bzhi
NK114(ye)001:14735: po'i gnas skabs thams cad du mnyam 1bzhag gi gnas
NK114(ye)001:14736: skabs na 'jig rten pa'i sgom byung gi stobs kyis
NK114(ye)001:14737: 3stong nyid la sems zhugs pa dang 4 /
NK114(ye)001:14738: rjes 2thob tu snying 5rje'i blo sngar tshogs lam gsum
NK114(ye)001:14739: du yang yang goms po'i stobs kyis ngang gis 'char
NK114(ye)001:14740: bar 'gyur ro // lam 'di'i rgyu ni tshogs lam mo //
NK114(ye)001:14741: 'bras bu ni theg chen mthong lam mo //
NK114(ye)001:14742: lus rten ni 'gro ba lnga gang rung ngo //
NK114(ye)001:14743: bsam pa'i rten ni bsam gtan sa drug gang rung ngo //
NK114(ye)001:14744: mtshan nyid ni theg chen tshogs lam gyi rjes su
NK114(ye)001:14745: skyes pa'i lam gang mos spyod kyis sas bsdus pa'o
NK114(ye)001:14746: // de dag la rim bzhin theg pa chen po'i snang ba thob pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:14748: chos kyi snang ba phyogs gcig pa la zhugs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:14749: de ma thag pa'i ting nge 'dzin zhes rnam pa bzhi las /
NK114(ye)001:14750: dang po ni yid kyi snang ba tsam du mthong
NK114(ye)001:14751: bas phyi don rnam par 'jig pa'i tshul la shes
NK114(ye)001:14752: pa'i snang ba cung zad gsal ba des don du
NK114(ye)001:14753: 'dzin pa'i gnyen po byed pas dro bar gyur ba
NK114(ye)001:14754: zhes bya'o // gnyis pa ni shes snang de nyid
NK114(ye)001:14755: sngon bas gsal bar gyur bas chos kyi snang ba
NK114(ye)001:14756: 'phel ba'i phyir brtson 'grus brtan par bya ba la
NK114(ye)001:14759: de kho na nyid kyi phyogs gcig la zhugs pas
NK114(ye)001:14760: phyi don gzung ba'i rnam pa mi snang bas shes
NK114(ye)001:14761: pa'i rnam pa 'byung ba de'i tshe sems tsam la
NK114(ye)001:14762: gnas pa'i phyir bzod pa zhes bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:14764: gang zhig 'dzin pa'i rnam pa gnyis med kyi shes
