NK114(ye)001:14765: pa de yang rnam par 'jig pa de'i tshe 'jig
NK114(ye)001:14766: rten pa'i sgom byung gi snang ba yongs su rdzogs
NK114(ye)001:14767: pas chos kyi mchog ces bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:14768: de yang drod rtse gnyis ni mthong lam skye ba la dus ma nges pa'i sbyor lam mo //
NK114(ye)001:14769: bzod pa ni tshe phyi ma la mthong lam skye bar nges pa'i sbyor lam mo //
NK114(ye)001:14770: chos mchog ni tshe de nyid la mthong lam skye nges pa'i sbyor lam yin te /
NK114(ye)001:14772: de tshe bar chad med pa yi //
NK114(ye)001:14773: ting nge 'dzin la myur du reg /
NK114(ye)001:14775: gnas skabs 'di ni byang chub sems dpa' sgyu ma
NK114(ye)001:14776: mkhan ltar phyin ci ma log pa'i phyir 'jig rten
NK114(ye)001:14777: las 'das pas ye shes la sbyor ba'i lam thabs
NK114(ye)001:14778: dang shes rab zung du 'brel bar 'jug cing mos
NK114(ye)001:14779: pa shin tu brtan pa tsam du zad pas /
NK114(ye)001:14780: bdag med gnyis kyi de kho na nyid mngon sum
NK114(ye)001:14781: du mi byed pas mos pas spyod pa'i sar bzhag
NK114(ye)001:14782: ste / lam 'di la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' ni so so skye bo yin mod kyi /
NK114(ye)001:14783: 'on kyang khyad par gyi chos lnga dang ldan par 'phags pa dkon mchog sprin las bshad de /
NK114(ye)001:14784: gnyen po'i khyad par la bzhi las /
NK114(ye)001:14786: zag bcas rnams la nad dang 'bras dang zug rngu
NK114(ye)001:14787: la sogs pa'i rnam par lta zhing sun 'byin pa'o
NK114(ye)001:14789: spang bya spong ba la rim gyis sbyor ba'i lam
NK114(ye)001:14790: dang spang bar brtsam pa de bar chad med lam
NK114(ye)001:14791: mtha' dag go // rten gyi gnyen po ni /
NK114(ye)001:14792: a d+ha ra zhes rten nam kun 'dzin pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:14793: spangs pa'i thob pa kun 'dzin zhing gnas 'gyur nyams su myong ba rnam grol lam mo //
NK114(ye)001:14794: thag bsring gi gnyen po ni /
NK114(ye)001:14795: khyad par gyi lam la sogs pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:14796: spangs pa'i khyad par ni sgrib pa'i sa bon dang mngon gyur nyams smad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:14797: byis pa'i phongs pa thams cad las yang dag par 'das pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:14798: rtogs pa'i khyad par ni bsgom byung gi cha nas bdag med gnyis rtogs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:14799: yon tan gyi khyad par ni ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK114(ye)001:14802: rdzu 'phrul la sogs pa du ma dang ldan pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:14803: tshogs lam las 'phags pa'i khyad par ni tshogs lam
NK114(ye)001:14804: chen po'i gnas skabs dang bsgom byung du 'dra yang
NK114(ye)001:14805: / mthong lam la nye ring dang /
NK114(ye)001:14806: ye shes la drod brtan mi brtan gyi khyad par yod par gsungs so //
NK114(ye)001:14807: de nas mthong lam thob pa nas bzung ste spyir
NK114(ye)001:14808: btang tsam du ni 'phags pa'i sa thams cad du
NK114(ye)001:14809: stong pa nyid dang snying rje gnyis po ni zung
NK114(ye)001:14810: du 'jug cing 'du 'bral med de stong nyid la
NK114(ye)001:14811: mnyam par bzhag pa na snying rje chen po'i rtsi
NK114(ye)001:14813: rjes thob sbyin sogs kyi spyod pa la bslab pa
NK114(ye)001:14814: na 'khor gsum mi rtog pa'i shes rab kyis zin
NK114(ye)001:14816: de yang gang gi tshe chos mchog gi rjes thog
NK114(ye)001:14817: de nyid du 'jig rten las 'das pa'i ye shes
NK114(ye)001:14818: spros pa thams cad dang bral ba'i de kho na
NK114(ye)001:14819: nyid yang dag par mthong ba la zhugs pas mthong
NK114(ye)001:14820: lam zhes bya ba ste sa bcu'i nang nas rab
NK114(ye)001:14821: tu dga' ba zhes bya ba dang po'i sar chos
NK114(ye)001:14822: rnams la chos kyi mig rdul med cing dri ma
NK114(ye)001:14823: dang bral ba rnam par dag pa thob pas chos
NK114(ye)001:14824: nyid kyi bdena pa mngon sum du mthong ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:14825: mthong lam 'di skye ba'i lus rten ni tshogs sbyor dang 'dra la /
NK114(ye)001:14826: sems rten ni bsam gtan bzhi pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:14827: rgyu ni theg chen tshogs sbyor gyi lam yin zhing /
NK114(ye)001:14828: de ma thag pa'i nye rgyu ni chos mchog go //
NK114(ye)001:14829: 'bras bu ni theg chen sgom lam mo //
NK114(ye)001:14830: mtshan nyid ni zag med sgom lam ma skyes gong
NK114(ye)001:14831: gi bdag med gnyis rtogs pa'i 'jig rten las 'das
NK114(ye)001:14833: de nas 'phags pa'i lam goms par byed pa'i sgom
NK114(ye)001:14834: pa'i lam la ma dag sa bdun du thabs shes
NK114(ye)001:14835: zung 'brel du yod kyang mnyam rjes kyi nyams len
NK114(ye)001:14836: so sor yod la de yang yul dang yul can
NK114(ye)001:14837: gnyis snang gi rtog pa thams cad lan tsh+wa chur
NK114(ye)001:14838: thim pa ltar rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes
NK114(ye)001:14839: gcig gi klong du dag ste blo'i spros pa thams
NK114(ye)001:14840: cad dang bral ba'i don dam mngon du gyur pas
NK114(ye)001:14842: 'phags pa'i mnyam bzhag gi ye shes de mi rtog
NK114(ye)001:14843: pa'i ye shes yin par smra ba tsam du 'dra
NK114(ye)001:14844: yang / rang lugs la bden par mi rtog pa
NK114(ye)001:14845: tsam ma yin par gnyis snang gi rtog pa thams
NK114(ye)001:14846: cad bral ba zhig tu 'dod do //
NK114(ye)001:14847: rjes thob zhes bya ba ni rnam pa dang bcas
NK114(ye)001:14848: pa'i ting nge 'dzin mngon du byed pa'i gnas skabs
NK114(ye)001:14849: la bya ste / dper na sdong po bkod pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:14850: nor bzang gi dge ba'i bshes gnyen rnams kyis rang
NK114(ye)001:14851: rang gi ting nge 'dzin gyi rnam par thar pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14852: mthu dag bstan pa bzhin du sbyin sogs rgyal sras
NK114(ye)001:14853: kyi spyod pa rlabs po che rnams kyang ting nge
NK114(ye)001:14854: 'dzin kho na'i stobs kyis sgrub par byed pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:14855: dag sa thob nas rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong
NK114(ye)001:14856: pa nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la brten nas zag
NK114(ye)001:14857: pa med pa'i dbyings su de bzhin gshegs pa'i yon
NK114(ye)001:14858: tan gyi rnam pa thams cad pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:14860: bsam gyis mi khyab pa rnams rim pa bzhin thob
NK114(ye)001:14861: pas mtshan med 'bad rtsol dang bral ba'i lam la
NK114(ye)001:14862: brten nas rang gzhan gyi don gnyis lhun gyis grub
NK114(ye)001:14863: pas mnyam rjes kyi nyams len dbyer med du 'gyur
NK114(ye)001:14864: ro // bsgom lam 'di dag skye ba'i lus kyi rten ni /
NK114(ye)001:14865: gling gsum gyi mi yin par ma nges te 'dod
NK114(ye)001:14866: gzugs kyi lha dang bcas pa la skye ba mang
NK114(ye)001:14868: bsam bzhin srid pa len pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:14869: zhes gzhan la yang skye bar rung ngo //
NK114(ye)001:14870: bsam pa'i rten ni bsam gtan bzhi pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:14871: rgyu ni theg chen gyi tshogs sbyor mthong lam gsum mo //
NK114(ye)001:14872: 'bras bu ni theg chen mi slob pa'i lam mo //
NK114(ye)001:14873: mtshan nyid ni theg chen mthong lam gyi rjes su
NK114(ye)001:14874: skyes pa'i ye shes gang theg chen slob pa'i lam
NK114(ye)001:14875: gyis bsdus pa'o // lam 'di dag gi dus kyi
NK114(ye)001:14876: sa bcu'i rnam bzhag sogs ni sngar bshad zin no
NK114(ye)001:14877: gyis bsdus pa'o // // sa lam de dang de'i
NK114(ye)001:14878: skabs kyi yon tan gyi rnam pa ji snyed cig
NK114(ye)001:14879: bshad pa de thams cad sngon med gsar du thob
NK114(ye)001:14880: gyis bsdus pa'o // // pa dang / khams kyi
NK114(ye)001:14881: sgrib pa bral ba'i stobs las gzhi na yod pa'i
NK114(ye)001:14882: yon tan mngon du snang bar bshad pa'i phyogs gnyis
NK114(ye)001:14883: su snang ba ni bde gshegs snying po drang nges
NK114(ye)001:14884: gnyis su 'dod pa'i phyogs las byung bar gsungs te
NK114(ye)001:14885: gyis bsdus pa'o // // pa dang / / de
NK114(ye)001:14886: yang slob dpon zla grags kyis bde gshegs snying po
NK114(ye)001:14887: drang don du gsungs pa de yang 'gro ba'i rgyud
NK114(ye)001:14888: la rtag brtan ther zug gi sku mtshan dpe gsal
NK114(ye)001:14889: rdzogs can yod par bshad pa de drang don yin
NK114(ye)001:14890: par gsungs kyi 'od gsal ba'i ye shes spros pa
NK114(ye)001:14891: dang bral ba'i stong nyid dang ro gcig pa tsam
NK114(ye)001:14892: zhig med par gsungs pa ma yin pas shing rta
NK114(ye)001:14893: chen po gnyis kyi bshad srol tshig tsam du tha
NK114(ye)001:14894: dad par snang yang don la dgongs pa'i chu bo
NK114(ye)001:14895: gcig tu 'dres pa'i tshul shes pa gal che bar
NK114(ye)001:14896: gyis bsdus pa'o // // pa dang / / gsungs te / zla ba sgron me'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:14897: 'jig rten khams ni stong dag tu //
NK114(ye)001:14898: ngas ni mdo sde gang bshad pa //
NK114(ye)001:14899: tshig 'bru tha dad don gcig ste //
NK114(ye)001:14900: thams cad brjod par nus ma yin //
NK114(ye)001:14902: chos thams cad 'byung ba med pa'i mdo las /
NK114(ye)001:14903: chos kyi rang bzhin yongs su mi shes pa //
NK114(ye)001:14904: tshig gi dam pas byang chub 'tshang mi rgya //
NK114(ye)001:14907: mang du thos pa zhes bya ba ni don la mkhas pa yin gyi /
NK114(ye)001:14908: tshig la mkhas pa ma yin no //
NK114(ye)001:14910: gsum pa 'bras bu thob tshul bshad pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:14911: de nas bsgom pa'i lam thams cad mthar phyin te
NK114(ye)001:14912: sa bcu pa'i rgyun gyi mtha' ma la lhan skyes
NK114(ye)001:14913: kyi sgrib pa'i bag chags shin tu phra ba spang
NK114(ye)001:14914: dka' ba 'joms pa la'ang thogs pa med pa'i rdo
NK114(ye)001:14915: rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyisa shes sgrib phra
NK114(ye)001:14916: ba de lhag ma med par bcom nas spangs rtogs
NK114(ye)001:14917: kyi yon tan mtha' dag mngon par rdzogs par byang
NK114(ye)001:14918: chub par 'gyur ba ni mi slob pa'i lam ste
NK114(ye)001:14919: / 'di'i lus kyi rten ni thun mong ba 'dzam bu'i gling pa'i rgyal rigs sam /
NK114(ye)001:14920: bram ze'i rigs las sangs rgya bar 'dod la /
NK114(ye)001:14921: thun mong ma yin pa ltar na 'og min du sangs rgya ba'i rten gang yin pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:14922: bsam pa'i rten bsam gtan bzhi pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:14923: rgyu ni slob pa'i lam bzhir tshogs gnyis mthar phyin pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:14924: 'bras bu ni mngon rtogs rgyan las /
NK114(ye)001:14925: gang dang yang dag ldan pas thub rnams rnam pa kun ldan sna tshogs 'di gsungs pa //
NK114(ye)001:14927: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba sogs phrin las phun
NK114(ye)001:14928: sum tshogs pas 'gro ba mtha' dag byang chub gsum
NK114(ye)001:14929: la 'god pa'o // mtshan nyid ni theg chen sgom
NK114(ye)001:14930: lam gyi rjes su 'byung ba'i ye shes gang zhig
NK114(ye)001:14931: spangs rtogs mthar phyin pa'i ngo bor gyur ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:14932: 'di'i skabs su mnyam par ma bzhag pa'i dus med
NK114(ye)001:14933: pa la sogs pa rgyal ba'i ma 'dres pa'i chos
NK114(ye)001:14934: bco brgyad dang / gzhan yang stobs bcu dang ni
NK114(ye)001:14935: mii 'jigsa pa bzhi la sogs pa'i yon tan mtha'
NK114(ye)001:14936: dag pa mngon du gyur te sangs rgyas pa yin
NK114(ye)001:14937: bco brgyad dang / no // 'di dag gi rnam grangs rgyas par bshad na gsum ste /
NK114(ye)001:14941: dang po rten sku la sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku ni gcig ste /
NK114(ye)001:14942: spangs rtogs kyi yon tan mthar phyin pa'i rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes chos kyi sku'o //
NK114(ye)001:14946: chos sku longs sku sprul sku'o //
NK114(ye)001:14952: dang po ngo bo nyid sku ni /
NK114(ye)001:14954: thub pa'i ngo bo nyid sku ni //
NK114(ye)001:14955: zag pa med pa'i chos gang dag /
NK114(ye)001:14956: thob gyur rnam kun rnam dag pa //
NK114(ye)001:14957: de dag rang bzhin mtshan nyid can //
NK114(ye)001:14958: zhes gsungs pas mthar thugs sangs rgyas kyi sa'i zag
NK114(ye)001:14959: pa med pa'i ye shes sde tshan nyi shu rtsa
NK114(ye)001:14960: gcig la sogs pa de dag gi rang bzhin nam
NK114(ye)001:14961: chos nyid de bzhin nyid dag pa gnyis dang ldan
NK114(ye)001:14963: gnyis pa ye shes chos sku ni mkhyen cha ye
NK114(ye)001:14964: shes kyi rnam grangs sangs rgyas nyid kyi thugs rgyud
NK114(ye)001:14965: na bzhugs pa'i rtogs pa'i chos rnams te /
NK114(ye)001:14967: byang chub phyogs 1mthun tshad med dang 2 //
NK114(ye)001:14968: rnam par 3thar dang mthar gyis ni //
NK114(ye)001:14970: zad par bcu 5yi bdag nyid dang //
NK114(ye)001:14971: zil gyis gnon pa'i skye mched ni //
NK114(ye)001:14972: rab tu dbye bas rnam brgyad dang 6 //
NK114(ye)001:14975: rnam pa thams cad dag bzhi dang 11 //
NK114(ye)001:14977: mi 'jigs pa ni bzhi dag dang 14 //
NK114(ye)001:14978: bsrung ba med pa rnam gsum dang 15 //
NK114(ye)001:14979: dran pa nyer bzhag rnam 16gsum dang //
NK114(ye)001:14980: bsnyel ba mi mang'i chos nyid dang 17 //
NK114(ye)001:14981: bag chags yang dag bcom pa dang 18 //
NK114(ye)001:14982: skye la thugs rje chen po dang 19 //
NK114(ye)001:14983: thub pa kho na'i ma 'dres chos //
NK114(ye)001:14984: bco brgyad 20bshad pa gang yin dang //
NK114(ye)001:14985: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen nyid dang 21 //
NK114(ye)001:14986: chos kyi sku zhes brjod pa yin //
NK114(ye)001:14987: zhes pa ltar sde tshan nyer gcig las /
NK114(ye)001:14988: dang po byang phyogs so bdun ni /
NK114(ye)001:14989: sngar lam gyi dus na tshogs lam nas bzung ste
NK114(ye)001:14990: byang phyogs rim gyis rdzogs pa rnams thob la ma
NK114(ye)001:14991: nyams pa'i tshul du thugs rgyud la bzhugs pa ste
NK114(ye)001:14992: snga ma dag dang rnam grangs 'dra'o //
NK114(ye)001:14993: tshad med pa bzhi ni mdo sde'i rgyan gyi lung don sngar bshad pa ltar ro //
NK114(ye)001:14994: rnam par thar pa brgyad ni /
NK114(ye)001:14995: sprul pa'i lam rnam thar gsum dang /
NK114(ye)001:14996: gzugs med kyi rnam thar bzhi /
NK114(ye)001:14997: 'gog pa'i rnam par thar pa dang brgyad do //
NK114(ye)001:14998: dang po sprul pa'i lam la gsum las /
NK114(ye)001:14999: nang gzugs yod par 'du shes pas phyi rol gyi
NK114(ye)001:15000: gzugs rnams la bltas nas sprul pa dang bsgyur ba
NK114(ye)001:15001: la sogs pa byed pa gzugs can gzugs la blta
NK114(ye)001:15002: ba'i rnam thar / nang gzugs med par 'du shes
NK114(ye)001:15003: pas de ltar byed pa gzugs med gzugs la blta
NK114(ye)001:15004: ba'i rnam thar / ba'i rnam thar / de ltar
NK114(ye)001:15005: sprul par goms kyang gzugs mdzes pa dang yid du
NK114(ye)001:15006: 'ong ba sogs sprul 'dod kyang mi mdzes pa dang
NK114(ye)001:15007: yid du mi 'ong ba sogs la sprul mi 'dod
NK114(ye)001:15008: pa lta bu byung na sprul pa mi rdzogs pas
NK114(ye)001:15009: de'i phyir gzugs mdzes pa dang mi mdzes pa gnyis
NK114(ye)001:15010: ka'ang phan tshun ltos pa tsam dang blos btags pa
NK114(ye)001:15011: tsam las don la med cing mnyam par blta ba
NK114(ye)001:15012: sdug pa'i rnam par thar pa dang gsum /
NK114(ye)001:15013: gnyis pa gzugs med kyi rnam par thar pa bzhi ni /
NK114(ye)001:15014: nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched kyi rnam par thar pa /
NK114(ye)001:15015: rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched kyi rnam par thar pa /
NK114(ye)001:15016: ci yang med pa'i skye mched kyi rnam par thar pa /
NK114(ye)001:15017: yod min med min skye mched kyi rnam par thar pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15018: gsum pa 'gog pa'i rnam par thar pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:15019: bsam gzugs brgyad ka thob pa'i 'phags pas tshogs bdun 'khor dang bcas pa bkag nas /
NK114(ye)001:15020: kun gzhi ma gtogs pa'i sems med pa'i 'du shes
NK114(ye)001:15021: dang tshor ba 'gog pa'i snyoms 'jug la snyoms par
NK114(ye)001:15022: zhugs pa'o // 'di la nyan thos rnams rnam par
NK114(ye)001:15023: shes pa tshogs drug las mi bzhed pas tshogs drug
NK114(ye)001:15024: bkag pa'i lus tsam ma gtogs sems kyi rgyun med
NK114(ye)001:15025: kyang phyis sems 'byung ba na sngar 'gags pa'i sems
NK114(ye)001:15026: kyi sa bon las skye bar 'dod pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15027: kha cig lus la sems kyi sa bon yod pa las skye bar 'dod pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15028: yang 'ga' zhig yid shes phra ba mi 'gag par
NK114(ye)001:15029: 'dod pa la sogs yod kyang theg pa chen po
NK114(ye)001:15030: rnams kun gzhi las skye bar 'dod do //
NK114(ye)001:15031: 'di la 'jug nus pa ni theg dman ltar na gnyis te /
NK114(ye)001:15032: dgra bcom pa gnyis ka'i cha las rnam grol dang /
NK114(ye)001:15033: phyir mi 'ong bsam gzugs brgyad thob pa zhig snyoms par 'jug nus so //
NK114(ye)001:15034: de las gzhan gyis mi nus te /
NK114(ye)001:15035: so skye thams cad ni dus dang rnam pa thams
NK114(ye)001:15036: cad du ngar 'dzin dang 'bral mi shes pas nyon
NK114(ye)001:15038: rgyun zhugs dang phyir 'ong la srid rtse'i sems thob
NK114(ye)001:15039: pa mi srid pas de shin tu phra ba'i 'gog
NK114(ye)001:15040: pa la snyoms par 'jug mi nus so //
NK114(ye)001:15041: dgra bcom shes rab kyi cha las rnam par grol
NK114(ye)001:15042: ba yang srid rtse'i sems mi thob pas snyoms par
NK114(ye)001:15044: des na 'gog par snyoms par 'jug pa la phyis goms pa'i skabs su bsam gzugs gang rung ngam /
NK114(ye)001:15045: 'dod pa'i sems las kyang 'gog snyoms la 'jug nus kyang dang po gsar du thob pa'i tshe na /
NK114(ye)001:15046: phra ba phra ba'i mjug thog tu //
NK114(ye)001:15047: zhes gsungs pas srid rtse'i sems de 'gyu ba phra bas /
NK114(ye)001:15048: de la brten pa'i 'du shes dang tshor ba'i 'gyu ba phra rags 'gog sla bas /
NK114(ye)001:15049: de la brten nas 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lam
NK114(ye)001:15050: gyis nyon mongs pa can gyi yid bkag nas 'gog
NK114(ye)001:15052: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms 'jug dgu ni /
NK114(ye)001:15056: rnam thar dang snyoms 'jug gi khyad par ni /
NK114(ye)001:15057: rang sa'i sgrib pa las rnam par thar pas na rnam par thar pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15058: lus kyi 'byung ba chen po rnams dang /
NK114(ye)001:15059: sems dang sems byung cha snyoms par byed pas na snyoms 'jug go //
NK114(ye)001:15060: mthar gyis gnas pa zhes pa ni snyoms 'jug dgu
NK114(ye)001:15061: po 'di dang po mngon du byed pa'i tshe mthar
NK114(ye)001:15062: chags su rim gyis rgyud la skye yi bsam gtan
NK114(ye)001:15063: dang po ma thob gong du gnyis pa thob pa
NK114(ye)001:15064: lta bu mi srid pa'i phyir ro //
NK114(ye)001:15065: zad par gyi skye mched bcu ni /
NK114(ye)001:15067: kha dog gi zad pa bzhi /
NK114(ye)001:15068: nam mkha' rnam shes gnyis dang bcu'o //
NK114(ye)001:15069: de dag gi sgom tshul ni /
NK114(ye)001:15070: dang po zad par rang rang gi dmigs rten la
NK114(ye)001:15071: brten nas sa sa zhes pa la sogs pa las
NK114(ye)001:15072: sems gzhan du mi yengs par rtse gcig tu yid
NK114(ye)001:15073: la byed cing / sems zin pa na sa la
NK114(ye)001:15074: sogs pa rgya chen por spros te bsgom pas 'grub
NK114(ye)001:15075: la byed cing / pa'o // dmigs rten ni sa
NK114(ye)001:15076: la chu'i steng na gnas pa'i sa'i zam pa la
NK114(ye)001:15077: la byed cing / pa'o // sogs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15078: chu la nam mkha' nas chu dri ma med pa
NK114(ye)001:15079: la byed cing / pa'o // sogs pa dang / 'bab pa / me la 'og tu bud shing /
NK114(ye)001:15081: steng du du ba dang bcas pa'i me /
NK114(ye)001:15082: rlung la skar khung la sogs pa nas rlung 'ong bas lus la reg pa /
NK114(ye)001:15083: kha dog bzhi po mthing ga la sogs pa'i tshon
NK114(ye)001:15084: gyis dkyil 'khor zlum po kha dog gzhan gyis mtha'
NK114(ye)001:15085: chod dang bcas bris pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15086: nam mkha' la rtsig pa la sogs pa'i bug pa'i nang gi nam mkha'/
NK114(ye)001:15087: rnam shes la rtsig khung sogs nas nyi zla dang
NK114(ye)001:15088: sgron me'i 'od shar ba'i 'od kyi thig le rnams
NK114(ye)001:15089: so // de ltar bsgoms pas grub pa na /
NK114(ye)001:15090: sa grub pas chu la sa bzhin du byed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15091: nam mkha' sar bsgyur ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:15092: lus sar bsgyur ba sogs dang /
NK114(ye)001:15093: chu grub pas chu'i char 'bebs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15094: sa la yang chu ltar bye'u 'dzul gyis 'gro ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:15095: lus chur bsgyur ba sogs byed /
NK114(ye)001:15096: me grub pas lus me dpung du bsgyur ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:15097: dngos po gzhan dang tha mal gyi me la sogs pa'ang sreg pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15098: rlung grub pas rlung ltar thogs pa med par 'gro ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:15099: lus rlung du bsgyur ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:15100: kha dog rnams grub pas lus dang snang ba thams
NK114(ye)001:15101: cad sngon po ser po dkar po dmar po ste
NK114(ye)001:15102: rtsa ba'i kha dog rang rang du bsgyur ba dang
NK114(ye)001:15103: / nam mkha' dang rnam shes grub pas lus dang dngos po mi snang ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:15104: lha'i mig gis yul snang bar byed pa la sogs pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15105: zil gnon gyi skye mched brgyad ni /
NK114(ye)001:15106: nang gzugs su 'du shes pas phyi rol gyi gzugs chen po rnams zil gyis mnan nas shes /
NK114(ye)001:15107: zil gyis mnan nas mthong ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:15108: nang gzugs su 'du shes pas phyi rol gyi gzugs
NK114(ye)001:15109: chung ngu thams cad zil gyis mnan sogs sngar ltar
NK114(ye)001:15110: / nang gzugs med par 'du shes pas phyi rol gyi gzugs chen po thams cad sogs sngar ltar /
NK114(ye)001:15111: nang gzugs med par 'du shes pas phyi rol gyi
NK114(ye)001:15112: gzugs chung ngu thams cad sogs sngar ltar te dbyibs
NK114(ye)001:15114: nang gzugs med par 'du shes pas phyi rol gyi kha dog sngon pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15117: dmar po thams cad zil gyis mnan nas shes /
NK114(ye)001:15118: zil gyis mnan nas mthong ba ste /
NK114(ye)001:15119: kha dog zil gyis gnon pa bzhi dang brgyad do //
NK114(ye)001:15120: de dag gi don rang gi lus la gzugs med pa'i 'du shes bzhag pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15121: yang rang gi lus la gzugs kyi 'du shes mi
NK114(ye)001:15122: bshig pa gnyis kyi sgo nas phyi rol gyi gzugs
NK114(ye)001:15123: mdzes pa dang / mi mdzes pa bzang po dang
NK114(ye)001:15124: ngan pa sogs la mtha' gcig tu mi zhen par
NK114(ye)001:15125: bltas nas de las che ba dang chung ba sogs
NK114(ye)001:15126: gzhan du bsgyur bas sprul bsgyur byed pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:15127: de yang zhi gnas kyi sgo nas zil gyis mnan nas shes /
NK114(ye)001:15128: lhag mthong gi sgo nas zil gyis mnan nas mthong ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:15129: nang gzugs yod pa dang med par 'du shes pa'i
NK114(ye)001:15130: don ni sprul pa byed pa'i tshe sprul pa po
NK114(ye)001:15131: rang nyid gzhan la snang ba dang mi snang ba'i
NK114(ye)001:15132: khyad par ro // yang na gzugs med par 'du
NK114(ye)001:15133: shes pa ni gzugs med kyi sems thob pa yin
NK114(ye)001:15134: na ni sla la min kyang gzugs med pa'i 'du
NK114(ye)001:15136: nang gzugs su 'du shes pa ni gzugs med pa
NK114(ye)001:15137: ma thob pa yin na sla la min kyang gzugs
NK114(ye)001:15138: med mngon du mi byed par gzugs kyi 'du shes
NK114(ye)001:15139: tsam bzhag pa'o // des na gzugs med kyi sems
NK114(ye)001:15140: thob pa yin na bsam gzugs gang rung la brten
NK114(ye)001:15141: tsam bzhag pa'o // pa dang / gzugs med pa
NK114(ye)001:15142: ma thob pa yin na bsam gtan bzhi pa la
NK114(ye)001:15143: brten nas zil gnon rnams sgom par bzhed do //
NK114(ye)001:15145: nyan thos nyon mongs med pa'i lta //
NK114(ye)001:15146: mi yi nyon mongs yongs spong nyid //
NK114(ye)001:15147: grong sogs su de'i nyon mong rnams //
NK114(ye)001:15148: rgyun gcod rgyal ba'i nyon mongs med //
NK114(ye)001:15150: nyan thos rnams kyis grong sogs su 'gro ba'i tshe
NK114(ye)001:15151: rang la brten nas gzhan chags sdang sogs skye bar
NK114(ye)001:15152: 'gyur mi 'gyur mngon shes kyis brtags nas skye bar
NK114(ye)001:15154: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis ni de ltar dgongs tshe
NK114(ye)001:15155: der ched du gtad nas phebs te chos ston pa
NK114(ye)001:15156: dang rdzu 'phrul sogs kyis btul nas de'i rgyud la
NK114(ye)001:15157: phyin chad nyon mongs pa rgyun gcod pa'i thabs mdzad
NK114(ye)001:15158: pa'o // smon gnas mkhyen pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:15159: nyan thos kyi yid kyis 'dod pa'i don gang shes
NK114(ye)001:15160: par 'dod kyang dang po don 'di dang 'di shes
NK114(ye)001:15161: par bya'o snyam nas rab matha'i bsam gtan la snyoms
NK114(ye)001:15162: par zhugs nas brtags pas shes so //
NK114(ye)001:15164: sangs rgyas smon gnas mkhyen pa ni //
NK114(ye)001:15165: lhun gyis grub dang chags spang dang //
NK114(ye)001:15166: thogs pa med dang rtag gnas dang //
NK114(ye)001:15167: dri ba kun lan 'debs par bzhed //
NK114(ye)001:15168: ces gsungs pa ltar 'bad rtsol la ma ltos par lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15169: nyon sgrib spangs pas ma chags pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15170: shes sgrib spangs pas ma thogs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15171: rgyun chad med pas rtag tu gnas pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15172: khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad kyis dus gcig
NK114(ye)001:15173: tu skad mi 'dra ba du ma'i sgo nas so
NK114(ye)001:15174: sor dris kyang rang rang gi skad dang bsam pa
NK114(ye)001:15175: bzhin lan manya ma du 'debs pa dang khyad chos
NK114(ye)001:15176: lnga ldan no // mngon shes lnga dang so so
NK114(ye)001:15177: yang dag par rig pa bzhi ni sngar bshad pa
NK114(ye)001:15178: lnga ldan no // dang 'dra'o // rnam pa thams cad dag pa bzhi ni /
NK114(ye)001:15181: gtong ba la mnga' brnyes pa rten lus dag pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15182: gzugs dang sgra dang dri dang ro dang reg bya
NK114(ye)001:15183: sogs sgrub pa dang bsgyur ba la mnga' brnyes pas
NK114(ye)001:15184: longs spyod dag pa dmigs pa dag pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15185: ting nge 'dzin la mnga' brnyes pas thugs dag pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15186: shes rab la mnga' brnyes pas ye shes yongs su dag pa zhes bya'o //
NK114(ye)001:15187: dbang bcu stobs bcu mi 'jigs pa bzhi rnams sngar dang 'dra'o //
NK114(ye)001:15188: bsrung ba med pa rnam pa gsum ni /
NK114(ye)001:15189: sku gsung thugs kyi mdzad spyod thams cad ngang gis
NK114(ye)001:15190: dge bas spyod lam thams cad la gzhan gyis shes
NK114(ye)001:15191: kyis dogs nas bcabs dgos pa'i 'khrul ba'i mi mnga'
NK114(ye)001:15192: ba'o // dran pa nyer bzhag rnam gsum ni /
NK114(ye)001:15193: sangs rgyas rnams chos 'chad pa'i tshe kha cig gus
NK114(ye)001:15194: pa dang bcas zhe sa dang bcas rna ba blags
NK114(ye)001:15195: te chos nyan par byed kyang de la rjes su
NK114(ye)001:15196: chags pa med / yang kha cig ma gus pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:15198: rna ba gtad de chos nyan par mi byed kyang /
NK114(ye)001:15199: de la thugs khro ba med pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15200: yang kha cig gus pas nyan par byed /
NK114(ye)001:15201: kha cig gus pas nyan par mi byed kyang de la chags sdang mi mnga' ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:15202: bsnyel ba mi mnga' ba'i chos nyid ni /
NK114(ye)001:15203: sngon bskal ba dpag tu med pa'i gong du byung
NK114(ye)001:15204: ba rnams kyang thugs kyis mi brjed par da ltar
NK114(ye)001:15206: bag chags yang dag par bcom pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:15207: nyan rang dgra bcom pa rnams ni nyon mongs pa
NK114(ye)001:15208: thams cad spangs kyang nyon mongs pa'i bag chags ma
NK114(ye)001:15209: bcom pa'i dbang gis lus ngag gi 'khrul pa cung
NK114(ye)001:15210: zad mnga' la / sangs rgyas rnams kyis bag chags
NK114(ye)001:15211: thams cad zad par bcom pas nyes spyod 'khrul pa'i
NK114(ye)001:15213: skye la thugs rje chen po ni /
NK114(ye)001:15214: sangs rgyas rnams ni thugs rje chem pos sems can
NK114(ye)001:15215: thams cad la dus dang rnam pa thams cad du
NK114(ye)001:15218: su ni ngan song gi sdug bsngal las drangs nas
NK114(ye)001:15219: mtho ris dang thar pa'i lam dang bde ba la
NK114(ye)001:15220: 'god / su ni nyon mongs pa'i 'ching ba thams
NK114(ye)001:15221: cad las dgrol bar bya snyam pa sogs nyin lan
NK114(ye)001:15222: gsum mtshan lan gsum du dgongs pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15223: ma 'dres pa bco brgyad ni sngar bshad pa dang 'dra'o //
NK114(ye)001:15224: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen nyid dang //
NK114(ye)001:15225: zhes pa'i dang sgras bsdus pa gnyis dang mkhyen pa gsum ste /
NK114(ye)001:15226: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid dang /
NK114(ye)001:15227: lam thams cad mkhyen pa nyid dang /
NK114(ye)001:15230: shes bya'i chos thams cad kyi rnam pa tha dad pa ma 'dres par mkhyen pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15232: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems dpa'i lam gsum ga don dam par skye ba med pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15233: kun rdzob tu rgyu ngo bo 'bras bu dang bcas pa mkhyen pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15235: gzhi phung po khams dang skye mched thams cad gang zag gi bdag gis stong par shes pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15236: de ltar mkhyen pa'i ye shes sde tshan nyi shu rtsa gcig po de dag las stobs bcu /
NK114(ye)001:15241: bag chags yang dag bcom pa /
NK114(ye)001:15242: thugs rje chen po rnams sangs rgyas kho na'i yon tan yin la /
NK114(ye)001:15243: dbang bcu so so yang dag par rig pa bzhi rnams byang sems rnams dang thun mong dang /
NK114(ye)001:15244: byang phyogs snyoms 'jug rnam thar sogs nyan rang byang
NK114(ye)001:15245: sems sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thun mong ba'i yon
NK114(ye)001:15246: tan no // de dag nyan rang dang byang sems
NK114(ye)001:15247: kyi thugs rgyud na byang phyogs sogs mtshan nyid pa
NK114(ye)001:15248: yod pa tsam la ltos nas chos dbang btsan du
NK114(ye)001:15249: byas te thun mong ba'i yon tan zhes bzhag gis
NK114(ye)001:15250: tan no // / sangs rgyas kyi thugs rgyud la
NK114(ye)001:15251: bzhugs pa'i khyad par can la ltos nas rgyud dbang
NK114(ye)001:15252: btsan du byas na ni sde tshan nyer gcig po
NK114(ye)001:15253: thams cad kyang sangs rgyas kyi thun mong ma yin
NK114(ye)001:15255: 'di la zil gnon dang rnam thar la sogs pa dang po sgom tshul dang /
NK114(ye)001:15256: mthar yang ting nge 'dzin la brten nas mngon du
NK114(ye)001:15257: byed tshul sogs bshad pa rnams ni spyi'i dbang du
NK114(ye)001:15258: byas kyi sangs rgyas kyis ni sprul pa la sogs
NK114(ye)001:15259: de dag bzhed pa tsam gyis lhun gyis grub par
NK114(ye)001:15260: rtsol byung gi dge ba cung zad kyang mi mnga'
NK114(ye)001:15261: la / 'gog pa'i snyoms 'jug gsungs pa'ang 'gog pa
NK114(ye)001:15262: la snyoms par 'jug nus pa tsam la dgongs kyi
NK114(ye)001:15263: la / / dngos su rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'gog
NK114(ye)001:15264: pa la snyoms par 'jug pa mi srid ces gsungs
NK114(ye)001:15265: la / / so // de lta bu'i yon tan
NK114(ye)001:15266: gyi rnam grangs bsam gyis mi khyab pa rnams sangs
NK114(ye)001:15267: rgyas kyi thugs rgyud kyi rtogs pa'i chos yin pas
NK114(ye)001:15268: rtogs pa ye shes kyi chos sku'o //
NK114(ye)001:15270: mtshan ni sum cu rtsa gnyis dang //
NK114(ye)001:15271: dpe byad brgyad cu'i bdag nyid ni //
NK114(ye)001:15272: theg chen nye bar longs spyod phyir //
NK114(ye)001:15273: thub pa'i longs spyod rdzogs skur bzhed //
NK114(ye)001:15275: 'og min gyi gnas su byang sems sa bcu pa
NK114(ye)001:15276: rnams la snang ba'i sangs rgyas kyi gzugs sku mtshan
NK114(ye)001:15277: dang dpe byad kyi bdag nyid can de ni dus
NK114(ye)001:15278: rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lor chos theg pa chen
NK114(ye)001:15279: po kho na la longs spyod pa'i phyir na longs
NK114(ye)001:15280: spyod rdzogs sku'o // mtshan bzang po so gnyis la bcu tshan gsum dang gnyis las /
NK114(ye)001:15282: phyag zhabs 'khor lo'i mtshan dang rus sbal zhabs //
NK114(ye)001:15283: phyag dang zhabs sor d+r+wa bas 'brel ba dang //
NK114(ye)001:15284: phyag ni zhabs bcas 'jam zhing gzhon sha chags //
NK114(ye)001:15285: 'di yi sku ni bdun dag mtho ba dang //
NK114(ye)001:15286: sor mo ring dang rting yangs sku che drang //
NK114(ye)001:15287: zhabs 'bur mi mngon spu ni gyen du phyogs //
NK114(ye)001:15288: zhes pas rus sbal zhabs ni /
NK114(ye)001:15289: rus sbal gyi lto ba ltar zhabs kyi mthil thams
NK114(ye)001:15290: cad mnyam par sa la 'jog pas zhabs mthil gyi
NK114(ye)001:15295: ltag pa ste bdun por gshongs bu med par shas gang bas mtho ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:15297: zhabs long bu'i 'bur mi mngon pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15298: spu gyen du phyogs pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:15299: ba spu thams cad g.yas su 'khyil ba'i rtse mo gyen du phyogs pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15302: byin pa e na ya'i 'dra phyag ring mdzes //
NK114(ye)001:15303: 'doms kyi lba ba sbubs su nub pa'i mchog /
NK114(ye)001:15304: pags pa gser mdog pags pa srab pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:15305: spu ni re re nas g.yas legs 'khrungs dang //
NK114(ye)001:15306: zhal mdzod spus brgyan ro stod seng ge 'dra //
NK114(ye)001:15307: 'di yi dpung pa'i mgo zlum thal gong rgyas //
NK114(ye)001:15309: byin pa e na ya'i 'dra zhes pas e na ya ni /
NK114(ye)001:15312: bse kha sgo zhes pa yin zhes gzhung 'ga' zhig las bshad /
NK114(ye)001:15313: gang yin kyang zhabs kyi byin pa byin gyis phra zhing snyoms pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15315: gser dri ma med pa ltar dag cing gsal ba'i
NK114(ye)001:15316: don yin gyi ser po yin pa'i don min zhes
NK114(ye)001:15317: gsungs so // ro stod seng ge 'dra ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:15320: phrag pa g.yas g.yon gyi bar te de na sgrog rus kyi gshongs med par shas gang ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:15322: 'di la ro mi zhim pa'ang ro mchog snang //
NK114(ye)001:15323: sku ni nya gro ta ltar chu zheng gab //
NK114(ye)001:15324: gtsug tor dbur ldan ljags ring mdzes pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:15325: tshangs dbyangs 'gram pa seng ge 'dra dang tshems //
NK114(ye)001:15326: shin tu dkar dang tshad mnyam thag bzang dang //
NK114(ye)001:15327: grangs ni bzhi bcu tham pa tshang ba dang //
NK114(ye)001:15330: rta chas kyi nas rul ba gsol kyang tshems par
NK114(ye)001:15331: du slebs nas lha'i zhal zas ro brgya ba ltar
NK114(ye)001:15332: bsod pa'o // nya gro ta ltar chu zheng gab pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:15333: shing gi rgyal po nya gro ta ltar chur dbu'i spyi bo nas zhabs mthil gyi bar dang /
NK114(ye)001:15334: zheng du phyag sor gyi rtse nas phyag sor gyi
NK114(ye)001:15335: rtse'i bar 'dom gang tshad shin tu mnyam zhing ring
NK114(ye)001:15336: thung med pa'o // ljags ring zhing mdzes pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:15337: rdzu 'phrul gyi rnam rol ma mdzad kyang ljags brkyang
NK114(ye)001:15338: pas zhal gyi dkyil 'khor sgra mtshams kyi bar khebs
NK114(ye)001:15339: pa'o // rdzu 'phrul gyi sprul pa'i dbang du byas na ni stong gsum la sogs pa 'gebs pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15341: gsung tshangs pa'i skad ltar snyan zhing yid du 'ong ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:15342: drung nas nyan yang gsung che bar mi mngon la /
NK114(ye)001:15343: rgyang ring po nas nyan yang chung bar mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:15345: 'gram pa 'khyil che zhing zlum por 'dug pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15347: tshems thams cad che chung dang ring thung med pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15349: tshems kyi bar na bar stong med pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15351: spyan ni mthong mthing spyan rdzi ba mchog gi //
NK114(ye)001:15352: 'dra ba 'di dag sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan //
NK114(ye)001:15354: spyan rin po che mthon ka chen po ltar mthing gar 'dug pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15355: spyan gyi rdzi ma ba mchog gi rdzi ma ltar ma 'dzings shing dri ma med pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15356: dpe byad brgyad cu ni bcu tshan brgyad de /
NK114(ye)001:15358: thub pa'i sen mo zangs mdog dang //
NK114(ye)001:15359: mdog snum mtho dang sor mo rnams //
NK114(ye)001:15360: zlum rgyas byin gyis phra ba dang //
NK114(ye)001:15361: rtsa mi mngon dang mdud pa med //
NK114(ye)001:15362: long bu mi mngon zhabs mnyam dang //
NK114(ye)001:15363: zhes pas sor mo rnams byin gyis phra ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:15364: phyag sor rnams tshigs mdud med par rtsa ba nas rim gyis phra ba'o //
NK114(ye)001:15367: long bu mi mngon zhes pa'i skabs mtshan bzang du gtogs pa ni long bu chen po yin la /
NK114(ye)001:15368: dpe byad du gtogs pa ni long bu chung ngu yin zhes gsungs so //
NK114(ye)001:15370: zhabs g.yas g.yon gnyis ring thung med par mnyam pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15372: seng ge glang chen bya dang ni //
NK114(ye)001:15373: khyu mchog stabs gshegs g.yas phyogs dang //
NK114(ye)001:15374: mdzes gshegs drang dang 'khril bag chags //
NK114(ye)001:15376: zhes pas mi zil gyis gnon pa la mkhas pas seng ge ltar gshegs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15377: klu zil gyis gnon pa la mkhas pas glang chen ltar gshegs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15378: nam mkha' la 'gro ba bya'i rgyal po'i stabs su gshegs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15379: tshogs kyi sna 'dren pa la mkhas pas ba glang
NK114(ye)001:15380: dang glang po khyu mchog ltar gshegs pa dang stabs
NK114(ye)001:15381: gshegs pa bzhi / g.yas phyogs ni /
NK114(ye)001:15382: zhal bskor nas gshegs pa'i tshe dus nam yang g.yas phyogs su bskor nas gshegs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15383: mdzes gshegs dang drang por gshegs pa yan gshegs stabs so //
NK114(ye)001:15387: che chung dang sbom phra rim par 'tshams pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15389: gtsang dang 'jam dang dag pa'i sku //
NK114(ye)001:15390: mtshan ni yongs su rdzogs pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:15391: sku yi kho lag yangs shing bzang //
NK114(ye)001:15392: gom snyoms pa dang spyan gnyis ni //
NK114(ye)001:15393: dag dang gzhon sha can nyid dang //
NK114(ye)001:15394: sku zhum med dang rgyas pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:15395: zhes pas sku dri ma med pas gtsang ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:15397: sku gnag bag med par dag pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15398: sku'i khyon che bas kho lag yangs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15399: gshegs pa'i tshe gom pa che chung med par gom pa snyoms pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15400: spyan dri ma med pas dag pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15401: sku sha mi skem pas zhum pa med pa sogs so //
NK114(ye)001:15403: shin tu grim pa'i sku nyid dang //
NK114(ye)001:15404: yan lag shin tu rnam 'byes dang //
NK114(ye)001:15405: gzigs pa sgrib med dag pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:15406: dku zlum skabs phyin ma rnyongs dang //
NK114(ye)001:15407: phyang nge ba dang lte ba ni //
NK114(ye)001:15408: zab dang g.yas phyogs 'khyil pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:15409: kun nas lta na sdug pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:15410: zhes pas yan lag 'byes pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:15411: yan lag gi skabs phyed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15413: spyan rab rib la sogs med pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15415: lte ba'i thad kyi rked pa zlum por yod pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15416: rked pa phra sbom gyi mtshams legs par 'dod pas skabs phyin pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15417: rked pa mi ring bas sku ma rnyongs pa rnams so //
NK114(ye)001:15419: phyal phyang nge zhes lto ba'i ngos khod mi mnyam pa med pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15420: kun nas lta na sdug pa ni sku thams cad do //
NK114(ye)001:15422: kun spyod gtsang dang sku la ni //
NK114(ye)001:15423: sme ba gnag bag med pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:15424: phyag ni shing bal ltar 'jam dang //
NK114(ye)001:15425: phyag ris mdangs yod zab ring dang //
NK114(ye)001:15426: zhal ni ha cang mi ring dang //
NK114(ye)001:15427: mchu ni bim+pa ltar dmar dang //
NK114(ye)001:15428: ljags mnyen pa dang srab pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:15429: zhes pas phyag ris mdangs yod pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15431: phyag gi ri mo ring ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:15432: mchu bim+pa zhes pas shing tog bim+pa ltar dmar ba sogs so //
NK114(ye)001:15434: dmar dang 'brug gi sgra nyid dang //
NK114(ye)001:15435: gsung mnyen 'jam dang mche ba zlum //
NK114(ye)001:15436: rno dang dkar dang mnyam pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:15437: byin gyis phra dang shangs mtho dang //
NK114(ye)001:15438: mchog tu dag pa dag dang ni //
NK114(ye)001:15439: zhes pas ljags dmar ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:15440: mche ba zlum pa nas byin gyis phra ba'i bar dang /
NK114(ye)001:15442: shangs snabs lud med par mchog tu dag pa sogs so //
NK114(ye)001:15444: spyan yangs pa dang rdzi ma stug /
NK114(ye)001:15446: smin tshugs ring dang 'jam pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:15447: snum dang spu ni mnyam pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:15448: phyag ring rgyas dang snyan mnyam dang //
NK114(ye)001:15449: nyams pa rnam par spangs pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:15451: de yang mig gi steng na skye ba'i spu ni smin ma yin la /
NK114(ye)001:15452: mig sgor skye ba ni rdzi ma'o //
NK114(ye)001:15454: pad+ma 'dab ma dang ze'u 'brur bcas kha tshang bar
NK114(ye)001:15455: yod pa ltar dkar nag gi mtshams phyed cing mdzes
NK114(ye)001:15457: snyan g.yas g.yon mnyam pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15458: nyams pa rnam par spangs pas dri ma med pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15460: dpral ba legs par 'byes pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:15461: dbyes che ba dang dbu rgyas dang //
NK114(ye)001:15462: dbu skra bung ba ltar gnag dang //
NK114(ye)001:15464: mi gshor dri zhim skyes bu yi //
NK114(ye)001:15465: yid ni 'phrog par byed pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:15466: dpal gyi be'u dang bkra shis ni //
NK114(ye)001:15467: g.yung drung 'khyil bas mtshan pa ste //
NK114(ye)001:15468: sangs rgyas dpe byad bzang por bzhed //
NK114(ye)001:15469: ces pas dpral ba legs par 'byes pa ni dpral ba'i skra mtshams legs par 'dod pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15470: dbyes che ba ni dbral ba'i khyon che ba dang /
NK114(ye)001:15471: dbu skra ma 'dzings pa ni dbu skra nyag ma
NK114(ye)001:15472: phan tshun ma 'dres shing nag nog tu gyur ba
NK114(ye)001:15473: med pa dang / mi gshor ba ni dbu skra gyen du ma bardzisa pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15474: dbu skra la dri zhim po bro bas skyes bu'i yid 'phrog par byed pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15475: thugs ka na dpal gyi be'u dang phyag dang zhabs
NK114(ye)001:15476: kyi mthil na ri mo gru bzhi pa bkra shis
NK114(ye)001:15477: pa dang / g.yung drung 'khyil ba la sogs pas brgyan pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15478: mtshan dang dpe byad 'di dag ni sangs rgyas kyi gzugs sku'i yon tan yin la /
NK114(ye)001:15479: sangs rgyas kyi gzugs kyi sku dngos ni longs spyod rdzogs sku yin pas /
NK114(ye)001:15480: 'di dag longs sku la bzhag pa yin la /
NK114(ye)001:15481: sprul sku la'ang mchog gi sprul sku la mtshan dpe 'di dag yod mod kyang /
NK114(ye)001:15482: sprul sku gzhan don gdul byar snang ba tsam yin pas mtshan dpe dngos ma bzhag go //
NK114(ye)001:15483: mtshan bzang rnams las dbu gtsug tor dang /
NK114(ye)001:15484: mdzod spu gnyis ma gtogs gzhan rnams 'khor los sgyur ba la'ang cha 'dra tsam yod kyang /
NK114(ye)001:15485: sangs rgyas kyi mtshan bzang gsal ba dang mdzes pa sogs khyad par che'o //
NK114(ye)001:15486: mtshan dang dpe byad kyi sgra don ni /
NK114(ye)001:15487: skyes bu chen po mtshon par byed pas na mtshan dang /
NK114(ye)001:15488: nang gi yon tan gyi dpe lta bu phyi rol na snang bas na dpe byad do //
NK114(ye)001:15490: gang gis srid pa ji srid du //
NK114(ye)001:15491: 'gro la phan pa sna tshogs dag /
NK114(ye)001:15492: mnyam du mdzad pa'i sku de ni //
NK114(ye)001:15493: thub pa'i sprul sku rgyun mi 'chad //
NK114(ye)001:15495: srid pa 'khor ba'i 'jig rten ma stongs kyi bar
NK114(ye)001:15496: du phan bde bsam gyis mi khyab par mdzad pa'i
NK114(ye)001:15497: sprul sku grangs med pa dus mnyam du snang zhing
NK114(ye)001:15498: de yang 'khor ba ma stongs bar du rgyun mi
NK114(ye)001:15499: 'chad pa'o // gnyis pa brten pa ye shes ni /
NK114(ye)001:15500: le'u bcu gsum par 'chad pa ltar me long lta bu la sogs pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15501: de dag kyang bsdu na ji lta ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes gnyis dang /
NK114(ye)001:15502: de yang bsdu na rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes gcig go //
NK114(ye)001:15503: gsum pa mdzad pa phrin las ni /
NK114(ye)001:15504: gdul bya rnams lam gyi rten la 'god pa dang /
NK114(ye)001:15507: dang po lam gyi rten la 'god pa ni /
NK114(ye)001:15508: ngan song gi sems can rnams thugs rje'i 'od zer
NK114(ye)001:15509: la sogs pas rgyud sbyangs nas mngon mtho lha mi'i
NK114(ye)001:15510: lus rten khyad par can yang dag pa'i chos kyi
NK114(ye)001:15511: snod du rung ba la 'god pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15513: rigs can gsum gyi gdul bya rang rang gi skal
NK114(ye)001:15514: ba dang mthun par theg pa gsum gyi lam la
NK114(ye)001:15516: lam de dag gi 'bras bu mya ngan las 'das pa la 'god pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15517: phrin las de dag kyang bya ba yul la yod pa'i phrin las dang /
NK114(ye)001:15518: byed po yul can la yod pa'i phrin las so //
NK114(ye)001:15520: gdul bya rnams mtho ris thob pa dang lam rgyud
NK114(ye)001:15521: la skye ba sogs gdul bya'i rgyud kyis bsdus la
NK114(ye)001:15523: de ltar mdzad pa'i thabs sam nus pa ste sangs rgyas nyid kyi thugs rgyud kyis bsdus pa'o //
NK114(ye)001:15524: bzhi pa phyin drug gi don bsdu ba ni /
NK114(ye)001:15525: 'di ltar pha rol tu phyin pa drug ston pa'i theg pa chen po'i sde snod rnams dang /
NK114(ye)001:15526: de dag gi brjod bya'i don rnams ni dus gsum
NK114(ye)001:15527: du byon bzhugs 'byon 'gyur gyi rgyal ba kun slob
NK114(ye)001:15528: pa lam gyi gnas skabs na thos bsam byed pa'i
NK114(ye)001:15529: gzhung dang nyams su len pa'i lam ste /
NK114(ye)001:15530: de yang sngar bshad pa ltar mthar 'dzin dang bral
NK114(ye)001:15531: ba'i lta basa lam bsgrub tshul la ma rmongs shing
NK114(ye)001:15532: / phyin drug gi spyod pa'ang rang don yid byed dang /
NK114(ye)001:15533: 'khor gsum du zhen pa'i dri ma shin tu rnam par dag pa ste /
NK114(ye)001:15534: de lta bu'i tshogs gnyis po de mthar phyin nas
NK114(ye)001:15535: nges pa lnga ldan 'og min gyi zhing du 'gro
NK114(ye)001:15536: ba ste der mngon par sangs rgyas te sku gnyis
NK114(ye)001:15538: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba las /
NK114(ye)001:15539: smon 'jug gi bslab bya bstan pa'i tshoms te le'u
NK114(ye)001:15540: dgu pa'i 'grel ba ste de yan gyis rgyu mtshan
NK114(ye)001:15541: nyid kyi theg pa la yongs su grags pa'i rgya
NK114(ye)001:15543: zab mo lta ba'i grub pa'i mtha' legs par gtan la phab pa'o ////
NK114(ye)001:15544: dpal ldan bla ma'i sku tshe brtan pa dang //
NK114(ye)001:15545: mkha' mnyam yongs la bde skyid 'byung ba dang //
NK114(ye)001:15546: bdag gzhan ma lus tshogs rdzogs sgrib byang nas //
NK114(ye)001:15547: myur du sangs rgyas go 'phang thob par shog /
